NK116(le)001:2: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi dka' gnad rdo
NK116(le)001:3: rje'i rgya mdud 'grol byed legs bshad gser gyi thur
NK116(le)001:4: ma bzhugs so // 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa
NK116(le)001:5: dang gnyis su med pa dpal ldan bla ma'i zhabs
NK116(le)001:7: sa gsum 'gro ba'i la thod gser mngal can //
NK116(le)001:8: 'dren byed stong 'bar 'khor lo'i lag can sogs //
NK116(le)001:9: dregs pa'i yal 'dab lnga zung snying zlum ste //
NK116(le)001:10: gtsug gis mchod 'os rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas basngagasa //
NK116(le)001:11: srid pa'i sdug mun 'thug po'i tshang tshing nags //
NK116(le)001:12: mthar byed gtan bde'i 'dun ma'i khang bzang du //
NK116(le)001:13: bde blag dgod la dpa' ba lung rtogs chos //
NK116(le)001:14: kho na'i mthur rig gus pas dad phyag brtsegs //
NK116(le)001:15: rgyal ba'i ring lugs 'jog po'i gtsug gi rgyan //
NK116(le)001:16: dam pa'i bya ba rnam gsum rgyal mtshan rtser //
NK116(le)001:17: btegs nas lus can 'dod dgu'i re skong ba //
NK116(le)001:18: gtad rab bdun sogs dge 'dun yongs la basngagasa //
NK116(le)001:19: mi 'gyur bde chen 'dus ma byas dbyings su //
NK116(le)001:20: bla med ye shes bdud rtsi'i mchog brnyes pas //
NK116(le)001:21: dus gsum rgyal kun spyi dpal 'jigs med gling //
NK116(le)001:22: byang chub bar du khyod zhabs 'bral med bsnyen //
NK116(le)001:23: gang gis legs bshad yon tan rin chen mdzod //
NK116(le)001:24: rdo rje'i tshig 'grel bdag 'os ma lags te //
NK116(le)001:25: 'on kyang bla ma'i drin las rtogs pa'i don //
NK116(le)001:26: rgyas min bri la mkha' 'gros bka' gnang mdzod //
NK116(le)001:27: de yang gang bshad par bya ba la /
NK116(le)001:30: mjug gi don te gsum mo //
NK116(le)001:46: pra mo da prish+ti dga' ba'i char /
NK116(le)001:49: de yang mngon mtho dang nges legs kyi yon tan
NK116(le)001:50: mtha' dag gi 'byung gnas rina po che'i mdzod mchog
NK116(le)001:51: gya nom phul du byung ba dam pa'i chos kyi
NK116(le)001:52: mdzod chen po lus can rnams gtan gyi dga' ba
NK116(le)001:53: dang bde ba'i go sar dbugs dbyung zhing nyes tshogs
NK116(le)001:54: kyi dbal me 'joms byed la gru chara lta bu'i
NK116(le)001:58: rab la mtshan bstan 'bring la dbye //
NK116(le)001:60: zhes ming smos pas dbang po rab kyi gzhung don
NK116(le)001:61: khong du chud par 'gyur ba'i dgos pa dang bstan
NK116(le)001:63: lung rtogs kyi chos rnams rgya gar nas byung ba'i
NK116(le)001:64: phyir 'dir yang rten 'brel ched du drangs shing yul
NK116(le)001:65: gyi nges tshig ni rgya gar nag gnyis las chos
NK116(le)001:66: dang spyod pas cig shos las ldog pa'i cha nas
NK116(le)001:67: dkar por smros pa lo ts+wa bas brjod bde ba'i
NK116(le)001:68: phyir gar ces pa'am gzhan du 'dod rgyal du yang
NK116(le)001:71: gus pa dang yon tan rjes dran gyi basngagasa pa gnyis las /
NK116(le)001:73: dkon mchog ces bya ba la sogs te /
NK116(le)001:74: sgo gsum gus pa chen pos phyag 'atshala lo //
NK116(le)001:75: gang la na 'jig rten gyi khams 'dir dkona pa'i mchoga sangs rgyas chos dge 'dun gsuma la'o //
NK116(le)001:76: gang gis na 'jigs med gling pas so //
NK116(le)001:77: ces phyir na 'gro ba ma lus pa nyes tshogs las skyobs pa'i ched du'o //
NK116(le)001:78: dus nam du na deng nas bzungs ste byang chub snying po'i bar du'o //
NK116(le)001:80: sngon byung gi gtam rgyud dang sbyar te rin chen
NK116(le)001:81: rnam gsum zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te
NK116(le)001:82: / dkona mchoga rina chena rnama pa gsum gyi gragas
NK116(le)001:83: pa'i spring yiga gisa ces pa gzugs can rgyan du
NK116(le)001:84: / sbyar la / gtam dpe seng ga la'i rgyal
NK116(le)001:85: po'i lha lcam mu tiga 'khri shinga rab tu dag'a
NK116(le)001:86: ba byasa pa'i dus de nasa /
NK116(le)001:87: chos brgyad bduda kyi bu mo'i bzhin ras kun+da'a tshal
NK116(le)001:88: ltar mdzes pa de'i skala ngana bgyida ces phra rab
NK116(le)001:89: gyur pa la mngona par phyogas pa ni sangsa rgyas
NK116(le)001:90: kyi mathu'o // de yang dpag bsam khri shing las //
NK116(le)001:91: nor chen zhes bya'i tshong pa ni //
NK116(le)001:92: wa ra na sir sngon byung gyur //
NK116(le)001:93: de yi khyim thabs bsod nams can //
NK116(le)001:94: rin chen ldan zhes bya bar gyur //
NK116(le)001:95: bdag po lnga la ma nyid gyur tshe //
NK116(le)001:96: bud med de yi mchod rten rtser //
NK116(le)001:97: do shal chen po gus ldan pas //
NK116(le)001:98: mchod pa byas nas phul bar gyur //
NK116(le)001:99: bsod nams rnam smin des de nyid //
NK116(le)001:100: sing+ga la yi bdag po yi //
NK116(le)001:101: bu mo mu tig 'khri shing gyur //
NK116(le)001:102: de nyid skye ba gzhan la ni //
NK116(le)001:103: phyug pas rgyags shing rmongs gyur nas //
NK116(le)001:104: mchod pa smod cing sgrin gyur pa //
NK116(le)001:105: de yis yun ring 'bangs mor gyur //
NK116(le)001:106: dge dang mi dge'i las gang gang //
NK116(le)001:107: skye ba'i zhing la skye bos btab //
NK116(le)001:108: ces pa ltar sh+aakya'i khyim du 'bangs mo ro hi
NK116(le)001:109: ta zhes bya ba tshe 'phos nas sing+ga la'i rgyal
NK116(le)001:110: po'i bu mo mu tig 'khri shing zhes bya bar
NK116(le)001:111: gyur // de'i bsod nams kyi mthus mnyan yod kyi
NK116(le)001:112: tshong pa rnams rgya mtshor song nas sing+ga lar slebs
NK116(le)001:113: gyur // / mtshan mo'i thun mthar ngal bso'i dbugs 'byin thob pa'i tshe /
NK116(le)001:114: sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa'i chos tshigs su bcad pa dag glur blangs pas /
NK116(le)001:115: bu mos thos nas tshong pa rnams la de'i rgyu dris so //
NK116(le)001:116: de dag gis ni sangs rgyas kyi gsung zhes smras so //
NK116(le)001:117: des sangs rgyas kyi mtshan thos pa tsam gyis rma
NK116(le)001:118: bya la 'brug gi sgra grags pa ltar gyur cing
NK116(le)001:119: sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin mi shes nas slar dris
NK116(le)001:120: pa na / tshong pa de dag gis bsod nams
NK116(le)001:121: kyi rang bzhin bcom ldan 'das de'i spyod pa'i lugs
NK116(le)001:122: smras pas de de'i rkyen gyis sngon bas dga' ba'i
NK116(le)001:123: dga' ba chen po thob nas bcom ldan 'das la
NK116(le)001:124: gsol ba'i spring yig phul te /
NK116(le)001:125: thams cad mkhyen pa bcom ldan 'das kyis mkhyen bzhin du spring yig bklags pa'i don /
NK116(le)001:126: kye ma bsod nams tshong zong dag gis rnyed par gyur pa khyod ni dran pa nyid /
NK116(le)001:127: rgud dang gdung ba dang ni sred pa 'joms pa'i sman bzang ci yang yin /
NK116(le)001:128: bcom ldan las byung gtam gyis nyer bskrun yang dag rig pa myong ba'i sa /
NK116(le)001:129: bcom ldan 'di de bdag gi bdud rtsi yang dag bgo skal chen por gyur pa yin /
NK116(le)001:130: ces pa nyid du ni gzigs /
NK116(le)001:131: ri mo mkhan gyis bri bar mi nus pa'i rang
NK116(le)001:132: gi sku gzugs ras la bkod pa de la spring
NK116(le)001:133: pas tshong pa de dag gis slar bstan te /
NK116(le)001:134: mu tig 'khri shing gis de mthong ba'i mod la
NK116(le)001:135: de las byung ba'i bsam gtan dgongs pa gcig pa
NK116(le)001:136: lta bu nyamasasu myongs nas skyabs su 'gro ba gsum
NK116(le)001:137: dang / bslab pa'i gnas lnga dang /
NK116(le)001:139: 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad la sogs pa'i bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin shes nas /
NK116(le)001:140: rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu la mngon tu spyod do //
NK116(le)001:141: sku de la thub pa 'od zer mar grags shing
NK116(le)001:142: sku gzugs kun gyi thog ma yin zhes bshad do
NK116(le)001:145: khengs pa bskyungs shing rgyu mtshan gyis 'thad par gdams
NK116(le)001:146: pa blo mchog ces bya ba la sogs pas ston
NK116(le)001:147: ste / blo'i mchoga mnga' ba thub chen rnams kyis gnas dus ston pa chos 'khor te /
NK116(le)001:148: phun sum tshogs pa lngas bstan pa'i bka' dang /
NK116(le)001:149: chos nyid kyi bden pa mthong lhag pa'i lhas gnang ba byin /
NK116(le)001:150: rig pa'i gnas lnga rdzogs pa ste /
NK116(le)001:151: rgyu gsum tshogs pa'i gang zag rnams kyis ching chen
NK116(le)001:152: po lnga dang dgos 'grel yan lag bzhis gtan la
NK116(le)001:153: phab pa'i bstan bcos don dang ldan pa /
NK116(le)001:155: sgrub pa lhur len pa ste nang pa'i tshul gsum gyi yona tan dang ldan pas /
NK116(le)001:156: daga byed gter zhes rgya mtsho ltar don cha shas
NK116(le)001:157: tsam ma yin par phyogs thams cad gciga tu 'ubs
NK116(le)001:158: chub par bstan pas zab cing barlingas gzhig na /
NK116(le)001:159: kho bo ni spyi brtol te dpral ko 'thug po
NK116(le)001:160: khre la mi shes par dper na gcong rong gi
NK116(le)001:161: 'bab chu rlabas phreng g.yo ba gang gisa ca co
NK116(le)001:162: sgroga pa lta bu 'di tshig dang don gyi mdzesa
NK116(le)001:163: pa ha cang mi ngoma yang /
NK116(le)001:169: rtsod pa lhur len te phyi rol ba'i ngan pa
NK116(le)001:170: drug gis lta ba ltar ma yin par dama pa'i
NK116(le)001:171: chosa kyi dgongs don brjod pa la brtena pa'i slad
NK116(le)001:172: du na mnyan para 'osa zhes gdams pa ni /
NK116(le)001:174: chos rnams thams cad bka' dang bstan bcos gnyis //
NK116(le)001:175: legs par gsungs dang de yi dgongs 'grel bas //
NK116(le)001:176: de yi dbang gis sh+aakya'i bstan pa 'di //
NK116(le)001:177: 'jig rten khams 'dir yun ring gnas par 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:179: bstan bcos 'di nyid bshad ma thag pa ltar na dgos rgyu chung ngam zhe na /
NK116(le)001:180: dam pa'i yon tan pha mtha' klas kyang mi spyom pa ni /
NK116(le)001:182: sngon chad ma byung ba yang 'dir brjod med //
NK116(le)001:183: sdeb sbyor mkhas pa'ang bdag la yod min te //
NK116(le)001:184: de phyir gzhan don bsam pa'ang bdag la med //
NK116(le)001:185: rang gi yid la goms phyir ngas 'di brtsoms //
NK116(le)001:187: shing rta chen po klu sgrub kyis //
NK116(le)001:188: ji ltar bde gshegs sku gzugs shing las kyang //
NK116(le)001:189: bgyis pa ci 'dra'ang rung ste mkhas pa mchod //
NK116(le)001:190: de bzhin bdag gi snyan dngags 'di ngan yang //
NK116(le)001:191: dam chos brjod la brten slad smad mi bgyid //
NK116(le)001:193: tshul mthun pas de ltar blta bar mi rigs so //
NK116(le)001:194: gnyis pa yul gnas min gyi tshul la skyo bas
NK116(le)001:195: mtshang 'don pa thog ma zhes bya ba la sogs
NK116(le)001:196: pa gsungs te / 'di ltar thog ma meda pa'i
NK116(le)001:197: dus nasa skye rga na 'chi'i rimas nad shin tu
NK116(le)001:198: drag po'i sdug bsngal kyisa btab nas ma rungs par
NK116(le)001:199: pa gsungs te / byas kyang / gnyan por 'gyur
NK116(le)001:200: ba'i smana chena bduda rtsi'i ro bcud dang ldan pa
NK116(le)001:201: dama pa'i chosa lag tu mchisa pa thos bsam bsgom
NK116(le)001:202: pas nyams su mi bltar bar sponga bar byed pa'i
NK116(le)001:203: skye bo mya ngam thang du 'khyams pa rnams la
NK116(le)001:206: gang zhig skye nad rga shi bsil ba'i badud rtsi de //
NK116(le)001:207: thob bar mi byed mi spyod 'dzin par mi byed pa //
NK116(le)001:208: de dag nyes mang gti mug 'thib sosa bslad pa ste //
NK116(le)001:209: yun ring nad kyis thebs pas sman chen mi brten bzhin //
NK116(le)001:212: 'gro ba kun gyi mig gcig dri ma med pa gang //
NK116(le)001:213: de ni sa rnams gsum po'i spyi mthun sgron ma ste //
NK116(le)001:214: bstan pa de legs rnyed nas gang zhig 'dor ba de //
NK116(le)001:215: gti mug shin tu rmad byung dag gis gces par zad //
NK116(le)001:217: de ltar na'ang las su rung ba'i gdul bya'i don ched du nges par 'chad dgos pa ni /
NK116(le)001:219: dge slong dag gang zag gnyis po 'dis bsod nams
NK116(le)001:220: mang po bskyed de sdig pa'i rtsa ba 'byin cing
NK116(le)001:221: bdud dang g.yul 'gyed par byed bdud kyi rgyal mtshan
NK116(le)001:222: snyol bar byed / chos kyi rgyal mtshan bsgreng bar byed /
NK116(le)001:223: de bzhin gshegs pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar byed do //
NK116(le)001:225: gang gus par byas te chos 'chad pa dang /
NK116(le)001:226: gang 'di na gus par byas te chos nyan pa'o //
NK116(le)001:227: de bas na khyod kyis gus pas chos bshad par
NK116(le)001:228: bya zhing bla ma rnams la gus par byas te
NK116(le)001:231: tshe rabs gang du chos kyi mdzod 'dzin /
NK116(le)001:232: de bzhin gshegs pa sras dang bcas pas dgongs par 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:234: sangs rgyas las chos thos shing myur du de'i gong 'phang thob pa la sogs pa'o //
NK116(le)001:235: nyan pas ni sems kyi sgrib pa sbyong /
NK116(le)001:237: rtag tu dam pa'i chos dang mi 'bral /
NK116(le)001:239: ngan 'gro dang log par mi ltung /
NK116(le)001:240: dkar phyogs kyi lhas bsrungs shing nad dang gnod pa nyung /
NK116(le)001:241: shes rab kyi mig rnyed pas myur du 'khor ba
NK116(le)001:242: las 'das nas thams cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang rnyed
NK116(le)001:243: par gdon mi za bas na /
NK116(le)001:245: thos pas chos rnams shes par byed //
NK116(le)001:246: thos pas sdig las ldog par byed //
NK116(le)001:247: thos pas don ma yin pa spongs //
NK116(le)001:248: thos pas mya ngan 'das pa thob //
NK116(le)001:249: gsungs pa sogs kyis shes so //
NK116(le)001:250: da ni rtsa ba'i sa bcad gnyis pa gzhung gi
NK116(le)001:251: don dkyus la 'jug pa la spyir bstan bcos rnams
NK116(le)001:252: rtsis mgo rnam pa lnga'i chings kyis bcings ba dang
NK116(le)001:253: / bstan bshad bsdu gsum gyis gtan la phebs pa'am chu babs su bkral kyang rung ste /
NK116(le)001:259: sgrung 'grel rnam pa drug gi ston pa'i skabs ma nges pas na /
NK116(le)001:260: 'dir ngo bo tshig 'grel la bstan bya'i don rnams
NK116(le)001:261: nyams su myong bar gtso bor byas pa yin no
NK116(le)001:262: // de la re zhig dang po dal 'byor gyi tshoms rnam par bzhag pa la lnga /
NK116(le)001:263: mi lus rnam par dbye ba /
NK116(le)001:264: 'gal zla mi khoms pa brgyad bshad pa /
NK116(le)001:265: dal 'byor gyi rang bzhin ngos bzung nas /
NK116(le)001:266: rnyed dka' ba'i rgyu mtshan bshad pa /
NK116(le)001:269: ring nas zhes pa la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:270: zhes 'das pa'i dus ringa po nas nyon mongs pa
NK116(le)001:271: mdza' bshesa su bltas pa 'khora ba'i tshang tshing stug
NK116(le)001:272: po'i 'broga dgona du mgo dang yana lag bacada pa
NK116(le)001:273: sogs kyis gdung bar byas shinga /
NK116(le)001:274: phyin chad kyang gdon mi za bar gdunga bar 'gyur
NK116(le)001:275: ba da lta bltar mi mngon pa'i lkoga tu gyur
NK116(le)001:276: pa ma rig pa'i ling thog gis blo mig ldongs
NK116(le)001:277: ba rnams ni / da dung yang zag bcas mtho
NK116(le)001:278: risa kyi bde ba la sred cing thob na ci
NK116(le)001:279: ma rung snyam ste zhen pa dag ches rmongas pa
NK116(le)001:280: ba rnams ni / ni / ma ti tsi tra sa /
NK116(le)001:281: dga' bar bgyid pa'i yul rnams dang /
NK116(le)001:282: rgyag par bgyid pa'i lang tsho dang //
NK116(le)001:283: bdag nyid rang dgar spyod pa de //
NK116(le)001:284: kun tu don med bgyid pa'i sgo //
NK116(le)001:287: gang zhig 'khor ba'i 'khor lo rtag tu 'khor gyur ba //
NK116(le)001:288: nang du zhugs nas bsti ba tsam la bder sems pa /
NK116(le)001:289: de ni nges par rim gyis dbang med brgya phrag tu //
NK116(le)001:290: 'gro ba mnyam dang mi mnyams kun tu 'khyams par 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:291: zhes mnyam pa ni lha dang mi /
NK116(le)001:292: mi mnyam pa ni ngan 'gror shes par bya'o //
NK116(le)001:293: de la nang gses su dge sdig mi spyod pas mi lus tsam po dang /
NK116(le)001:294: 'dres mar spyod pas khyad par zhes grags so //
NK116(le)001:295: gnyis pa dge ba'i phyogs su khoms su mi ster
NK116(le)001:296: ba'i 'gal zla ston la bstan bshad bsdu gsum gyi
NK116(le)001:297: dang po ni / bsam brlag zhes bya ba sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:298: phyin ci log gi bsam pas gtan bde'i 'bras bzang
NK116(le)001:299: brlag par byed pa de ni skye ba 'di nasa
NK116(le)001:300: mu mtha' med pa'i bar du yanga 'og nas 'og
NK116(le)001:305: dabnga po ma tshanga ba dang /
NK116(le)001:307: sangas rgyas 'byung ba meda pa'i mun skal dag tu 'khyamas par 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:308: gnyis pa so sor bshad pa la brgyad de /
NK116(le)001:310: thang cig ces bya ba la sogs pas gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:311: dus thang ciga tsam du'ang bde bar ngal gso ba'i
NK116(le)001:312: go skabas zad pas batsala ba ma yin te lcagsa
NK116(le)001:313: bsregas kyi sa gzhira sna tshogs mtshona gyi chada pa
NK116(le)001:314: rtsub mosa yanga dang yanga du sroga gi dbang gi
NK116(le)001:315: dbang po 'phrog par byas kyang las kyi dbang gis
NK116(le)001:316: 'chi bar mi nusa pa'i dmyal ba pa gang zhig
NK116(le)001:317: da dung khonga khro'i lasa ngan gyi snyi la thogsa
NK116(le)001:318: nas gtan du brgyud mar mnar ro //
NK116(le)001:319: gnyis pa ni rnag khrag zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:320: mi gtsang ba rnam khrag phyi sa sogas kyi gza'
NK116(le)001:321: ba'ang mi rnyeda pa'i yi dwagas rnams 'phonga zhing dbul
NK116(le)001:322: basa nyamsa thaga pa smros ci dgosa te chu klunga
NK116(le)001:323: dang ljon para sred cing bltas pa'i moda la bskam
NK116(le)001:324: pa dang zas skom cung zad khong du song bar
NK116(le)001:325: srid tshe nang khrola mes yis 'tshiga pa'i sduga bsngal
NK116(le)001:326: sogs zad mi shesa pa myong zhing las kyi sgrib
NK116(le)001:327: pa'i mthu che chung gis byas pas tshe tshad la
NK116(le)001:329: gsum pa dud 'gro zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:330: dud 'gro rnams ni phana tshun gciga la gciga gis
NK116(le)001:331: baza'a zhing rngona pa'i dama la bazhaga pa ste bslu
NK116(le)001:332: nges pa'i mtshon cha sogs shin tu bsam sbyor rtsub
NK116(le)001:334: rang dbang du bkola phyir 'dula ba'i las thabs 'dzina
NK116(le)001:335: pasa nyamsa thag pa'i gnas su skye ba thoba na
NK116(le)001:336: ci byar yoda de med do //
NK116(le)001:337: bzhi pa 'tsho ba'i zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:338: 'tsho ba'i lasa matha'a ste tshe shina tu ringa posa
NK116(le)001:339: bsring na'ang 'khor ba'i gnas la skyo ba'i go skabsa
NK116(le)001:340: cung zad kyang mi dbye ba'i gzugas meda dang /
NK116(le)001:341: thosa bsam gyi snod du ma rung bas rten 'aggas
NK116(le)001:342: pa ste chos kyi 'du shesa meda pa'i lha dag
NK116(le)001:343: nam zhig 'chi khara bab tshe phyin ci loga tu
NK116(le)001:345: shes pas 'gyur ba'i sdug bsngal gyi gdung ba las khomas ldana gyi lus mina no //
NK116(le)001:346: lnga pa rkang ba zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:347: gang zhig rkanga pa gnyisa pa'i khyogsa te 'degs byed
NK116(le)001:348: la raba tu brten nasa rnam pa mi ltar 'dug
NK116(le)001:349: na yanga de yi 'du shesa sam kun slong bsoda
NK116(le)001:350: nams ma yin pa nyon mongs kho nas 'ching bas
NK116(le)001:351: dam la bzhag cing mi dge ba'i las la yid
NK116(le)001:352: gzhungs pa ste mkhas pa'i kla kla rnams ni dge
NK116(le)001:353: sdig gi blang dor shina tu 'chol pa'i gnas mi
NK116(le)001:354: bsrun pa'i nagsa na rnam par 'khyamsa so //
NK116(le)001:355: drug pa dbang po'i zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:356: dbang po'i dam baca'a nyamsa pa'i ste ngag yid lkugsa
NK116(le)001:357: pa rnams rim par brda' mi 'phrod cing don mi
NK116(le)001:358: 'jal pa rnams 'aphagas pa'i deda dpona dge ba'i bshes
NK116(le)001:359: gnyen dag dang phrad par gyur kyang /
NK116(le)001:360: brag cha'i cho ga'i gzunga ba'i zhes ci rtsam bshad
NK116(le)001:361: kyang ca co tsam las brtags dpyad dang lan ldon
NK116(le)001:362: med pa bzhina / rgyu 'bras kyi brda'a mi 'phroda
NK116(le)001:363: pa'i skye bo gang zhig 'jigs rung 'khor ba'i 'broga
NK116(le)001:364: dgona chen pora ya nga bas gadung ba'o //
NK116(le)001:365: bdun pa skye ba'i zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:366: skye ba la sogs pa'i sdug bsngal gyi rgya mtsho
NK116(le)001:367: chen po bzhi brgala bar brtsams kyang son pa'i gru
NK116(le)001:368: bo che lta bu'i lus rten rnam riga gi ba
NK116(le)001:369: dan g.yo ba can 'di thoba nasa /
NK116(le)001:371: des gsungs par 'gyur ba'i chos dang de la brten
NK116(le)001:372: pa'i dge 'dun la mnyesa para mi bgyida cinga loga
NK116(le)001:373: par lta ba ngan par 'dzina pa de ni badud
NK116(le)001:374: kyisa gtsesa pa ste dbang du gyur ba'i mi khom
NK116(le)001:375: pa'o // brgyad pa thub pa zhes la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:376: thub pa rnams kyis spangsa pa'i bskala pa yi ni sangs rgyas ma byon pa'i dus te /
NK116(le)001:377: kun tu gconga ronga sdig pa'i mun naga 'thib po'i
NK116(le)001:378: 'obs su rnam par ltung ba de nyid slar bde
NK116(le)001:379: ba'i go skabs 'thob tu re nas ldang bar brtson
NK116(le)001:380: kyang lam mina bsdig lta rgyud la ldan pas de
NK116(le)001:381: dag nyam nga ba'i gnas ngan song du ltung ba
NK116(le)001:382: las slar yang 'og nas 'oga tu ste ngan song
NK116(le)001:383: nas ngan song 'oga tu 'gro bas khoms par mi
NK116(le)001:384: 'gyur ro // zhar byung rtsa bas dngos su ma
NK116(le)001:385: gsungs par shugs kyis rtogs par bya ba thun mong
NK116(le)001:386: ma yin pa kun mkhyen chen pos bzhed pa'i mi
NK116(le)001:387: khoms brgyad tshan gnyis kyi dang po ni /
NK116(le)001:389: dug lnga 'khrug dang blun rmongs bdud kyis zin //
NK116(le)001:390: le lo can dang las ngan mtsho chen brdol //
NK116(le)001:391: gzhan dbang 'jigs skyobs chos ltar bcos pa ste //
NK116(le)001:392: 'phral byung rkyen gyi mi khoms rnams pa brgyad //
NK116(le)001:393: thar lam chos kyi snod min phyin ci log /
NK116(le)001:394: ces phral byung rkyen gyi mi khoms pa brgyad dang //
NK116(le)001:395: 'ching ba dam ldan kun spyod shin tu ngan //
NK116(le)001:396: 'khor bar mi skyo dad pa cung zad med //
NK116(le)001:397: mi dge sdig spyod chos la sems pa med //
NK116(le)001:398: sdom dang dam tshig nyams pa zhes bya ba //
NK116(le)001:399: ris chad blo yi mi khoms rnam pa brgyad //
NK116(le)001:400: chos las ring 'gyur thar lam sgron me nub //
NK116(le)001:401: ces ris chad blo yi mi khoms brgyad de bcu
NK116(le)001:402: drug dang snga ma'i brgyad po bsdoms pas nyi shu
NK116(le)001:404: gsum pa skabs kyis don bsdu ba ni /
NK116(le)001:405: sdig sdug zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:406: de ltar bstan zin pa bzhin du sdiga pa'i mngon
NK116(le)001:407: rtogs sdug bsngal sna tshogs kyi 'thora rlung 'khrugas pa'i
NK116(le)001:408: gansa rigas rnams su ngal zhing dub ste skrag pa
NK116(le)001:409: dang bacasa pa'i bsoda nams ma yin pa'i las rnyog
NK116(le)001:410: pa can gang zhig chosa la phrag pa dog ces
NK116(le)001:411: 'dun pa bral ba'i mi khoms pa brgyad po'i tshul
NK116(le)001:412: la bsam gzhig legs par btang nas ranga gira bgyid
NK116(le)001:413: pa'i da la rten thob bzhin dona yoda par mdzoda
NK116(le)001:415: gsum pa dal 'byor gyi rang bzhin ngos bzung ba
NK116(le)001:416: la ngo bo dal ba dang khyad par gyi chos
NK116(le)001:417: 'byor pa bshad pa gnyis las dang po ni /
NK116(le)001:418: gong gi gnas min nyi shu rtsa bzhi'i sgo gsum
NK116(le)001:419: la dbye na bcos te brel ba las ldog pas
NK116(le)001:420: na dal ba zhes bya ste /
NK116(le)001:421: yab sras mjal ba'i mdo las //
NK116(le)001:422: mi khoms brgyad po thams cad rab spangs shing //
NK116(le)001:423: dal ba phun tshogs rnyed dka' thob gyur nas //
NK116(le)001:424: bde gshegs bstan la dad pa rnyed gyur ba'i //
NK116(le)001:425: mkhas pa rnams kyis rig pa'i rnal 'byor spyod //
NK116(le)001:428: dga' byed khyed kyi legs par mthong ba dang /
NK116(le)001:429: legs par thos pa gang yin pa de ni dal
NK116(le)001:430: ba bsam pa las byung ba ji lta ba bzhin
NK116(le)001:431: tu mi rnams kyang bde ba dang legs pa'i chos
NK116(le)001:432: gang yin pa de dag thams cad 'grub par blta'o
NK116(le)001:434: gnyis pa khyad chos la gnyis te /
NK116(le)001:436: yul dbus zhes bya la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:437: dam pa'i chos gang du dar ba'i yul dbus sa
NK116(le)001:438: gzhi gatsanga mara skyes pa'i myu gu rdol te dabnga
NK116(le)001:439: po dang yan lag la skyon med de lus kyi
NK116(le)001:440: kho lag raba tu rdzogsa shing dad pa'i gansa rgyal
NK116(le)001:441: pa'i bstan pa rin po che la dad de lasa
NK116(le)001:442: matha'i dge ba'i me toga sdig to ste bdud kyi
NK116(le)001:443: ba mos ma bcoma pa'i mira gyur pa ni dapaga
NK116(le)001:444: bsam ljon pa las chos shina tu dkona no zhes
NK116(le)001:445: basngagasa pa'o // de yang ji skad du /
NK116(le)001:446: mi nyid dbus skyes dbang po tshang //
NK116(le)001:447: las mtha' ma log gnas la dad //
NK116(le)001:450: rgyal ba zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:451: bdud kyi sde rnams rab tu pham par byed pa'i
NK116(le)001:452: rgyal ba u dum wa ra las kyang dkon pa
NK116(le)001:453: cha mthun bsod nams shing rtas bsus nas 'jiga rten
NK116(le)001:454: 'dir 'byon te / dam pa'i chosa kyi 'khor lo
NK116(le)001:455: me tog gi kha phye bzhin rgya cher gyes te
NK116(le)001:456: bstan pa mdo sngags kyi pad tshala nub pa med
NK116(le)001:457: para dar ba'i gansa la yang dag par bzhugs shing
NK116(le)001:458: 'dir 'byon te / / skyes bu dama pa'i skyabs
NK116(le)001:459: 'og gi grib bsila la bsten pa ni snga ma
NK116(le)001:460: snga ma de basa phyi ma phyi ma nyung ngo
NK116(le)001:462: sangs rgyas byon dang des chos gsungs /
NK116(le)001:463: bstan pa gnas dang de la zhugs /
NK116(le)001:464: gzhan phyir snying nas brtse ba'o //
NK116(le)001:466: bzhi pa rnyed par dka' ba'i tshul la /
NK116(le)001:469: grangs te rgyu mtshan gsum gyis gtan la phab pa'i dang po ni /
NK116(le)001:470: gang phyir zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:471: de yang don gang gi phyir 'byor bcu thob ste
NK116(le)001:472: rang nyida kyi ngos nas 'byor ba'i chos lnga po
NK116(le)001:473: dpag bsam gyi ljon pa ltar dkon pa dang de
NK116(le)001:474: las kyang gazhana dabnga rkyen gyi 'byora ba lnga bo'i
NK116(le)001:475: chos ni u du ma wa ra'i me tog ltar
NK116(le)001:477: rang gzhan gnyis ka'i yona tan gyi khyad chos 'byor
NK116(le)001:478: ba rnam pa bcu pos dala pa brgyad kyi rten
NK116(le)001:479: la 'khyud pa 'di lta bu slar mi rnyed de
NK116(le)001:481: shes byed rtog pa brjod pa'i mdo las /
NK116(le)001:482: mtsho chen po ma dros pa 'das pa'i byang phyogs na zhes sogs kyi gsal lo //
NK116(le)001:484: ci'i phyir zhes rkang pa dang pos bstan te /
NK116(le)001:485: ci'i phyir daka'a na gong du ngo bo'i bstan par ma zad /
NK116(le)001:486: ru sbala long ba'i mgrina pa dang manya'a shinga gi
NK116(le)001:487: bu ga 'phrad pa lta bu'i dpesa kyang dka' ba
NK116(le)001:489: dge slong dag 'jig rten rgya mtsho chen po gcig
NK116(le)001:490: tu gyur ba'i zhes rgya cher gsungs pa ni khrid
NK116(le)001:491: yig rnams su 'dug pas shes sla'o //
NK116(le)001:493: grangs ni zhes gong gi rkang lhag gsum gyis bstan te /
NK116(le)001:494: grangsa kyi bka' tshul ni mi dang dud 'gro rim
NK116(le)001:495: bzhina nyin matshana gyi skar mas phye ba'i de rnyeda
NK116(le)001:496: yi dwagsa dang / dmyal ba rnams la rima par sbyar bas shes par yang 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:497: lnga pa don bsdu ba ni /
NK116(le)001:498: de phyir zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:499: rgyu mtshan de'i phyir na dala pa'i gru bo che
NK116(le)001:500: lus rten 'di bdag gir 'dzina pa'i dusa su 'khor
NK116(le)001:501: ba sdug bsngal gyi chu gtera chen po'i pha mathara
NK116(le)001:503: chosa lam mgrona posa zhes dper byas te ji ltar
NK116(le)001:504: mgron po'i ched du gnyera zhing nor bu len pa'i
NK116(le)001:505: go skabsa batsala kyang ma 'bad na rlabs sam chu
NK116(le)001:506: gnas sogs pa'i rkyen gyis gru bshig ste gnyena pa
NK116(le)001:507: 'bras bu med par rgyud chud zos su bgyid pa
NK116(le)001:508: la phyogsa pa yin no zhes so //
NK116(le)001:510: mi yi gru la brten nas ni //
NK116(le)001:511: sdug bsngal chu bo che las sgrol //
NK116(le)001:512: gru 'di phyin chad rnyed dka' bas //
NK116(le)001:513: rmongs pa dus su gnyid ma long //
NK116(le)001:515: le'u ni pa dra la'i sgra las ris su bcad
NK116(le)001:516: pa'am yang na pa da gos kyi don te skyobs
NK116(le)001:517: pa'i mtshan nyid can la ni 'dzin pa'i don la
NK116(le)001:518: 'jug pa'i mtshan gyi gzhungs khebs shing gzhung khol bul
NK116(le)001:519: bcad pa'i sde tshan 'dres pa las nye bar skyobs
NK116(le)001:520: pa'i phyir de ltar smos te bstan bcos 'di le'u
NK116(le)001:521: bcu gsum gyi bdag nyid yin pa yas nas bgrang
NK116(le)001:522: ba'i thog ma yin pas dang po'o //
NK116(le)001:523: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi le'u dang po'i 'grel pa'o ////
NK116(le)001:524: gnyis pa 'dus byas mi rtag tshul la spyi dgos gnyis las /
NK116(le)001:526: srid pa zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:527: yod cing srid pas na srid pa /
NK116(le)001:529: g.yo ba ni bcud de chagas gansa 'jiga stong bzhi
NK116(le)001:530: so so'i yun bar skal nyi shu re ste bsdom
NK116(le)001:531: pas brgyad cu'i ngo bo'i bskal pa ste ring ba'i
NK116(le)001:532: tshad du btagsa pa'ang 'jigas pa'i rten gyur zhes ming
NK116(le)001:533: gi bla dwags kho nas sma phaba pa'i don dang
NK116(le)001:534: mtshungs ldan gzhom pa'am chada pa gcoda la me bduna
NK116(le)001:535: dang / chu gciga 'onga bar 'gyur te ji ltar
NK116(le)001:536: na gleng gzhi bye ba phrag brgya'i nyi ma de
NK116(le)001:537: snyed re re bzhin tshad pa bdun 'gyur gyi 'bar
NK116(le)001:538: ba'am drug drug 'khor du 'char bar 'dod pa gnyis
NK116(le)001:540: stong bar 'gyur ba spel mar lan bdun 'khor /
NK116(le)001:543: gang zhig dus rnams bsregs gyur te //
NK116(le)001:544: lhun po'ang thal bar 'jig pa dang //
NK116(le)001:545: rgya mtsho'i chu yang skam gyur na //
NK116(le)001:546: lus can de dag smos ci dgos //
NK116(le)001:548: spro na bden gnyis shing rtar gzigs pas chog gi 'dir yi ges 'jigs pas de tsam mo //
NK116(le)001:550: dam pa'i skyes bu la bsam ste /
NK116(le)001:551: skye rgu'i bdag po la bsam ste /
NK116(le)001:552: 'chi ba'i rang bzhin la bsam ste /
NK116(le)001:553: dpe don sna tshogs la bsam ste mi rtag pa bstan pa'o //
NK116(le)001:555: lha ma'i ston pa zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:556: 'gro ba lha mi'i bcas pa'i ston pa gang zhig
NK116(le)001:557: rdo rje'i khams su mtshan dpe'i yon tan rgya mtsho'i
NK116(le)001:558: sku mchoda grub kyang rtag para blta ba sun phyin
NK116(le)001:559: re zhig gdul bya la gzigas pa yol pa yi
NK116(le)001:560: tshul gyis gzhoma gzhiga brala ba'i chos nyid btang phyir
NK116(le)001:561: bsti stang sri zhu lhod par gyur nasa spros bral
NK116(le)001:562: zhi ba'i dbyingsa la dgyes pa'i mngona rtogsa ngomas pa
NK116(le)001:564: ci ste sangs rgyas rnams kyi sku //
NK116(le)001:565: mtshan dang dpe byad kyis brgyan pa //
NK116(le)001:566: rdo rje'i sku yang mi rtag na //
NK116(le)001:567: chu shing snying po med 'dra ba'i //
NK116(le)001:568: lus can gzhan rnams smros ci dgos /
NK116(le)001:571: gzugs dang long spyod thos pa dang //
NK116(le)001:572: tshul khrims la sogs rtag min te //
NK116(le)001:573: gang yang 'dod chags bral ba yang //
NK116(le)001:574: kun tu gnas pa ma mthong ngo //
NK116(le)001:577: bsam gtan zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:578: 'jig rten pa'i bsam gtan grub nasa srid rtser son
NK116(le)001:579: pa'i lha rnams bskala chen brgyad khri'i bar du gansa
NK116(le)001:580: pa sogs kyis 'tsho ba'i khur zad pas dona meda
NK116(le)001:581: par gyur te 'chi ba de dag mthonga nasa /
NK116(le)001:585: mi'i 'khora losa bsgyur ba rnams kyang 'chi badag gi
NK116(le)001:586: bduda la mi 'dod bzhin du gus pa las gzura
NK116(le)001:589: mya ngan bsal pa zhes bya ba'i spring yig las //
NK116(le)001:590: rtag par 'du shes rnams log nas //
NK116(le)001:591: srid rtse las kyang 'gro ba rnams //
NK116(le)001:592: 'chi ba'i zhags pas drangs gyur ba //
NK116(le)001:593: zhags pas glang po bzhin du'o //
NK116(le)001:594: bsam gtan las skyes bde ba myong //
NK116(le)001:595: tshangs pa tshangs pa'i gnas las kyang //
NK116(le)001:596: mi rtag phyir ni ltung gyur ba //
NK116(le)001:597: chu yi klung gi gram pa bzhin //
NK116(le)001:598: brgya byin dang ni stong rnams kyang //
NK116(le)001:599: 'khor los bsgyur ba brgya dag dang //
NK116(le)001:601: mar me 'bar ba rlung gis bzhin //
NK116(le)001:602: drang srong chen po lnga mngon shes //
NK116(le)001:603: mkha' la rgyang ring 'gro ba yang //
NK116(le)001:604: gang na spyod yul 'chi med par //
NK116(le)001:605: der ni 'gro bar nus ma yin //
NK116(le)001:608: mtho ris zhes bya ba la sogs gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:609: mtho risa mi'i gnas su smana gyi ljongas te myu
NK116(le)001:610: gu sna tshogs 'khrungs pa'i skyed tshal nyamsa dga' bar
NK116(le)001:611: ri dwags dal gyis 'tshogs pa lta bur 'khrigas pa
NK116(le)001:612: yi skyes bu'i zhes mis mtshona lus can rnams kyi
NK116(le)001:613: tshe srog 'phrog par yida la dus re 'ga' bar
NK116(le)001:615: bgyida pa'i rngona pa lag na be cona thogs pa
NK116(le)001:616: cana ni gshin rje'i pho nya ste dona bshad ma
NK116(le)001:617: thag pa'i ched gnyer gciga pu nyid las gazhana mi
NK116(le)001:618: semsa pa ni rgyal po la gdams pa'i mdor rgya
NK116(le)001:619: cher bstan zhing / slob dpon rta dbyangs kyis kyang /
NK116(le)001:620: 'chi bdag bzlog par bya ba yis //
NK116(le)001:621: gang tshe thabs kun med pas na //
NK116(le)001:622: spro bseng pa dag mi bskyed par //
NK116(le)001:623: chu la nya bzhin ci zhig 'gre //
NK116(le)001:625: skyes nas la la ma shi ba //
NK116(le)001:627: thos sam 'on tu the tshom za //
NK116(le)001:629: bzhi pa dpe sna tshogs kyis bstan par dgongs te
NK116(le)001:630: mi rtag pa ba ga nyal ston phyir so ka'i
NK116(le)001:631: zhes bya ba la sogs par gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:632: dus drug las so ka'i tsha basa rab tu gdung
NK116(le)001:633: bar gyur ba'i skye bo gang dag bsil ba'i phyir
NK116(le)001:634: du ston zla gasla ba'i 'oda la dga' bar gyur
NK116(le)001:635: nas te / yi rangs byas tshe nyin zhaga brgya
NK116(le)001:636: yi rang gi tshe bltungs par thal ba'i gansa la
NK116(le)001:637: semsa nas skrag para gyur ba meda pa 'di ni
NK116(le)001:638: nas te / blun te / mi rtag pa'i gtam las /
NK116(le)001:639: so ka zla ba bsil bas mtshon pa'i ston dus 'di 'byung zhes /
NK116(le)001:640: rab tu dga' gyur skye bo thams cad bdag gi tshe /
NK116(le)001:641: zad par 'gyur zhes shin tu mi dga' 'gyur ba med /
NK116(le)001:643: de bzhin gzhan gyi shi ba la mya ngan byed
NK116(le)001:644: rang gi mdun nam lhan gcig par 'chi bdag gnas
NK116(le)001:645: pa la cang mi sems par phyi chus rgya cher
NK116(le)001:646: byed pa 'di ni shin tu rigs pa ma yin
NK116(le)001:649: las kyi lam zhugs thob pa yis //
NK116(le)001:650: bsnon pa med pa'i skye bo gang //
NK116(le)001:651: nyes par med par song gyur pa //
NK116(le)001:652: de la ci zhig yongs su gdung //
NK116(le)001:654: gzhan ni su yang min na go //
NK116(le)001:655: 'di ni byur chen non pa zhes //
NK116(le)001:656: cho nges chen po gdab par rigs //
NK116(le)001:657: 'di ltar thams cad skye ba yi //
NK116(le)001:658: mdun na gnas pa 'chi ba ste //
NK116(le)001:659: kun kyang 'pho ba snang ba'i phyir //
NK116(le)001:660: mya ngan bya ba 'os ma yin //
NK116(le)001:662: tshe 'gro ba dal myur gyi dpe ston phyir skyes bu'i zhes bya ba la sogs par gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:663: 'di ltar skyes bus rtsola basa byas pa'i mgyogs tshad la ni /
NK116(le)001:664: gyad stobs po che bzhi rgyab sprad nas rang rang
NK116(le)001:665: gi gdong thad du nyag phran re 'phang ba bar
NK116(le)001:666: snang nas dus gcig tu lon pa myur mthar thug
NK116(le)001:667: par bzhag la / de basa kyang sa la rgyu ba'i yi dwagas mgyogs te /
NK116(le)001:668: de basa kyang mkha'a rgyu yi dwags dang /
NK116(le)001:669: de basa kyang nyi zla'i shing rta /
NK116(le)001:670: de bas kyang shin tu myur ba'i lha mgyogs de
NK116(le)001:671: dag kun lasa kyang mgyogsa pa ni mi yi tshe
NK116(le)001:673: ched du brjod pa'i tshom las /
NK116(le)001:674: ji ltar chu srin kha ru rgya mtsho'i gzings rgyug bzhin du mi 'dod kyang /
NK116(le)001:675: rmongs pa bdag 'dra las kyi dbang gis 'chi bdag kha ru rings par rgyug /
NK116(le)001:676: snying rje med pa'i 'chi bdag bdud kyis 'gro ba gzhan yang de bzhin med /
NK116(le)001:678: khyad par 'khor ba 'jig pa'i 'khrul 'khor chen po bzhi ston phyir /
NK116(le)001:679: dar la babs zhes bya la sogs par gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:680: rtag tu srid zhus bsnyen bkur ba'i lang tsho dar
NK116(le)001:681: la baba pa mtha' dag rga ba'i chad pasa 'tshe
NK116(le)001:682: zhing 'byung bzhi'i 'du ba rnal mara te snyoms par
NK116(le)001:683: gansa pa na basa dkrugsa te /
NK116(le)001:684: phun sum tshogas pa'i mnga' thang rten cinga 'brela bar 'byung ba dag rgud pasa 'jomas /
NK116(le)001:685: 'chi bas srog la rgol ba myur bor myur bor 'onga ba ni /
NK116(le)001:686: rgyal po la gdams pa'i mdo las /
NK116(le)001:687: rgyal po chen po 'di lta ste dper na /
NK116(le)001:688: phyogs bzhi nas ri chen po srab zhes sogs rgyas par gsungs so //
NK116(le)001:689: de nas lus bral ba'i mtshan nyid kyi skyo pa
NK116(le)001:690: bskul phyir gang tshe zhes bya ba la sogs par
NK116(le)001:691: gsungs te / kye ma gang gi tshe 'du byed
NK116(le)001:692: phung po gshina rje'i g.yul ngora phama ste 'chi ba'i
NK116(le)001:693: dus la bab pa de na skyabsa mgon dang dpunga
NK116(le)001:694: gnyen bral ba'i mya ngam thang gi gayanga sara rnam
NK116(le)001:695: par shes pa gcig pur rgyug la nye zhing 'tsho
NK116(le)001:696: ba'i zungs madngas dang dabnga po lnga'i mthu nyams pas
NK116(le)001:698: sman dang sman pa daga kyang de la mig rig
NK116(le)001:699: rig blta zhing 'brosa la rings pa las bya thabs
NK116(le)001:700: zad do // lus bems por 'gro la khad pa'i
NK116(le)001:701: mgul bskyod la ngala ba'i gnas thoba pa'i yan lag
NK116(le)001:702: dang dbugsa ni dabnga med par bskal pa las kyi
NK116(le)001:703: 'byung rlung 'khrugs pa'i mthu yisa g.yoba cinga ngar bar
NK116(le)001:704: byed dus nye du 'brela bas mal mtha' bskor zhing
NK116(le)001:705: sdug bsngal gyis gdungs te cho nge bton na yang
NK116(le)001:706: tshur 'gugs pa'i bshol 'debs lcags kyus brtan pa bral
NK116(le)001:707: ba ste shor bar gyur ba'i tshe de yi dbugsa
NK116(le)001:708: kyi 'gyur ba brtsegs 'phen res mos byas mthar rta
NK116(le)001:709: rnga'i lce lta bu shin tu phra ba de snying
NK116(le)001:710: rje med pa'i 'chi badga gi dgra s+t+wa rnon posa
NK116(le)001:711: tshal bar bakasa bar gyur pas /
NK116(le)001:712: mdzesa pa spangsa pa'i zhes bzhin mi sdug par gyur
NK116(le)001:713: nasa mchu yas mas su thon pa'i bar na so
NK116(le)001:714: zho ngomsa bzhina bde 'gro'i gnas las nyams nyes pa
NK116(le)001:715: 'di 'dra zhes pa'i ngang tshul mchi ma'i rba rlabs
NK116(le)001:717: lasa mi dge sogs pa gang zhig de yi dabnga
NK116(le)001:718: gis srid pa'i muna naga stug po'i phong bora 'juga
NK116(le)001:719: dgos pa'i phyir / las brgya ba las /
NK116(le)001:720: rtag tu spyod yul thams cad du //
NK116(le)001:721: 'chi bdag rjes su dran par bya //
NK116(le)001:724: nyin mtshan kun tu bdag gi ni //
NK116(le)001:727: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi le'u gnyis pa'i 'grel ba'o ////
NK116(le)001:728: gsum pa rgyu 'bras kyi rnam par bzhag pa la /
NK116(le)001:729: rnam pa thams cad du las la rag las pas
NK116(le)001:730: las rnams nges par byas nas mi dge ba bsrung
NK116(le)001:731: ba'i slad du de ltar zhes bya la sogs par
NK116(le)001:732: gsungs te / de ltar 'jiga rten 'di nas pha
NK116(le)001:733: rol son pa rnams ni gnas rigs mtho dman gyi
NK116(le)001:734: go 'phang ganga gi tha gus 'dogas pa'i tshul yang
NK116(le)001:735: gsungs te / / tshe 'dir dge ba spyad pa
NK116(le)001:736: dang cig shos sdig pa'i las la gomas shugs kyi
NK116(le)001:737: mthu kho nasa skye ba nye bar lena pa yin
NK116(le)001:738: gsungs te / / te / ci'i phyir na kun
NK116(le)001:739: rdzoba rten cing 'brel 'byung gi bdena pa bslu ba
NK116(le)001:740: meda pa yina pa'i shes byed /
NK116(le)001:742: dge ba las ni bde ba dang //
NK116(le)001:743: de bzhin bde 'gro thams cad do //
NK116(le)001:744: mi dge pa las sdug bsngal dang //
NK116(le)001:745: de bzhin ngan 'gro thams cad do //
NK116(le)001:747: de nyid dpe don gyis ston pa'i phyir gang zhig zhes bya la sogs par gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:748: 'di na ganga zhiga sa bona rnam pa sna tshogas
NK116(le)001:749: btab pa'i mthu dus su rtol te zhing pa rnams
NK116(le)001:750: kyi lo thoga la gasla ba bzhina /
NK116(le)001:751: skye ba gazhana thog ma'i dusa nas da bar 'dris
NK116(le)001:752: shinga gomas par byas pa'i dkar nag gi lasa tshul
NK116(le)001:753: manga posa / 'gro ba'i gnas rigs mtho dman dang
NK116(le)001:754: gzugs dbyibs sogs 'di dag sna tshogas byas zhes pa'i
NK116(le)001:755: rgyu las 'bras bu grub tshul dang /
NK116(le)001:756: 'dor len gyi gnas ris gnyis bstan to //
NK116(le)001:757: da lta byed bzhin pa'i las kyi rnam smin mod
NK116(le)001:758: la mi 'byung bas smina par mi 'gyur snyam du
NK116(le)001:759: sems na / sa bla mthon por zhes bya ba la sogs par gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:760: ji ltar sa bla mthona pora zhes nam mkhar gshegsa
NK116(le)001:761: pa'i mkha'a ldinga ste 'dab chags dag gi griba ma
NK116(le)001:762: re zhiga lta bar mi mngona na yanga /
NK116(le)001:763: gzugsa can rang nyid dang 'du 'brala spang ba'i mngon
NK116(le)001:764: rtogs nam zhig sar sleb dus brang 'og tu ril
NK116(le)001:765: gyis 'ong ba bzhina du las kyi 'bras bu gang
NK116(le)001:766: du 'a tshogas shinga dus la baba tshe /
NK116(le)001:767: mthong chos su'ang lhag para mngona pa ni /
NK116(le)001:769: lus can dag gis las rnams ni //
NK116(le)001:770: bskal pa brgyar yang chud mi za //
NK116(le)001:771: tshogs shing dus la bab pa na //
NK116(le)001:775: sdig pa'i las rnams spyad pa gang yin pa //
NK116(le)001:776: de yi mod la mtshon bzhin mi gcod kyang //
NK116(le)001:777: 'chi ba'i dus la bab tshe las kyi ni //
NK116(le)001:778: 'bras bu gang lags de ni mngon par 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:780: yang 'di ltar phyin ci log pa'i las rnams mthu
NK116(le)001:781: rmad du byung ba ni bsod nams zhes bya ba
NK116(le)001:783: bsoda namsa ma yina pa'i bya ba ni dpe can
NK116(le)001:784: mi dge ba rta gdonga gi me'i dper bkod des
NK116(le)001:785: mtho risa lha mi'i dpal 'byor rgya mtsho'i rlabsa kyang
NK116(le)001:786: skemsa par nus shing ma zad rnam mkhyen sangs rgyas
NK116(le)001:787: 'phags gyi go 'phang bsgrub pa la rang skya 'phel
NK116(le)001:788: ba'i rten mi lus rin po che'i gru gzingas lta
NK116(le)001:789: bu'ang bshiga pa'i dpe dang dona /
NK116(le)001:792: rgya chera rola ba sogs kyi gzhung du rgyas par bastan pas der blta bar bya'o //
NK116(le)001:794: bslab gsum dam bca' nyams pa sogs sun dbyung phyir /
NK116(le)001:795: mnar la zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:796: gang zhig manra ba la shina tu dapal zhing brtul
NK116(le)001:797: phoda pa ngana songa gisa 'jigs pas dge ba bcu'i
NK116(le)001:798: dpung ba dang go cha btsan pa'i dapa'a bo'i tshogs
NK116(le)001:799: rnams kyi yul du dmyal ba la sogs pa'i g.yula
NK116(le)001:800: gyi phru mas te dmag sgar btab pa ma mchisa
NK116(le)001:801: te / 'o na su la zhe na dam baca'a
NK116(le)001:802: nyamsa pa zhes mi dge bcu bsgrub pa matha'a dag
NK116(le)001:803: khyoda kyi dabnga du songa ngo //
NK116(le)001:804: de yang la la'i bslab pa'i tshul khrimsa dang /
NK116(le)001:806: la la'i sdom pa'i bka'a thub dang /
NK116(le)001:807: la la'i dam pa'i chos dang /
NK116(le)001:808: la la'i zang zing nor dang /
NK116(le)001:809: la la'i rang ngor ltos pa'i ngo tsha dang /
NK116(le)001:810: la la'i gzhan ngor ltos pa'i khrel yoda pa rnams
NK116(le)001:811: sdig pa'i ched du btong ba shina tu mang ngo
NK116(le)001:812: // 'di ltar mi dge ba'i las ni gzhan phyir
NK116(le)001:813: byas kyang rnam smin bgo bsha' med par ston pa
NK116(le)001:814: // / gang phyir zhes bya ba la sogs par gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:815: gang gi phyir du zhe na yona gansa te mchod
NK116(le)001:816: yul dang cig shos nye du 'khora 'abngas dang yul
NK116(le)001:817: khamsa sogs bsrung ba'i slad du rang bzhin rnam smin
NK116(le)001:818: stobsa chena gyi sdiga pa'i dpe gnyisa 'thung ste glang
NK116(le)001:819: por bkod nas / de nyid spongs sems kyi thags
NK116(le)001:820: pas dkris ba las btab nas bag med du spyod
NK116(le)001:821: por bkod nas / pa yanga / byed pa po
NK116(le)001:822: rang nyid ma gtogs rnam smin gyi 'bras bu khong
NK116(le)001:823: tshor bgo bashala bya ru meda para yina no //
NK116(le)001:824: de skad du slob dpon 'phags pas kyang //
NK116(le)001:825: khyod kyi bram ze dge slong lha dang ni //
NK116(le)001:826: ma gron dang yab yum dag dang btsun mo dang //
NK116(le)001:827: 'khor gyi slad du sdig pa mi bgyid de //
NK116(le)001:828: dmyal ba'i rnam smin skal nod 'ga' ma mchis //
NK116(le)001:830: yang tshur mthong chos brgyad la gnas par 'phags lam mi tshol na /
NK116(le)001:831: rnyed la zhes bya ba la sogs par gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:832: nor rdzas sogs rnyed pa la brkama pa ste chags
NK116(le)001:833: zhen che zhing rang nyid kho na bde ba'i thabs
NK116(le)001:835: snyan pa'i gtam thos nas lhur lena cing bstoda basngagasa
NK116(le)001:836: brjod par thos tshe nga rgyal gyi grogs su 'bar
NK116(le)001:838: gang de lasa cig shosa mi rnyed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:841: smad pa ste bzhi yisa yid mi bde bar 'gyur bas sma phab pa ste /
NK116(le)001:842: de bas na gtan bde'i 'dun ma cang mi sems
NK116(le)001:843: pa'i blo chung byis pa 'di daga 'jiga rten chosa
NK116(le)001:844: brgyad rdzun ris kyisa baslus pa ni /
NK116(le)001:846: 'jig rten mkhyen pa rnyed dang ma brnyed dang //
NK116(le)001:847: bde dang mi bde snyan dang mi snyan dang //
NK116(le)001:848: bstod smad ces bgyi 'jig rten chos brgyad po //
NK116(le)001:849: bdag gi yid yul min par mgo snyoms mdzod //
NK116(le)001:851: gzhan yang bslu byed kyi yan lag bcu gsum kyang yod ces ston pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:852: rigs gzugs zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:855: dabnga thang 3 dang la sogas kyis sdus pa /
NK116(le)001:857: lang tshos rgyags pa ste lnga po mgo 'aphanga bstoda cinga /
NK116(le)001:858: brtson 'grus kyi 'gal zla snyomsa 6 lasa kyis dus 'da' bar 'phyo ba ste /
NK116(le)001:859: zhwa bo lta bu'i phag tu yib pa dang /
NK116(le)001:860: ma thos pa thos zin du mngona par rlomas pa'i nga rgyal sogs ma rung slonga ba rnams ni /
NK116(le)001:861: bka' thuba kyi dapala la 'gong ba'am sdang ba'i srin
NK116(le)001:862: po chags sdang gnyis yin la de'i rgyu rkyen du
NK116(le)001:864: gzhan gyi dngos po'i ro myong ba'i brkam pa dang /
NK116(le)001:865: rang gi yo byad la chagas pa'i semsa kyis nus
NK116(le)001:866: pa brtan po yi zhes stobs su gyur basa zil
NK116(le)001:867: gyis non pa'i bsam pa rab tu mi brtan pa
NK116(le)001:868: gya gyu'i 'du shes can gyi g.yo dang /
NK116(le)001:869: pha rol bslu ba la goms pa'i sgyu'i 'khri shinga
NK116(le)001:870: gisa gazhana daga mgo rmongas par byas te badga nyida
NK116(le)001:871: bsrung pa ni 'jig rten gyi bya bzhag la mkhas
NK116(le)001:872: par grags na yanga thar lam gyi srog 'dor ba'i
NK116(le)001:873: dug lnga'i gnod chen de ni rang gi khong du
NK116(le)001:875: ser sna g.yo sgyu chags dang snyoms las dang /
NK116(le)001:876: mngon pa'i nga rgyal 'dod chags zhe sdang dang /
NK116(le)001:877: rigs dang gzugs dang thos dang lang tsho dang /
NK116(le)001:878: dbang thang che bas rgyags pa dgra bzhin gzigs /
NK116(le)001:880: dge sdig gi rnam smin phyi'i rgyu 'bras las 'phel che bar ston pa ni /
NK116(le)001:881: 'khor ba zhes bya ba la sogs gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:882: 'khora bar 'du byed pa ni dakara naga gi lasa 'brasa gnyisa te /
NK116(le)001:883: sa bona nyung ngu las kyang 'brasa bu'i gzugas sbo
NK116(le)001:884: ma pora bskyed pa'i rgyu mtshan bshad pa la mi
NK116(le)001:886: spyi bor skyes pa de sngon byis sba zhig tu gyur tshe /
NK116(le)001:887: sangs rgyas rnam gzigs la srana ma spar gang gtor
NK116(le)001:888: bas rdoga po bduna lhung bzed du chags pa lasa
NK116(le)001:889: 'bras bu gling bzhir dbang ba'i gseng gyi 'khora losa
NK116(le)001:891: rim pas rgyal chen bzhi dang /
NK116(le)001:892: lha'i dbang po dang stan gcig tu 'dug par thob pa bzhina no //
NK116(le)001:893: gang zhiga sa bona yungsa 'bru tsam pa'i shinga /
NK116(le)001:894: a sho ta ste de yi 'bras bu lo dus su thon pa na /
NK116(le)001:895: yala ga re la'ang dapaga tshad tsam 'phela bar 'gyur bas kyang /
NK116(le)001:896: dge sdiga gi gzugsa brnyan 'phela ba'i dpera mi phod de mtshon mi nus so //
NK116(le)001:897: las de dag kyang byed po kun slong kho nas nus pa che ba ston pa ni /
NK116(le)001:898: gang la zhes bya ba la sogs par gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:899: chos gang la'ang byed po ma mchisa pas na /
NK116(le)001:900: rang bzhina dngos su bde sdug srid pa mina te
NK116(le)001:901: 'on ci lan zhen bsam pa dkar naga gi chos
NK116(le)001:902: kyisa btsos pa'i kun slong gisa /
NK116(le)001:903: rgyu dge sdig las kyi sa bon rgya cher bskrun pa dang /
NK116(le)001:904: phugs su de yi 'bras bu mthu chen por byas /
NK116(le)001:905: de yang sngon du nyon mongs pa drag po dang bcas te las la sbyor rteng /
NK116(le)001:906: rjesa su yid rang byed pa gnyis po dang mi ldana na nus pa chung ba /
NK116(le)001:908: gal te mtho ris thar bar mngon bzhed na /
NK116(le)001:909: yang dag blta la goms pa nyid du mdzod /
NK116(le)001:910: gang zag log par blta bas legs spyad kyang /
NK116(le)001:911: thams cad rnam par smin pa mi bzad ldan /
NK116(le)001:913: de ltar kun slong gi 'phen byed kho na las
NK116(le)001:914: rnam pa'i rjes su mi 'gro ba'i tshul na ba
NK116(le)001:915: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:916: rtsa ba smana du mchisa na myu gu'ang sman yin la /
NK116(le)001:917: rtsa ba dug yin par gyur tshe myu gu 'ang dug yin pa smosa ci dgosa te /
NK116(le)001:918: de bzhin du gang gi rgyu'am rtsa ba bsam pa yin pas /
NK116(le)001:919: de kho nar ltos kyi dge dang mi dge'i 'phena
NK116(le)001:920: byed kyi las dge sdig ltar snang du bsgrub rgyu'i
NK116(le)001:921: gzugs barnyan che chung gi rjes su mi 'gro'o //
NK116(le)001:922: dge sdig lci yang gi bye brag gtso bor ston phyir /
NK116(le)001:923: 'di ltar zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:924: 'di ltar sbyor ba sdig pa byed 'dod rtag tu yid la bcag pa dang /
NK116(le)001:925: bsam pa ha cang brnag pas mngona par zhena pa dang /
NK116(le)001:927: sems kyis ma bshags pa dang /
NK116(le)001:928: gzhi la gnyis kyi snga ma /
NK116(le)001:929: yona tana gtso ldan ni mchod 'os kyi yul dang /
NK116(le)001:930: gzhi las byung ba'i phyi ma phan 'dogs gyi yul
NK116(le)001:931: na pha ma dang rjes mthun gzhan dag kyang ste
NK116(le)001:932: / dang po gsum rang ngor rag la /
NK116(le)001:933: phyi ma gnyis yul la rag ste /
NK116(le)001:934: lasa rnam pa lnga po de la brten pa'i dge sdig gang rung lci zhing /
NK116(le)001:935: ldog nas cung zad yang gi /
NK116(le)001:936: cis phyir ce na rnam smin gyi gtos chen po nye bar len pa'i rnam riga ste /
NK116(le)001:938: sus shes na thub pa chen pos legs par gsungs pa'i rjes su klu sgrub kyis so //
NK116(le)001:939: gang du na spring yig las /
NK116(le)001:940: rtag dang mngon par zhen dang gnyen po med //
NK116(le)001:941: yon tan gtso ldan gzhi las byung ba'i las //
NK116(le)001:942: dge dang mi dge rnam lnga chen po ste /
NK116(le)001:943: de bas dge ba spyod la brtson par gyis /
NK116(le)001:945: las kyi 'char gzhi dang dbye ba ston phyir kun gyi zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:946: 'khor ba kun gyi rten yul byed po kun gzhi
NK116(le)001:947: dge sdig gang rung du'ang lung ma bstana pa gti
NK116(le)001:948: mug gi mtshungs ldan can de yod phyir /
NK116(le)001:949: de lasa 'dzin byed kyi yid dang yula lnga'i ste sgo lnga'i shes pa langas pa yin la /
NK116(le)001:950: snga phyi kuna la khyab byed rgyu bdag nyid gcig
NK116(le)001:951: pa dang lhan skyes kun brtag ste ma riga pa
NK116(le)001:952: gsum pos gdona chen gyi rgyus /
NK116(le)001:953: nyon mongas pa chags sdang bar ma gsum bdag gir
NK116(le)001:954: bzung ba'i rkyen gyis 'khora ba'i gnas rigs gang rung
NK116(le)001:955: bar / skye ba mtho damna blangs par byas shing byed la byed par 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:957: de ltar skye ba'i khams gsum po phyi nang gnyis las dang po go sla zhing phyi ma /
NK116(le)001:960: ngag phra ba gzugs kyi khams /
NK116(le)001:961: yid ches phra ba gzugs med pa'i khams te /
NK116(le)001:962: grong khyer de gsum na khye'u snang ba dam pa gnas so //
NK116(le)001:963: zhes rten yid dang brten pa rang byung gi yi shes kyi khyad par kyang bstan no //
NK116(le)001:964: 'di gsum la phra rags kyi dbye ba /
NK116(le)001:965: snang bar ngang phyed snang dang /
NK116(le)001:966: mi snang ba'i grong zhes grags so //
NK116(le)001:967: gzhan yang dge sdig gi 'phen rdzogs mu bzhi dang /
NK116(le)001:969: du mas lus du mar 'phen min gyi mu bzhi
NK116(le)001:970: yod pa sogs spro na gzhung chen rnams su gzigs
NK116(le)001:971: shig / tshul min gyi las bsags zin nas slar gsor rung min skal pa mnyam mam zhe na /
NK116(le)001:972: ji ltar zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:973: dpe ji ltar na me dpung chen po ni 'abra
NK116(le)001:974: zhing dngos po rnams bsregs para 'gyur bas de yi
NK116(le)001:975: gnyen po ste gsod bar byed pa la chasa pa
NK116(le)001:976: chu lasa gazhana gang yang meda para 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:977: de bzhin gnas min las skyob nges pa dkon mchoga gsuma po kho na yin phyir /
NK116(le)001:978: sku gsung thugs rten zong du 'tshong bas bslus shinga /
NK116(le)001:979: dpangs su btsugs te mna' za ba'am /
NK116(le)001:980: skur 'debs byas nas skyabs yul spangas pa yi las
NK116(le)001:981: ngan sdig to'i khur chen pos non pa can de
NK116(le)001:982: nyid re zhig ngan song du ltung ba la /
NK116(le)001:983: 'phags pa'i thugs rjes kyang do zla rnyed pa mina te skal ba med pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:984: sems dang sems byung gi dbye ba dngos ston pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:985: de la zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:986: sngar gsungs pa'i yid dang sgo lnga'i zhes pa tsam
NK116(le)001:987: gyis las mi gsog cing de lasa gazhana du gyur
NK116(le)001:988: pa 'gro ba'i nyon yid kyis byas pa ni kun
NK116(le)001:989: rtog sna tshogs bshad pa la chu dang rlabs ltar
NK116(le)001:990: rang bzhina 'brela bar gyur ba'i semsa dang semsa byung
NK116(le)001:991: gi las matha'a dag grangs las 'das pas na /
NK116(le)001:992: 'di tsam zhes blo yisa kha tshon gcod pa'i mthar thuga pa ma mchisa mod kyang /
NK116(le)001:993: lus ngaga yida la rten dang brten pa cana ngag
NK116(le)001:994: bsdus spanga blang bya ba'i rgyu 'brasa rnam pa bcura
NK116(le)001:999: dang po la lus kyi zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1000: lus kyi gsuma po srog gcoda ma byin blangsa /
NK116(le)001:1001: log para g.yema lasa dang po srog gcoda ni /
NK116(le)001:1002: 'du shes ma 'khrula bar gazhana sroga bsam bzhina gcoda pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1003: phyogsa mthuna rdo dbyug sogs kyis brdeg pa dang btsoga pa la sogas 'tshe ba bgyid pa yin no //
NK116(le)001:1004: ma byin rlang ba ni gazhana nor yin par shesa bzhina brku ba dang /
NK116(le)001:1005: phyogsa mthuna 'os min gyi chad pa sogs thabs kyi blangs pa g.yo dang /
NK116(le)001:1006: bre srang la sogs log par bcos pa lta bu sgyu yisa lena pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1007: 'doda loga ni smad 'tshora ma la gzhan gyis 'khrigs
NK116(le)001:1008: pa'i ched du gla rngana thoba pa ste sprad nas
NK116(le)001:1009: dus btab pa la bar du bcad de reg pa
NK116(le)001:1011: phyogsa mthuna bgroda bya ma yin pa'i yul kha dang
NK116(le)001:1012: gshang lam la sogs par 'khrigas pa'i chosa gazhana yin
NK116(le)001:1014: yan lag gi dbang po rang gi rtsol ba byas pa la sogs pa'o //
NK116(le)001:1016: gnyis pa la ngag gi zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1017: ngag gi bzhi ni 'gro ba phal ba'i brdzun dang /
NK116(le)001:1018: yon tan ma thob pa thob ces mi chos bla
NK116(le)001:1019: ma'i brdzun chen po gang rung smras pas gazhana dag
NK116(le)001:1020: 'khrul du bcug pa dang phyogsa mthuna ni drang po'i
NK116(le)001:1021: zol gyis 'adu shesa bslada nas gazhana gyi semsa bslu
NK116(le)001:1022: ba'o / phra ma ni pha rol mthuna nam btang
NK116(le)001:1023: snyomsa la gansa pa dbyen sbyor gyis 'drala bcug pa
NK116(le)001:1024: ba'o / dang / phyogsa mthuna skyon tshiga brjod pa /
NK116(le)001:1025: gazhana pha rol po la bzlosa nas 'khona du 'chosa pa'o //
NK116(le)001:1026: brdzun dang phra ma gnyis 'dra bar snyams na /
NK116(le)001:1027: snga ma ni bslu sems dang phyi ma ni dbye sems kyis khyad par ro //
NK116(le)001:1028: ngag 'khyal ba ni bre mo'i gtam ste ku re
NK116(le)001:1029: dang rtsed mo sogs las chagas sdang bskyeda pa dang
NK116(le)001:1030: / phyogsa mthuna damga jag dang chom rkun la sogs chos dang 'gal ba'i 'brela med kyi gtam mo //
NK116(le)001:1032: ngag kyal ba ni chos min gyi gtam dang /
NK116(le)001:1033: bre mo 'dod rgyal ste gang babs su brjod pa zhes gsungs so //
NK116(le)001:1035: pha rola po'i lkog gyur gyi skyon mngon du brjod
NK116(le)001:1036: pas snying la 'bigsa pa ste yid kyi tsher mar
NK116(le)001:1037: gyur ba dang / phyogsa mthuna snyan snyan 'dra mo'i
NK116(le)001:1038: gazhana gyi yid mi bde ba'i rkyen dang sprod pa'o
NK116(le)001:1039: gyur ba dang / // gsum pa la /
NK116(le)001:1040: yid kyi zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1041: yid kyi gsuma la dang po brnaba semsa ni /
NK116(le)001:1042: gazhana gyi 'byora ba'i dapala la ha cang barngamas shinga thob rlom gyis badga gira byed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1043: phyogsa mthuna pha rola po'i rdzas rnams nga la yod
NK116(le)001:1044: na ci ma rung snyam ste brkama zhing ro myang
NK116(le)001:1045: ba'o // gnod semsa ni gazhana la kun nas mnar
NK116(le)001:1046: sems kyi dngos po dgu 'brel ba'i chos lngas khonga
NK116(le)001:1048: phyogas mthuna phana pa'i sems kyis 'brela ba la 'du 'brala bsgom nas de'i cho ga la brtson pa'o //
NK116(le)001:1049: log lta ni rgyu 'brasa meda par 'dzin pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1050: rtag chada blta bar dmigs yul gtong ba dang /
NK116(le)001:1051: phyogsa mthuna gang zhig meda nges pa la yod ces sgro 'dogas pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1052: yod bzhin la med ces bskur ba 'debs pa'o //
NK116(le)001:1053: da ni de dag gi 'bras bu bshad pa la /
NK116(le)001:1054: kun la zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1055: kun la 'brasa bu bzhira bzhira smina pa'i tshul zhes /
NK116(le)001:1058: dbang ngama bdag po'i 'bras bu te gsum dang /
NK116(le)001:1059: man ngag gis byed pa'i 'bras bu bsnan pa'i bzhi po lasa /
NK116(le)001:1061: rnam smin zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1062: rnam smin gyi 'brasa bu srog gcod lta bur mtshon na /
NK116(le)001:1063: gzhi bsam spyor ba mthar thug yid rang ba ste /
NK116(le)001:1064: chos lnga po dang ldan na ma gal te mina /
NK116(le)001:1065: kun slong gsum gyi chung ngu gti mug gis dud 'gro dang /
NK116(le)001:1066: 'bringa 'dod chags kyi dbang gis yi dwags /
NK116(le)001:1067: chena po zhe sdang gis dmyal bar 'phen no //
NK116(le)001:1069: rgyu mthun zhes bya ba la sogs gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1070: rgyu mthuna gyi 'brasa bu rnams pa gnyis grub ste
NK116(le)001:1071: byed pa rgyu mthuna ni snga ma gang byas kyi
NK116(le)001:1072: las de dang da lta byed lasa mthuna par skye
NK116(le)001:1073: zhing myong ba rgyu mthuna gyi mtho risa gsum gyi
NK116(le)001:1074: ya gyal mi lus thoba par gyur kyang /
NK116(le)001:1075: rima bzhina mi dge bcu la 'bras bu gnyisa gnyis dang ldana pa'i tshul ni /
NK116(le)001:1077: 'tsho ba ste tshe thung la nad kyang rnam grangsa manga pos ma nar ro //
NK116(le)001:1079: yoda byad nyunga zhing de dag dgra dang thun mong cana no //
NK116(le)001:1080: gsum pa khyim thabsa ste grogs mi mdzesa shing dgra zlara 'brela ba ba'o /
NK116(le)001:1082: rtag tu smad pa'am bskura basa gdunga zhing gazhana gyisa bslu ba manga ngo //
NK116(le)001:1084: 'khora g.yoga ngana zhing 'duma para daka' ba can dang /
NK116(le)001:1086: mi snyan manga du thosa shing legs par smras pa'ang /
NK116(le)001:1089: gsang tshiga sogs bzunga mi 'osa shing gzhan yida chesa zhana pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1091: 'byor bas chog mi shesa pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1092: thob par 'doda pasa gdunga ba dang /
NK116(le)001:1094: gnod byed pa 'ba' zhig 'du zhing phan 'dogs pa 'drala ba dang /
NK116(le)001:1096: rtag chad sogs lta ba ngana pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1097: sems rnal du mi gnas par g.yo sgyu'i 'khrugas pa'o //
NK116(le)001:1098: gsum pa dbang gi zhes bya ba la sogs par gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1099: dabnga gi 'brasa bu'am bdag po'i 'bras bu ni /
NK116(le)001:1100: gang du skye yula dang rten cinga 'brela 'byung gi tshul du 'ong ste /
NK116(le)001:1101: ji ltar srog gcoda kyi las sdig to'i khura gyis non ba de /
NK116(le)001:1102: sa phyogsa bag chunga zhing sman shing dang me tog nyung la /
NK116(le)001:1103: lo 'bras sogs kyi baza'a btung mthu nyamsa pa ste nus pa med pas 'ju daka'a zhing /
NK116(le)001:1104: sroga la rgol ba che ba'i ya nga'i gnas su phyin para 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:1105: ma byin blangs bas log rtog gi myu gu rnams
NK116(le)001:1106: mi barlinga ste 'jomas par sla zhing bza' shinga yod
NK116(le)001:1107: kyang 'bras bu mi 'khrungs pas rnam par smad de
NK116(le)001:1108: sad kyi gdung zhing ser basa rnama par 'athaga pas
NK116(le)001:1109: mu ge'i sdug bsngal gyis khur chen snying gi yol
NK116(le)001:1112: gshang dang gci'i 'admas rdzab khrod du dri nga ba
NK116(le)001:1113: ste mi zhim pa'i tshora ba rtsub mosa dbugas mi
NK116(le)001:1114: phyin cing gzhan mi gatsanga sna tshogs ci rigs pa'i
NK116(le)001:1116: skam sa'i khrod doga cinga nyamsa mi dag'a ba'i yula
NK116(le)001:1117: du skye ba'i 'khri shinga dbang med du 'dzuga dgos
NK116(le)001:1118: so // rdzun gyis 'byor ba mi brtan pas g.yo
NK116(le)001:1119: zhing yul phan tshun dgra zla lta bur mi mthuna
NK116(le)001:1120: so // te / gzhan gyisa bslu ba mang ba
NK116(le)001:1121: dang sna tshogs 'jigsa pas stobsa pa ste dngas shinga
NK116(le)001:1122: so // te / skraga pa'o // phra mas sa
NK116(le)001:1123: phyogsa ngam groga ste sdug pa'i gconga rong can dang
NK116(le)001:1124: so // te / skraga pa'o // / bsgroda daka'a
NK116(le)001:1125: ba'i yul khad mi snyoms par mtho damna can gyi
NK116(le)001:1127: brjod pa rtsub mos rdo dang /
NK116(le)001:1129: tsher ma can gyi shing dang sdonga dum 'bras ngana
NK116(le)001:1130: ste yal ga rtsub pa dang nyamsa mi bde zhing
NK116(le)001:1131: tsha sgo te ba tsha cana dang rdula mang nyala
NK116(le)001:1132: nyila gyi khroda du skye zhing /
NK116(le)001:1133: yida mi bde ba'i tshora ba nyamsa su myong /
NK116(le)001:1134: kyal kasa so namas la brtson pa chen pos rang
NK116(le)001:1135: shed ngala bar byas kyang 'bras bu med cinga tsha
NK116(le)001:1136: grangs go ldog pa lta bur dus kyi rjes su
NK116(le)001:1137: mi 'gro zhing mi brtan par 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:1138: brnaba semsa kyis spun dang 'bras bu go ldoga pa ste /
NK116(le)001:1139: lo tog gi shun pa'i nang na snying po med cinga /
NK116(le)001:1141: dus ma rung bar gduga pa sna tshogs kyis rgol ba'i skabsa batsala 'ba' zhig mthonga bar skye'o //
NK116(le)001:1142: gnoda semsa kyis sdig spyoda rgyal po dang 'brel zhing gzhan choma rkun dang /
NK116(le)001:1143: sbrul gduga mi rgoda gcan zan la sogs gdug pa
NK116(le)001:1144: can gyis rtsub pa ste 'tshe zhing lo tog dang
NK116(le)001:1145: 'bras bu'i ro yang mi mngar bar tsha zhing kha
NK116(le)001:1146: ba dang / 'di zhes dmigs gsal med par rang bzhina gnoda pasa bakaba pa'i yul du skye'o //
NK116(le)001:1147: loga ltas rin po che sogsa phun tshogas kyis /
NK116(le)001:1148: 'byor basa kun nasa spongsa shinga dbul te sman shinga mi skye bas nyung zhing /
NK116(le)001:1149: me tog 'bras bu daga kyang nus pa zhen pas mthu chunga la /
NK116(le)001:1150: skyabsa dang skyob pa dpung gnyena meda pa'i yul du nges para skye'o //
NK116(le)001:1152: skyes bu zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1153: skyes bu byed pa'i 'bras bu tshe 'adi'am snga ma
NK116(le)001:1154: gang byas kyis mi dge ba'i las phyir zhing mang
NK116(le)001:1155: pora 'phela bas sdug bsngal gyi rgyu 'bras mtha' daga
NK116(le)001:1157: de yang dran pa nyer bzhag chung ngu las /
NK116(le)001:1158: skyes bu gti mug can sdig pa byed pa de dag ni /
NK116(le)001:1159: yang phyir zhing sdig pa 'phel bas rab tu sdug bsngal bar 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:1161: blo gsar bu ba 'ga' zhig gi skyes bu byed
NK116(le)001:1162: pa'i 'bras bu 'di gong gi gsum po dang 'dra
NK116(le)001:1164: de'i khyad par ni srog gcod lta bu la dbye na /
NK116(le)001:1165: rnam 'bras kun slong gi rjes mthun ngan song du 'gro la /
NK116(le)001:1166: byed 'bras phyi nas kyang gzhan srog gcod pa'i skye ba len zhing /
NK116(le)001:1168: skyes bu byed 'bras ni sdig pa de dag gi ngo bos 'phel zhing /
NK116(le)001:1169: rab tu 'phel kun tu 'phel nyes mang gi rgyu byed pa yin no //
NK116(le)001:1171: 'di ltar mun pa las kyang mun zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1172: 'di ltar khams gsum po gnas rigs muna pa 'dra
NK116(le)001:1173: ba lasa kyanga phyin ci log pa'i las muna rug
NK116(le)001:1174: pa'i steng nas char smag nag po 'thib pa lta
NK116(le)001:1175: bu bsags pa can ni 'khora ba'i brtson rara tshud
NK116(le)001:1176: pa spyi mthun la bye brag shina tu brnag daka'a
NK116(le)001:1177: bar / nyer len phunga po lnga'i steng du rigs
NK116(le)001:1178: drug gi sdug bsngal mtshon cha'i dabla phog nas bzod
NK116(le)001:1179: para daka'a ba'i tshora ba rtsub mo thob pa /
NK116(le)001:1180: 'di sdig pa kho na'i mthus byas pa yin no //
NK116(le)001:1181: de lta'i mi dge la phra rgyas sna tshogs te /
NK116(le)001:1182: yul gyi ngos nas stobs che ba /
NK116(le)001:1185: dgra bcom pa bsad pa gsum /
NK116(le)001:1186: dge 'dun gyi dbye na byed pa /
NK116(le)001:1187: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku la ngan sems kyi khrag 'byin pa ste mtshams med lnga'o //
NK116(le)001:1188: de dang nye ba lnga yod de /
NK116(le)001:1191: dgra bcom ma la mi tshangs pa spyod pa /
NK116(le)001:1193: dge 'dun gyi zhal du 'du ba'i sgo 'phrog pa'o //
NK116(le)001:1194: ma skyes dgras lhung byang las /
NK116(le)001:1196: dgra bcom ma la mi tshang spyad pa /
NK116(le)001:1197: dkon mchog gsum gyi dkor la spyod pa /
NK116(le)001:1198: 'dum pa'i dge 'dun gyi dbye na byed pa ste nye ba bzhi yang bshad do //
NK116(le)001:1199: zhar la lci ba'i kha na ma thob bcu drug dang /
NK116(le)001:1200: log pa brgyad kyang bshad do //
NK116(le)001:1206: de bzhin du mi chos kyi mna' zos pa /
NK116(le)001:1207: nyan thos kyi khrims nyams pa /
NK116(le)001:1208: byang sems kyi bslab pa nyams pa /
NK116(le)001:1209: gsang basngagasa kyi dam tshig nyams pa rnams bsdams pas lci ba brgyad do //
NK116(le)001:1210: gti mug gi dbang gis ston pa'i sku la smad pa /
NK116(le)001:1211: nga rgyal gyi dbang gis mkhas pa'i yon tan la smad pa /
NK116(le)001:1212: phrag dog gi dbang gis bden pa'i tshig la smad pa /
NK116(le)001:1213: phyogs ris kyi dbang gis chos la dgag bsgrubs bgyis pa rnams bsnan pas lci bas bcu gnyis so //
NK116(le)001:1214: mtshams med pa lnga las khrag 'byin pa /
NK116(le)001:1215: mi dge ba bcu las log par lta ba mnyam pa'i chos la khyad du gsod pa /
NK116(le)001:1216: rang bzhin med pa la gal 'dzugs pa rnams kyis lci ba bcu drug go //
NK116(le)001:1221: skur ba'i lci ba zhes bya ba rim par sbyar ro //
NK116(le)001:1225: dge ba can gyi thugs dkrugs pa /
NK116(le)001:1226: dad pa can gyi tshogs bcag pa /
NK116(le)001:1227: bla ma dang yi dam dang /
NK116(le)001:1229: dkyil 'khor gnyen po 'dral ba rnams so //
NK116(le)001:1230: de dag gi ldog phyogs bstan pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:1231: de phyir zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungas te /
NK116(le)001:1232: de'i phyir na ma dag pa'i gazhana dbang srid par
NK116(le)001:1233: 'khrula ba'i gansa skabsa na snga ma rnam dkar gyi
NK116(le)001:1235: mtho risa su 'phena byed dge ba'i lasa lam bcu yod de ji ltar na /
NK116(le)001:1236: mi dge bcu lasa phyi rola phyogsa pa yi /
NK116(le)001:1237: zhes pa'i mi dge ba bcu las ldog pa tsam gyis dge bcur 'dod de /
NK116(le)001:1238: rgyud bsdams pa med cing lung ma bstan yin cing /
NK116(le)001:1239: de dag spangs pa'i dam baca'i steng srog bsrung sbyin gtong /
NK116(le)001:1248: dge ba'i lasa bcu bo de la /
NK116(le)001:1249: yang dag par bsnyen para mdzoda cig ces so //
NK116(le)001:1250: de bsnyen par gyur ba lasa bsoda namsa cha mthun
NK116(le)001:1251: lha ma'i dge 'bras bcu po bsags stobs chung bas
NK116(le)001:1252: mi 'bring gis 'dod lha chen pos tshangs pa'i gnas
NK116(le)001:1253: bzhi sogs bde 'grora 'phena cinga cig shos mi dge
NK116(le)001:1254: ba rnam pa bcusa ngana 'grora 'phena pas /
NK116(le)001:1255: dakara nag gi rgyu 'brasa la mi tsing par dpyad nas blang dora bgyida pa /
NK116(le)001:1257: chos 'dis dmyal ba yi dwags dang //
NK116(le)001:1258: dud 'gro rnam las rnam grol zhing //
NK116(le)001:1259: lha dang mi yi nang dag tu //
NK116(le)001:1260: bde dpal rgyal srid rgyas par thob //
NK116(le)001:1261: bsam gtan tshad med gzugs med ni /
NK116(le)001:1262: tshangs sogs bde ba myong bar byed /
NK116(le)001:1263: ces mtho ris mngon par bsgrub cing ngan song gi
NK116(le)001:1264: sgo gcod par byed pas na lha ma'i theg pa'am
NK116(le)001:1265: skyes bu chung ngu'i lam zhes bshad do //
NK116(le)001:1266: de nas nges par legs pa'i go 'phang thob pa'i rgyu ni /
NK116(le)001:1267: thar pa zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1268: thar pa'i cha mthuna zag meda dam pa mya ngan la 'das pa'i rgyu'ang dag pa bcu dang /
NK116(le)001:1269: bsam gatana bzhi dang gzugas med bzhi dang sbyin sogas phar phyin druga dang /
NK116(le)001:1270: tshogas sbyor mthonga sgoma mi slob pa ste lam lngasa bsdus pa'i zag med kyi dge tshogs yin no //
NK116(le)001:1271: thabs shes snga phyi med par zung du 'jug pa'i theg chen 'phags tshul /
NK116(le)001:1272: de yang zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1273: de yang bdag la dbye na /
NK116(le)001:1274: gang zag gi bdag gi bdag nga'am bdag ces bya ba med par gtan la phab pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1275: chos kyi bdag gzugs nas rnam mkhyen bar rang bzhin meda par shes pa gnyis kyi don rtogsa nasa /
NK116(le)001:1276: thabsa snying rje chen po dang /
NK116(le)001:1277: shes rab stong nyid zab mo zung du 'brel ba'i dge ba gser 'gyur gyi rtsi lta bus /
NK116(le)001:1279: zhi ba myang 'das kyi chos gnyis phan tshun so so 'gal ba 'khor ba ba'i lugs khams la /
NK116(le)001:1280: thebas pas mi gansa ye shesa rgyal ba'i khamas su
NK116(le)001:1281: grub par byed pa 'jiga rten las 'das pa'i dge
NK116(le)001:1282: ba ces bya ba de yina no //
NK116(le)001:1283: de ltas mthar thug gi 'bras bu bde brlag thob pa ni /
NK116(le)001:1284: lam dus zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1285: 'di ltar slob lam gyi dus su dmigas pa dang bacasa para /
NK116(le)001:1286: rgyu bsod namas kyi tshogas dang /
NK116(le)001:1287: snang la rang bzhin med pa chu zla lta bu'i
NK116(le)001:1288: rjes thob pa la mnyam bzhag nam mkha' lta bur
NK116(le)001:1289: dmigas pa med pa'i don rtogs pa nas 'bras bu
NK116(le)001:1290: ye shesa kyi tshogas te zunga 'juga gisa nyon shes
NK116(le)001:1291: kyi sgrib pa gnyis sbyangsa te gzugs kyi sku dang
NK116(le)001:1292: chos kyi sku gnyis mngona du 'thob pa ni yang
NK116(le)001:1293: dag pa'i rgyu 'bras zab mo'i rten cing 'brel bar
NK116(le)001:1295: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi le'u gsum pa'i 'grel ba'o ////
NK116(le)001:1296: bzhi pa 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs 'khor lo dang pho'i gtam dang 'brel bar ston pa las /
NK116(le)001:1297: mtho ris kyi bde bas tshim pa tsam gyi mtshang
NK116(le)001:1298: la rgol ba mngon mtho'i zhes bya la sogs par
NK116(le)001:1299: gsungs te / mngona tho'i gnas na gru bo che'i
NK116(le)001:1300: mchoga lta bu'i dpal 'byor gyi rten la brten pa
NK116(le)001:1301: gsungs te / rnams / re zhiga ngana songa gsum
NK116(le)001:1302: gyi chu srin gduga pa'i lce lta bus btang ba
NK116(le)001:1303: 'dra yanga ma rig srid matha'i 'jigs las ma 'grol
NK116(le)001:1304: ba'i skyon gyis thara ba'i skama sara ma phyin pasa
NK116(le)001:1305: na 'aphagas pa'i bdena pa bzhi yi deda dpona bsten
NK116(le)001:1307: de la bdag cag gi ston pas w+aa ra na sir /
NK116(le)001:1309: dge slong dag 'di ni sdug bsngal lo //
NK116(le)001:1317: lam rgyud la brten par bya'o //
NK116(le)001:1319: sdug bsngal shes par bya ste /
NK116(le)001:1320: shes par byar med pas mi skye ba dang /
NK116(le)001:1322: spang du med pas mi skye ba shes pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1324: mngon du byar med pas mi skye ba /
NK116(le)001:1325: lam rgyud la brten par bya ste /
NK116(le)001:1326: brten par byar med pas mi skye ba shes par bya ba /
NK116(le)001:1327: zhes bden pa bzhi lan gsum du bzlos te gsungs pa bzhin /
NK116(le)001:1328: sdug bsngal shes par bya ba'i phyir de la zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1329: de la sdug bsngal shes para bya ba ni /
NK116(le)001:1330: 'khor ba'i gansa rigas drug po dam'a ba ngan song
NK116(le)001:1331: gsum po'am mtho ba mtho ris rnam gsum gang yanga
NK116(le)001:1332: rung ste brtsegs mar byung ba sduga bsngal gyi sdug
NK116(le)001:1333: bsngal / bde sdug ri mos barje ba 'gyur ba'i sdug bsngal dang /
NK116(le)001:1334: bag la nyal ba ltar mi mngon pa khyab pa
NK116(le)001:1335: 'du byed kyi sdug bsngal de gsum pos dama la
NK116(le)001:1336: ma bazhaga pa'i 'khora ba yoda pa ma yin te
NK116(le)001:1337: / de'ang 'dod yul gnyis rten brten par 'brel ba ni /
NK116(le)001:1338: phung dkrol zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1339: 'di ltar 'dod pa phung dkrola bskyeda pa'i rtsa ba yin la /
NK116(le)001:1340: bdag gzhan gnod pa'i rgyu de sbrul gdug gi mgo 'aphanga bstod pa ltar byas pa de yi /
NK116(le)001:1341: ma runga 'doda pa'i gdona dang yul gyi dug rnams /
NK116(le)001:1342: phana tshuna 'dzingas shinga gtugsa pa ste sems yul phyir
NK116(le)001:1343: shor bas chags sdang bar gsum bsags te 'khor ba'i
NK116(le)001:1344: brtsona ra nasa nam yang thara ba'i skabas meda pa'i
NK116(le)001:1345: nyamas thaga pa rnams la skyo ba 'phela ba'i gnas
NK116(le)001:1346: yin pa ni / bshes spring las /
NK116(le)001:1347: 'dod pa rnams ni phung dkrol bskyed pa ste /
NK116(le)001:1348: thub pa'i dbang pos kim+ba'i 'bras 'drar gsungs /
NK116(le)001:1349: de dag spang bgyid de yi lcags sgrog gis /
NK116(le)001:1350: 'khor ba'i brtson rar 'jig rten 'di dag bcing /
NK116(le)001:1353: bde ba zhes bya ba la sogs par gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1354: bde ba 'dod pa'i thabs la mngon par sbyor bar brtson pa daga ni /
NK116(le)001:1355: gti mug gi mthus nona pas cho ga dag ni phyin ci log tu song ste /
NK116(le)001:1356: sduga bsngal gyi rgyu 'brasa kyisa rang mtshan bzod du
NK116(le)001:1357: med pa'i mtshona cha rnon po'i dapala la brten par
NK116(le)001:1358: byas pasa gnoda pa 'ba' zhig pa'i gansa su ranga
NK116(le)001:1359: nyida yang daga pa ste gegs med par sbyar ba'i
NK116(le)001:1360: dpe yang / mar me'i gzugs dang bye ma leba 'phrad pa tsam na 'tshig pa de bzhina du /
NK116(le)001:1361: sgra dang dri ro rega byas bslusa pa ni /
NK116(le)001:1362: ri dwagas sgra la chags nas barngona pas bsad pa /
NK116(le)001:1363: bunga ba dri la chags pas pad+ma'a kha zum nas shi ba /
NK116(le)001:1364: nya ro la chags pas lcags kyus zin nas gsod pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1365: glanga po che dga' ba'i reg byar chags pas mtshor bying nas shi ba ltar /
NK116(le)001:1366: 'doda pa'i yul lnga po daga dang rgyu rkyen rten cinga 'brela bas nges par bslu ste /
NK116(le)001:1368: 'bar ba chen po'i tshogs dag gi /
NK116(le)001:1369: me chen dag ni mthong nas kyang //
NK116(le)001:1370: gzugs la chags pa chen po yang //
NK116(le)001:1373: rtsa yig myu gu gtsang ma za //
NK116(le)001:1374: shin tu ring du 'gro nus pa //
NK116(le)001:1375: ri dwags rngon pas glu dbyangs kyis //
NK116(le)001:1376: nges par gsod pa tshol bar 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:1378: rtag tu nam mkha' la rgyu zhing //
NK116(le)001:1379: gzugs ni shin tu yid 'ong ba'i //
NK116(le)001:1380: bung ba dri yi nyes pa yis //
NK116(le)001:1383: bkag pa med pa'i lam 'gro zhing //
NK116(le)001:1384: rtag tu rnam par rgyu ba yang //
NK116(le)001:1385: ro myong pa la chags pa yis //
NK116(le)001:1386: nya ni lcags kyus brlag par byed //
NK116(le)001:1388: sa bsrung dang ni rab 'gran zhing //
NK116(le)001:1389: ri yi rgyal po rgyun shes pas //
NK116(le)001:1390: ba glang mo yi nye reg gis //
NK116(le)001:1391: ngees par glang po bsad par 'ong //
NK116(le)001:1393: de dag kun gyi bslu ba ni //
NK116(le)001:1395: skyes bu dag ni gcig la yang //
NK116(le)001:1396: lnga po 'di dag rtag ldan zhing //
NK116(le)001:1398: bde ba ji ltar thob par 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:1400: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal mthu che bar ston pa ni /
NK116(le)001:1401: srid pa'i zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1402: 'di ltar srida pa'i yul la 'phrad pa tsam gyis gzhom pa la thu ba gtum po me /
NK116(le)001:1403: khro ba'i mngona spyod ste drag shul gyi las rtsub mo ston pa gacana zana dang /
NK116(le)001:1405: rgyal po'i chada pa lasa myur ba'i /
NK116(le)001:1406: sdug bsngal snga ma'i rgyab nas phyi ma slebs shing brgyuda mas 'gro ba 'di rnams manra ro //
NK116(le)001:1407: phan gnod kyi yul la rgyu 'bras spyod pas sdug
NK116(le)001:1408: bsngal ba'i tshul bdag la zhes bya ba la sogs
NK116(le)001:1409: pa gsungs te / de la 'jig rten 'dir grags
NK116(le)001:1410: pa ltar thog ma med pa'i dus nas badga la
NK116(le)001:1411: madza'a bshesa sam mi mthuna pa dang nye du dang
NK116(le)001:1412: 'khona zla sogs bsam para mi nus pa ni /
NK116(le)001:1414: pha ni bu nyid ma nyid chung ma nyid //
NK116(le)001:1415: skye bo dgrar gyur pa yang bshes nyid dang //
NK116(le)001:1416: bzlog pa nyid du mchi bas de slad du //
NK116(le)001:1417: 'khor ba dag na nges pa 'ga' ma mchis //
NK116(le)001:1419: de dang de'i skabs matha'a dag tu semsa ldana gyisa lus thob pa'i rten de nyid kyis /
NK116(le)001:1422: 'di ni bar ma snyoms pa'i phyogas su blos kha
NK116(le)001:1423: bzung nas phana btags pa dang gnoda pa sbyin pa
NK116(le)001:1426: khyim bdag gcig la bsod snyoms bslangs bas /
NK116(le)001:1427: des dgra bo bu chung ngu gyur pa pang du thogs /
NK116(le)001:1428: pha nya ru gyur pa bza' zhing /
NK116(le)001:1429: ma khyir gyur nas nya rus 'cha' ba la brdeg pa gzigs nas /
NK116(le)001:1430: pha sha za zhing ma la brdeg /
NK116(le)001:1431: las ngan dgra bo pang du khur /
NK116(le)001:1432: chung mas khyo yi rus pa 'cha' //
NK116(le)001:1433: 'khor ba'i chos la gad mo bro //
NK116(le)001:1435: thog ma med pa nas lus grangs med pas sdug bsngal dmyong bas yun ring bar bstan pa /
NK116(le)001:1436: rdul phran zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1437: 'dir skye ba'i thog mtha' ring ba smos ci dgos te /
NK116(le)001:1438: sems can phra mo rdula phrana lta bu'i lusa kyi
NK116(le)001:1439: badga nyid gciga bu'i sroga gi rtena gzugas su gyur
NK116(le)001:1442: gzhan gyi mtshon cha sogs kyis mgo dang yan lag
NK116(le)001:1443: bacada gtuba bgyis so coga kun gcig tu spungsa na
NK116(le)001:1444: ri rab las mtho ba'i phyir lhun po'i che thanga
NK116(le)001:1446: da ni rigs drug so so'i chos nyid bshad pa la bstan bshad bsdu gsum gyi dang po ni /
NK116(le)001:1447: dmyal gnas zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1448: dmyal gansa su skyes dus zangas zhun khola ma dbang med du 'thungas pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1449: yi dwagas kyi lus su gyur dus rnag khrag dang /
NK116(le)001:1450: mi gatsanga ba zosa pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1451: rnam pa kun tu sduga bsngal gyi rgyu lasa mchi
NK116(le)001:1452: ma zaga pa gcig tu bsdoms na phyogsa matha'a gtuga
NK116(le)001:1453: pa'i chu klung dag lasa kyang manga ngo //
NK116(le)001:1455: gnyis pa so sor bshad pa la /
NK116(le)001:1456: khyad par zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1457: 'gro ba gzhan las khyad para dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal tshad meda de /
NK116(le)001:1458: phana tshuna gciga gis gciga mtshon sna tshogs kyis gsoda
NK116(le)001:1459: pa yang shi yang sos byed pas na yanga sosa
NK116(le)001:1460: la / de bzhin lus la thig naga pos drangs
NK116(le)001:1461: te soga lesa gshoga cing 'dral ba 'phral 'byar te
NK116(le)001:1462: sdug bsngal rgyun mi 'achada pas na thig nag go
NK116(le)001:1463: la / // bsdus 'jomas ni srog chags 'jigs pa'i
NK116(le)001:1464: mgo brnyan can gyi ri phan tshun 'dus par gyur
NK116(le)001:1465: pas bar du bcar ba dang tho basa phye mar
NK116(le)001:1467: khyim rim gcig gi nang du lcags kyi yol gor
NK116(le)001:1468: lcagsa zhun bskola bar 'tshoda cinga phyi rol nas mtshon
NK116(le)001:1469: la / // 'athaga pa'o // chas dabda pa'o // ngu 'boda kyi sgra sgrogas pa chen po ni //
NK116(le)001:1470: lcagas kyi khang khyima nyis rim 'abra bar bsreg pa'o //
NK116(le)001:1471: tsha ba ni lcags kyi gasla shinga 'abra basa lusa kun la 'bigas pa'o //
NK116(le)001:1474: lusa kyi gzhunga mas nas gyen du 'bigas pas phrag
NK116(le)001:1475: gong gnyis dang klad par zengs 'then te phyi nasa
NK116(le)001:1476: lcagas bsregas leb mo'i thag pas dkrisa shing /
NK116(le)001:1477: khro chu khola ma'i nang der 'tshoda pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK116(le)001:1479: lcagsa khyim shin tu 'bar bar 'di ni sreg byed
NK116(le)001:1480: kyi me dang 'di ni sreg bya'i sems can zhes
NK116(le)001:1481: gnyis su meda par bsregsa te /
NK116(le)001:1482: kun tu me'i phung po gcig gi klong na 'o dod 'bod pa tsam zhig go //
NK116(le)001:1483: de dag gi 'khor lhag pa nye 'khor ba bstan pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:1484: sdug bsngal zhes ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
