NK116(le)001:1485: nam zhig gong ltar myong bya'i las phal cher byang
NK116(le)001:1486: zhing sdug bsngal de nyid lasa dbugsa 'abyin cing bde
NK116(le)001:1487: ba'i go skabs btsal ba'i kun rtog gisa 'bros par
NK116(le)001:1488: brtsams pa na nye 'khora sgo 'aphara phye ba'i dang
NK116(le)001:1489: po madga me'i 'obas te thal tshan chu klung du
NK116(le)001:1490: 'khrul nas bsgal ba la sked pa la thug gi
NK116(le)001:1492: rus pa rnams kyang phye ste dral ba slar sos shing /
NK116(le)001:1493: 'gram dag na sngon rnam par brtsen pa'i gshin rje'i skyes bus bsrung bar snang ngo //
NK116(le)001:1495: phyi sa'i 'adma rdza ba sdug por tshud nas srog
NK116(le)001:1496: chags lus dkar la mgo bo gnag pa mchu rnon
NK116(le)001:1497: can gyis pags 'bigs shing lus rnyi dang 'dra ba
NK116(le)001:1498: la srog bya 'dra ba 'thogs nas sdug bsngal lo
NK116(le)001:1499: // gsum pa rala gri'i nagas tshal ni /
NK116(le)001:1500: rgyangs ring por nags tshal sngon po'i rnam pa mthong
NK116(le)001:1501: nas brgyug pas slebs pa na ljon shing rlung gis
NK116(le)001:1502: g.yos nas mtshon cha'i char dbab pas lus dbad par
NK116(le)001:1503: 'gyur ro // bzhi pa chu bo rab meda ni /
NK116(le)001:1504: thang thams cad spu gris btams pa'i dkyil nas bul tog tsha sgo can gyi chu tshan /
NK116(le)001:1505: rtsee gsum mdung thung mda' dang ral gri rnon pos
NK116(le)001:1506: gang ba bzod du med pa'i nang du 'tshod nas
NK116(le)001:1507: brlag par 'gyur ba gshin rje'i kha nang basa kyang
NK116(le)001:1508: thu'o // 'di rnams mnar med kyi phyogs bzhir bzhi tshan gyis yod pas na bcu drug go //
NK116(le)001:1509: bshad ma thag pa'i spu gri'i thang dang /
NK116(le)001:1510: 'chad 'gyur shal ma li gnyis gong gi bzhi bor
NK116(le)001:1511: mi bgrangs ba slob dpon blo gros chen pos kyang
NK116(le)001:1512: bstan pa la / snga ma spu gri'i thang rtsa bas ma zin cing /
NK116(le)001:1513: phyi ma sha ma li ni /
NK116(le)001:1514: mdza' gtsug ces bya ba la sogs gsungs bas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:1515: 'di snang khyo shugs sogs snying nye bas shal ma
NK116(le)001:1516: li'i sdong po'i rtser 'bod snang shar tshe mdza' gcug
NK116(le)001:1517: kyi dama baca'a drana nasa bsnyegsa la rings pasa phyin
NK116(le)001:1518: pa na / khyi bong bu lce spyang mang pos
NK116(le)001:1519: ded cing lam du lcags kyi tshe ra ma rnona
NK116(le)001:1520: po thur du gzings pasa tshabas chena phuga ba'i lusa
NK116(le)001:1521: khrag chal chil zag pa de la reg bya 'abra
NK116(le)001:1522: zhing rtsub pa'i lcags kyi khyo pho dang buda meda
NK116(le)001:1523: rang lus gang snang gis cig shos kyisa 'khyud nas
NK116(le)001:1524: sdug bsngal myong mathara yang sdong po'i rtsar 'bod snyams
NK116(le)001:1525: byung bas phyin pa na gong ltar tsher ma dang
NK116(le)001:1526: mdung thung sogs gyen du gzengs pas dbugs shing g.yang
NK116(le)001:1528: kha dang bya rgod la sogs pas miga la 'dru
NK116(le)001:1529: zhing rgyu lto 'dren pa sogs kyis sdug bsngal gyis
NK116(le)001:1532: kye ma rgyud tsha ba'i reg bya bzod du med
NK116(le)001:1533: pa 'di las ches grang na ci ma rung snyam
NK116(le)001:1534: pa'i yid smon gong ltar myong byed kyi rgyu bsrabs
NK116(le)001:1535: pa dang mtshungs ldan skye ba yin te /
NK116(le)001:1536: de la spyi mthun dang so sor bshad pa gnyis kyi /
NK116(le)001:1538: bu yug zhes bya la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1539: 'di ltar sa'i dkyil 'khor ldog pa bzhag pa tsam
NK116(le)001:1540: yang mi mngon pa'i gangs ri chen po gcong rong
NK116(le)001:1541: mi bzod pa can gyis ljongs su kha char dang
NK116(le)001:1542: 'thab pa'i bu yuga rab tu sbrebsa pa /
NK116(le)001:1543: 'dra ba'i lus shin tu bsil ba'i mthar thug pas
NK116(le)001:1544: ji ltar thag pa yisa ji bzhin bcingas te kum
NK116(le)001:1545: kum por gyur nas bskyod para mi nusa kyang /
NK116(le)001:1546: da dung sdug bsngal gyi tshor ba la rnam par shes pa 'thogs nas bzhina gsona por 'dra yanga /
NK116(le)001:1547: rlung gi nus pa rno ngar can gyi mtshona chasa
NK116(le)001:1548: rusa pa'i gting phug pa'i rkyen gyis granga pa'i reg
NK116(le)001:1549: bya so yi bar du 'tshira ba ltar gdungsa bas
NK116(le)001:1552: chu bur zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1553: ha cang grang ches pas lus chu bur gyis gang bas chu bura cana dang /
NK116(le)001:1554: de bzhin chu bur bardol nas rmar gyur ba dang /
NK116(le)001:1555: des a chu'i smre sngagas 'byin pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1556: kyi huda ces shugs ring 'byin pa tsam las skad gdangs chag pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1557: de'ang mi thon bas so 'tham 'athams pa cana dang /
NK116(le)001:1558: ut+pala ltar pagas pa druga tshala du gas pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1559: pad+ma dang ni pad+ma chena po ltar du brgyada dang
NK116(le)001:1560: bcu druga dang de nas nyer bzhi so gnyis phan
NK116(le)001:1561: chad nas grangas meda gas pa'i rmara /
NK116(le)001:1562: srog chagas mchu rnon cana gyisa 'bigas shinga baza'a bzhin par chu ser dang /
NK116(le)001:1565: de dag gi tshe tshad la sogs pa rgyas par gzhan nas gsal lo //
NK116(le)001:1566: yan lag nyi tshe ba bstan pa ni /
NK116(le)001:1567: 'gal dum zhes bya ba la sogs par gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1568: shing sdong ngam 'agla rdum bacada pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1569: gtub par byas pa la rang lus su 'khrul ba
NK116(le)001:1570: dang sgo 'aphara meda pa'i rdo dang brag la sogs
NK116(le)001:1576: sgo dang ka ba dang thab ka dang /
NK116(le)001:1577: thag pa sogas sna tshogas lasa kyisa sprul pa'i ranga
NK116(le)001:1578: gzugas ma dag gzhan dbang can mtha' dag gis rang
NK116(le)001:1579: gi phung por bltas te de la nye bar lena
NK116(le)001:1580: pa'i sduga bsngal zada mi shesa pa spyod dgos pa'i
NK116(le)001:1581: shes byed 'dul ba lung sogs su gsungs so //
NK116(le)001:1582: 'di ltar dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal bco brgyad po yongs su grags pa ste /
NK116(le)001:1583: gzhan du nam mkha'i snying po'i mdo las mnar med kyi 'khor bshad pa'i skabs 'di skad du /
NK116(le)001:1585: yon bdag dad pa can gyi yon blangs pa'i las
NK116(le)001:1586: kyis dmyal ba chung ngu rnams kyi nang du 'jug
NK116(le)001:1587: ste / de la dmyal ba grang sbrebs dang /
NK116(le)001:1588: dmyal ba mun nag pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1589: dmyal ba rab tu tsha ba dang /
NK116(le)001:1596: nags tshal ral gri'i so dang lo ma can dang /
NK116(le)001:1598: lcags kyi shal ma ri ka ba can dang /
NK116(le)001:1601: lcags kyi phug pa can dang /
NK116(le)001:1602: lcags kyi tho lu ma dang /
NK116(le)001:1605: zangs khol dang zhes pa la sogs kyang gsungs so //
NK116(le)001:1606: de ltar dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal gzhan pas ches zab pa ni /
NK116(le)001:1608: 'di na nyin gcig mdur thung sum brgya yis /
NK116(le)001:1609: rab tu drag btab sdug bsngal gang lags pa /
NK116(le)001:1610: des ni dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal chung ngu la'ang /
NK116(le)001:1611: 'ol yang mi bgyi char yang mi phod do //
NK116(le)001:1613: dmyal ba bris pa mthong dang thos pa dang //
NK116(le)001:1614: dran nam bklags dang gzugs su bgyis rnams kyang //
NK116(le)001:1615: 'jigs pa skye bar 'gyur na mi bzad pa'i //
NK116(le)001:1616: rnam smin nyams su myong rnams smos ci dgos //
NK116(le)001:1618: ngan song gzhan gnyis po le'u dang por mi khom
NK116(le)001:1619: par bshad zin pas zlos pa ltar bstan chos kyi
NK116(le)001:1620: skyon du dgongs nas 'dir sa bcad tsam las ma
NK116(le)001:1621: gsungs kyang / rgya cher 'grel du bshes spring gis bstan pa bzhin kho bos kyang de ltar bya'o //
NK116(le)001:1623: spyi dang bye brag gnyis kyi dang po ni /
NK116(le)001:1624: yi dwags na'ang 'dod pas phongs pa yis //
NK116(le)001:1625: bskyed pa'i sdug bsngal rgyun chags mi 'chos pas //
NK116(le)001:1626: bkres skom grang dro ngal dang 'jigs pa yis //
NK116(le)001:1627: bskyed pa shin tu mi bzad bsten 'tshal lo //
NK116(le)001:1628: re zhig spyi'i dbang du byas pa ni //
NK116(le)001:1629: yi dwags su skyes pa'i 'gro ba dag na'ang 'dod
NK116(le)001:1630: pas phongs shing de yis bskyed pa'i sdug bsngal ba'o
NK116(le)001:1632: bzlog pa'i thabs med pa ni mi 'chos pa'o //
NK116(le)001:1633: ha cang bkres pa dang skom pa dang grang dro mi snyoms pas gdung ngo //
NK116(le)001:1634: rtag tu zas skom 'tshol ba'i phyir du rgyugs pas ngal ba dang /
NK116(le)001:1635: gshed ma mang pos bdas par mthong bas 'jigs shing
NK116(le)001:1636: skrag pa de yis bskyed pa'i sdug bsngal yang shin
NK116(le)001:1637: tu mi zad pa bsten 'tshal lo //
NK116(le)001:1638: zhes bya ba'i tha tshig go //
NK116(le)001:1639: gnyis pa bye brag gi sdug bsngal bstan pa la /
NK116(le)001:1640: nang gi sgrib pa can ni /
NK116(le)001:1642: kha cig kha ni khab kyi mig tsam la //
NK116(le)001:1643: lto ba ri yi gtos rtsam bkres pas nyen //
NK116(le)001:1644: mi gtsang gyi nar bor ba cung zad kyang /
NK116(le)001:1645: 'tshal ba'i mthu dang ldan pa ma lags so //
NK116(le)001:1648: kha cig kha ni khab kyi mig tsam las med pas /
NK116(le)001:1649: lto ba ri yi gtos tsam zas phyir bkres pas nyen te /
NK116(le)001:1650: mi gtsang gyi nang bor ba'i gshang gci sogs cung
NK116(le)001:1651: zad tsam rnyed kyang kha'i sgo phra ba nyid kyi
NK116(le)001:1652: 'tshal pa ste za ba'i mthu dang ldan pa ma
NK116(le)001:1653: lags so // zas skoms kyis sgrib pa can ni /
NK116(le)001:1654: kha cig mtshan zhing kha nas 'bar ba ste /
NK116(le)001:1655: zas su 'bar ba'i khar babs bye ma 'tshal /
NK116(le)001:1656: kha cig mtshan mo re re zhing kha nas me
NK116(le)001:1657: 'bar ba'i steng du zas za ba'ang 'bar ba'i rang
NK116(le)001:1658: bzhin can khar 'bab ste gang na bye ma tsha
NK116(le)001:1659: ba 'tshal ba ste za bar byed do //
NK116(le)001:1660: spyi mthun gyi sgrib pa can ni //
NK116(le)001:1661: kha cig pags rus lus shing gcer bu ste /
NK116(le)001:1662: ta la'i yangs tog bsgams pa lta bu lags /
NK116(le)001:1663: kha cig pags rus gnyis kyi bar na sha med
NK116(le)001:1664: pas skems shing rid pa tsam lus shing gcer bu
NK116(le)001:1665: 'ba' zhig pa / dper na shing ta la'i yang togs te mgo bskams pa lta bu lags so //
NK116(le)001:1666: khyad par rmad rigs sam dmangs rigs zhes bsod nams chung ba'i mthar thug pa ni /
NK116(le)001:1667: dmangs rigs 'ga' ni rnag dang phyi sa dang /
NK116(le)001:1668: khrag sogs mi gtsang ba yang mi rnyed do //
NK116(le)001:1669: phan tshun gdong du btsog zhing mgrin pa nas /
NK116(le)001:1670: lba ba 'byung pa smin pa'i rnag 'tshal lo //
NK116(le)001:1671: yi dwags dmangs rigs 'gas ni mi rnyed do //
NK116(le)001:1672: gang na zas bzang po lta yang ci smos /
NK116(le)001:1674: khrag la sogs pa mi gtsang pa yang mi rnyed do //
NK116(le)001:1675: khros pa'i dbang gis lags nas dbyug pa phyung ste /
NK116(le)001:1676: phan tshun gcig gis gcig gi gdong du 'tshog cing brdegs res byed do //
NK116(le)001:1677: mgrin pa nas lba ba 'byung ba smin pa'i rnag
NK116(le)001:1678: khong du 'dzag pa rnams las zas su gzhan mi
NK116(le)001:1679: 'tshal lo // phyi'i sgrib pa can ni //
NK116(le)001:1680: yi dwags rnams la so ka'i dus su ni //
NK116(le)001:1681: zla ba'ang tshal dgun dus nyi ma'ang grang //
NK116(le)001:1682: ljon shing 'bras bu med 'gyur 'di dag gis //
NK116(le)001:1683: bltas pa tsam kyis klung yang skam par 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:1684: yi dwags rnams la tsha grang go ldog ste //
NK116(le)001:1685: so ka'i dus su ni zla ba'ang tsha la dgun ni nyi ma'ang grang bas gdung ngo //
NK116(le)001:1686: ljon shing gi 'bras bu phun sum tshogs pa yang
NK116(le)001:1687: snang ba med par 'gyur zhing 'di dag gis bltas
NK116(le)001:1688: pa tsam gyis yan lag brgyad ldan gyi chu klung
NK116(le)001:1689: yang thigs pa tsam yang ma lus par bskam par
NK116(le)001:1690: 'gyur ro // yang mkha' la rgyu ba'i yi dwags ni lus srul po dang ro langs dang /
NK116(le)001:1700: rgyal po sogs 'byung po'i rigs can ste /
NK116(le)001:1702: gang zhig byis pa rnam la 'tshe //
NK116(le)001:1703: sreng pas 'drid pa byed pa de //
NK116(le)001:1704: khong gi dri ma za byed pa'i //
NK116(le)001:1705: lus srul po ni skye bar 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:1707: sred dang seng sna'i skyon gyis ni //
NK116(le)001:1708: shi nas yi dwags skye bar 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:1711: yul gyi snang ba'i dron gcig la rigs drug so
NK116(le)001:1712: so'i las kyi bye brag la mthong tshul drug tu
NK116(le)001:1713: 'gyur ro // de yang las bzang ngan gyi bye
NK116(le)001:1714: brag gis mthong tshul bzang ngan sna tshogs par 'gyur
NK116(le)001:1715: 'gyur ro // ro // dper na snang ba'i don gcig pa la /
NK116(le)001:1716: las dman pas rnag khrag dang /
NK116(le)001:1718: bzang po'i mthus bdud rtsir snang ba lta bu'o //
NK116(le)001:1719: 'dir don gcig la mthong tshul tha dad du mi 'chad pa ni /
NK116(le)001:1722: dngos gcig yid ni tha dad phyir /
NK116(le)001:1723: zhes don gcig la mthong tshul drug tu bshad pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1725: chu snang ba gcig la rdzas tha dad drug yod
NK116(le)001:1726: pa la snang rung ma dmigs pas kyang gnod do
NK116(le)001:1727: // gal te las kyi phan tshun bsgribs pas mi mthong ngo zhe na /
NK116(le)001:1730: dgra gnyen gnyis kyis blta ba'i dus su yid du
NK116(le)001:1731: 'ong mi 'ong gi cha gnyis su gnas kyang gnyis
NK116(le)001:1732: kas gnyis ka mi mthong bar thal te /
NK116(le)001:1733: phan tshun las kyis bsgribs pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:1734: smra na khyod ji skad du /
NK116(le)001:1736: chu bab pa klung la yi dwags rnag blo yang /
NK116(le)001:1737: mdor na ji ltar shes bya med de bzhin /
NK116(le)001:1738: blo yang med ces don 'di shes par gyis //
NK116(le)001:1739: zhes gsungs pa'i dpe 'di dgos pa gang gi phyir
NK116(le)001:1740: du bkod pa'i don soms shig khyod ltar na dpe
NK116(le)001:1741: don mi mtshungs nyid du 'gyur zhing nyi ma la'ang
NK116(le)001:1744: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor mngon par 'char bar gyur tshe mun pa'i gnas med cing mi dmigs so //
NK116(le)001:1745: zhes gsungs pa dang yang 'gal lo //
NK116(le)001:1746: snang mun lhan cig mi gnas te 'gal bar yin par yang 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:1747: 'dod pa de ltar na don blo las tha dad
NK116(le)001:1748: du bden pa med pas shes byed du don gcig
NK116(le)001:1749: tha dad snang ba mi 'god par don rdzas drug
NK116(le)001:1751: yul rang ngos nas grub pa med ces smra ba yang brdzun du 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:1753: lcags bsregs sa gzhi su yis byas //
NK116(le)001:1754: me tshogs 'di dag ci las byung //
NK116(le)001:1755: de 'dra de dag thams cad ni /
NK116(le)001:1756: sdig sems yin par thub pas gsungs /
NK116(le)001:1757: zhes pa tsam yang rna bar ma grags par zad do //
NK116(le)001:1758: 'di 'dra ha cang blun pa'i mngon rtogs yin pas rna ba gtor tsam yang ga la bya /
NK116(le)001:1759: dud 'gro la yang spyi dang bye brag gnyis kyi dang po ni /
NK116(le)001:1761: dud 'gro'i skye gnas na yang gsod pa dang //
NK116(le)001:1762: bcings dang brdeg sogs sdug bsngal sna tshogs pas /
NK116(le)001:1763: zhi gyur dge ba spangs pa rnams la ni //
NK116(le)001:1764: gcig la gcig za shin tu mi bzad pa //
NK116(le)001:1766: gsum pa dud 'gro'i skye gnas na yang bde ba med de /
NK116(le)001:1767: de la gnyis kyi kha 'thor ni /
NK116(le)001:1768: bdag tu bzung min gang rung yang /
NK116(le)001:1771: brdeg pa sogs mi dang mi min gyis gnod byas pas sdug bsngal sna tshogs pa myong ngo //
NK116(le)001:1772: gang la na zhi ba myang 'das thob par 'gyur
NK116(le)001:1773: ba'i rgyu dge ba spangs pa ste snod du mi
NK116(le)001:1776: rgya mtsho chen po sogs su gnas pa ste phan
NK116(le)001:1777: tshun che bas chung ba gyur mid dang chung bas
NK116(le)001:1778: che ba 'bigs te gcig la gcig za ba sogs
NK116(le)001:1779: rnam smin shin tu mi bzad pa dang ldan no
NK116(le)001:1781: kha cig mu tig bal dang rus pa dang //
NK116(le)001:1782: sha dang pags pa'i ched du gsod par gyur //
NK116(le)001:1783: dbang med gzhan dag rdog pa lag pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1784: lcags dang lcags kyu 'debs pas btabs te bkol /
NK116(le)001:1785: ces kha cig ces pa so sor sbyar te /
NK116(le)001:1786: mu tig phyir du nya lcibs dang /
NK116(le)001:1787: bal phyir lug la sogs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1788: rus pa'i phyir tu glang po che sogs /
NK116(le)001:1789: sha'i phyir ri dwags sogs dang /
NK116(le)001:1790: pags pa'i ched du stag gzig sogs gsod par 'gyur ba dang /
NK116(le)001:1792: gzhan dag rta la sogs par rdog pas bkol ba dang /
NK116(le)001:1793: lags pas btab te bkol ba ma he /
NK116(le)001:1794: lcags gis bkor ba bong bu dang /
NK116(le)001:1795: lcags kyus bkor ba glang po la sogs pa 'debs
NK116(le)001:1796: sa pa dag gis btabs te las su rung ba
NK116(le)001:1799: de bzhin du klu rnams kyang 'gyur ba'i sdug bsngal dang /
NK116(le)001:1800: gdengs ka mang ba de tsam du //
NK116(le)001:1801: sdug bsngal de snyed bskyed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1802: kha gcig la bye tshan gyi char 'babs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1803: rang gi khyur mi tshud pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1804: nam mkha' lding gi 'jigs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1806: spyi mthun du rmongsa pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1807: tshe tshad ma nges mkha' lding rdzus skyes kyis klu rigs bzhi ka za sgong skyes rang mthun /
NK116(le)001:1808: mngal skyes kyi mngal sgong gnyis kar za /
NK116(le)001:1809: drod gsher skyes kyi rdzus skyes las gzhan gsum ka za'o //
NK116(le)001:1810: skyes ba bzlog pa'i thabs la 'bad par gdams pa ni /
NK116(le)001:1811: de phyir zhes bya la sogs par gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1812: de lta bu'i sdug bsngal chen po myong ba'i rgyu byed pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:1813: grangs med pa'i skye ba'i phreng ba gcong rong gi
NK116(le)001:1814: shwa 'oda brdol ba lta bu'i sdug bsngal gyi rba
NK116(le)001:1815: rlabas ca co sgroga pa can 'di myur bor ma
NK116(le)001:1816: bzloga na / lha basa lhag pa'i dpal 'byor gyi
NK116(le)001:1817: lusa rten chu lona te rag pa brtsegs pa lta
NK116(le)001:1818: bu 'di thob yanga brtan pa brala pa'i zhes bshigs
NK116(le)001:1819: nas srid pa'i mya ngana thanga du yang yang 'khyamsa
NK116(le)001:1820: bzloga na / par 'gyur ro // tshur 'dir ltos
NK116(le)001:1821: tshe mngon mtho'i go 'phang thob na bdag ci ma
NK116(le)001:1822: bzloga na / par 'gyur ro // rung snyam na
NK116(le)001:1823: / de yang rigs pa ma yin par gdam pa
NK116(le)001:1824: bzloga na / par 'gyur ro // rung snyam na
NK116(le)001:1825: / ni / gzugs med ces bya ba la sogs
NK116(le)001:1826: bzloga na / par 'gyur ro // rung snyam na
NK116(le)001:1827: / ni / pa gsungs te / gzugas meda kyi
NK116(le)001:1829: lunga ma bstan pa'i lasa yin phyir zad nas sad
NK116(le)001:1830: pa'i gnas skabs srid pa phyi mara 'adu byed pa
NK116(le)001:1831: dang / tshangs ris sogs gzugas khamas 'bras bu che
NK116(le)001:1832: ba'i bar yang 'chi ba'i tshe der 'phen byed kyi
NK116(le)001:1833: bsam gtan snga ma'i lasa zada de 'og ma 'oga
NK116(le)001:1834: mara ltung ba'i 'gyur ba'i sdug bsngal myong ngo //
NK116(le)001:1837: 'khora losa bsgyur ba sogs kyi mnga' thang yang /
NK116(le)001:1838: sprin bar nyi ma bzhina dakara po'i rnam smin gyisa
NK116(le)001:1839: re zhig thob zin pa'i skabsa batsala ba slar zad
NK116(le)001:1840: nas rgyu spangsa pa'i moda la mara me'i lces /
NK116(le)001:1844: de yang nang gses rnam grangs mang po'i nyes dmigs ston phyir /
NK116(le)001:1845: mnan na zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1846: blta na sdug gi gzhi rkang pas manna na nemas
NK116(le)001:1847: pa sor bzhi'i dma' bar 'gyur ba'i rega pa shin
NK116(le)001:1848: tu 'ajamas po la chags pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1849: lha dang klu dang mi'am ci'i mgo bosa la thoda
NK116(le)001:1850: sogs btsug gi rgyan gyis gang gi zhabs la gtug
NK116(le)001:1851: pa de'i 'od kyi rkanga pa'i chu skyes damra por
NK116(le)001:1852: snang bar byasa pa lha'i dabnga po brgya byin yanga
NK116(le)001:1853: phyi nas 'jig rten dmyal bo'i gnas su lcagsa kyi
NK116(le)001:1854: gasla shinga 'abra ba'i rtse mora 'dzer nas sdug bsngal
NK116(le)001:1855: gyis gdunga ngo // mtho risa su matshe'u dal gyis
NK116(le)001:1856: 'babs par lha'i bu mo'i nu ma gasla ba la
NK116(le)001:1857: gyis gdunga ngo // / rega pa'i 'khri shinga brtena
NK116(le)001:1858: te zhes lang tsho rab tu brtas pa'i reg byas
NK116(le)001:1859: gyis gdunga ngo // / / 'dod pa'i tsha ba bsil bar byed de bde ba myong bas na /
NK116(le)001:1860: reg bya 'khri shing la bkod la /
NK116(le)001:1861: gzhan yang dpag bsam shing gi dga' 'atshala dang /
NK116(le)001:1862: gazhala meda khanga bzang rab tu mdzesa pa mu tig
NK116(le)001:1863: gi dra ba dang dra ba phyed pa cana dril
NK116(le)001:1864: bu'i sgra snyan sgrogs pa sogs phun sum tshogs pa
NK116(le)001:1865: yang dbang med du spangas nasa me mura gyi 'obas
NK116(le)001:1866: nanga du spyi tshugs su ltung ba 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:1867: lha rnams la gnad 'chad pa'i tshor ba mod pas lus kyi sdug bsngal med kyang /
NK116(le)001:1868: 'chi 'pho'i snga ltas kyi sdug bsngal ston phyir /
NK116(le)001:1869: gos stan zhes bya ba la sogs par gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1870: lus kyi gzig brjid nyams pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1873: me tog gi phreng ba rnyingsa pa'i lha mo dag
NK116(le)001:1874: ni lus la sngan chad med pa'i rdul gyi chu
NK116(le)001:1875: zag nas gdonga ba bkru ba lta bu'i zola gyis
NK116(le)001:1876: mdzes pa'i nyams kun cig char zhiga nasa phyi ma'i
NK116(le)001:1877: skye gnas mig gis mthong bas basngangasa te nye du
NK116(le)001:1878: rnamas ring por phyog pa la blta zhing ngu ba
NK116(le)001:1879: de lta bu yi lha'i 'chi 'pho'i sdug bsngal lta
NK116(le)001:1881: 'di na mngon par 'phags pa'i nyi zla'ang sdug bsngal la 'thogs pa'i dus ston phyir /
NK116(le)001:1882: gnya' shing zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1883: ri gnya' shing 'dzina ri'i sa bla ste steng gi nam mkha'i lam 'gegas para byed pa yi /
NK116(le)001:1884: gdugs gyur snang byed chen po nyi zla gnyis kyis gleng gzhi'i mun pa gsal ba byed nus kyang /
NK116(le)001:1885: slana chada rten gzhan med khang pa'i 'od kyi brten
NK116(le)001:1886: pa lta bu gnyis po spangs ba'i tshe so sosa
NK116(le)001:1887: gling bar du mun pa'i smaga gisa gtams pa'i gling
NK116(le)001:1888: du brtsona du tshud par ltar gyur nas /
NK116(le)001:1889: rang gi lag pa brkyang bskums tsam yang mi mthong
NK116(le)001:1890: bas longa ba chena po'i gansa skabsa 'thoba para 'gyur
NK116(le)001:1892: lha min gyi sdug bsngal ston phyir //
NK116(le)001:1893: lha yi zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1894: lha yi dapala 'byor phun sum tshogs pa la sdang pa'i phraga doga gisa /
NK116(le)001:1895: dgra ltas ranga snying tshala par bkas nasa slara drag
NK116(le)001:1896: shul gyi dpunga pa gtum po'i g.yula chen po bshams
NK116(le)001:1897: pa'i ngor zhugs pa'i mod la badga nyid kyi /
NK116(le)001:1898: mgo dang yan lag rnams gtub pasa lha min rnams sdug bsngal gyis mnar ba'o //
NK116(le)001:1900: sdug bsngal gyi sdug bsngal dang /
NK116(le)001:1902: 'du byed kyi sdug bsngal te rtsa ba'i sdug bsngal chen po gsum /
NK116(le)001:1907: dgra mi sdug pa dang 'phrad pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1908: gnyen sdug pa dang bral ba dang /
NK116(le)001:1909: 'dod pa thog tu ma phyin pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1910: nye bar mi 'dod pa thog tu 'bab pa sogs
NK116(le)001:1911: nye bar len pa'i phung po lngas sdug bsngal gyi
NK116(le)001:1912: mtshan nyin 'dzin pas rnam pa brgyad kyis rtag tu
NK116(le)001:1913: mnar ba las / sdug bsngal gyi sdug bsngal ston
NK116(le)001:1914: phyir 'tsho ba zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs
NK116(le)001:1915: mnar ba las / te / 'tsho ba ste tshe
NK116(le)001:1916: srog glog gi rol rtsed dam chu bura lta bura
NK116(le)001:1917: mnar ba las / te / g.yo ba yi /
NK116(le)001:1918: mi daga ni bshad ma thag pa brgyad po'i gzeb
NK116(le)001:1919: tu tshud nas 'khor yul 'byams klas su yida mi
NK116(le)001:1921: sdug bsngal snga ma ma sang bzhin tu re mos
NK116(le)001:1922: su 'byung basa na phyi ma nye bar lena pa
NK116(le)001:1923: dpe ji ltar na mdze nad cana gyi thoga tu
NK116(le)001:1924: phola gyi rmasa gtugas pa bzhina gdung bar 'gyur ro
NK116(le)001:1926: mngon mtho zhes bya la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1927: 'di na mngona par mtho ba'i yona tan gyi kho lag rdzogs pa'i skyed mos tshala du /
NK116(le)001:1928: 'doda pa'i longs spyod kyi ro la gdungsa ba dang
NK116(le)001:1929: /'di ltar dug dang sbyar ba cana gyi baza'a basa
NK116(le)001:1930: rnama para sma phab pa ni /
NK116(le)001:1931: yud tsam la lus kyi madngas nyams /
NK116(le)001:1932: mig gi 'phang smad mal du 'dre ldog pa'i daka'a thuba kyis /
NK116(le)001:1933: dal ba'i lusa rten miga 'phrula lta bu lan cig
NK116(le)001:1934: thoba pa 'di skad cig gis 'gyur ba ste mi
NK116(le)001:1936: khyab pa 'du byed kyi sdug bsngal ston pa'i phyir skang ba'i zhes bya ba la sogs gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1937: ha cang bde ba'i tshad rkanga ba'ii rega pa tsam
NK116(le)001:1938: yang khur du mi bzoda pa'i skyo ngala dang bacasa
NK116(le)001:1939: pa'i semas kyis glanga po che'i ganya'a bar 'dzegas te
NK116(le)001:1940: song kyang glang mo'i dri phog pas de yis bsam
NK116(le)001:1941: pa brtse dagsa rab tu rgoda par gyur nasa brgyugs
NK116(le)001:1942: pas gayanga sa chen pora ltung la khad du lus
NK116(le)001:1943: shad smad pasa ni 'du byed kyi sdug bsngal mtshona
NK116(le)001:1944: no // skyes rabs kyi gtam rgyud dang sbyar de /
NK116(le)001:1945: 'od ldan zhes bya ba'i rgyal po'i khab tu /
NK116(le)001:1946: rgyal po rab gsal glang po'i gnya' ba la 'dzegs par spro nas 'dul sbyong mkhan la smras pa /
NK116(le)001:1947: ka ye shes par gyis shig /
NK116(le)001:1948: glang po'i mchog 'di ni bdag cag gi rkang ba
NK116(le)001:1949: sa la reg pa mi bzod pa'i bsod nams kyi
NK116(le)001:1950: mthus thob na khyod kyi 'di nyid 'dul ba 'dzin
NK116(le)001:1951: du chug cig / des kyang bka' bzhin 'tshal lo zhes khas blangs nas /
NK116(le)001:1952: lcags kyi tho lu ma me 'bar ba'ang snas tsham
NK116(le)001:1953: tshom med par len pa'i bsgo ba nyan pa de
NK116(le)001:1954: srid du 'dul ba 'dzin pa byas so //
NK116(le)001:1955: de nas rjes 'bangs gnyis glang po'i gnya' ba la
NK116(le)001:1956: zhon nas yul nye bar spyod pa'i skyo bsangs la
NK116(le)001:1957: spro bzhin tu / btegs pa na bdag nyid la
NK116(le)001:1958: sdug bsngal bsgrub pa'i rgyu thams cad bltar mi mngon
NK116(le)001:1959: pa 'dus byas pa nyid kyi phyir dang /
NK116(le)001:1960: glang po che gang dag ni thub pa mchog gis
NK116(le)001:1961: nyon mongs pa 'dul ba'i sdom pa'i sems ma dul
NK116(le)001:1962: la 'dul sbyong mkhan gyis lcags kyus lus btul pa
NK116(le)001:1963: tsam du gyur phyir glang mo'i dri bsnom pas brtse
NK116(le)001:1964: dgas yid rab tu rgod par gyur nas /
NK116(le)001:1965: sa gzhi thams cad shing rta'i 'phang lo bskor ba
NK116(le)001:1966: nyid dang 'khrul pa bskyed pa tsam du rgyug pas
NK116(le)001:1967: rgyal po rab gsal nyid srog dang bral ba la
NK116(le)001:1968: nye ba'i sdug bsngal thob pa lta bu ste /
NK116(le)001:1969: 'du byed kyi sdug bsngal 'di ni sems can thams
NK116(le)001:1970: cad la bltar mi mngon pa nyid du shes che
NK116(le)001:1971: bar yod par rig par bya'o //
NK116(le)001:1972: kha cig 'di ni 'gyur ba'i sdug bsngal las 'du
NK116(le)001:1973: byed mi 'thad ces mu cor smra ba ni rnam
NK116(le)001:1974: par ma brtags pa'i rtsing po'i gtam ste /
NK116(le)001:1975: g.yang sar gsod la khad kyi sdug bsngal gyi snga ma'i bde ba gzhig pa ni /
NK116(le)001:1976: de ltar 'dod na rang gi mod kyang /
NK116(le)001:1977: rkang pa'i reg pa tsam yang sdug bsngal du skyo nas /
NK116(le)001:1978: ha cang bde ba la mngon par sred de glang
NK116(le)001:1979: po zhon par 'dod pa'i dus su duhkha myong byed
NK116(le)001:1980: kyi rgyu 'dod chags bag nyal du yod pas sdug
NK116(le)001:1981: bsngal rang bzhin gyi yod pas der khyab pa 'du
NK116(le)001:1984: kho bos bzlog pa'i dus la bab par rig pas lan rgya cher bsnyad par bya'o //
NK116(le)001:1985: de ltar rtsa ba'i duhkha chen po gsum gyi steng
NK116(le)001:1986: du skye sogs rnam pa brgyad kyi sdug bsngal ba'i
NK116(le)001:1987: tshul bstan bshad kyi dang po ni /
NK116(le)001:1988: de ltar zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:1989: de ltar sduga bsngal nyid gsuma gyis 'byams klas su
NK116(le)001:1990: sha thang byed pa'i 'broga dgona pa na skye ba
NK116(le)001:1991: dang / rga ba dang na ba dang 'chi ba'i
NK116(le)001:1992: zug rdu'i sdug bsngal gyi tshora ba rtsub mo'i khri
NK116(le)001:1993: mun du rnama para 'khyamsa par 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:1994: gzhan yang smona pa meda pa'i mi sdug pa'i dgra dang 'phrada pa dang /
NK116(le)001:1995: 'bral mi phod pa'i sduga bsngal yida la bcags shing
NK116(le)001:1996: gomas par byas pa 'phar bzhin gansa mina te gzhan
NK116(le)001:1999: legs tshogs 'byor bas ngo tshara byas pa ste ring du bor ba dang /
NK116(le)001:2000: nye bar lena pa'i phunga po lnga'i steng du daka'a thuba ces mi mthun phyogs 'dusa pa dang /
NK116(le)001:2001: rnama pa brgyud kyis sduga bsngal brtul phoda pasa /
NK116(le)001:2002: mi yi skye ba'i khri shinga rtag tu yang dag par gtsera nas mnar ro //
NK116(le)001:2003: gnyis pa so sor bshad pa la /
NK116(le)001:2005: shin tu zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te //
NK116(le)001:2006: skyes ba'i gnas ni shina tu dri nga zhing mi
NK116(le)001:2007: gatsanga ba 'ba' zhig gi rnyog ma can kuna nas
NK116(le)001:2008: go skabs dog pa muna naga 'thiba po'i khroda de
NK116(le)001:2009: gang na mangla gyi gansa de dper na lcagsa khyim
NK116(le)001:2010: sgo 'aphara spangas pa lta bu nanga du ma riga
NK116(le)001:2011: pas dam la bzhag pa'i yid kyi rnam shesa 'khyams
NK116(le)001:2012: po de nyid pha ma 'khrig pa'i khu khraga gi
NK116(le)001:2013: dbus na brten bcas pa ni mer mer zhes bya
NK116(le)001:2014: ba la sogs par gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:2015: zhugs pa'i bdun phrag dang por ni /
NK116(le)001:2016: mera mera gya gyu ba dngul rdu'i rnams pa lta bu'o //
NK116(le)001:2017: gnyis pa nur nur po ngal snabs kyi rnam pa lta bu'o //
NK116(le)001:2018: gsum par ltar ltar po mdzub mo'i rnam par lta bu'o //
NK116(le)001:2019: bzhi par mkhrang 'gyur sgo nga'i rnam pa lta bu'o //
NK116(le)001:2020: lnga ba gora po khur ba'i rnam pa lta bu'o //
NK116(le)001:2021: drug pa khyab mjug nya yi rnam pa lta bu'o //
NK116(le)001:2022: bdun pa ru sbala bzhina te bdun phrag bdun /
NK116(le)001:2023: mgo dang rkang lag cung zad mngon pa'i bar du bduna phrag bdun dang /
NK116(le)001:2024: de nas bduna phrag nyi shu rtsa druga gi bar
NK116(le)001:2025: du rim bzhin gansa 'gyur te yida mi 'onga ba'i
NK116(le)001:2026: rnama pa de snyed mched la /
NK116(le)001:2027: mig sogs dabnga po'i rten dang /
NK116(le)001:2034: skra dang ba spu la sogas grub cing /
NK116(le)001:2035: de nas bduna phrag suma cu rtsa bduna gyi grangas
NK116(le)001:2036: rnyed pa'i tshe ma'i spyod lam bza' btung gi dwangs
NK116(le)001:2037: mas bu 'tsho zhing lus nyams brtas pa dang cher
NK116(le)001:2038: bskyed de skabs su ma yang lus su khye'u g.yo
NK116(le)001:2039: zhing 'gul ba sogs kyi tshor ba'i skyo bas gdung
NK116(le)001:2040: la / ma ya spyod lam dang bkres skom dang
NK116(le)001:2041: tsha grang dang bza' btung ga rnam 'gyura lasa byung
NK116(le)001:2042: ba'i sduga bsngal dapaga tu med pa bu la yang
NK116(le)001:2043: la / yod do // skabs 'dir phyin ci ma log pa'i 'du shes lnga 'byung ba ni /
NK116(le)001:2050: bdun phrag sum cu rtsa brgyad la batsa'a ba'i dusa
NK116(le)001:2051: kyi rjesa su 'gro ste rdzogs ma thag de yi
NK116(le)001:2053: lug lta bu'i ri bo'i bar du sen mos shig
NK116(le)001:2054: ltar 'thags pa dmyal ba bsdusa 'jomas khura du 'phosa
NK116(le)001:2055: pa lta bu'i sduga bsngal nye bar spyad pasa mtho
NK116(le)001:2056: batsams nasa / ma bu gnyis ka de'i mod la srog 'dora rama /
NK116(le)001:2057: ciga shosa gson na'ang gnyis kar bshad ma thag pa'i
NK116(le)001:2058: gnod pa brdo bzhin pa'i khura gyis non te phyir
NK116(le)001:2059: batsa'a / sngar mangla gyis gansa su khrag sogs rlona
NK116(le)001:2060: pasa dkrisa shinga dri nga ba can phyir byung tshe
NK116(le)001:2061: srana mi bzoda pa ni dper na pags pa bshus
NK116(le)001:2062: pa'am sha rmena zhiga pa lta busa sngona gyi mngal
NK116(le)001:2063: gnas su gtsog pa'i 'du shes kyi drana pa'i stobsa
NK116(le)001:2064: rnams yongs su nyamsa par byasa shinga khrus dang lag
NK116(le)001:2065: pas rega pa'i gnoda pasa shin tu gzira ba'i sduga
NK116(le)001:2066: batsa'a / bsngal myong ngo // zhes so //
NK116(le)001:2067: spro na dga' bo la mngal gnas bstan pa dang /
NK116(le)001:2068: mngal 'jug gi mdo ga nyis la gzigs pas gsal lo //
NK116(le)001:2069: gnyis pa la rga ba'i zhes bya la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:2070: skye bar srid do cog kun nges par rga ba'i
NK116(le)001:2071: chada pasa nona ma thag pa'i dus lus kyi langa
NK116(le)001:2072: tsho'i stobs la rgud pa'i nyamsa pa dang /
NK116(le)001:2073: yida mi bde ba'i khura babsa pasa yan lag yang
NK116(le)001:2074: bskyod pa'i mthu nyamsa te mkhar ba'i rten la rogs
NK116(le)001:2075: su bcol ba'i gazhana dabnga cana /
NK116(le)001:2076: 'gro ldoga gi skabs su lus 'dar zhing g.yo ba'i
NK116(le)001:2077: rkyen gyis gom pa 'khyal 'khyol byed cing lhu dang
NK116(le)001:2078: sor mo'i tshigas kuna rnam para 'gyura te 'khyogs pa
NK116(le)001:2079: dang dabnga po lnga nyams shing mi gsal bas kuna
NK116(le)001:2080: nasa sgrib ste 'doda pa yona tana lnga dang yula
NK116(le)001:2081: gyi phun sum tshogs pa'i longs spyod sprin gyis bakaba
NK116(le)001:2082: pa yi / tsha zera bzhina tu 'grib ste shes pa rmongas pa dang /
NK116(le)001:2083: blo groos kyi mthu nyamsa pa'i 'du shesa phyin ci
NK116(le)001:2084: logs su 'khrugsa pa'i mala du shin tu 'khyamsa par
NK116(le)001:2085: 'gyur ro // gsum pa bstan pa'i phyir rang bzhin zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:2086: rlung mkhris bad kan 'dus pa ste bzhi po ranga
NK116(le)001:2087: bzhina snyomsa par ldana tshe re zhig bde bde 'dra
NK116(le)001:2088: yang / 'byung ba 'phel zad kyis 'du ba'i rdzinga
NK116(le)001:2089: bu ni 'khrug pa'i rnyogsa pa cana du bgyid pas
NK116(le)001:2090: yang / na / na ba'i tshora ba yisa /
NK116(le)001:2091: phunga po lnga yi nyer lena gyi shugs duba ngal bar byas te gdung ba na /
NK116(le)001:2092: de lta bu'i sdug bsngal bar ma zad tshe srog
NK116(le)001:2093: 'tsho ba'i brtana pa dang bral te 'gro la thug
NK116(le)001:2094: par gyur to snyam pa'i dogsa pasa skrag cing dngangs
NK116(le)001:2095: pa yang su yis ldog pa mi 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:2096: bzhi pa srid pa la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:2097: srida pa'i dngos kun mtha' dag 'di na phyogs gcig tu spungs kyang sroga gi rina thanga la /
NK116(le)001:2098: thuga pa meda pasa 'phang sems can pa gang tshe
NK116(le)001:2099: 'chi bar byed pa'i pho nyas bzung ba'i sduga bsngal
NK116(le)001:2100: gyisa rnama para gtugas pa'i skyes bu dag gnyen 'duna
NK116(le)001:2101: dang / longas spyod lasa kha thala te sa tshugas med pa'i bar ma dor /
NK116(le)001:2102: skyabs mgon meda para tshor ba thams cad sdug bsngal /
NK116(le)001:2103: snang ba thams cad 'jigs skrag dang lhan cig para 'gro bem po tha gus bcings //
NK116(le)001:2105: dur khrodasogasa su bor ba'i skabs la soms shig ces so //
NK116(le)001:2106: lnga pa la mi sdug ces bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:2107: 'di ltar shes rab rnon po'i mthu med pa'i nyams
NK116(le)001:2108: chung byis pa gang zhig blang dor gyi cho ga
NK116(le)001:2109: 'khrug pas mi sduga pa'i yula te sgol ba'i phyogs
NK116(le)001:2110: kho na dang 'phrada pasa sduga bsngal gyi pho nyas
NK116(le)001:2111: dus rnama para gzira zhing rmada pa rnams ni /
NK116(le)001:2112: dper na khur gyis non pa'i skyes bu bde ba'i 'abbas stegas zhiga pa'i ngala gso ltar /
NK116(le)001:2113: bde bar dbugs 'byin nam yang thoba pa meda pasa lhag par nyen no //
NK116(le)001:2114: drug pa la rtsa ba bshad pa dang gtam rgyud
NK116(le)001:2115: bshad pa gnyis dang po byams sdug ces bya ba
NK116(le)001:2117: yid la byamsa shing sdug pa'i mdza' bshes kyi 'du 'bral gasla bar bkoda pa yi /
NK116(le)001:2118: phyogs la chags pa'i gdung ba phun sum tshogs pa'i
NK116(le)001:2119: longs spyod gzhan la ci yang mi bsam par sems
NK116(le)001:2120: khong du chud pas spro ba nyamsa te sdug bsngal
NK116(le)001:2121: pa'i daka'a thuba kyis non pa ni gzugas su gyura
NK116(le)001:2122: pa'i phyir du ste gang na /
NK116(le)001:2123: gzhon nu nora bazanga dri za mo yisa bor ba la /
NK116(le)001:2124: rje nyid 'dod pa'i dabnga du gyur ba'i dus na /
NK116(le)001:2125: bshul ba'i lam 'phranga 'jigs pa'i 'tshe ba sna tshogs
NK116(le)001:2126: kyis bakaba pa srog la brdos te dri za'i yul
NK116(le)001:2127: du phyin pa lasa kyang gzhan pa lasa kyi dbang
NK116(le)001:2128: gi bshes pa ring du phyogs pa'i ngogs mi sleb
NK116(le)001:2130: gnyis pa de'i gtam rgyud ni 'di ltar thos so //
NK116(le)001:2131: sngon gyis dus su yul rnga len zhes par grong
NK116(le)001:2132: khyer glang po'i khyim gyi rgyal srid kyi bdag por
NK116(le)001:2133: rgyal po nor can zer ba bu med pa zhig
NK116(le)001:2134: yod pa des 'jig rten lha la gsol ba btab
NK116(le)001:2135: 'bras kyis bu zhig yod pa de nyid legs par
NK116(le)001:2136: skyed bsring nas ming nor bzang du btags so //
NK116(le)001:2137: des kyang 'jig rten lugs kyi bstan bcos dang gnas
NK116(le)001:2138: rigs kun la byang bar byas te chung ma gsum
NK116(le)001:2139: dang lhan gcig brtse tshe skabs zhig tu rngon pa
NK116(le)001:2140: spangs leb can ri dwags bshol pa zhig ri bo
NK116(le)001:2141: gzhan zhig tu byin pa na lo ma dang myu
NK116(le)001:2142: gu dang me tog dang 'bras bu phun sum tshogs
NK116(le)001:2143: pa'i bsti gnas zhig na drang srong dka' thub la
NK116(le)001:2144: gnas pa zhig bzhugs pa mthong ba dang /
NK116(le)001:2146: khyed 'dir bzhugs nas ci tsam yin zhus pas /
NK116(le)001:2148: khyod yun ring de srid du 'dir sdod ring la
NK116(le)001:2149: ngo mtshar ba'i chos 'ga' gzigs lags sam zhus pas
NK116(le)001:2150: / drang srong gis rngon pa la khyod kyis mtsho ma ki mthong ngam dris pas /
NK116(le)001:2152: drang srong gi 'di ni tshangs pa 'dul ba'i rdzing zhes bya ste /
NK116(le)001:2153: me tog sna tshogs dang chu bya sna tshogs yod
NK116(le)001:2154: dri zhim pa'i me togs du mas bskor ba'i chu
NK116(le)001:2155: rdzing 'dir tshes bco lnga'i nyin mi'am ci'i rgyal po
NK116(le)001:2156: ljon pa'i bu mo yid 'phrog ma bu mo lnga
NK116(le)001:2158: khrus dang bku ma nye sna tshogs byed cing klu
NK116(le)001:2159: gar bro dang rol mo sna tshogs kyis yid 'phrog
NK116(le)001:2160: par byed do // kho bo yang de'i sgra thos
NK116(le)001:2161: pas dga' ba dang yid bde ba chen po skyes
NK116(le)001:2162: nas zhag bdun 'da' nus pa'i ngo mtshar de 'dra
NK116(le)001:2163: par byed do // mthong ngo // zhes gsungs pas /
NK116(le)001:2164: rngon pa de'i klu las don yod zhags pa thogs
NK116(le)001:2165: pa des yid 'phrog ma bzung snyams nas tshes bco
NK116(le)001:2166: lnga'i dus la bab tshe mtsho 'gram du 'khris nas
NK116(le)001:2168: ji zhig na yid 'phrog ma 'khor bcas byung nas
NK116(le)001:2169: khrus kyi bya bar 'jug par brtsam tshe rngon pas
NK116(le)001:2170: don yod zhags pas bzung ba dang 'khor rnams bros
NK116(le)001:2171: so // der mos rngon pa la ma rabs khyod
NK116(le)001:2172: kyis ngal ma reg cig zer bas rngon pas bu
NK116(le)001:2174: mos gtsug gis nor bu bkrol te rngon par gtad pa dang /
NK116(le)001:2175: de'i tshe gzhon nu nor bzang yang ri dwags basholabar
NK116(le)001:2176: der slebs pa dang 'phrad tshe rngon pas bu mo
NK116(le)001:2177: 'di gzhon nu la 'os so snyams te phul nas
NK116(le)001:2178: / gzhon nus brtags par bud med kyis skyon thams
NK116(le)001:2179: cad dang bral zhing yon tan kun tshangs pa thugs
NK116(le)001:2180: / su chud do // yid 'phrog ma brgyan dang
NK116(le)001:2181: bcas pa bzhes te glang po'i khyim gyi grong khyer
NK116(le)001:2182: du phyin nas pho brang gi rtse'i khang bzang zhig
NK116(le)001:2183: tu dga' mgur spyod cing gnas so //
NK116(le)001:2184: de'i dus bram ze gnyis ljongs rgyu la yong tshe /
NK116(le)001:2186: ci shos nor bzang la brten bcas shing /
NK116(le)001:2187: rgyal pos mdun na 'don byed du bcug cing longs
NK116(le)001:2188: spyod kyi skal pa yang byin rgyal bus longs spyod
NK116(le)001:2189: kyi skal pa tsam zhig byin pa dang /
NK116(le)001:2191: gzhon nu nyid rgyal por bzhugs tshe ngal ci zhig bgyi zhus pas /
NK116(le)001:2192: de ltar na khyod kyi grogs po yab kyi bgyi ba ci bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:2193: zhes gsungs pas rab rgyal pos mdun na 'don de'i
NK116(le)001:2194: thos tshe phrag dog skyes nas gzhon nu rgyal srid
NK116(le)001:2195: mi thob pa'i thabs bsam pa la /
NK116(le)001:2196: yul gzhan gyi ri bor pa zhes chom pos yul
NK116(le)001:2197: der gnod 'tshe byed pa zhig yod pa la de
NK116(le)001:2198: brlag pa'i ched du dmag gi dpung chen po zhig
NK116(le)001:2199: chas nas rgyal bu yang dmag dpon du btang thabs
NK116(le)001:2200: byas na de nas phyir ldog mi thub snyam nas
NK116(le)001:2201: rgyal po la g.yo thabs kyi de tshul zhus par
NK116(le)001:2202: rgyal pos de bzhin du bya'o //
NK116(le)001:2203: zhes gzhon nu mdun du bos nas de bzhin bsgos
NK116(le)001:2204: pas de kyang khas blangs nas 'gro grab la zhugs
NK116(le)001:2205: tshe yid 'phrog ma yid la bcags te 'phrad tsam
NK116(le)001:2206: byas nas mo'i gtsug rgyan gyi nor bu blangs te
NK116(le)001:2207: ma la gtad nas gal te yid 'phrog ma'i srog
NK116(le)001:2208: gi nyen pa'i gal la thug na 'di gtod min
NK116(le)001:2209: na ma byin zer nas dpung tshogs bzhi'i dmag dpung
NK116(le)001:2210: khrid nas phyin pas rgyal po'i bsod nams kyi mthu
NK116(le)001:2211: la rgyal chen rnam thos sras kyi grogs bgyid pa'i
NK116(le)001:2212: thugs bskyed nas gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon lnga len
NK116(le)001:2213: la khyod kyi dmag dpung khrid la ri bor pa
NK116(le)001:2214: rnams phob cig / ces bsgos pa bzhin du /
NK116(le)001:2215: de rnams cham la phab nas las rnams bsgos te /
NK116(le)001:2216: dpya thag bcad gati'u bzung ste dmag dpung phyir log tshe /
NK116(le)001:2217: rgyal po nor can gyi rmi lam na bya rgod
NK116(le)001:2218: gcig 'ong ste rgyal po'i lto dral nas rgyu ma
NK116(le)001:2219: drangs shing grong khyer gyi mtha' bskor ba dang rin
NK116(le)001:2220: po che sna bdun gyis khyim gang ba rmis so
NK116(le)001:2221: // der rgyal po shin tu skrag cing 'jigs nas
NK116(le)001:2222: bram ze'i 'dun na 'don la de tshul bshad pas
NK116(le)001:2223: // / de'i rmi lam de ni rgyal srid las
NK116(le)001:2224: nyams shing rgyal po'i sku tshe bar chod kyi ltas
NK116(le)001:2225: // / su nges so // zhus pas rgyal pos bzlog thub bam zer bar /
NK116(le)001:2226: bram zes bzlog thabs nus dang mi nus mang rabs
NK116(le)001:2227: las khyad par mi ma yin gyis tshil bdug na
NK116(le)001:2228: rgyal po skyon las grol lo zhes g.yo zol gyis
NK116(le)001:2230: rgyal pos de bzhin bsgrub rgyu byas nas gzhan rnams grub pa dang /
NK116(le)001:2231: mi ma yin gyi tshil gu'i ched du yid 'phrog
NK116(le)001:2232: ma bsad rgyur shom tshe gzhon nu'i mas gtsug nor
NK116(le)001:2233: bcol bar gtad de bros shig ces bsgos pa de
NK116(le)001:2234: ma thag tu nam mkha' la 'phul te bros nas
NK116(le)001:2235: sngon gyi bram ze de'i gam du phyin nas /
NK116(le)001:2236: khyod kyi bdag bstan pa mi'i lag tu song yang srog dang 'bral tsam du thar gyur pas /
NK116(le)001:2237: nga'i rjes su gzhon nu nor bzang sleb byung na
NK116(le)001:2238: sor gdub 'di gtod la kho mo'i rjes su lam
NK116(le)001:2239: bgrod par dka' bas ma 'ongs shig /
NK116(le)001:2240: gal te ldog ma nus na gtam 'di rnams zlos
NK116(le)001:2241: shig ces bram ze la smras nas mo rang bzhud
NK116(le)001:2242: do // de nas gzhon nu rang yul sleb tshe
NK116(le)001:2243: yid 'phrog ma bros pa'i gtam de go nas kun
NK116(le)001:2244: nas kun tu rgyu zhing 'tshol ba na bram ze
NK116(le)001:2245: des sor gdub gtad cing mo'i rjes su 'ong bar
NK116(le)001:2246: brtsom na bgrod daka'i tshul shod la phyir ldog thabs
NK116(le)001:2247: do // kyis / gal te nan gyis ma ldog na gtam 'di zlos byas la /
NK116(le)001:2249: ri'i rgyal po gangs can la /
NK116(le)001:2250: shing 'o ma 'dzag ces pa'i sman yod pas /
NK116(le)001:2251: de mar du btsos nas btung na skoms pa dang
NK116(le)001:2252: bkres pa med cing dran pa mthu stobs 'phel lo
NK116(le)001:2259: pi wang bcas bcang bar bya'o //
NK116(le)001:2260: zhes dang lam 'phrang gi 'jigs pa chen po so
NK116(le)001:2261: so la 'di dang 'di dgos kyi bslab bya bsnyad
NK116(le)001:2262: do // de nas bram zes bskad kyang ma nyan
NK116(le)001:2263: nas yid 'phrog mas bslab pa'i chas rnams thogs te
NK116(le)001:2264: bshul lam rim bgrod kyis ri dang /
NK116(le)001:2267: g.yang sa sogs 'jigs pa'i yul thams cad la sman
NK116(le)001:2268: dang gsang sngags dang sman dug bsal gyi sbyor ba
NK116(le)001:2269: sogs kyis rgyal bar byas nas mi'am ci'i rgyal po'i
NK116(le)001:2270: grong khyer nyer phyin pa dang /
NK116(le)001:2271: der khrus kyi rdzing bu dpal yon gyis brgyan par
NK116(le)001:2272: mi'am ci mo rnams chu len du 'ong bar gzhon
NK116(le)001:2273: nus / chu mang po 'dis ci byed dris par
NK116(le)001:2274: yid 'phrog ma'i khrus chu yin pa zer byung nas
NK116(le)001:2275: nus / / gzhon nus sngon gyi sor gdub de
NK116(le)001:2276: bum pa zhig tu mi mthong bar bcug nas bum
NK116(le)001:2277: pa 'dis sngon du khrus gyis shig bsgo bas des
NK116(le)001:2278: kyang de la don cig yod snyams nas khrus bgyis
NK116(le)001:2279: nus / / par / ji zhig na sor gdub lhung byung bas mkhrig nas /
NK116(le)001:2280: chu blangs sar mi zhig 'ongs sam dris pas 'ong zer /
NK116(le)001:2281: de khrid la dben pa zhig tu zhog zer ltar byas so //
NK116(le)001:2282: der yid 'phrog mas zhu ba sna tshogs phul mthar
NK116(le)001:2283: yab kyi gzhon nus tshod 'gom shing nyams sad pa'i
NK116(le)001:2284: las mang po byas kyang de rnams las rgyal nas
NK116(le)001:2285: mthar yid 'phrog ma 'khor stong gis bskor ba brgyan
NK116(le)001:2286: yongs kyis spud nas rin po che'i skyes dang bcas
NK116(le)001:2287: te gzhon nur byin nas yul der re zhig bzhugs
NK116(le)001:2288: 'jag gnang mthar mi'am ci'i rgyal po dang bgros te
NK116(le)001:2289: nam mkha'i lam nas mi'am ci'i shugs kyis bstod nas
NK116(le)001:2290: glang po'i khyim gyi grong khyer du sleb bo //
NK116(le)001:2291: der ngal sos pa dang yab rgyal po'i drung du
NK116(le)001:2292: phyin nas de lta bu'i lo rgyus rnams zhib tu
NK116(le)001:2293: zhus bas rab tu mnyes nas gzhon nu rgyal sar
NK116(le)001:2294: bkod pa dang / gzhon nus sngon bsod nams bsags
NK116(le)001:2295: pa'i stobs kyis de ltar byung ba yin par shes
NK116(le)001:2296: nas lo bcu gnyis su gtan pa med pa'i mchod
NK116(le)001:2297: sbyin rgya chen byas pa grags so //
NK116(le)001:2298: kha cig nor bzang rgyal ba'i rnam sprul yin pas
NK116(le)001:2299: sdug bsngal 'di gsal byed du bkod pa mi 'thad
NK116(le)001:2300: zer bas ngag 'phros rgyangs nas thos kyang /
NK116(le)001:2301: blun po'i rang mtshan grub pa'i nang cha ngoms pa la su yid rton /
NK116(le)001:2302: kun mkhyen chos rje 'di rgya gar shing rta chen
NK116(le)001:2303: po rnam gnyis dang lung rtogs mnyam par khyod cag
NK116(le)001:2304: gis dpyad pa tsam bzod ma nus pa ga la
NK116(le)001:2305: yin / slob lam la gnas pa'i byang chub sems
NK116(le)001:2306: dpa' chen po'ang 'dod pa'i phyir 'di ltar gyur na
NK116(le)001:2307: gzhan pa la lta ci smos /
NK116(le)001:2308: 'on kyang 'jig rten bya ba zin dus med pas
NK116(le)001:2309: spang bar rigs zhes gdams pa 'di 'thad pa las
NK116(le)001:2311: bdun pa la 'dod pa'i zhes bya la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:2312: sngon bsags nams zhan pa'i stobs kyis 'doda pasa longas
NK116(le)001:2313: pa dang dbul ba'i skyes bu rnams ni bkresa bar
NK116(le)001:2314: zas dang skom par btung ba'i dona la grub ma
NK116(le)001:2315: grub pa'i re dogs kyis zho shas 'tsho bas gazhana
NK116(le)001:2316: dabnga kho nara lus ngaga chuda du gsona pa'i tha
NK116(le)001:2317: shal gang zhig sdug bsngal ba'i tshad sa la rgyu
NK116(le)001:2318: pa'i yi dwagsa dngosa dang mtshungs na 'dod ba'i nyes
NK116(le)001:2319: dmigs bsam nas chog shes pa 'byor ba'i yang rtse
NK116(le)001:2320: yin no // brgyad pa sdug bsngal de dag nye
NK116(le)001:2321: bar len pa sogs phung po lnga yin par ston
NK116(le)001:2322: yin no // pa'i phyir // gzugs la zhes bya la sogs par gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:2323: gzugsa kyi phung po la brten bacasa shing tshora bas bde sdug bar ma'i ranga bzhina shesa te /
NK116(le)001:2324: 'du shes dge min gyis lasa de rgyun chagsa /
NK116(le)001:2326: phyin chad skye ba'i sa bon bkruna pa dang /
NK116(le)001:2327: rnam shes kyisa sdug bsngal nyamsa su myong ba'i nye bar lena pa po byed do //
NK116(le)001:2328: des na phunga po lnga bo 'di daga sdug bsngal rnams ma lus pa kuna gyi 'phyung gnas dang /
NK116(le)001:2329: kuna gyi rten dang snod dang kun gyi rgyu dang
NK116(le)001:2330: 'abras bu dang badga pora byed pa mkhyen par 'atshala
NK116(le)001:2331: nasa / kuna 'byung ba'i rgyu lasa dang nyon mongas pa spang bar 'atshala lo //
NK116(le)001:2332: mi mthun phyogs la rgyang bsrings nas /
NK116(le)001:2334: de ltar zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:2335: de ltar spangsa nas skyes bu 'bringa po nyan rang gi lam sdug bsngal shes par bya //
NK116(le)001:2339: bdena pa bzhi yi shinga rta la zhona pa rnams
NK116(le)001:2340: 'goga pa'i mthar thug pa mngona du gyur te lhag
NK116(le)001:2341: med du mya ngana las 'adsa pa'i dbyings su zin
NK116(le)001:2342: nas slar bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rgyal ba'i khamas
NK116(le)001:2343: thara pa mchoga gi go 'aphanga nyid du 'gro'o //
NK116(le)001:2344: 'di ltar chos thams cad rten cing 'brel bar 'byung
NK116(le)001:2345: ba ston phyir rten chos zhes bya ba la sogs
NK116(le)001:2346: pa gsungs te / rten cing 'brel ba 'khor ba'i chosa kuna gyi rtsa ba ma riga pa ste /
NK116(le)001:2350: de lasa skye shinga mcheda pa rnama pa drug dang /
NK116(le)001:2356: sreda lasa skye ba ste skye ba yoda phan chad na 'doda pasa phongas pa dang /
NK116(le)001:2358: na ba dang rga ba dang 'chi ba sogas sdug
NK116(le)001:2359: bsngal gyi phunga po shina tu gtos che ba gruba
NK116(le)001:2360: pa'i phyir na / bden bzhi lugs su ldog ste
NK116(le)001:2361: skye ba 'agga par byas pasa 'khor ba'i chos thams
NK116(le)001:2363: rtena cinga 'brela bar 'byung ba'i rgyu 'brasa zaba mo 'di ni /
NK116(le)001:2364: rgyal ba bdena para smra ba'i gsunga gi mdzoda /
NK116(le)001:2365: yin pas gces par zungs shig ces so //
NK116(le)001:2366: spong byed kyi gnyen po mthar thug pa ston phyir /
NK116(le)001:2367: de ltar zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:2368: de lta mod kyi srida pa 'du byeda pa'i /
NK116(le)001:2369: mtho damna gyi gnas rigs su 'phen pa'i las dang
NK116(le)001:2370: dakara naga ste dge sdig gi rgyu dang 'brasa bu'i
NK116(le)001:2371: chosa kuna lasa 'adsa pa zhi ba dama pa'i dngosa
NK116(le)001:2372: po gang zhig bsnyen pa gang zhig gzhan gyis ma
NK116(le)001:2373: yin te skye ba meda pa'i chosa nyid rtogsa pa
NK116(le)001:2375: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi le'u bzhi ba'i 'grel ba'o ////
NK116(le)001:2376: mchog gi 'jug ngogs kyi thog mar 'khor lo chen
NK116(le)001:2377: po bzhi la bstan bshad gnyis kyi dang po ni
NK116(le)001:2378: / yul ni zhes bya ba la sogs par gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:2379: sdig grogs sogs chos kyi gegs su gyur pa'i 'tshe
NK116(le)001:2380: bas dben pa'i yula ni mthuna para gyur ba 'chad
NK116(le)001:2382: lung dang rtogs pa'i chos kun gyis 'byor ba'i skyes
NK116(le)001:2383: bu dama pa bstena pa lasa yona tan mtha' dag
NK116(le)001:2384: 'thoba pa dang / ji skad bshad pa'i don rab
NK116(le)001:2385: tu bsgrims te bsgrub pa legas para smon pa dang
NK116(le)001:2386: 'thoba pa dang / / rgyu 'bras la yid ches
NK116(le)001:2387: te bsoda namas dang ye shes kyi tshogs zung bsags
NK116(le)001:2388: pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i bar skyabsa yul gyis 'duna
NK116(le)001:2389: ma ste bzhi po de la 'khor lo chena po
NK116(le)001:2390: bzhi zhesa klu'i dabnga pos bzheda do //
NK116(le)001:2391: de la 'khor lo ci'i phyir smos snyam na /
NK116(le)001:2392: glang po che sogs sems can phal gyis nyin zhag
NK116(le)001:2393: tu mar bgrod pa'i bshul lam 'khor lo bzhi'i khrul
NK116(le)001:2394: 'khor dang ldan pa'i shing rtas bgrod pas yud tsam
NK116(le)001:2396: thams cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang la 'phags pa'i lam
NK116(le)001:2397: gyi shing rtas bde blag bgrod pas tha snyad chags
NK116(le)001:2398: so // gnyis pa bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK116(le)001:2400: dang po yul ston pa la 'du 'dzi las ring
NK116(le)001:2401: du phyogs pa'i phyir tshogs kyi zhes bya ba la
NK116(le)001:2403: 'di ltar byis pa sgo gsum las su ma rungs
NK116(le)001:2404: pa dag tshogas te kha na ma tho ba'i las
NK116(le)001:2405: kyi mtha' la bsten nas dus 'da' pa'i dbus na
NK116(le)001:2406: duga cana gyi zasa lta bu ste /
NK116(le)001:2407: yula gzugs sgra dri ro reg lnga dang /
NK116(le)001:2408: rkyen chags sdang bar ma gsum gyisa blang dor byed
NK116(le)001:2409: pa'i rnama 'gyur shina tu rgoda pa'i spyir rnam pa
NK116(le)001:2410: kun tu bslu bar 'gyur bas na /
NK116(le)001:2411: de lasa bsringas nasa rang gcig pura dben pa'i gnas su rnam rtog zhi ba'i thabs la mosa bzhin /
NK116(le)001:2412: rnyed la ma chagas pa nam mkha'i rlung dang gnas
NK116(le)001:2413: dang 'tsho bar bdag bzung med par mkha'a la lding
NK116(le)001:2415: de lta'i bya ba la zhugs min gyi yon skyon bstan phyir /
NK116(le)001:2416: ri dwags zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:2417: ri dwagas bzhina du dbena para gcig pur gansa pa
NK116(le)001:2418: de nyid sgo gsum bab bcola gyi spyod pasa gzu
NK116(le)001:2419: lum can gang gis 'khruga para mi 'gyur la /
NK116(le)001:2420: cig shos gzhi la rtag tu brten na bdag nyid
NK116(le)001:2421: bsrung ba'i slad du gazhana gyi ngo bsrung dgos pa
NK116(le)001:2422: dang / dpya dang khral gyis gdung ba sogs dang /
NK116(le)001:2423: gal te mi chos lugs bzhin spyad kyang snyigs dus
NK116(le)001:2424: kyi sems can shin tu mi bsrun pas phrag pa
NK116(le)001:2425: doga ste tho mtshams pa'i rkyen gyis bdag gi bzoda
NK116(le)001:2426: pa'i snying stobsa bri bar 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:2427: sgo gsum las sems gtso phyir yid ni zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:2428: 'di ltar sems shin tu ma rungs pa 'ba' zhig
NK116(le)001:2429: pas na yida ni shina tu ringas pa'i ste gang
NK116(le)001:2431: de ltar tshul 'chos mkhan yanga gzhan ngor dal bu'i
NK116(le)001:2432: dal bur rgyu ba'i 'gro 'duga zhi zhing spyod lam
NK116(le)001:2433: ngesa pa ltar snang yang yid rton mi rigs te
NK116(le)001:2434: / sdig pa'i las la mngon par phyogs pa'i grogas
NK116(le)001:2435: kyisa baga phebas par brtena pa'i yul du gnas na
NK116(le)001:2436: / / thar ba'i skyabs yul phuna suma tshogas kyang
NK116(le)001:2437: phyir phyogs te rang gi chos bsgrub pa'i gzugs brnyan
NK116(le)001:2438: gyi lasa 'phrala du nyamsa te 'jig go //
NK116(le)001:2439: gnas res mos su barje ba la dgos ched ston
NK116(le)001:2440: phyir bskyod pa zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs
NK116(le)001:2441: te / nyin zhag re re bzhin 'pho bas na
NK116(le)001:2442: bskyod pa yangas ba'i nyi zla lus can kuna dang
NK116(le)001:2444: yul gcig tu mchog dman kun dang 'drisa shinga gnyuga
NK116(le)001:2445: mara zhes rgyun du gansa pa dag ngo 'dzin gyis
NK116(le)001:2446: sun te phan tshun khro bas gdunga bar 'gyur phyir
NK116(le)001:2447: / gasra ba gasra bar gyur pa'i yula dang mi rnams 'ajama zhing /
NK116(le)001:2448: skye bo kuna kyang mdza' bshesa para gyura ba ni chos nyid yin /
NK116(le)001:2449: skyes rabs sogs su gsungs par ma zad mthonga chos su'ang snang ngo //
NK116(le)001:2450: snying stobs go cha btsan po gyon pa gang zhig rkyen gyis mi bardzi ba ni /
NK116(le)001:2451: sems ldan zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:2452: 'di ltara dam pa rnams ni semas ldana so so'i
NK116(le)001:2453: skye bo lta bura re 'ga' ca co sgrogsa par
NK116(le)001:2454: 'gyur yanga / brjod pa bazanga ngana la ltos pa'i
NK116(le)001:2455: re dogs kyi rjesa su de'i semsa 'gro ba ma
NK116(le)001:2456: 'gyur yanga / yina pa ni / dper na brag
NK116(le)001:2457: cha ji bzhin rjes su rtog pa cung zad kyang
NK116(le)001:2458: med de de lta bu yi kun spyod cana la
NK116(le)001:2459: yul rkyen gyis bkol bar mi 'gyur bas dama baca'a
NK116(le)001:2460: 'gyur yanga / yina pa ni / bral ba'o //
NK116(le)001:2461: de las gzhan pa rnams ni rkyen gyis bsgyur tshul
NK116(le)001:2462: skyes bu zhes pa la sogs gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:2463: de la skyes bu tshangsa para zhes mya ngan las 'das pa'o //
NK116(le)001:2464: de'i ched du spyod pas na mtshungsa para spyod pa rnams dang /
NK116(le)001:2465: bsam gtan gyi dona la rtse gcig tu semas pa
NK116(le)001:2466: yi ting nge 'dzin gyi ched du gnyer pa gang
NK116(le)001:2467: zhig brtul zhugsa nyams myong brtan para ma sona pa
NK116(le)001:2468: ganga dang ganga zhes su yang rung ste yul dang
NK116(le)001:2469: grogas dag chos dang mthun min la brten nasa dge
NK116(le)001:2471: mtsho ba yang dag yin min blang dor ston phyir
NK116(le)001:2472: ston pas zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te
NK116(le)001:2473: / bya ba rung min ji bzhin ston pa 'jig
NK116(le)001:2474: rten gsum gyi mgon pos gannga para gyur pa gang
NK116(le)001:2475: zhig gis gazhana 'gro ba yongs kyi /
NK116(le)001:2477: badga kyang dka' thuba ste sdom pa nyamsa pa mi
NK116(le)001:2478: 'gyur pa chos nyid yin la des na ji ltar
NK116(le)001:2479: slong ba rnams kyis yida bzhina nora bu lta bur
NK116(le)001:2480: thar ba'i gsos su mthuna para gyur pa'i 'tsho ba
NK116(le)001:2481: bsoda snyomsa kho na yina no //
NK116(le)001:2482: de las ldog pa log pa'i 'tsho ba lnga ni ma dag pa dmigs gsal ste /
NK116(le)001:2483: 'tsho ba zhes bya ba la sogs par gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:2484: 'tsho ba shina tu ma dag pa ni /
NK116(le)001:2485: ster du re ba'i gzhog slong gis nyams nga ba'i skad 'don pa'am /
NK116(le)001:2486: zas gos yod pa phag tu sbas nas mu to
NK116(le)001:2487: ba'i tshul bstan te blangs pa thams cad thabsa kyisa
NK116(le)001:2489: bza' btung phra mo bag re btang nas tshur mang
NK116(le)001:2490: po sdud pa'i thabs la brtson pa rnyed pasa rnyed
NK116(le)001:2491: pa tshola ba'o // 'thob par dmigs nas rang gi
NK116(le)001:2492: basngagasa pa dang rnam dkar gyi yon tan bshad pas
NK116(le)001:2493: blang ba kha gasgas gis 'tshol pa'o //
NK116(le)001:2494: so byang sngags gsum gang rung gi yon tan sna
NK116(le)001:2495: gcig kyang med bzhin yod pa ltar bardzusa nas snyed
NK116(le)001:2496: pa tshul 'tshosa zhes bya ba dang bdag la yon
NK116(le)001:2497: bdag 'di zhes bya bas rdzas 'di tsam byin ste
NK116(le)001:2498: / byin pa de yang de ga'i ched du yul
NK116(le)001:2499: gnyen po la mchod sbyin btang ba skad kyi thoba
NK116(le)001:2500: kyis 'ajala pa'i log par 'tsho ba ste rnama pa
NK116(le)001:2501: de lngas rnyed pa thob pa ni dug las kyang
NK116(le)001:2502: thu ste ngan song gi rgyu rngam po che yin
NK116(le)001:2503: pas dranga sronga ste sngon rgyal ba sras bcas rnamas
NK116(le)001:2504: kyi brtula zhugas gang rang gis nus tshod blangs pa
NK116(le)001:2506: de'i phyir na gansa mala bzang po bsam gtan gyi tsher ma med pa'i dben gnas dang /
NK116(le)001:2507: 'tsho ba bazanga po sman shing me tog sogs kyis bcud len slong mo sogs dang /
NK116(le)001:2508: grogas bazanga po chos dang mthun pa dang /
NK116(le)001:2509: sbyor ba bazanga po thos bsam bsgom pa'i lam la
NK116(le)001:2510: yang yang brtson pasa rgya cher spyod pa'i phyogs su
NK116(le)001:2512: zhes pa'i bar gyis 'khor lo dang po bstan to //
NK116(le)001:2513: skyes bu dam pa bsten pa'i tshul rgyas par bstan
NK116(le)001:2514: pa'i phyir bslab pa zhes bya ba la sogs pa
NK116(le)001:2515: gsungs te / rnam grol lam gyis bslab pa'i gnas
NK116(le)001:2516: kuna gyi yon tan rang rgyud la byang chub par
NK116(le)001:2517: rdzogas pa'i phyir du 'og nas ston pa'i mtshan nyid
NK116(le)001:2518: dang ldan pa'i skyes bu dama pa dag la brten
NK116(le)001:2519: para bgyid dgos te ji ltar lho phyogs ma la
NK116(le)001:2520: ya yi tsan+dana gyi nagas klung ltug po gang du
NK116(le)001:2521: rnama para 'khyamsa pa'i sdoda duma phala ba yanga ji
NK116(le)001:2522: zhig na yala 'adba brlan ba'i tsan+dana gyi dri ngad
NK116(le)001:2523: bsunga pos de la bgos pa ltar gyur nas mchog
NK116(le)001:2524: dman 'khrul ba bskyed pa yod pa de bzhin ganga
NK116(le)001:2525: la bsten pa'i skyes bu de yi rjesa su 'gro'o
NK116(le)001:2526: gsungs te / // bsten bya'i mtshan nyid ni dam pa'i zhes bya ba la sogs par gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:2527: sngon rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang sar gnas kyi byang
NK116(le)001:2528: sems sogs yon tan mngon sum snang ba dag byon
NK116(le)001:2529: la dengs skabs dama pa'i chosa tshul ji snyed matha'a
NK116(le)001:2530: daga par rdzogas pa'i bshes gnyen ni snyigsa ma lnga'i
NK116(le)001:2531: mthusa bslad par byas te rnyed para daka'a ste /
NK116(le)001:2533: de lta'i yon tan ma lus pa ldan pa dag /
NK116(le)001:2534: rtsod pa'i dus na shin tu dkon pas na //
NK116(le)001:2535: yon tan phyed dam bzhi cha brgyad cha can //
NK116(le)001:2537: gal te re 'ga' srid kyang sbas tshul du yod pas dpyad daka'o //
NK116(le)001:2539: sdoma pa zhes tshul khrims gsum gyi gannga bakaga gtsang ma'i sa gzhi lta bu la /
NK116(le)001:2541: snying rje chen posa thugas rgyud rab tu brlan zhing sde snod gsum dang /
NK116(le)001:2542: khyad par sngagas phyi nang gi rgyud sde rgya mtsho'i
NK116(le)001:2543: cho ga nyams su bltar ba la makhasa shing nyon
NK116(le)001:2544: shes kyi sgrib pa spangs te rtogsa pa'i ye shesa
NK116(le)001:2545: dri ma meda pa'i 'brasa busa phyug cing /
NK116(le)001:2548: don dang mthun par bsgrub pa /
NK116(le)001:2549: gdul bya'i don la spyod pa ste bsdu ba'i dngosa
NK116(le)001:2550: po bzhi yi me tog gi rnam par bkra basa
NK116(le)001:2551: / dad dam dang ldan ba'i skal pa bazanga po'i
NK116(le)001:2552: slob ma'i bunga ba sdud pa la ched du brtson
NK116(le)001:2553: pa'i dam pa gang zhig la brten par rigs so
NK116(le)001:2554: / // de dag las kyang gsang sngags ston pa'i
NK116(le)001:2555: bla ma ni khyad par man ngag zhes bya ba
NK116(le)001:2557: khyad para rgyud lung rgya cher gting dpog dka' ba
NK116(le)001:2558: bde blag tu rtogs pa'i phyir du grub thob rnams
NK116(le)001:2559: kyi mana ngaga gnad du dril ba ji bzhin par
NK116(le)001:2560: ston pa'i bla ma dam pa ni /
NK116(le)001:2561: phan nus zab mo gsum gyis dabnga thoba pas smin
NK116(le)001:2562: cing dama tshiga la tshul bzhin gansa te shina tu
NK116(le)001:2563: zhi zhing gzhi lam 'brasa bu gsum ston pa'i rgyud
NK116(le)001:2564: sde thos shing dona yang khonga du chud de bsnyen
NK116(le)001:2565: bsgrub tshad du 'khyol zhing phyi nang gsang gsum gyi
NK116(le)001:2566: rtagsa rnams rdzogsa / bdag med rtogsa pas shes rab kyis ranga rgyud grol ba /
NK116(le)001:2568: las rab 'byams kyis gazhana don 'ab'a zhiga nyer ba /
NK116(le)001:2569: chos brgyad spangs pas tshul mthong gi bya ba nyung
NK116(le)001:2570: zhing 'khor yul 'byams klas su nana tana chosa la
NK116(le)001:2572: srid pa'i sdug bsngal la skyo shas ches chera ldana zhing /
NK116(le)001:2573: gazhana yanga tshul de kho na la bskul ba /
NK116(le)001:2574: rang gzhan gyis don gnyis bsgrub pa'i sgo ji snyed
NK116(le)001:2575: pa'i thabsa la makhasa shing brgyud pa gser gyi nyag
NK116(le)001:2576: thag la dam sel g.ya' yis ma gos pa'i phyir
NK116(le)001:2577: byin brlab dang ldana pa de lta bu'i dge ba'i
NK116(le)001:2578: bshes gnyen la bsten na mchog thun mong gi dngosa
NK116(le)001:2579: grub myur por thob par 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:2581: bsten bya ma yin pa bram ze zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:2582: brama ze bzhina du zhes pa gang de'i spyod pa
NK116(le)001:2583: na cho ste zhang po'i phyog dang rigas ni pha'i
NK116(le)001:2584: phyogs yin la de gnyis ga'i rang rang lugs gang
NK116(le)001:2586: bsti gnas te gnas dgon sogs mnga' thang nyams para
NK116(le)001:2587: dogas shing srid pa'i dpal 'byor gyis rgyags pa'i rdzinga
NK116(le)001:2588: bu spel ba la brtson pa'i rgyu ru thosa bsam
NK116(le)001:2589: cung zad byas pa sogs song bas na 'brasa bu
NK116(le)001:2590: gansa ma yin pa'i khrus la zhugsa pa gang zhig
NK116(le)001:2591: dper na shinga gi ranga 'athaga gis 'bras bu'i rigs
NK116(le)001:2592: gang yang mi chod pa lta bura rang rgyud las
NK116(le)001:2593: su mi rung bas gzhan rgyud thar bar byed pa'i
NK116(le)001:2594: lam ston dang / 'phags pa rnams ni so skyes kyi chos nyid dang shin tu 'gal te /
NK116(le)001:2598: gtod pa la gom pa dang /
NK116(le)001:2602: shes rab dang ldan pa ste rang gi rigs de'i nor gyis phyugs la /
NK116(le)001:2603: ser sna la sogs pa nyon mongs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:2605: lta ba thams cad dang bral bas na 'phags pa zhes bya ste /
NK116(le)001:2606: byis pa so so'i skye bo'i ranga bzhina ni /
NK116(le)001:2607: slob dpon ma ti tsi tras /
NK116(le)001:2608: khyod kyis blun dang phungs chos can //
NK116(le)001:2609: bskam zhing byas pa mi gzo dang /
NK116(le)001:2610: kha gsag gtum po mi bzad dang /
NK116(le)001:2611: yul na gnas su ma rtsal cig /
NK116(le)001:2612: rtag tu so so'i skye bo yi //
NK116(le)001:2613: khyad par mkhyen par mdzod cig dang /
NK116(le)001:2614: rang don tsam phyir 'brang bas na /
NK116(le)001:2615: gzhan dag skye bo phal ba bas /
NK116(le)001:2616: zhes gsungs pa bzhin dang ma 'agla te nyon mongs
NK116(le)001:2617: pa gra ma chag yanga thugs rje yas sprul gyi
NK116(le)001:2618: gang zag tu sgro btags nas gang zhig blangs dor
NK116(le)001:2619: gyis mtshams 'byed pa'i shes rab kyi mig zum pa'i
NK116(le)001:2620: blun po'i rmongs dada dang rang phyogs kyi kha bzung
NK116(le)001:2621: pasa baba bcola hol rgyug gis basngagasa yul lta bu'i
NK116(le)001:2623: mi mkhas pa'i phal ba gzhan gyisakyanga ltar snang gi rjes su phyogs te /
NK116(le)001:2624: rnyed pa dang bkura bsti'i mchoda pa chen po thob tshe /
NK116(le)001:2625: nga la 'di ltar cis mi 'ong snyams nas rgyags
NK116(le)001:2626: shing khengas par gyur pa khrona pa'i lag 'gro lta
NK116(le)001:2627: bu'i bshesa gnyen zhes ji ltar na gang gi tshe
NK116(le)001:2628: rgya mtshor gnas pa'i sbal ba zhig rlabs kyis 'phangs
NK116(le)001:2629: nas khron pa zhig tu phyin pa dang de na
NK116(le)001:2630: sbal ba zhig yod pas khyod gang nas 'ongs dris
NK116(le)001:2631: pas rgya mtsho chen po nas 'ong tshul bshad par
NK116(le)001:2632: / kho rang gnas pa'i khron pa las lhag pa med snyam nas /
NK116(le)001:2633: de las sum cha zhig tsam bstan nas rgya mtshor
NK116(le)001:2634: 'di tsam yod dam dris pas des de las lhag
NK116(le)001:2636: yang gnyis cha tsam sogs dpags te dris mthar de
NK116(le)001:2637: 'dra ba mang pos kyang do zla med pa'i gtam
NK116(le)001:2638: bshad pas kho skyengs tshul skye bo gso thig las
NK116(le)001:2639: bshad pa bzhin / mdo rgyud kyi bzhung la goms
NK116(le)001:2640: dris chung bas thosa pa nyung zhing gnang bkag mi
NK116(le)001:2641: shes pas sdom dang dama tshiga 'chal te sgo gsum
NK116(le)001:2642: tha mal du lus pas rgyud tshod dam'a ba la
NK116(le)001:2643: ci mi sems par gos dang rgyan chas rdzig rdzig
NK116(le)001:2644: byas te kuna spyod sa blara gshegsa pa ste mthon
NK116(le)001:2646: 'gro ba'i yul la byamsa dang snying rje sogs tshad
NK116(le)001:2647: med bzhi'i dpyang thag chad pa yi smyon pa'i lam
NK116(le)001:2648: makhana lta bu'i mi dge ba'i bshes gnyen rnams lasa
NK116(le)001:2649: sdig pa ches cher 'phela bar 'gyur la //
NK116(le)001:2650: khyad para zhes dmigs su bkar te bsdu na bslab
NK116(le)001:2651: pa gsum gang rung la ranga lasa yona tan lhag
NK116(le)001:2652: bacasa mina cing / byang chub kyi semsa dang bral
NK116(le)001:2653: ba dag tshe 'di'i snyan pa dang gragas pa'i mthu
NK116(le)001:2654: che ba tsam la yid rton byas te bstena na
NK116(le)001:2656: dper na mig longa pa'i skye bo zhig la deda
NK116(le)001:2657: dpon bcol na nor ba chena po ste rgya mtshor
NK116(le)001:2658: bying ba'am g.yang sar lceb pa bzhin du ma brtags
NK116(le)001:2659: pa zol gyis 'gogs pas muna pa'i smag rum ste
NK116(le)001:2660: srid pa'i myal ngam thang la rgyun ldan du 'khyamsa
NK116(le)001:2662: de'i phyir gtan gyi 'dun ma'i mchod sdong dama pa shina tu ma brtags na /
NK116(le)001:2663: dada pa cana gyi dge ba'i tshogsa chud gasna cing /
NK116(le)001:2664: dala ba skabsa shiga ces da ltar thob pa tsam
NK116(le)001:2665: las rnyed pa dka' ba sbrul gduga dang shinga gi
NK116(le)001:2666: griba ma nora ba bzhina du bslu par 'gyur ro
NK116(le)001:2667: // zhes sngon gyi skye bo ma brtags pa zhig
NK116(le)001:2668: gi mtshan mor phyin pas lam khar dug sbrul nyal
NK116(le)001:2669: ba shing grib tu 'khrul nas steng du ngal bsos
NK116(le)001:2670: pa ji zhig nas sbrul gyis khyud mid byas par
NK116(le)001:2671: grags pa'i gtam rgyud dang sbyar bar byas so //
NK116(le)001:2672: yang dag pa'i skyes bu dam pa bsten pa ni /
NK116(le)001:2673: rnyed pa chen po rnyed pa yin te /
NK116(le)001:2674: de ji ltar rtogs snyam na mtha' dag ces bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:2675: mdo rgyud nas bstan pa'i matha'a dag yona tana 'byor ba'i bla ma ni /
NK116(le)001:2676: sangsa rgyas kuna gyi mkhyen pa'i ye shesa brtse ba'i
NK116(le)001:2677: thugas rje'i khamas gcig tu dril ba'i spyi gzugs 'dula
NK116(le)001:2678: bar bya ba'i yula la skyes bu'i gzugas kyi byon
NK116(le)001:2680: sangs rgyas rnams dang de yi sras //
NK116(le)001:2681: gang gis gdul bya de nyid la /
NK116(le)001:2682: de dang mthun pa'i gzugs ston to //
NK116(le)001:2683: zhes gsungs ltar dngos grub kuna gyi 'byung gnas sam rtsa ba bla na meda pa yin no //
NK116(le)001:2684: mdzad pa yang ma nges pa ni drangs pa'i zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:2685: re zhig 'dul bya kha drangas pa'i dona du kun gyi mdzad spyod dang phyogsa mthuna la /
NK116(le)001:2686: ngesa pa'i dona du ranga rgyud yon tan mang pos
NK116(le)001:2687: phyug cing gzhan don kho nar brtson pas kun dang
NK116(le)001:2689: gang la gang mtshams kyis tshul ston pa dgongas pa
NK116(le)001:2690: cana du nges phyir ma rtogs log rtogs phyogs tsam
NK116(le)001:2691: rtogs pa kuna lasa kyang khyad para 'aphagas shing /
NK116(le)001:2692: yin lugs phu thag chod pa'i shes bya'i gnas kyi the tshoma gcoda pa la makhasa shing /
NK116(le)001:2693: gzhan gyis loga par sgrub pa'i dka' thub kyi skyo
NK116(le)001:2694: ngal bzoda pa de lta bu ni dpe don mthun
NK116(le)001:2695: par basngagasa pa / srid pa'i zhes bya ba la sogs pa ste /
NK116(le)001:2696: sdong po bkod pa las gsungs pa ltar /
NK116(le)001:2697: srida pa'i mtsho chen bzhi lasa sgrol ba'i /
NK116(le)001:2698: gru bo che lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:2699: thams cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang sgrub pa'i lam mchoga
NK116(le)001:2700: 'khrula bar mi 'gyura pa'i phyir deda dpona dngosa dang
NK116(le)001:2701: / lasa nyona gyi me tshogas gdon mi za bar
NK116(le)001:2702: 'jomas pa'i bduda rtsi'i chara chen po lta bu dang
NK116(le)001:2703: / / ma rigas pa'i muna pa basla ba'i nyi zlara mtshungsa shing /
NK116(le)001:2704: ha cang lci ba'i khur 'degs shing bzod pas theg pa shina tu che ba ste /
NK116(le)001:2705: de basa sa gzhi dang 'dra zhing /
NK116(le)001:2706: phana dang bde ba'i 'byunga gansa yina pas dpag bsam gyi shinga dang 'dra la /
NK116(le)001:2707: lung rtogs chosa kyi mdzoda dang ldan pas buma pa bazanga po lta bu te /
NK116(le)001:2708: dgos 'dod kuna lhun grub tu 'byung bas yida bzhina
NK116(le)001:2709: nora bu lasa kyang lhag cing ris med kun la
NK116(le)001:2710: snyomsa para byamsa pasa pha ma yina te /
NK116(le)001:2711: khyab che zhing 'jug myur basa snying rje chu klunga dang mtshungsa la /
NK116(le)001:2712: gzhan gyi legs tshogs la 'pho 'gyur meda pa'i dag'a ba ri dabnga dang 'dra zhing /
NK116(le)001:2713: chags sdang ring du spangs bas na 'khrug pa meda pa'i btang snyomsa char sprin bzhina ste /
NK116(le)001:2714: de 'dra ba'i bla ma dus gsum sangsa rgyas kun dang mnyam par 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:2715: gnoda pa byas kyang bde ba'i lam dang /
NK116(le)001:2716: 'brel na bsti stang byas pa'i phan yon lta ci /
NK116(le)001:2718: gang la gnod pa byas kyang bder 'brel ba //
NK116(le)001:2719: bde ba'i 'byung gnas de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK116(le)001:2720: zhes pa lta bu'i bshes gnyen la /
NK116(le)001:2721: g.yo zola meda par dang pa dang gus pasa bsten
NK116(le)001:2722: pa'i skyes bu de la mngona par mtho ba dang
NK116(le)001:2723: ngesa par legas pa'i dpal dang yona tana ji snyed
NK116(le)001:2725: tshul ji lta bus bsten snyam na /
NK116(le)001:2726: nad pa zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:2731: gru basa mnyena pa bzhina tu skye shi dang /
NK116(le)001:2732: nyon mongas pa'i dgra'i 'jigas pasa mi tshugs pa'i phyir skyabs su bstena para bya ste /
NK116(le)001:2734: rigs kyibu khyod kyis bdag la nad pa'i 'du shes bskyed par bya'o //
NK116(le)001:2735: chos la sman gyi 'du shes bskyed par bya'o //
NK116(le)001:2736: nan tan nyams su len pa la nad nye bar 'tsho ba'i 'du shes bskyed par bya'o //
NK116(le)001:2737: dge ba'i bshes gnyen la sman pa mkhas pa'i 'du shes bskyed par bya'o //
NK116(le)001:2738: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK116(le)001:2739: slob ma snod min gyi mtshan nyid brtag pa ni /
NK116(le)001:2740: de la zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:2741: 'di ltar bla ma dam pa'i thugs rje dang byin
NK116(le)001:2742: rlabs de la byams sdang dang nye ring med kyang
NK116(le)001:2743: rang gi skal bar lena pa sloba ma la rag
NK116(le)001:2744: las te dman par chos bshad kyang dper na snoda
NK116(le)001:2745: dang bral ba ste zhabs rdol la rdzas mi chags
NK116(le)001:2746: pa bzhin tu bcud ces chos kyi phana mi thogas
NK116(le)001:2747: te / cis phyir na snying dang 'dra ba'i gdam
NK116(le)001:2748: ngag las zanga zing cung zad ster ba tsam gyis
NK116(le)001:2749: tshima pa ste dga' ba thoba par 'gyur nas so
NK116(le)001:2750: te / // de 'dra'i rigs la bcosa ma'i dada
NK116(le)001:2751: pa yod yod 'dra mo byas kyang dbyar la sogs
NK116(le)001:2752: pa'i dusa bzhi'i 'gyur ldoga ngoma pa 'dra ste yid
NK116(le)001:2753: te / // brtan med do // lar phyin ci
NK116(le)001:2754: log gi snga ltas tshang ba'i las ngan can dag
NK116(le)001:2755: ni dang po rgyu 'bras kyi mngon rtogs bshad de
NK116(le)001:2756: nan gyis gzhol yang chosa lam du mi tshuda pa
NK116(le)001:2757: dper na gayaga rgoda bkol du mi btub pa bzhina
NK116(le)001:2758: te / // brtan med do // la / bar
NK116(le)001:2759: du thosa bsam bsgom gsum rang gi g.yel ba ci
NK116(le)001:2760: smos gzhan gyis rtsom pa la yang dgra ltar sdang
NK116(le)001:2762: tha ma sdiga pa'i grogas kyi khyu ru bag pheb ste /
NK116(le)001:2763: de'i spyod pa'i phyogsa bzunga nasa /
NK116(le)001:2764: lasa matha'a loga pa gang zhig nagas mathara gnas pa'i mi rgod dang 'dra'o zhes so //
NK116(le)001:2765: gal te rkyen dbang 'dra mo'i khug ste dama pa'i
NK116(le)001:2766: drung na gansa par gyur pa'i dus kyi tshe na'ang
NK116(le)001:2767: phyogs gzhan du 'bros pa la ringas zhes skad gcig
NK116(le)001:2768: tu yang mi brtan par bral te yula ganga du
NK116(le)001:2769: bgroda para gyur pa'i phyogsa der gzhi tshugs pa tsam
NK116(le)001:2770: na sdiga pa 'ba' zhig gisa 'dzina cing /
NK116(le)001:2771: dbena para sogs la 'di phyi'i ched du dam chos
NK116(le)001:2772: sgrubs shig ces bskula te sdod du bcug na'ang chosa
NK116(le)001:2773: tshugas zhiga nas ci bya gtol med du gyur nas
NK116(le)001:2774: ni dper na rlung gi rjesa su 'gro ba ku
NK116(le)001:2775: sha'i rtse mo yas mas su res mo 'khyogs pa
NK116(le)001:2776: bzhin du lugs zung gang la nges gtad med pa'i
NK116(le)001:2777: mi gzhi ngana pa'i zola gyis sbyor ba dper na
NK116(le)001:2778: gla ba 'dzin cing gsod pa'i sbyor ba snyi dang
NK116(le)001:2779: snyod kyi tha gu'i lce lta bu g.yo sgyu'i sgo
NK116(le)001:2780: nas bla ma sbos kyi glang po ste gla ba
NK116(le)001:2781: khyi ra bas mthong na rang 'dod dmigs nas dga'
NK116(le)001:2782: ba ltar bardzu bag gis bsnyen na dama pa'i chos
NK116(le)001:2783: gla rtsi 'dra ba'i rnyed pa thob par zin nasa
NK116(le)001:2784: slar rngon pa'i bya ba la yang dag par spro
NK116(le)001:2785: ste bka' drin gzo ba phar zhog gshe bskur dang
NK116(le)001:2786: log par lta ba nas gsod ba'i bar yang ji
NK116(le)001:2787: mi sems pa'i dama tshiga chu la rdo skyur ba
NK116(le)001:2788: bzhin du 'phena nas dmyal ba'i go 'phang sgrub pa
NK116(le)001:2789: ni / dam tshig gsum bkod pa'i ti kar /
NK116(le)001:2790: gsang sngags rdo rje'i slob dpon smod /
NK116(le)001:2791: chos la dbang zas nor dang barje /
NK116(le)001:2792: rigs pas dam tshig mi bsrung ba /
NK116(le)001:2793: de dag tshe 'dir tshe thung zhing /
NK116(le)001:2794: dpal dang skal pa bzang po nyams /
NK116(le)001:2795: mkha' 'gro'i chad pas sdug bsngal zhing /
NK116(le)001:2796: phyi ma ngan song nyid du lhung /
NK116(le)001:2798: gzhan yang so skyes rigs kha cig la dgongs nas
NK116(le)001:2799: bloo sna zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te
NK116(le)001:2800: / blo sna nyamsa 'oga tu ma chuda pa matha'a
NK116(le)001:2801: daga ni bskyed rdzogs kyi gdamsa pa'i ganda 'agga thoba
NK116(le)001:2802: pa rnams nyams su mi len par thos pa kho
NK116(le)001:2803: nas chog par sems te slara ring du btang nas
NK116(le)001:2804: / / sna tshogas pa'i yiga sna mang po 'tshola
NK116(le)001:2805: basa nam zhig na ngal zhing duba pa'i mathara rang
NK116(le)001:2806: rgyud 'dul ba'i zab don gasra pa ci yang mi
NK116(le)001:2807: mthonga zhing sngana ma'i go lo bsags pa'i rnam grangs
NK116(le)001:2808: matha'a daga nyamas par 'gyur pa ni chos nyid yin
NK116(le)001:2809: / / no // yang chos la 'jug tshul tsam
NK116(le)001:2810: mthun kyang don gyi dbye ba la yang dag ces
NK116(le)001:2811: bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:2812: 'khor bar skye ba dang bcas te yang dag pa'i
NK116(le)001:2813: dona la sbyor pa'i thabs cis mi bsgrubs snyams pa'i
NK116(le)001:2815: ltar snang tshe 'di'i zang zing bsgrub pa'i ched du dmigs nas 'dod pas 'jug pa ba /
NK116(le)001:2816: de gnyis kara ltar ma bsam ste ltas dbang lta
NK116(le)001:2817: bur lunga du ma bstana pas 'jug pa gzu luma
NK116(le)001:2818: cana / gsuma du gansa pa'i matshana nyid rnam par
NK116(le)001:2819: brtagas nas gang dang mtshams pas rjes su 'dzin pa
NK116(le)001:2821: de dag gi slob ma'i mi mthun phyogs ston mod kyi /
NK116(le)001:2822: 'o na snod dang ldan pa ji ltar shes zhe na /
NK116(le)001:2823: go cha zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:2824: 'di ltar sa gsum 'gro ba srid pa'i sdug bsngal
NK116(le)001:2825: gyi chu bo las sgrol ba'i gru bo gcig pu
NK116(le)001:2826: bdag nyidayina no // snyams pa'i snying stobs rmad du
NK116(le)001:2827: byung ba'i go cha chena po bgo la dus de
NK116(le)001:2828: nas le los bar mi chod pa'i blo grosa shina
NK116(le)001:2829: tu brtana pa dang 'jig rten 'di na gces pa'i
NK116(le)001:2830: mthar thug pa lusa dang srog la yang phang ba
NK116(le)001:2831: mi blta ste bla mar srid zhu'i ched du rim
NK116(le)001:2832: gro bgyid cing ci gsunga tha na 'jig rten lugs
NK116(le)001:2833: kyi 'bel gtam yan chad rgyal ba'i bka'a dang mtshungs
NK116(le)001:2834: par dkri zhing badga nyid mi bsrung pa'i skyes bu
NK116(le)001:2835: de ni mos gus kho nasa grola lo //
NK116(le)001:2836: spyi'i mtshan nyid la gces pa ni dad dang zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:2837: dada pa dang shesa raba dang thosa pa dang snying rje che /
NK116(le)001:2838: sdoma pa gsum dang dama tshiga gi gnas rnams la
NK116(le)001:2839: rtse gcig tu gusa shing sgo gasum dge ba las
NK116(le)001:2840: su rung bas dula zhing blos gting sgom pas khongas
NK116(le)001:2841: yangas shing gtong phoda che ba daga snang dang khrola
NK116(le)001:2842: yoda pa sogs dang ldana pa ci nas kyang gal
NK116(le)001:2843: che'o // mtshan nyid de ldan gyi slob ma'i bslab
NK116(le)001:2844: bya bla ma zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan
NK116(le)001:2845: che'o // te / lan gcig tsam min par bla
NK116(le)001:2846: ma la rang gi mig las kyang gces spras su
NK116(le)001:2847: byed pa ci smos de'i char gtogs rigs kyang shina
NK116(le)001:2848: tu bsrunga basa madzangas pa dang /
NK116(le)001:2849: bka'a bkyona ji ltar gnang ba daga la mi khro ba'i dpe rta mchoga bzhina te /
NK116(le)001:2850: ji ltar lcags gis brab kyang 'khon lan mi bgyid pa lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:2851: gru ltar mngag gzhug phyag dar tshun chod 'gro 'onga gi gansa la skyo ngala spangas pa dang /
NK116(le)001:2852: zama pa lta bura skyid sdug la sogs pa'i bazanga ngana thams cad thega pa /
NK116(le)001:2853: bzo stegsa te mgar ba'i 'og rdo bzhina du tsha
NK116(le)001:2854: granga gis gdung ba dang ltog skom la sogs pas
NK116(le)001:2855: nyen pa ganga yanga chos phyir bde ba ltar dang
NK116(le)001:2856: du len pas bzoda pa dang /
NK116(le)001:2857: daka'a ji ltar phebs pa de bzhina nyan pa bran khola lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:2858: nga rgyal spang nas dman sa 'dzin pa phyag dara pa zhes rdul phyag pa lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:2859: dregas pa spangsa pasa khyu mchoga ces ma he ra
NK116(le)001:2860: chad pa lta bu ste bshad ma thag pa'i bsam
NK116(le)001:2861: spyod de dag gis bla ma bsten dgos so zhesa
