NK116(le)001:2862: sde snoda daga lasa gsungsa so /
NK116(le)001:2863: rang nyid la 'byor ba yoda na dkona mchoga gsum
NK116(le)001:2864: 'dus kyi ngo bo bla ma yin phyir bzhi ba'i
NK116(le)001:2865: tha snyad gsol te de la mchoda pa'i thabs kho
NK116(le)001:2866: nar brtson cig / de ci'i slad du zhe na /
NK116(le)001:2869: slob dpon gnyan par shes par bya //
NK116(le)001:2870: ci phyir bskal pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK116(le)001:2871: slob dpon dag la brten nas byung /
NK116(le)001:2873: don dang ldan pa'i mkhas pa la //
NK116(le)001:2874: dus gsum du ni thams cad du //
NK116(le)001:2875: phyogs bcu'i zhing na bzhugs pa yi /
NK116(le)001:2876: bde gshegs rgyal ba kun byon nas //
NK116(le)001:2877: basngagasa dang 'dun pas phyag mdzad do //
NK116(le)001:2878: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs pa bzhin zhabas tog dang /
NK116(le)001:2879: srida zhu'i cheda du lusa ngaga bkola ba'i lasa /
NK116(le)001:2880: phra rags matha'a daga nama yanga 'bras bu med pa
NK116(le)001:2881: ma yin pas chud zosa su 'gyur ba meda cing
NK116(le)001:2882: khyad par mnyes pa gsuma gyi nanga nas zhes zang
NK116(le)001:2884: lus ngag gi zhabs tog bsgrub pa lhur len pa
NK116(le)001:2885: ste kun las mchoga tu gyur pa ni phyi ma'o
NK116(le)001:2886: // rang gi snang pa'i rkyon 'gog par ston pa ni /
NK116(le)001:2887: mdzad spyod zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:2888: gong du bshad pa ltar bla ma legs par brtags
NK116(le)001:2889: nas 'os su rig pa brten zin phyin madzada spyod
NK116(le)001:2890: ganga ltar gnang yanga loga para mi blta ste /
NK116(le)001:2891: 'aphagas pa'i yula du rnal 'byor gyi dabnga phyug phala
NK116(le)001:2892: mo che zhig gtsang tsog med par spyod pas rigs
NK116(le)001:2894: bran g.yog sogs zho shas 'tsho ba'i las kho na la rtson pas g.yunga po //
NK116(le)001:2895: rngon pa dang nya ba dang bya bye'u sogs gsod
NK116(le)001:2896: pa'i las la 'jug pa sdiga spyod phala ba'i tshula
NK116(le)001:2897: bzung nas / nyamsa pa lasa kyang shina tu nyamsa para 'gyur ba ltar yoda mod de /
NK116(le)001:2898: 'on kyang gang 'dul gyi gdul bya'i mos blo ltar byed pa yin pas na /
NK116(le)001:2899: ranga gi nye bar lena pa ni sems yin la /
NK116(le)001:2901: dabnga du ma gyur gyi bar rang snang 'khrula ba
NK116(le)001:2902: gzhan skyonadu bden par bzung nas brtagsa pa'i nyes pa
NK116(le)001:2903: mtha' mi gtugs pas tshad meda pa yin te /
NK116(le)001:2904: sde snod bcu gnyis blo la byang zhing chuba pa yi /
NK116(le)001:2905: dge slong skar bazanga kyang sdiga pa'i mthusa btab nas phyin ci log tu bsgyur tshe /
NK116(le)001:2906: skyon bral yon tan kun ldan gyi ston pa rdzogs
NK116(le)001:2907: pa'i sangs rgyas kyi madzada pa rnam par dag pa'ang
NK116(le)001:2908: g.yo rgyur mthonga pa'i tshul la legas para bsam nas
NK116(le)001:2910: de basa na ranga gisa ranga nyid la brtags dpyad bya ste /
NK116(le)001:2911: dge ba'i lam du 'chosa par byos shing /
NK116(le)001:2912: gala te badga gis nyes min gang rung la bla
NK116(le)001:2913: mas byams brtse chung zhing sdang bar mngona gyur na'ang
NK116(le)001:2914: / badag nyid chen po'i thugs la g.yo zol med
NK116(le)001:2915: pas gang shar lkog gyur gyi sbubs su mi bsnyal
NK116(le)001:2916: bar ston pas na mi 'os pa'i las shig bdag
NK116(le)001:2917: gis byas par gdon mi za bas skyon du gzigas
NK116(le)001:2919: dusa la baba para yang dag par rigas nasa sngon
NK116(le)001:2920: chad nongs pa bashagas shing slad nas bsdomsa par bya'o
NK116(le)001:2921: // de ltar byeda pa ni canga shesa lta bu'i skyes bu ste /
NK116(le)001:2922: bdudkyi dabnga du nam yang mi 'gro'o //
NK116(le)001:2924: spyod lam gyi cha nas brten tshul bla ma zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan to //
NK116(le)001:2925: bla ma bzhengas pa'i tshe rang nyid 'phral du ldang ba las stana la 'duga pa mina no //
NK116(le)001:2926: bzhugas pa'i dusa na skad gsang mi stod par zhe
NK116(le)001:2927: sas sku la snyun mi mnga' 'am zhes 'dri zhing
NK116(le)001:2928: nye bar mkho ba'i longs spyod ci yod dbula bar
NK116(le)001:2929: bya la / gshegas pa'i tshe na zhabas 'bringa byed
NK116(le)001:2930: pa la sngona rjesa gayasa nasa bsgrod pa mina te
NK116(le)001:2931: ci'i phyir na rim par rgyab ston pa dang /
NK116(le)001:2933: gral mgor yin pa ste nyes pa 'byung bas spang ste /
NK116(le)001:2934: cung zad phyir phyogs pas g.yon nas 'agro'o //
NK116(le)001:2935: gzims mal sogs stan dang gzhona pa smad ces der
NK116(le)001:2936: 'dug pa dang zhon par byed pa sogas kyis bsoda
NK116(le)001:2937: namas nyamsa par 'gyur bas bag byed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:2938: gzhan yang bzhugs pa'i sgo 'phar dbye gcod skabs brdegas pa dang /
NK116(le)001:2939: tshad las thal ba'i gos rgyan sogs kyis sgega chosa
NK116(le)001:2940: ngo 'dzuma ma yin par bzhin bsdus te ganga pa
NK116(le)001:2941: dang / rdzuna dang baba col gyi bazhada gada 'brela meda kyi gtam dang /
NK116(le)001:2942: mdor na gusa dang 'jigas bacasa ma yina par ci
NK116(le)001:2943: mi snyam par byung rgyal byed pa mtha' dag spangas
NK116(le)001:2944: dgos pa ni / spyi mdo las /
NK116(le)001:2945: ci'iphyira dam par gyur ba la //
NK116(le)001:2946: ma nges gyu gya'i las byas pas //
NK116(le)001:2947: dam par gyur ba kun bslus te //
NK116(le)001:2948: rdo rje'i dmyal bar de ltung 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:2951: ngag tshig barlanga pos zhe 'gengs pa //
NK116(le)001:2952: bskal pa stong phrag dmyal bar ltung //
NK116(le)001:2953: zab mo'i tshig la sgro bskur bas //
NK116(le)001:2954: mnar med gnas su ltung bar 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:2956: gsang ba kun snyoms kyi rgyud las //
NK116(le)001:2957: bla ma mchog las rang nyid kyis //
NK116(le)001:2958: che mchog rlom sems smra ba ni //
NK116(le)001:2959: bskal pa stong phrag du ma ru //
NK116(le)001:2960: thur du bltas te dmyal bar 'gro zhes sogs rgya
NK116(le)001:2961: cher gsungs bas na shin tu bsgrimas la sgo gsuma
NK116(le)001:2962: nye bar zhi basa bstena pa gal che'o //
NK116(le)001:2964: dad med dang mi 'grogs pa ni //
NK116(le)001:2965: bla ma zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te //
NK116(le)001:2966: de yang rang gi ngos nas nyes pa med kyang
NK116(le)001:2967: bla ma la gshe bskur gyis dmoda cinga zhe sdang
NK116(le)001:2968: ba'i ganga zaga de dang lan cig tsam yang bshesa
NK116(le)001:2971: log pa'i blo can de ni g.yang sar 'phyan pa'i snga 'gros yin te /
NK116(le)001:2973: log par sgrub pa'i blo gros mkhan //
NK116(le)001:2974: g.yang sar mchong ba'i snga 'gros mkhan //
NK116(le)001:2975: byams blo'i yul du rung ba min /
NK116(le)001:2977: spob pa yong na kho'i bsod nams ma yin pa'i
NK116(le)001:2978: rgyun gcod phyir thabs gang rung gis nusa pasa de
NK116(le)001:2979: bzloga cinga min na ring du phyogs pa las /
NK116(le)001:2980: baga phebas bzhin smra bar 'gyur na sdiga pa'i gazhana
NK116(le)001:2981: dabnga ni lhag para sdong zla bdud kyi mthu che
NK116(le)001:2982: bas dama tshiga skyon can du bslad de ma rung
NK116(le)001:2983: bar byed do // phyogs ris med par mdza' zlar
NK116(le)001:2984: blta ba ni 'grogs par la sogs pas bstan te
NK116(le)001:2985: bar byed do // / yun du 'grogas para gyur
NK116(le)001:2986: kyang skyo sun med pa bde ba ska raga lta
NK116(le)001:2987: bar byed do // / bu dang / kun gyi
NK116(le)001:2988: mos pa'i rjes su 'gro bas 'juga pa bde ba
NK116(le)001:2990: gzhan gyi gnod lci ba'i khur phogs kyang bzoda pa'i
NK116(le)001:2991: srana tshan che ba ka ba lta bu yisa bslab
NK116(le)001:2993: de bas kyang bla ma dang de'i nye ba 'khora dang /
NK116(le)001:2994: rdo rje'i spuna sring rnams la bsnyen zhing mnyes par bya dgos pa kho na'o /
NK116(le)001:2995: spyod pa de ldan gyi dam pa'i chos kyi ro myong ba ni /
NK116(le)001:2996: rdzing bu zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:2997: 'di ltar rdzing bu'i mchog ni yan lag brgyad ldan
NK116(le)001:2998: gyi mtsho yin la de'i zur gyi bstan pa'i chu
NK116(le)001:2999: gzhan pa sogs gang rung la brtena pa'i nganga pa
NK116(le)001:3000: sogs chu las bskrad kyang phyir snyegs ste rol ba
NK116(le)001:3001: dang / skyed mos tshal du bunga basa me tog gi bcuda la ro myang ba bzhina /
NK116(le)001:3002: rtag tu 'gyur ldog med par 'grogas pa'i spyod pa ni chos ngo matshara cana zhes smon pa'o //
NK116(le)001:3003: skyo sems dang ngala dub meda pasa bla ma'i thugas
NK116(le)001:3004: 'ba' zhig bzunga nas dga' ba dang gus dang dada
NK116(le)001:3005: pa'i mchog ni nye bar bzhag ste be'usa nu ma
NK116(le)001:3006: 'jib bzhin gdam ngag lena pasa bla ma'i lung rtogs
NK116(le)001:3007: yona tan gyi ro myong bar bya'o //
NK116(le)001:3008: de lta bu'i 'juga par 'os pa'i spyod phyogs la ngesa par zhugsa pa de yi /
NK116(le)001:3009: dama pa'i mchoga ni sangs rgyas yin la de dang gnyis su med pa'i bla ma ste /
NK116(le)001:3010: rang gi bsoda namas dang ye shesa kyi tshogas chen
NK116(le)001:3011: gnyis rdzogs phyir gang gi bka' bzhin khrod du'nga dona
NK116(le)001:3012: dang mthuna par spyod pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3013: tha na chos phyir mangga gzhuga bang mir phyin pa
NK116(le)001:3014: dang bla ma'i bzhugs gnas phyaga dara byas pa tshuna
NK116(le)001:3015: choda kyang rung ste ngala ba byas pa gang yang
NK116(le)001:3016: 'brasa bu med par mi 'gyur bar don chen po
NK116(le)001:3017: dang bacasa pa lam lnga'i ya gyal tshogas kyi lam
NK116(le)001:3018: myur bor bgrod pa'i thabs mchoga tu gyur ba yina
NK116(le)001:3019: no // rgyu mtshan ci yod snyam na ci'i phyir zhes bya ba la sogs par gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:3020: don ci'i phyir na skyabsa su 'gro ba'i yul dang
NK116(le)001:3021: tshogsa gnyis bsags pa'i thabs kyi zhing gi rab dang
NK116(le)001:3023: bla ma gang zhig bsgrub par 'dod pa'i rnal 'byor
NK116(le)001:3024: bas tshogs rdzogs phyir mdun mkhar gsal ba phyi dang
NK116(le)001:3025: / rgyud dag phyir spyi bor gsal ba na nanga ste gnyis dang /
NK116(le)001:3026: byin rlabs 'jug phyir snying khar dmigs pa'am rang lus gsal ba gsang ba ste /
NK116(le)001:3027: gang rung gi bskyed rdzogs kyis bsgrub bya'i ngo bo mthar thug pa 'dira 'dusa pasa na /
NK116(le)001:3028: mdo rgyud kun nas sangsa rgyas nyid du nges pa ji snyed par bsten pas so //
NK116(le)001:3029: 'di ltar ma rtogs pa'i nyes dmigs ston phyir rmongs pa zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:3030: dengs sang 'di na rmong pa phala chera gyis lha
NK116(le)001:3031: dang bla ma'i gzugsa brnyan 'dags blugs su sgrub pa'am
NK116(le)001:3032: 'dri zhing bsgoma lo byed na'ang legs par ma sems
NK116(le)001:3033: te dngosa su bzhugas pa la sri zhu dang rima
NK116(le)001:3034: gro bgyi ba med pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:3035: mig gcer ba'am btsums te gansa lunga sgom pa yin
NK116(le)001:3036: zer na'ang ma lags te bla ma'i thugas kyi gsang
NK116(le)001:3038: de bas na bsgrub pa'i thabs dang rten 'brel 'chug
NK116(le)001:3039: pas bsgrub bya'i 'bras bu mi thob pas 'agla ba
NK116(le)001:3040: can yin pas na nyon re mongsa te /
NK116(le)001:3041: tshe 'dir mosa gusa meda pas thugs yid phan tshun
NK116(le)001:3042: rgyang thag ring bzhina bar do'i skabs der majala du
NK116(le)001:3043: re ba kye ma kye hud ngo matshara ro //
NK116(le)001:3044: zhes thugs gting nas mug pa'i gsung zhig go //
NK116(le)001:3045: rgyu mtshan de'i phyir dang po zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:3046: dang po bla mara yon tan ldan min brtagsa pa la makhasa pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3047: bar du bla ma bstena tshul gzhan las shes pa'am
NK116(le)001:3048: min kyang khong la zhus te tshul bzhin bsgrub pa'i
NK116(le)001:3049: makhasa pa dang / tha ma dgongas pa'i spyod yul
NK116(le)001:3050: te lung rtogs kyi chos rnams ma lus par bslaba
NK116(le)001:3052: skyes bu de ni yang dag pa'i lam du 'gro
NK116(le)001:3053: ba nas yang dag pa'i go 'phang tshegs med du
NK116(le)001:3054: thob bo // zhar la sdig pa'i grogs po spang
NK116(le)001:3055: ba gal che ba'ang gang tshe zhes bya ba la
NK116(le)001:3057: bla mar chos zhus te nyams su len pa'i dus
NK116(le)001:3058: ganga gi tshe zhi ba ste byang chub phyogs la
NK116(le)001:3059: mi mos shing sdang ba'i skye bo gang zhig 'byung
NK116(le)001:3060: po yi sdig to sogs bdud kyiminga gi rnam grangs
NK116(le)001:3061: so // de'i bsam pa skyes bu'i gzugsa su 'ongas
NK116(le)001:3062: para gor ma chags pa dang de dang mtshungs ldan
NK116(le)001:3063: so // du / rang rgyud mi drangs pa'i g.yo
NK116(le)001:3064: dang gzhan bslu ba'i sgyus phyin ci log tu spyod
NK116(le)001:3065: cing naga po'i chosa bzhi la gcig tu brten cing
NK116(le)001:3066: dama pa dmoda pa sogas dakara po'i chosa bzhi la
NK116(le)001:3067: rnam par spanga bar 'gyur ba de la dus ring
NK116(le)001:3068: thung ci tsam 'grogas bzhina de tsam gyi sdiga spyod
NK116(le)001:3069: sna tshogs pa'i 'thora rlung 'tshubsa pas grogs kyis dge
NK116(le)001:3070: ba'i lo tog rmis med par 'jomas pa'i sdiga grogas
NK116(le)001:3071: de la bsten pa'i blo grosa blun po gang zhig
NK116(le)001:3072: bduda sdesa gdon mi za bar bcoma par byed na
NK116(le)001:3073: mkhas pas skad cig tu yang 'brel bar mi byed
NK116(le)001:3074: so // du / do // sdig grogs spangs pa'i
NK116(le)001:3075: yon tan ni tshad med par de phyir zhes bya
NK116(le)001:3076: ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:3077: de dag gi phyir na spang bya bzlog ste /
NK116(le)001:3078: cig shes dge ba'i bshesa dang grogas po la bstena
NK116(le)001:3079: pasa gtan bde'i legas tshogs kyi yona tan thams cad
NK116(le)001:3080: 'phral du mthonga ba'i chosa la'ang mngon gsum par zina
NK116(le)001:3081: na skye ba gzhan du rgyu las 'bras bu 'grub
NK116(le)001:3083: dus 'di nas bzung byang chub snying po'i bar du //
NK116(le)001:3084: rgyal dang rgyal srasa rnams kyis rtag tu dgongas shing
NK116(le)001:3085: byin gyis rlobs pas mngona mtho dang ngesa legas kyi
NK116(le)001:3086: yona tan kuna gyis mi phongs par 'byor zhing /
NK116(le)001:3087: tshogas gnyis rdzogas shing sgrib gnyis daga ste /
NK116(le)001:3089: sa bcu lam lnga'i yona tan bla nas blar zhes
NK116(le)001:3090: gang ma gong mar na 'phar te 'gro'o de basa
NK116(le)001:3091: na bla ma'i rnal 'byora bsgom zhing bsgrub pa bsoda
NK116(le)001:3093: thugas yid kyi rgyud gciga tu bsre ba ni ye shesa kyi tshogs te /
NK116(le)001:3094: tshogas chen gnyis rdzogs pa'i 'brasa busa thus ka ste
NK116(le)001:3095: snying po bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes yina
NK116(le)001:3096: pa gang zhig bde blag tu brnyes pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:3097: bskala pa du mar rgyal dang rgyal sras rnams la
NK116(le)001:3098: bsnyen bkura rgya cher bgyi zhing bskyed rima brgya phraga
NK116(le)001:3100: bla ma dam pa ni skad cig tsam du dran
NK116(le)001:3101: pa kho na mchoga cesa rgyal ba bden pa smra
NK116(le)001:3102: basa gsungas so zhes pa'i bar gyi 'khor lo gnyis
NK116(le)001:3103: pa bstan to // da ni legs smon gyi don
NK116(le)001:3104: gsal phyir dam chos zhes bya ba la sogs pa
NK116(le)001:3105: pa bstan to // gsungs te / de skad du'ang mdo sde rgyan las //
NK116(le)001:3106: dmigs pa bzang dang ston pa bzang //
NK116(le)001:3107: thabs bzang pa dang nges 'byung bzang //
NK116(le)001:3108: nges legs smon gyi mtshan nyid yin /
NK116(le)001:3109: gsung pa dang rjes su 'gro ba 'di ltar mdo
NK116(le)001:3110: sngags dama pa'i chosa kyis bduda rtsi'i chu klong dapaga
NK116(le)001:3111: tu med pa'i mdzoda chen po rang gi rgyud la
NK116(le)001:3112: 'drongsa pa'i gang zag dmigas pa bazanga po zhes rnam
NK116(le)001:3113: dpyod zab mo mchis pa rnams chos kyi don ston
NK116(le)001:3114: pa'i bla ma bazanga pora 'phrad tshe yas mas rtena
NK116(le)001:3115: cinga 'brela ba 'byung ba'i thabsa bazanga ba /
NK116(le)001:3116: de dag lasa brten nas mngon par 'dod pa'i don
NK116(le)001:3117: gang yin pa dka' tshegs la mi ltos par myur
NK116(le)001:3118: du thob par byed pa gang zhig mana ngaga yin
NK116(le)001:3119: la de lung ma bstan du chud zos su mi
NK116(le)001:3121: de thams cad kyi grogs su med thabs med pa
NK116(le)001:3122: ni gnas dang gnas ma yin pa'i khe nyen gyi
NK116(le)001:3123: gnad la sogs par rtogs pa'i ngesa 'byung bazanga po'i
NK116(le)001:3124: dpe ni rigas sngagas nusa pa cana lta bu ste
NK116(le)001:3125: // ji ltar na sngags kyi nus pas char dus
NK116(le)001:3126: nam mkha'i chu gter gyi phang phung stug po yang
NK116(le)001:3127: skem pabazhina du 'khora bar skyo ba meda pa'i gdona
NK116(le)001:3128: ni gsor mi rung ba'i bdud chen po yin pa
NK116(le)001:3129: theba tshul 'dis theba nas srid pa'i phra rgyas kyi
NK116(le)001:3130: rtsa ba drung nas 'joms par 'gyur bas na bazanga
NK116(le)001:3131: po bzhi dang ldana pa'i legas smon zhes brjod pa
NK116(le)001:3132: // yina no // de'i ldog phyogs chos sgor zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:3133: 'di ltar chosa kyi sgor zhugas lo byas kyang de'i
NK116(le)001:3134: moda la suna nas dad pa snum drad khyer ba
NK116(le)001:3136: 'gran sems dang 'phrag par dog pas kuna slonga ngan
NK116(le)001:3137: pa duga cana dang 'dresa pa'i thosa bsam bsgoma pa
NK116(le)001:3138: bag re byas kyang 'phral du chosa lasa blo nyamsa
NK116(le)001:3139: shing bsrunga bya sdoma pa dang dam tshig gi gnas
NK116(le)001:3140: rnams mi lcog pa'i khura du songa zhing chosa brgyad
NK116(le)001:3141: kyi bya ba mi tshe 'phyid pa'i dmoda pa drag
NK116(le)001:3142: posa thega pa chen po'i brtul zhugas le lo'i g.yang
NK116(le)001:3143: sar 'khyamsa par ma zad legas smon gyi daka'a thuba
NK116(le)001:3144: phra sbom thams cad bshiga pa'i phyir dal rten gyi
NK116(le)001:3145: rdzing bu sdig to'i 'dam gyis rnyogsa para bgyid pa
NK116(le)001:3147: de las grol ba'i thabs ni thad ka zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:3148: de yang thada ka thada ka ste glo bur du
NK116(le)001:3149: byung ba'i nyon mongas pa'i duga chena lnga bo so
NK116(le)001:3150: so'i gnyen po che ba gang na /
NK116(le)001:3151: bdag cag gi ston pas skyes bu rnam pa gsuma
NK116(le)001:3152: gyi ched du dgongs nas gsung pa'i dam pa'i chos
NK116(le)001:3153: kyi shinga rta chena po dera 'joga pa la /
NK116(le)001:3154: sngon gyi mtha' dben pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3155: phyi ma'i mtha' mi dpog pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3156: da ltar byung ba 'jig par shes pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3157: dus gsum mnyam pa nyid de bzhi bor skyo ba meda cing /
NK116(le)001:3158: dam 'cha' ba dag ni ji zhig na tshogs drug
NK116(le)001:3159: gi yul gyi snang ba matha'a daga chosa dang bla
NK116(le)001:3160: mara shara te / de tsam na rnam pa thams
NK116(le)001:3161: cad mkhyen pa'i rgyu ru songa pas legas par smon
NK116(le)001:3162: pa'i re 'bras gruba pa yina mod zhes pa'i bar
NK116(le)001:3163: gyis 'khor lo gsum pa bstan to /
NK116(le)001:3164: bsod nams kyi skyabs la 'dun pa nyid ston phyir
NK116(le)001:3165: mtho ris zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te
NK116(le)001:3166: / ji skad du dbyig gnyen gyis //
NK116(le)001:3167: sna tshogs yon tan 'dod pa yis //
NK116(le)001:3168: 'bad bya sa bon med par ni //
NK116(le)001:3169: myu gu skye ba yod ma yin //
NK116(le)001:3170: nyes pa dag ni gcig pu yis //
NK116(le)001:3171: yon tan mang po 'joms par byed //
NK116(le)001:3172: tshe ring de bzhin nad med pa //
NK116(le)001:3173: gzugs dang bskal pa bzang dang rigs //
NK116(le)001:3174: nor dang shes rab dag dang bdun /
NK116(le)001:3175: zhes mtho risa kyi yona tan bduna pa'i dag'a ba dang /
NK116(le)001:3176: de'i char gtogs dmigs su bkar ba gnyis mi khom
NK116(le)001:3177: rkyen gyis ma gtses par dala ba'i dngos po thob
NK116(le)001:3178: pasa yang dag par mtho ba dang /
NK116(le)001:3179: rten de la'ang nada meda cing bde ba'o //
NK116(le)001:3180: ting nge 'dzina las su rung ba dang /
NK116(le)001:3181: drang nges kyi chos rnam par 'byed pa'i shesa raba ste /
NK116(le)001:3182: lnga po ni sngona chada bsoda namas kyi gnas la gusa pa'i mngona rtogsa yina pa /
NK116(le)001:3184: dga' dang dal bar skye ba dang //
NK116(le)001:3185: nad med pa dang ting 'dzin dang //
NK116(le)001:3186: rnam par 'byed pa'i byed rgyu ni //
NK116(le)001:3187: sngon tshe bsod nams bsags pa yin /
NK116(le)001:3189: de'i ldog phyogs 'ga' zhig ni ma bsgoms zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:3190: shes bya'i gnas la bslab cing ma bsgomas pasa ni rmongs pa'i gnyen po riga pa 'jomas shinga 'onga /
NK116(le)001:3191: rgyagsa pa ste rang mthong gis spos shing sems rgyas pasa dpal 'abyor 'jomas shinga 'onga zhing /
NK116(le)001:3192: khong 'khrugs te rnam para sdang pasa legas tshogsa kyi dngos po 'jomas shinga 'onga ste /
NK116(le)001:3193: 'dod pa'i gnas la chagas shing sred pasa yang dag
NK116(le)001:3194: par mthonga ba 'jomas shinga 'onga ba gdon mi za'o
NK116(le)001:3195: // de yang dpag bsam 'khri shing las //
NK116(le)001:3196: ma bsgoms pa yis rig pa 'joms //
NK116(le)001:3198: rnam sdang gis ni legs nyid 'joms //
NK116(le)001:3199: chags pas yang dag mthong ba 'joms /
NK116(le)001:3201: ltar snang tsam du dge ba sgrub tshul mthun na'ang //
NK116(le)001:3202: yang dag pa'i rnam par spyod pa dang bcas pa
NK116(le)001:3203: ni rgyu stobs su gyur ba'i mthu yin pa gang
NK116(le)001:3204: phyir zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:3205: ched du gnyer pa ganga gi phyir lasa dang nyon mongas pa'i sdiga pa yisa /
NK116(le)001:3206: rnam para ma dkrugsa shing bslad pa ma yina pa'i blogrosa bzang po ni /
NK116(le)001:3207: rang ngos nas rnam par dpyod pa'i shesa raba kyi mthu dang /
NK116(le)001:3208: gzhan ngos su dam pa'i chos kyi skal pa thob
NK116(le)001:3209: pasa bkola pa ste sgo gsum las su rung bar
NK116(le)001:3210: thub pa tshe rabs gong mar bsoda namsa rgya cher
NK116(le)001:3211: basgas pa'i rang gzugs ngoms pa'i rtagsa las gzhan pa
NK116(le)001:3212: su yi mthu min par mdo sde'i rgyan lasa bashada
NK116(le)001:3214: tshul 'di ni mya ngan med pa'i gtam rgyud las kyang //
NK116(le)001:3215: bsod nams me yis mi tshig ste //
NK116(le)001:3218: sa bzhin du ni byer mi 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:3219: rgyal po dang ni chom rkun gyis //
NK116(le)001:3220: 'phrog tu med par bsod nams gnas //
NK116(le)001:3221: skyes pa dang ni bud med kyis //
NK116(le)001:3222: phrog bar nus pa ma yin no //
NK116(le)001:3223: bsod nams bde ba bskyed pa'i gter /
NK116(le)001:3225: gang dang gang du skye ba rung //
NK116(le)001:3226: de dang der ni rjes su 'brang //
NK116(le)001:3227: sogs gzhan yang rgya cher snang ngo //
NK116(le)001:3228: de ltar bsod nams 'ba' zhig las gus par blta
NK116(le)001:3229: ba'ang gnas skabs kyi bde skyid la dmigs pa can
NK116(le)001:3230: ma yin par chos la sems pa'i snying stobs chen
NK116(le)001:3231: po bskyed dgos tshul chos la zhes bya ba la
NK116(le)001:3233: 'di ltar thams cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang dmigs phug
NK116(le)001:3234: byas nas dam pa'i chosa bsgrub pa la gcig tu
NK116(le)001:3235: semas pa'i go cha bgo ba ni nam yang rkyen
NK116(le)001:3236: gyis mi phyed par rnama pa kun tu yang dag
NK116(le)001:3237: par sra zhing gting zaba zhing khyon rgyas pa'i chosa
NK116(le)001:3238: khamas rgya mtsho lta bu lha'i dabnga po'i mtshona zhes
NK116(le)001:3239: gzhu la sbyar te gling bzhi'i gyad stobs po ches
NK116(le)001:3240: kyang gdunga bar mi rigs na'ang gal te lag tu
NK116(le)001:3241: mchis na blo yi spobas sam mi spobas snyam ba'i
NK116(le)001:3243: ci ste mi nus nyams pa'i snying stobsa gnyena po'i
NK116(le)001:3244: dabnga du gtong nas rta gon la brtsom pa rnams
NK116(le)001:3245: ni skad gcig kyang lung ma bstan gyi lam du
NK116(le)001:3246: / mi 'chug para pha rol du phyin pa druga gi steng du 'gro ba kho na'o //
NK116(le)001:3247: de yi mthuna pa'i phyogsa ni ji ltar phyogs su
NK116(le)001:3248: 'gro ba la bza' btung la sogs pa'i yo byad
NK116(le)001:3249: 'du byed pa bzhin du bsod nams kyi bya ba'i
NK116(le)001:3250: cha rkyen du yan lag bduna pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3251: chu gtor tsh+wa tsh+wa la sogas pa'i dge ba basgas
NK116(le)001:3252: shing sgrib pa sbyangsa pa'i thabs matha'a daga nyams su
NK116(le)001:3253: bstar ba de ni rgyal ba'i sras su gyur ba
NK116(le)001:3254: yina pas mi mthuna sdig to'i phyogsa kyis de la
NK116(le)001:3256: lam du rim gyis 'gro ba'i ring la bsoda namas
NK116(le)001:3257: rgya chen po gsogs pa daga la brtena pa 'di
NK116(le)001:3258: ni skyes bu chen po'i lam stegsa yina no //
NK116(le)001:3259: zhes pa'i bar gyis 'khor lo bzhi ba'i don bstan to //
NK116(le)001:3260: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi le'u lnga ba'i 'grel ba'o ////
NK116(le)001:3261: da ni bstan pa la 'jug pa'i sgo dam pa
NK116(le)001:3262: skyabs su 'gro ba bstan pa'i phyir 'jigs pa zhes
NK116(le)001:3263: bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:3264: de yang spyir 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal /
NK116(le)001:3266: nyid dgos tha mal 'khrul 'dzin te 'jigas pa gsuma
NK116(le)001:3267: gyi chu gter gyi rba rlabs 'khrugsa pa can la
NK116(le)001:3268: lhung zin par gyur ba'i dus 'dir skyabsa su 'gro
NK116(le)001:3271: gting mtha' med pa'i 'khor ba ni //
NK116(le)001:3272: rgya mtsho'i nang na rnam par gnas //
NK116(le)001:3273: 'dod chags la sogs mi bzad pa'i //
NK116(le)001:3274: chu srin gyis ni lus zos pa //
NK116(le)001:3275: de rang gang la skyabs su 'chi /
NK116(le)001:3276: gsungs pa bzhin tshur mthong bus pas basngagasa yul tshangs
NK116(le)001:3277: dang dbang po brgya byin la sogs pa'i dregs pa
NK116(le)001:3278: rnams kyang rang nyid srid pa'i ra ba las ma
NK116(le)001:3279: brgal bas rgyab tu bskyur te /
NK116(le)001:3280: gcig tu basngagasa su 'osa pa'i gnas der gting nas
NK116(le)001:3281: yida chesa shing thar ba'i srog brten pa'i dus la
NK116(le)001:3282: babs so // de gang zhe na slob dpon ma tho btsun grub rjes //
NK116(le)001:3283: bdag ni ston pa gzhan spangs nas //
NK116(le)001:3284: khyod la skyabs su mchi lags kyis //
NK116(le)001:3285: ci yi slad du zhe na khyod //
NK116(le)001:3286: skyon mi mnga' la yon tan rdzogs /
NK116(le)001:3288: bstod pa brgya lnga bcu pa las //
NK116(le)001:3289: gang zhig gang la nyes pa kun //
NK116(le)001:3290: gtan nas yongs ye mi mnga' zhing //
NK116(le)001:3291: gang la rnam pa thams cad du //
NK116(le)001:3292: yon tan thams cad gnas gyur ba //
NK116(le)001:3293: gal ste sems shig yod na ni //
NK116(le)001:3294: de nyid la ni skyabs 'gro zhing //
NK116(le)001:3295: de bstod de ni bkur ba dang //
NK116(le)001:3296: de yi bstan la gnas pa'i rigs //
NK116(le)001:3297: zhes sangs rgyas nyag gcig tu ma zad la //
NK116(le)001:3299: de'i rjes su bzung ba'i dge 'dun te dkonamachoga rin
NK116(le)001:3300: po che rnam pa gsum po'i mtshan gyi gragas pa
NK116(le)001:3301: thob pa kho nas kyang srid pa'i tshad gdung bsil
NK116(le)001:3302: bar byed pa'i phyir na gdugas dakara po lta bu
NK116(le)001:3303: gang yin pa de ni nang ba'i bstan pa la
NK116(le)001:3304: 'juga pa'i thoga ma nyid du gces par 'dzin dgos
NK116(le)001:3305: so // de skad du'ang myang 'das las //
NK116(le)001:3306: ji ltar skas kyi rim pa bzhin //
NK116(le)001:3307: nga yi bstan pa zab mo yang //
NK116(le)001:3308: rim gyis bslab cing nan tan bya //
NK116(le)001:3309: thod brgal ma yin mthar chags so //
NK116(le)001:3311: rten dang brten pa 'brel dgos pa'i tshul thar ba zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:3312: de yang rgyal ba thabs mkhas shing thugs rje chen
NK116(le)001:3313: po'i mnga' bdag des lus can thara para yang dag
NK116(le)001:3314: tu 'gro ba'i lam bslab pa gsum ste spang dang
NK116(le)001:3315: rtogs pa'i yona tan gyi tshogs ma lus pa'i 'byung
NK116(le)001:3316: gnas bstan zin pas phyi'i yan lag rdzogs na'ang /
NK116(le)001:3317: nang gi yan lag de'i rten dang snod du bdag
NK116(le)001:3318: nyid rung bar bya'o snyam pa'i zhe dama brtan po
NK116(le)001:3319: baca'a bzhin nges par mi slu ba skyabsa su 'gro
NK116(le)001:3320: ba kho na nyid yin te /
NK116(le)001:3321: de'i sngona du ston pa dang bstan pa'i chos kyi yona tana shesa pa shin tu gcesa zhes so //
NK116(le)001:3322: de yang basngagasa 'os bstod pa las //
NK116(le)001:3323: phyi yi yan lag stobs kun ni //
NK116(le)001:3324: khyod kyi yang dag bsgrub lags kyang //
NK116(le)001:3325: nang gi stobs dag ma tshangs bas /
NK116(le)001:3326: byis pa rnams ni sdug bsngal bsten //
NK116(le)001:3328: rgyu mtshan de mthong bas dwangs pa'i dad pa skyes
NK116(le)001:3329: pas blo sna khrid tshul chos rnams zhes bya la
NK116(le)001:3331: dge ba'i chosa rnams kuna gyi rtsa ba dada pa yin la /
NK116(le)001:3332: de ni tshur mthong skyes bu'i semas la lhan skyes su med pas lunga du ma bstan pa la //
NK116(le)001:3333: gang tshe ston pa sangs rgyas kyi sku dngos sam
NK116(le)001:3334: brgyud mar snang bsnyan nam dge ba'i bshes gnyen mthonga
NK116(le)001:3335: ba dang / sde snod gsum gyi chos gang rung
NK116(le)001:3336: bklag pa yi moda la ba spu'i rnam grangs ji
NK116(le)001:3337: ltar 'khri shinga gi lo 'dabs rlung gis slong ba
NK116(le)001:3338: bzhina du ldang ba de la dang ba'i dada pa
NK116(le)001:3340: de bzhina yang dag pa'i go 'phang thob par 'doda pa ste gnyis pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3341: thabs de nyid sangs rgyas kho na'i mthu la rags
NK116(le)001:3342: las par rigs pa yida chesa te gsum pa blo
NK116(le)001:3343: de bcos su mi btub pas phyir mi ldoga pa
NK116(le)001:3344: ste dad pa rnam pa bzhira gsungs la /
NK116(le)001:3345: de lasa kyang skyabsa 'gro'i gansa skabsa 'dira dang po
NK116(le)001:3346: gnyis ni 'jig sla bas srog la baba kyang phyir
NK116(le)001:3347: mi ldoga pa'i dad pa dgosa so //
NK116(le)001:3348: zhes pa'i shugs kyis gsum pa yang gal che ba ston to //
NK116(le)001:3349: yang de slong byed kyi rgyu ma nor ba ston
NK116(le)001:3350: phyir dad pa zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs
NK116(le)001:3352: skal ba dge ba can kha cig la gdod nas dang pa yod la /
NK116(le)001:3353: cig shos dang po'i las can rnams la dada pa skye ba'i rgyu ni rnam pa bzhi yina te /
NK116(le)001:3354: skyes bu dam pa la brten pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3355: dama pa'i grogas zhes chos sgrub pa'i gang zag dang 'grogas pa /
NK116(le)001:3356: dkona mchoga gsum gyi yon tan rjesa su drana pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3357: 'khor ba la snying po meda pa'i nyes dmigas bsam pa lasa skye'o //
NK116(le)001:3358: de las dkon mchog gi yon tan basngagasa pa'i phyir thub pa zhes pa la sogs par gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:3359: thuba pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyi yona tan ni matha'a yasa pa zhig ste /
NK116(le)001:3360: mthong dang bsgom pa'i lam du spangsa pa gnyis kyisa
NK116(le)001:3361: nyon mongs pa dang shesa bya'i phyogs kyi sgrib pa
NK116(le)001:3362: gnyis yang dag par bcom pa des na /
NK116(le)001:3367: rim bzhin gang zag dbang po rno rtul rtogs pa /
NK116(le)001:3368: chos thams cad rang gi ngo bos stong ba'i don mthong ba /
NK116(le)001:3369: 'gro ba rnams kyi skye 'pho shes pa /
NK116(le)001:3370: dpag tshad brgya nas stong gsum tshun gyis gzugs phra
NK116(le)001:3371: rabs gzigs pa dang bcas pa rnams so so'i yon
NK116(le)001:3372: tan no // thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyan ni mi
NK116(le)001:3373: slob lam gyis bsdus la rjes mthun sa brgyad pa
NK116(le)001:3375: mngona par shes pa so so'i 'og tu sbyar la /
NK116(le)001:3380: lha'i mig gi zag pa zad pa'i ste /
NK116(le)001:3381: drug po so so'i yon tan ni /
NK116(le)001:3382: rim bzhin sa g.yo ba dang /
NK116(le)001:3383: gcig du mar bardzusa pa'i 'phrul byed pa dang po //
NK116(le)001:3384: 'jig rten khams kyi sgra che chung mtha' dag gsan pa gnyis pa /
NK116(le)001:3385: gzhon nu nyon mongs dang bral min rtogs pa gsum pa /
NK116(le)001:3386: rang gzhan gyi tshe rabs mtha' klas shes pa bzhi pa /
NK116(le)001:3387: bskal dang bskal min gyi gzugs phra rag thams cad gzigs pa lnga ba /
NK116(le)001:3388: sgrib gnyis spongs pa'i thabs dang bral 'bras shes pa drug go //
NK116(le)001:3400: bskal ba'i bar du 'dod na 'tsho ba ting 'dzin gyi sgo grangs med pa la dabnga thob pa //
NK116(le)001:3401: nam mkha'i mdzod la mnga' brnyes pa /
NK116(le)001:3402: bzo dang rgyu rtsal gyi gnas sogs las kyi 'bras bu ston pa /
NK116(le)001:3403: gang 'dod pa de der skye bar nus pa /
NK116(le)001:3404: 'jig rten gyi khams sangs rgyas kyi skus gang bar ston pa /
NK116(le)001:3405: byang chub chen po'i sprul pa 'gyed nus pa /
NK116(le)001:3406: sna tshogs pa'i gdul bya las de snyed kyi rdzu 'phrul dus gcig tu ston pa /
NK116(le)001:3407: shes bya thams cad thogs med du mkhyen pa /
NK116(le)001:3408: chos kyi tshig don thams cad la mkhas pa ste /
NK116(le)001:3409: bcu po 'di ni dag sa gsum gyi byang chub sems dpa'i khyad chos so //
NK116(le)001:3416: shes rab mngon du byed pa /
NK116(le)001:3417: chos thams cad kyi tshig rab tu tha dad pa'i shes pa la sogs par gsungs so //
NK116(le)001:3420: gnas dang gnas min mkhyen stobs dang //
NK116(le)001:3421: de bzhin las rnams smin blo dang /
NK116(le)001:3422: mos pa sna tshogs thugs chud dang /
NK116(le)001:3423: sna tshogs khams kyi mkhyen stobs dang //
NK116(le)001:3424: de bzhin dbang mchog mchog ma yin //
NK116(le)001:3425: mkhyen dang thams cad du 'gro dang /
NK116(le)001:3426: bsam gtan rnam thar ting 'dzin dang /
NK116(le)001:3427: snyoms par 'jug sogs mkhyen stobs dang /
NK116(le)001:3428: sngon gnas dran pa mkhyen pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3430: zag rnams zad pa mkhyen stobs dang /
NK116(le)001:3431: stobsa bcu po ni 'di dag go /
NK116(le)001:3433: dge mi dge 'dres mar spyod pa ste gsum po'i
NK116(le)001:3434: 'bras bu bde sdug bar mar 'byung na gnas dang
NK116(le)001:3435: / de las ldog pa gnas ma yin par mkhyen pa dang po //
NK116(le)001:3436: dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i las dang de'i rnam smin mkhyen pa gnyis pa /
NK116(le)001:3437: skye 'phags kyi mos pa sna tshogs so sor mkhyen pa gsum pa /
NK116(le)001:3438: dbang yul shes gsum sogs kyi khams dang de dag gi rang bzhin shes pa bzhi pa /
NK116(le)001:3439: mig la sogs pa'i dbang po rno rtul 'bring gsum gzigs pa lnga ba /
NK116(le)001:3440: so so'i skye bo nas sangs rgyas kyi bar 'gro ba'i lam so sor mkhyen pa drug pa /
NK116(le)001:3441: 'jig rten khams kyi bsam gtan bzhi dang rnam thar
NK116(le)001:3442: brgyad dang snyoms 'jug dgu'i ting 'dzin sogs ma 'dres
NK116(le)001:3444: bdag gzhan gyi sngon gnas gang yin pa'i rnam pa ma 'dres par gzigs pa brgyad pa /
NK116(le)001:3445: de bzhin du rang gzhan gyi 'chi 'pho dang skye ba la sogs mkhyen pa dgu pa /
NK116(le)001:3448: bla na med pa'i byang chub rnam pa gsum gyi spang bya dang /
NK116(le)001:3449: zag zad kyi skabs ma 'dres par gzigs pa bcu pa'o //
NK116(le)001:3454: 'di dag ni lam gyi gegs so //
NK116(le)001:3455: zhes so sor zhal gyis bzhes pa la chos mthun gyi rgol ba med pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3456: so so yang dag par riga pa bzhi ni /
NK116(le)001:3457: kun nas nyon mongs pa dang rnam byang gi phyogs
NK116(le)001:3458: kyi khams dang ming gi rnams grangs mkhyen pa chos
NK116(le)001:3459: de dag gi rang spyi'i mtshan nyid la ma rmongs
NK116(le)001:3460: pa don / gdul bya'i yul dang mthun pa'i gsung rnam pa thams cad pa'i tshig /
NK116(le)001:3461: rang gi ngo bo nyid dang rnam dbye'i bye brag
NK116(le)001:3462: thams cad mkhyen pa la chags thogs med par 'jug
NK116(le)001:3463: pa'i spobs pa ste so so yang dag pa rigs
NK116(le)001:3464: pa bzhi ka'i gsham du sbyar ro //
NK116(le)001:3465: ma 'dres pa'i chos bco brgyad ni /
NK116(le)001:3467: 'khrul dang ca co mi mnga' ste //
NK116(le)001:3468: ston la dran pa nyams mi mnga' //
NK116(le)001:3469: mnyam par ma bzhag thugs mi mnga' //
NK116(le)001:3470: 'du shes sna tshogs kyang mi mnga' //
NK116(le)001:3471: ma brtags btang snyoms mi mnga' ste //
NK116(le)001:3472: 'dun dang brtson grus dran pa dang //
NK116(le)001:3473: shes rab rnam grol rnam grol gyi //
NK116(le)001:3474: ye shes gzigs pa nyams mi mnga' //
NK116(le)001:3475: las rnams ye shes sngon 'gro dang /
NK116(le)001:3476: dus la ye shes sgrib pa med //
NK116(le)001:3477: de ltar bco brgyad 'di rang bzhin /
NK116(le)001:3478: ston pa'i ma 'dres yon tan yin //
NK116(le)001:3479: gsungs pa bzhin sku'i spyod pa la 'khrul ba mi
NK116(le)001:3480: mnga' ba la sogs bcu gnyis dngos su bstan la
NK116(le)001:3481: phyi ma drug ni rkang ba gnyis kyis bsdus te
NK116(le)001:3482: mi gsal ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK116(le)001:3486: phrin las ye shes kyi sngon du 'gro zhing ye shes kyi rjes su 'brang pa gsum /
NK116(le)001:3490: ma chags ma thogs pa ste gsum mo //
NK116(le)001:3491: thams cad rdzogas pa ni sangsa rgyas kho na tsam yin te //
NK116(le)001:3492: de gzhan la ma yin no //
NK116(le)001:3493: de ltar rnam pa kuna gyi mchoga dang ldan pa ni sangs rgyas chosa kyi sku'i ngo bo ste /
NK116(le)001:3495: chos sku mkha' 'dra gzugs sku mdzes skur ldan /
NK116(le)001:3497: kha gcig chos sku la mtshan dpe 'dod pa //
NK116(le)001:3498: longs sprul la ltos nas ha cang spros par zad de /
NK116(le)001:3499: sku'i tha snyad zhugs pa tsam du mtshan dpe yod pas khyab na /
NK116(le)001:3500: der ma zad ngo bo nyid la'ang yang yod pa thal /
NK116(le)001:3501: 'dod na dbyings dag mnyam chen po'i cha nas ngo bo nyid sku dang /
NK116(le)001:3502: spang rtogs mthar phyin pa'i ye shes kyi cha nas chos kyi sku ste /
NK116(le)001:3503: de gnyis chu dang rlan bzhin tha dad min la /
NK116(le)001:3504: gzhi gcig la phyi kho nar ltos pa'i mtshan bzang drug cu rtsa bzhi dang /
NK116(le)001:3505: dpe byad drug cu'i lhag pa'i brgya ni bcom ldan
NK116(le)001:3506: 'das kyis ma bstan pas phyin ci log gi blo
NK116(le)001:3507: gros zhig ste / mtha' dag gcig tu khegs pas dogs pa tsam yang skye bar mi sems so //
NK116(le)001:3508: tshul 'di'i rnam par bzhag pa mngon rtogs rgyan las //
NK116(le)001:3509: thub pa'i ngo bo nyid sku ni //
NK116(le)001:3510: zag pa med pa'i chos gang dag /
NK116(le)001:3511: thob gyur rnam kun rnam dag pa //
NK116(le)001:3512: de dag rang bzhin mtshan nyid can /
NK116(le)001:3514: byang chub phyogs mthun tshad med dang /
NK116(le)001:3515: rnam par thar dang mthar gyis ni //
NK116(le)001:3516: snyoms 'jug dgu yi bdag nyid dang //
NK116(le)001:3517: zad par bcu yi bdag nyid dang //
NK116(le)001:3518: zil gyis non pa'i skye mched ni //
NK116(le)001:3519: rab tu dbye bas rnam brgyad dang //
NK116(le)001:3520: nyon mongs med dang smon mkhyen dang //
NK116(le)001:3521: mngon shes so so yang dag rigs //
NK116(le)001:3522: rnam pa tha dad bzhi dag dang //
NK116(le)001:3523: dbang bcu dang ni stobs bcu dang //
NK116(le)001:3524: mi 'jigs pa ni bzhi dag dang //
NK116(le)001:3525: bsrung ba med pa rnam gsum dang //
NK116(le)001:3526: dran pa nyer bzhag rnam gsum dang //
NK116(le)001:3527: snyel pa mi mang'i chos nyid dang //
NK116(le)001:3528: bag chags yang dag bcom pa dang //
NK116(le)001:3529: skye la thugs rje chen po dang //
NK116(le)001:3530: thub pa kho na'i ma 'dres chos //
NK116(le)001:3531: bco brgyad bshad pa gang yin pa //
NK116(le)001:3532: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen nyid dang //
NK116(le)001:3533: chos kyi sku zhes brjod pa yin //
NK116(le)001:3534: zhes tshig rkang dang po'i don byang chos so bdun
NK116(le)001:3535: 'og tu rtogs pa'i chos bshad pa'i skabs su ston
NK116(le)001:3536: par 'gyur la // gzugs can gzugs la blta ba'i /
NK116(le)001:3537: gzugs can ma yin par gzugs la blta ba'i sdug par blta ba'i zhes gsum dang /
NK116(le)001:3538: gzugs med bzhi 'gog pa dang bcas pa lnga ste
NK116(le)001:3539: brgyad po so so'i 'og tu rnam par thar ba
NK116(le)001:3542: nang gzugs kyi snang ba ma 'gag pas yul snang la bden zhen log pa dang po /
NK116(le)001:3543: nang gzugs su mi dmigs pas phyi nang gi bden zhen 'gags pa gnyis pa /
NK116(le)001:3544: chos rnams stong pa nyid du ro gcig par blta ba'i 'dzin pa kun las thar ba gsum pa /
NK116(le)001:3545: sems nyid nam mkha'i don mthong ba bzhi pa /
NK116(le)001:3546: thams cad sems dang ye shes kyi rol par rtogs pa lnga ba /
NK116(le)001:3547: phyi nang gang du'ang gzung 'dzin med pa drug pa /
NK116(le)001:3548: spros dang mtshan ma'i spyod yul zhi ba bdun pa /
NK116(le)001:3549: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad la dmigs zhen 'dzin pa gtan du mi mnga' ba brgyad pa'o //
NK116(le)001:3550: bsam gtan dang gzugs med pa'i dngos gzhi bzhi bzhi dang /
NK116(le)001:3551: 'gog pa ste so so'i 'og tu snyoms 'jug sbyar ba'i /
NK116(le)001:3552: mthar gyi gnas pa'i snyom par 'jug pa dagu'o /
NK116(le)001:3553: zad par zhes so so'i thog tu sbyar ba'i 'byung ba lnga rtsa ba'i kha dog bzhi /
NK116(le)001:3554: rnam shes kyis skye mched de zad par gyis rnam pa bcu /
NK116(le)001:3555: dbyibs dang kha dog zil gyis non pa bzhi bzhi ste zil gyis gnon pa'i skye mched brgyad /
NK116(le)001:3556: nyon mongs pa med pa dang smon lam mkhyen pa ste /
NK116(le)001:3557: lhag ma phal cher gong du bshad pas shes la 'ga' zhig 'og tu yang ston no //
NK116(le)001:3558: de nyid slob lam sa bcura gnas pa'i byang sems
NK116(le)001:3559: kyi 'khora la nges pa lnga ldan gyi longas spyoda
NK116(le)001:3560: rdzogas pa'i skur ston pa ni /
NK116(le)001:3561: dper na me long nang du byad dbyib 'char ba bzhin te /
NK116(le)001:3563: zhi sku dpag bsam shing ltar gsal 'gyur la //
NK116(le)001:3564: yid bzhin nor bu ji bzhin rnams mi rtog /'gro
NK116(le)001:3565: sgrol bar du 'jig rten 'byor slad rtag /'di ni
NK116(le)001:3566: spros dang bral la snang ba yin /
NK116(le)001:3568: chos kyi yon tan ston pa'i phyir chos ni zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:3569: dam pa'i chosa ni tshogs gnyis bsoda namas bsags pa'i thabs dad lam lnga bgrod pa'i them skas dang /
NK116(le)001:3570: mya ngana las 'adsa pa 'gog pa'i bden pa gsum
NK116(le)001:3571: ni brjod par bya ba'i dona te de la'ang 'brasa
NK116(le)001:3572: bu dang / bya ba'i ranga bzhina gnyis su gansa pa la dgongs nas /
NK116(le)001:3574: gang zhig gang gis chags bral ba //
NK116(le)001:3575: bden gnyis mtshan nyid can de chos //
NK116(le)001:3576: chags bral nyid ni 'gog pa dang //
NK116(le)001:3577: lam gyi bden pa dag gis bsdus //
NK116(le)001:3578: gsungs pa ltar don dam dang /
NK116(le)001:3579: kun rdzogs kyi ste bdena gnyis zhesa bya 'goga pa dang lam ste rnama pa gnyis yina no //
NK116(le)001:3580: brjod bya ni bshad ma thag pa bzhin la rjoda byed ni tshig yin no //
NK116(le)001:3581: de gnyis la ltosa te lunga dang rtogsa pa'i chosa su grags so //
NK116(le)001:3582: lunga ni gsunga raba yan lag bcu gnyis dang /
NK116(le)001:3584: mdo sde dbyangs bsnyad lung bstan dang /
NK116(le)001:3585: tshig bcad ched brjod glenga gzhi dang //
NK116(le)001:3586: rtogs brjod de lta bu byung dang //
NK116(le)001:3587: skyes rabs shin tu rgyas pa dang //
NK116(le)001:3588: rmad byung gtan la dbab pa'i sde //
NK116(le)001:3589: gsung rabs yan lag bcu gnyis so //
NK116(le)001:3591: gnyen po'i sgo nas dbye na bshad ma thag pa'i /
NK116(le)001:3593: nyan thos kyi mdo sde'i sde snod /
NK116(le)001:3595: tha ma bzhi las skyes rabs kyi sdes byang sems
NK116(le)001:3596: kyi 'dul ba'i sde snod shin tu rgyas pa rmad
NK116(le)001:3598: phyi ma gcig ni nyan byang gnyis ka'i thun mongs du mngon pa'i sde snod bzhag pa ste /
NK116(le)001:3599: sde snod gsuma du shar ba yin no /
NK116(le)001:3600: rang rgyal nyan thos kyi theg pas bsdus pas log tu ma gsungs so //
NK116(le)001:3601: de las kyang thabas kyi sgo grangs med pas che
NK116(le)001:3602: ba ni riga 'dzina gyi sde snod yina te le'u
NK116(le)001:3604: de dag bdag po'i rkyen gyis yi ge de la
NK116(le)001:3605: ming dang tshig nas glegsa bama gyi yi ge'i bar
NK116(le)001:3606: du bsgrubs ste gansa pa skyabs yul gyi dama tshiga
NK116(le)001:3608: rtogsa pa'i rgosa ni drana pa nye bar bazhaga pa
NK116(le)001:3609: bzhi nasa bzung rima bzhina zhes pa cung zad phral
NK116(le)001:3610: na / rtogs pa'i yon tan gyi gzhi ni sa yin te /
NK116(le)001:3612: yon tan gyi rten du gyur pas na sa'o //
NK116(le)001:3613: zhes pa la nang gses dman dang mchog gi dbye
NK116(le)001:3614: bas dang po la brgyad dang phyi ma la bcu'o
NK116(le)001:3615: // dang po ni yum bar ma las gsungs pa ltar /
NK116(le)001:3621: rang sangs rgyas kyi sa ste /
NK116(le)001:3622: nyan rang gi thun mongs pa'o //
NK116(le)001:3623: rin chen phreng ba las kyang /
NK116(le)001:3624: ji ltar nyan thos theg pa las /
NK116(le)001:3625: nyan thos pa ni brgyad bshad pa /
NK116(le)001:3626: de bzhin theg pa chen po la //
NK116(le)001:3627: byang chub sems dpa'i sa bcu'o //
NK116(le)001:3629: sa'i rten du gyur ba lam lngara nges te /
NK116(le)001:3630: de yang tshogs lam la nang gses su chung 'bring chen po ste /
NK116(le)001:3633: sems chos dran pa nye bar bzhag pa bzhi /
NK116(le)001:3636: mi 'gag pa dang mi gnas pa dang sgyur ma'i dpe brgyad kyi rjes thob bzhi'o //
NK116(le)001:3637: byed las ni go rim ltar bden pa bzhi la 'jug go //
NK116(le)001:3638: gnyis pa ni mi dge ba'i chos ma skyes pa rnams mi bskyed skyes pa'i rgyun gcod /
NK116(le)001:3639: dge ba'i chos rnams ma skyes pa bskyed /
NK116(le)001:3640: skyes pa gong du spel ba ste /
NK116(le)001:3641: yang dag par spong ba bzhi bsgom mo //
NK116(le)001:3643: zhi lhag zung 'brel gyi ting nge 'dzin rtse gcig
NK116(le)001:3644: pa bsam gtam gyi sems las su rung nas grub
NK116(le)001:3645: pas rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang ba bzhi ste /
NK116(le)001:3654: dang po gnyis kyi thun mong ni /
NK116(le)001:3659: shes rab kyi dbang po ste lnga bsgom zhing /
NK116(le)001:3664: sems rtse gcig par sbyor ba /
NK116(le)001:3665: rang bzhin shes pa ste go rim ltar sbyar ro //
NK116(le)001:3666: phyi ma gnyis kyis kyang bshad ma thag pa lnga
NK116(le)001:3667: po stobs su gyur bas na stobs lngar smros so
NK116(le)001:3668: // de'ang drod rtse mo gnyis su mthong lam skye ba'i dus ma nges pas chung ngu dang /
NK116(le)001:3669: bzod ba'i phyi mar skye bas 'bring dang /
NK116(le)001:3670: chos mchog gi tshe 'dir mthong ba'i lam la sbyor bas chen po zhes so //
NK116(le)001:3673: dran dang chos rab rnam 'byed brtson 'grus dang /
NK116(le)001:3674: dga' dang shin tu sbyangs dang ting 'dzin dang /
NK116(le)001:3675: btang snyoms 'di bdag byang chub yan lag ste /
NK116(le)001:3676: gsungs pa lam de'i bslab bya yin te /
NK116(le)001:3679: chos kyi dbye bar mkhas pa /
NK116(le)001:3681: dmigs pa de la yid spro ba /
NK116(le)001:3682: lus sems las su rung ba /
NK116(le)001:3683: sems rtse gcig las mi 'gyur ba /
NK116(le)001:3684: sems dang sems byung rnams rnal mar 'jug ste lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK116(le)001:3686: kun btags kyi nyon sgrib dang /
NK116(le)001:3687: gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa rags pa'i shes sgrib gnyis spang bar 'gyur te /
NK116(le)001:3688: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i ye shes kyi sa dang po rab tu dga' ba thob bo //
NK116(le)001:3689: bsgom pa'i lam du bslab bya'i rnam grangs yang /
NK116(le)001:3691: yang dag lta dang 'tsho dang rtsol ba dang /
NK116(le)001:3692: dran dang ting 'dzin ngag dang las mtha' dang //
NK116(le)001:3693: yang dag rtog nyid lam gyis yan lag brgyad /
NK116(le)001:3694: zhes so so'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK116(le)001:3696: kha bsag dang log 'tsho spang ba /
NK116(le)001:3700: ngag la ltos pa'i dge ba'i las lam bzhi /
NK116(le)001:3701: lus kyi mi dge ba'i las kyi lam spong ba'i rang bzhin gsum /
NK116(le)001:3702: gnod sems med pas nges 'byung dge ba'i rtog pa ji snyed do /
NK116(le)001:3704: lhan skyes kyi nyon sgrib dang /
NK116(le)001:3705: gnyen po'i rtog pa phra ba'i shes sgrib lhag ma rnams spong ngo //
NK116(le)001:3706: chung 'bring chen po gsum la nang gses su yang de bzhin dbye bas dgu ste /
NK116(le)001:3707: so so'i thob bya'i sa ni /
NK116(le)001:3717: gnyen po'i khyad par la ltos nas lam bzhir bsdus pa'i don ni /
NK116(le)001:3718: sa de dang de'i gegs su gyur ba'i rags pa spong ba sbyor lam /
NK116(le)001:3719: phra ba gting nas 'byin pa'i bar chad med lam /
NK116(le)001:3720: dngos gzhi thob pa rnam grol kyi lam /
NK116(le)001:3721: sa de'i 'jug thogs su yon tan khyad par pa
NK116(le)001:3722: thob nas gong nas sa gong mar 'gro bzhin pas
NK116(le)001:3724: de ltar mthong bsgoms kyis bsdus pa'i sa bcu po
NK116(le)001:3725: so so'i rnam smin gyi skye ba dang yon tan
NK116(le)001:3728: 'dzam gling la dbang ba'i rgyal po dang /
NK116(le)001:3730: lha'i dbang po brgya byin dang /
NK116(le)001:3734: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed rnams kyi lha rgyal dang /
NK116(le)001:3735: stong gi bdag po tshangs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3737: gnas gtsang gi lha'i bdag po rnams su bsam bzhin skye ba 'dzin nus so //
NK116(le)001:3738: de lta'i skye ba theb so cog gis sa dang de'i yon tan rdzogs sam zhe na /
NK116(le)001:3740: 'jig rten pa'i dge ba stobs su gyur ba'i rnam
NK116(le)001:3741: smin gyis kyang de dang der skye ba bshes spring
NK116(le)001:3744: sa dang po'i skabs su dus skad cig ma la sangs rgyas brgya'i zhal blta ba dang /
NK116(le)001:3745: sangs rgyas brgyas byin gyis brlabs par shes pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3747: dus bskal pa brgyar ston pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3748: sngon dang phyi ma'i gnas brgya la ye shes kyi gzigs pa 'jug pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3749: ting 'dzin brgya la snyoms par 'jug cing ldang pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3750: sems can brgya smin par byed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3751: zhing khams brgya g.yo bar byed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3752: zhing khams brgya 'od kyis gsal bar byed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3753: chos kyi sgo brgya 'byed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3754: rang gi lus brgya ston pa dang lus re re
NK116(le)001:3755: la 'khor phun sum tshogs pa brgya brgya ston nus
NK116(le)001:3756: te / de bzhin stong phrag bcu gnyis dang /
NK116(le)001:3757: bye ba phrag bcu gnyis dang /
NK116(le)001:3758: bye ba stong phrag bcu gnyis dang /
NK116(le)001:3759: bye ba khrag khrig 'bum phrag bcu gnyis dang /
NK116(le)001:3760: stong chen 'bum phrag gcig gi rdul gyi grangs dang /
NK116(le)001:3761: stong chen grangs med pa 'bum phrag bcu'i rdul gyi grangs dang /
NK116(le)001:3762: sangs rgyas kyi zhing brjod du med pa'i yang brjod
NK116(le)001:3763: du med pa'i rdul gyi grangs dang mnyam pa'i rdul
NK116(le)001:3764: phra rab snyed kyi sangs rgya blta ba la sogs
NK116(le)001:3766: de'i rjes la mi slob pa'i lam ste /
NK116(le)001:3767: rgyun matha'i sems dpa' des phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas la mchod pa chen po byas ma thag tu /
NK116(le)001:3768: de dag gi mdzod spu las 'od zer gyi tshogs dpag tu med pa byung ste /
NK116(le)001:3769: sems dpa' chen po de'i spyi bor nub pas sangs
NK116(le)001:3770: rgyas thams cad kyi 'od zer chen po'i dbang bskur
NK116(le)001:3771: ba thob / rdo rje lta bu la sogs pa'i
NK116(le)001:3772: ting nge 'dzin 'bum phrag grangs med pa brnyes te
NK116(le)001:3773: ba thob / / ma rig pas bzhag pa'i bag
NK116(le)001:3774: chags phra mo yang dag par bsal nas chos dbyings
NK116(le)001:3775: ye shes mngon sum bar snang ba'o //
NK116(le)001:3776: bshad ma thag pa'i yona tana matha'a daga pa de dang /
NK116(le)001:3777: de rnams 'aphagas pa'i spanga rtogsa mthar phyin pa'i ye
NK116(le)001:3778: shesa te snying po cana dang gzhan yang bskyed pa
NK116(le)001:3779: dang rdzogas pa'i rim pa gnyis dang /
NK116(le)001:3781: slob lam bzhi dang mi sloba lam gyi dngosa gzhi ni /
NK116(le)001:3782: rgyu'i sa bcu zhes btags par dgongs pa ni /
NK116(le)001:3784: sa dgu 'das nas ye shes ni /
NK116(le)001:3785: gang gi sangs rgyas sa gnas la //
NK116(le)001:3786: de ni byang chub sems dpa'i sa //
NK116(le)001:3787: bcu pa yin pa shes par bya /
NK116(le)001:3789: yang dag pa ni kun tu 'od kyi sa'o //
NK116(le)001:3790: 'brasa bu'i theb pa nas gsungs pa ste de'i steng du bcu gnyis pa ma chags pad+ma can dang /
NK116(le)001:3791: bcu gsuma rdo rje 'dzin pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3792: bcu bzhi 'khor lo tshogs chen dang /
NK116(le)001:3793: bco lnga bde ba chen po dang /
NK116(le)001:3794: bcu drug ye shes bla ma dang /
NK116(le)001:3801: rdo rje thega pa'i rigas kyi dbye bas dapaga tu
NK116(le)001:3802: meda pa ganga gi don dam pa'i ye shesa rgyud
NK116(le)001:3803: la brten pa ces rtogs pa de'o //
NK116(le)001:3805: riga grola gnyis dang ldana pa yin te /
NK116(le)001:3807: ji lta ji snyed nang gi ni //
NK116(le)001:3808: ye shes gzigs pa dag pa'i phyir //
NK116(le)001:3809: blo ldan phyir mi ldog pa'i tshogs //
NK116(le)001:3810: bla med yon tan dang ldan zhing /
NK116(le)001:3811: ces ji lta ba rig pa'i yon tan /
NK116(le)001:3812: ji snyed pa rig pa'i yon tan /
NK116(le)001:3813: nang ye shes gzigs pa'i yon tan dang gsum /
NK116(le)001:3814: de nyid thob byed kyi thabs su gyur ba'i bar
NK116(le)001:3815: chad med lam gyi ngo skal spang bya chags sgrib
NK116(le)001:3816: thogs sgrib dman sgrib gsum las grol ba'i yon tan
NK116(le)001:3817: te drug / dbye gzhi ni rig pa'i yon tan dang /
NK116(le)001:3818: grol ba'i yon tan bsnan pa'i brgyad do //
NK116(le)001:3819: de lta bu ni byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun la te /
NK116(le)001:3820: nyan ranga gi dge 'dun la rgyun zhugs /
NK116(le)001:3822: dgra bcom pa ste bzhi po dang der zhugs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3823: de'i 'bras bur gansa pa gnyis re ste zhugs gnas
NK116(le)001:3824: gcig tu bsdoms pas skyes bu zunga bzhi'am phral ba'i
NK116(le)001:3825: ya brgyada / rgyal ba'i srasa kyi sa la yang
NK116(le)001:3826: dag para gansa pa matha'a daga pa'i ranga sa'i yona
NK116(le)001:3827: tan brjod kyisa mi langa pa gang zhig mnga' yanga
NK116(le)001:3828: ya brgyada / / lam dang skyobsa pa'i ngo bo dama pa'i chosa la bstan pa yin la /
NK116(le)001:3829: chosa de ni ston pa lasa byunga ba yin mod /
NK116(le)001:3830: de sgrub ba'i grogas sama bslaba pa'i gnas kun gyi brten gansa /
NK116(le)001:3831: dge 'duna yin phyir dkona mchoga gsuma zhesa skyabsa kyi yula mchog tu gruba pa'o //
NK116(le)001:3832: skyabs 'gro'i mtshan nyid ni de la zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:3833: de la rgyu dang 'brasa bura ltos pa'i skyabsa 'gro yi dama baca'a ba gnyis lasa /
NK116(le)001:3834: 'dod bya'i 'bras bu dusa gazhana ma 'ong bar 'gruba par 'doda pa rgyu /
NK116(le)001:3835: da lta gruba pa ranga semas sku gsum gyi ngo
NK116(le)001:3836: bor ji bzhin mthong pa de ni 'brasa bu'i skyabsa
NK116(le)001:3837: 'gro ste rdo rje thega pa daga gi khyad chosa
NK116(le)001:3838: yina no // rgyu'i skyabs yula ni sangs rgyas chos
NK116(le)001:3839: dge 'dun te dakon mchoga rnama pa gsuma gtso zhing
NK116(le)001:3840: yina no // / sngags su de dang de yi
NK116(le)001:3841: ngo bo bla mara 'dusa pa shes pas phyi ma
NK116(le)001:3842: gcig po 'di gtso bor byed do //
NK116(le)001:3843: mthar thug gi dbang du byas na de dag gzugs sku kun rdzob yin la /
NK116(le)001:3844: chos kyang lam gong mar song dus 'og ma dri bcas su 'dor te /
NK116(le)001:3845: nyan rang byang sems rnams kyang da dung sangs rgyas
NK116(le)001:3846: la ltos dgos pas tshad ldan gyi yul min no
NK116(le)001:3847: // de yang rgyud bla ma las //
NK116(le)001:3848: spang phyir bslu ba'i chos can phyir //
NK116(le)001:3849: med phyir 'jig dang bcas pa'i phyir //
NK116(le)001:3850: chos rnams gnyis dang 'phags pa'i tshogs //
NK116(le)001:3851: gtan gyi skyabs gnas ma yin no //
NK116(le)001:3852: skyabs ni sangs rgyas nyag gcig nyid //
NK116(le)001:3853: skyob pa chos kyi sku can phyir //
NK116(le)001:3854: tshogs kyang de yi mthar thug yin /
NK116(le)001:3856: lung de'i dgongs pa ltar na chos dge 'dun bshad ma thag pa bzhin yina du chug kyang /
NK116(le)001:3857: sangs rgyas mthar thug tu basngagasa so zhe na /
NK116(le)001:3858: de'i don so so ni 'di ltar gsal lo //
NK116(le)001:3859: drin lan bsab pa'i mdor gsol ba //
NK116(le)001:3860: gzugs kyi sku la skyabs su mchi'am /
NK116(le)001:3861: chos kyi sku la skyabs su mchi /
NK116(le)001:3863: chos kyi sku la skyabs 'gro yi //
NK116(le)001:3864: gzugs kyi sku la skyabs su 'gro ba ma yin te //
NK116(le)001:3865: gzugs kyi sku sangs rgyas ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:3868: dag thob bral ba'i ye sangs rgyas //
NK116(le)001:3869: mi 'gyur dri med chos dang ni //
NK116(le)001:3870: yon tan lhun rdzogs dge 'dun nyid //
NK116(le)001:3871: yin phyir rang gi sems nyid mchog /
NK116(le)001:3873: skyabs su 'gro ba po rten gyi gang zag la
NK116(le)001:3874: rigs can gsum yod pa nye tshe zhes bya ba
NK116(le)001:3876: nye tshe ba dang mchoga dang bla na meda pa
NK116(le)001:3877: yi kuna slonga gsuma las dang po skyes bu chung
NK116(le)001:3878: ngu ni / ngana 'gro'i sdug bsngal la 'jigas nas
NK116(le)001:3879: mngona mtho'i go 'phang thob kyi bar du 'gro zhing
NK116(le)001:3880: ngu ni / / 'bringa gnyisa srida pa'i sdug bsngal
NK116(le)001:3881: sna tshogs pas 'jigas nasa thara ba don du gnyer
NK116(le)001:3882: zhing dus ni gansa skabsa ji srida 'tsho'i bar dang
NK116(le)001:3883: mathara thuga ni nyan ranga gi 'bra bu thoba pa'i
NK116(le)001:3885: skyes bu chena po gazhana dona spangas ba'i rang nyid
NK116(le)001:3886: zhi bde'i blo la zhen pas 'jigas nas srid par
NK116(le)001:3887: 'khora ro cog pa'i sems can dbugas 'byina chena po
NK116(le)001:3888: sangs rgyas kyi sa la bsgral phyir byang chuba mchog
NK116(le)001:3890: de yanga ranga gi semas rang bzhin gyis rnam par
NK116(le)001:3891: dag pa'i de kho na nyid la bral rgyu'i dri
NK116(le)001:3892: ma dang thob rgyu'i yon tan gsar bsgrub med pas
NK116(le)001:3893: bslu ba spangas pa gang zhig 'brasa bu'am bla na
NK116(le)001:3895: rgyal ba'i thugs rje 'gro khams la mi g.yel ba
NK116(le)001:3896: ni lam dus zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs
NK116(le)001:3897: te / de la rmi lam gyi lam de bzhin du bag chags kyi /
NK116(le)001:3899: 'khrul 'khor ma nges pa'i rgyu dang 'bras bu so
NK116(le)001:3900: sor nges pa'i lam ste rgyud lngas bsdus pa'i 'gro
NK116(le)001:3901: ba la dus der sangsa rgyas rnams ni semas cana
NK116(le)001:3902: gyi khamas la thugas rje 'jug pa dusa lasa yola
NK116(le)001:3903: ba meda de / 'di skad du las brgya ba las /
NK116(le)001:3904: rgya mtsho chu srin gnas pa'i rlabs /
NK116(le)001:3905: dus las yol bar 'gyur srid kyang /
NK116(le)001:3906: gdul bar bya ba'i sras rnams la /
NK116(le)001:3907: sangs rgyas dus las yol mi mnga'/
NK116(le)001:3909: bstod pa brgya lnga bcu pa las /
NK116(le)001:3911: khyad med nyon mongs rnams kyis bcings //
NK116(le)001:3912: khyod ni 'gro ba'i nyon mongs dag /
NK116(le)001:3913: dgrol slad yun ring thugs rjes bsdoms /
NK116(le)001:3915: gang gi rnam mkhyen dngos la lkog tu gyur ba'i
NK116(le)001:3916: shes bya zhig nam mkha'i khongs su mi srid pa
NK116(le)001:3919: khyod 'ba' zhig gi ye shes kyi /
NK116(le)001:3920: shes bya mtha' dag khyab lags kyi /
NK116(le)001:3921: khyod las gzhan pa thams cad kyi /
NK116(le)001:3922: shes bya kho na lhag pa lags /
NK116(le)001:3924: ba spu'i khung bu gciga gi yona tan tsam yanga
NK116(le)001:3925: matha'a daga pa ni sangs rgyas nyid ma gtogs gzhan
NK116(le)001:3926: sa chen po non pa'i byang 'phags rnams kyis kyang
NK116(le)001:3927: brjod pasa 'di tsam mo zhes pa'i mtha' la ma
NK116(le)001:3928: thuga pa ni dper na nama mkha'a ldinga dar la
NK116(le)001:3929: bab pa'i lang tsho rgyags pa zhig bya lam gyi
NK116(le)001:3930: pha mtha' gzhal ba la zhugs na /
NK116(le)001:3931: de la grub pa'i matha'a ma mchis pas ngogs su
NK116(le)001:3932: mi gtugsa te nam zhig rang stobs phri ste ngal
NK116(le)001:3933: zhig dub pa'i mtha' gnyis kyi khur lci bas non
NK116(le)001:3936: bya lam nam mkha' dpag pa nus kyang srid //
NK116(le)001:3937: rgya mtsho bum pas gzhal du rung yang srid /
NK116(le)001:3938: sangs rgyas yon tan pha mtha' rtogs ni nus /
NK116(le)001:3940: de'i phyir skyabs yul gcig las gnyis pa ma mchis
NK116(le)001:3941: pa 'di na zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan
NK116(le)001:3943: yanga nasa yanga du skye ba brgyud de lasa ngana
NK116(le)001:3944: basgas pa'i skyon gyis matshangas cana rnamas 'khora losa bsgyur
NK116(le)001:3945: ba'i rgyal po dang dabnga phyug chen po la sogas
NK116(le)001:3946: pa skyabsa gazhana ganga gisa bslu ba mthonga nasa ni
NK116(le)001:3947: sdug bsngal la 'jigas pa dang thar ba la dang
NK116(le)001:3948: pa dang 'gro ba la snying rje ba dang rnam
NK116(le)001:3949: pa gsuma gyi sgo nas gazhana dona 'ba' zhig semas
NK116(le)001:3950: pa skyes bu chen po'i blos dkona mchoga rin po
NK116(le)001:3951: che gsum gyi yon tan rjesa su drana pasa skyabsa
NK116(le)001:3952: te / su 'agro'o // rgyu'i skyabs 'gro'i phan yon
NK116(le)001:3953: ni ji ltar zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan
NK116(le)001:3954: te / su 'agro'o // te / dpe ji ltar
NK116(le)001:3955: na nama mkha'a tshad gzunga meda pa ni nam mkha'
NK116(le)001:3956: lding gi bgrod pas shes la /
NK116(le)001:3957: de ltar dpe can dkona mchoga gsum la bstan pa'i
NK116(le)001:3958: dakara naga ste dge sdig gi lasa 'brasa kyi pha
NK116(le)001:3960: gal te skyabsa su songa ba'i yon tan gzugas su
NK116(le)001:3961: grub par gyur na nam mkha'i snod du mi shong
NK116(le)001:3962: ba'i phyir de nyid kyis brten para nus pa ma
NK116(le)001:3963: yina pa'o // dus de nas bzung nanga ba sangs
NK116(le)001:3964: rgyas pa'i khyur 'gro zhing sdoma pa matha'a daga gi
NK116(le)001:3965: rtena du rung ba'i gzhir gyur la sdiga sgrib kun
NK116(le)001:3966: madzada cinga gnoda pa'i phyogsa kyis sponga zhing /
NK116(le)001:3967: ngana 'gro'i gayanga sa las bsrung ste dkona mchoga gsuma
NK116(le)001:3968: dang mi 'brala bar phuna suma tshogas pa tshe 'dir
NK116(le)001:3969: mthonga ba'i chosa la 'ong ba dang /
NK116(le)001:3970: rgyu bsoda namsa kyi tshogas rdzogsa shing longs sku dang
NK116(le)001:3971: sprul sku'i gzugas kyi sku gnyis 'grub par 'gyur ro
NK116(le)001:3972: // 'bras bu'i skyabs 'gro'i phan yon ni 'bras bu'i zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:3973: 'brasa bu'i skyabsa 'gro baslu ba meda pa'i yon tan
NK116(le)001:3974: ni rnam par thara ba'i sgo gsum ste stong pa
NK116(le)001:3975: nyid dang / mtshan ma med pa dang /
NK116(le)001:3976: smon pa meda pa'i nang dbyingsa su byang chub pa
NK116(le)001:3977: ni gansa lugas rdo rje 'dus ma byas pa yina
NK116(le)001:3978: pa gang zhig ye shesa kyi tshogas rdzogas 'bras te
NK116(le)001:3979: / ngo bo ye dag rang bzhin 'phral dag ces
NK116(le)001:3980: dag pa gnyis ldan gyi sangs rgyas zhes bya ba
NK116(le)001:3983: bslab bya zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:3984: de yang bslab bya rgyu dang 'bras bu gnyis lasa /
NK116(le)001:3986: rgyal po'i mang'a risa kyi phun tshogs bya daga' thob pa'i slad du mi 'dor ba smos ci dgosa //
NK116(le)001:3987: sroga gi phyir yanga dkona mchoga gsum gtong ba mina no //
NK116(le)001:3988: nang gses so so'i sdom pa ni /
NK116(le)001:3989: mchog gsum de'i ngo bo bla ma yin pas der skyabsa su songa nasa /
NK116(le)001:3990: dama pa bslu ba dang mi snyan sgrogsa pa spanga zhing /
NK116(le)001:3991: de bzhina du sangsa rgyas chosa dang dge 'duna la
NK116(le)001:3992: skyabs su songa nas rima pa bzhina du badga nyid
NK116(le)001:3993: kyis ni 'khora bar 'khora ba'i lta la phyag mi
NK116(le)001:3995: grogs su mu stegsa cana la mi 'grogas pa gsum spang ba'i bslaba bya dang /
NK116(le)001:3996: dkona mchoga gi sku gsung thugs rten la dada pasa bsnyen bskura bya zhing /
NK116(le)001:3997: nyin matshana thun drug gam 'byams klas su brjed pa
NK116(le)001:3998: spangas nas skyabsa su 'gro ba sgrub pa'i bslab bya'o
NK116(le)001:3999: // gnyis pa 'bras bu'i bslab byar thuba pa chosa kyi sku /
NK116(le)001:4000: bral thoba spangas pa'i dbyingsa rang gi de kho na
NK116(le)001:4001: nyid la byang chub pasa skyob dang skyabsa byar mi
NK116(le)001:4002: dmigs pa gang zhig gnyis 'dzina gyi tha snyad las
NK116(le)001:4003: 'das phyir sdom pa gtong rgyu 'ang btags pa bla
NK116(le)001:4005: lam gyi gnas skabs gtong ba'i rkyen ni /
NK116(le)001:4006: rgyu'i zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te rgyu
NK116(le)001:4007: yi bsrung sdom gtong mtshams skyabs 'gro matshana nyid pa
NK116(le)001:4008: dag skyabs su 'gro ba'i yula la loga lta skyes
NK116(le)001:4010: bslaba bya snga ma gsum po'i steng /
NK116(le)001:4012: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong ba dang /
NK116(le)001:4013: dkon mchog mchod pa ste drug po dang 'gal na gtong bar 'dod pa dang /
NK116(le)001:4014: 'ga' zhig de'i steng sku gzugs la sogs pa'i gzugs
NK116(le)001:4015: brnyan gyi sprul pa gsum la brnyas pa la sogs
NK116(le)001:4016: pa la sogs bsnan te dgu po nyamsa na damna
NK116(le)001:4017: pa'i sar lhung ba'i phyir na ji ltar rma'i baga
NK116(le)001:4018: byed pa bzhina du bsgrimsa te bsrunga bar bya ba
NK116(le)001:4019: gal che / de las kyang dmigs bsal gyis skal
NK116(le)001:4020: dman ston phyir las kyi zhes bya ba la sogs
NK116(le)001:4021: gal che / pa gsungs te / log pa'i lasa kyi mthu lce spyang gduga pa lta busa /
NK116(le)001:4022: dge bar chom rkun gyi brtul zhug byed pa'i go
NK116(le)001:4023: skabsa batsala ba'i skye bo rnams ni tshig tsam 'dod
NK116(le)001:4024: rgyal du brjod kyang dona ci yang mi gnas pas
NK116(le)001:4025: 'dzola ba'i yida gnyis te the tshom can gyi snod
NK116(le)001:4026: ngana du / bslu ba meda pa'i dkon mchog gi
NK116(le)001:4027: yon tan la snying nas blo khel ba'i ngesa shesa
NK116(le)001:4028: bri ba'i mngon rtagsa yin la /
NK116(le)001:4029: rmongs pa thos pa nyung zhing 'ching ba can kha cig yi dwaga mthu bo che /
NK116(le)001:4030: gshin rje ru bardzu ba rnams la brten pas tshe
NK116(le)001:4031: 'di nyid la legs smon gyi re 'bras kun nyamsa
NK116(le)001:4032: par 'gyur ro // rgyu mtshan gyi sgo nas yid
NK116(le)001:4033: ches par gdams pa 'di na zhes bya ba la
NK116(le)001:4035: srid pa 'di nasa dang nama mkha'a ri raba rnams
NK116(le)001:4036: chags 'jig dbang gi go 'chol bas yana mana gansa
NK116(le)001:4037: 'gyur zhing nyi zla gnyis kyang go la'i 'khrul 'khor
NK116(le)001:4038: zhig nas de na mi gnas par thanga du lhunga
NK116(le)001:4039: ba'i tha snyad thogs pa sogs mi srida pa yang
NK116(le)001:4041: dkona mchoga gsuma gyis baslu bar gtan nas mi srida
NK116(le)001:4042: pa'i ngesa shesa brtana po 'byams klas 'byongs pa 'di
NK116(le)001:4043: rnam pa kuna tu dona che po yoda pa yina
NK116(le)001:4044: no // de lta'i mjug bsdu ba'i phyir rmi lam zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:4045: de lta'i yid ches thob pa dag la rmi lam na yanga dkona mchoga mthonga ba dang /
NK116(le)001:4046: rtag tu baga yoda dgos pa drana cinga legs tshogs kyi yona tan kuna gyis 'byor ba dang /
NK116(le)001:4047: tshe ra basa drana zhing pha rol tu nying mtshams
NK116(le)001:4048: sbyor tshe bar do'i 'jig pa rnam bgroda para sla
NK116(le)001:4049: ba sogs lusa cana kuna gyi dpunga grogs dang bshes
NK116(le)001:4051: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi le'u drug pa'i 'grel pa'o ////
NK116(le)001:4052: de ltar skyabs su song nas theg pa chen po
NK116(le)001:4053: dngos la 'jug pa'i thog mar mtshan nyid dbye phyir
NK116(le)001:4054: / theg dman zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:4055: theg damna rdzinga bu lta bur gnyer ba de ni /
NK116(le)001:4056: theg chen byang chub sems kyi khams dang de'i rigas lasa nyamsa pa can no //
NK116(le)001:4057: gang na rang don kho nar sems pa'i nyana ranga skyes bu'i semas so //
NK116(le)001:4058: de nyid stong nyid snying rje zung du 'abrelaba'i ded
NK116(le)001:4059: dpona mtshungs lta'i mthusa sada par byas nasa thega pa
NK116(le)001:4060: chena po rgya mtsho lta bur zhugs nas kuna mkhyen
NK116(le)001:4061: rgyal pa'i go 'phang nor bu'i glinga du 'gro'o //
NK116(le)001:4062: tshul ji ltar 'gro na phar phyin drug gi gru gzings la brten nas so //
NK116(le)001:4063: de yang sbyin sogs pha rola tu phyin pa rnam pa lnga'i /
NK116(le)001:4064: stobs kho nas srid rtse las mi brgal ba'i ngo
NK116(le)001:4065: bo lunga du ma bstana pa ste dper na lcagsa
NK116(le)001:4066: khamas ltar tshur mthong gi las su rnama para nyamsa
NK116(le)001:4067: pa gang zhig thabas shesa gsera 'gyur gyi rtsi lta
NK116(le)001:4068: bus theba pa'i moda la lus can yongs kyi gnyen
NK116(le)001:4069: du 'gyur bas na rina thang chena pora byed do
NK116(le)001:4070: // tshul de ji ltar yin zhes dri na gang phyir zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:4071: 'di na ganga sa gsum 'gro ba nyam nga'i g.yang
NK116(le)001:4072: sar mchod pa srid do cog gi phyir du snying
NK116(le)001:4073: rje chen po'i zhag pa 'phen pa ni thabas dang
NK116(le)001:4074: / de'i rang bzhin stong nyid kyi nganga du ro gcig par mthong ba shesa raba ste /
NK116(le)001:4075: phan tshun zunga du 'jug pa'i byang chub kyi semsa
NK116(le)001:4076: zhes mtshan nyid ngos bzung nas gdul bya'i khams la
NK116(le)001:4077: dngos su sbyor ba'i tshul ni 'di ltar sems can
NK116(le)001:4078: tshad med pa la dmigs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:4081: ye shes tshad med pa ste byams sogs tshad meda bzhi'i /
NK116(le)001:4082: sa makhana gyis byang chub smon pa'i sems 'juga pa'i
NK116(le)001:4083: sems gnyis dang bcas pa'i bslaba bya'i rim pa rnams
NK116(le)001:4084: yang dag par slob pa kho na lasa skye ba
NK116(le)001:4085: yin no // tshad med bzhi po so so'i ngo
NK116(le)001:4086: bo ni byams pa zhes bya ba la sogs pas
NK116(le)001:4087: yin no // bstan te / de yang byamsa pa'i
NK116(le)001:4088: ngo bo ni gazhana sems can thams cad bde bar
NK116(le)001:4090: yid la shin tu sduga pa'i ma yisa bu gcig
NK116(le)001:4091: po la brtse byams ji bzhina du lusa dang longs
NK116(le)001:4092: spyod dang / rnam dkar gyi dge ba kuna gcig
NK116(le)001:4093: tu spungsa nasa gazhana la phana 'dogas shing gal te
NK116(le)001:4094: tshur gnoda pa brtsam nas bzoda pa la nan tan
NK116(le)001:4095: spyod dang / bslaba bo // snying rje'i ngo bo
NK116(le)001:4096: gazhana gyi sduga bsngal la bzoda pa'i g.yang lugs ral
NK116(le)001:4097: te bsten mi phod pa'i semas stobsa drag po ches
NK116(le)001:4099: 'gro ba drug po matha'a dag sduga bsngal 'ba' zhig
NK116(le)001:4100: pa'i rgyu 'bras kyi matha'a la gcura par mthonga nas
NK116(le)001:4102: dag'a ba'i ngo bo ni gazhana daga la longs spyod
NK116(le)001:4103: phuna sum tshogas par mthong bas phrag par mi dog
NK116(le)001:4104: par rang gi thob pa lasa kyang rgya cher spro
NK116(le)001:4106: kuna la legas par smon pa bsgom zhing /
NK116(le)001:4107: khong tsho ranga ranga gi sngon bsags bsod nams kyi
NK116(le)001:4108: mthu yisa thoba po snyam la dag'a bar byed cinga
NK116(le)001:4109: / phyin chad kyang de dang mi 'brala bar smona pa yina no //
NK116(le)001:4110: batanga snyomsa kyi ngo bo ni yul la phan gnod
NK116(le)001:4111: mi byed par cham gyis gtong ba min par gnyen
NK116(le)001:4112: dang dgra la byamsa sdang 'dral ba zhig ste 'di
NK116(le)001:4113: ltar phyogsa dang risa su chada pa ma yin te
NK116(le)001:4114: mnyam pa nyid du brdala nas /
NK116(le)001:4115: dgra dang gnyen dang bar mar ltos pa'i 'du shesa gsuma byung ba dang po dang /
NK116(le)001:4116: gsum pa yang gnyis pa'i phyogs su bltas ste /
NK116(le)001:4117: phana 'dogas pa'i yula la mnyam para raba tu spyad
NK116(le)001:4118: pa'i rnam pa'i dge ba dmigas bacasa can ni dmigas
NK116(le)001:4119: meda kyi rtsi yisa sbyar bar bya'o //
NK116(le)001:4120: tshad med bzhi yi mi mthun phyogs tshangs pa'i gnas
NK116(le)001:4121: pa bzhi spang bar gdams par 'dod pa zhes pa
NK116(le)001:4123: de yang 'doda khams su skye bar re ba'i phyir byamsa pa /
NK116(le)001:4124: rang phyogs rgud kyi dog pa sera sna'i snying rje dang /
NK116(le)001:4125: rigs chos cho 'brang sogs mthun phyogs 'byor bas spro ba nga rgyal dga' ba /
NK116(le)001:4126: rgyu 'bras la blo kha ma phyogs par bem po
NK116(le)001:4127: bzhin sdod pa gti muga gi btang snyomsa dang bcas
NK116(le)001:4128: pa 'di ni thara ba'i lam mina te tshangsa pa'i
NK116(le)001:4129: gansa pa bzhi'i phyogsa su nye ba sogs des na
NK116(le)001:4130: 'di lta'i dmiga pa phra mo dang bacasa pa rnam
NK116(le)001:4132: spangs nas 'jig rten las 'das pa'i phyogs 'di na zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:4133: gnas skabs 'di na zhi ba mya ngan 'das pa'i
NK116(le)001:4134: lam dang 'brel ba de yi dmigas pa'i yula ni
NK116(le)001:4135: semas cana thams cada yin kyang /
NK116(le)001:4136: bden grub tu mi sems te ji ltar snang la
NK116(le)001:4137: ranga bzhina meda pa chu zla lta bu'i chosa nyid
NK116(le)001:4138: kyi rol ba'i rnam pa'i sgoma tshul stobsa su gyur
NK116(le)001:4139: pa lasa / byanga chuba smon 'jug semas gnyis skye
NK116(le)001:4140: ba'i rgyur 'gro basa na snga ma las khyad chos
NK116(le)001:4141: dang ldana pa'i tshad meda pa bzhi ru sangs rgyas
NK116(le)001:4143: sgom pa'i tshul byams pa nas bzung go rima cana
NK116(le)001:4144: dang gtong snyams sngon du 'gro bas ngesa pa meda
NK116(le)001:4145: pa yod mod mdor na dmigas pa'i yula ganga rung
NK116(le)001:4146: la skye bar sla ba de la gtad dgos so
NK116(le)001:4147: // go rim la dag grol du byed pa'i gnyen
NK116(le)001:4148: po 'on kyang zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs
NK116(le)001:4149: // te / 'ona kyang byamsa pa bsgomsa pa stobs
NK116(le)001:4150: su gyur pas chagas pa'i rten du gyur na nye
NK116(le)001:4151: ringa brala ba'i btang snyomsa bsgoma pa spo la /
NK116(le)001:4152: de nyid stobs su gyur te rmongsa nasa lunga ma bstan du gyur na /
NK116(le)001:4153: snying rje bsgoma para sposa pasa sduga bsngal gyi rgyu 'brasa 'goga cing //
NK116(le)001:4154: mkha' khyab snying rje 'dzin pa'i stobsa zhana nas risa su chada pa na /
NK116(le)001:4155: dag'a ba bsgom para spos pasa damna pa'i semas skye ba 'goga ste /
NK116(le)001:4156: dag'a ba bsgom pa bul nasa semas rgoda sprosa pa'i yula du gyur na /
NK116(le)001:4157: byamas pa sogas matha'a dbus barjesa nasa spel mara bsgom pa yum bar ma las /
NK116(le)001:4160: snying rje la mnyam par 'jog go /
NK116(le)001:4162: zhes thod rgal du yar mchong mar mchong la rtsal sbyangs bar gsungs bas so //
NK116(le)001:4163: 'bras bu ston pa'i phyir de ltar zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:4164: de ltar bsgoms pasa rnama par smin pa ni mngona
NK116(le)001:4165: para mtho zhing 'doda para lha ma'i lusa rten thob
NK116(le)001:4166: pa dang / ma zad ngesa legas kyi go 'phang
NK116(le)001:4167: yang 'thob ste gnyis ka rgyu mthun dang byed pa'i
NK116(le)001:4168: 'bras bu de 'dra myong ba ni mi mthuna pa'i
NK116(le)001:4169: phyogsa dang bral zhing bde ba kho na 'thoba la
NK116(le)001:4170: pa dang / / dabnga gi 'bras bus yida du
NK116(le)001:4171: 'onga ste bde zhing dag'a ba'i yula la spyod pa'o
NK116(le)001:4172: pa dang / / // byed pa tshad med bzhi
NK116(le)001:4173: po stobsa su gyur ba de yisa dona gnyis 'byor
NK116(le)001:4174: ba'i yona tan 'thoba par 'gyur te ji ltar 'thob
NK116(le)001:4175: na byams pa zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs
NK116(le)001:4177: pasa 'gro ba rnams la bu gcig po ltar brtse
NK116(le)001:4179: la zhe sdang meda cing gazhana gyisa kyang de nyid
NK116(le)001:4181: byamas pa'i ngo bo spros pas stong la ranga bzhina
NK116(le)001:4182: meda pa'i phyir me longa ye shesa mngon du gyur
NK116(le)001:4183: te longas spyod rdzogas pa'i sku 'thoba bo //
NK116(le)001:4184: de bzhin snying rje 'byongsa pasa gazhana gyi sdug bsngal kyang /
NK116(le)001:4185: badga gi khura du 'gro ba ste len cing /
NK116(le)001:4186: 'tshe ba gtan nas brala ba'i semas dang ldan la /
NK116(le)001:4187: khams gsum gyi 'doda chagas phra rgyas dang brala /
NK116(le)001:4188: stong nyid snying rje 'brel zhing so sor rtog pa'i
NK116(le)001:4189: ye shesa mngon du gyur nasa chosa kyi sku ru
NK116(le)001:4191: dag'a ba 'byongsa pasa phraga doga gi rtsa ba rmings nas choda de /
NK116(le)001:4192: chos srid kyi 'byor ba brtana cing zhi bde'i ting
NK116(le)001:4193: 'dzin rgyun mi chad par sems la rang dbang thob
NK116(le)001:4194: nas bsam gtan gyi dag'a ba dmigas pa meda pa
NK116(le)001:4195: dang bya ba gruba pa'i ye shesa mngon du 'gyur
NK116(le)001:4196: te sprul pa'i sku mchoga thoba bo //
NK116(le)001:4197: btang snyomsa 'byongsa pasa badga gazhana ris su mi gcod de /
NK116(le)001:4199: nga rgyal meda cinga zaba pa dang zhi ba'i rtogsa
NK116(le)001:4200: pa skye ba'i phyir rmongas pa meda cinga chosa dbyingsa
NK116(le)001:4201: ye shesa la dbang 'byor ba dang ngo bo nyid
NK116(le)001:4202: sku mngona sum du thoba para 'gyura ro //
NK116(le)001:4203: skabs kyi mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK116(le)001:4204: de ltar zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:4205: de lta bu'i tshad meda pa bzhi'i yona tan ni /
NK116(le)001:4206: rgyu dang 'brasa bu shina tu matha'a yasa pa'i phyir bslu ba meda pa yin te /
NK116(le)001:4207: lam ngana gazhana ma rtogs pa dang log rtogs dang
NK116(le)001:4208: phyogs rtogs kyi gruba matha'a gsum las snga ma gnyis
NK116(le)001:4209: srida pa'i rgyu phyi ma de las thar tsam rung
NK116(le)001:4210: yang stong nyid snying rjera 'agla bas na de dang
NK116(le)001:4212: thara pa dri ma meda pa rgyal srasa dama pa'i lam rmad du byung ba gang zhig /
NK116(le)001:4213: rnyogsa pa de dag zhi ba'i phyir dge ba mthar thug pa 'di la gomas par 'atshala lo //
NK116(le)001:4214: zhes gom dgos so zhes bya ba'i tha tshig go /
NK116(le)001:4215: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi le'u bdun pa'i 'grel pa'o ////
NK116(le)001:4216: da ni 'jug pa'i ngo bo byang chub tu sems
NK116(le)001:4217: bskyed pa'i don gtso bor ston pa'i phyir rnyed pa
NK116(le)001:4218: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:4219: dper na rnyed pa ganga zhig gi dona la ched du dmigs nas yona gyi mchoga stob pa bzhin /
NK116(le)001:4220: tshad meda rnam pa bzhisa thob pa'i 'bras bu ni
NK116(le)001:4221: byang chub kyi semas rin po che smona dang 'juga
NK116(le)001:4222: pa'i shinga rta'i sgyu 'phrul gyi thabas la drangsa pasa
NK116(le)001:4223: zhi bde'i nyan rang gi lta ba ngana pa nyamsa
NK116(le)001:4224: para byed do // spro ba bskyed phyir sdig sdug la sogs par gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:4225: 'di na sdiga dang sduga bsngal gyi rlabs drag po
NK116(le)001:4226: 'khrugs pa 'khora ba'i brtsona rara bcingas pa rnams kyang
NK116(le)001:4227: / byang chub kyi semas bskyeda pa'i moda la rgyal
NK116(le)001:4228: ba'i srasa kyi yul du basngagasa pa'i minga gi coda
NK116(le)001:4229: pana 'thoba pa de la raba tu dag'a nasa 'jiga
NK116(le)001:4230: rten gyi lha dang mira bacasa pas kyang bsti stang
NK116(le)001:4231: / byed do // de'i mi mthun phyogs ni las nyon ces bya ba la sogs pas ston to /
NK116(le)001:4232: lasa dang nyon mongs pa'i muna naga 'thib por 'khrigas pa'i sprin gyi gtos chen po'i bar nasa /
NK116(le)001:4233: skad cig kyang mi sdod pa gtum po'i gloga 'oda
NK116(le)001:4234: 'khyuga lta'i dam pa gsum dang bral ba'i dge ba
NK116(le)001:4235: la skabsa 'agra cung zad gomas kyang rgyun chags su
NK116(le)001:4236: med pa'i phyir bsoda namas tsam po ba des ni
NK116(le)001:4237: / chu shinga bzhina du 'brasa busa bslus pas rtsa ba smad pa'o //
NK116(le)001:4238: dpe'i sgo nas spro ba bskyed pa sa gzhi zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:4239: ji ltar sa gzhi bazanga posa bstan pa'i zhing sa la /
NK116(le)001:4240: dge ba'i lo tog gang btabs pa de ltar phuna
NK116(le)001:4241: suma tshogas pa skye ba ltar ma rgan 'gro ba'i
NK116(le)001:4242: khams la 'khrungs pa'i byanga chub sems kyi ljona shing
NK116(le)001:4243: nam srida pa na 'khor 'das gnyis bsdus kyi legs
NK116(le)001:4244: tshogs 'bras bu manga zhing zhi ba thams cad mkhyen
NK116(le)001:4246: srid las grol byed kyi rgyu'i gtso bo'ang yin pa
NK116(le)001:4247: las nyon zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston te
NK116(le)001:4248: / lasa dang nyon mongas 'du bar byed cing duhkha'am
NK116(le)001:4249: sduga bsngal kuna gyi snoda du gyur ba gang zhe
NK116(le)001:4250: na 'khora ba'i rgya mtsho zab cing barlinga bas gting
NK116(le)001:4251: mtha' mi mngon pa rnam par rtog pa'i rba rlabsa
NK116(le)001:4252: chal chil g.yo ba can de semas can rnams kyis
NK116(le)001:4253: khyim ltar raba tu bzunga du med pa'i chu srin
NK116(le)001:4254: gdug pa'i gre bar tshud pa lasa myur du gdona
NK116(le)001:4255: par byed pa'i thabs sam snying stobsa chena po semas
NK116(le)001:4256: bskyeda pa gcig pu yina pa /
NK116(le)001:4258: srid pa'i sdug bsngal brgya phrag gzhom 'dod cing //
NK116(le)001:4259: sems can mi bde gsal bar 'dod pa dang //
NK116(le)001:4260: bde mang brgya phrag spyad par 'dod pas kyang //
NK116(le)001:4261: byang chub sems nyid rtag tu btang mi bya //
NK116(le)001:4263: de yang mtshan nyid ston par bya ba'i phyir gang la zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:4264: ganga la la dag ranga dona yid byed kyi semas pa rdul tsam yoda pa ma yina pa /
NK116(le)001:4265: bakres pa zasa dang skom pa chur gdung ba bzhina
NK116(le)001:4266: du semas can 'ab'a zhiga gi dona du rnam mkhyen
NK116(le)001:4267: sangs rgyas kyi go 'aphanga gnyer ba la byang chuba
NK116(le)001:4268: kyi semas zhes su gragas pa'o //
NK116(le)001:4269: sems bskyed kyi ngo bo smon 'jug gi khyad par ston pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:4270: de'ang zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:4271: de la'nga 'brasa bura dama baca'a ba smon pa'i semas bskyed yin te /
NK116(le)001:4272: ji ltar zhe na sems can gyi don du sangs rgyas thob par bagyi'o snyam pas so //
NK116(le)001:4274: badga gazhana phan tshun bde ba thob sdug bsngal spangs
NK116(le)001:4275: 'dod kyi blo mnyam pas bsod nams mnyam par bsngo
NK116(le)001:4276: ba dang / bde ba gzhan la gtong zhing sdug bsngal rang gis len pas barje ba dang /
NK116(le)001:4277: sems can gyi phyir du dmyal me'i sdug bsngal myong
NK116(le)001:4278: yang ci ste bdag gis mi bzod snyams pa badga
NK116(le)001:4279: basa gazhana gcesa te gsum du bazhaga pa yanga zhes
NK116(le)001:4280: pa'ang gi sgras rnam grangs gzhan yang yod pa shugs
NK116(le)001:4281: kyis ston no // de lta bu ni bslaba pa'i
