NK116(le)001:4282: gnas kun rgyas par ston pa'i mdo kun gyi don
NK116(le)001:4283: bsdusa pa'i snying po yina phyir de'i ngo bo byamsa
NK116(le)001:4284: pa la sogas tshad meda bzhi la yang dag par
NK116(le)001:4286: rgyu la dama baca'a ba 'juga pa'i semas yina te /
NK116(le)001:4287: ci'i phyir rgyu la zhes gsungs snyams na thams cad
NK116(le)001:4288: mkhyen pa'i 'bras bu rgyu la ltos par rigs pas
NK116(le)001:4289: so // de yi bslaba bya pha rola tu phyin
NK116(le)001:4290: pa druga sogs spyod par 'os pa'i yula yongas su
NK116(le)001:4291: dag pa rnams la bstena pa yin no //
NK116(le)001:4292: rang bzhin rgyas par dbye ba ni /
NK116(le)001:4293: dbye ba'i sgo nasa so skye dang 'aphagas pa'i semas bskyeda gnyis dang tshul khrims kyi /
NK116(le)001:4296: bslaba pa gsuma la ltos pa'i semas bskyed gsuma rnams yod pa las /
NK116(le)001:4297: khyad par tshogas sbyor gyi lam na mosa pasa spyod pa'i sems bskyed /
NK116(le)001:4298: dang po'i sa nasa bdun pa'i bar nyon mongs pa
NK116(le)001:4299: can gyi yid log pas na lhag bsam rnam daga
NK116(le)001:4300: gi sems bskyed / daga sa gsum na rim bzhin
NK116(le)001:4301: yid shes dang sgo lnga'i shes pa dang kun gzhi'i
NK116(le)001:4302: rnam shes gsum log pas rnam para smin pa'i sems
NK116(le)001:4303: gi sems bskyed / bskyed dang // sangsa rgyas kyi
NK116(le)001:4304: sa nasa kuna gzhi log pas sgrib pa spangas ba'i
NK116(le)001:4306: de bzhina tshogs sbyor sogs lam lnga'i rjesa su 'gro
NK116(le)001:4307: ba'i las dang po la sogs semas bskyeda lnga dang
NK116(le)001:4308: pha rola tu phyin pa druga la ltos pa'i de
NK116(le)001:4310: gzhan yang sa matshamas dbye basa nyi shu rtsa gnyis sogas yod de /
NK116(le)001:4312: de yang sa gser zla ba me //
NK116(le)001:4313: gter dang rin chen 'byung gnas mtsho /
NK116(le)001:4314: rdo rje ri sman bshes gnyen dang //
NK116(le)001:4315: yin bzhin nor bu nyi ma glu //
NK116(le)001:4316: rgyal po mdzod dang lam po che //
NK116(le)001:4317: bzhon pa bkod ma'i chu dang ni //
NK116(le)001:4318: sgra snyan chu bo sprin rnams kyis //
NK116(le)001:4319: rnam pa nyi shu rtsa gnyis so //
NK116(le)001:4320: zhes pa'i dpe don phral na /
NK116(le)001:4326: lhag pa'i bsam pa gsum mo //
NK116(le)001:4327: de la 'dun pa dang lhan cig 'dres pa'i chos
NK116(le)001:4328: thams cad mngon par byang chub par 'dod pa'i mtshan
NK116(le)001:4329: nyid can ni sa lta bu'o //
NK116(le)001:4330: bsam pa dang 'dres pa'i sa ni phyin drug gi
NK116(le)001:4331: mtshan nyid de 'gyur ba med pa'i phyir gser bzang
NK116(le)001:4332: po lta bu'o // lhag pa'i sems dang 'dres pa
NK116(le)001:4333: ni byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa
NK116(le)001:4334: bdun po sgom par 'dod pa'i mtshan nyid des dkar
NK116(le)001:4335: po'i phyogs thams cad yar 'phel bar 'dod pas zla
NK116(le)001:4338: sbyor ba dang 'dres pa gcig dang /
NK116(le)001:4339: sbyin pa la sogs pa pha rol tu phyin pa bcu dang /
NK116(le)001:4340: de'i steng du mngon par shes pa dang /
NK116(le)001:4341: bsod nams dang ye shes dang ldan pa dang /
NK116(le)001:4342: byang chub kyi phyogs dang ldan pa dang /
NK116(le)001:4345: chos kyi skyed mo'i tshal dang /
NK116(le)001:4346: bgrod pa gcig pa'i lam dang /
NK116(le)001:4347: chos kyi sku dang ldan pa'o //
NK116(le)001:4348: de la smon pa'i gsum ni tshogs lam /
NK116(le)001:4349: chung 'bring che gsum gyi sems bskyed dang po pa'i gnas skabs yin la /
NK116(le)001:4350: 'dir 'jug pa'i dang po sbyor ba me lta bu ni sbyor lam bzhi'i sems bskyed do //
NK116(le)001:4351: de bzhin sbyin pa gter lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:4352: tshul khrims rin po che'i 'byung gnas lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:4353: bzod pa mtsho lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:4354: brtson 'grus rdo rje lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:4355: bsam gtan ri lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:4356: shes rab sman lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:4357: thabs la mkhas pa bshes gnyen lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:4358: smon lam yid bzhin nor bu lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:4359: stobs nyi ma lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:4360: ye shes kyi pha rol du phyin pa glu dbyangs
NK116(le)001:4361: lta bu ni rgyu'i gnas skabs te mthong ba dang
NK116(le)001:4362: sgom pa'i lam gyi spyod yul can sa dang po
NK116(le)001:4363: nas bcu pa'i bar la rim pa bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:4364: dag sa gsum la khyad chos thun mong pa yod de //
NK116(le)001:4365: mngon shes rgyal po lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:4366: tshogs gnyis mdzod khang lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:4367: byang chub kyi phyogs dang mthun pa'i chos lam po che lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:4368: snying rje dang lhag mthong bzhon pa bzang po lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:4369: gzungs dang spobs pa bkod ma'i chu mig lta bu dang lnga'o //
NK116(le)001:4370: bcu pa kho na la snga ma las khyad par pa yod de /
NK116(le)001:4371: chos kyi dga' ston sgra snyan lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:4372: bgrod pa gcig pa'i lam chu bo lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:4373: chos kyi sku dang mtshungs par ldan pa sprin lta bu gsum mo //
NK116(le)001:4374: bshad ma thag pa'i nyer gcig po tshogs lam nas bcu pa'i bar gsungs la /
NK116(le)001:4375: bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi 'bras bu dang mi sbyor te /
NK116(le)001:4376: sa der chos nyid kyis thob pa'i don dam sems bskyed las dpe mi dmigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:4377: sogs khongs su rgyal ba'i dgongs spyod mtha' yas pa
NK116(le)001:4378: bsdus pa de lta bu'i bsam pasa smona pa dang
NK116(le)001:4379: 'juga pasa spyod pa la khyab la de'i khungs su
NK116(le)001:4381: smon 'jug so so'i yon tan la nges par 'dren
NK116(le)001:4382: phyir gang zhig zhes bya ba la sogs par gsungs
NK116(le)001:4383: te / ganga su zhiga ranga nyid legas pa don
NK116(le)001:4384: du gnyera nas dus rtag tu gcoda pa meda pa'i
NK116(le)001:4385: sgo 'aphara phye ba'i nanga du slong ba po'i yida
NK116(le)001:4387: nang du bsus te tshim par byed pa de la gtan pa meda pa'i mchoda sbyin bagyi'o //
NK116(le)001:4388: zhesa basngagas para 'osa na matha'a daga te tshad med
NK116(le)001:4389: pa'i semas cana rnams kyi dona du phana pa'i smon
NK116(le)001:4390: semas thanga gciga skyes pasa kyang ngana songa gsum gyi
NK116(le)001:4391: sgo gcoda cing lha ma'i gansa rigas su bde ba
NK116(le)001:4392: la bsten pa'i yona tan zad mi shesa par thob
NK116(le)001:4393: par 'gyur ro // de las kyang khyad para 'juga pa'i yona tan pha matha'a yasa te /
NK116(le)001:4394: dngosa su pha rol phyin pa drug dang sbyor basa
NK116(le)001:4395: rgyal sras lam gyi slab byar khyab pa'i cho ga
NK116(le)001:4396: la dus ganga nasa bzunga ste ldoga pa meda pa'i
NK116(le)001:4397: byang chub semas ni 'gro rnams srid mtsho nas sgrola
NK116(le)001:4398: pa'i dama baca'a shina tu yida brtan pasa na /
NK116(le)001:4399: de nasa bzunga ste baga meda par nyin mtshan 'byamsa
NK116(le)001:4400: klas su gnyid du loga kyang bsoda nams kyi tshogs
NK116(le)001:4401: rgyun chagas nyid du 'brel bar 'gyur ba //
NK116(le)001:4402: byang chub spyod pa'i sa lasa 'athada pa dang bacasa bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:4403: tshogs bzlum pa'i tshul bskal ba zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:4404: de yang bskal pa manga po'i tshogsa kyanga skad cig
NK116(le)001:4405: re la 'dumas par gyur pa yod de ji ltar
NK116(le)001:4406: na / ded dpon snying rje chen po'i mi nag
NK116(le)001:4407: mdud thung can bsad pas bskal pa bzhi khri'i tshogs
NK116(le)001:4408: na / 'dums pa dang / bram ze'i khye'u skar
NK116(le)001:4409: mas tshong dpon gyi bu mo'i phyir tshang spyod btang
NK116(le)001:4410: bas tshogs bskal pa nyi khri 'dums pa rnams so
NK116(le)001:4411: na / 'dums pa dang / // don de'i phyir
NK116(le)001:4412: phyugs dang zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te
NK116(le)001:4414: phyugsa dang glang po che'i shing rta lta bu gnyis
NK116(le)001:4415: na / 'dums pa dang / // / dang / nyi zla lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:4416: sogas kyis nyan thos kyi rdzu 'phrul lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:4417: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rdzu 'phrul lta bu yang ston /
NK116(le)001:4418: dpe lnga'i bgroda pa'i brtul zhugas myura bul matha'a yasa pa ltar las phyi ma'o //
NK116(le)001:4419: de yang sems bskyed pa'i skabs su nyan thos 'ba' zhig la 'dun pa dang po //
NK116(le)001:4420: theg pa che chung la 'dres mar spyod pa gnyis pa /
NK116(le)001:4421: dman phyogs dor ba gsum pa /
NK116(le)001:4422: theg chen la mos pa nas kun chub pa'i bar brtson pa bzhi ba /
NK116(le)001:4423: de las kyang ches cher stobs su gyur pa lnga pa ste /
NK116(le)001:4424: snga ma gnyis ni so skyes mi bstan pa dang gsum pa ni brten pa dang /
NK116(le)001:4425: bzhi pa sa dang po nas bdun pa'i bar dang /
NK116(le)001:4426: lnga pa rnam par smin pa'i sas bsdus so //
NK116(le)001:4427: phyogs dang po gnyis phyir ldog go /
NK116(le)001:4428: phyi ma gsum mi ldog go /
NK116(le)001:4429: byang sems dbang po shin tu rtul po rnams ni
NK116(le)001:4430: grangs med sum cu rtsa gsum ste tshogs sbyor gnyis
NK116(le)001:4431: su gsum / sa bcu po re re la'ang gsum gsum mo //
NK116(le)001:4433: tshogs sbyor gnyis la gnyis gnyis /
NK116(le)001:4437: khyad par gzhan don la blo stobsa chen po mnga'
NK116(le)001:4438: basa thabas la brtson pa dang shesa raba kyi mthu
NK116(le)001:4439: phul du byung basa grangas meda gsuma gyi mthar sangs
NK116(le)001:4440: rgyas so zhes dbu ma rin chen sgron mar lung
NK116(le)001:4441: gis grub pa'i dama bazhaga 'jigas pa yina no //
NK116(le)001:4442: de'i 'thad pa ni ji ltar zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:4443: ji ltar sa bona gyi rim pa sa la ltung
NK116(le)001:4444: ba mthun rkyen mang po ma tshogs par chud za
NK116(le)001:4445: ba bzhina byang chub semas kyi mchoga ni bskyed pa
NK116(le)001:4446: tsam mi gtso rang bzhin gyis stobs su gyur la
NK116(le)001:4447: bar chod med pas skyes pa kho na gtso 'o
NK116(le)001:4448: // gang las skye ba'i stobs kyi khyad par stobs gsum zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:4449: bsam pa'i stobs snying rje chen po'i blo 'byongs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:4450: sbyor ba'i stobs tshogs bsags pa /
NK116(le)001:4451: rgyu'i stobs skyabs 'gro khyad par can bya ba ste
NK116(le)001:4452: stobsa gsuma po de lasa ni byang chub kyi semas
NK116(le)001:4453: skye basa na snying rje che dang tshogas basgas skyabsa
NK116(le)001:4454: su 'gro ba gsum la nan tan bya'o //
NK116(le)001:4455: de lta'i bsam pa dang sbyor ba lto sbyor ba rgyu yi stobsa su bashada /
NK116(le)001:4456: rten ni rten gyi zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:4457: rten gyi ganga zaga rnam pa gnyis su bstan te /
NK116(le)001:4458: spyir sems bskyed tsam theg dman la yang yod kyang de'i cho gar spyod pa med de /
NK116(le)001:4459: 'dir theg chen la sems tsam dang /
NK116(le)001:4460: dbu ma ba'i lugs gnyis las dang po ltar na /
NK116(le)001:4461: so so thara pa rigas bduna ganga runga gi sdoma ldana nama yang dgos te /
NK116(le)001:4463: so sor thar pa rigs bdun gyi //
NK116(le)001:4464: rtags tu sdom gzhan ldan pa la //
NK116(le)001:4465: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa yi //
NK116(le)001:4466: skal pa yod kyi gzhan du min /
NK116(le)001:4469: dkona mchoga ta lara bsam pa'i rtena gtso bor gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:4470: de'i rjesa su phyogsa pa ni /
NK116(le)001:4472: 'juga pa'i go skabs shin tu yangas pa yin no //
NK116(le)001:4473: sems de skye ba'i sbyor ba ston pa'i phyir tshogs bsags zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:4474: tshogas rgya cher basgas pa ni byang chub kyi sems lhag para skye ba'i thabas dang /
NK116(le)001:4475: rgyu ni 'gro ba srid do cog kuna kyang bde bar gshegsa pa'i snying po can yin pa dang /
NK116(le)001:4476: rkyen ni dge ba'i bshesa gnyen la raba tu brten pasa ste gsum por ltos dgos la /
NK116(le)001:4477: de yang bshes gnyen ni thos bsam bsgom gsum sogs
NK116(le)001:4478: yon tan mtha' dag gi 'byung gnas yida bzhina gyi
NK116(le)001:4479: nora bu lta bu'i bla ma mchoga /
NK116(le)001:4480: mdo sngags spyi dang byang chub semas kyi thugas brgyud
NK116(le)001:4481: ganga zhig gzhan phan la rtag tu brtson pa desa
NK116(le)001:4482: thoga matha'a bar du dge ba'i chosa spyi'i rim pa
NK116(le)001:4484: rgyan dang sdonga po bkoda pa'i mdo lasa legas par
NK116(le)001:4485: gsungas pa'i byang chub semas kyi yona tan dapaga yasa
NK116(le)001:4486: brjod pa ni kun slong 'chos pa'i thabs kyi don
NK116(le)001:4487: mtha' dag go / tshogs gsogs pa'i sngon 'gro'i sbyor
NK116(le)001:4488: ba rkyang nul zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan
NK116(le)001:4489: mtha' dag go / te / gnas khang gang dag
NK116(le)001:4490: rkyang nul te phyi dor gyis mdzesa shing sdug par
NK116(le)001:4491: ngoma pa'i gansa gzhal yas khanga ltar byas pa yanga
NK116(le)001:4492: mtha' dag go / te / / gura gum sogs
NK116(le)001:4493: dri bzang gi sposa chus brana pa dang bacasa te
NK116(le)001:4494: mtha' dag go / te / / / bslab pa
NK116(le)001:4495: len pa pos kyang gdonga sogs yan lag lnga dag
NK116(le)001:4496: mtha' dag go / te / / / par bkru
NK116(le)001:4497: zhing / dkona mchoga 'ab'a zhiga yida la semas pa
NK116(le)001:4498: yi ngang nas phyi nang gi mchoda tshogas phru ma
NK116(le)001:4499: 'debas la zhes rgya cher bshams pa la dag'a zhing
NK116(le)001:4500: mtha' dag go / te / / / par bkru
NK116(le)001:4501: zhing / dgonga pa'o // de ltar man+dala gyi bkod
NK116(le)001:4502: pa legs par bdar ba'i steng du /
NK116(le)001:4503: dama tshig gi rten sku gsung thugs kyi rten gzugas brnyena rigs /
NK116(le)001:4504: matha'a daga dera bosa nasa zhes gdan drangs shing bzhugs
NK116(le)001:4505: su gsol par byas nas dag pa'i zhing du bzhugs
NK116(le)001:4506: pa'i ye shesa semas dpa'i tshogs rnams 'dun pa'i lcags
NK116(le)001:4507: kyus dguga shing rten la gzhuga pa'i cho ga ni
NK116(le)001:4508: nyams su bstar ba'i mod la 'adza'a gcugas kyis dus
NK116(le)001:4509: btabs pa'i dama baca'a dran pa lasa kyang thugs rjes
NK116(le)001:4510: 'jug pa myur basa rgyal ba sras bcas rnama zhing
NK116(le)001:4511: khamas gazhana du gzigas pa dus las yola nas gnas
NK116(le)001:4512: 'di kho nar dgyes shing brtse ba'o //
NK116(le)001:4513: de'i yan lag ngag 'don gyi rim pa ni /
NK116(le)001:4514: gang zhig ces bya ba la sogs par gsungs te
NK116(le)001:4515: ganga zhiga ces pa spyi la khyab pa'i sgra ste
NK116(le)001:4516: / lusa pa meda pa'i semas cana thams cad kyi
NK116(le)001:4517: skyabs dang mgona dang dpunga gnyen du gyur kyang bduda
NK116(le)001:4518: sde'i dpung tshogs kyi dgra gyur pa ji ltar ji
NK116(le)001:4519: snyed mngon sum par mkhyen cing gzigas pa yi bcoma
NK116(le)001:4520: ldana 'khor dang bcas pa badga gi sdum pa ste
NK116(le)001:4521: gnas khang 'dir 'byon par mchisa su gsola zhes spyan
NK116(le)001:4522: / drangs la / mchod pa ni sgyu ma'i lasa
NK116(le)001:4523: kyisa sprul pa'i rta glang sogs log pa'i kun slong
NK116(le)001:4524: yin pas de lta ma yina no //
NK116(le)001:4526: 'o na 'phrul dga' dang gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi
NK116(le)001:4527: lhas spyad bya dang ma zad ting 'dzin gyis sprul
NK116(le)001:4528: pa'i mchod pa thams cad de ltar thal bar mi
NK116(le)001:4530: phyogs dang po gnyis re zhig 'khor ba'i snang tshod
NK116(le)001:4531: du don byed nus pa kun rdzob yang dag pa
NK116(le)001:4532: yin pa dang / phyi ma ni gdod nas bri
NK116(le)001:4533: gang med pa kun tu bzang po'i mchod sprin rnal
NK116(le)001:4534: 'byor bas ting nge 'dzin gyi lam du drangs pa'i
NK116(le)001:4535: phyir de dang mi mthun no //
NK116(le)001:4536: gang du rkyang nul byed pa sogs so skye thun mong ste /
NK116(le)001:4537: de las lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa
NK116(le)001:4538: ni sras bcas rgyal ba 'byona pa'i shula te gnas
NK116(le)001:4539: ni bdag sogs sems can gyi dri ma 'khru ba'i
NK116(le)001:4540: phyir sku khrus kyi chog gsol ba'i khanga bu ni
NK116(le)001:4541: gser gyi ba gam brtsegsa pa dri bsunga gi ngad
NK116(le)001:4542: pa cana / shela dang nora bu'i sa gzhi dang ka bar ldana zhing /
NK116(le)001:4543: g.yu damra dang mu tig gis bla bre dpyangsa pasa blta na sdug pa'i nang dera /
NK116(le)001:4544: bde bar gshegas pa rnams dang rigas kyi bu mchoga
NK116(le)001:4545: nye sras brgyad sogs kyi tshogs dang bacasa pa la
NK116(le)001:4546: / spos chus ganga ba'i nora bu sna tshogs pa'i buma pa nasa /
NK116(le)001:4547: khrusa kyi rima gro bgyid pa'i bya ba la mkhas
NK116(le)001:4548: pa smina ma sogs byad kyi rnam pa du mas
NK116(le)001:4549: legas shing mdzes ma mang pos glu dang gara dang
NK116(le)001:4550: / rola mo'i rnam par 'gyur ba dag phan tshun
NK116(le)001:4551: 'gran pa lta bu la brtsona bzhin nye rega ste
NK116(le)001:4552: khrus kyi cho ga makhasa pa'i ri dwagas miga can
NK116(le)001:4553: ma gzhan dag gis kyang khrus gsol 'phral /
NK116(le)001:4554: 'og tu ston pa'i dar gyi dril phyis dang spos
NK116(le)001:4555: mar gyis bsku mnye'i srid zhusa brel zhing g.yeng ba'ang
NK116(le)001:4556: kha tog gciga tu mi gansa te ji ltar na
NK116(le)001:4557: dabnga po'i mtshona zhes mkha' la 'ja' tshon bkra ba
NK116(le)001:4558: lta bu thabas su btagsa pa'i rnam pa meda pa'i
NK116(le)001:4559: lha rdzasa sogs kyis mchod pa de rnams sems las
NK116(le)001:4560: su rung ba'i stobs kyi khug pa yin pas na
NK116(le)001:4561: nyo pa'o // gzhan yang dapaga bsam ljona pasa btsonga
NK116(le)001:4562: ba'i zhes snyan ngag mkhan gyis rab btags kyi rgyan
NK116(le)001:4563: nyo pa'o // te / de las byung ba'i dar
NK116(le)001:4564: pany+tsa li ka gdos skyon bral bas lcid kyis nona
NK116(le)001:4565: pa spangsa shing sraba la 'ajama zhing yanga ba'i gosa
NK116(le)001:4566: de nyid la dri bzang dang sposa chus bgosa shinga
NK116(le)001:4567: nyo pa'o // te / byugsa pa dang / rina
NK116(le)001:4568: thanga 'di tsam mo zhes kha tshon bcad na brjod
NK116(le)001:4569: pa po la khrela ba'i rina chena rgyan gyi bye
NK116(le)001:4573: coda pana la sogas pa 'di rnams 'bul bar bgyid na /
NK116(le)001:4574: 'doda pa'i yona tan spangas pa'i thuba dabnga rnams kyis
NK116(le)001:4575: kyanga bkrena ldana te dbul phongs kyi nyams thag pa
NK116(le)001:4576: rnams bsoda namas rgya cher thob pa'i slad du badga
NK116(le)001:4577: gir bzhesa shig / de'i nye 'khor 'jiga rten dabnga phyug la sogas nye ba'i sras chen po brgyad /
NK116(le)001:4578: ngana songa kuna 'drena la sogas skal bazanga gi semas
NK116(le)001:4579: dapa'a bcu druga dang ni khyim pa'i tshul bzung ba'i
NK116(le)001:4580: byang sems chen po chosa 'aphagas dang rtag tu ngu
NK116(le)001:4582: dri ma meda para gragas pa la sogs pa la'ang dbula bar bgyi'o //
NK116(le)001:4583: stong gsuma ciga chara khyab pa'i dri'i gzhona pa ni rlung ste /
NK116(le)001:4584: der 'khyud pa'am khyab pa'i tsana dana dang sposa sna
NK116(le)001:4585: tshogs kyisa bsunga zhima drisa bsoda namas bye ba'i 'byung
NK116(le)001:4586: gansa ni sangs rgyas te gang gi matshana dpe'i byad
NK116(le)001:4587: kyis gsera lan mang bzhu btul byas te sbyangsa pa
NK116(le)001:4588: ni ches legs kyang de yang mog mog por bgyid
NK116(le)001:4589: pas na brtan pa 'phroga ces basngagasa pa de la
NK116(le)001:4590: phyugsa para bgyi'o // tshad med batanga snyomsa rgya khyon yangas pa'i /
NK116(le)001:4591: shel gyi sa gzhi'i ngos la /
NK116(le)001:4592: skyon bral byamsa pa'i pad+mo ge sara stong phrag brdala bar /
NK116(le)001:4593: ris med snying rje'i nyi zla bkraga tu 'tshora ba bstar ba la /
NK116(le)001:4594: dag'a ba chena po rtsom pa'i bdag nyid /
NK116(le)001:4595: bcoma ldana 'khora dang bacasa pa bzhugas su gsola /
NK116(le)001:4597: lus gus tshul bab bcol la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:4598: baba bcola bag med byu nga rgyal la gomas pa'i
NK116(le)001:4599: skyon mina pa'i lusa btud kyi rnam pas snying gara
NK116(le)001:4600: gusa bacasa kyi / mngona rtogsa ngoma pa la /
NK116(le)001:4601: me tog gi dogsa pasa thal mo'i snod de /
NK116(le)001:4602: raba tu bazanga ba ces 'di yang snyan ngag gi rgyan te /
NK116(le)001:4603: don du sdong bu me tog gi mgo lcogs can
NK116(le)001:4604: snyim pa'i snod thal mo kha sbyar te ga'u chung
NK116(le)001:4605: gi dbyibs ltar byed pa'i brtul zhugas ngoms bzhin 'dzina
NK116(le)001:4606: pa yina / rigas pa dang zhabas su ldana pa
NK116(le)001:4607: sogs gong du bshad zin pa'i bde bar gshegas pa
NK116(le)001:4608: rnams kyi yona tana ci rig pa matha'a daga gansa
NK116(le)001:4609: pa'i sangs rgyas khyod kyisa bdag bashala ba ste /
NK116(le)001:4610: sngon chad ring du btang bzhina pa /
NK116(le)001:4611: deng mi ldog dang ba'i skyed mosa tshala du 'ongas pa'i moda la skyo ba'i sems /
NK116(le)001:4612: mina par dad pa'i rlung shugs drag pos ba spu'i 'khri shing gcig tu gzengas pa'o //
NK116(le)001:4613: de ltar dad pa bskyed nas yan lag bdun pa 'bul ba las dang po phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK116(le)001:4614: zla gzhon zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsung te /
NK116(le)001:4615: zla 'oda khrusa la 'juga pa'i zhes sprin bral zla
NK116(le)001:4616: ba'i snang brnyan 'char du rung ba rdzinga bu'i dwangs
NK116(le)001:4617: pa'i tshad de'i nang du pho med pa'i shugs kyi
NK116(le)001:4618: bu mo zhes rma bya'i bu mo 'jo sgega can
NK116(le)001:4619: gyi khyu tshogs rnams rtse dgas rola ba lta bu'i
NK116(le)001:4620: dpe bzhin bdag kyang yang dag par spro ba'i lus
NK116(le)001:4622: sa chen po'i rdula gyi rnam grangas dang phan tshun
NK116(le)001:4623: shina tu 'khrula ba bskyed para byed de dbye ba
NK116(le)001:4624: mi phyed par 'phrul nas phyag 'tshal ba 'ba' zhig
NK116(le)001:4625: gisa brel lo // gnyis pa mchod pa'i yan lag
NK116(le)001:4626: ni gtong ba'i zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs
NK116(le)001:4627: gisa brel lo // te / gtong ba'i yan lag
NK116(le)001:4628: gzhi bsam pa sbyor ba mthar thug bzhi rdzogas pa'i
NK116(le)001:4630: desa kyang mtshona para mi nus pa dpe meda pa
NK116(le)001:4631: yida kyisa sprul pa bla na mchisa pa ma yina
NK116(le)001:4632: pa'i mchoda pa'i sprina 'phags pa kuna tu bazanga po'i
NK116(le)001:4633: mchod pa'i yona tan la phraga doga bgyida pa lta
NK116(le)001:4634: bu'o // rnam pa gcig tu na bla na med pa'i mchod pa 'di yin te /
NK116(le)001:4635: nam mkha' mdzod kyi mdo las //
NK116(le)001:4636: byang chub tu sems bskyed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:4638: sems can la snying rje bsgom pa dang /
NK116(le)001:4639: chos bsgrub pa dang bzhir gsungs pa'o //
NK116(le)001:4640: de mchod pa cis 'grub na rgyal ba dgyes pa'i thabs de las gzhan med pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:4641: gsum pa sdig pa bshags pa'i yan lag ni mu cor zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te //
NK116(le)001:4642: de yang sdig pa'i sgo drug ni /
NK116(le)001:4643: dug gsum kun slong yin la lus ngag yid gsum
NK116(le)001:4644: ni byed por grub kyang gtso che ba'i ngos nas
NK116(le)001:4645: kha sdig pa'i sgo yin pas dngos su gsungs pa
NK116(le)001:4646: 'di ltar mu cora smra ba ngag gi mi dge
NK116(le)001:4647: bzhi la brtson pa'i lasa dang yid ni dug can
NK116(le)001:4648: nyid yin pas baga chagas mtha' dag der bsags pa'i
NK116(le)001:4649: sdiga sgrib bcas dge ba'i las la 'jigas nas gazhana
NK116(le)001:4650: du brosa pa lus med pa'i gzugas su gyur ba'i
NK116(le)001:4651: skye bo rnams / srida pa'i muna naga ste ma
NK116(le)001:4652: rig gti mug shin tu stuga po'i klung der 'achaba
NK116(le)001:4653: pa kun mi dge ba'i las spyod na las de
NK116(le)001:4654: las 'gyod pa mang ba sun 'byin pa dang mi
NK116(le)001:4655: dge ba'i las spyod kyang gnyen po dge ba'i las
NK116(le)001:4656: la shin tu brtson pa kun tu spyod pa dang
NK116(le)001:4657: skye bo rnams / / sdom pa yang dag pa
NK116(le)001:4658: blang nas sdig pa mi byed pa'i sdom pa thob
NK116(le)001:4660: sangs rgyas chos dge 'dun gsum la skyabs su 'gro
NK116(le)001:4661: nas byang chub sems mi gtong ba rten gyi ste
NK116(le)001:4662: stobsa bzhi'i nyin byed 'abra basa sbyangsa shinga bashagas so
NK116(le)001:4663: // bzhi pa rjes su yi rang ba'i yan lag
NK116(le)001:4664: ni sbyor ba zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan
NK116(le)001:4665: // te / sgo gsum rnal mar bzhag nas sbyor
NK116(le)001:4666: ba ganga gisa badga nyid ma 'khrugas bzhina du gzhan
NK116(le)001:4667: gyi dge ba bsgrub par byed pa la dga' ba'i
NK116(le)001:4668: bsam pa'i khyad para gciga gisa gazhana pa daga gisa
NK116(le)001:4669: rnama dakar bsod nams kyi phung po yud tsam la
NK116(le)001:4670: 'phroga pa'i choma rkuna gyi brtul zhugas rjesa su yi
NK116(le)001:4671: ranga ba kho nasa byas so //
NK116(le)001:4672: de yang phrog pa med la bsod nams thob pa'i
NK116(le)001:4673: phyir phrogs zhes dpe zlar rung ba dan+da'i tshig gi
NK116(le)001:4674: rgyan du drangs pa yin no //
NK116(le)001:4675: lnga pa chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i yan lag ni /
NK116(le)001:4676: thar med ces bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:4677: 'di ltar thara ba'i go skabs meda pa 'khora ba'i khri mun te /
NK116(le)001:4678: der gnas 'gro ba'i spyod pa bskala pa'i rlung ltar 'khrugs pas bdag nyid ma dul zhing /
NK116(le)001:4679: las nyon shugs kyi rnama para sra zhing mkhregas par myong bas na tha ba ste /
NK116(le)001:4680: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas ganga gisa kyang 'dula ba'i thabas
NK116(le)001:4681: kyi spyod yul du ma gyur bas brtana pa brala
NK116(le)001:4682: ba rnams la dam pa'i chosa kyi 'khora lo gang
NK116(le)001:4683: la gang 'tshams kyi phrin las rtsi brnon stong phrag
NK116(le)001:4684: 'bar ba zab cing barlinga pa'i don gyi mu khyud
NK116(le)001:4685: 'dzin pa de bskora bar bskul lo //
NK116(le)001:4686: drug pa mya ngan las mi 'da' bar bzhugs gsol gyi yan lag ni /
NK116(le)001:4687: rgyal dang zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs ste /
NK116(le)001:4688: 'das pa'i rgyal dang de srasa bcas pa rnams kyis
NK116(le)001:4689: spangsa bar gyur ba'i 'gro ba 'di rnams kyis snyigs
NK116(le)001:4690: ma lnga ba do'i sduga bsngal gyi gansa skabs bstan
NK116(le)001:4691: par mthonga nasa / da lta'i rgyal ba sras bcas
NK116(le)001:4692: kun nam zhig ma rgan 'gro rnams khyed dang skal
NK116(le)001:4693: ba mnyam par ma gyur bar du mya ngana 'ad'a
NK116(le)001:4694: ba mina par gsol ba 'debs pa'i phyir du gadna
NK116(le)001:4696: lus srog gi gtsos dngosa po kuna gyi rina thanga gciga tu spungsa nas dbul bar bagyi'o //
NK116(le)001:4697: bdun pa bsngo ba'i yan lag ni bdag tu zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:4698: 'di dngul chu'i sbyong bas lcags khams gser du bsgyur ba gnas skabs gsum ste 'dar ba dang /
NK116(le)001:4700: mtho bar 'phags pa'i skab gsum gyi gser du 'gyur
NK116(le)001:4701: ba'i dpe dang sbyang te badga tu lta basa bcing
NK116(le)001:4702: ba mi brtan pa 'dra bar gyur ba'i rnama dakara
NK116(le)001:4703: dman pa lcags khams lta bu yanga /
NK116(le)001:4704: srida para rgyu ba na lana ciga mngon mtho thob nas bde 'gro'i sgra grags pa cho nge ste /
NK116(le)001:4705: de nyid bla na med pa'i byang chub tu bsngo
NK116(le)001:4706: ba'i gsera 'gyura rtsi lta busa thebas par byed pa
NK116(le)001:4707: 'di ni ston pa gzhan gyi ste mu stegs sogs
NK116(le)001:4708: la lta ci nyan rang gi lugas la'ang meda do
NK116(le)001:4709: // tshul de ci lta bu zhig yin snyam na /
NK116(le)001:4711: dang po ni sdug bsngal gsum gyi rgyal tshud pa'i
NK116(le)001:4712: sems can snying rje snyam ste sangs rgyas kyi go
NK116(le)001:4713: 'phang brnyes phyir bsngo ba sems can la dmigs pa
NK116(le)001:4714: dang / 'gro ba rlung gis g.yo ba'i chu nang
NK116(le)001:4715: gi zla gzugs ltar skad cig gis 'jigs par mthong
NK116(le)001:4716: nas snying rjes bsngo ba chos la dmigs pa /
NK116(le)001:4717: de bzhin tu 'gro ba chu nang gi zla gzugs
NK116(le)001:4718: ltar rang bzhin nyid kyis ma grub par snang yang
NK116(le)001:4719: des stong bar mthong nas snying rje bzhin bsngo ba
NK116(le)001:4721: kun slong rnam par ma dag pa'i mchod pa ni
NK116(le)001:4722: skyon can yin phyir chog shes zhes bya ba la
NK116(le)001:4724: 'di na gang zhig 'byor bas choga shesa thob pa
NK116(le)001:4725: bduda rtsi'i btung bar mtshungs bas 'tsho bar byas te
NK116(le)001:4726: 'byor bas mchod sbyin ma byas na /
NK116(le)001:4727: longs spyod kyis ma ngomas par chags nasa zhing bsam
NK116(le)001:4728: dngos po gsum skyes bu'i yida la ma bzunga na
NK116(le)001:4729: / ltar snang chos brgyad dang 'dres pa'o //
NK116(le)001:4730: kun bzang mchoda pa'i sprin du dmigs pas sprul nas
NK116(le)001:4731: 'bul zhes kha skad che yanga don gyi stong ste
NK116(le)001:4732: tshiga gisa pha mathara 'khyamsa pa la skrag par gyur
NK116(le)001:4733: nasa badga gi lusa yang sras bcas rgyal ba bzhugs
NK116(le)001:4734: pa'i stan da 'bula ba la'ang do gala chen po
NK116(le)001:4735: bgyid 'tshal lo // mchog gsum rin po cher blo
NK116(le)001:4736: khel na don che ba dkon mchog ces bya ba
NK116(le)001:4738: dkona mchoga gsuma gyi 'abngas su dam bacasa pa'i 'gro ba su yang rung ste /
NK116(le)001:4739: gang gi skyabs grib nyi ma'i tsha gdung bsila byed
NK116(le)001:4740: so ka'i me tog lang tsho'i 'jo sgeg cana lta
NK116(le)001:4741: bu 'di rnam pa kuna tu rgyu mtshan med par
NK116(le)001:4742: khong drag por 'khrugsa pa'i gshina rje'i pho nya 'am
NK116(le)001:4743: mduna sara yanga / khro gnyer 'jigas pa'i rina thanga
NK116(le)001:4744: zada par mi shesa pa yin na gzhan smos ci
NK116(le)001:4745: mduna sara yanga / 'tshal / de ltar yan lag
NK116(le)001:4746: bdun pa sngon rjes su 'brel bar sems sbyangs pa'i
NK116(le)001:4747: tshul 'di'i yon tan des ni zhes bya ba la
NK116(le)001:4749: desa ni gati muga gi mthusa nona pa'i sdiga ldana badga dang gzhan dag /
NK116(le)001:4750: ji ltar byi dora shina tu bsten pa'i dwangsa shela
NK116(le)001:4751: ltar du bsoda namas kyi rnyog pa sgrib pa'i skyon
NK116(le)001:4752: rnams rab tu dwangas pa'i semas kyi nanga du semas
NK116(le)001:4753: baskyed kyang cho gasa thoba pa'i smon 'jug gi sdom
NK116(le)001:4754: pa yang dag pa'i gzugas brnyana ngoma par 'gyur ro
NK116(le)001:4755: // dngos gzhi ni dang por tshogs zhing la gdung ba bskyed pa /
NK116(le)001:4756: nyes pa zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:4757: de yang bdag sogs dug lnga'i gzhan dbang du gyur
NK116(le)001:4758: ba'i steng du sdig to'i mda' lnga dang bcas pa
NK116(le)001:4759: bsnun pa'i nyes pa bargya phrag gis gayanga sara ltung
NK116(le)001:4760: bar ma zad de yi sdong zlar rtog tshogs brgyad
NK116(le)001:4761: khri bzhi stong gi rimas kyi nad drag po gsor
NK116(le)001:4762: mi rung basa shina tu btab pa'i nada pa rnams
NK116(le)001:4763: ni / yan lag brgyad pa so ma ra dza
NK116(le)001:4764: sogs kyi rig pa khongs su chud pa'i gso dpyad
NK116(le)001:4765: mkhan phala pa'i mduna sara gtugs kyang dbugas mi phyin
NK116(le)001:4766: ni / no // 'o na thabs zad dam zhe na /
NK116(le)001:4767: sman pa'i mchoga rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas la skyabsa su song bas bde blag tu gso bar 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:4768: de bas na lhag para donga zhig /
NK116(le)001:4769: tshogs zhing gsal gdab ni mos pa zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:4770: gdul bya'i mosa pa ganga gi slada du 'dira gshegas
NK116(le)001:4771: nasa gdan gshoms pa nyid la bzhugs su gsol cig
NK116(le)001:4772: / su zhe na semas cana thams cad kyi khamas
NK116(le)001:4773: la nyin lan gsum mtshan lan gsum ste dus drug
NK116(le)001:4776: su ni gdul bar bya ba'i dus la babs par gzigs shing dgongas pa'i ston pa mchoga rnams ni /
NK116(le)001:4777: thega pa chena po'i skyes bu 'ab'a zhiga pa'i tshogas
NK116(le)001:4778: kyi dbus na mtshan dpe'i mngon rtogs lham mera mdzesa
NK116(le)001:4779: pa la'o // slob dpon klu sgrub dang zhi ba
NK116(le)001:4780: lha'i lugs ltar smon 'jug stabs gcig pa'i byang sdom
NK116(le)001:4781: gyi cho ga mtshan nyid pa ston pa'i phyir skyabs
NK116(le)001:4782: su zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:4783: dkon mchog gsum la skyabsa su 'gro ba lan gsuma
NK116(le)001:4784: gyi gzhi bacasa sdom pa len pa'i tshul skyabs 'gro
NK116(le)001:4786: sdom pa kun la yod mod kyang //
NK116(le)001:4787: skyabs su ma song pa la med //
NK116(le)001:4789: de nas sems bzung ba'i phyir bsam pa rtse gcig
NK116(le)001:4790: pas skyabs yul 'bod nas bdag la dgongas su gsola
NK116(le)001:4791: ba rnams suma gyis mdun mkhar sada par byas nas
NK116(le)001:4792: ngag 'don gyi rim pa gzhan du shes la 'dir
NK116(le)001:4794: rgyal ba sras dang bacasa pa'i thugas bskyed dang bslaba
NK116(le)001:4795: pa'i brtula zhugas kyi rim pa matha'a daga rnams yang
NK116(le)001:4796: dag par bdag gis blangsa pa yina no zhes so
NK116(le)001:4797: // ji ltar sems bskyed na nyon sgrib nad kyi zuga ngu lta bu'i duma bu bacada par gyurakyanga /
NK116(le)001:4798: shesa sgriba gnyen po'i yula gyi ro la bacaga pa
NK116(le)001:4799: yi nyan ranga dgra bcoma theg chen sar ma bsgrala
NK116(le)001:4801: sgrib pa gnyis ka'i 'chinga bas kuna nasa dam por
NK116(le)001:4802: dkrisa pa yi tshangas pa la sogas so so'i skye
NK116(le)001:4803: bo nasa / sloba pa 'aphagas pa'i bar la gansa
NK116(le)001:4804: so cog pa yi semas cana ma grola ba rnams
NK116(le)001:4805: dgrola ba dang shina tu sduga bsngal draga po'i shugas
NK116(le)001:4806: ringa ba las dbugs 'byin thoba pa meda pa'i ngana
NK116(le)001:4807: songa gsuma ni gong du le'u bzhi bas bstan la
NK116(le)001:4808: bo nasa / / de dag dbugas 'byin chena po
NK116(le)001:4809: lha ma'i gansa la sbyar ba dang dera yang ma
NK116(le)001:4810: zad mdora dri la na rten cinga 'brela 'byunga bcu
NK116(le)001:4811: gnyis kyi 'khora lo'i rgyar tshud pa'i semas can yoda
NK116(le)001:4812: do cog rnams srid zhi'i mtha' la mi gnas pa'i
NK116(le)001:4813: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shesa chen po mya
NK116(le)001:4815: dgoda byed kyi cho ga ni byang sems lam rim
NK116(le)001:4816: yin pa la des ji ltar bstan pa'i bslab bya
NK116(le)001:4817: bzunga ba'i brjod pa rnams ni sngona dus byon pa'i
NK116(le)001:4818: dranga sronga rnams kyi lugas la brten pa'o //
NK116(le)001:4819: de ltar blangs nas kyang rtag tu nyin dang matshana
NK116(le)001:4820: mora lana gsum gsuma du byang chuba semas gnyisa bskyed
NK116(le)001:4821: la nana tan bya ba gal che'o //
NK116(le)001:4822: 'thob tshul gyi nges pa ston phyir 'dun pa'i zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:4823: de ltar 'thob po sems na 'duna pa'i rtse la
NK116(le)001:4824: chosa mthun gyi yon tan rnams rkyen gyis chagas par
NK116(le)001:4825: 'gyur basa bshad ma thag pa lan gsum brjod pa
NK116(le)001:4826: las dang posa smona pa dang /
NK116(le)001:4828: gsuma pasa gnyis ka brtan pa thoba pa ni /
NK116(le)001:4829: pan+di ta rgya mtsho'i sprin gyisa bzheda pa bla na meda pa'i chos so //
NK116(le)001:4830: de ltar sems thob nas phyi phyir rgyas pa'i phyir
NK116(le)001:4831: rang la gzengs bstod pa sngon chad zhes bya ba
NK116(le)001:4833: sngona chada gazhana gyi dona la de lta'i bslab pa thos bsam bsgom pa lta ci smos /
NK116(le)001:4834: ranga dona nyid du rmi ba'ang ma myongsa pa'i rina
NK116(le)001:4835: chena semas kyi khyud para gasla ba ngo skal thob
NK116(le)001:4836: pa 'disa badga gi mi'i srida pa rgyu lus kyi
NK116(le)001:4837: gog po 'di nyid stong gsum nor gyi gzhal yang
NK116(le)001:4838: rina thanga meda para byas pa e ma ngo mtshar
NK116(le)001:4839: ro // rgyu gang gis na rigs las zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:4840: 'jig rten 'di na gdol ba g.yung po sogs riga
NK116(le)001:4841: lasa nyamsa dmas pa ganga zhiga cho rigas dang ldan
NK116(le)001:4842: pa'i rgyal po'i srid kyi mnga' thang la dbang bskur
NK116(le)001:4843: na lhaga para btsuna pa'i gansa thoba pa ji bzhina
NK116(le)001:4844: du / bdag cag sngon chad byang sems kyi rigs las nyams par kha tshon chod pa zhig na /
NK116(le)001:4845: rgyal ba kuna gyi srasa su denga nas bzung ste
NK116(le)001:4846: gyur basa byang chub semas dapa'a zhes bya ba'i dkon
NK116(le)001:4847: pa'i mchog de'i minga gi coda pana rmad du byung
NK116(le)001:4848: ba de bla ma'i bka' drin gyis thoba pas so
NK116(le)001:4849: // rang gzhan spro ba bskyed pa'i phyir srid pa gsum zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:4850: sa 'og sa steng sa bla ste srida pa gsuma
NK116(le)001:4851: gyi badga po byas pa ni lha'i gtso bo rnams
NK116(le)001:4853: 'di na rgyal po zhes bya ba'i sgra ldir po
NK116(le)001:4854: che rmongas pa'i bla dagas dpyangsa pa tsam la'ang dag'a
NK116(le)001:4855: bar byed na / de dag las ni bsam gyis
NK116(le)001:4856: mi khyab pas mngon par 'phags pa byang chub semas
NK116(le)001:4857: dpa'i gansa skabs thoba pa de ringa tsam yin te
NK116(le)001:4858: bar byed na / / ji ltar dag'a ba'i khri
NK116(le)001:4859: shinga yongs 'du sa brtol ljon pa 'gyel nas ring
NK116(le)001:4860: du ma song bar slar slong bar gyur ba la
NK116(le)001:4861: lha yanga ste yang gi sgras mi yang spro ba
NK116(le)001:4862: bzhin du bdag cag lus can yongs kyi sman du
NK116(le)001:4863: 'gyur bas na kun gyi brtse zhing phyogsa par 'gyur
NK116(le)001:4864: bar byed na / / ro // dus ma yin
NK116(le)001:4865: pas 'chi bar mi 'gyur bas na 'chi badga gi
NK116(le)001:4866: bdud 'jomas pa'i bduda rtsi mi zada pa'i gter lta
NK116(le)001:4867: bu dang dbul ba sela pa'i gnyen por yid bzhin
NK116(le)001:4868: gyi nora bu rin po che dang mtshungs shing 'du
NK116(le)001:4869: ba'i ljong snyoms par gnas pas nada zhi ba'i sman
NK116(le)001:4871: srida pa'i lam du yin ring sa 'phyan pas sems
NK116(le)001:4872: stobs la sha thang zhing duba pa'i mgrona po'i ngala
NK116(le)001:4874: badga ni denga nasa 'gro ba srid do cog ba'i nyer 'tshora 'gyur ba yin no //
NK116(le)001:4876: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi le'u brgyad pa'i 'grel ba'o ////
NK116(le)001:4877: da ni bslab bya'i gnas ston pa'i thog mar bag
NK116(le)001:4878: yod dgos pa sngon chad zhes bya ba la sogs
NK116(le)001:4879: pas ston te / de yang sngona chada legas para
NK116(le)001:4880: ma brtagsa par baba bcola gyi spyod pa chos brgyad
NK116(le)001:4881: kyis g.yeng ba'i bya ba gang zhig mu mtha' med
NK116(le)001:4882: par 'khyams pa'i rgyu yin na'ang tshur mthong gis 'di
NK116(le)001:4883: bya 'di byed kyi dama bca' bzung ste gtong ba
NK116(le)001:4884: la'ang rung min yida gnyis kyi gansa mchi na /
NK116(le)001:4885: 'dir rgyal dang de srasa rnams kyi shesa raba chen po'i mthusa /
NK116(le)001:4886: gdona mi za bar brtagsa shing dpyad pa'i blang ba
NK116(le)001:4887: dang dora ba'i gansa gsungs pa dag batanga na badga
NK116(le)001:4888: gisa semas cana kuna bslus par 'gyur pasa //
NK116(le)001:4889: mu matha'a meda pa'i ngana 'gro'i g.yang sar 'khyamsa para 'gyur to //
NK116(le)001:4890: de'i phyir semsa cana gciga gi bde ba yanga /
NK116(le)001:4891: bshigas nas badga nyid nyamsa pa'i lasa mi rigs pa mi bgyid do //
NK116(le)001:4892: snyams pa'i zhe da ma bca' ba gal che'o //
NK116(le)001:4893: byang sems kyi bslab pa blangs pa la ltung ba dang byang chub kyi semas stobsa /
NK116(le)001:4894: gnyis kara ldana na'ang 'khora ba srid rtse nas mnar
NK116(le)001:4895: med par resa mos kyi 'dre ldog byed pa ganga
NK116(le)001:4896: yina pa mos pas spyod pa'i sa thoba pa tsam
NK116(le)001:4897: la yang yuna ringa 'thogas par 'gyur na rab tu
NK116(le)001:4899: de bas na bslaba bya'i gnas gtong ba'i skyes bu
NK116(le)001:4900: smon pa yina na ma gtogs dran pa rnal mar
NK116(le)001:4901: gnas pa su zhig yod nyes pa kun gyi phyi
NK116(le)001:4902: mo nyon mongs yin pas de la mkhon tu bzung
NK116(le)001:4903: ba'i tshul gang zhig ces bya ba la sogs pas
NK116(le)001:4904: ston te / ganga zhiga gnoda pa'i rgyu 'brasa chunga
NK116(le)001:4905: ngu tsam la'ang yid mi srun par khrosa pa'i nga
NK116(le)001:4906: rgyal shina tu bdo ba dang bcas te rgol ba
NK116(le)001:4908: pha rol pos mad'a mdunga sogs mtshona gyi chada pa
NK116(le)001:4909: drag po 'phen yang ci mi sems te bzoda par
NK116(le)001:4910: byas nasa / rang rgyal ba'i dona ma gruba para phyir phyogsa par mi byed na /
NK116(le)001:4911: dus dang rnam pa kun tu badga la sdug bsngal
NK116(le)001:4912: gyi khur chen po 'phos pa'i dgra zlara gyur pa'i
NK116(le)001:4913: nyon mongas brgyad khri bzhi stong gi dmag dpung shugs
NK116(le)001:4914: stobsa chena po // 'di dang g.yula sprad nasa /
NK116(le)001:4915: 'khona du bzunga ba'i cho ga ma zhiga bar du
NK116(le)001:4916: mchog gsum rin po che la ram zla sbran nas
NK116(le)001:4917: bslaba pa bsrunga pa'i brtula zhugas sems yod su zhiga
NK116(le)001:4918: gis gtong ste mi gtong mod /
NK116(le)001:4919: de bas na bslab pa bsrung ba'i brtul zhugs kyi
NK116(le)001:4920: grogs su mi dbang 'phags pa la 'os pa'i rgyal
NK116(le)001:4921: srid rin po che bdun gyi khyad nor bsnyen par
NK116(le)001:4922: bya ste / slob dpon dpa' bos kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems bsgom pa las //
NK116(le)001:4923: dad pa'i 'khor lo rin po ches //
NK116(le)001:4924: nyin mtshan dge ba'i lam sna drongs //
NK116(le)001:4925: tshul khrims btsun mo rin po ches /
NK116(le)001:4926: rab tu mdzes pa'i rgyan cha gdags //
NK116(le)001:4927: gtong ba'i blon po rin po ches //
NK116(le)001:4929: thos pa'i dmag dpon rin po ches //
NK116(le)001:4930: log rtog dgra yi g.yul ngo gzhom //
NK116(le)001:4931: ngo tsha shes pa'i rta mchog gis //
NK116(le)001:4932: nyon mongs bdag med spubs su sba //
NK116(le)001:4933: khrel yod stobs kyi glang po ches //
NK116(le)001:4934: phyin ci log gi las rnams spangs //
NK116(le)001:4935: shes rab nor bu rin po ches /
NK116(le)001:4936: bdag dang gzhan gyi re ba bskong //
NK116(le)001:4937: yon tan mtha' yas 'phags pa'i nor //
NK116(le)001:4938: nor gzhan phal ba sdug bsngal rgyu /
NK116(le)001:4940: so so'i skye bo'i ngang tshul 'di na zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:4941: 'jig rten 'di na nyon mongas pa'i brtsona rara bsdamas
NK116(le)001:4942: pa yi gang zag rnams ni badga gi las mtha'
NK116(le)001:4943: ci 'gyur gyi tshoda kyang riga para mi 'gyur na
NK116(le)001:4944: / matha'a daga 'gro ba sdug bsngal de lasa dbugas
NK116(le)001:4945: 'byina zhing sgrol ba'i nus pa brtana ba mi nyamsa
NK116(le)001:4946: ga la zhiga ste med do //
NK116(le)001:4947: de bas na shin tu bsgrims dgos pa ni bag yod ces bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:4948: ma brtags byung rgyal du spyod pa rnams ring du
NK116(le)001:4949: spangs nas baga yoda cing bslab bya'i gnas kun shesa
NK116(le)001:4950: bzhina bsgrub bya'i cho ga yang de dang ldana pa'i
NK116(le)001:4951: sa gzhi bzang po la byang chuba semas kyi myu
NK116(le)001:4952: gu bskyeda par sla basa na /
NK116(le)001:4953: cung zad kyang mi nyamsa par bzunga ba 'di thog med nas song ba'i dri ma sbyongsa ba dang /
NK116(le)001:4954: dge ba'i tshogs spel ba'i thabas la mi lhod par nana tan 'gyi bar 'atshala lo //
NK116(le)001:4955: zhes bgyid dgos so zhes bya ba'i tha tshig go /
NK116(le)001:4956: da ni byang chub sems dpa'i tshul khrims bshad pa las /
NK116(le)001:4957: thog mar nyes spyod sdom pa'i spang bya cha dang
NK116(le)001:4958: bcas pa ston pa'i phyir khyad par zhes bya ba
NK116(le)001:4960: de la ltung ba'i raba tu dbye ba nyi shu ni /
NK116(le)001:4962: mchod rten gyi rdzas dang dge 'dun la phul ba
NK116(le)001:4963: dngos sam brgyud nas 'phrog tu 'jug pa 'di ni
NK116(le)001:4964: ltung ba'i rtsa ba dang po yin la sogas khong
NK116(le)001:4965: nas gang zhig nyan thos sam /
NK116(le)001:4966: theg chen gang rung gi bshad pa spong zhing 'gog tu 'jug pa gnyis pa dang /
NK116(le)001:4967: gang yang rab byung gi rtags dang cho ga rdzogs
NK116(le)001:4968: par byas nas slar bslab pa 'chol min gang yin
NK116(le)001:4969: kyang rung ste / de yi chos gos phrog pa
NK116(le)001:4970: nas srog 'dor ba'i bar mi mtshams pa byas pa
NK116(le)001:4971: kyang rung ste / gsum pa / rgyal rigs gang
NK116(le)001:4972: zhig pha dang ma dang nyan thos dgra bcom gsod
NK116(le)001:4975: sangs rgyas la ngan sems kyi khrag 'byin pa dang lnga po ni bzhi pa /
NK116(le)001:4976: gang zhig log par lta bas mi dge ba bcu'i
NK116(le)001:4977: las kyi lam la rang gzhan yang dag par 'jug
NK116(le)001:4978: pa ste rgyala po las byung ba'i ltung ba lnga'o
NK116(le)001:4979: // de bzhin tu blon po gang yang mchod rten
NK116(le)001:4980: gyi rdzas dang phyogs bzhi'i dge 'dun gyi rdzas 'phrog
NK116(le)001:4982: gang zhig gronga zhes khyim gcig pa dang /
NK116(le)001:4983: ljong zhes mi rigs bzhi gnas pa dang /
NK116(le)001:4984: grong khyer ste bzo sna bco brgyad yod pa dang /
NK116(le)001:4985: gronga rdal te tshong ba mang po 'du sa dang /
NK116(le)001:4986: yul 'khor ni yul tsam pa ka lta bu ste /
NK116(le)001:4987: de dag 'jomas par byed pa na 'di ni gnyis pa /
NK116(le)001:4988: sogas khongs nas snga ma zin la phyi ma gsum ni /
NK116(le)001:4989: gang yang nyan rang theg chen gsum gyi bshad pa
NK116(le)001:4990: spang zhing 'gog pa bsubs par byed pa 'di ni
NK116(le)001:4991: gsum pa / gang yang rgyal ba'i rjes su zhugs
NK116(le)001:4992: nas rtags dang cho ga blangs pa tshul khrims 'chal
NK116(le)001:4994: ngur smrig phrog pa nas srog la 'tshe ba'i bar 'di ni bzhi pa /
NK116(le)001:4995: gang zhig mtshams med pa lnga las gang rung ba'i
NK116(le)001:4996: sdig la sogs pa ste 'di ni blona po las
NK116(le)001:4998: gzhan yang gang zag blo ma sbyongsa pa'am sbyang tsam yang ma nges te /
NK116(le)001:4999: de dag la stong pa nyid sgra ji bzhin pa ston pa dang po /
NK116(le)001:5000: sogas khongs nas theg chen lam du zhugs pa gang dag theg dman la basngagasa te /
NK116(le)001:5002: gang zhig sngon gyi bag chags yod pas theg dman la spro zhing /
NK116(le)001:5003: theg chen don du mi 'gyur bzhin du bshad pas //
NK116(le)001:5004: gnyis ka min par 'chol bas gsum pa /
NK116(le)001:5005: las dang po pa theg pa chen por lung du
NK116(le)001:5006: ma bstan pa'i gang zag gi blo bsgyur nas theg
NK116(le)001:5007: chen basngagasa te nyan rang gi lam 'dor du 'jug
NK116(le)001:5008: pa bzhi pa / rnyed bkur gyi don du bdag
NK116(le)001:5009: la bstod cing phrag dog gis gzhan smod pa lnga
NK116(le)001:5010: pa bzhi pa / pa / gzhan gyi bdag yon gnas bzang por mthong phyir /
NK116(le)001:5011: khyad par zab mo ma rtogs bzhin du rtogs bardzu byed pa drug pa /
NK116(le)001:5012: rgyal po la sogs pa'i phyogs dang bshes par byas
NK116(le)001:5013: nas dge sbyong gzhan dag 'phrog brdeg byed pa dang
NK116(le)001:5014: / dkon mchog gi sbyin bdag 'phrog cing dkor la ci mi snyam par longs spyod pa bdun pa /
NK116(le)001:5015: spong ba bsam gtan ba'i longs spyod las phri zhing
NK116(le)001:5016: phrog nas kha ton pa'am klog pa dag la ster
NK116(le)001:5017: zhing chos bzhin spyod pa'i rnal 'byor 'dor du 'jug
NK116(le)001:5018: pa ste phala ba'i brgyad dang snga ma'i lnga tshan
NK116(le)001:5019: gnyis bcas bsdoms pas bco brgyad yod kyang rdzas bcu
NK116(le)001:5020: bzhir 'du ste / rgyal po'i rtsa ltung lnga pa dang /
NK116(le)001:5021: blon po'i rtsa ltung gnyis pa tha dad pa las /
NK116(le)001:5022: gzhan bzhi po rdzas su 'gal ba ma yin pas so //
NK116(le)001:5023: de lta na'ang bco brgyad po'i steng du smona sems
NK116(le)001:5024: dang 'juga pa'i sems gnyis bsnan pa'i nyi shur 'gyur
NK116(le)001:5025: te / de lta'i bslab bya'i gnas gtong bar byed pa rnams spanga dgos so //
NK116(le)001:5026: gal te nyams na phyir 'chos dgos pa mdor na zhes bya la sogs pas gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:5027: mdora na dngos su nyams par mi byed pa lta
NK116(le)001:5028: zhog rmi lam gyi skabs su sdiga pa'i las byed
NK116(le)001:5030: de ma thaga tu 'gyod pa dang bcas te phunga po gsuma pa gdona pasa bashagas pa bya'o //
NK116(le)001:5031: byang chub kyi sems rten pa'i gzhi smon semas shora ba dang /
NK116(le)001:5032: 'agla zla rtsa ba'i ltung ba byung ba dang /
NK116(le)001:5033: spongs rkyen bslaba pasa sun nas yar phula ba gasum po daga lasa /
NK116(le)001:5034: nyin mtshan cha drug bgos pa'i thuna tshoda gang rung
NK116(le)001:5035: gcis la ltung ba byung na de ma thag gam
NK116(le)001:5036: 'og mar thal nas ltung nyamsa shor na yang gnong
NK116(le)001:5037: 'gyod drag po'i semas kyis skya rengas 'char ba na
NK116(le)001:5038: yan lag lnga khrus bya zhing mduna du 'phags pa
NK116(le)001:5039: nama mkha'i snying po la gdung ba'i sems kyis 'boda
NK116(le)001:5040: nas yan lag bduna pa brjod pas ltung ba las
NK116(le)001:5041: ldang ngoo // bshags pa'i tshad las ma 'das na phyir bcos yod de /
NK116(le)001:5042: de las thal na gtugs pa zhes bya ste /
NK116(le)001:5043: phyir bcos kho nas sor chud pa ma yin te /
NK116(le)001:5044: bshags bsdoms sngon du 'gro bas slar cho ga bzhin du blangs par bya dgos so //
NK116(le)001:5045: spyir dbang po rab tu gyur pa la lta snang
NK116(le)001:5046: tsam las ltung ba med de gdod nas ngo bo
NK116(le)001:5047: nyid med pa'i kun rtogs ban bun shar ba chu
NK116(le)001:5048: la ri mo bris pa'am mkha' la 'dab chags 'phur
NK116(le)001:5049: pa'i rjes mi chags pa bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:5050: de skad du'ang thar ba chen po phyogs su rgyas pa'i mdo las /
NK116(le)001:5052: drang por 'dug la yang dag ltos //
NK116(le)001:5053: yang dag nyid la yang dag blta //
NK116(le)001:5054: yang dag mthong nas rnam par grol //
NK116(le)001:5057: byang sems kyi sdom pa'i rten ni //
NK116(le)001:5058: brtan rtsa 'dul ba la dgongs te /
NK116(le)001:5059: so thar rigs bdun gang rung gi steng du smon
NK116(le)001:5060: 'jug gi sems bskyed dang ldan pa'i rab byung byang
NK116(le)001:5061: sems te mdo sde brgyan gyis basngagasa pa ltar /
NK116(le)001:5062: byams pas bka' bsdus shing thog med sku mched kyis
NK116(le)001:5063: bkral ba rgya cher spyod par grags pa'i rjes su
NK116(le)001:5064: 'brang ba sems tsam pa'i lugs so //
NK116(le)001:5065: sems can mang po la sangs rgyas kyi sa bon
NK116(le)001:5066: 'jog cing phan pa rlabs po che gdags su rung
NK116(le)001:5067: ba dbu ma ba'i man ngag ste /
NK116(le)001:5068: shin tu rgyas pa'i sde snod rnams kyi lugs 'jam dpal dbyangs kyis bka' bsdus shing /
NK116(le)001:5069: klu grub snying pos bkral ba ltar na /
NK116(le)001:5070: gling gsum gyi rten can dang /
NK116(le)001:5071: lta klu gnod sbyin sogs brda shes don go ba
NK116(le)001:5072: byang sdom gyi snod du bzhag cing tha na nyin
NK116(le)001:5073: gcig tu srog gcod spang ba'i sdom pa blang pa
NK116(le)001:5074: tsam yang sems bskyed du mdzad pa ni zab mo
NK116(le)001:5076: kha gcig tshul khrims zhes bya ba rab byung gi rtags 'dzin pa kho na la 'dod kyang /
NK116(le)001:5077: mtha' gcig tu ma nges so //
NK116(le)001:5078: ci'i phyir zhe na byang chub sems dpa' chos 'phags
NK116(le)001:5079: bud med drug khri brgyad stong dang lhan cig 'dod
NK116(le)001:5080: yon lnga la spyod par grags pas /
NK116(le)001:5081: de la tshul khrims med par 'dod dam /
NK116(le)001:5082: 'dod na phar phyin lhag ma lnga yang med par thal /
NK116(le)001:5084: khrims ni rgyu dang mi rgyu'i sa bzhin du /
NK116(le)001:5085: yon tan kun gyi gzhi rten thub pas gsungs /
NK116(le)001:5086: zhes klu yi dbang pos gsungs pa'i phyir rten gzhi ma grub par /
NK116(le)001:5087: der brten gyi chos mi srid pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:5088: 'dod na byang chub sems dpa' chos 'phags de byang sems ma yin par thal /
NK116(le)001:5089: 'jug pa'i bslab bya med pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:5090: de ltar gtan nas 'dod mi nus te /
NK116(le)001:5091: sa chen po la gnas pa'i byang 'phags yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:5092: 'o na dogs pa ji ltar bsal na /
NK116(le)001:5094: sdom pa'i tshul khrims ni byang chub sems dpa'i sems gnas par byed do //
NK116(le)001:5095: dge ba'i chos sdud pa'i tshul khrims ni sangs rgyas kyi chos yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
NK116(le)001:5096: sems can gyi don byed pa'i tshul khrims ni sems can yongs su smin par byed do //
NK116(le)001:5099: gal te byang chub sems dpa' 'dod yon lnga spyod kyang /
NK116(le)001:5100: sangs rgyas chos dang 'phags pa'i dge 'dun skyabs song te /
NK116(le)001:5101: sangs rgyas 'grub bya snyam du kun mkhyen yid byed na /
NK116(le)001:5102: mkhas pa'i tshul khrims pha rol phyin gnas rig par bya /
NK116(le)001:5104: de nas badga gi bde ba gazhana la yang dag pa'i sems kyis spo ba dang /
NK116(le)001:5105: gazhana gyi sduga bsngal badga gisa khura bzoda pa'i sems kyis len pa ste /
NK116(le)001:5106: de lta'i gtong lena gyi snying stobsa rmada du byung ba rang dbang du 'du bar byed cing /
NK116(le)001:5107: ji srid byang chuba snying po'i bar du bsam spyod
NK116(le)001:5108: de dang mi 'bral ba'i steng du phyi phyir bkod
NK116(le)001:5109: ma'i chu bzhin du spel bar smon pa byed do
NK116(le)001:5110: // de ltar spel sbyong tshad med bzhi'i ngo bor gnas zhing /
NK116(le)001:5111: bzhi po'i thog ma'ang byas pa drin du gzo ba las skye zhing /
NK116(le)001:5112: de las rig par snga phyi rgyu 'bras lta bur
NK116(le)001:5113: 'grub pa'i tshul smon pa'i zhes bya ba la sogs
NK116(le)001:5114: pas bstan te / smon pa'i bslaba bya byams sogas tshad meda bzhi po yanga /
NK116(le)001:5115: thog mar byas pa drina du bzo ba las byamsa
NK116(le)001:5116: pa skye zhing byamsa lasa snying rje dang de lasa
NK116(le)001:5117: byang chuba kyi semas skye ba ni tshad ma'i lunga
NK116(le)001:5118: gisa yang dag par gang du gruba ce na b+ham
NK116(le)001:5120: mar shes pa dang drin dran pa dang /
NK116(le)001:5124: brtse ba'i snying rje chen po dang /
NK116(le)001:5125: rang 'bras bla na med pa nyid rgyu 'bras man ngag bdun ldan du bzhed pa yin no //
NK116(le)001:5126: de bas sems can thams cad mar shes par byas nas /
NK116(le)001:5127: de'i drin dran pa'i tshul btsas ma zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:5128: de nas batsasa ma thaga pa'i skyes bu bzhina gzugs
NK116(le)001:5129: ngana pa nyar nyer po can la 'gul spyod mi
NK116(le)001:5131: ma yisa dapanga du blangs nasa khrus khanga ltar byas so //
NK116(le)001:5132: ji ltar byas na de nas /
NK116(le)001:5133: mi gatsanga ba matha'a dag lag pasa nye rega byas nas gtsang bar byas so //
NK116(le)001:5134: nu zhos bsnyena bkura te lusa kyi rega byas g.yogas nas /
NK116(le)001:5135: bu chunga de nyid cung zad na ba lasa badga nyid 'chi bar 'admas shing /
NK116(le)001:5136: ched du sdiga dang sduga bsngal dang gtam ngana matha'a
NK116(le)001:5137: dag pa srana nus pa sogs gzhal du med pa'i
NK116(le)001:5138: drina dang rima gro byas pa la ci yang mi
NK116(le)001:5139: bsam par khyad du gsoda par byed na /
NK116(le)001:5140: de nyid lasa bsgrub bya'i cho ga phyin ci log tu 'khruga pa su zhiga yoda de med do //
NK116(le)001:5141: de ltar bsam sbyor log pa'i khur ni shin tu
NK116(le)001:5142: mi rungs bar bstan phyir sa 'di zhes bya ba
NK116(le)001:5144: sa 'di rira rgya mtsho dang bacasa pa badga gi
NK116(le)001:5145: khura du babs kyang de tsam lci ba ma yina
NK116(le)001:5146: te // de dag las kyang ches lci ba byas
NK116(le)001:5147: pa'i drin mi bzo ba'i khura chena 'di bor na
NK116(le)001:5148: ni ji ltar duga ldana gyi baza'a ba khonga du
NK116(le)001:5149: chud pa'i skye bo bzhina du nyams nyes par 'gyur
NK116(le)001:5151: de bas na drin du gzo ba'i tshul de phyir zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:5152: de'i phyir na pha matha'a yasa pa'i semas cana srid do cog kuna /
NK116(le)001:5153: ma ru ma gyur pa gcig kyang med la gyur
NK116(le)001:5154: nasa kyang phana gadgas 'ba' zhig las mi 'os pa
NK116(le)001:5155: ma byas na dama pa'i drina te /
NK116(le)001:5156: yang yang drana pasa byamsa sogas tshad med bzhi po gonga du 'phela zhing rgyas par 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:5158: byas pa shesa pa dang drin du bzo ba yi
NK116(le)001:5159: skyes bu gang dang ganga la 'aphagas pa'i nora bdun
NK116(le)001:5160: sogs kyis bsnyen par 'gyur ba chosa nyid yin pas
NK116(le)001:5161: so // de ltar shes kyang 'gal zla ston par
NK116(le)001:5162: smon sems zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te
NK116(le)001:5163: so // / de yang smon semas ston ka'i yar ngo'i zla ba gasra ba lta bu la /
NK116(le)001:5164: sgra gacana gyi gdonga ba'i dug barlangasa las kyang thu ba'i mi ma thuna phyogsa ni /
NK116(le)001:5165: naga po'i chos bzhi yin pas ringa du bskrad para bya'o //
NK116(le)001:5166: gang zhe na bla ma sogs mchoda du 'osa pa bslu ba dang /
NK116(le)001:5167: gazhana gyisa bsoda namas la sogs thar ba'i rgyu ci
NK116(le)001:5168: rigs bsgrub pa la 'dun pa bsgyur te the tshoma
NK116(le)001:5169: bskyed nasa 'gyoda pa'i gansa la sbyar ba dang /
NK116(le)001:5170: byang chub kyi sems dang ldan pa'i dama pa rnams la bskur zhing mi snyan pa sgrog pa dang /
NK116(le)001:5171: rang rgyud ngan g.yo dang ldan zhig der bsten gyi
NK116(le)001:5172: rgyus bslu thabs la spyod pas gazhana daga mgo bo
NK116(le)001:5173: bskora ba te / chosa bzhi po las ganga runga
NK116(le)001:5174: nyamsa su myong tshe smona semas shora ba yin la
NK116(le)001:5175: bskora ba te / / de 'phral 'gyod pa dang
NK116(le)001:5176: gnyen po bshags pasa ma sleb par thuna tshad las
NK116(le)001:5178: de yi moda la semas bskyed 'chora ba yina no //
NK116(le)001:5179: de'i gnyen pora che ba dakara po'i chosa bzhi ni /
NK116(le)001:5180: sroga la baba kyang bsam bzhina tu rdzuna mi smra ba dang /
NK116(le)001:5181: rgyal srasa byang sems rnamas la theg chen ston pa
NK116(le)001:5182: po yin para gusa shinga basngagasa pa brjod pa dang
NK116(le)001:5183: / g.yo sgyu med pa'i semas can thams cada kyi don 'ba' zhig gnyer ba dang /
NK116(le)001:5184: ris med 'gro ba matha'a daga byang chub mchog gi lam la dkri ba'o //
NK116(le)001:5185: spyir mi nyams shing brten par bya ba'i 'du shes
NK116(le)001:5186: bzhi la rtag par slob pa'i tshul brten bya'i zhes
NK116(le)001:5188: brten par bya ba'i sgo nas bsrunga ba'i 'du shesa
NK116(le)001:5189: bzhi ste gang zhe na dge ba'i bshesa gnyen la
NK116(le)001:5191: desa bstan pa'i chosa la lam gyi 'du shesa dang /
NK116(le)001:5192: de ltar sgruba pa'i dge 'dun rnams la grogas kyi 'du shes dang /
NK116(le)001:5193: semas cana kuna la bu gcig po'i 'du shesa te /
NK116(le)001:5194: 'di daga ni smon pa'i bslab bya yang dag pa 'ba' zhig go /
NK116(le)001:5195: da ni 'jug pa'i bslab bya'i ngo bo mdor bstan
NK116(le)001:5196: bye brag so sor bshad pa gnyis las dang po
NK116(le)001:5197: // 'jug pa'i zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:5198: gong du smon pa'i bslab bya rgyas par bstan zin
NK116(le)001:5199: pa'i steng nas 'juga pa'i bslaba bya pha rola tu
NK116(le)001:5200: phyin pa druga yod pa lasa sbyin pa sogs dang
NK116(le)001:5201: po lnga ni bsoda namas dam pa'i tshogas dang /
NK116(le)001:5202: phyi ma gciga ni shes rab ste ye shes dam pa'i tshogas chena yin te /
NK116(le)001:5203: thabs shes gnyis lam brtena pa'i sangsa rgyasa yoda pa
NK116(le)001:5204: ma yina la de'i steng du thabas stobas smon lam
NK116(le)001:5205: ye shesa bzhi bsnan pasa bcu ste /
NK116(le)001:5206: rgyal sras rnams kyi spyi nor yin no //
NK116(le)001:5207: gnyis pa la gnyis te 'jug byed gang zag gi blo stobs kyi rim pa bshad pa dang /
NK116(le)001:5208: 'jug bya'i dbye ba rgyas par ston pa'o //
NK116(le)001:5209: dang po ni blo stobs zhesabya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:5210: blo stobsa kyi mthu yisa 'jug ngog ji ltar sgrub
NK116(le)001:5211: par byed pa'i tshul gyis rgyal ba'i sras la gsum
NK116(le)001:5212: / 'di na gang ranga gis ched du gnyer bya'i
NK116(le)001:5213: dona po thams cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang sngona du
NK116(le)001:5214: thob zin par byas nas slar 'gro ba rnams srid
NK116(le)001:5215: pa'i sdug bsngal gyi rgya mtsho las sgrola bar 'doda
NK116(le)001:5216: / pa / rgyal po lta bu'i 'doda chena semas bskyed dang /
NK116(le)001:5217: ranga dang 'gro ba stabsa gciga tu sgrol bar 'doda
NK116(le)001:5218: pa grub lta bu'i ye shesa dama pa'i semas dpa'
NK116(le)001:5219: dang / 'gro ba srid do cog kun sngona du
NK116(le)001:5220: bsgral nas rjesa la zhi ba'i go 'phang 'doda pa
NK116(le)001:5221: skyong byed lta bu'i tshul 'di ni dpe meda pa'i
NK116(le)001:5222: semsa bskyed de go rim bzhin brtula posa grangas meda
NK116(le)001:5224: 'bringa posa bduna dang rnona posa grangs med gsuma na
NK116(le)001:5225: grola bar byed pas na rmad du 'byung ba'i snying
NK116(le)001:5226: stob kyi go cha gyon par rigs so //
NK116(le)001:5228: mgo la sems can khur chen khyer ba yin /
NK116(le)001:5229: sems dpa' mchog rnams dal gyis 'gro mi mdzes /
NK116(le)001:5230: bdag gzhan sna tshogs 'chings bas rab bcings pas //
NK116(le)001:5231: brtson pa brgya 'gyur gyis kyang bya bar rigs //
NK116(le)001:5233: gnyis pa 'jug bya'i dbye ba rgyas par ston pa las /
NK116(le)001:5234: dang po sbyin pa'i pha rol du phyin pa ni /
NK116(le)001:5235: sbyin pa'i zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:5236: de la bstan bshad gnyis las dang po sbyin pa'i ngo bo ni chagas pa meda pa ste /
NK116(le)001:5238: byang chub sems dpa'i sbyin pa ni //
NK116(le)001:5239: ma chags mi chags chags pa med //
NK116(le)001:5240: chags pa nyid kyang ma yin te //
NK116(le)001:5241: ma chags mi chags chags pa med /
NK116(le)001:5244: dabye na chosa dang zanga zinga mi 'jigas gsum /
NK116(le)001:5245: zhes gtso che ba'i cha nas sa bcad dang por
NK116(le)001:5246: chos kyi sbyin pa smos kyang byed las gtso che
NK116(le)001:5247: ba'i cha nas skabs 'dis zang zing dang mi 'jigs
NK116(le)001:5249: dang po zang zing zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:5250: zanga zinga la'ang dbye ba rnama pa gsuma yina te /
NK116(le)001:5251: gtong ba dang gtong pa chena po dang /
NK116(le)001:5253: gtonga ba zhes bya ba ni zasa dang /
NK116(le)001:5255: glang po che dang yula khamas sogs rang la dbang thob tshod gazhana la sbyin pa'o //
NK116(le)001:5256: gtong ba chen po ni bu dang bu mo dang
NK116(le)001:5257: khyim thabas la sogs lhug par gtong ba yin no
NK116(le)001:5258: // shina tu gtong ba ni tshur thong skye bos
NK116(le)001:5259: bya daka'a ba'i gnas gang slong ba po dera mgo
NK116(le)001:5260: dang yan lag don snying gi bar ji ltar 'dod
NK116(le)001:5262: de yang 'di na thoga mara sbyin gtong gomas su 'juga pa rnams /
NK116(le)001:5263: ser snas bsdamas pa'i skyes bu'i lag pa zung gis
NK116(le)001:5264: ni gciga gi ni sbyin pa po byas nasa ni
NK116(le)001:5265: gciga shosa slong ba por dmigs te sbyin para bsam
NK116(le)001:5266: pa'i semas / yanga yanga sposa pasa tshoda ma la sogas bza' btung gang rung la /
NK116(le)001:5267: skam chagas 'jiga pa stobsa su ma gyur bar la bslaba par bya ba spyod 'jug las /
NK116(le)001:5268: goms na sla bar mi 'gyur ba'i //
NK116(le)001:5269: dgos te gang yang yod ma yin /
NK116(le)001:5271: gnyis pa mi 'jigs pa zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:5273: gang gzhan dag 'chi nges kyi sroga bsrunga pa dang //
NK116(le)001:5274: 'jigas pa'i yul gang du ci yang rung ba bsgral
NK116(le)001:5275: te dbugas 'byin gyi gansa bde ba'i go skabs la
NK116(le)001:5276: 'goda pa'o // de ltar slob pa'i tshe'ang rang gi
NK116(le)001:5277: sems stobs la dpag ste spyod pa las mi nusa
NK116(le)001:5278: bzhina du baba col cho ga yisa /
NK116(le)001:5279: rnam para ma dag par sbyar ba'i sbyin pa'ang slad pa'i gnas su gyur ba ste /
NK116(le)001:5280: khyad par gtong pa chen po ni mi skye ba'i
NK116(le)001:5281: chos la bzod pa thob pa'i spyod yul yin no
NK116(le)001:5282: // snying rje'i bsam pa shina tu ma daga pa'i bar du /
NK116(le)001:5283: lus dang srog gatong ba ni bslaba pa kun btus
NK116(le)001:5284: nyid lasa bakaga yod de ci'i phyir na las dang
NK116(le)001:5285: po ba'i sems rma'i sha'u ltar bsran mi bzod pas
NK116(le)001:5288: dus ma yin par 'dod pa ni bdud kyi las so //
NK116(le)001:5290: de bzhin tu kha na ma thosa pa zhes rgyu
NK116(le)001:5291: mi dge bcus bskrun pa'i ser sna dang bcas te
NK116(le)001:5293: tshul bzhin gyi gansa mina par smad pa'i gansa te
NK116(le)001:5294: yang dag pa ni rang la bdoga pa la zhena
NK116(le)001:5295: pa dang chags pa btang ba sbyin pa'i mthar thug
NK116(le)001:5297: gsum pa ni chos kyi zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:5298: sbyin pa snga ma gnyis kyis gang zhig bsdus nas chosa kyi sbyin pa byed pa na de la'ang /
NK116(le)001:5299: rnam pa gsum yod pa lasa dang pos ni mosa
NK116(le)001:5300: pasa spyod pa'i lam la gnas pas ji bzhina par
NK116(le)001:5302: ranga gi nyon mongsa basla ba'i thabs kyi cho ga dang /
NK116(le)001:5303: ris med 'gro la byamsa dang snying rjera ldan pas /
NK116(le)001:5304: gsung raba dag bklagas pa sogs dge ba'i bsam spyod gang yin pa de yisa /
NK116(le)001:5305: dakara po'i phyogsa kyi rgyud rnams pad+ma'i 'dab ma ltar rnam par grol ba'i smon lam gadba cing /
NK116(le)001:5306: ranga rgyud grola ba'i dus de nas 'gro ba'i skal ba dang /
NK116(le)001:5307: dbang po'i ranga bzhina la matshamas pasa gazhana dona gtso bora bya ba kho na'o //
NK116(le)001:5308: de skad du'ang 'phags pa 'jig rten 'dzin gyis dris pas lung bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK116(le)001:5309: de la chos kyi sbyin pa gang zhe na /
NK116(le)001:5312: glegs bam sbyin pa ni chung ngu'o //
NK116(le)001:5313: skal pa ji lta ba bzhin tu nyan thos dang /
NK116(le)001:5315: bla na med pa'i chos ston pa ni chen po'o //
NK116(le)001:5316: bla na med pa'i byang chub 'dzin du 'jug cing /
NK116(le)001:5317: nam mkha' ltar bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos ston pa ni shin tu chen po'o //
NK116(le)001:5318: gnyis pa tshul khrims kyi pha rol du phyin pa
NK116(le)001:5319: ni tshul khrims zhes bya la sogs pas ston te
NK116(le)001:5323: dbye ba cung zad bkral ba gzhung rgyas par bshad
NK116(le)001:5324: pa gsum gyi dang po tshula khrimas kyi ngo bo
NK116(le)001:5325: ni bslab pa'i phyogs su mi mthuna pa thams cad
NK116(le)001:5326: la bsgrims nas rab tu sdoma pa gang lags pa
NK116(le)001:5327: yina no // gnyis pa so sor dabye na nyes spyod sdom pa dang /
NK116(le)001:5329: semas cana dona byed de rnam pa gsuma du bshad do //
NK116(le)001:5330: de yang lus ngag yid de sgo gsum gyi mi
NK116(le)001:5331: dge ba phra rags sdoma pa gang zhig nyes spyod
NK116(le)001:5332: sdom pa dang / pha rola tu phyin pa druga
NK116(le)001:5333: dang ldana pa gang zhig dge ba'i chosa sdud pa
NK116(le)001:5334: sdom pa dang / / bshad ma thag pa gnyis
NK116(le)001:5335: kyis gazhana la phana 'dogas lhur len pa gang zhig
NK116(le)001:5336: semas cana dona byed kyi tshul khrims yina no //
NK116(le)001:5337: gsum pa rgyas par bshad pa la so byang gi
NK116(le)001:5338: mtshan nyid rags par ston pa nang gses zhes bya
NK116(le)001:5339: ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:5340: nanga gsesa su so so thara ba lasa byang chub semas dpa' ni /
NK116(le)001:5341: khyad para bzhi yi sgo nasa 'aphagas pa 'di bzhin te /
NK116(le)001:5342: so so thara ba gazhana gnoda gzhi dang bacasa pa las ldoga pa tsam du zad la /
NK116(le)001:5343: byang semas de yi steng du /
NK116(le)001:5344: phana pa rgya cher 'doda pa bsnona pa yin no //
NK116(le)001:5345: so thara srog gcod sogs gsum dang /
NK116(le)001:5346: rdzun sogs bzhi ste spanga ba bduna bsdusa lusa ngaga gtso che la /
NK116(le)001:5347: byang semas de'i steng du yid kyi gsum ste spanga pa bcu ka gtso bora byed do //
NK116(le)001:5348: de tsam du ma zad gnang bkag gis khyad par zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:5349: khyad para bslaba ba'i gansa ni so so thara ba'i
NK116(le)001:5350: skabsa su gazhana gyi dona du rgya cher 'gyur yang
NK116(le)001:5351: ngos kyis bacasa pa'i sdom pa mi 'drala la /
NK116(le)001:5352: byang chuba semas dapa'a gazhana gyi dona du 'gyur ba na /
NK116(le)001:5353: lusa ngaga gnyis kyi byed las can mi dge ba rnam pa bduna gazhana dona du 'gyur ba dang /
NK116(le)001:5354: 'gyur bar shes pa dang ranga gi dmigs bcas dmigs
NK116(le)001:5355: med kyi dge tshogas mi sgrib cing 'phela ba yi
NK116(le)001:5356: gansa skabsa gsum rnam par bsgrims shing brtagsa te 'thad
NK116(le)001:5357: na gannga ba'i skabsa yoda de bdag cag gi skyabs
NK116(le)001:5358: mgon mchog gi sprul sku slob pa'i dus su ded
NK116(le)001:5359: dpon semas stobsa chena pora gyur tshe tshong pa lnga
NK116(le)001:5360: brgya'i srog dang kho rnam par smin pas gces par
NK116(le)001:5361: gzigs nasa mi naga mdunga thunga cana bsgral ba dang
NK116(le)001:5362: brama ze'i khye'u skara ma la dga' bas lo grangs
NK116(le)001:5363: brgyad khri gnyis stong nags khrod du tshangs par spyad
NK116(le)001:5364: pa'i mthar grong khyer du bsod snyoms la byon par
NK116(le)001:5365: / tshong dpon gyi bu mo de la chags te
NK116(le)001:5366: 'dod pas gdung bas skabs der 'chi bar brtsams pa
NK116(le)001:5367: las ldog pa'i slad du tshangs spyod btang bas tshangs
NK116(le)001:5368: pa'i 'jig rten du skyes pa sogs dpera mtshona nasa
NK116(le)001:5369: rnam pa'i cha nas nyes pa 'dra na'nga dona la
NK116(le)001:5371: rten cing 'brel ba'i rgyu 'brasa gang zhig nus mathu
NK116(le)001:5372: cana du bsam pa kho nasa byas pa'i phyir ro
NK116(le)001:5373: / des na yida kya gsum la gannga ba'i skabas cung zad kyang meda do /
NK116(le)001:5374: de'i phyir theg chen gyi gang zag la dmigs nas
NK116(le)001:5375: de lta na'ang zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs
NK116(le)001:5376: te / de ltar bshad ma thag pas shes par
NK116(le)001:5377: 'gyur mod na'ang zhes 'ang gi sgra ni nges par
NK116(le)001:5378: te / bzung ba'o // mdor dril na rgyal srasa
NK116(le)001:5379: byang chub sems dpa'i sdoma pa la ranga gi dona
NK116(le)001:5380: du zhi bde'i go 'phang gnyer ba dang /
NK116(le)001:5381: dgos ched byung kyang bya daka'a ba lus srog gtong rgyu spang ba dang /
NK116(le)001:5382: gazhana gyi phyira du phan pa mi bsgrub pa de
NK116(le)001:5383: dag ganga dang ganga rung ltung ba'i rgyu ru gciga
NK116(le)001:5384: para lha mi'i ston pa zas gtsang sras kyis gsungsa
NK116(le)001:5385: pa yina la cung zad bshad na /
NK116(le)001:5387: de'i gzugs brnyan dang ltung med dang /
NK116(le)001:5388: de'i gzugs brnyan du 'chad pa'i mi bzhi po tshul khrims gsum du sbyar na /
NK116(le)001:5389: sdom pa'i tshul khrims zhe sdang gi srog gcod pa ltung ba /
NK116(le)001:5390: phan sems kyis gsod pa ltung ba'i gzugs brnyan /
NK116(le)001:5391: snying rjes mi gsod pa ltung med /
NK116(le)001:5392: gzhan la phan kyang mi gsod pa ltung med kyi gzugs brnyan no //
NK116(le)001:5394: ser snas mi ster ba ltung ba /
NK116(le)001:5395: phan sems kyis mi ster ba ltung ba'i gzugs brnyan /
NK116(le)001:5396: bsam pa dag bas ster ba ltung med /
NK116(le)001:5397: gzhan la gnod phyir ster ba ltung med kyi gzugs brnyan no //
NK116(le)001:5399: nad pa'i rim gro ma byas na ltung ba /
NK116(le)001:5400: don chen bsgrub pa'i slad du de las ldog pa ltung ba'i gzugs brnyan /
NK116(le)001:5401: brtse bas nad g.yog byed pa ltung med /
NK116(le)001:5402: de la rim gro yod bzhin du rang gi dge
NK116(le)001:5403: las don chen po dor nas nad g.yogs byed pa
NK116(le)001:5404: ltung med kyi gzugs brnyan no //
NK116(le)001:5405: so byang gi sdom pa rnams 'dod pa spangs pa
NK116(le)001:5406: la rags las pas thog mar sdom pa'i tshul khrims
NK116(le)001:5407: dag par bya ba'i tshul dang po'i zhes bya ba
NK116(le)001:5409: theg chen la zhugs ma thag pa'i dang po'i lasa
NK116(le)001:5410: can byang chub semas dapa'a rnams kyi blo ni gonga
NK116(le)001:5411: nasa gonga du rim gyis spyod pa gtso che basa
NK116(le)001:5412: na thoga mara so sor thar bas nyes spyod sdoma
NK116(le)001:5413: pa'i tshul khrimas ma daga pa /
NK116(le)001:5414: gazhana chos sdud don byed gnyis gtso bora gnyer na
NK116(le)001:5415: dus su ma bab pas bar chada manga bar 'gyur
NK116(le)001:5416: te / b+ham ga la'i pan+di tas /
NK116(le)001:5417: tshogs kyi lam la ni sdom pa'i tshul khrims gtso bo yin no //
NK116(le)001:5418: sbyor ba'i lam la dge ba chos sdud pa'i tshul khrims gtso bo yin no //
NK116(le)001:5419: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lam ni sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims gtso bo yin no //
NK116(le)001:5420: gang zag gcig gi rgyud la brtsis na tshogs lam
NK116(le)001:5421: chung ngu'i dus su gang zag dang po'i bslab pa
NK116(le)001:5423: tshogs lam 'bring gi dus su gang zag 'bring po'i bslab pa la brtson par bya'o //
NK116(le)001:5424: gang zag gsum pas ni gsum pa'i bslab pa la brtson par bya'o //
NK116(le)001:5426: de bas na raba tu byung ba'i byang chub semsa dapa'a ni /
NK116(le)001:5427: khyad para cana du mdo sde'i rgyan lasa bashada pa ni /
NK116(le)001:5428: rab tu byung ba'i phyogs dag ni /
NK116(le)001:5429: yon tan tshad med rnams dang ldan //
NK116(le)001:5430: de lta'i sdom brtson khyim pa yi //
NK116(le)001:5431: byang sems rnams las mchog tu bshad /
NK116(le)001:5433: 'on kyang byang sems kyi sdom pa tsam la so
NK116(le)001:5434: thar gyi rnam dbye ma grub pa'i tshul byang chub
NK116(le)001:5435: ces bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:5436: de la byang chub sems dpa'i so so thar ba
NK116(le)001:5437: chos bzhi bstan pa zhes bya ba'i mdo sde tshan
NK116(le)001:5438: pa gcig pa zhig bod du 'gyur gyi rnam dbye
NK116(le)001:5439: ma grub pa'i phyir de la 'dul ba gleng gzhis
NK116(le)001:5440: 'chad pa ltar lus ngag gi nyes spyod sdom pa'i
NK116(le)001:5441: rab dbye dang cho ga'i khyad par zur du ma
NK116(le)001:5442: bstan mod / de bas na byang chub semas dapa'a ranga sa'i gzhung du sdoma pa la /
NK116(le)001:5443: so thara gyi bca' khrims matshana nyid pa zhig cho gasa gasla ba meda do //
NK116(le)001:5444: spyir so sor thar ba'i sgra bshad ni /
NK116(le)001:5445: legs pa'i lam bstan pa las /
NK116(le)001:5446: lam 'di ni so sor thar bar 'gro bas na so so thar ba ste /
NK116(le)001:5448: rgyu la 'bras bu'i ming chags pa'o //

NK116(le)001:5742: so so'i rtsa ba bzhi ni /
NK116(le)001:5743: dge slong pha dang thun mong pa yin la steng du //
NK116(le)001:5744: skyes pa la reg pa dang /
NK116(le)001:5747: bzlog pa bsnan pas brgyad de phama pa dang //
NK116(le)001:5748: nyes byas sboma po pha dang phyogsa mthuna gyi khyad
NK116(le)001:5749: pa yang yoda de rnam dbye rags pa ni lung
NK116(le)001:5750: snga ma las / dge slong ma la pham brgyad lhag nyi shu /
NK116(le)001:5751: spang ltung so gsum ltung byed brgya brgyad cu //
NK116(le)001:5752: sor bshags bcu gcig nyes byas brgya bcu gnyis /
NK116(le)001:5753: sum brgya drug cu rtsa bzhi mdo tsam mo //
NK116(le)001:5755: de dag las kyang phama pa brgyad po gang rung
NK116(le)001:5756: gis sdoma pa ljon shing gi rtsa ba nas bton
NK116(le)001:5757: pa ltar gtong ba yina pas //
NK116(le)001:5758: phyin chada sdom pa phyir bcos kyi sora chuda runga
NK116(le)001:5759: dang mi runga gi matshamas ni 'chab pa ste nyams
NK116(le)001:5760: pa sbed semsa skyes dang ma skyes daga la raga
NK116(le)001:5761: las so // de ltar bcas dang ma bcas pa'i
NK116(le)001:5762: tshul khrims rnams yid kyis shes par bya ba dang
NK116(le)001:5763: las so // / tshul khrims dang brtul zhugs mchog
NK116(le)001:5764: tu 'dzin pa sogs kyi gnyen por 'gyur ba mtha'
NK116(le)001:5765: dag khong du chud par ma byas pa'i nyes dmigs
NK116(le)001:5766: ston pa ni bsrung zhes bya ba la sogs pa
NK116(le)001:5767: las so // / gsungs te / deng sang 'di
NK116(le)001:5768: na bsrung bya bcu tsam sbrel bar mi shes bzhin
NK116(le)001:5769: tu rgyal ba'i rjes 'jug dang sdom pa bsrung para
NK116(le)001:5771: ma bsrung na shes pa kho nas ci byed snyan na /
NK116(le)001:5772: de ltar yin du chug kyang /
NK116(le)001:5773: spyir srid par 'khyams pa'i rgyu mi shes pa kho nas lan te /
NK116(le)001:5774: 'dir rgyu 'bras dang ltung ba'i rnam smin shes pa
NK116(le)001:5775: tsam gyisa nyams pa 'gog cing gal te nyams par
NK116(le)001:5776: gyur na'ang slar gso ba dang ltung ba sbyongsa sla
NK116(le)001:5777: ba yin no // de lta'i shes byed kyang ltung
NK116(le)001:5778: ba 'byung ba'i sgo bzhi'i dang po yanga mi shesa
NK116(le)001:5779: pa zhesa thogas meda kyis bzheda pa yina no //
NK116(le)001:5781: ltung ba yin min gyi dbye ba mi shes pa dang /
NK116(le)001:5782: bslab pa la mi gusa pa dang /
NK116(le)001:5784: nyon mongs pa shug drag ldan pa'o //
NK116(le)001:5785: bsgrub pa'i bslaba bya lung gzhi las bslab pa gsum
NK116(le)001:5786: gyi rten gzhir gyur pa'i gzhi bcu bdun gsung pa
NK116(le)001:5787: las tshul khrims kyi snying po dag par byed pa'i
NK116(le)001:5790: dgag dbye ste gzhi gsum cho ga mkhan chen d+harma
NK116(le)001:5791: sh+ris mdo nas khol bur du bsgrigs pa thar gling
NK116(le)001:5792: bsgrod pa'i gru chen ji lta ba'o //
NK116(le)001:5793: de'i yan lag gtso bo sbyangs ba'i yon tan bcu gnyis ni /
NK116(le)001:5795: phyag dar khrod pa nyid dang /
NK116(le)001:5799: zas phyis mi len nyid dang /
NK116(le)001:5800: chos gos gsum pa nyid dang /
NK116(le)001:5802: gzhi ji bzhin pa nyid dang /
NK116(le)001:5805: bla gab med pa nyid do //
NK116(le)001:5806: da ni zhar byung shugs bstan gyi rung mthun bstan
NK116(le)001:5807: pa'i phyir 'di na zhes bya ba la sogs pa
NK116(le)001:5808: gsungs te / gzhung 'di na phama lhag bcu bduna ma gtogsa pa'i /
NK116(le)001:5809: gzhan mi runga ba longas spyod dgos na byin gyis brlab par bya ba ni //
NK116(le)001:5810: dusa ma yina para kha zasa spyod dgos par gyur
NK116(le)001:5811: na rang nyid sdod pa'i sa gnas byang sgra mi
NK116(le)001:5812: snyan pa'i glinga du mosa para spyad do //
NK116(le)001:5817: spong ba zhes bya ba'i tshul khrims rnam pa bzhi las /
NK116(le)001:5818: sgra mi snyan pa rnams ni dang po dang ldan pas so //
NK116(le)001:5819: de bzhina khrusa lhag ma byed dgos pa byung ba la /
NK116(le)001:5820: nada pa yin pa'i 'du shes dang /
NK116(le)001:5821: gosa lhag gam kha dog runga ba ma yina ba'i bgo ba dakara po sogs gyon pa dang /
NK116(le)001:5822: ko lpaga sogas 'os min bcad dgos byung ba la phongsa pasa nyam thaga para /
NK116(le)001:5823: sroga bsrunga ba'i slada du gannga ba yina snyamsa pa dang /
NK116(le)001:5824: rina po chera rega dang bdag gir bgyid dgos na /
NK116(le)001:5826: semas cana gso ba'i slad du gannga bar bsgom dgos so //
NK116(le)001:5827: de las gnang pa meda cing bkag pa'ang meda pa'i
NK116(le)001:5828: rigs rnams phyogs gnyis ka'i rjesa su mthun par brtsi
NK116(le)001:5829: ba yin te / sdom gsum rnam nges las //
NK116(le)001:5830: mdor na ye nas gnang dang bkag pa med //
NK116(le)001:5831: byar rung dang nye mi rung zlog byed na //
NK116(le)001:5832: de dag spyod cig mi rung dang nye zhing //
NK116(le)001:5833: rung ba bzlog na kun tu spong zhes gsungs //
NK116(le)001:5835: mdor bsdu ba'i phyir thams cad ces bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:5836: thams cada yoda par smra ba dang /
NK116(le)001:5839: manga posa bskura ba ste bzhi las /
NK116(le)001:5841: rgyal rigs sgra gcan 'dzin gyi brgyud pa ste /
NK116(le)001:5842: de las gyes pa bdun ni /
NK116(le)001:5846: mang du thos par smra ba /
NK116(le)001:5849: rnam par phye ste smra ba'i sde dang bdun no //
NK116(le)001:5851: rigs bram ze 'od srung chen po'i brgyud pa ste /
NK116(le)001:5852: de las gyes pa lnga ni /
NK116(le)001:5857: 'jig rten las 'das par smra ba'i sde'o //
NK116(le)001:5859: rigs smyig ma mkhan kat+ya ya na'i brgyud pa /
NK116(le)001:5861: rgyal byed tshal la gnas pa'i sde /
NK116(le)001:5862: 'jigs med ri la gnas pa'i sde //
NK116(le)001:5863: gtsug lag khang la gnas pa'i sde'o //
NK116(le)001:5865: 'dreg mkhan gyi rigs nye ba 'khor gyi brgyud pa /
NK116(le)001:5866: de las gyes pa gsum ni /
NK116(le)001:5869: gnas ma bu'i sde ste dril ba'i nyan thos sde ba bco brgyad do //
NK116(le)001:5870: bod 'dir dar ba ni gzhi thams cad yod par smra ba nyid de /
NK116(le)001:5871: sde ba bzhi ka'i bslaba pa'i rnam pa mi mthun
NK116(le)001:5872: kyang thams cad rab byung sde lnga'i spyod pa dang
NK116(le)001:5873: 'brel la / ston pa'i bacasa pasa ma khyab pa
NK116(le)001:5874: mi srida pasa kri ki'i rmis ltas dang mthun par
NK116(le)001:5876: bslab pa kun la dabnga thoba par byas nas nan
NK116(le)001:5877: tan du bsrung bar byed pa gnad che ba yina
NK116(le)001:5878: no // de ltar bsrung ba'i phan yon ci ltar thob na /
NK116(le)001:5880: lha rdzas dga' rgyu mi yi longs spyod dang /
NK116(le)001:5881: bde mchog ro mchog lha yi phun sum tshogs /
NK116(le)001:5882: tshul khrims rgyus byung ci zhig ngo mtshar che /
NK116(le)001:5883: sangs rgyas chos rnam de las byung la ltos /
NK116(le)001:5885: khyad par bstan pa yar ldan gyi dus bslab gzhi yongs rdzogs bsrung pa las //
NK116(le)001:5886: de'i dus nyin zhag gcig gi bar du bslab gzhi sna gcig bsrung ba'i phan yon che ste /
NK116(le)001:5888: bskab ba bye ba gang ga'i bye snyed du //
NK116(le)001:5889: dang pa'i sems kyis zas dang skom rnams dang /
NK116(le)001:5890: gdugs dang ba dan mar me'i phreng ba yi //
NK116(le)001:5891: sangs rgyas bye ba khrag khrig rim gro byas //
NK116(le)001:5892: gang zhig dam chos rab tu 'jigs pa dang //
NK116(le)001:5893: bde gshegs bstan pa 'gag par 'gyur ba'i tshe //
NK116(le)001:5894: nyin mtshan du ni bslab pa gcig spyod pa //
NK116(le)001:5895: bsod nams de ni de bas khyad par 'phags /
NK116(le)001:5897: 'dir lus can 'gro ba'i sgron me gcig pu gang
NK116(le)001:5898: gi bka' drin 'khor ba med par rig nas dang
NK116(le)001:5899: pa'i yul gyis dbugs khar 'tshang ba dang chab gcig
NK116(le)001:5900: 'di lta'i rnam rtog thol gyis shar ba brjod pa
NK116(le)001:5901: don yod pa'i phyir smras pa /
NK116(le)001:5902: bcom ldan 'das thams cad mkhyen pa sh+aakya'i tog la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK116(le)001:5903: bskal mang thugs bskyed rlung shugs 'khor lo yis //
NK116(le)001:5904: 'phangs pa'i nyi na byed dam pa rtog dkar zhabs //
NK116(le)001:5905: mtho ris dbang po'i legs byas she mong gis //
NK116(le)001:5906: do kar khug pas rab rib yal ba bzhin //
NK116(le)001:5907: phyogs bcu'i rgyal kun mgrin pa'i rgyud mang glus //
