NK116(le)001:5908: nyer bskur sgyu 'phrul lha mo'i lhum tshal du //
NK116(le)001:5909: mtshan dpe'i pad+mo 'dab stong bzhad pa na //
NK116(le)001:5910: lus can bung ba'i gsos su gyur ba bzhin //
NK116(le)001:5911: lang tshos rgyags pas sh+aakya'i gzhon nus spobs //
NK116(le)001:5912: sgyu rtsal drug cu bzhi yi sba zhags kyis //
NK116(le)001:5913: pham mdzad grags pa'i dbyar gyi rnga gsang sgra //
NK116(le)001:5914: 'chi med lam gyi yol gor 'phyur ba bzhin //
NK116(le)001:5915: nges 'byung rkyen bzhi'i sha ba ris gtses pa //
NK116(le)001:5916: srid pa'i legs tshogs sboms lta'i rgyal srid kyi //
NK116(le)001:5917: lcags kyus khyod thugs brtan par ma zin te //
NK116(le)001:5918: ji ltar rmis pa'i ri skyes bu mos bzhin //
NK116(le)001:5919: grangs med rnam gsum dka' ba'i khur lcid kyis //
NK116(le)001:5920: rgya mtsho'i ska rag can yang 'dar nus nas //
NK116(le)001:5921: gang khyod dam bcar sha thang ngal gyur nas //
NK116(le)001:5922: rdzing 'gram brtson pa'i snying stobs 'bar ba bzhin //
NK116(le)001:5923: gdod ma'i legs smon dus su bab rigs nas //
NK116(le)001:5924: byang chub shing drung ku sha'i mal stan la //
NK116(le)001:5925: gnad bdun chings kyis bsdams pa'i brtan pa 'dir /
NK116(le)001:5926: rwa lngas dkris pa'i ri rab co 'dri bzhin //
NK116(le)001:5927: de tshe mdzod spu'i snang ba 'bum phrag gzis //
NK116(le)001:5928: bdud sde mog mog btang ba'i rting 'phral du //
NK116(le)001:5929: mkha' ltar dag pa'i chos dbyings sad byas te /
NK116(le)001:5930: ma 'dres bco brgyad khyad chos grub pa bzhin //
NK116(le)001:5931: gting mtha' ma dmigs g.yang sar rgyug pa'i 'gro //
NK116(le)001:5932: theg gsum chos kyi 'khor lo'i grus brten nas //
NK116(le)001:5933: kun tu 'od kyi gser gling bder phyin te /
NK116(le)001:5934: rnam mkhyen nor bu'i pha phog bstsal ba bzhin //
NK116(le)001:5935: phyin ci log lta'i man da nas myos pas //
NK116(le)001:5936: du shes las rung mun pa'i rgol ngan lce //
NK116(le)001:5937: mnyan yod cho 'phrul rdo rje rtse brgya bas //
NK116(le)001:5938: bcad pa'i mod la mya ngan khung 'dzul bzhin //
NK116(le)001:5939: chos kun stong gzigs don dam bskal ba'i mes //
NK116(le)001:5940: skye sogs 'gyur ba'i mtsho chen bskam zin kyang //
NK116(le)001:5941: rtag lta g.yang lug go cha ral phyir du /
NK116(le)001:5942: mtshan gyi me tog dbang gzhu yal ba bzhin /
NK116(le)001:5943: bsod nams dbul ba'i 'gro bar sman slad du //
NK116(le)001:5944: 'dod 'byung ring bsrel nor bu cha brgyad du /
NK116(le)001:5945: bzhag nas mi gnas dbyings su gzims pa'i mod //
NK116(le)001:5946: sa rnams gsum po skyo bas brgyal ba bzhin //
NK116(le)001:5947: e ma mi srid srid pa 'di 'dra tshul //
NK116(le)001:5948: bsam nas ji ltar don du ra med bzhin /
NK116(le)001:5949: ma rig chom pas kun rtog 'gog min te /
NK116(le)001:5950: 'du shes stor bas thom thom bem bzhin gyur //
NK116(le)001:5951: kye ma dus gsum rgyal ba'i spyi dpal khyod //
NK116(le)001:5952: gang du gshegs der rdzogs smrin sbyang gsum po /
NK116(le)001:5953: ring por mi thogs mthar phyin bdag bgrod nas //
NK116(le)001:5954: sku bzhi lhun grub 'gro ba'i mgon gyur shog /
NK116(le)001:5955: da ni sdoms pa gsum gang zag gcig gi rgyud
NK116(le)001:5956: la gnas tshul mya ngan zhes bya ba la sogs
NK116(le)001:5957: pas bstan te / rang nyid mya ngana las 'adsa
NK116(le)001:5958: para bsngo basa lhag pa'i tshul khrimsa 'chang ba so
NK116(le)001:5959: pas bstan te / thar dang // gazhana la phana pa bsgrub pasa byang sdoma yina la //
NK116(le)001:5960: rgyud sde chen po nas dabnga bskura rnala ma ste
NK116(le)001:5961: ji bzhin par thoba nasa sngagsa kyi sdom pa thob
NK116(le)001:5962: pa ste / de ltar sdom pa gsuma ka rdzogas tshe lung gi bslab bya dang //
NK116(le)001:5963: rtogs pa'i yona tan mtha' daga je cher mang du 'gro zhing //
NK116(le)001:5964: ngo bo sems nyid gciga pu lasa ma 'das shing ldoga pa tha dada du //
NK116(le)001:5965: gang zaga gciga gi rgyud la gansa pa yina no //
NK116(le)001:5966: de dag nanga 'agla byung na 'og ma las gonga
NK116(le)001:5967: ma gtso bora bton pa ni sngona byon makhasa gruba
NK116(le)001:5968: rnams kyi lugas la gragas pa yin te /
NK116(le)001:5969: 'oga ma so so thar ba'i rnama pa 'agla ba ltara snang yanga /
NK116(le)001:5970: gnoda pa sponga dang phana 'dogas pa gnyis po dgongas pa mthuna te /
NK116(le)001:5971: ganga zhiga bcas pa la 'agla pa gyur na gannga bar mi srida la /
NK116(le)001:5972: gannga na 'agla ba mi srida de chosa cana yin pa /
NK116(le)001:5974: thugs rje mnga' bas rigs gzigs nas //
NK116(le)001:5975: bkag ba rnams kyang de la gnang /
NK116(le)001:5977: khyad par sngags kyi theg pa ltos nas 'di ltar zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:5978: 'di ltar nyan thosa pa la ltung ba phog byed kyi rgyu dang /
NK116(le)001:5979: byang chub semas dapar yang snga ma dang phyogsa mthuna
NK116(le)001:5980: na nyes byas su gyur ba'i myos byed chang gi
NK116(le)001:5981: rim pa sngagas kyi skabs su dama rdzasa su shes
NK116(le)001:5982: par spyod pa'i skyes bu'i rtogsa tshogas thams cad lha
NK116(le)001:5983: dang lha mor shara basa na gzhi chang dang bsam
NK116(le)001:5984: pa sred pa gnyis ka gazhana dag pa'i rang bzhin
NK116(le)001:5986: dge slong ma yina la byang chub semas dapa'nga mina te /
NK116(le)001:5987: thabas dang bral ba'i chagas spong nyan thos dang /
NK116(le)001:5988: nyon mongas pa'i mthusa nona pa so skye phal pa la yang gnang ba mina no //
NK116(le)001:5991: snang ba matha'a daga lha dang dkyil 'khora dang /
NK116(le)001:5992: spyad par bya ba'i dama rdzasa bduda rtsi'i ranga bzhina du /
NK116(le)001:5993: 'du shesa gansa 'gyur ba'i ganga zag de la gannga ba yina no //
NK116(le)001:5995: so so thara ba dang byang chuba semas dapa'a yi /
NK116(le)001:5996: dge slong dang ni dge 'duna la byin pa lasa /
NK116(le)001:5997: yi dama gyi lha la phula bas tshogsa kyang yara ldan du 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:5998: bslab pa'i cha shes phra rab gazhana rnams la'ang de yi 'dre bar shes par byos shig /
NK116(le)001:5999: de ltar sdom gsum so so'i cho ga'i dus su
NK116(le)001:6000: rdzas mi gcig pas sdom pa yang de ltar gnas
NK116(le)001:6001: pa 'on kyang zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston
NK116(le)001:6004: sngags gsum po gang las blangs pa'i yul /
NK116(le)001:6005: gang gis len pa'i bsam pa /
NK116(le)001:6006: ji ltar len byed kyi cho ga rang rang gi ldog pa ma 'dres pa'i sgo nas /
NK116(le)001:6007: ji srid blangs pa'i dus kyang tha dad du nges
NK116(le)001:6008: pa kho na yin pa'i phyir rang rang gi ldog
NK116(le)001:6009: pa la gzhi mthun pa'i mi srid cing mtshan nyid
NK116(le)001:6010: so sor 'dzin pas rang ldoga ma 'dresa par yod
NK116(le)001:6011: pa'i phyir gang zag gcig gi rgyud la so so'i
NK116(le)001:6012: dagga dgosa rnams tshanga ba yin no //
NK116(le)001:6013: de ltar na'ang ngo bo gansa 'gyur te yona tan yara ldana pasa ganda kyisa mi 'gal te /
NK116(le)001:6015: thabs chen rnams dang ldan pa la //
NK116(le)001:6016: nyon mongs byang chub yan lag 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:6019: bla med mchog gi sdom pa ru /
NK116(le)001:6020: 'dul ba'i dbang gi tshul khrims dang //
NK116(le)001:6021: byang chub sems dpa'i bslab pa kun //
NK116(le)001:6022: ma lus kun 'dus rnam par dag /
NK116(le)001:6024: de yang dusa skabsa kyi gdul bya'i mthun snang gtso bora spyod pa'i tshul gal che ste /
NK116(le)001:6026: 'di la sdig to mi dge'i phyogs //
NK116(le)001:6027: phal cher nyan thos lugs bzhin bsrung //
NK116(le)001:6029: byang chub sems dpa'i lugs bzhin bsrung //
NK116(le)001:6030: 'jig rten ma dad gyur ba'i cha //
NK116(le)001:6031: gnyis ka mthun rnams 'bad pas bsrungs //
NK116(le)001:6034: 'jig rten ma dad gyur ba'i cha //
NK116(le)001:6035: mthong dang dris te spang bar bya //
NK116(le)001:6037: yang na dus skabs gtsor spyad ni //
NK116(le)001:6040: lam la rnal du 'byor ba dang /
NK116(le)001:6042: thams cad mkhyen pa'i gnas skabs de dang de dag gi spyod pa ma 'dres par blang dor bya'o //
NK116(le)001:6043: grub matha'i 'dod gzhung phye nas ngo bo gnas 'gyur
NK116(le)001:6044: sogs 'dod tshul ston pa'i phyir grub pa'i zhes bya
NK116(le)001:6045: ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:6046: gzhan yang gruba pa'i matha'a la dpyad pa zhugas pa rnams kyi bzhed tshul ni //
NK116(le)001:6047: gansa 'gyur ngo bo gciga tu 'doda pa ni yongs
NK116(le)001:6048: grub chen po'i rtogs pas rgyud grol pa la bya
NK116(le)001:6050: shes rab kyis ni ye shes rnam par dag pa 'thob //
NK116(le)001:6051: ye shes rnam par dag pas tshul khrims phun sum tshogs //
NK116(le)001:6052: zhes pa'i don dang ldan pa yin no //
NK116(le)001:6053: gciga la bzhi mi mthuna du 'doda pa dang ni shes rab don gcig tu yod kyang /
NK116(le)001:6054: 'du shes kyi cha nas gzhi mi mthun par tha dad du grub pa'o //
NK116(le)001:6055: gsuma ka rdzasa 'agla gonga 'phela 'doda pa dang ni /
NK116(le)001:6056: sdom gsum rdzogs pa'i gang zag de dngos kyi blo'i
NK116(le)001:6057: rim pa las so so nas yod do snyam byed
NK116(le)001:6058: kyi shes ngor rdzas 'gal bas gong ma'i thabs dang
NK116(le)001:6059: shes rab kyis 'og ma'i sdom pa dngos po dang
NK116(le)001:6061: zil gyis gnon par mi nusa te /
NK116(le)001:6062: 'on kyang rang rang ngos nas 'phel bar 'dod do //
NK116(le)001:6063: de yang so thar gyi sdom pa rten 'phos pas ldog cha tsam gtong yang /
NK116(le)001:6064: ngo bo gnas par 'dod pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6065: la la shi 'phos pas gtong yang /
NK116(le)001:6066: de'i ngo bo sdom pa tsam po ba zhig byang sdom du gnas 'gyur ba yin no //
NK116(le)001:6067: zhes 'dod pa yang don gyi gnas 'gyur dang dngos po gcig ste //
NK116(le)001:6068: dman sems kyis blangs pa'i so thar de nyid byang
NK116(le)001:6069: sems nyes spyod sdom pa'i tshul khrims gnas 'gyur ba
NK116(le)001:6070: yin no // gtong thoba matshamas nas rnama para dbye
NK116(le)001:6071: ba na gnas dus kyi dgag bya dmigs bsal la
NK116(le)001:6073: gong ma'i sgom pa thob dus 'og ma gtong ba'i
NK116(le)001:6074: shes byed rnam pa thams cad du dgod na mi
NK116(le)001:6075: 'thad de / dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pa mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK116(le)001:6076: dbang bzhi ma rdzogs na sangs rgyas mi thob pa dang 'gal lo //
NK116(le)001:6077: donga rtse brtsegsa bzhina sdom rdzas tha dad ma 'dresa par 'doda pa ni /
NK116(le)001:6078: dang po gang zag gcig gi rgyu tshogs las skyes pa //
NK116(le)001:6079: bar du sdom pa gsum gyi 'gal ba ltag mi sprod pa //
NK116(le)001:6080: tha ma sgrub sde gcig pa ste chos gsum tshangs
NK116(le)001:6081: pa'i rdzas ldog dang snga phyi thams cad gcig pa
NK116(le)001:6082: med pa'i dbang du 'thad du rung ngo //
NK116(le)001:6083: nyi zla skara gsum rima cana 'tshogas pa ltar gyi bag la zhar 'dod pa'ang //
NK116(le)001:6084: mtshan nyid so sor 'dzin pa'i cha nas gzhal na
NK116(le)001:6085: bri gang med pa'i phyir ranga 'oda ma nyamsa te
NK116(le)001:6086: / nus pa'i che chung gi khyad zhugsa pa bzhin 'doda do /
NK116(le)001:6087: mdor na de dag thams cad gang zag gi rgyud
NK116(le)001:6088: dang 'brel nas grub pa'i tshul de sogs zhes bya
NK116(le)001:6089: ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:6090: de la sogas pa rnam par rig byed tha dad
NK116(le)001:6091: pa'i phyir khasa blangsa ji snyed matha'a daga kyang rang
NK116(le)001:6092: ranga gi cho ga'i dusa ltar rang sdom gsum ranga
NK116(le)001:6093: ldoga ma 'dres par yod pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6094: de ltar yod pas bsrung matshamas kyi dusa na'ang dagga
NK116(le)001:6095: bya'i gnyen por dgosa pa 'gog byed rang gzhunga tshanga
NK116(le)001:6096: bar byas te spyod pa gal che ste dge dang
NK116(le)001:6097: sdig pa rnams rtog gi gzugs brnyan yin pas so
NK116(le)001:6098: // 'o na de rnam par rig pa gansa 'gyur
NK116(le)001:6099: te ngo bo nyid med pa'i zad par 'khyol ba
NK116(le)001:6100: rtogs pa'i ye shesa kyi mthusa byed pasa na /
NK116(le)001:6101: gong du bshad pa rnams spyir btang tsam ste /
NK116(le)001:6102: dmigas basla gnas lugs phu thag chod min gyis dbye
NK116(le)001:6103: ba phyed para ba yina pa blo gros rab gsal
NK116(le)001:6104: gyis zhus pa'i mdor 'du shes dang bcas pa'i khrims
NK116(le)001:6105: la smad pa'i gsham du gang la sdom pa dang
NK116(le)001:6106: sdom pa ma yin pa'i rlom sems med cing rtog
NK116(le)001:6107: pa med pa de ni mya ngan las 'das pa'i
NK116(le)001:6108: tshul khrims rnam par dag pa yin no //
NK116(le)001:6110: de ltar mod kyis chu bran rgya mtshor phyin pa'i tshe ba tsh+wa can duganasa 'gyur ba yin gyis /
NK116(le)001:6111: bgrod pa'i lam du rang mtshan log kyang 'dir 'jig
NK116(le)001:6112: pa'i tshul glengs gzhi zhes bya ba la sogs pas
NK116(le)001:6113: bstan te / de yang glengsa gzhi sdom gsum gansa
NK116(le)001:6114: 'gyur du 'doda pa dag la phyir bcos kyi dgos
NK116(le)001:6115: pa meda de so so thar pa'i ngosa la ltos
NK116(le)001:6116: nasa byung ba'i ltung ba gciga so thar ranga ngosa
NK116(le)001:6117: nas 'chosa par 'dod na byang sems du gansa 'gyur
NK116(le)001:6119: gonga ma byang sems kyi sdom pa'i ngosa nasa 'chosa par 'dod na'ang mi 'thad de /
NK116(le)001:6120: gnang na 'gal mi srid pas na de nyid la
NK116(le)001:6121: ltung ba ma byung ba'i phyir 'chosa mi dgosa te
NK116(le)001:6122: snyon dor ba'o // 'on kyang lam zhugs kyi gang
NK116(le)001:6123: zag gsum ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khas 'che so
NK116(le)001:6124: cog rnam shes kyi ngos nas gnas 'gyur khyab brdal
NK116(le)001:6125: du med pa'i tshul lus ngag ces bya ba la
NK116(le)001:6127: so thar ni lus ngaga lasa skyes pa'i sdoma pa gzugas cana nama /
NK116(le)001:6128: nyon mongs sponga semsa rgyuna chagsa kyi sa bona la
NK116(le)001:6129: bdena par zhena pa'i mthu brtas pa dang ldana pa'i
NK116(le)001:6130: rigs la / gong mar mi 'chol te nyon mongs
NK116(le)001:6131: bsgyur ba dang gong ma'i lam 'khyer sogs thabsa shes
NK116(le)001:6133: theg pa chena po'i lam du zhugas nas dbang bskur
NK116(le)001:6134: ba tsam noda na'ang sdom gsum gansa 'gyur la dbang
NK116(le)001:6135: thoba pa'i rdo rje 'dzina pa min no //
NK116(le)001:6136: 'o na gnas 'gyur ba'i tshad sus shes snyam na
NK116(le)001:6137: sdom pa zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te
NK116(le)001:6138: / sdom pa daga para byed pa la 'du shesa rnam par dag dgos pa yin pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6139: 'du shesa daga byed lha yi rnal 'byor la rang byan chub dgos pa yin zhing /
NK116(le)001:6140: de nyid daga byed snang stong dbyer med kyi ye shesa la goms pa tshad du 'khyol na /
NK116(le)001:6141: bacasa pa'i ltung ba chosa can gzhan la ltos pa'i
NK116(le)001:6142: phyir skye ba dang rkyen gyis 'phrog pa'i phyir 'jiga
NK116(le)001:6143: par nges pa can yin te /
NK116(le)001:6144: skabs 'dir de dag ranga matshana par mi 'dzina pas
NK116(le)001:6145: thoba pa dang shora ba meda cing thoga matha'a bar
NK116(le)001:6146: gsum gang du'ang 'agla bar mi gansa pa'i don dam
NK116(le)001:6148: sdom pa'i ngo bo kuna rdzoba yina pa'i gansa 'gyur grub pa sla'o //
NK116(le)001:6149: ji ltar grub pa'i tshul skabs su ma bab le'u bcu bas ston par 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:6150: de lta na'ang dmigs bsal gzhi dang zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:6151: gzhi so byang sngags gsum gyi rten dang bsam pa
NK116(le)001:6152: gnang bkag gi skyon yon gnyis ka bdena grub mngona
NK116(le)001:6153: gyur dang ldana pa'i rigs der /
NK116(le)001:6154: mos pasa spyod pa'i sdoma pa gsuma du nges phyir de ldanagyi gang zag la gnad du che ba /
NK116(le)001:6155: gansa na gsum bye braga tu gnas shing bsunga na 'chola ba ste so sor bsrung dgos la /
NK116(le)001:6156: ma nyams par ldana na yara ldana dang 'chosa na
NK116(le)001:6157: gang nyams pa'i ranga sa nasa nyamsa pa khola bur
NK116(le)001:6158: phyung ba'i bshags pasa phyir bcosa 'grub pa yin no
NK116(le)001:6159: / ci'i phyir zhe na nyes pa bskyed pa'i rgyur 'gro na ganga yanga 'goga cing /
NK116(le)001:6160: dge ba dang yona tan bskyed pa'i rgyur 'dug na gannga ba'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:6161: gannga bakaga gnyis ka don gyi khyad che ba las
NK116(le)001:6162: tshig gi lam na gansa pa mina te gang zag
NK116(le)001:6163: so so'i rgyud dang 'brel nas gruba pa kho na'o
NK116(le)001:6164: // de yang rin chen phreng ba las /
NK116(le)001:6165: spyir btang ba las dmigs kyis bsal /
NK116(le)001:6166: bstan bcos dag ni kun la basngagasa /
NK116(le)001:6168: de ltar sdom pa'i tshul khrims kyis rgyud bsngomasa nas
NK116(le)001:6169: chos sdud pa'i tshul khrims pha rol zhes bya ba
NK116(le)001:6171: sbyin sogs pha rola tu phyin pa druga dang 'brela
NK116(le)001:6172: ba'i tshogas chen rnam pa gnyis kyi yona tan ji
NK116(le)001:6173: snyed ma skyes pa bskyed para byed par dang //
NK116(le)001:6174: skyes pa spel ba la dge ba chosa sdud kyi
NK116(le)001:6175: tshul khrimas zhesa bya ba sems kyi bslaba pasa bsdusa
NK116(le)001:6176: pa ste / de yang byamsa dang snying rjesa zina pa'i dge ba ni /
NK116(le)001:6177: ganga dang gang du semsa can dona byed pa sbyin pa yina cing /
NK116(le)001:6178: de la rang 'doda kyi khris meda pa tshul khrimas yin la /
NK116(le)001:6179: gazhana dona bsgrub pa la skyo ngala meda pa bzoda pa'o //
NK116(le)001:6180: bya ba de la lhag para spro bzhina 'juga pa brtsona 'grusa te /
NK116(le)001:6181: semas cana dona la rtse gciga tu dmigs pa bsam gtan dang /
NK116(le)001:6182: dngosa po dang matshana mar zhen pa spangas pa shesa raba ste /
NK116(le)001:6183: de lta bas na pha rola tu phyin pa druga po dus nama yanga 'du 'bral meda do //
NK116(le)001:6184: 'dir sems canagyi don la rim gro mi lhod pa'i
NK116(le)001:6185: cha nas phyogs gcig tu bkral ba yin la de
NK116(le)001:6186: las rnam grangs gzhan yang mang ngo //
NK116(le)001:6187: rgyun gyi spyod lam rnam bzhi kuna la sangs rgyas
NK116(le)001:6188: chos dge 'dun gsum gtong ba tshul khrims lha ste
NK116(le)001:6190: chos rnams kyi de kho na nyid shesa bzhin ldana par bya ba dang /
NK116(le)001:6191: gzhan yang sangs rgyas phal po che'i /
NK116(le)001:6192: lung shing rtar drang bzhin du spyod yula yongas su
NK116(le)001:6193: dag pa'i dge tshogsa la blo stobs su gyur ba'i
NK116(le)001:6194: dus kyi tshe goma pa'i 'degas 'joga tshun chad sgo
NK116(le)001:6195: gsum gyi bya ba mtha' daga kyang pha rol tu
NK116(le)001:6196: phyin pa druggi lam du rtsola ba meda par 'juga
NK116(le)001:6197: pasa tshogas gnyis rdzogas pa'i thabs su shina tu myur
NK116(le)001:6198: ba'o // de skad du bslab btus las /
NK116(le)001:6199: bdag gi lus dang longs spyod dang /
NK116(le)001:6200: dus gsum dge ba skyes pa rnams /
NK116(le)001:6201: sems can kun la gtong ba dang //
NK116(le)001:6202: de bsrug dag pa spel ba'o //
NK116(le)001:6203: zhes gsungs pa'i rkang pa phyi ma gnyis ni sa dang sbyar na /
NK116(le)001:6204: las dang po bas bsrung ba /
NK116(le)001:6205: mos spyod kyi sa dag pa /
NK116(le)001:6206: ma dag sa bdun la btang ba /
NK116(le)001:6207: dag pa gsum na spel ba'i tshul bslab btus las rgya cher gsungs pas /
NK116(le)001:6209: de la sems can don byed tshul khrimsa ni thabs la zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:6210: byang sa'i bslab bya khong du chud cing /
NK116(le)001:6211: thabas la makhasa pasa dngosa sama brgyud ma nasa /
NK116(le)001:6212: semas can kuna la phana pa lhur lena par byed1 cing /
NK116(le)001:6214: gzhan mgu ba'i phyir snyan par smra ba 2dang /
NK116(le)001:6215: gdul bya'i 'khor yid rton pa'i phyi rang ngos nas kyang dona ji bzhina spyod pa 3dang /
NK116(le)001:6216: gzhan la ji skad bstan pa'i dona dang mthuna par rang yang byed 4 pa ste /
NK116(le)001:6217: bsdu dngos bzhi dang dge ba'i chosa mtha' dag sdud
NK116(le)001:6218: pa'i tshula khrimas 'di ni byang chub glinga du 'jug
NK116(le)001:6219: pa la gtan pa med pa'i sgo 'aphara phye ba
NK116(le)001:6220: lta go skabs shin tu yangas pa'o //
NK116(le)001:6221: 'di la'ang brtags pa'i gnas drug gsungs pa gang la zhes bya la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:6222: lam 'dir zhugs pa ganga la brtaga pa gzhi bdag 1 dang /
NK116(le)001:6224: yan lag zang zing gis 'phong ba 3dang /
NK116(le)001:6226: 'byor ba ste bzhi bsdom pa'i rnam pa drug tu gsungas pa yanga /
NK116(le)001:6227: mdor na ranga gi chosa la 'byor rguda brtag para 'du ba'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:6228: ranga nyid chosa lam gyis bslab bya ma nyamsa bzhin gazhana dona bya la /
NK116(le)001:6229: ranga dona nyamsa pa'i rgyu so skyes kyi 'khrula pa
NK116(le)001:6230: bdag gi rgyud du ji ltar yod min brtag nas
NK116(le)001:6231: nyes pa gting nas 'dod pa la brtson par bya'o
NK116(le)001:6232: // bag yangs kyi skabs dmigs gsal ba gzhan la zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:6233: gzhan la phan pa rlabs chen 'grub par srid na
NK116(le)001:6234: bslab sdom gyi bcas pa chung ngu bag yangs su
NK116(le)001:6235: gnang ba'i skabs yod de grong khyer gyi rim gro'i
NK116(le)001:6236: phyir na grong rdal blos btang ba dang bdag bsrung
NK116(le)001:6237: ba'i phyir sa gtong zhing chos kyi phyir du bdag
NK116(le)001:6238: kyang gtong ba sogs gnang ba yin no /
NK116(le)001:6239: bshad ma thag pa'i 'khor bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa 'chad pa la /
NK116(le)001:6240: sa bcad ston pa'i phyir 'di na zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:6241: 'jig rten 'di na mi mjeda ces pa sdug bsngal sogs kyis dbye dka' ba'am /
NK116(le)001:6242: skyon yon gnyis kyi cha nas thog ste /
NK116(le)001:6243: dang po ltar na 'gro ba'i las nyon zab pa'i mtshams mi 'byed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6244: phyi ma ltar na zhing 'dir byang sems rnams bzoda
NK116(le)001:6245: pa'i stobs kyi yon tan 'byams su klas pa'i phyir
NK116(le)001:6246: gnod pas mi 'byed gang rung bris kyang 'thad pa'i
NK116(le)001:6247: dpe can gang zhig sa gzhi'i dpe ru bkod pa
NK116(le)001:6248: de la chosa kyi dri bazanga rgyas pa ma nyams
NK116(le)001:6249: par raba tu bsrunga ba'i don la /
NK116(le)001:6250: nang gses su bslab pa'i gnas daka'a ba sna tshogs dang du lena pa'i bzoda pa 1dang /
NK116(le)001:6251: gnod byed la khong mi 'khrugs shing ji mi snyam pa'i bzod pa 2dang /
NK116(le)001:6252: zaba mo'i dona blo la shong ste mi skrag pa'i bzod pa ste rnama 3pa gsuma mo //
NK116(le)001:6253: de dag las kyang las dang po bas khro ba
NK116(le)001:6254: 'gog pa'i bzod pa gtso bor bsgrub pa'i tshul yid
NK116(le)001:6255: ni zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:6256: gang zhig yida ni shina tu rengsa pa ste zhes
NK116(le)001:6257: las su ma rung bas byas pa'i zhe sdang gi
NK116(le)001:6258: sdiga pa'i mngona rtogsa muna pa las kyang cher gnag
NK116(le)001:6259: pa'i bang bar tshud pa'i khri shing cana gtan du
NK116(le)001:6260: thara meda dmyal ba'i brtson rara 'dzula ba la skrag
NK116(le)001:6262: dus nama yanga khro ba'i go skabsa dbye bar mi bgyida de /
NK116(le)001:6264: zhe sdang lta bu'i sdig pa med //
NK116(le)001:6265: bzod pa lta bu'i dka' thub med //
NK116(le)001:6266: de bas bzod la nan tan du //
NK116(le)001:6267: sna tshogs tshul gyis bsgoms par bya /
NK116(le)001:6269: rang sems gdul ba'i tshul gnod pa'i zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:6270: de yang gnoda pa'i yul ni nagsa kyi tshera ma kun nas grangs mang pa bzhina /
NK116(le)001:6271: so sora gdul gyi mi langas te slar yang kuna nasa kun tu 'phela pa cana yin pas so //
NK116(le)001:6272: de bas 'khona dang khro ba'i byed po bdag 'dzin
NK116(le)001:6273: gciga pu yin pas de btula na bzoda pa'i daka'a
NK116(le)001:6274: thuba ces mi lcogs pa'i khur chen de badga la
NK116(le)001:6276: gnod rkyen rang gi kun rtog nyer len gyis bos
NK116(le)001:6277: tshul reg pa zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston
NK116(le)001:6278: te / 'di ltar rega pa shina tu rtsub pa'i
NK116(le)001:6279: zhes gtum po'i tshiga gi mad'i rtse mosa skyes bu'i
NK116(le)001:6280: snying la zuga pa canga 'chi'am ste ma zug go
NK116(le)001:6281: te / / de nyid bden par dang du blanga ba'i nyer lena gyis /
NK116(le)001:6282: phana tshuna rten dang brten para 'khruga bzhina manra ba yin no /
NK116(le)001:6283: tshur rol mthong ba'i gnas skabs 'di na gnod pa'i
NK116(le)001:6284: rgyu dang 'brasa bu gnyis ka matha'a yasa su 'gyur
NK116(le)001:6285: ba yang badga nyid kho na lasa byung ba yin
NK116(le)001:6286: te dper na sgra bsgrags pa dang mnyam du brag
NK116(le)001:6288: badga nyid ma byung na gnoda pa'i yula meda pasa
NK116(le)001:6289: ranga gi 'khon tshig sogs sngona du byas pa'i rkyen
NK116(le)001:6290: gyis bosa pa la ltos shig /
NK116(le)001:6291: rkyen la brten nas 'tsheng pa'i tshul brtag na zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:6292: zhib mor brtagsa na gnoda chena ma yina par ma zad shin tu phana chena yin te /
NK116(le)001:6294: de lta'i yul ganga la brten nas bzoda pa'i rang
NK116(le)001:6295: bzhin gru gzengas lta bu yang daga thob tshe byang
NK116(le)001:6296: chuba semas kyi nora bu rin chen 'thoba para 'gyur
NK116(le)001:6297: basa na / de 'dra'i 'phral gyis gnoda pa thar
NK116(le)001:6298: ba'i gsos su che phyir dama pa'i chosa ltar mchoda
NK116(le)001:6299: basa na / par rigs so // lar rnam pa
NK116(le)001:6300: thams cad du 'gro ba ma rigs pas bsgribs pa'i
NK116(le)001:6301: rigs la khro yang gang zag min te /
NK116(le)001:6302: nyon mongs su nges na kho la ji ltar 'khro ste /
NK116(le)001:6304: khro yang 'byung pos bzung pa la //
NK116(le)001:6305: sman pa 'khrugs pa min de ltar //
NK116(le)001:6306: thub pas nyon mongs dag gzigs kyi /
NK116(le)001:6307: nyon mongs dang 'brel gang zag min /
NK116(le)001:6309: don dam pa'i ngos nas khro ba'i tha snyad stong
NK116(le)001:6310: tshul shin tu zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan
NK116(le)001:6311: te / 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lta bas shina
NK116(le)001:6312: tu brtagsa na gnoda pa'i ngo bo la mtshon byed
NK116(le)001:6313: matshana nyid rdul tsam meda de glo bur ba'i rtog
NK116(le)001:6314: pa cung zad shar yang chu yi ri mo bzhina
NK116(le)001:6315: gnyen po mi dgos te rnama rtog khro gnyer rtsub
NK116(le)001:6316: mo rang sar zhiga pa'i mod //
NK116(le)001:6317: mkha'a dbyings bzhina du rnam para stong bar gyur la thoba dang shora ba meda do //
NK116(le)001:6318: rgyu mtshan gyis snying stobs bslang ba gang phyir zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:6319: spyir ganga ci'i phyir bzoda pa'i daka'a thuba bshad ma thag pa gsuma po nyamsa par gyur na /
NK116(le)001:6320: sbyin pa la sogas pa'i pha rola tu phyin pa
NK116(le)001:6321: gazhana lnga po yanga dper na mgron po'i phyi matha'a
NK116(le)001:6322: dgra yisa bskora ba'i bshula lam bzhina du /
NK116(le)001:6323: 'doda pa'i gansa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ngogs su phyin
NK116(le)001:6324: par daka'a basa na blo'i stobsa mi zhum bar yang
NK116(le)001:6326: brtson 'grus kyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'chad pa
NK116(le)001:6327: la ngo bo ni dus las zhes bya ba la
NK116(le)001:6329: dusa skad cig tsam yang ched du gnyer bya'i lasa
NK116(le)001:6330: la yola ba meda pa'i brtsona 'grusa kyisa rkyen gyi
NK116(le)001:6331: khar ma shor ba ranga dabnga nyid du dge ba'i
NK116(le)001:6332: chosa matha'a dag rnams sdud pa ni ji ltar skyed
NK116(le)001:6333: mosa tshala du nganga ba'i khyu dga' zhing 'gro ba
NK116(le)001:6334: bzhina du / le lo'i gayangas la ldog ste bskyud
NK116(le)001:6335: pa ste brjed pa meda para ched du bya ba
NK116(le)001:6337: de'i 'gal zla ston pa bya ba zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:6338: tshe 'di ched gnyer gyi bya ba ngana pa la zhena cing 'du 'dzi'i thaga pasa dkrisa te /
NK116(le)001:6339: skyid lugs pa'i mthusa nona nas dam pa'i chos la sbyor ba'i nus pa'ang btang zhing /
NK116(le)001:6340: badga nyid lta bu'i ga la 'grub snyam ste brnyas nasa semas zhuma pa'i brtula zhugas blangsa pa /
NK116(le)001:6341: de 'dra'i tha shal ba'i gang zaga rnams nyes pa'i
NK116(le)001:6342: gzengas zhes dper na khrol tshag can gyi gru gzengs
NK116(le)001:6343: la zhona na chur bying ba bzhin srid mtshor brgal
NK116(le)001:6344: mi rigs pa'o / rang bzhin dbye phyir bdud bzhi zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:6345: byang chub sems dpa' sbyor ba gang zhig la rtsom
NK116(le)001:6346: tshe lus ngag gi las rtab rtab po tsam gyis
NK116(le)001:6347: mi chog par / lha dang nyon mongs phung po
NK116(le)001:6348: 'chi bdag ste bduda bzhi 'jomas pa'i snying stobs kyi
NK116(le)001:6349: go cha rkyen gang gis kyang mi shig pa'i brtsona
NK116(le)001:6350: mi chog par / 'grusa dang / pha rol phyin
NK116(le)001:6351: pa drug gam bcu la brten nas sa bcu'i go
NK116(le)001:6352: sar lam lnga'i 'gros kyis bgrod de rang sa'i yon
NK116(le)001:6353: tan mtha' dag rang rgyud la sbyor ba'i brtsona 'grusa
NK116(le)001:6354: mi chog par / 'grusa dang / dang / sems
NK116(le)001:6355: can don byed pa'i brtson 'grus ni rang gzhan gnyis
NK116(le)001:6356: kyi don du thog mar dam bcas pa'i gnas gang
NK116(le)001:6357: yin pa de la slar mi 'gonga zhing bar ma
NK116(le)001:6358: dor mi ldoga ste de tsam bsgrub bo snyams pa'i
NK116(le)001:6359: chog shesa meda pa yi brtsona 'grus can gyis ji
NK116(le)001:6360: ltar yid la smon pa'i dona kuna 'grub pa gdon
NK116(le)001:6361: mi chog par / 'grusa dang / dang / mi
NK116(le)001:6362: za'o // khyad par tshe la longs med bsam pa
NK116(le)001:6363: brtson pa'i yan lag yin pa'i tshul bdag gi zhes
NK116(le)001:6364: bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:6365: de yang chos la brtson pa ma bskyed na badga
NK116(le)001:6366: gi tshe ni nyin mo'i matha'a ste nyi ma nub
NK116(le)001:6367: rir lhung ba'i dus ltar gyur te /
NK116(le)001:6368: myur bar myur bar 'chi ba'i muna naga gisa /
NK116(le)001:6369: gtuga par gyur na 'khora ba'i 'khrul snang gi spyod
NK116(le)001:6370: pa rgyu skar lasa rnam grangas manga basa kyang shul
NK116(le)001:6371: du lus par ma zad sbu ba'i snying po'i chos
NK116(le)001:6372: can du nges phyir de yisa dabugsa mi 'byina no
NK116(le)001:6373: // de'i phyir le lo ring du bsreng ba le lo zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:6374: sgyid lug dang le lo'i rnyog pa dwangsa pa'i brtsona 'grusa kyi /
NK116(le)001:6379: bak+shu ste rgyun bzang chu bo bzhi lta bu las /
NK116(le)001:6380: phyogsa su lhung bar ston pa zhes ko mog gam
NK116(le)001:6381: chu phran lam du skam par 'gyur ba ltar ma
NK116(le)001:6382: yina para rnama pa thams cad nas thams cad du
NK116(le)001:6383: kuna mkhyen ye shes rgya mtsho lta bur phyin par
NK116(le)001:6384: ma gyur ba de srid du /
NK116(le)001:6385: sgo gsum g.yo zhing myura ba'i brtul shugas nyamsa par mi bgyid pa ni dran pa nyer bzhag las //
NK116(le)001:6386: nyon mongs kun gyi gzhi gcig ni //
NK116(le)001:6387: le lo yin te gang la yod //
NK116(le)001:6388: gang la le lo gcig yod pas /
NK116(le)001:6389: de la chos kun med pa yin /
NK116(le)001:6391: da ni bsam gtan gyi pha rol tu phyin pa
NK116(le)001:6392: 'chad pa'i thog mar bsam gtan 'grub pa'i tshogs bstan
NK116(le)001:6393: pa las / dang po nags kyi yon tan ston
NK116(le)001:6394: phyir nags tshal zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston
NK116(le)001:6395: pa las / te / gnas gang zhig nags tshal
NK116(le)001:6396: dang me tog sna tshogs 'khrigas pa'i smana ljongas yid
NK116(le)001:6398: ngang ba dang ngur ba dag spyod lam mi rtsing
NK116(le)001:6399: bar shina tu zhi zhing dul basa bstan par byas
NK116(le)001:6401: blta na sdug pa braga ri'i dbyibs pha gu dang //
NK116(le)001:6402: rta babsa sogs kyi rnam pa can gyi spo na
NK116(le)001:6403: bya dang khyams su ri dwagas sna tshogs gzhon nus
NK116(le)001:6404: mdzesa par byas pa yang yoda do //
NK116(le)001:6405: de las nyams dga' ba'i khyad chos gzhan ma mchis
NK116(le)001:6406: sam zhen yod de shin tu nyams dag'a ba'i nagas
NK116(le)001:6407: tshala lha mo'i gzugs 'dra ba'i rked chingsa ni //
NK116(le)001:6408: shinga bala gzhona nus 'phyangs 'phrul byas pa'i mdo mtshams
NK116(le)001:6409: d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa phyed dpyangs pa lta bu dang
NK116(le)001:6410: yal ga'i lcug phran ldem por mu tig len tshar
NK116(le)001:6411: dbyangs ba lta bu'i lo ma phang phung bsil bu'i
NK116(le)001:6412: rlung gis cung zad g.yo ba'i rtse na /
NK116(le)001:6413: 'tshe ba dogas pasa yid skrag pa mina 'dab chags
NK116(le)001:6414: in+ta ni la'i lang tsho can la byi ru'i 'dren
NK116(le)001:6415: byed 'dar zhing 'khrig lta'i khu byug rnams kyi 'khora
NK116(le)001:6416: ba'i rang bzhin gang der skyo ba skye ba'i gtam
NK116(le)001:6417: gyi spring yiga 'gremsa zhes rgyud mngas kyi 'gyur khug
NK116(le)001:6418: bzhin dal bu dal bu sgra snyan sgrog par 'gyur
NK116(le)001:6421: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor rgyas pas nye bar brgyan byas shing //
NK116(le)001:6422: sked chings char chen sprin gyis 'khrigs pas 'khyud gyur pa /
NK116(le)001:6423: ri rtse nags kyi mthong der chags pa med par ni /
NK116(le)001:6424: rlung ltar g.yo ba'i rang bzhin tshe gzugs skal ba che /
NK116(le)001:6427: bung ba rgyags lding glu len zhing //
NK116(le)001:6428: ljon shing yan lag gar byed la //
NK116(le)001:6429: bya rnams snyan pa'i skad kyang 'byin //
NK116(le)001:6430: bsil yab pad 'dab phyogs na g.yo //
NK116(le)001:6431: phu chu lhung rgyun sgra yang sgrog /
NK116(le)001:6432: mdzes pa'i ri dwags rgyug cing bskor //
NK116(le)001:6434: tsad nan spos sogs dri ngad ldan //
NK116(le)001:6435: dgon pa'i yon tan 'di lta bus //
NK116(le)001:6436: rang gzhan dag la phan 'dogs shing //
NK116(le)001:6437: lan la cung zad mi re ste //
NK116(le)001:6438: grogs mang rnal 'byor ci'i phyir skyo //
NK116(le)001:6439: 'jig rten phal pa de ltar min //
NK116(le)001:6441: de lta bu'i nags tshal du 'gro bar bskul ba
NK116(le)001:6442: de ru zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te
NK116(le)001:6443: / bshad ma thag pa'i gnas de ru rings stabs
NK116(le)001:6444: su gshegas shiga su zhig na bsam gtan sgom par
NK116(le)001:6446: ci'i phyir na 'jig rten phun tshogs kyi longas spyod
NK116(le)001:6447: sprin gyi gtos chen po bla bre lta bu'i nanga
NK116(le)001:6448: sheda na skyes bu'i tshe srog rnam par rola ba'i
NK116(le)001:6449: gloga ni skad cig gis g.yo zhing 'dar ba lta
NK116(le)001:6450: bu la / 'gyur pa'i sdug bsngal dang sduga bsngal gyi sdug bsngal /
NK116(le)001:6451: khyab pa 'du byed kyi sdug bsngal gsum gyi choma
NK116(le)001:6452: rkuna char ltar dkyu zhing 'phral phug gnyis la phunga
NK116(le)001:6453: dkrola bskyed pa'i las ri gzar gyi chu klung ca
NK116(le)001:6455: mya ngam thang du rgyug pa ni gsoga pa dang
NK116(le)001:6456: bsrunga pa dang spel ba'i mtha' mi gtugs pa'i 'doda
NK116(le)001:6457: pa'i rlabs phreng gis 'khrugas bzhin cung zad 'byor bas
NK116(le)001:6458: khengas sems dang / bri yis dogs nas 'jungas pa
NK116(le)001:6459: dang sera sna'i kun 'byung 'phel ba gsum gyis shug
NK116(le)001:6460: drag gi pho nyas tshe'i chu sna pha rol tu
NK116(le)001:6461: gtugsa pa'i rting nas gtan du thar med ngana 'gro'i
NK116(le)001:6462: chu gter mu dang matha'a meda pa'i klung du rnam
NK116(le)001:6464: nor rdzas sdug bsngal gyi rgyur nges pa g.yo sgyu'i zhesabya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:6465: g.yo sgyus char sprin rtag tu zhe la brnaga pa'i
NK116(le)001:6466: rina thanga cana gyi no ni klu mchog rnams kyi
NK116(le)001:6467: gdengs ka bzhin du ji tsam 'byora bzhina sdug bsngal
NK116(le)001:6468: gyi rgyu lasa ma mchis te /
NK116(le)001:6469: de bas yo byad bsnyungsa pa rnams la dgra rkun 'tshe basa sponga zhing /
NK116(le)001:6470: choga shesa thoba pa ni 'byor ba phun sum tshogs pa'i rtse mora 'gro ba yin no //
NK116(le)001:6471: skye bo phal bar 'grogs pa'i nyes pa so so'i zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:6472: so so skye bo'i ranga bzhina ni byis pa gyi
NK116(le)001:6473: na ba lta bu ste rgyang du dor bar bya'o
NK116(le)001:6475: byis pa rnams ni rtag tu nyes pa'i sprin gyis 'khrigsa pas so //
NK116(le)001:6477: badag nyid la mngon par bstod cinga gazhana la dngos brgyud gang rung nas mi snyan pa sgrog ste /
NK116(le)001:6478: nyon mongas pa lngas khongs 'gegs shing dug sbrul gyi
NK116(le)001:6479: lce rtsub mo lta bu'i gtum po'i tshig spyod nyamsa
NK116(le)001:6480: la bstar zhing baga pheb par bsten pa tsam du
NK116(le)001:6481: ma zad dapala dang 'byor ba mi rtag cing mi
NK116(le)001:6482: brtan par g.yo ba gang la'ang rtag para semas shing
NK116(le)001:6483: drin chen po khyad du gsod pas byasa pa mi
NK116(le)001:6484: bzo ba dang ji ltar bskyang kyang mgu pa'i dus
NK116(le)001:6485: med pas 'du shes kyi gzugsa brnyan phyin ci log
NK116(le)001:6486: tu 'khyogsa pa yid la 'khona 'dzin gyi me lce
NK116(le)001:6487: 'bar ba phra ma'i rlung gisa bskyod pa la 'bad
NK116(le)001:6488: pa / rang bzhin mi brtan par spre'u bzhina du
NK116(le)001:6489: brel tshub kyi ngos nas yongs la gnoda pa sna
NK116(le)001:6490: pa / tshogas ster ba / chu srina bzhina du
NK116(le)001:6491: sdig pa'i las sna tshogs pa'i lto ba ngom dus
NK116(le)001:6493: dug rlangs 'thul ba'i sbrul gduga bzhina du g.yo sgyu'i
NK116(le)001:6494: dug gi barlangasa pas su dang 'phrada pa 'jomas pa
NK116(le)001:6495: / me bzhina du rgyu 'bras khyad du gsod pas
NK116(le)001:6496: dge ba'i ljona shinga yang dag par bsreg par 'gyur
NK116(le)001:6497: pa gdon mi za ba'i phyir na /
NK116(le)001:6498: tha chad byis pa'i grogas lasa ringa du bsring bar bya'o //
NK116(le)001:6499: yul gyi nyes dmigs yul gyi zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:6500: yula lnga ni duga lasa kyang ches thu ste rnam par smin pa rtsub pas so //
NK116(le)001:6501: re zhig 'dir snang du spyad pa'i moda la 'ad'a ba'i ro mngar po ltar bro yanga /
NK116(le)001:6502: dug gis tshe rabas gciga tsam 'joms mod kyi de ltar mina par skye ba thams cada du /
NK116(le)001:6503: gasnga sngagas mchoga dang sman gyi rigas su gyur pa kun gyisa gsoda mi runga par byed pas na /
NK116(le)001:6504: ganga zhiga rang gi semas kyi rnam rtog glanga po
NK116(le)001:6505: che myos pa lta bu ma dul gyi bar du
NK116(le)001:6506: / bslu ba'i rdzu 'phrula la 'dod pa'i yula lnga lasa che ba meda de /
NK116(le)001:6507: nam zhig be ma rig bral te phunga po'i 'du byed khyogsa la bazhagas pa de srid du /
NK116(le)001:6508: zhi ba'i nagsa mthongas gong du bstan pa bzhin brag
NK116(le)001:6509: skyibs dang nags gseb daga la bsnyen para mdzoda cig
NK116(le)001:6510: / de yang dben pa'i gtam las //
NK116(le)001:6511: ji srid skyes bu bzhi yi lus //
NK116(le)001:6512: khyogs la brten par ma gyur bar //
NK116(le)001:6513: de srid dgon par rab phyogs te //
NK116(le)001:6514: zhi ba'i ting 'dzin bsgrub par bya /
NK116(le)001:6516: der song pa'i yon tan ni bas mtha' zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:6517: de la basa matha'a ni grong zad pa'i mur thug pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6518: 'broga dgon pa ni ma mtha' rgyang grags las thal pa'i dben pa yin zhing /
NK116(le)001:6519: de na sems gtse ba med pas yida du 'onga zhing skyo shesa 'phela te /
NK116(le)001:6520: tshonga dang so namas kyi bya ba dang sdiga pa'i grogas kyis spangs la /
NK116(le)001:6521: dpya dang khrala dang zho shasa 'tsho pasa rang nyid mi gdunga zhing /
NK116(le)001:6522: bya dang ri dwagsa rnams kyis mi snyan pa sgrog pa meda cing /
NK116(le)001:6523: chu gatsanga dang bza' shing gi 'bras bu la sogs pa'i nyer spyod rgya che la /
NK116(le)001:6524: brag ri'i phug pa dang shing gi lo ma phan tshun 'phyang ba'i khang bzang yangs shing /
NK116(le)001:6525: ljon pa'i grib bsil du 'grogs na bde ba sogs
NK116(le)001:6526: kyi yon tan yid la yang dang yang du bcags
NK116(le)001:6527: te / e ma dus nama zhiga na badga nyid
NK116(le)001:6528: ni gnas der lhan cig tu gansa para 'gyur na
NK116(le)001:6529: ci ma rung bsam nas spro ba bskyed dgos pa'i
NK116(le)001:6531: rtsa ba 'bras bu shun pa lo ma phun sum tshogs pa'i ljon shing ldan //
NK116(le)001:6532: nags tshal ltos med ri bo'i chu rgyun bsil 'bab chags pa med pa'i gnas /
NK116(le)001:6533: chu klung langs pa'i mtha' tu 'bras bu me tog lhung bas brgyan pa yi //
NK116(le)001:6534: nyams dga' bas mthar ci zhig med de dmyal dong khyim gyis bslus te sdod /
NK116(le)001:6536: phan yon gyi sgo nas basngagasa pa de na zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:6537: gnas de na dbyar dgun ston dpyid de dus bzhi'i mgrona po gasra pa yisa //
NK116(le)001:6538: snga ma 'das 'phral phyi ma slebs pas shun pa
NK116(le)001:6539: dang lo 'bras 'pho 'gyur ma nges pa'i mngona rtogsa
NK116(le)001:6540: ngoma pa'i nagas tshala rnams kyis /
NK116(le)001:6541: ranga nyid nyon mongas pa can ma yina no zhes
NK116(le)001:6542: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bka' la gtan tshigsa su byas
NK116(le)001:6543: nas / gang zhig deng la goma bduna phyogsa pa'i
NK116(le)001:6544: bsoda namsa tshad med do zhes sgrogs gyin 'dug pa
NK116(le)001:6545: la thar ba 'dod pa rnams kyi ltos shig /
NK116(le)001:6547: nags tshal sems med kyis sems yod bzhin gang zag chos la bskul ba 'dra mo byas pa ni /
NK116(le)001:6548: dan+t+ra'i bstan chos kyi khungs su drangs so //
NK116(le)001:6549: de yang 'phags pa ting 'dzin rgyal po las /
NK116(le)001:6550: gang la la zhig gis sangs rgyas thams cad la bskal ba'i bar du me tog dang /
NK116(le)001:6553: bde bar sbyar ba'i yo byad thams cad kyis bskal bar mchod pa bas /
NK116(le)001:6554: rab tu skyo ba'i sems kyis dgon par phyogs te
NK116(le)001:6555: gom pa bdun tsam bor na 'di de bas ches
NK116(le)001:6556: bsod nams kyi phung po dpag tu med de /
NK116(le)001:6557: lus dang srog la blta ba rab spongs la /
NK116(le)001:6558: stong pa zhi ba mchog tu bsgom par gyis //
NK116(le)001:6559: brtson zhing rab tu brtson pa'i yid kyis kyang /
NK116(le)001:6560: ri dwags bzhin du dgon par gnas par gyis /
NK116(le)001:6563: ri sul yangs par skye bo bud med med pas rab bde ba /
NK116(le)001:6564: nyer spyod nags tshal sngo 'khrungs phreng bas dpyang sbreng phreng /
NK116(le)001:6565: chu ngogs snyan pa phu chu'i rgyun 'dra rnga ltar snyan pa yis /
NK116(le)001:6566: bag chags nyon mongs yul ma yin zhes 'don pa sgrog pa bzhin /
NK116(le)001:6568: de nas bsam gtan bsgom pa dngos bshad pa ni
NK116(le)001:6569: gang du zhes bya ba la sogs pas brtan te
NK116(le)001:6570: / ganga du phyin pa der bsam gatana shina tu mi g.yo zhing bstana pa ni /
NK116(le)001:6571: lhag pa semas kyi bslaba pa'i matshana nyid desa de
NK116(le)001:6572: yang chos thams cad rten cinga 'brela bar 'byung ba'i
NK116(le)001:6573: phyir thog mar lusa kyi cho ga ni /
NK116(le)001:6574: rnam snang chosa bduna na go sla ste de nyid
NK116(le)001:6575: semas kyi sroga shinga cana gyis 'du shes rtse gciga
NK116(le)001:6576: lasa gnyis pa ma yina pa'i mnyam bazhaga brtsona la
NK116(le)001:6577: dmigas pa gang yanga runga ba'i 'dzina dpyad kyisa yida
NK116(le)001:6578: kyi shes pa ni dge ba'i dona la gcig tu
NK116(le)001:6579: rnama para bcinga ste bsgom pas /
NK116(le)001:6580: ji zhig na ting 'dzin nar son nas /
NK116(le)001:6581: spros pa'i snang ba thams cad chosa nyid stong pa'i
NK116(le)001:6582: klong gciga tu nuba nas snang yula ma 'aggas par
NK116(le)001:6583: chu zla ltar gsal kyang ngera 'dzina gyi rtog pa
NK116(le)001:6585: de yang shesa pa yula la mi rtog par mnyam pa nyid du bazhaga pa la /
NK116(le)001:6586: ngo bo stong gsal gciga pa'i rjesa thoba so sor rtog pa'i shes rab ni lhag mthonga ste /
NK116(le)001:6587: las dang po pa'i dus zhi gnas bsgrub pa'i thabs ni /
NK116(le)001:6589: gser gyi kha dog lta bu'i sku lus kyis //
NK116(le)001:6590: 'jig rten mgon po kun tu mdzes pa ste //
NK116(le)001:6591: dmigs pa de la gang gis sems 'jog pa //
NK116(le)001:6592: byang chub sems dpa' de mnyam bzhag ces bya /
NK116(le)001:6593: zhes sangs rgyas kyi mtshan dpe'i yon tan rtse gcig
NK116(le)001:6594: gi bsam na zhi gnas 'grub pa'i rgyu tsam du
NK116(le)001:6595: ma zad bsam las 'das pa'i phan yon thob pa
NK116(le)001:6597: dbye ba ni dbye na byis pa zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:6598: dbye na byis pa nyer spyod kyi dona raba 'byed pa'i /
NK116(le)001:6599: de bzhina gshegas dge'i bsam gatana te rnam pa gsum dang /
NK116(le)001:6600: rtog dpyod yoda meda kyi dbye bas mu bzhi'i bsam gatana bzhi dang /
NK116(le)001:6601: de bzhina du gzugas meda bzhi ste bcu gcig gi rnam pa'i grangas so //
NK116(le)001:6602: lam la ma zhugsa pa'i so skyes rgyud kyi ting nge 'dzina ni /
NK116(le)001:6603: bsam gtan bzhi dang gzugas meda bzhi'i ting 'dzin yin
NK116(le)001:6604: te byis pa nye bar spyod pa'i lam yina pa'i
NK116(le)001:6605: phyir ro // lam zhugs tshogas dang sbyor ba'i ting 'dzina gyis /
NK116(le)001:6606: rim par thara ba'i lam mngona du byed pas na dona raba 'byed par gragas so //
NK116(le)001:6607: mthong lam dang po'i sa yana chad 'aphagas pa'i ting 'dzin yin te /
NK116(le)001:6608: de nas zaga pa meda pasa na de bzhina gshegas dge'i yina no //
NK116(le)001:6609: khyad gzhi dang khyad chos ni kun kyang zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:6610: de dag kuna kyang ngo bo ni nanga du rtse
NK116(le)001:6611: gcig par semas 'dzina pa yin pa 'grub pa'i rgyu
NK116(le)001:6612: ni drana pa bar ma chad par rgyun chagas su
NK116(le)001:6613: bsgom pa la brtson 'grusa can gyis gal te rnam
NK116(le)001:6614: para g.yengas na slar yanga de kho na la bslana
NK116(le)001:6616: de'i byed lasa ni 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las
NK116(le)001:6617: 'das pa'i bde ba bskyed cing rdzu 'phrul ci rig
NK116(le)001:6619: 'brasa bu mngona par shes pa drug la sogas pa 'thoba pa yina pa gang zhig khyad chos so //
NK116(le)001:6620: 'jig rten pa dang 'das pa'i bsam gtan dngos gzhi
NK116(le)001:6621: ni bsam gtan zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan
NK116(le)001:6622: te / de yang 'dod pa'i khams na lhag mthong shas che ba'i bsam gtan dang /
NK116(le)001:6623: gzugs med pa'i khams zhi gnas shas che ba'i bsam gtan dang /
NK116(le)001:6624: gzugs kyi khams na zhi lhag zung 'brel gyi bsam gtan te /
NK116(le)001:6625: phyogs phyi ma la nang gses kyi dbye ba bzhi las /
NK116(le)001:6626: bsam gtan dang po'i nyer bsdogsa te sta gon ni
NK116(le)001:6627: sbyor ba'i sems de ni bde gsal mi rtog pa'i
NK116(le)001:6628: nyams gang rung la 'adi'o zhes rnam par rtog cing
NK116(le)001:6629: de'i rang bzhin la dpyod pa tsam dang /
NK116(le)001:6630: de nyid nar son nas dngosa gzhi'i skabs su rtog pa meda la dpyod pa tsam zhig go //
NK116(le)001:6631: lhag ma gsuma pora rim bzhin rtog pa yod la dpyod pa med pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6632: dpyod pa yod la rtog pa med pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6633: rtog dpyod gnyis ka med pa'o //
NK116(le)001:6634: de yang rtsing ba dang rag pa'i rtog pa ni rtog pa'o //
NK116(le)001:6635: zhib tu 'dzin cing dpyod pa ni dpyod pa'o //
NK116(le)001:6636: bsam gtan snga ma snga mas zhes dang po nas
NK116(le)001:6637: rim bzhin phyi ma phyi ma'i nyer bsdogas byed pa
NK116(le)001:6638: la 'aphagas pa'i lam gyi rten gzhi zhesa su gragas
NK116(le)001:6639: so // de nas bsam gtan bzhi la yan lag bco brgyad de /
NK116(le)001:6640: dang po la yan lag lnga ste /
NK116(le)001:6646: gnyis pa la yan lag bzhi ste /
NK116(le)001:6650: sems rtse gcig pa nyid do //
NK116(le)001:6651: gsum pa la yang yan lag lnga ste /
NK116(le)001:6656: sems rtse gcig pa nyid do //
NK116(le)001:6657: bzhi pa la yang yan lag bzhi ste /
NK116(le)001:6658: btang snyoms yongs su dag pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6659: dran pa yongs su dag pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6661: sdug bsngal yang ma yin pa'i tshor ba yongs su dag pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6662: sems rtse gcig pa nyid do //
NK116(le)001:6664: de la yona tan thams cada bskyed pa'i bsam gtan ni /
NK116(le)001:6665: thabs snying rje chen po dang ni shes rab ye shesa dama pasa zina pa yin te /
NK116(le)001:6666: des na ting 'dzina manga po dang ldana zhing legs
NK116(le)001:6667: tshogs yon tan gyi rnam pa ci rigs pa thamsa
NK116(le)001:6669: blo rdzasa gciga pa'i phyir mnyam rjesa gang du'ang gzunga 'dzina spong zhing /
NK116(le)001:6670: manyama bazhaga de lasa langas nas rjesa thoba kyi dus rgya yana pa /
NK116(le)001:6671: sa bduna pa tshun chada kuna na yoda pa yina zhes rgya bo mkhas pas gsungs so /
NK116(le)001:6673: zhi lhag gnyis la gal che chung yod dam /
NK116(le)001:6674: 'dir bshad pa med pa ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK116(le)001:6675: yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa chen po'i mdo
NK116(le)001:6676: las nyan thos rnams kyis ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK116(le)001:6678: ting nge 'dzin shas che ba'i phyir dang /
NK116(le)001:6679: shes rab chung ba'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:6680: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis ni mthong mod kyi
NK116(le)001:6681: mi gsal te shes rab shas che ba'i phyir dang
NK116(le)001:6682: / ting nge 'dzin chung ba'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:6683: de bzhin gshegs pas thams cad gzigs te /
NK116(le)001:6684: zhi gnas dang lhag mthong mtshungs par ldan pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:6686: de la zhi gnas kyi stobs kyis ni rnam par
NK116(le)001:6687: rtog pa'i rlung gis sems g.yo ba 'gag par byed
NK116(le)001:6688: la / lhag mthong gi ni rmongs pa'i sgrib pa
NK116(le)001:6689: dang 'jig tshogs la blta ba la sogs pa'i phas
NK116(le)001:6690: rgol gyi lta ba ngan pa'i d+r+wa ba mtha' dag
NK116(le)001:6691: gis g.yo bar mi nus shing /
NK116(le)001:6692: grub mtha' ngan pa dang lung ma bstan gyis sems
NK116(le)001:6693: la gnod par mi 'gyur ba'i tshul zla ba sgron
NK116(le)001:6694: ma'i mdo las / zhi gnas stobs kyis g.yo ba med par 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:6695: lhag mthong gis ni ri dang 'dra bar 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:6697: dengs sang kha gcig gis rnam pa du ma'i dmigs
NK116(le)001:6698: pa can sems kyi rnam par g.yeng ba'i rtog dpyod
NK116(le)001:6699: la mtha' gcig tu so sor rtogs pa'i shes rab
NK116(le)001:6701: de dag gis yang dag pa'i phyogs tsam yang ma mthong bar zad do //
NK116(le)001:6703: 'jam dpal rnam par 'phrul ba las kyang lha'i bu ji tsam du rtog pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6709: rnam par shes pa'i gnas ci tsam pa de tsam du bdud kyi las so ///
NK116(le)001:6712: shin tu mnyam par bzhag pa'i gnas skabs na chos
NK116(le)001:6713: thams cad nam mkha'i dbyings ltar rang bzhin gyis 'od
NK116(le)001:6714: gsal la go 'byed pa'i cha de lhag mthong ma
NK116(le)001:6715: nor ba yin pa'i tshul 'og tu yang 'chad do
NK116(le)001:6718: de ltar ting nge 'dzin gyi spyod yul gzugs brnyan
NK116(le)001:6719: de dag la shes bya'i don de rnam par 'byed
NK116(le)001:6720: pa dang / rab tu rnam par 'byed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6725: lta ba dang rnam par rtog pa gang yin pa de ni lhag mthong zhes bya ba ste /
NK116(le)001:6726: de ltar na byang chub sems dpa' lhag mthong la mkhas pa yin no //
NK116(le)001:6727: gsungs pa dang 'gal bar mi 'gyur ram /
NK116(le)001:6729: snga ma sgom byung shes rab la ltos pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6730: phyi ma ni las dang po pas thos bsam gyi shes rab la ltos pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:6732: 'o na rgyal ba'i mnyam bzhag gi ngos na ji
NK116(le)001:6733: snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes med par mi 'gyur ram
NK116(le)001:6735: rgyal ba thams cad mkhyen pa ni /
NK116(le)001:6736: dper na mtsho la gza' skar shar ba bzhin du yin gyi /
NK116(le)001:6737: rtog dpyod dang bcas pa ni ma yin no //
NK116(le)001:6738: de yang zhi lhag gis bsdus pa'i ting 'dzin de la /
NK116(le)001:6740: kun rdzogs kyi chos thams cad med bzhin snang ba
NK116(le)001:6741: sgyu ma lta bu'i mnyam bzhag nyams 'og tu chud
NK116(le)001:6743: rjes thob sgyu ma mkhan bzhin du sprul ba'i bya
NK116(le)001:6744: ba ci 'dod du byed cing dbang 'byor bas sgyu
NK116(le)001:6745: ma lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK116(le)001:6746: dpa' bo g.yul du 'jug pa na dpung tshogs yan lag bzhi dang /
NK116(le)001:6747: 'khor los bsgyur rgyal 'gro na rin chen sna bdun yang 'gro ba bzhin du /
NK116(le)001:6748: byang chub phyogs kyi chos thams cad ting nge 'dzin
NK116(le)001:6749: de'i rjes su 'brang bas na dpa' bar 'gro ba'i
NK116(le)001:6751: rdo rjes dngos po thams cad 'joms pa bzhin du /
NK116(le)001:6752: ting nge 'dzin gang gis phra rgyas thams cad 'joms
NK116(le)001:6753: pas rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin zhes bya'o
NK116(le)001:6754: // de yang ma dag sa bdun na dang po dang /
NK116(le)001:6755: dag pa gsum na gnyis pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6756: rgyun matha'i sa na gsum pa'o /
NK116(le)001:6757: sbyor ba'i lam du de dag bslab tshul yod kyang /
NK116(le)001:6758: dang po dang gnyis pa ni mos pas spyod pa tsam dang /
NK116(le)001:6759: phyi ma ni sgrib pa bshig pa'i cha nas brjod do //
NK116(le)001:6760: bar chad med pa'i lam gyis bsdus pa'i rdo rje
NK116(le)001:6761: lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin ni rgyun matha'i ye shes
NK116(le)001:6762: nyid kyi skad cig phyi ma la mi slob lam
NK116(le)001:6763: 'byung ba'i phyir ro phar phyin lnga ka'i 'bras bu
NK116(le)001:6764: shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin pa slob pa
NK116(le)001:6765: la rkyen gyi cha nas lhag pa zhes bya ba
NK116(le)001:6767: lhag pa shesa raba kyi bslab pa'i ngesa 'byeda ni /
NK116(le)001:6768: gong du bstan pa'i ting nge 'dzina /
NK116(le)001:6769: de dag kun gyi sbyor pa lasa skyes shing /
NK116(le)001:6770: dngosa bstan dang rjesa dpag lasa byung ba'i shesa raba bam /
NK116(le)001:6773: bsgoma pa lasa byung ba'i shesa raba ste /
NK116(le)001:6774: rnam pa gsuma gyis lhag mthonga yang dag par 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:6775: byed las ni nyon mongs zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:6776: shes rab kyi bslab pa la yon tan ci yod ce na /
NK116(le)001:6777: nyon mongas pa'i tshogas mtha' dag 'joma pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6778: rgyu 'bras bslu ba med pa la nges pa rnyed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6779: chosa dang chosa cana te yul sems kyi gnas tshul ji bzhin par shesa pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6780: ston pa dang bstan pa'i yon tan la snying thag pa nas nges shes skye ba dang /
NK116(le)001:6781: yon tan mtha' dag dge ba'i bshes gnyen la rags las pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6782: drang nges kyi rnam par bzhag pa blo gros phyogs
NK116(le)001:6783: re ba can la 'gal ba rnams shes rab kyi
NK116(le)001:6784: klong shong che bas mi mthun pa med pa srida
NK116(le)001:6785: pa'i grong lasa mya ngana meda para 'ad'a bar byed
NK116(le)001:6786: pa yin no // sbyin sogas pha rol tu byina
NK116(le)001:6787: pa rnam pa druga po'ang rim par gonga nas gonga
NK116(le)001:6788: du khyad par zhugas shing shesa raba kyi pha rola
NK116(le)001:6789: tu phyin pas lhag ma lnga la khyab cing khyab
NK116(le)001:6790: bya de dag kyang 'di la brten pa ni /
NK116(le)001:6792: pha rol phyin lnga byang chub yon tan ji snyed pa /
NK116(le)001:6793: de dag kun kyang shes rab pha rol phyin la brten /
NK116(le)001:6795: mthong dang ma mthong yod tan 'di //
NK116(le)001:6796: kun gyi rtsa ba shes rab yin //
NK116(le)001:6797: de ltar gnyis ka bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK116(le)001:6798: shes rab yongs su bzung bar bya /
NK116(le)001:6799: zhes dang slob dpon dpa' bos /
NK116(le)001:6800: sbyin la sogs pa'i bsod nams 'di dag ni //
NK116(le)001:6801: shes rab mgon bcas lhag par mthu ldan 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:6803: de bas na thog mar thos pa'i yon tan la
NK116(le)001:6804: brten dgos pa'i tshul de 'ang zhes bya ba la
NK116(le)001:6806: de'ang 'di na so so'i skye bo'i sa la gnas
NK116(le)001:6807: para thosa pa lasa byung ba'i shesa raba nan tan
NK116(le)001:6808: ma bsten na / bsam pa dang bsgoma pa'i yona
NK116(le)001:6809: tan cung zad kyang mi skye bas na gansa mina
NK116(le)001:6810: par 'khyamsa pa ste des na thosa pa'i shesa rab
NK116(le)001:6811: ni sa lam gyi yon tan ji snyed kuna gyi
NK116(le)001:6812: rgyu ru thams cad mkhyen pas gsungas so //
NK116(le)001:6813: de skad du slob dpon dpa' bos thos nyung dmus long bsgom pa'i tshul mi shes /
NK116(le)001:6814: de med de kos ci zhig bsam par bya /
NK116(le)001:6815: de bas thos la brtson bya de rgyu la /
NK116(le)001:6816: bsam bzhin bsgom pa'i shes rab yangs ba 'byung /
NK116(le)001:6819: shes rab mchog yin de'i gzhi ni /
NK116(le)001:6820: thos pa de phyir thos pa mchog /
NK116(le)001:6823: bzod bya thos pa btsal bar bya /
NK116(le)001:6824: de nas nags su gnas par bya //
NK116(le)001:6825: mnyam par bzhag la brtson bya zhing /
NK116(le)001:6827: gang thos par bya na lung dang rtogs pa'i chos gnyis te //
NK116(le)001:6828: de yang gzhal bya 'jal byed kyis gtan la phab
NK116(le)001:6829: tshul gzhal bya'i zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan
NK116(le)001:6830: te / gazhala bya'i chosa gsung rab yan lag bcu
NK116(le)001:6831: gnyis dang des bstan bya lam lnga'i yon tan ci
NK116(le)001:6832: rigs pa la 'ajala byed shesa raba gsum gyis /
NK116(le)001:6833: dranga ngesa gnyis dang ldema dgongas rnam pa bzhira gazhala ba yin no //
NK116(le)001:6834: de yang chosa rnama kuna gyi ngo bo ni de bzhina nyid ces /
NK116(le)001:6835: rnam par thara ba'i sgo stong pa nyid dang /
NK116(le)001:6837: smon pa med pa gsuma du gansa pa ni ngesa
NK116(le)001:6838: pa'i dona yina la chosa cana kun rdzob snang tshoda
NK116(le)001:6839: tsam gyi lam la 'juga pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:6840: rnam par riga pasa gzhal nas chos thams cad yod
NK116(le)001:6841: pa nyid de 'di dang 'adi'o zhes sgro btagsa pa
NK116(le)001:6842: gang zhig dranga pa'i lam yin no //
NK116(le)001:6843: de ltar gnyis posa drangsa ngesa ganga la yid rton mi rton /
NK116(le)001:6844: 'di ltar don la rton gyis tshig 'bru la mi rton pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6845: ye shes la rton gyis rnam par shes pa la mi rton pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6846: nges pa'i don gyi mdo sde la rton gyis drang ba'i don gyi mdo sde mi rton pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6847: chos nyid la rton gyis gang zag la mi rton pa'o //
NK116(le)001:6848: tshul de dag shesa pa'i phyir na de ni gsunga raba la blta ba'i lde miga yina no //
NK116(le)001:6849: rjod byed de daga gi ranga bzhina gasla para byasa pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6850: brjod bya nges pa'i dona gyi dgongsa pa rtogsa para
NK116(le)001:6851: bya ba'i phyir dgongas dang ldem po gnyis su bashada
NK116(le)001:6852: pa las / dang po dgongsa pa can la ni
NK116(le)001:6853: bstan bshad gnyis las dang po cung zad ces bya
NK116(le)001:6854: ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:6855: ched du bya ba gang zhig dmigs yul du bcags
NK116(le)001:6856: nas sgra ci bzhin du ma yin par cung zada
NK116(le)001:6857: sgro btagsa te bashada du yanga yoda la /
NK116(le)001:6858: de yang gdula bar bya ba'i yul rnams re zhiga kha drang ba /
NK116(le)001:6859: gciga pu'i slad du'ang ma yina par dgosa cheda khyad
NK116(le)001:6860: par ba dang bacasa nas dgongas pa rnam bzhira ston
NK116(le)001:6861: pa ste / gnyis pa so so bshad pa ni /
NK116(le)001:6862: mnyam pa zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:6863: dang po mnyam pa nyid dgongas 'agla ba'ang gciga tu bstan pa ni /
NK116(le)001:6864: tshu rol mthong pa can gyi snang ngor 'khor 'das
NK116(le)001:6865: dang bzang ngan dang blang dor gyi mtshan nyid shin
NK116(le)001:6866: tu 'gal bar gnas pa de yang chos thams cad
NK116(le)001:6867: kyi gnas lugs rang bzhin gyis rnam par byang pa'i
NK116(le)001:6868: bar du gcig dang tha dad med par mnyam pa
NK116(le)001:6869: nyid de / 'phags tshul brgya lnga bcu pa las //
NK116(le)001:6870: thams cad nam mkha'i mtshan nyid de //
NK116(le)001:6871: nam mkha' la yang mtshan nyid med //
NK116(le)001:6872: nam mkha'i mtshan nyid sbyor basa na //
NK116(le)001:6873: kun mchog mnyam nyid rdzogs pa'o //
NK116(le)001:6875: gnyis pa dona gazhana la dgongas pa ni gzugs nas
NK116(le)001:6876: rnam mkhyen gyi bar gyi chos thams cad 'khrul ngor
NK116(le)001:6877: yod pa ltar snang yang dpyad na ma gruba par
NK116(le)001:6879: rmi lam ni snang la yod pa ma yin no //
NK116(le)001:6880: de bzhin tu chos thams cad snang la yod pa ma yin no //
NK116(le)001:6882: gsum pa dusa gazhana la dgongas pa ni sangs rgyas
NK116(le)001:6883: kyi mtshan nam gzungs lta bu zhig thos pas sangs
NK116(le)001:6884: rgya bar 'gyur ba gsungs pa ni sbyong pa sngon
NK116(le)001:6885: song gi gang zag gam min kyang dge ba'i sa
NK116(le)001:6886: bon bzhag nas nam zhig stobs su gyur dus 'bad
NK116(le)001:6887: meda 'atshanga rgya bar bstan pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6888: bzhi pa ganga zaga la dgongas pa de de'i mchoga 'dzina nam /
NK116(le)001:6889: dge ba gang la brtul zhugs byed na 'di las
NK116(le)001:6890: gzhan lhag pa med par snyams pa lam gyi sgrib
NK116(le)001:6891: byed du 'gyur ba'i phyir de la smada de gzhan
NK116(le)001:6892: zhig basngagasa pa'o // gnyis pa la yang bstan bshad
NK116(le)001:6893: gnyis kyi dang po ni ldem por zhes bya ba
NK116(le)001:6895: ldema pora dgongsa pa zhes bya ba ni gdula bya ganga zhiga gi /
NK116(le)001:6896: blo la zab mo'i don ji lta bar mi chud de yida gnyis kyi gansa thoba pa rnams la /
NK116(le)001:6897: re zhig de nyid dag'a ba'i minga dang cha ldana gyis /
NK116(le)001:6898: ji bzhin min par rnama para kyogsa nas bshad kyang
NK116(le)001:6899: dgongs pa'i phugs su yang dag pa'i lam la gzunga
NK116(le)001:6900: phyir / tshiga mthuna dona mi mthuna para bashada pa ste /
NK116(le)001:6901: gnyis pa so sor bshad pa ni dbye na zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:6905: bsgyur ba ldem por dgongs pa ste /
NK116(le)001:6906: dang po zhugsa pa ldem dgongas ganga zhig nyan thosa dang /
NK116(le)001:6907: stong pa nyid gsungs pasa yid skrag nasa thega chena mtshan nyid med pa'i chos spangs pa la /
NK116(le)001:6908: gzugsa sogs yoda par smros pasa rang mtshan du gruba para go nasa de ma thag 'juga la /
NK116(le)001:6909: rgyal bas tshur rol snang tshoda rmi lam lta bura dgongas nas gsungs pa'o //
NK116(le)001:6910: gnyis pa matshana nyid ldem dgongas ni ngo bo nyid
NK116(le)001:6911: meda pa'i dona shes pa'i dona du rima bzhina kuna
NK116(le)001:6912: brtagsa dang / gazhana dabnga dang yongsa gruba rnama pa gsuma daga bstan pa lasa /
NK116(le)001:6913: dang po kun brtags rang gi matshana nyid kyis stong ste ngo bo nyid med pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6914: gnyis pa gzhan dbang skye basa stong ste ngo bo nyid meda pa dang /
NK116(le)001:6915: gsuma pa yongs grub dona dama pas stong ste ngo bo nyid meda pasa /
NK116(le)001:6916: chos rnamas thams cad gang du'ang mi gnas pas na
NK116(le)001:6917: brjod para bya ba'i don chos zab pa daga tu
NK116(le)001:6918: ston pa'o // gsum pa gnyen po ldema dgongas ni
NK116(le)001:6919: gazhana gyis de bzhin gshegs pa 'di ni rgyal ba
NK116(le)001:6920: gzhan las sku tshe thung zhing 'od kyang chung la
NK116(le)001:6921: ston pa'o // / 'khor yang nyung ngo snyam pa'i
NK116(le)001:6922: log rtog ldog pa'i thabs su dgongs nas rnam snang
NK116(le)001:6923: gangs chen mtsho'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las
NK116(le)001:6924: mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i sprul gzhi bdag
NK116(le)001:6925: nyid yin pa zhal gyis bzhes pa lta bu ste
NK116(le)001:6926: ston pa'o // / / sku tshe ring thung dang
NK116(le)001:6927: rigas mchog dman dang sku bongas che chung tshad kyis
NK116(le)001:6929: sangsa rgyas thams cad kyi spangs rtogs la bzang ngan
NK116(le)001:6930: med pa'i phyir gzugas kyi sku gdul bya'i snang ngor
NK116(le)001:6932: don du chosa sku dang ro gcig par mnyam pa ste /
NK116(le)001:6933: tshogas bsags kyi yula la'ang bzang ngan med par mnyam pasa na don de lta bura dgongas pa'o //
NK116(le)001:6934: bzhi pa bsgyur ba ldema dgongas ni basda bya ma yina pa'i /
NK116(le)001:6936: de bzhina du bcoma bya mina pa /
NK116(le)001:6937: rgyal po dang ni gatsanga sbra can gnyis bcoma par gsungs pa 'di ltar ste /
NK116(le)001:6940: de gnyis las rlung dbu mar bcings pa'i tshe rnam
NK116(le)001:6941: par dag pa la gsod pa'i sgrar zhugs pa dang
NK116(le)001:6943: de bzhin du bram ze ni 'jig tshogs la blta ba dang /
NK116(le)001:6944: dge sbyongs tshul khrims dang brtul zhugs la mchog 'dzin gyi lta ba'i gtsang sbra can gnyis yin la /
NK116(le)001:6945: nang gi skyed mched rnam shes tshogs brgyad sogas ni yul 'khor bcas te /
NK116(le)001:6946: de dag rang bzhin gyis dag pa la bcom pa'i
NK116(le)001:6947: tha snyad tsam las btagsa pa'i dona ji bzhin du
NK116(le)001:6948: rnal mara bzunga na nora ba chena po'o //
NK116(le)001:6949: skabs kyis don bsdu ba ni mdor na zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:6950: mdora na dgongas pa can dang ldem pora dgongs pa'i khyad para ni /
NK116(le)001:6951: dgongas pa ni ched du bya ba'i don de nyid
NK116(le)001:6952: yida yul la rnam para bazhaga pa tsam yina gyis
NK116(le)001:6953: pha rola po mngon sum par rjes su bzunga pa
NK116(le)001:6955: ldema pora dgongas pa pha rola gang zhig rjes su
NK116(le)001:6956: bzunga ba la ltos pa'i bye brag sogs rnam par
NK116(le)001:6957: 'byed pa ni gsunga raba kun la blta ba'i miga
NK116(le)001:6958: dang mtshungs so // gzhal bya dam pa'i chos kyi
NK116(le)001:6959: rnam grangs gzhal bya'i zhes bya ba la sogs pas
NK116(le)001:6960: dang mtshungs so // bstan te / gazhala bya'i ngosa
NK116(le)001:6961: nasa rgyal basa chosa kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi
NK116(le)001:6962: stong gsungas pa matha'a daga gi dona gcig tu bsdus
NK116(le)001:6963: dang mtshungs so // bstan te / na / 'jiga rten kuna rdzoba pa dang dona dama pa ste /
NK116(le)001:6964: bdena pa gnyis lasa gsuma pa ma mchisa so zhes rnam grangs gzhan med do //
NK116(le)001:6965: yab sras mjal ba'i mdo las /
NK116(le)001:6966: 'jig rten mkhas pas bden pa 'di gnyis te /
NK116(le)001:6967: khyed kyis gzhan las ma gsan rang gi gzigs //
NK116(le)001:6968: de ni kun rdzob bden dang don dam ste /
NK116(le)001:6969: bden pa gsum pa gang yang ma mchis so //
NK116(le)001:6971: dang po'i dbye ba ni kun rdzob zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:6972: 'di ltar 'dus byas kuna rdzoba pa'i chos la snang lugas rnam pa gnyis te /
NK116(le)001:6973: spyir 'khor ba'i rang bzhin glo bur gyi sgrib pas 'khrul ba pa yin gyi /
NK116(le)001:6974: de'i shesa ngo la snang ba'i bye brag ji snyed
NK116(le)001:6975: kyi rnam bzhag mchis pa las mngon sum par snang
NK116(le)001:6976: tshoda ji lta ba nyid dang mthuna para dona byed
NK116(le)001:6977: pa ste nyi ma dang mar mes mun pa sel
NK116(le)001:6978: ba sogs rnams / yang dag pa'i kuna rdzoba nyid
NK116(le)001:6979: de gzhan mig btsir bas mar me gnyis snang ba'i
NK116(le)001:6980: ba sogs rnams / cig shos dang / chu la
NK116(le)001:6981: nyi zla'i snang brnyan shar ba lta bu ni snang
NK116(le)001:6982: na'ang dona mi byed pa la loga pa'i kuna rdzoba
NK116(le)001:6983: ba sogs rnams / cig shos dang / tu gragas so // de yang bden gnyis las //
NK116(le)001:6984: snang du 'dra rung don byed gang /
NK116(le)001:6985: nus pa'i phyir dang mi nus phyir //
NK116(le)001:6986: yang dag yang dag ma yin pa'i //
NK116(le)001:6987: kun rdzob kyi ni dbye bar bya //
NK116(le)001:6989: 'di gnyis tshig tu so sor snang yang gshis nas brtags na tha dad mi mngon te /
NK116(le)001:6990: gnyis ka bden med glo bur ba yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:6991: de bas na bden par zhen pa'i chos thams cad log pa'i kun rdzob dang //
NK116(le)001:6992: bden zhen med par snang ba thams cad yang dag kun rdzob ste /
NK116(le)001:6994: me long dkyil 'khor yongs dag la //
NK116(le)001:6995: bzhin gyi zla ba snang ba ltar //
NK116(le)001:6996: ji ltar rang bzhin ma grub par //
NK116(le)001:6997: ljon pas chos rnams shes par gyis /
NK116(le)001:6999: gnyis pa ni don dam zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:7000: dona dama pa'i bdena pa zhes bya ba ni rang gi gshisa sems nyid kyi bzhugas tshula te /
NK116(le)001:7001: 'khora ba dang ni mya ngana las 'adsa pa'i chosa
NK116(le)001:7002: thams cad ngo bo nyid meda par gdoda nasa bsam
NK116(le)001:7004: rtogsa ces bya ba dang ma rtogsa ces byas pa blo yisa rnam par ma bazhaga go /
NK116(le)001:7006: gzhan las shes min zhi ba dang //
NK116(le)001:7007: spros pa rnams kyis ma spros pa //
NK116(le)001:7008: rnam par rtog med tha dad med //
NK116(le)001:7009: de ni de yi mtshan nyid do //
NK116(le)001:7011: bde pa gnyis po de ye nas dbyer med du 'dresa pa'i snang stong zung 'juga ni //
NK116(le)001:7012: ji ltar rdzinga bura zhugas pa'i zla ba'i gzugs kyi skye mcheda bzhina du /
NK116(le)001:7013: snang ba'i cha nasa kuna rdzoba bdena pa dang /
NK116(le)001:7014: ranga bzhina ma gruba pa'i cha nas dona dam bdena pa'o //
NK116(le)001:7015: de lta na'ang re zhig 'khrul ba'i blor dpags na
NK116(le)001:7016: yul lnga'i zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te
NK116(le)001:7017: / de yang mig sogs yula lnga'i shes pa tshona risa ma 'dresa pa lta bus /
NK116(le)001:7018: gzugas sogas 'doda pa'i longas spyod kyi cha bzung ba /
NK116(le)001:7019: de la dera 'dzina gyis dagga sgrub blo rtog gi
NK116(le)001:7020: 'khrul ba'i snang ba bden med sgyu ma la sogs
NK116(le)001:7021: pa'i dpe brgyad nyid du brtag dgos so //
NK116(le)001:7022: 'bras dus la ltos nas mthar thug zhes bya ba
NK116(le)001:7023: la sogs pa gsungs te gal te mathara thuga pa'i
NK116(le)001:7024: chos nyid blo yisa rnama para dpyad bzoda par gyur
NK116(le)001:7025: na / don dama ma yina par thal te blo ni kuna rdzob yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7026: de bas na gciga dang du mara dmigs pa'i yul
NK116(le)001:7027: las 'agla ba'i phyogs chos kyi dbyings kyi matshana nyid
NK116(le)001:7028: rnams / blo yi spyod yula la nama yanga gansa ma myong ba ste /
NK116(le)001:7030: don dam blo yi spyod yul min //
NK116(le)001:7031: blo ni kun rdzob yin par 'dod //
NK116(le)001:7033: 'dir re zhiga grub pa'i matha'a yi rnam par bazhaga pa ni /
NK116(le)001:7034: dbye na thog mar nyan thos bye mdo gnyis kyi
NK116(le)001:7035: 'dod tshul shes pa'i zhes bya ba la sogs pas
NK116(le)001:7036: bstan te / 'di la rtsa bshad dang /
NK116(le)001:7037: mtha' dpyad gnyis las dang po ni /
NK116(le)001:7038: shesa pa'i dona dama blo yisa dpyad pa'i dus kyi
NK116(le)001:7039: thung ngu'i mthar thug pa skad cig cha med dang
NK116(le)001:7040: / dngosa po'i dona dama pa tho bas bcoma pa
NK116(le)001:7041: yi rdzas kyi chung mtha' mthar thug pa rdula phrana
NK116(le)001:7042: cha meda du 'dod pa gang zhig nyan thosa bye
NK116(le)001:7043: brag sde pa spyi'i lugas yin la /
NK116(le)001:7044: dona byed nus pa ganga yina pa de /
NK116(le)001:7045: 'dira ni dona dama yoda pa yina la gazhana ni kuna rdzob yoda pa yin te /
NK116(le)001:7046: de la yang ranga mtshan dang spyi'i matshana nyid kyisa
NK116(le)001:7047: bashada pa gang zhig mdo sde ba'i lugas ngo bo
NK116(le)001:7050: bye mdo thun mong gi 'dod tshul cung zad spros te bshad pa dang /
NK116(le)001:7051: so so'i rger 'dod cher bsdus te bshad pa gnyis kyi dang po la gnyis te /
NK116(le)001:7053: rig pas dgag pa gnyis pos dang po la bdun te /
NK116(le)001:7067: bden pa dag ni bzhi bshad de //
NK116(le)001:7068: sdug bsngal kun 'byung de bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:7069: 'gog pa lam ste de ltar na //
NK116(le)001:7070: de dag ji ltar mngon rtogs rim /
NK116(le)001:7073: gong du bshad pa ltar shes dngos kyi don dam gnyis gzhig bcom mi rung ba ste /
NK116(le)001:7075: gang la bcom dang blo yis gzhal //
NK116(le)001:7076: bsal na de blo mi 'jug la //
NK116(le)001:7077: bum pa'i chu bzhin kun rdzob par //
NK116(le)001:7078: med de don dam yod gzhan no //
NK116(le)001:7081: mthong spang sgom spang gi phra rgyas spangs pas lhag bcas lhag med kyi mya ngan 'das 'thob pa'o //
NK116(le)001:7083: mig sogs dbang po lnga dang yid kyi rnamashesa las kun gzhi dang /
NK116(le)001:7084: de'i rnam shes sogs kyi rnam grangs mi 'dod do //
NK116(le)001:7086: 'dul ba lung sde bzhi so thar dang bcas pa dang /
NK116(le)001:7087: mdo sde gcig las 'phros pa sogs las sher phyin
NK116(le)001:7088: stong phrag brgya ba sogs theg chen gyi mdo sde
NK116(le)001:7089: rnams sangs rgyas mya ngan las 'das zin nas bdud
NK116(le)001:7090: dang mu stegs kyi bstan pa la tha brtsams pa'i
NK116(le)001:7091: ched du byas pa ste phyag rgya bzhi dang 'gal
NK116(le)001:7092: ba la sogs 'gal 'du mang ba'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7094: so so skye bo sa las grangs med gsum du
NK116(le)001:7095: tshogs bsags nas nub gcig gi stan thog tu nges
NK116(le)001:7096: 'byed cha bzhi yan chad mngon du byas nas mi
NK116(le)001:7097: skye shes pa dang zag pa zad pa las sa
NK116(le)001:7098: bcu la sogs pa'i rnam grangs rim gyis bgrod par
NK116(le)001:7100: sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku ma yin te /
NK116(le)001:7101: lhas byin gyis rgyogs 'phags pas zhabs snad pa dang /
NK116(le)001:7102: sku la khrag zag pa dang /
NK116(le)001:7103: sku rgyab bsnyungs pa la sogs pa rnam smin gyi lhag ma dang bcas la /
NK116(le)001:7104: ting nge 'dzin de las bzhengs te bsod snyoms la
NK116(le)001:7105: gshegs so zhe sa rtag tu mnyam par bzhag pa
NK116(le)001:7107: mya ngan las 'das nas 'gro don rgyun chad par 'dod pa'o //
NK116(le)001:7108: gnyis pa go rim ltar dgag pa las /
NK116(le)001:7111: 'di ltar snang ba thams cad med pa la yod
NK116(le)001:7112: par sgro btags pa'i snang ba rten cing 'brel 'byung
NK116(le)001:7116: sdug bsngal yod pa ga la 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:7117: mi rtag sdug bsngal gsungs pa de //
NK116(le)001:7118: rang bzhin nyid la yod ma yin /
NK116(le)001:7121: dper na srog gcod lta bur mtshon pa /
NK116(le)001:7122: gsad bya'i dngos po'i dus sum du phye la /
NK116(le)001:7124: skad cig snga phyi'i dbye bas /
NK116(le)001:7125: gsod pa'i dus 'gags pas dngos por ma grub pa nyid do //
NK116(le)001:7127: dper na thams cad rmi lam gyi rta glang dang mtshungs te /
NK116(le)001:7129: rang bzhin las ni yod min na //
NK116(le)001:7131: de phyir stong nyid gnod byed la //
NK116(le)001:7132: kun 'byung yod pa ma yin no //
NK116(le)001:7135: snga ma gnyis khegs pas 'di yang khegs te /
NK116(le)001:7136: dgag gzhi ma grub na 'gog ci la dgos te /
NK116(le)001:7137: nad med na sman mi za ba bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:7139: sdug bsngal rang bzhin gyis yod la //
NK116(le)001:7143: nyon mongs dang gnyen po gnyis dus mnyam par bsgom mam tha dad par bsgom /
NK116(le)001:7144: mnyam na rgyud gcig la spangs gnyen rdzas 'gal la //
NK116(le)001:7145: tha dad na bsal bya bsal byed ji ltar rung ste //
NK116(le)001:7146: na ning gi nad la da lo'i sman bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:7148: gang tshe mar me skye bzhin pa //
NK116(le)001:7149: mun pa dang ni 'phrad pa med //
NK116(le)001:7150: ji ltar mar me skyes bzhin pas //
NK116(le)001:7151: mun pa sel bar byed ma yin //
NK116(le)001:7152: mar mer 'phrad pa med par yang //
NK116(le)001:7153: gal te mun pa sel byed na //
NK116(le)001:7154: 'jig rten kun na gnas pa'i mun /
NK116(le)001:7157: lam dang de'i spang bya dang skad cig snga phyi phrad pa med pas ma grub pa yin no //
NK116(le)001:7158: 'gog pa mngon du byed pa mi rung ste //
NK116(le)001:7159: 'gog pa nyid bkag pas mngon du byed pa khog pa nyid do //
NK116(le)001:7160: dgag pa 'das na 'gog pa'i rgyu med la /
NK116(le)001:7161: ma 'gag na mi khegs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:7162: de gnyis dus mnyam na ngo bo tha dad du mi rung /
NK116(le)001:7163: mi mnyam na dgag bya dang 'gog byed du mi rung ba'i phyir de ma grub pa kho na'o //
NK116(le)001:7164: gnyis pa rtsom byed don dam dgag pa la gnyis te /
NK116(le)001:7168: rdul de dag la brtag pa lnga las /
NK116(le)001:7169: 'phrad ma 'phrad rags pa rtsom na rdul rnams mu stegs bye brag pas phrad par 'dod /
NK116(le)001:7170: nyan thos bye brag pa bar dang bcas par 'dod /
NK116(le)001:7171: mdo sde ba ma 'byar la bar med par 'dod do //
NK116(le)001:7172: de yang 'phrad na dbus kyi rdul de phyogs drug gi rdul dang phrad pa'i tshe /
NK116(le)001:7173: ngos cha drug gis 'phrad par 'dod dam /
NK116(le)001:7174: shar sogs phyogs gang rung gcig gis 'phrad par 'dod /
NK116(le)001:7175: dang po ltar na rdul de cha drug tu thal te ngo drug yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7176: phyi ma ltar na phyogs thams cad shar sogs gang rung gcig tu thal ba'i skyon yod do //
NK116(le)001:7178: bar na snang mun rdul gyis chod dam ma chod dang po ltar na /
NK116(le)001:7179: snang mun gyi rdul dang 'byar ram ma 'byar /
NK116(le)001:7180: 'byar na yang snga ma bzhin skyon mi khegs la /
NK116(le)001:7181: ma 'byar na yang 'chad 'gyur gyi skyon yod do /
NK116(le)001:7182: ma chod na yang dag la 'thad de /
NK116(le)001:7183: gzugs can gyi bar la skya tha le ba'am nag
NK116(le)001:7184: thibs se ba gcig las mi srid pa'i phyir ro
NK116(le)001:7185: // gal te thug med du ma 'byar zhe na /
NK116(le)001:7186: rdul phran du ma 'tshogs pa'i phung por snang ba'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:7187: yungs 'bru gcig gi nang du blang po che sogs shong bar thal te /
NK116(le)001:7188: bar thugs med kyi phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7189: der ma zad de ma 'byar na ha cang rig pas gnod de mda' yis 'ben 'bigs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:7190: thog gis brag gzhom pa dang /
NK116(le)001:7191: lnga la sgra 'byung ba yang rgyun chad par thal lo //
NK116(le)001:7192: de yang nyi shu pa las /
NK116(le)001:7193: drug gi cha ni sbyar ba na /
NK116(le)001:7194: drug po dag ni go gcig par /
NK116(le)001:7195: gong bu yang rdul phran tsam du 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:7198: phyogsa bcu'i dbye ba phye ba yis /
NK116(le)001:7199: rdul phran la yang dbye ba mthong //
NK116(le)001:7200: gang la cha shas kyis brtags pa /
NK116(le)001:7201: de la rdul phran ji ltar 'dod /
NK116(le)001:7203: gnyis pa bltas ma bltas kyis brtags pa ni /
NK116(le)001:7204: dbus rdul gyi phyogs drug gi ngos la skyes bu'i
NK116(le)001:7205: bltas na cha drug tu 'gyur la 'khor yang shar
NK116(le)001:7206: la sogs pa gang rung gcig tu bltas na de
NK116(le)001:7207: kho na rgyu 'di ltar ri la sogs pa'i phyogs
NK116(le)001:7208: bcu'i snang yul thams cad yod par thal lo //
NK116(le)001:7210: dbus na rdul phran rdul gcig la /
NK116(le)001:7211: bltas pa'i rang bzhin gang yin pa //
NK116(le)001:7212: rdul phran gzhan la lta ba yang //
NK116(le)001:7213: de nyid gal te yin brjod na //
NK116(le)001:7214: de ltar yin na sa chu sogs //
NK116(le)001:7215: ji ltar rgyas 'gyur ma yin no //
NK116(le)001:7216: rdul phran gzhan la blta ba'i ngos /
NK116(le)001:7217: gal te shar nyid yin brjod na //
NK116(le)001:7218: rab tu phra rdul ji lta bu //
NK116(le)001:7219: gcig pu cha shas med par 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:7221: gsum pa nyi 'od phog min gyis brtags pa ni /
NK116(le)001:7222: ji ltar snga gro nyi ma shar ba'i tshe /
NK116(le)001:7223: rdul ril po nyi ma logs su yod na gcig
NK116(le)001:7224: gis gcig shos la mi sgrib par shel sgong bzhin
NK116(le)001:7225: nam / gal te grib ma yin na nyin par
NK116(le)001:7226: mun nag tu thal te nyi ma'i 'od ma phog
NK116(le)001:7227: nam / pa'i phyir ro // gal te nyi ma'i
NK116(le)001:7228: phyogs snang ba dang gcig shos grib mar 'dod na
NK116(le)001:7229: yang cha med pa'i dam bca' zhig ste shar nub
NK116(le)001:7230: kyi cha gnyis yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7231: bzhi pa 'pho ba'i brtags pa ni /
NK116(le)001:7232: mda' 'phangs pa dang nyi grib mtshams khang dmig du
NK116(le)001:7233: nur ba'i rdul dag lam gyi rdul dang kha bsnol
NK116(le)001:7234: ba'i yun ring thung yod dam med /
NK116(le)001:7235: med na mda' dang khang dmig gi grib ma mgyogs bu la mnyam par thal /
NK116(le)001:7236: dus ring thung yod na khang dmig gi grib ma
NK116(le)001:7237: dang lam gyi rdul gcig 'grogs pa'i bar du mdas
NK116(le)001:7238: rdul stong chod par thal lo /
NK116(le)001:7239: 'dod na mad'i rdul gyis lam gyi rdul phran stong
NK116(le)001:7240: gcod pa'i bar du grib ma'i rdul go stong 'pho
NK116(le)001:7241: ba thal / 'dod na de'i bar la dus cha stong grub par thal lo //
NK116(le)001:7242: 'dis ni skad cig cha med kyang nges par khegs te /
NK116(le)001:7243: grib ma gnas pa'i skad cig la mda' 'phos pa'i dus cha stong grub pas so //
NK116(le)001:7244: 'pho ba snga phyi byas pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:7245: skad cig dus cha du mar 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:7246: nur ba 'dor len byed pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:7247: rdul phran cha ni du mar 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:7249: lnga ba ring thung gi brtags pa ni /
NK116(le)001:7250: rdul gnyis gshib pa'i srub non du rdul gcig bzhag dus /
NK116(le)001:7251: zhabs kyi gnyis po dang steng gcig po la ring thung yod dam med /
NK116(le)001:7252: med na rdul gcig gi gor gcig thim par thal te /
NK116(le)001:7253: gcig las ma 'phel ba'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7254: yod na gsum ka cha gnyis gnyis su thal te /
NK116(le)001:7255: steng ma ni gcig pos 'og ma gnyis kyi phyed non pas so //
NK116(le)001:7256: gnyis pa dus can dgag pa la //
NK116(le)001:7257: 'di ltar yul shes pa la sogs pa'i dus skad cig du ma mthud nas rgyun brtsam pa na /
NK116(le)001:7258: skad cig snga phyi phrad dam ma 'phrad /
NK116(le)001:7259: ma 'phrad na khyod kyi lus sems so sor thal te shes pa snga ma 'gags la /
NK116(le)001:7260: phyi ma ma skyed kyi bar shes pa 'gal yang med pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7261: shes pa phyi ma rgyud med du thal te chad pa las skye ba'i phyir ro /
NK116(le)001:7262: gal te 'phrad nas ra ha brjod dus /
NK116(le)001:7263: ra de yi ge snga phyi gnyis dang dus gcig 'phrad dam res mos su phrad /
NK116(le)001:7265: dus gsum gyi dngos po thams cad ma nyams pas
NK116(le)001:7266: na skad cig kho na las mi srid par thal
NK116(le)001:7267: la / res mos su 'phrad na ra'i skad cig de nyid cha gnyis su thal te /
NK116(le)001:7268: snga phyi gnyis dang 'phrad pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7269: 'dod na skad cig cha med nyams so //
NK116(le)001:7270: snga phyi gnyis kyis phrad pa na /
NK116(le)001:7271: skad cig dus cha gnyis su 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:7272: gnyis po dag ni dus mnyam na //
NK116(le)001:7273: bskal pa skad cig gcig tu 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:7275: dgra bcom mthar thug dgag pa la gsum ste /
NK116(le)001:7280: tshogs mi gsog ste khams gsum du skye ba mi len no //
NK116(le)001:7281: rgyu mthong sgom gyi spang bya phra rgyas spang ba'i phyir ro //
