NK116(le)001:7283: sangs rgyas ma thob na phra rgyas gtan spang dang zhi ba las mi ldog mi srid /
NK116(le)001:7285: de na sangs rgyas ma thob par //
NK116(le)001:7286: mya ngan 'das pa thob mi srid //
NK116(le)001:7288: nyi ma blta bar mi nus bzhin //
NK116(le)001:7291: sgrib pa glo bur ba yin pas sbyang rung du
NK116(le)001:7292: mtshungs pas de sbyongs na nyan thos kyang sangs rgyas
NK116(le)001:7293: su mi 'gyur ba med pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7295: re zhig dbang po dman pa rnams 'khor ba las ldog pa las mthar thug 'phags pa min te /
NK116(le)001:7296: 'gog pa'i dbyings su bskal pa stong phrag bcur gnas pa las /
NK116(le)001:7297: bskul nas dag pa'i zhing du pad+ma las skyes te /
NK116(le)001:7298: bzod byang chub tu thugs bskyed de sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang 'thob par 'gyur ba'o //
NK116(le)001:7299: kun gzhi med par dgag pa la yang gsum te 'khor bar 'jug pa /
NK116(le)001:7301: chad nas 'byung ba mi rung ba ste /
NK116(le)001:7303: rgyun chags pa'i kun gzhi med na mngal gyi gnas
NK116(le)001:7304: skabs mer mer po la sogs pa'i dus su tshogs
NK116(le)001:7305: drug med pa'i phyir ro 'khor bar lus len par
NK116(le)001:7306: mi rigs so / gnyis pa ni /
NK116(le)001:7307: shes pa rdzas gcig gi steng du spang bya spong byed gnyis med pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:7308: sgo lnga'i rnam shes ni 'phags pa'i mnyam bzhag gi dus su 'gags pas so //
NK116(le)001:7309: chad nas 'byung mi rung ba ni /
NK116(le)001:7310: gnyid kyi rjes su tshogs drug 'byung bar mi rigs te /
NK116(le)001:7311: snga ma 'gags nas ring zhig bar du chod pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7313: rnam par shes pa yid las 'byung //
NK116(le)001:7314: yid ni kun gzhi las 'byung te //
NK116(le)001:7315: kun gzhi las ni sems kun yang //
NK116(le)001:7318: theg chen med pa dgag pa la gsum ste /
NK116(le)001:7323: phyag rgya bzhi las 'dus byas mi rtag pa dang mi 'gal te /
NK116(le)001:7324: longs sku 'dus byas ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7326: 'dus ma byas shing lhun gyis grub /
NK116(le)001:7328: sdug bsngal dang mi 'gal te sdug bsngal srab pa
NK116(le)001:7329: la bde ba 'dod pa phan tshun mthun pa'i phyir
NK116(le)001:7330: / bdag med pa dang mi 'gal te bde gshegs snying po spros pa dang bral ba'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7331: zhi ba dang mi 'gal te dgra bcom gtan gyi myang 'das ma yin zhing //
NK116(le)001:7332: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal rags pa tsam zhi ba'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7333: gzhan yang sde snod dang mi 'gal te dgos pa
NK116(le)001:7334: chen po'i phyir dgag bya chung ngu gnang skabs yod
NK116(le)001:7335: la bag med kyi las byung rgyal du byang sems
NK116(le)001:7338: las rang zad du 'gyur ba theg chen yang mi 'dod pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7340: theg chen ma bden pas na sangs rgyas mi srida de /
NK116(le)001:7341: rgyu ma tshangs pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7343: ma tshang ba dang 'gal ba dang /
NK116(le)001:7344: thabs min de ltar ston min phyir /
NK116(le)001:7345: nyan thos kyi ni theg pa 'di /
NK116(le)001:7346: theg chen chos zhes bya ba min /
NK116(le)001:7349: theg chen bka' yin pa lung gis grub bo //
NK116(le)001:7350: gal te khas mi len na /
NK116(le)001:7351: khyod kyi lung de yang de ltar thal lo //
NK116(le)001:7353: sangs rgyas kyi gsung thams cad bka' ma yin pa'i
NK116(le)001:7354: skyon yod de phyi rol bas the tshom za ba'i
NK116(le)001:7356: gal te theg chen bka' min na /
NK116(le)001:7357: skyon ni khyed cag la yang mtshungs /
NK116(le)001:7359: sa bcu med pa dgag pa ni /
NK116(le)001:7360: sa bcu mi thob bar so skyes sar dbang rnams
NK116(le)001:7361: ma thob pas tshogs cung zad las mi rdzogs pa'i
NK116(le)001:7362: phyir ro // 'phags pa'i sa mthong sgom du tshogs bsogs pa 'thad do //
NK116(le)001:7364: gang tshe mar me mdzad kyis nga //
NK116(le)001:7365: lung bstan gyur pa de yi tshe //
NK116(le)001:7367: dbang bcu dag kyang rdzogs par gyur /
NK116(le)001:7369: sangs rgyas rang rgyud pa dgag pa ni /
NK116(le)001:7370: thub pa nyid sangs rgyas ma yin par thal te /
NK116(le)001:7371: rig pa gsum gyis 'di ltar gnod de /
NK116(le)001:7372: mi nag mthung thung can bsad pa'i rnam smin ma sbyangs te /
NK116(le)001:7373: zhabs la seng ldeng gi tshal bas snad pa dang /
NK116(le)001:7374: thams cad mkhyen pa ma yin te //
NK116(le)001:7375: lhag spyod dang ring 'phur la dris pa dang //
NK116(le)001:7376: thugs rje 'pho 'gyur med pa ma yin te /
NK116(le)001:7377: 'das nas 'gro don rgyun chad pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7378: gnyis pa so so'i 'dod pa bsdus te bshad pa gnyis las /
NK116(le)001:7379: dang po bye brag smra ba la mtshan nyid /
NK116(le)001:7383: rang rig tha snyad du'ang khas mi len pa theg dman gyi bye brag smra ba'i mtshan nyid do //
NK116(le)001:7384: gnyis pa ni sde ba bco brgyad do //
NK116(le)001:7387: gzhal bya'i chos la dbye na //
NK116(le)001:7390: skye mched bcu gnyis rnams su yod par 'dod cing /
NK116(le)001:7391: phung po lngar 'dus ma byas kyi chos ma gtogs shes bya thams cad 'dus kyang //
NK116(le)001:7392: shes bya thams cad khams bco brgyad du 'dus shing skye mched bcu gnyis su'ang 'adu'o /
NK116(le)001:7393: de thams cad legs par bsdus na bden pa gnyis su 'dus la /
NK116(le)001:7394: de yang bye brag smra ba'i lugas la bcom mam
NK116(le)001:7395: blos gzhig pa gang rang gi sgo nas der 'dzin
NK116(le)001:7396: gyi blor 'dod du rung ba'i chos rnams ni kun
NK116(le)001:7397: rdzob kyi bden par bzhed la /
NK116(le)001:7398: de'i bsam ngo na yang rdza yi bum pa lta
NK116(le)001:7399: bu ma zhig ba'i gnas skabs su de la dmigs
NK116(le)001:7400: nas bum pa'o // snyam pa'i blo skye yang /
NK116(le)001:7401: de tho ba lta bus bshigs pa na bum pa'o
NK116(le)001:7402: snyam pa'i blo mi skye ba la bsam pa yin
NK116(le)001:7403: zhing / mtshan gzhi yang rdza bum de nyid do //
NK116(le)001:7404: don dam pa'i bden pa ni bcom gzhig gang rung
NK116(le)001:7405: gi sgo nas rang 'dzin gyi blo 'dor du mi
NK116(le)001:7407: mtshan gzhi ni rdul phran cha med dang /
NK116(le)001:7408: shes pa skad cig cha med dang /
NK116(le)001:7409: 'dus ma byas kyi chos rnams don dam bden par 'dod cing /
NK116(le)001:7410: kun rdzob bden pa dang btags yod don gcig par 'dod cing /
NK116(le)001:7411: don dam bden pa dang rdzas yod don gcig par 'dod do //
NK116(le)001:7412: gnyis pa lam gyi rnam bzhag ni /
NK116(le)001:7413: bden bzhi'i rnam pa mi rtag pa sogs bcu drug
NK116(le)001:7414: po la dmigs nas lam lnga'i rnam bzhag tsam byed
NK116(le)001:7415: kyang / sa bcu la sogs pa'i rnam bzhag mi 'dod la /
NK116(le)001:7416: spang bya nyon mong pa can dang nyon mongs pa can ma yin pa'i mi shes pa gnyis so //
NK116(le)001:7418: nyon mongs pa can gyi sgrib pa spangs nas dman pa'i dgra bcom pa'i go 'phang dang /
NK116(le)001:7419: nyon mongs pa can ma yin pa'i sgrib pa spangs
NK116(le)001:7420: bas sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob par 'dod do
NK116(le)001:7421: // de yang bdag cag gi ston pa lta bu la mtshon na /
NK116(le)001:7422: dang po byang chub mchog tu thugs bskyed pa nas
NK116(le)001:7423: bzung ste srod la bdud btul ba yan chad thar
NK116(le)001:7424: ba cha mthun tsam la gnas pa'i so skye dang
NK116(le)001:7426: sbyor lam gyi gnas skabs drod sogs bzhi dang mthong
NK116(le)001:7427: lam skad cig ma bco lnga rnams stan thog de
NK116(le)001:7428: nyid du rdzogs par mdzad nas tho rengs sgom lam
NK116(le)001:7429: rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis nyon mongs
NK116(le)001:7430: can ma yin pa'i mi shes pa drud nas phyung
NK116(le)001:7431: ste sangs rgyas par 'dod la de ltar sangs rgyas
NK116(le)001:7432: pa de yang thugs rgyud kyi zad pa dang mi
NK116(le)001:7433: skye ba shes pa'i ye shes de nyid yin gyi
NK116(le)001:7434: phyi'i gzugs phung de nyid ni sdug bsngal bden pa
NK116(le)001:7435: yin pas sangs rgyas su mi 'dod do //
NK116(le)001:7436: 'on kyang thugs rgyud la dpags nas sangs rgyas pa
NK116(le)001:7437: phyin gyi mdzad pa rnams sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa
NK116(le)001:7438: / sku lus la dpags nas lhag bcas dgra bcom pa zhes 'dod cing /
NK116(le)001:7439: mya ngan las 'das pa na lhag med kyi dbyings
NK116(le)001:7440: su gzhugs pa yin pas bem rig gi 'jug pa
NK116(le)001:7441: rgyun chad nas zhing khams gzhan du gzugs sku'i rnam
NK116(le)001:7443: longs spyod rdzogs sku sogs kyang mi 'dod //
NK116(le)001:7444: lhag bcas lhag med gnyis las mi gnas pa'i myang 'das kyang khas mi len la /
NK116(le)001:7445: de bzhin skyes bu zung bzhi dang /
NK116(le)001:7446: gang zag ya brgyad kyi rnam bzhag tsam 'dod kyang
NK116(le)001:7447: de dag gang zag yin pas dge 'dun dkon mchog
NK116(le)001:7449: de dag gi rgyud kyi slob pa dang mi slob
NK116(le)001:7450: pa'i chos rnams la dge 'dun dkon mchog tu 'dod
NK116(le)001:7451: do // gnyis pa mdo sde ba la'ang /
NK116(le)001:7456: phyi don dang rang rig gnyis ka bden zhen gyis
NK116(le)001:7457: khas len pa theg dman mdo sde ba'i mtshan nyid
NK116(le)001:7458: do // gnyis pa dbye ba la lung dang rig pa'i rjes 'brang gi mdo sde ba gnyis las /
NK116(le)001:7460: bye brag smra ba rnams bkar 'dod pa mngon pa
NK116(le)001:7461: sde bdun po sh+aa ri'i bu sogs kyi bstan bcos
NK116(le)001:7462: su 'dod bzhin grub mtha' der smra la /
NK116(le)001:7463: gnyis pa tshad ma sde bdun la sogs nas bshad pa'o //
NK116(le)001:7464: spyir bstan bcos gang zag gis brtsams pas 'khrul ba
NK116(le)001:7465: yod la de la sangs rgyas kyi gsung rab tshad
NK116(le)001:7466: mar 'dod de mdo sde la brten nas smra bas
NK116(le)001:7467: chos ming gang zag la chags pa ste /
NK116(le)001:7468: chos rnams dpe dang 'brel bar ston pas dpe ston pa zhes su grags so //
NK116(le)001:7469: gsum pa grub matha'i 'dod tshul la gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las /
NK116(le)001:7470: gzhi'i chos la bden pa gnyis su grangs nges pa
NK116(le)001:7471: las kun rdzob bden pa gang gis bden par 'jog
NK116(le)001:7472: pa ni blo kun rdzob pa ste /
NK116(le)001:7473: rtogs pas btags tsam yin te /
NK116(le)001:7474: des don rang mtshan gyi gnas lugs mthong ba la sgrib par byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7475: des na rtog pa'i snang yul spyi mtshan gyis khyab pa dang /
NK116(le)001:7476: spyi mtshan dang dngos med kyi chos dang /
NK116(le)001:7477: kun rdzob kyi bden pa rnams yin khyab mnyam yin la /
NK116(le)001:7478: mngon gsum gyi snang yul la rang mtshan gyis khyab pa dang /
NK116(le)001:7480: dngos po dang don dam bden pa rnams yin khyab mnyam dang 'dod pa'o //
NK116(le)001:7482: don byed nus pa gang yin pa /
NK116(le)001:7483: de 'dir don dam yod pa yin /
NK116(le)001:7484: gzhan ni kun rdzob yodapa ste /
NK116(le)001:7485: de dag rang spyi'i mtshan nyid bshad /
NK116(le)001:7487: gzhan yang rdul phran phyogs kyi cha med dang /
NK116(le)001:7488: shes pa skad cig cha med sogs khas len la /
NK116(le)001:7489: bye brag smra ba bzhin dus gsum rdzas grub dang /
NK116(le)001:7490: nam mkha' rtag dngos sogs khas mi len no //
NK116(le)001:7491: gnyis pa lam gyi dmigs pa ni bden bzhi'i rnam
NK116(le)001:7492: pa mi rtag pa sogs bcu drug po nyid yin
NK116(le)001:7493: kyang gang zag rang rkya thub pa'i rdzas yod kyi
NK116(le)001:7494: stong par rtogs pa'i gang zag gi bdag med rtogs
NK116(le)001:7495: pa'i shes rab rkyang ba thabs snying rje chen po
NK116(le)001:7496: sogs dang ya bral ba nyams su len pa ni
NK116(le)001:7497: theg dman rang lam yin la /
NK116(le)001:7498: sangs rgyas kyi lam gyi bgrod tshul dang dman pa'i
NK116(le)001:7499: lam gnyis ka la lam lnga'i rnam bzhag tsam byed
NK116(le)001:7500: kyi sa bcu la sogs pa'i rnam bzhag mi byed
NK116(le)001:7501: do // spang bya gang zag gibadaga 'dzin dang /
NK116(le)001:7502: nyon mongs pa can gyi mi shes pa dang /
NK116(le)001:7503: nyon mongs pa can ma yin pa'i mi shes pa sogs kyi tha snyad tsam las /
NK116(le)001:7504: chos kyi bdag 'dzin dang shes sgrib sogs kyi tha snyad khas mi len no //
NK116(le)001:7505: gsum pa 'bras bu'i rnam bzhag la bsam sbyor phun
NK116(le)001:7506: tshogs gnyis yun ring nyams su blangs pas mi shes
NK116(le)001:7507: pa gnyis ka'i sa bon drung nas byung ste /
NK116(le)001:7508: spang ba khyad par gsum ldan dang rtogs pa khyad
NK116(le)001:7509: par gsum ldan gyis rang don mthar phyin pa'i bde
NK116(le)001:7510: gshegs gnyis las gzhan don mthar thug skyobs pas gdul
NK116(le)001:7511: bya la bden pa bzhi'i chos 'khor bskor te smin
NK116(le)001:7512: grol la 'god pa ni bla na med pa'i byang
NK116(le)001:7514: mi rtag sogs bcu drug rkyang ba tsam bsgom pas
NK116(le)001:7515: nyon mong pa can gyi mi shes tsam spangs te
NK116(le)001:7516: dgra bcom pa'i go 'phang mngon du byed pa ni
NK116(le)001:7517: dman pa'i byang chub mngon du byed pa'i tshul lo
NK116(le)001:7519: thun mongs gi skabs su bstan pa'i shugs kyis rtogs nus pas ma spros so //
NK116(le)001:7520: spyir bye mdo thun mongs la rigs kyi sgo nas dbye na bzhir 'dod de /
NK116(le)001:7522: nyan thos rnam bzhi sprul pa dang //
NK116(le)001:7523: rdzogs pa'i byang chub 'gyur ba dang //
NK116(le)001:7527: rab 'byor dang ma 'gags pa sogs so //
NK116(le)001:7528: myang 'das las ni lhas byin dang /
NK116(le)001:7529: drug sde yang der bsdus so //
NK116(le)001:7530: gnyis pa ni nyan thos kyi sbyor lam bzod pa thob nas sangs rgyas su 'gyur ba dang /
NK116(le)001:7531: gsum pa ni rang lam nas ji ltar bshad pa ltar 'jug pa'o //
NK116(le)001:7532: bzhi pa ni bsam pa theg chen pas nyan thos kyi grub mtha' 'dzin pa'o //
NK116(le)001:7533: theg dman gyis bsdus phyir rtsa bar rang rgyal logs su ma bstan la sa bcad tsam brjod na /
NK116(le)001:7534: grub mtha' de la dbye ba gsum ste /
NK116(le)001:7543: nyan byang gnyis gang rung min te dbang po 'bring du gyur pa'o //
NK116(le)001:7545: gang zag gi bdag dang phyi gzung ba rdul phran
NK116(le)001:7546: du mi 'dod kyang yul rdzun snang 'dzin mkhan gyi
NK116(le)001:7547: shes pa skad cig ma mi spangs pa yin te
NK116(le)001:7549: gzung don rtog pa spang phyir dang //
NK116(le)001:7550: 'dzin pa mi spang phyir dang ni //
NK116(le)001:7551: rten gyi bse ru lta bu'i la //
NK116(le)001:7552: yang dag bsdus par shes par bya /
NK116(le)001:7555: ma rig pa sogs rten 'brel bcu gnyis lugs ldog ste bsgom pas srid pa'i rtsa ba gcod pa'o //
NK116(le)001:7557: nyan rang gnyis tshogs lam gyi bar du dge ba'i bshes gnyen la thos bsam byas pa las /
NK116(le)001:7559: rigs stobs kyis dben par dga' ba'i 'du 'dzi spangs te bsgom pas rang gi byang chub grub pa'o //
NK116(le)001:7561: ne tsho ltar tshogs na spyod pa dbang po rtul
NK116(le)001:7562: zhing yon tan chung ba mang po dang lhan cig
NK116(le)001:7563: bsgoms pas tshe gsum na 'bras bu thob rung ste
NK116(le)001:7564: / myur ba srid pa gsum gyis thar /
NK116(le)001:7567: dbang rnon yon tan che ba gcig pur gnas so
NK116(le)001:7568: de ni tshogs bskal pa brgyas 'bras bu grub ste
NK116(le)001:7569: // bse ru bskal pa brgya yi rgyus /
NK116(le)001:7571: des ni tshogs lam gyi rten la tshogs bsags nas /
NK116(le)001:7572: stan thog gcig tu lam lnga mngon du byed pas
NK116(le)001:7573: na dbang po rnon por bzhag la snga mas de
NK116(le)001:7576: ston dang bse ru byang chub ba //
NK116(le)001:7577: bsam gtan mtha' rten gcig la kun /
NK116(le)001:7579: de'ang nyan thos dgra bcom dang rang sangs rgyas dbang rtul gnyis kyi mngon par shes pas /
NK116(le)001:7580: stong gsum las gnyis man chad mthong la /
NK116(le)001:7583: sangs rgyas kyis grangs med gzigs te /
NK116(le)001:7585: dgra bcom bse ru ston rnam gyis //
NK116(le)001:7586: stong gnyis gsum dang grangs med mthong /
NK116(le)001:7588: theg chen dbu sems gnyis las dang po ston pa'i
NK116(le)001:7589: phyir gzung 'dzin zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs
NK116(le)001:7590: te / rtsa bshad dang mtha' dpyad gnyis las dang po ni /
NK116(le)001:7591: 'di ltar gzunga ba chos dang 'dzina pa gang zag
NK116(le)001:7592: gnyis su snang ba'i yula yula cana dag kuna rdzoba
NK116(le)001:7593: kyi bden pa nyid de gang de lasa gazhana du
NK116(le)001:7594: chos rnams gnyis su meda kyi shesa pa ni dona
NK116(le)001:7595: dama bdena para 'doda pa semas tsam pa yi gruba
NK116(le)001:7597: gnyis pa la 'dod pa brjod pa dang /
NK116(le)001:7600: de'ang phyi don med kyang bdena grub khas len cing
NK116(le)001:7601: gzung 'dzin gnyis med kyi shes pa rang rig rang
NK116(le)001:7602: gsal don dam du 'dod pas na rnam rig pa
NK116(le)001:7603: zhes kyang bya'o // dbye na so so'i skye bo'i
NK116(le)001:7604: rgyud kyi dbang po'i mngon gsum la snang ba'i gzugs
NK116(le)001:7605: rags par snang ba 'di dag snang ba ltar du
NK116(le)001:7606: grub par 'dod pa rnam bden pa dang /
NK116(le)001:7607: ma grub par 'dod pa rnam rdzun pa'o //
NK116(le)001:7608: de la gzhi'i rnam bzhag yul dang yul can gnyis las /
NK116(le)001:7609: dang po ni shes bya thams cad kun brtag /
NK116(le)001:7610: gzhan dbang yongs grub gsum du 'du bar 'dod cing /
NK116(le)001:7611: dang po la gnyis te mtshan nyid chad pa'i kun brtag ni /
NK116(le)001:7612: ri bong gi rwa ltar mi srid bzhin du blos
NK116(le)001:7613: brtag pa gang zag dang chos kyi bdag lta bu'o
NK116(le)001:7615: rnam par rtog pas brtag pa'i don /
NK116(le)001:7616: kun tu brtags pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK116(le)001:7617: rnam par rtog pa gzhan gyi dbang /
NK116(le)001:7618: de yis stong nyid yongs su grub /
NK116(le)001:7621: gzugs nas rnam mkhyen gyis bar gyi chos la so sor tha snyad gdags pa'o //
NK116(le)001:7622: gzhan dbang la dag ma dag gnyis te /
NK116(le)001:7623: snga ma 'phags pa'i gzigs ngor grub pa dang /
NK116(le)001:7624: phyi ma ni 'jig rten pa'i mthun snang du grub pa'i lugs so //
NK116(le)001:7626: gzhi 'gyur ba med pa'i yongs grub ni de bzhin nyid dang /
NK116(le)001:7627: lam phyin ci ma log pa'i yongs grub ni /
NK116(le)001:7628: sems rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes so //
NK116(le)001:7629: kun brtag bden med dang gzhan dbang yongs grub gnyis bden grub tu bzhed do //
NK116(le)001:7630: kun rdzob bden pas bsdus pa'i chos thams cad kun brtag dang gzhan dbang gnyis su 'dus shing //
NK116(le)001:7632: yongs grub don gcig tu 'dod la //
NK116(le)001:7634: yongs grub mtshan nyid pa dang /
NK116(le)001:7637: gnyis pa ni tshogs brgyad khas len pa dag ni
NK116(le)001:7638: kun gzhi'i rnam shes ni ngo bo ma sgrib lung
NK116(le)001:7639: ma bstan du 'gyur ba'i gtso bo yid kyi rnam
NK116(le)001:7641: de dgra bcom pa'i rgyud la'ang yod pas bsgrib lung ma bstan yin la //
NK116(le)001:7642: dge rtsa chad pa'i rgyud la yod pas dge ba min //
NK116(le)001:7643: khams gong ma'i rgyud la yod pas mi dge ba'ang min no //
NK116(le)001:7644: nyon yid ni dmigs yul kun gzhi la dmigs nas
NK116(le)001:7645: rnam par rang sems pa'i rnam pa can ngo bo
NK116(le)001:7646: bsgrib lung ma bstan pa zhig la 'dod do //
NK116(le)001:7648: de yang gang zag rang rkya thub pa'i rdzas yod
NK116(le)001:7649: kyis stong pa'i gang zag gi bdag med dang gzung
NK116(le)001:7650: 'dzin rdzas gzhan gyis stong ba dang /
NK116(le)001:7651: kun brtag rang gi mtshan nyid kyis grub pas stong pa'i chos kyi bdag med rnams yin la /
NK116(le)001:7652: de rnams la dmigs nas bskal ba grangs med gsum
NK116(le)001:7653: gyi tshogs dang 'brel par nyams su blangs te lam
NK116(le)001:7654: lnga sa bcu rim gyis bgrod nas gang zag gi
NK116(le)001:7655: bdag 'dzin nyon sgrib dang chos kyi bdag 'dzin shes
NK116(le)001:7656: sgrib zad par spangs te byang chub par 'dod do
NK116(le)001:7658: lhag bcas lhag med mi gnas pa'i myang 'das te gsum dang /
NK116(le)001:7659: sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi rnam bzhag dang /
NK116(le)001:7660: chos sku la spangs pa'i bdag nyid ngo bo nyid sku dang /
NK116(le)001:7661: rtogs pa'i bdag nyid ye shes chos sku gnyis dang /
NK116(le)001:7662: lhun grub dang rgyun mi 'chad pa'i rnam bzhag rnams kyang 'dod do //
NK116(le)001:7663: gnyis pa dgag pa la gsum ste /
NK116(le)001:7664: spyir don dam myang 'das gnyis med kyi rang rig
NK116(le)001:7665: tu 'dod pa dang snang ba kun btags 'khrul bar
NK116(le)001:7666: 'dod cing rang rig bden pa dang gcig par mi
NK116(le)001:7667: 'thad pa dang gzhan dbang skye 'gags can gyi chos
NK116(le)001:7668: can don dam 'dod pa mi 'thad pa nyid do
NK116(le)001:7669: // 'dir sa bcad tsam smros pa las /
NK116(le)001:7670: rgyas par shes 'dod rnams kyis gzhan du blta bar bya'o //
NK116(le)001:7671: gnyis pa la nang gses dbu ma rang rgyud pa'i
NK116(le)001:7672: grub mtha' ni ji ltar snang ba zhes bya ba
NK116(le)001:7674: rtsa bshad dang mtha' dpyad gnyis las /
NK116(le)001:7676: ji ltar tshogs drug yul du snang ba thams cada kuna rdzoba tu gruba pa ste /
NK116(le)001:7677: dper na sgyu ma'i rta glanga lta bu'i matshana nyid de //
NK116(le)001:7678: dona dama par ci'i ngo bor yang gruba pa meda
NK116(le)001:7679: pa nam mkha'a ltar 'doda pa gang zhig dbu ma
NK116(le)001:7680: ranga rgyud pa yi lugas so //
NK116(le)001:7681: gnyis pa la rang rgyud 'og ma dang gong ma
NK116(le)001:7682: gnyis te phyogs dang po la 'dod pa brjod pa
NK116(le)001:7685: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis stong pa sgyu ma'i rang bzhin du /
NK116(le)001:7686: bden pa gnyis char gyi ngo bor gnas te /
NK116(le)001:7687: kun rdzob ni rgyu rkyen rten 'brel gyis tshogs pa
NK116(le)001:7688: las med pa gsal snang du 'khrul snang ji ltar
NK116(le)001:7689: snang bzhin pa'i ngo bor tha snyad tsam du don
NK116(le)001:7690: byed nus pa'i phyir na bden la /
NK116(le)001:7691: don dam ni kun rdzob kyi cha'i brtag pa log
NK116(le)001:7692: pa'i rgyu rkyen yin min sogs ming tshig yi ge
NK116(le)001:7693: la sogs pa'i spros pas stong yang /
NK116(le)001:7694: gzugs brnyan ltar na rten 'brel du gsal ba ma 'gags pa'i cha nas sgyu mar brjod de /
NK116(le)001:7695: des ni rgyu tshogs gnyis sgyu ma lta bu bsags
NK116(le)001:7696: pas 'bras bu byang chub sgyu ma lta bu thob
NK116(le)001:7697: nas / sgyu ma'i rang bzhin la rtag tu gnas pa ni mnyam par bzhag pa yin la /
NK116(le)001:7698: sgyu ma'i tshul gyis phrin las 'byung bas /
NK116(le)001:7699: sgyu ma lta bu'i sems can gyi don byed do //
NK116(le)001:7700: yum las chos thams cad rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu /
NK116(le)001:7701: mya ngan 'das pa yang rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu /
NK116(le)001:7702: mya ngan las 'das pa las ches lhag pa'i chos
NK116(le)001:7703: shig yod na yang de yang rmi lam lta bu
NK116(le)001:7708: don dam bden pa rmi lam 'dra ba dang //
NK116(le)001:7709: mya ngan 'das pa rmi lam mtshungs par 'jug /
NK116(le)001:7710: gang gi mkhas pa de ltar 'jug pa yang //
NK116(le)001:7711: de ni yid kyi sdom pa mchog tu bshad /
NK116(le)001:7713: ji ltar skye bo mang po'i mdun dag tu /
NK116(le)001:7714: sgyu ma byed pa dag gis gzugs sprul te //
NK116(le)001:7715: rta dang glang po shing rta sna tshogs byas /
NK116(le)001:7716: de la mi bden snang ba sna tshogs ltar //
NK116(le)001:7717: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par gyis /
NK116(le)001:7719: de'ang ma dag sgyu ma ni 'khrul brgya 'byams pa'i ngor snang ba dang /
NK116(le)001:7720: dag pa sgyu ma ni lam du snang la rang bzhin med par bsgom pas /
NK116(le)001:7721: 'bras bu chos sku dang gzugs sku dbyer med sgyu
NK116(le)001:7722: ma lta bu 'og min na bzhugs pa las sprul
NK116(le)001:7723: pa sgyu ma lta bu 'byung ba'o //
NK116(le)001:7725: tshul der rnam pa gsum gyi rig pas gnod de /
NK116(le)001:7726: rang bzhin don dam med pa dang /
NK116(le)001:7727: rig ngor sgyu ma mi 'grub pa dang //
NK116(le)001:7728: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa mthar thug ma yin pa'o //
NK116(le)001:7730: don dam chos can khyod skye 'jig byed par thal /
NK116(le)001:7731: sgyu ma skye 'jig byed pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:7733: 'dod na nam mkha' chos can mtshan nyid der thal /
NK116(le)001:7736: de 'dra'i nam mkha' de 'dus byas yin par thal /
NK116(le)001:7739: chos can de yin pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:7742: sa ni chu la chu rlung la //
NK116(le)001:7743: rlung ni mkha' la rab tu gnas //
NK116(le)001:7744: mkha' ni rlung dang chu dag dang //
NK116(le)001:7745: sa yi khams la gnas ma yin //
NK116(le)001:7746: zhes gsungs ba mi 'thad par thal /
NK116(le)001:7750: sgyu ma chos can ma grub par thal /
NK116(le)001:7753: dus dang phrad pa dang rgyun dang skad cig gis brtags pas chos gang yang mi 'grub pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:7754: don dam sgyu ma ltar khas blangs du mi rung ba yin no //
NK116(le)001:7757: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa mthar thug ma yin par thal /
NK116(le)001:7758: don dam ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:7761: nam mkha' gang la gnas min don 'di rtag par gyis /
NK116(le)001:7764: yod dang med dang yod med ces //
NK116(le)001:7765: khas mi len par gang yin pa /
NK116(le)001:7766: de la dus ni ring po yang //
NK116(le)001:7767: gcig kyang klan ka byar mi rung /
NK116(le)001:7769: de las gzhan kun rdzob snga ma dang mtshungs la /
NK116(le)001:7770: don dam mi 'dra ba'i 'dod tshul yod kyang mi spros so //
NK116(le)001:7771: gnyis pa rang rgyud gong ma'i 'dod pa ni /
NK116(le)001:7772: kun rdzob du rten 'brel sgyu ma'i rnam par ji ltar gnas pa bzhin 'jog la /
NK116(le)001:7773: de la yang don byed yin min gnyis la ltos nas kun rdzob dag min gnyis kyang dabye'o //
NK116(le)001:7774: de ltar snang bzhin pa 'di kun rdzob kyi bden pa dang /
NK116(le)001:7775: de nyid rig pas dpyad na gcig du ma yod med yin min /
NK116(le)001:7776: grub ma grub la sogs pa'i tha snyad med phyir
NK116(le)001:7777: sngar bzhin sgyu ma dang ma grub pa yang mi
NK116(le)001:7778: bzhag ste // bden gnyis las kun rdzob 'di ltar snang ba 'di //
NK116(le)001:7779: rig pas brtags na 'ga' mi rnyed //
NK116(le)001:7780: ma rnyed pa de don dam ste //
NK116(le)001:7781: ye nas gnas pa'i chos nyid do //
NK116(le)001:7783: de ltar bden pa gnyis kyi don shes pas /
NK116(le)001:7785: sku gnyis mngon du byed cing /
NK116(le)001:7786: don dam par sangs rgyas kyang med la /
NK116(le)001:7787: 'gro don byas pa yang med par 'dod de /
NK116(le)001:7789: dngos snang la bden rdzun gnyis yod pa mi 'thad de /
NK116(le)001:7790: chu zla dang gnam zla gnyis rkyen las snang ba dang /
NK116(le)001:7791: mig shes la snang ba dang /
NK116(le)001:7792: dpyad na ma grub par mtshungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7793: gnam zla nyid rdul phran cha med dang /
NK116(le)001:7796: mtha' dbus kyi rig pas kyang khegs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:7797: med bzhin snang ba chu zla dang mtshungs par thal ba'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7798: bag chags kyi 'khrul snang la khyad par med pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7799: don byed min gyi khyad par yod ce na /
NK116(le)001:7800: gnam zla chos can don byed mi nus par thal /
NK116(le)001:7801: rdzing bur shar ba'i don byed mi nus pa'i phyir to //
NK116(le)001:7802: mkha' zla yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7803: des na snang tsam gyis don byed pa las gnam zlas kyang min te /
NK116(le)001:7805: ji ltar mtshan mo chu yi zla ba dag /
NK116(le)001:7806: dwangs shing snyog pa med pa'i mtshor snang yang /
NK116(le)001:7807: chu zla stong la gsog ste snying po med //
NK116(le)001:7808: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par gyis /
NK116(le)001:7810: rgyu rkyen rten 'brel las snang ba tsam mi 'gog ste /
NK116(le)001:7811: ji ltar snang nyid dgag min gyi /
NK116(le)001:7812: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i phyir /'di ni sdug bsngal rgyur 'gyur pa'i //
NK116(le)001:7813: bden par rtog pa bzlog bya yin /
NK116(le)001:7817: gnyis ka las skyes par mi 'dod de /
NK116(le)001:7818: rang grub dus skye ba grub zin pas mi 'thad la /
NK116(le)001:7819: ma grub na med pa las skye mi srid do //
NK116(le)001:7821: rgyu 'gags nas skye ba rgyu med pa la 'bras bu med de nam mkhar pad+mo bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:7822: ma 'gags par skye ba rtag pa las skye bar thal ba'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7823: dus mnyam par mi 'thad de skye bya skye byed du ma grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7824: rgyun las skye na'ang 'phrad bkag phyir ma grub pa kho na'o ////
NK116(le)001:7825: da ni rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa'i rtse mo
NK116(le)001:7826: mthar thug dbu ma thal 'gyur ba'i tshul 'chad pa
NK116(le)001:7827: la ni / dang po gzhung 'di sgo dbye phyir
NK116(le)001:7828: 'di ltar zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te
NK116(le)001:7829: la ni / / 'di ltar snang ba nyid ni kuna rdzoba sgyu ma'i rta glang lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:7830: stong ba dona dama bden pa zhes bya ba'i tha snyad kyis /
NK116(le)001:7831: batagas pa ganga yanga spros pa'i matha'a thams cad dang bral zhing /
NK116(le)001:7832: tshogs drug gi yul snang dusa nyid nas skye ba dang /
NK116(le)001:7837: dngosa pora 'doda pa'i kuna rdzoba kyi chos rnams kyang /
NK116(le)001:7838: de yi gruba pa'i matha'a ru khasa ma blangsa so //
NK116(le)001:7839: de ni su zhig zhe na dbu ma thala 'gyura ba'i shinga rta'i srol 'byeda chena po /
NK116(le)001:7840: dpal mgon klu yi dabnga po yin no //
NK116(le)001:7841: gang des rgyal ba'i dgongs pa mthar thug pa 'grol
NK116(le)001:7842: byed gzhan la mi ltos par rang stobs kyis 'chad
NK116(le)001:7846: lho phyogs be da'i yul du ni //
NK116(le)001:7847: dge slong dpal ldan zhes bya ba //
NK116(le)001:7848: de ming klu zhes 'bod pa ste //
NK116(le)001:7849: yod dang med pa'i phyogs 'jig pa //
NK116(le)001:7850: nga yi bstan pa 'jig rten du //
NK116(le)001:7851: bla med theg chen rab bshad nas //
NK116(le)001:7852: rab tu dga' ba'i sa bsgrub te //
NK116(le)001:7856: de bzhin gshegs pa nga 'das nas //
NK116(le)001:7857: lo ni bzhi brgya lon pa na //
NK116(le)001:7859: bstan pa la ni dad cing phan //
NK116(le)001:7860: rab tu dga' ba'i sa 'thob pa //
NK116(le)001:7861: lo ni drug brgya dag tu 'tsho //
NK116(le)001:7862: rig pa rma bya chen mo ni //
NK116(le)001:7863: bdag nyid chen po des kyang 'grub //
NK116(le)001:7864: bstan bcos sna tshogs don dang ni //
NK116(le)001:7865: dngos po med pa'i don de rigs //
NK116(le)001:7866: gang tshe lus de bor ba na //
NK116(le)001:7867: bde ba can du skye bar 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:7868: de ni mthar gyi sangs rgyas nyid //
NK116(le)001:7869: nges pa kho nar yang dag 'thob //
NK116(le)001:7870: zhes nges don gyi theg pa chen po yod med
NK116(le)001:7871: kyi mtha' gnyis dang bral ba klu grub kyis 'grel
NK116(le)001:7872: bar bstan no // gzhan yang gser 'od dam pa nas bshad pa //
NK116(le)001:7873: ston pa zhal bzhugs dus kyi li tsa byi gzhon
NK116(le)001:7874: nu 'jig rten thams cad kyis mthong na dga' ba
NK116(le)001:7875: zhes bya ba de nyid skye ba bzhes pa yin
NK116(le)001:7877: gzhon nu 'di nga mya ngan las 'das nas lo bzhi brgya lon pa na /
NK116(le)001:7878: klu zhes bya ba'i dge slong du gyur nas nga'i bstan pa rgyas par byed de /
NK116(le)001:7879: mthar rab tu dngas pa'i 'od ces bya ba'i zhing
NK116(le)001:7880: du ye shes 'byung gnas 'od ces bya ba'i rgyal
NK116(le)001:7882: de'i phyir 'di la nges don gyi lugs phyin ci ma log par nges par yod par grub bo //
NK116(le)001:7883: li tsa bi gzhon nu 'jig rten thams cad kyi mthong na dga' ba 'di /
NK116(le)001:7884: ston pa 'das nas lo brgyad cu pa la bstan pa nyams pa'i tshe /
NK116(le)001:7885: ston pa'i mtshan 'chang ba'i dge slong du gyur nas bstan pa rgyas par byas te /
NK116(le)001:7886: lo brgya lon pa'i 'og tu 'das nas bde ba can du skye bar gsungs so //
NK116(le)001:7887: mdo sde de nyid du sa bdun pa la gnas par bshad do //
NK116(le)001:7888: de lta'i slob dpon gyi dgongs pa ji lta ba
NK116(le)001:7889: bzhin 'grel bas na mi 'phrog pa'i thugs rjer ldan
NK116(le)001:7890: pa 'phags pa zla ba gragsa pa'i khyad chosa thun
NK116(le)001:7891: mong ma yin pa yang yina no //
NK116(le)001:7892: tshul 'dira ni grub mtha' 'oga ma'i rnam pa thamsa
NK116(le)001:7893: cada la mtha' bral dbu ma'i rig pa'i shes rab
NK116(le)001:7894: rnon pos spros pa phyogs re ba tsam ma yin
NK116(le)001:7895: par brtsad cinga brtagsa pasa mthar 'dzin gyi zhen yul
NK116(le)001:7896: re re nas thal 'gyur gyis sun byung bas gonga
NK116(le)001:7898: gzhung 'dir yongs grags kyi gtan tshigs chen po bzhi ste /
NK116(le)001:7903: dang po dgag bya'i rgyud las dpyad nas dgag bya 'gog pa ste //
NK116(le)001:7904: 'di ltar snang bzhin pa thams cad chos can /
NK116(le)001:7906: bdag dang gzhan gnyis ka dang rgyu med las skye ba mi srid pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7908: rang skye zhes bya ba mi 'thad de /
NK116(le)001:7909: bdag las skye ba chos can //
NK116(le)001:7910: yod dus skye'am med dus skye bar 'dod grang /
NK116(le)001:7911: dang po ltar na mi 'thad de /
NK116(le)001:7912: skyed bya skye byed tha dad du med pa dang /
NK116(le)001:7913: yod bzhin skye bas na nam yang mi skye bar mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK116(le)001:7914: skye ba la thug pa med par 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7915: phyi ma ltar na mi 'thad de //
NK116(le)001:7916: rgyu med pa las skye ba ha cang thal te /
NK116(le)001:7917: nam mkhar pad+mo skye bar thal ba'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:7918: gzhan las skye ba'am mi 'thad do //
NK116(le)001:7920: thams cad las thams cad skye bar thal lo //
NK116(le)001:7921: 'dod na me lce las kyang mun pa skye bar thal lo //
NK116(le)001:7923: gnyis ka las skye'o zhe na'ang /
NK116(le)001:7924: de bzhin rtag pa las skye bar 'dod dam mi rtag pa las skye bar 'dod grang /
NK116(le)001:7925: dang po mi 'thad de rgyu mi 'pho bar 'bras bu skye bar mi 'grub pa'i phyir dang /
NK116(le)001:7926: gal te skye na 'pho bas rtag pa nyams so /
NK116(le)001:7928: skad cig gis 'gags nas rgyu ma grub pas 'bras bu skye bar mi rung ngo //
NK116(le)001:7929: de phyir gnyis ka'i rkyen gyis gnod do //
NK116(le)001:7930: phrad pa bkag pas kyang rgyu 'bras la 'phrad pa med pas rgyu las skye ba ma grub bo //
NK116(le)001:7932: bdag las ma yin gzhan las min //
NK116(le)001:7933: gnyis las ma yin rgyu med min //
NK116(le)001:7934: dngos po gang dag gang na yang //
NK116(le)001:7935: skye ba nam yang yod ma yin /
NK116(le)001:7938: dgag bya'i 'bras bu la dpyad nas 'gog pa ste //
NK116(le)001:7939: 'di ltar sna tshogs su snang ba chos can dngos po med par thal /
NK116(le)001:7940: rgyu las 'bras bu yod med skye ba gsum kas stong ba'i phyir te /
NK116(le)001:7941: de'ang ka ba dag ka ba'i dngos po yod dus
NK116(le)001:7942: grub na ka ba grub zin pas mi 'thad la
NK116(le)001:7943: // med dus grub na med pa la yod par
NK116(le)001:7944: 'gyur mi srid de ri bong gi rwa las grub
NK116(le)001:7945: pa'i rdzas nam yang mi srid pa bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:7946: de yang lung snga ma las //
NK116(le)001:7947: med dam yod pa'i don la yang //
NK116(le)001:7948: rkyen mi rung ba ma yin te //
NK116(le)001:7949: med na gang gi rkyen du 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:7950: yod na rkyen gyis ci zhig bya /
NK116(le)001:7953: rgyu 'bras gnyis ka las dpyad nas 'gog pa ste /
NK116(le)001:7955: dngos por ma grub par thal //
NK116(le)001:7956: don byed par ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:7957: 'di ltar snang ba yar don dam par gcig las cig shos dang gcig las du ma dang /
NK116(le)001:7958: du ma las du ma dang //
NK116(le)001:7959: du ma las gcig skye ba'i mu bzhi'i skye ba stong pa'o //
NK116(le)001:7960: de yang nam mkha' dngos por gdags pa bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:7962: du mas dngos po gcig mi byed //
NK116(le)001:7963: du mas du ma byed ma yin //
NK116(le)001:7964: gcig gis du ma'i dngos mi byed //
NK116(le)001:7965: gcig gis gcig nyid byed pa'ang min /
NK116(le)001:7967: bzhi ba la gnyis te ma yin dgag gtan tshigs
NK116(le)001:7968: su bkod pa rten 'brel chen po rang gi dngos
NK116(le)001:7970: med dgag gtan tshigs su bkod pa gcig dang du bral lo //
NK116(le)001:7973: dngos por ma grub par thal te /
NK116(le)001:7974: rten cing 'brel ba 'byung ba de yang skye 'gags
NK116(le)001:7975: la sogs pa'i mtha' brgyad dang bral ba yin pas
NK116(le)001:7976: bden pas rang bzhin gyis stong pa'i phyir chu zla
NK116(le)001:7978: gang zhig rkyen las skyes pa de ma skyes /
NK116(le)001:7979: de la skye pa'i rang bzhin yod ma yin /
NK116(le)001:7983: chos 'ga' yod pa ma yin no //
NK116(le)001:7984: de phyir stong pa ma gtogs pa'i //
NK116(le)001:7985: chos 'ga' yod pa ma yin no //
NK116(le)001:7988: don du snang ba chos can /
NK116(le)001:7990: gcig gam du ma dang bral bas khyab pa gang zhig bden pa'i dngos pos stong bas khyab ste /
NK116(le)001:7992: ji ltar skad cig mtha' yod ltar //
NK116(le)001:7993: thog ma sus kyang btags par gyis //
NK116(le)001:7994: skad cig gsum gyi bdag nyid phyir //
NK116(le)001:7995: 'jig rten skad cig la gnas min /
NK116(le)001:7998: dgag bya ci yang med pas na //
NK116(le)001:7999: ngas ni ci yang mi 'gog go /
NK116(le)001:8000: de phyir 'gogs pa byed do zhes //
NK116(le)001:8001: skur ba de ni khyod kyis gdab //
NK116(le)001:8003: 'o na bden pa gnyis kyi rnam par bzhag pa ji ltar snyam na /
NK116(le)001:8004: tshur rol mthong ba'i blo can rnams kyi ngor tha snyad la brten nas sbyor ba tsam las /
NK116(le)001:8005: bden gnyis yang dag pa na gcig gam gnyis su 'dod mi nus te /
NK116(le)001:8006: gcig na kun rdzob spang ba bzhin don dam yang de thal 'gyur ba dang /
NK116(le)001:8007: kun rdzob dri bcas su song bzhin don dam yang de ltar thal bas gnod do //
NK116(le)001:8008: tha dad na yang mi 'thad de /
NK116(le)001:8012: gzugs las stong pa nyid gzhan ma yin /
NK116(le)001:8013: stong pa nyid las kyang gzugs gzhan ma yin no //
NK116(le)001:8015: don de dag gi phyir slob dpon ni khas len thams cad dang bral ba ste /
NK116(le)001:8017: gal te ngas dam bca' 'ga' yod /
NK116(le)001:8018: de tshe nga la skyon 'di yod /
NK116(le)001:8019: nga la dam bca' med pas na /
NK116(le)001:8020: nga ni skyon med kho na yin /
NK116(le)001:8023: yod dang med dang yod med ces /
NK116(le)001:8024: gang la phyogs ni yod min la /
NK116(le)001:8025: de la yun ni ring por yang //
NK116(le)001:8026: klan ka brjod par nus ma yin /
NK116(le)001:8028: de lta bu'i shes rab ni chos dang chos min
NK116(le)001:8029: dbye ba dang nyon mong gzhil ba'i thabs su 'gyur
NK116(le)001:8030: ba rang rang zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan
NK116(le)001:8031: te / 'phags bod gang na'ang ranga ranga gi 'doda
NK116(le)001:8032: zhena gyis sbyar ba gang zhig blo dman phan tshun
NK116(le)001:8033: gcig gis cig shos la ltos nas grub kyi /
NK116(le)001:8034: de thams cad tshad thub tu stong bcad na /
NK116(le)001:8035: rgyal bstan rin po che snyogs par gyur ba dang /
NK116(le)001:8036: khong khro ba'i dgag bzhag gi lugs kyang mang phyir
NK116(le)001:8037: skye bo mang po phyogs su lhung ste ngan 'gro'i
NK116(le)001:8038: g.yang sa la gom pa 'jog go /
NK116(le)001:8039: de bas na gruba pa'i matha'a yi matshana nyid thams cad nyamsa 'oga tu tshud par byas nas /
NK116(le)001:8040: de dag lasa 'chos skyobs kyi yon tan gnyis ldan dngosa dang /
NK116(le)001:8042: de las ldog pa'i dngosa mina gyi /
NK116(le)001:8043: matshana nyid ji lta ba bzhin legas para byed pa'i shesa raba kyang /
NK116(le)001:8044: thosa pa la brten nas 'byung bar 'gyur zhing /
NK116(le)001:8045: de yisa nyon mongas pa'i tshogs thams cad bcila bar byed do //
NK116(le)001:8046: nyon mongas meda par gyur ba la bdud kyi glagas mi rnyed do /
NK116(le)001:8047: sgom byung gi shes rab 'dir gang zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:8048: 'dir mthar thug tu gang bzung na gshis kyi bzhugs
NK116(le)001:8049: tshul chos dbyings spros pa thams cad bral ba kho
NK116(le)001:8051: tshul de ji lta bu zhig go snyam na /
NK116(le)001:8052: smra bsam brjod du meda pa dona dam pa'i bdena pa yina te /
NK116(le)001:8054: 'od srung don dam pa stong pa nyid gang yin pa de ni sus kyang bltar med pa /
NK116(le)001:8057: ma thob pa med pa yin no /
NK116(le)001:8059: sras kyi yum la bstod pa //
NK116(le)001:8060: smra bsam brjod med shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK116(le)001:8061: ma skyes ma 'gags nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK116(le)001:8062: so sor rang rig ye shes spyod yul ba /
NK116(le)001:8063: dus gsum rgyal ba'i yul la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK116(le)001:8066: blo yi cha nasa smra bsam brjod pa ru sgro
NK116(le)001:8067: btaggas shinga snang ba 'di kuna rdzoba bdena pa'i chara
NK116(le)001:8068: bazhaga nasa bdena pa gnyis po rtogsa bya rtogs byed
NK116(le)001:8069: du khas len pa bzhed kyang /
NK116(le)001:8071: chos nyid bshad ma thag pa ltar susa kyang mngona du byar meda la //
NK116(le)001:8072: bltar meda pa dang thoba dang ma thoba gnyis ka meda do //
NK116(le)001:8073: stong pa nyid dang ngesa para rjes su yang dag par mthuna pa'i /
NK116(le)001:8074: blo skyes pa la rtogsa so zhes pa'i bla dagas btagsa pa'o //
NK116(le)001:8075: de bas na chos thams cad rten cing 'brel bar
NK116(le)001:8076: 'byung ba'i rang bzhin nyid du shes na de kho
NK116(le)001:8077: na nyid mngon par rtogs pa'i tshul gang zhig zhes
NK116(le)001:8078: bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:8079: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos gang dang gang zhiga rten cing 'brel 'byung du grub par gsungs pa ni /
NK116(le)001:8080: lung gi chos rnams ma lusa pa kuna gyi gsang
NK116(le)001:8081: mdzoda yin pa ganga la bsam pa'i shesa raba kyis
NK116(le)001:8082: / yang dag par 'juga pa shes bya thams cad
NK116(le)001:8083: kyi sgo 'phar rab tu phye ba'i lde miga lta
NK116(le)001:8084: / bu yina te / rtsa ba shes rab kyi lung sngar drangs ba bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:8085: rten 'brel la yang nang gses su dbye na /
NK116(le)001:8086: gshes sam gnas lugs rten cing 'brel pa ni snang srid ces bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:8087: de yang snang srid 'khora 'adsa kyi chosa rnams ma lus pa kuna //
NK116(le)001:8088: phyogs bcu dus gsum ganga nasa kyang ni ma 'ongas la /
NK116(le)001:8089: ganga du ma songa zhing mi gansa pa ni gnyug
NK116(le)001:8090: ma'i gshisa la gansa pa'i rten cing 'brel bar 'byung
NK116(le)001:8091: ba chosa cana nyid kyang skye 'agga gnas gsum byed
NK116(le)001:8093: snang ba'i dusa de nyid nasa stong par shara zhing /
NK116(le)001:8094: spros pa'i matha'a thams cad la mi gnas pa de
NK116(le)001:8095: ni dbu ma'i ranga bzhina ji lta ba nyid du
NK116(le)001:8099: de ni stong pa nyid du bshad /
NK116(le)001:8100: de la rten nas gdags pa ste /
NK116(le)001:8101: de nyid dbu ma'i lam yin no //
NK116(le)001:8102: zhes de lta'i lam gyi spros pa gcod pa'i tshul
NK116(le)001:8103: dag dang zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te
NK116(le)001:8104: / tshul rol mthong ba'i snang ngor daga pa dang /
NK116(le)001:8105: ma daga pa sna tshogs glo bur du shar ba rnams /
NK116(le)001:8106: dona la ri bong gi ra bzhin meda kyang /
NK116(le)001:8107: gzugs bsnyan ltar meda bzhina snang ba la bden med
NK116(le)001:8108: du ma shes par kuna tu btagsa pasa nye bar
NK116(le)001:8109: lena cing / gal te lam du zhugs na'ang rtog cinga dpyod pasa matha'a bzhi byung ba ni /
NK116(le)001:8114: gal te mu bzhi po de las 'das par sgom
NK116(le)001:8115: du re yang dbus la mchog 'dzin byas te de
NK116(le)001:8116: gansa pa'i grub mtha' bzung na'nga makhasa pa mina te
NK116(le)001:8117: / mtha' gcig tu lhung ba'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:8119: rtog can dag gis yod dang med ces btags /
NK116(le)001:8120: de ltar dpyod pas sdug bsngal zhi mi 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:8121: yod dang med ces bya ba gnyis ka mtha'/
NK116(le)001:8122: gtsang dang mi gtsang 'di yang mtha' yin ste /
NK116(le)001:8123: mkhas pas dbus la'ang gnas pa yod mi 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:8125: 'jig rten 'di na mi mkhas pa dag ji ltar
NK116(le)001:8126: dara gyi srin bu ste sdom srin gyis thag rgya
NK116(le)001:8127: bran tshe thabs pa'i skyon gyis rang gi rkang lag
NK116(le)001:8128: kha chu'i dar skud kyis 'ching ba bzhina du //
NK116(le)001:8129: phyogs re ba'i 'doda pa'i gruba matha'a ngan pasa ranga gi sems nyid bcingsa bar zad do //
NK116(le)001:8130: de'i phyir mtha' bral dbu ma'i shes rab rnon pos thams cad gtan la phab tshe /
NK116(le)001:8131: 'di na blo yisa btagsa pa'i chos kun /
NK116(le)001:8136: de nas 'onga zhes bya ba yod pa mina te /
NK116(le)001:8137: ci'i phyir na dona gciga ma yina zhing /
NK116(le)001:8139: rtag pa yang ma yina te chada pa'ang mina no //
NK116(le)001:8141: sprosa pa matha'a daga nye bar zhi ba'i /
NK116(le)001:8142: ranga bzhina gsal stong chos kyi dbyings nyid du shesa pa ni /
NK116(le)001:8143: thos bsam las byung ba'i shesa raba kyi ngo bo yina no //
NK116(le)001:8144: de yang lang ka'i mdo las dngos por shes pa'i sgra 'dzin pa /
NK116(le)001:8145: ji ltar dar gyi srin bu bzhin /
NK116(le)001:8146: byis pa mtshams sbyor mi mkhas pa /
NK116(le)001:8147: rang gi grub mtha' ngan pas 'chings /
NK116(le)001:8149: dbu ma rin chen sgron ma las /
NK116(le)001:8150: khas blangs pa yi dngos po ni /
NK116(le)001:8151: phra rab tsam yang yod min te /
NK116(le)001:8152: gdod nas skye ba med pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:8153: mo gsham gyis ni bu bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:8154: dper na bud med mo gsham la /
NK116(le)001:8155: khyod kyi bu ni gang yin dris //
NK116(le)001:8156: de la de ni yod min pas //
NK116(le)001:8157: smra ba nus pa ma yin no //
NK116(le)001:8160: snang yul zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te //
NK116(le)001:8161: snang yula 'dir sa chu me rlung nam mkha'a ste 'byung ba lnga dang //
NK116(le)001:8162: de la brten nas ri dang nagas tshala dang //
NK116(le)001:8163: khanga bu brtsegas pa sogs 'dusa byas kyi rgyu lasa thams cada skyesa pas na //
NK116(le)001:8164: 'khora ba yang rten cinga 'brel par 'byung ba yina no //
NK116(le)001:8166: ma rig ces bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:8167: 'khor ba'i rgyu ma riga pa lasa 'du byed de //
NK116(le)001:8168: de bazhana rnam par shes pa dang /
NK116(le)001:8178: 'chi ba rnams gciga la gciga brten gyis /
NK116(le)001:8179: rga shi'i bar du rim bzhin 'brel ba ni /
NK116(le)001:8180: nanga gi rten cing 'brela bar 'byung ba'o //
NK116(le)001:8181: de la dbye na gnas skabs pa'i rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba dang /
NK116(le)001:8185: tshe gsum gyis bsdus pa dang /
NK116(le)001:8186: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i tshul gnyis kyis bsdus pa dang /
NK116(le)001:8187: kun nas nyon mongs pa gsum gyis bsdus pa zhes bya bar shes par bya'o //
NK116(le)001:8188: de la gnas skabs pa ni /
NK116(le)001:8189: skye ba snga ma'i nyon mongs pa spyod pa'i gnas
NK116(le)001:8190: skabs kyi phung po lnga la ma rig pa zhes
NK116(le)001:8191: bya ste / ma rig pa gtso che ba'i phyir de skad du brjod do //
NK116(le)001:8192: 'og ma rnams la'ang gtso bo'i ming gis 'du byed
NK116(le)001:8193: la sogs par brtags te thams cad du phung po
NK116(le)001:8194: lnga lnga pa yin no zhes shes par bya'o //
NK116(le)001:8195: 'du byed ni skye ba snga ma'i las dge ba dang /
NK116(le)001:8196: mi dge ba byed pa'i gnas skabs kyi phung po lnga'o //
NK116(le)001:8197: rnam par shes pa ni de dag gis 'phangs pa'i
NK116(le)001:8198: rnam par shes pa skye ba'i srid par nying mtshams
NK116(le)001:8199: sbyor ba'i gnas skabs kyi phung po lnga'o //
NK116(le)001:8200: ming dang gzugs ni mngal du skyes nas mig la
NK116(le)001:8201: sogs pa ma dod gyi bar gyi phung po lnga
NK116(le)001:8202: ste / ming ni tshor ba dang /
NK116(le)001:8205: rnam par shes pa'i phung po bzhi dang //
NK116(le)001:8206: gzugs ni mngal gyi gnas skabs kyi nur nur po dang //
NK116(le)001:8210: rkang lag dkyus pa ste lnga'o //
NK116(le)001:8212: mngal du mig la sogs pa dod pa nas bzung ste /
NK116(le)001:8213: gsum 'dus nas yul yongs su dpyod mi shes pa'i bar gyi phung po lnga'o /
NK116(le)001:8217: rnam par shes pa gsum 'dus nas yul yongs su
NK116(le)001:8218: dpyod nas bde ba dang sdug bsngal gyi rgyu mi
NK116(le)001:8219: shes pa'i bar gyi phung po lnga'o //
NK116(le)001:8220: tshor ba ni bde ba dang sdug bsngal gyi rgyu shes pa'i byis pa'i dus nas bzung ste /
NK116(le)001:8221: 'khrig pa la spyod mi nus pa'i bar gyi phung po lnga'o //
NK116(le)001:8222: sred pa ni 'khrig la longs spyod nus pa'i gnas skabs kyi phung po lnga ste /
NK116(le)001:8223: lang tsho rgyas pa'i gnas skabs so //
NK116(le)001:8224: len pa ni bde ba'i rgyu nor dang /
NK116(le)001:8225: 'bru la sogs pa la sred pa 'phel ba te /
NK116(le)001:8226: de dag thob par bya ba'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:8228: tshong khe la sogs pa la rgyug pa'i gnas skabs kyi phung po lnga'o //
NK116(le)001:8230: de ltar len cing las byed pa na srid pa
NK116(le)001:8231: phyi mar 'phen pa'i las sogs pa'i gnas skabs kyi
NK116(le)001:8232: phung po lnga'o // skye ba ni 'di nas shing
NK116(le)001:8233: 'a phos nas phyi mar nyin mtshams sbyar ba'i gnas
NK116(le)001:8235: rga shi ni skye ba phyi ma'i ming dang gzugs
NK116(le)001:8236: nas tshor ba'i gzhi'i gnas skabs kyi phung po lnga
NK116(le)001:8237: yin te / gnas skabs pa'i rten cing 'brel ba
NK116(le)001:8238: 'byung ba ni bye brag tu smra bas 'dod la
NK116(le)001:8239: yin te / / de nyid rgyun chags dang 'brel pa'ang yin no zhes zer ro //
NK116(le)001:8240: mdo sde bas gnas skabs kyi rten cing 'brel ba
NK116(le)001:8241: 'byung ba mi 'dod kyi rgyun chags pa 'di ltar
NK116(le)001:8242: 'dod de / ma rig pa ni rig pa'i mi
NK116(le)001:8243: mthun phyogs su gyur ba'i sems las byung ba ste
NK116(le)001:8244: 'dod de / / 'du byed kun nas slong ba'i rgyu /
NK116(le)001:8245: 'du byed des kun nas bslang ba'i las bsod nams dang /
NK116(le)001:8246: bsod nams ma yin pa dang mi g.yo ba'o //
NK116(le)001:8247: rnam par shes pa ni las de dag gis rnam par shes pa skye ba'i gnas su 'phangs ba'o /
NK116(le)001:8248: ming dang gzugs ni mngal du 'phangs pa'i phung po lnga'o /
NK116(le)001:8249: skye mched drug ni mig la sogs pa dod pa'o /
NK116(le)001:8252: rnam par shes pa gsum 'dus pa las yul yongs su dpyod pa'i sems las byung ba'o //
NK116(le)001:8253: tshor ba ni de las skyes pa'i bde ba dang /
NK116(le)001:8256: sred pa ni bde ba'i yul la chags pa'o //
NK116(le)001:8257: len pa ni yul de don du gnyer ba'o //
NK116(le)001:8258: srid pa ni de dag gis kun nas bslangs bas
NK116(le)001:8259: skye ba phyi ma 'grub pa'i las la sogs pa'o
NK116(le)001:8260: // skye ba ni las des skye ba phyi mar nyid mtshams sbyor ba'o //
NK116(le)001:8261: rga shi ni tshe phyi mar skye shing tshe mthar phyin nas yang 'chi bar 'gyur ba yin la /
NK116(le)001:8262: 'brel ba'i rten 'brel yang de nyid yin par 'dod do //
NK116(le)001:8263: skad cig ma'i rten 'brel ni skad cig la'ang rten
NK116(le)001:8264: cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i yan lag bcu gnyis tshangs
NK116(le)001:8265: pa ste / 'ga' zhig srog gcod pa na der
NK116(le)001:8266: kun nas slong ba'i ma rig pa yang yod la
NK116(le)001:8267: pa ste / / 'du byed kyi srog gcod pa nyid yin pa dang /
NK116(le)001:8268: de'i tshe yul rig pa rnam shes dang /
NK116(le)001:8269: phung po lnga yod pa'i ming dang gzugs dang /
NK116(le)001:8270: mig la sogs pa skye ma ched drug dang /
NK116(le)001:8271: gsum 'dus nas yul gcod pa reg pa dang /
NK116(le)001:8272: bde ba la sogs pa myong ba'i tshor ba dang /
NK116(le)001:8273: sha la sogs pa la sred pa dang /
NK116(le)001:8274: de shas cher 'phel ba'i len pa dang //
NK116(le)001:8275: srog gcod pa la de nyid las mthu ldan gyi srid pa dang /
NK116(le)001:8277: 'gyur ba rga shi yin pa bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:8278: tshe gsum gyis bsdus pa la ma rig pa dang /
NK116(le)001:8279: 'du byed ni skye ba snga mas bsdus te rgyu'i yan lag go /
NK116(le)001:8281: ming dang gzugs dang skye mched drug dang /
NK116(le)001:8283: tshor ba ni tshe 'dis bsdus te 'bras bu'i yan lag go /
NK116(le)001:8286: srid pa gsum yang tshe 'dis bsdus te /
NK116(le)001:8287: phyi ma skye ba'i rgyu'i yan lag go /
NK116(le)001:8289: rga shi ni tshe phyi mas bsdus te /
NK116(le)001:8291: de ltar na tshe snga ma la gnyis dang /
NK116(le)001:8293: phyi ma la gnyis dang bcu gnyis yin no //
NK116(le)001:8294: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i tshul ni gnyis te /
NK116(le)001:8297: de la sngon gyi mtha' pa ni ma rig pa nyon mongs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:8299: de gnyis ni rgyu yin no //
NK116(le)001:8300: de gnyis las skye ba 'di'i rnam par shes pa dang /
NK116(le)001:8304: tshor ba dang lnga skye ste /
NK116(le)001:8305: 'bras bu'i yan lag yin pas de ni rgyu dang 'bras bu tshar gcig yin no //
NK116(le)001:8307: len pa nyon mongs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:8309: de gsum ni phyi ma'i rgyu yin no //
NK116(le)001:8310: de dag las skye ba phyi ma'i skye ba dang /
NK116(le)001:8312: 'bras bu'i yan lag yin pas de ni rgyu 'bras tshar gcig yin te /
NK116(le)001:8313: de ltar na rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i yan
NK116(le)001:8314: lag bcu gnyis kyang rgyu dang 'bras bu tshar gnyis
NK116(le)001:8315: kyis bsdus pa'o // nyon mongs gsum gyis bsdus pa ni /
NK116(le)001:8318: len pa ni nyon mongs pa'i kun 'byung yin no //
NK116(le)001:8319: 'du byed ni srid pa las kyi kun 'byung yin no /
NK116(le)001:8320: rnam par shes pa la sogs pa bdun ni skye ba'i kun 'byung yin no //
NK116(le)001:8321: de'ang las dang nyon mongs pa ni kun 'byung gi bden pa dang /
NK116(le)001:8322: skye ba'i kun 'byung ni sdug bsngal bden pa yin no //
NK116(le)001:8323: de 'gog pa'i rten 'brel myang 'das zhes bya la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:8324: mya ngana 'adsa pa'i rten cinga 'brel 'byung ni /
NK116(le)001:8325: lam dang 'brasa bu gnyis su gansa pa la lam
NK116(le)001:8326: ni 'khora ba'i rten cing 'brela ba bshad zin pa
NK116(le)001:8327: ltar lugas su 'juga pa bcu gnyis kyi /
NK116(le)001:8328: rtsa ba ma riga chena po'i bar yin no //
NK116(le)001:8329: de dag ni riga pa'i ya shesa kyisa ldoga pasa /
NK116(le)001:8330: 'du byed la sogas gazhana rnams kyang /
NK116(le)001:8331: lugas las ldoga ste bsgom pas srid pa'i rtsa ba choda par 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:8333: matshana nyid mthonga ba'i skyes bu de yisa /
NK116(le)001:8334: sdug bsngal shesa shing kuna 'byung spong ste /
NK116(le)001:8335: 'goga pa mngona du gyur ba dang lam /
NK116(le)001:8338: ma rig 'gags par gyur na ni //
NK116(le)001:8341: shes pas de nyid bsgom pa'o //
NK116(le)001:8342: de dang de ni 'gag gyur bas //
NK116(le)001:8343: de dang de ni mngon mi 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:8344: sdug bsngal phung po 'ba' zhig pa //
NK116(le)001:8345: de ni de ltar yang dag 'gags /
NK116(le)001:8347: de ltar snang ba dang snang yul thams cad skye ba meda pa'i ngang du /
NK116(le)001:8349: bsam pasa gtan la phaba pa de'i tshe /
NK116(le)001:8350: ranga bzhina shes pa'i chosa nyid mngon du 'gyur ba la /
NK116(le)001:8351: sgoma pa'i shesa raba cesa su gragsa so //
NK116(le)001:8352: de'i dus na nama mkha'a rnam para daga pa'i dbyingsa lta bu de bsgoma pa'i ngo bo yin la /
NK116(le)001:8353: sgom bya sgom byed med par dona de dang ro gciga tu gyur pa na /
NK116(le)001:8354: gshis de la gzugas sogas phunga po lnga dang /
NK116(le)001:8355: rnam par shes pa'i tshogsa brgyad kuna kyang yoda pa ma yina no //
NK116(le)001:8356: 'o na ci yang med pa yin nam zhe na /
NK116(le)001:8358: meda cesa blo yisa bkag para gyur na /
NK116(le)001:8359: shesa raba nyid dang lhag para 'agla ste /
NK116(le)001:8360: ci'i phyir na canga meda par bltas na chada pa
NK116(le)001:8361: nyid du thal bas de lta bu ma yina par
NK116(le)001:8362: / sku gsum dang ye shesa lnga sogs yon tan kuna gyi mdzoda chen po yin te /
NK116(le)001:8364: ji ltar sngon bzhin phyis de bzhin /
NK116(le)001:8365: 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid do /
NK116(le)001:8368: chos kyi dbyings ni skye ba min //
NK116(le)001:8370: dus rnams kun du nyon mongs med /
NK116(le)001:8371: thog ma bar mtha' dri ma bral /
NK116(le)001:8373: chos thams cad ranga bzhina skye 'gags med pa nyid du rnam para daga pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:8374: ngo bo yang dag pa nyid la lta ba yang dag pa nyid kyis blta ste /
NK116(le)001:8375: blta zhesa bya ba'ang kuna rdzoba tshig gi bla dwags tsam ste /
NK116(le)001:8376: gnas lugs kyi ngang du de lasa ma g.yosa pa sgom pa'i mchoga yin no /
NK116(le)001:8377: gang zag de blo yisa mdun na snyem byed kyi
NK116(le)001:8378: blo dang ni the tshom sogs yida la byed pa
NK116(le)001:8379: thamsa cad gansa pa ma yina te /
NK116(le)001:8381: 'di la bsal bya ci yang med /
NK116(le)001:8382: bzhag par bya ba cung zad med //
NK116(le)001:8383: yang dag nyid la yang dag blta //
NK116(le)001:8384: yang dag mthong na rnam par grol /
NK116(le)001:8386: kha gcig so sor rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis mthar
NK116(le)001:8387: 'dzin gyi skyon thams cad bsal te yang dag pa
NK116(le)001:8388: la 'jug pa la dpyad sgom zhes skur ba 'debs
NK116(le)001:8389: pa nii rmongs ba'i gtam ste /
NK116(le)001:8390: mdo las 'od srung bdag ces bya ba 'di ni
NK116(le)001:8391: mtha' gcig go bdag med ces bya ba 'di ni
NK116(le)001:8392: mtha' gnyis so // 'od srung yod ces bya ba mtha' gcig go /
NK116(le)001:8393: med ces bya ba 'di ni mtha' gnyis so //
NK116(le)001:8394: de gnyis kyi dbus mtha' gang yin pa de ni dpyad du med pa bstan du med pa /
NK116(le)001:8397: rnam par rig pa med pa /
NK116(le)001:8399: 'od srung 'di ni dbu ma'i chos rnams la so sor rtogs pa'o //
NK116(le)001:8400: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs pa bzhin yang dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK116(le)001:8401: shes rab kyis ji ltar gtsub shing gtsub pa'i mes
NK116(le)001:8402: shing rang nyid bsreg pa bzhin sgrib gnyis phra rags
NK116(le)001:8405: gang tshe ting 'dzin rdo rje yis //
NK116(le)001:8406: bum pa de ni bcag gyur ba //
NK116(le)001:8407: de tshe de ni nam mkha' yi //
NK116(le)001:8408: mthar thug bar du snang bar byed /
NK116(le)001:8410: kha gcig ci yang mi dmigs pa bsgom pa ni ha shang gi lta ba'am /
NK116(le)001:8411: lung ma bstan du 'khrul pa ni tha snyad kyi
NK116(le)001:8412: g.yengs pas rnam rig la sha thang gcod par kho
NK116(le)001:8413: nar zad do // mdo sdud pa las //
NK116(le)001:8414: byang chub sems dpa'i sngon gyi mtha' dang phyi mtha' dang //
NK116(le)001:8415: da lta byung ba mi dmigs dus gsum dag pa ste //
NK116(le)001:8416: gang dag de ni 'dus ma byas yin spros med de //
NK116(le)001:8417: 'di ni shes rab pha rol phyin mchog spyod pa yin /
NK116(le)001:8419: so sor rtogs pa'i lta ba'ang yang dag yin la //
NK116(le)001:8420: mi rtog pa'i lta ba'ang yang dag yin pa 'di
NK116(le)001:8421: ji ltar mthun snyam na mnyam par bzhag pa'i khyad
NK116(le)001:8422: chos ma mthong ba'i ring la re bden /
NK116(le)001:8423: kho bo cag gi bla ma'i byin rlabs kyis cung zad go tshul ltar na /
NK116(le)001:8424: 'di ltar gnyis snang spros pa rang spyi'i mtshan nyid
NK116(le)001:8425: kyis stong ste byed po med pa'i cha nas mi
NK116(le)001:8426: dmigs pa dang / gdangs kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal
NK116(le)001:8427: ba ji snyed mkhyen pa'i cha ma 'gags pa tsam
NK116(le)001:8428: zhig la so sor rtogs pa'i shes rab tha snyad
NK116(le)001:8429: du gdags pa las don la de tsam gyi khas
NK116(le)001:8431: don dam pa blo yi spyod yul du 'das pa ni /
NK116(le)001:8433: gang tshe dngos dang dngos min pa //
NK116(le)001:8434: blo yi mdun na mi gnas pa //
NK116(le)001:8435: de tshe rnam pa gzhan med pas /
NK116(le)001:8436: dmigs pa med pa rab tu zhi /
NK116(le)001:8438: kha gcig klu dbang yab sras kyis bzhed pa'i thal
NK116(le)001:8439: 'gyur dbu ma'i lta ba re zhig tha snyad bzlog
NK116(le)001:8440: pa'i phyir byas pas regs pa phyi'i dbu ma yin
NK116(le)001:8441: la / thogs med kyi bzhed pa'i /
NK116(le)001:8442: gzhan stong phra ba nang gi dbu ma mthar thug
NK116(le)001:8443: pa yin pas snga ma las ches 'phags par tha
NK116(le)001:8444: snyad pa dag phan tshun rnam dpyod kyi rtsal 'gran
NK116(le)001:8445: te / mkhyen pa'i tshod brgal ba yin na ma
NK116(le)001:8446: gtogs ci bzhin du bzung na bstan pa rin po
NK116(le)001:8447: che'i don gyi dbyings ma 'jal ba'i mngon rtog du
NK116(le)001:8448: te / zad de / ci'i phyir na /
NK116(le)001:8449: shes bya shes byed kyis btags pa'i grub pa'i matha'i
NK116(le)001:8450: spros pa dang bral ba'i cha nas shing rta chen
NK116(le)001:8451: po gnyis ka rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes
NK116(le)001:8452: kyang bzhed pa ma yin te /
NK116(le)001:8454: slob dpon 'phags pa thog med ni //
NK116(le)001:8455: yang dag par na gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyang mi bzhed la /
NK116(le)001:8456: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyi rjes la
NK116(le)001:8457: thob pa yang mi bzhed de sa gsum pa'i dbang
NK116(le)001:8458: phyug brnyes pas chos thams cad skye ba med par
NK116(le)001:8459: thugs su chud ba'i phyir ro /
NK116(le)001:8461: chos kyi dbyings gcig dang du ma'i yul las 'das pa de'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:8463: gal te mi stong cung zad yod //
NK116(le)001:8464: stong pa'ang cung zad yod par 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:8465: mi stong cung zad med pa na //
NK116(le)001:8466: stong pa yod par ga la 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:8467: zhes dang mnyam par bzhag dang ma bzhag pa //
NK116(le)001:8468: gang la 'di dag thams cad med //
NK116(le)001:8469: dngos dang dngos med rnams spang ba /
NK116(le)001:8470: zung 'jug yin par ston pas gsungs //
NK116(le)001:8472: kha gcig 'di la chad lta'i dogs pa skye ba yang blo gros tsing ba'i skyon te /
NK116(le)001:8478: de thams cad las 'das par gyur na skyon ji ltar yod /
NK116(le)001:8479: gal te dbyings de bzhin nyid kyi gshis na rgyal
NK116(le)001:8480: ba'i yon tan lhun gyi grub par ma sgrub par
NK116(le)001:8481: rang chas yod par mthar phyin gyi thob byar sgrub
NK116(le)001:8483: de mngon du byed pa la rnam par mi rtogs pa'i lta ba 'thad dam /
NK116(le)001:8485: dang po ltar na bshad ma thag pa las ma 'das la /
NK116(le)001:8486: phyi ma ltar na dpyad pa che ste bsam gtan
NK116(le)001:8487: dang ru ta phal cher sgom tshul gol ba'i skyon
NK116(le)001:8488: gyis ma rung bar gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:8489: gal te mnyam bzhag gi rgyu snga ma ltar sgom mod te /
NK116(le)001:8490: rjes thob la sku dang ye shes yod par 'bod dgos zhe na'ang /
NK116(le)001:8492: 'bras dus kyi ye shes kyi sku de chos can /
NK116(le)001:8493: ye nas lhun gyis grub pa zhig yin nam //
NK116(le)001:8494: lam dus dmigs pa'i rkyen las skye bar 'dod grang /
NK116(le)001:8495: phyi ma ltar na de ltar 'thad du rung gis la /
NK116(le)001:8496: dang por nges nas dmigs med kyi lta sgom de
NK116(le)001:8497: 'ba' zhig mthar phyin pa'i pha rol na 'bras bu
NK116(le)001:8498: la thug pa med pa des cho ga mod //
NK116(le)001:8499: sems rnam rtog gi rnyog par bcas te ye shes
NK116(le)001:8500: yod par ma bsgom kyang skyon 'bab pa ma sems
NK116(le)001:8501: so // de bas kyang rtag chad kyi mtha' sgrub
NK116(le)001:8502: pa las yang dag pa'i lam re bsgom na legs
NK116(le)001:8503: so // par snyam mo // 'dir smras pa /
NK116(le)001:8504: 'o na thal 'gyur gyi lta ba lam gyi gzhi rnam dag las 'bras bu min nam zhe na /
NK116(le)001:8506: bzhin bzang dag ma brtag bla rdol du smra ba 'di 'os sam /
NK116(le)001:8507: sangs rgyas kyi ji lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes
NK116(le)001:8508: 'bras bu yin nam min na de ltar 'khrul ba'i
NK116(le)001:8510: de las ldog na lta ba de'i ngos na /
NK116(le)001:8511: sangs rgyas sam ye shes yod med kyi dmigs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:8514: gang zhig yod pa ma yin de ni med ces bya /
NK116(le)001:8515: byis pa rnams kyis de brtags yod dang med par 'dzin yod dang /
NK116(le)001:8516: yod dang med pa 'di gnyis med pa'i chos can te /
NK116(le)001:8517: 'di ni shes rab pha rol phyin mchog spyod pa yin /
NK116(le)001:8519: ji ltar 'dren pa 'dus ma byas khams mi gnas shing /
NK116(le)001:8520: de bzhin 'dus byas la yang mi gnas gnas med spyod /
NK116(le)001:8521: de ltar byang chub sems dpa' gnas la gnas med gnas /
NK116(le)001:8522: gnas med gnas yin 'di ni rgyal ba'i gnas par gsungs /
NK116(le)001:8523: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i phyir na thal 'gyur lta ba 'bras bu 'thad pa dpyad bzod pa kho na'o //
NK116(le)001:8524: 'di la rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas las tshad mar gyur
NK116(le)001:8525: ba gzhan du med na su la phrag pa dog
NK116(le)001:8526: / tshur mthong gi blo gros rno yang /
NK116(le)001:8527: slob dpon 'phags pa'i gzhung la rgol ba nam mkha'
NK116(le)001:8528: spar bas 'dzin du re ba dang mtshungs par zad
NK116(le)001:8529: do // lta ba 'dis yon tan 'og tu lam
NK116(le)001:8530: thun mongs ma yin pa rdzogs chen khreg chod kyi
NK116(le)001:8531: skabs su rgya cher ston par 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:8532: thabs shes zung du 'brel dgos pa shes rab ces bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:8533: shesa raba de 'dra ba yongas su shesa par byas nasa /
NK116(le)001:8534: thabsa kyi cha snying rje chen po dang zung du 'jug pas rnama para grol bar 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:8535: yang dag lhag mthong gi shesa raba meda pa'i thabas phyogs gcig tsam kyisa ni /
NK116(le)001:8536: nyon mongs pa'i sbubs su bcingas pa nyid lasa /
NK116(le)001:8537: nam yang grola bar meda do /
NK116(le)001:8538: tshul des ni sbyor dngos rjes gsum ganga du stong nyid dang /
NK116(le)001:8539: snying rje gnyis po rgyud la brtena nas sbyin sogs
NK116(le)001:8540: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs mtha' dag bsgrub
NK116(le)001:8541: pa la 'jug pa tshogs kyi lam chung 'bring che
NK116(le)001:8542: gsum gyi thun mong gi bslab bya dang /
NK116(le)001:8543: sbyor lam chosa mchoga mana chada du /
NK116(le)001:8544: mnyam bazhaga dang rjesa thob gnyis la stong nyid dang snying rje go rim ltar 'achara ba yin la /
NK116(le)001:8545: mthonga lam thoba nasa stong nyid snying rje gnyis po
NK116(le)001:8546: ni rjes thob dus su'ang zunga du 'juga cinga 'du
NK116(le)001:8547: 'bral meda cing / de'i dus raba tu dag'a ba
NK116(le)001:8548: dang po'i sara slebs pa'i chosa nyid kyi bdena pa
NK116(le)001:8549: mngona gsuma du mthonga bar 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:8550: de'i skabs kyi spangs bya ni /
NK116(le)001:8551: kun brtags kyi nyon mongs drug la /
NK116(le)001:8562: tshul khrims dang brtul zhugs la mchog tu 'dzin pa'i blta ba /
NK116(le)001:8563: lta ba la mchog tu 'dzin pa'i lta ba'o //
NK116(le)001:8564: snga phyi sdom pa'i rtsa ba'i nyon mongs pa bcu
NK116(le)001:8565: po de 'dod khams na bden bzhi re re la
NK116(le)001:8567: khams gong ma gnyis na khong khro las gzhan pa
NK116(le)001:8568: dgu dgu yod pa bden bzhis phye ba'i sum cu
NK116(le)001:8569: rtsa drug pa gnyis snga ma dang sdom pas brgya
NK116(le)001:8570: dang bcu gnyis lam gyi ye shes skye 'gyur gyis
NK116(le)001:8571: rags pa brgyud nas spangs la /
NK116(le)001:8572: skye bzhin pa'i phra ba dngos su spangs pa yin no //
NK116(le)001:8573: de lta'i mthong lam bgrod zin pa'i 'og de nasa 'aphagas pa'i sgoma lam du /
NK116(le)001:8574: chung 'bring che gsum la nang gses kyis dbye bas dgu ste /
NK116(le)001:8576: nyon mongs pa bag la nyal ba'i lhan skyes las phye na drug ste /
NK116(le)001:8583: 'dod khams na drug po rnams re re la che 'bring chung gsum ste bco brgyad /
NK116(le)001:8584: de'ang re re bzhin de ltar phye bas lnga bcu rtsa bzhi /
NK116(le)001:8585: gzugs khams na khong khro bor ba'i lhag ma lnga
NK116(le)001:8586: la snga ma ltar bsgrang bas bzhi bcu zhe lnga
NK116(le)001:8587: / bsam gtan bzhi bzhi'i grangs kyis phye bas brgya dang brgyad bcu /
NK116(le)001:8588: gzugs med bzhi la'ang de bzhin brgya dang brgyad cu ste /
NK116(le)001:8589: khams gong ma gnyis bsdoms pas sum brgya drug cu
NK116(le)001:8590: la 'dod pa'i lnga cu rtsa bzhi bsnan pas bzhi
NK116(le)001:8592: de nas sa bcu rgyun gyi tha ma la /
NK116(le)001:8594: rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzina gyisa /
NK116(le)001:8595: shesa bya'i sgriba pa'i bag chags phra mo bcoma nasa
NK116(le)001:8596: skad cig der mthar thug gi 'bras bu la mngona
NK116(le)001:8597: par byang chuba pa'i tshe thugs mnyam para ma bazhaga
NK116(le)001:8598: meda para sogas le'u drug pas bstan pa ltar rgyala
NK116(le)001:8599: ba'i ma 'dresa pa'i chosa bco brgyad dang /
NK116(le)001:8600: stobsa bcu dang ni mi 'jigas pa bzhi la sogs
NK116(le)001:8601: pa'i yon tan matha'a daga pa mngona du gyur te
NK116(le)001:8602: yang daga par sangsa rgyas par yina no /
NK116(le)001:8604: rten sku brten pa ye shes /
NK116(le)001:8605: mdzad pa phrin las te gsum /
NK116(le)001:8614: shin tu rnam par dag pa'i dbyings dag mnyam chen
NK116(le)001:8615: po sku gsum gyi chos nyid byed pa'i cha ste
NK116(le)001:8617: thub pa'i ngo bo nyid sku ni //
NK116(le)001:8618: zag pa med pa'i chos gang dag /
NK116(le)001:8619: thob gyur rnam kun rnam dag pa //
NK116(le)001:8620: de dag rang bzhin mtshan nyid can /
NK116(le)001:8623: glo bur gyi sgrib pa sprin lta bu dengs pa
NK116(le)001:8624: na dbyings de nyid kyi rang gdangs 'dus ma byas
NK116(le)001:8626: nyi mkha' bzhin te ye shes dang /
NK116(le)001:8627: spangs rtog gnyis kyi mtshan nyid de /
NK116(le)001:8628: 'od gsal bya min dbyer med pa /
NK116(le)001:8629: 'jug can gang ga'i klung gi ni /
NK116(le)001:8630: rdul las 'das pa'i sangs rgyas kyis /
NK116(le)001:8631: chos rnams kun dang ldan pa nyid /
NK116(le)001:8634: tshogs brgyad kun gzhi dang bcas pa dbyings su nub
NK116(le)001:8635: pa'i stobs kyi cha nas bzhag pa'i gzhi'i gnas lugs
NK116(le)001:8636: kyi snang cha'i yon tan mtha' dag rdzogs pa ni
NK116(le)001:8637: nges pa lnga dang ldan pa ste /
NK116(le)001:8638: gnas nges pa 'og min stug po bkod pa dang /
NK116(le)001:8639: 'khor nges pa sa bcu'i byang sems /
NK116(le)001:8640: chos nges pa theg pa chen po /
NK116(le)001:8641: ston pa nges pa rnam snang sogs rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas /
NK116(le)001:8642: dus nges pa rtag par rgyun gyi 'khor lor bzhugs pa'o //
NK116(le)001:8643: de yang mgon po byams pas //
NK116(le)001:8644: sna tshogs dam chos 'od zer mnga' ba'i sku //
NK116(le)001:8645: 'gro ba'i rnam grol don grub la brtson pa //
NK116(le)001:8646: mdzad pa yid bzhin nor bu'i rgyal bzhin te //
NK116(le)001:8647: sna tshogs dngos de de yi rang bzhin yin /
NK116(le)001:8649: zhi sku dpag bsam shing ltar gsal gyur la //
NK116(le)001:8650: yid bzhin nor bu ji ltar rnam mi rtog /'gro
NK116(le)001:8651: grol bar du 'jig rten 'byor slad rtag /'di ni
NK116(le)001:8652: spros dang bral la snang ba yin /
NK116(le)001:8655: ji ltar chu snod yod na zla gzugs 'char ba
NK116(le)001:8656: ltar gdul bya'i snang ngor sprul pa 'byung ba ni
NK116(le)001:8658: thugs rje chen pos 'jig rten mkhyen //
NK116(le)001:8659: 'jig rten kun la gzigs nas ni //
NK116(le)001:8660: chos kyi sku las ma g.yos par //
NK116(le)001:8661: sprul pa'i rang bzhin sna tshogs kyis //
NK116(le)001:8662: skye ba mngon par skye ba dang /
NK116(le)001:8663: dga' ldan gnas nas 'pho ba dang /
NK116(le)001:8664: lhums su zhugs dang bltam pa dang /
NK116(le)001:8665: bzo yi gnas la mkhas pa dang //
NK116(le)001:8666: btsun mo'i 'khor dgyes rol ba dang /
NK116(le)001:8667: nges 'byung dka' ba spyod pa dang //
NK116(le)001:8668: byang chub snying por gshegs pa dang //
NK116(le)001:8669: bdud sde bcom dang rdzogs par ni //
NK116(le)001:8670: byang chub chos kyi 'khor lo dang //
NK116(le)001:8671: mya ngan 'da' bar gshegs mdzad pa //
NK116(le)001:8672: yongs su ma dag zhing rnams su //
NK116(le)001:8673: srid pa ji srid gnas par ston //
NK116(le)001:8675: gnyis pa brten pa ye shes la gnyis te //
NK116(le)001:8676: chos nyid ji lta ba mkhyen pa chos can shes bya ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'o //
NK116(le)001:8678: za bzhi spros bral 'dus ma byas pa'i chos nyid mngon sum par thugs su chud pa ste /
NK116(le)001:8680: gang tshe 'dus byas 'dus ma byas dang dkar nag chos //
NK116(le)001:8681: shes rab rnam par bshig nas rdul tsam mi dmigs te //
NK116(le)001:8682: 'jig rten dag ni shes rab pha rol phyin grangs 'gro //
NK116(le)001:8683: nam mkha' gang la'ang cung zad mi gnas de dang 'dra /
NK116(le)001:8686: dmigs pa med pa'i shes rab kyis 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad cig char mkhyen te /
NK116(le)001:8688: rgyal ba'i ye shes bla med kyis //
NK116(le)001:8689: skad cig gis ni don kun rigs /
NK116(le)001:8692: nyi ma'i 'od zer cig btang bas //
NK116(le)001:8693: 'gro ba snang bar byed pa ltar //
NK116(le)001:8694: de bzhin shes bya thams cad la //
NK116(le)001:8695: sangs rgyas ye shes gcig char snang /
NK116(le)001:8697: gsum pa mdzad pa phrin las ni //
NK116(le)001:8699: gzhan gyi dbang gi nges 'byung dang //
NK116(le)001:8700: bdag dang sems can mtshungs gzigs dang //
NK116(le)001:8701: mdzad pa yongs su ma rdzogs phyir //
NK116(le)001:8702: 'khor ba ji srid mdzad mi chad /
NK116(le)001:8707: rdzu 'phrul bsam gyi mi khyab pas gdul ba'o //
NK116(le)001:8708: tshul de dag le'u bcu gsum pa'i skabs su'ang 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:8709: skabs kyi don bsdu ba ni //
NK116(le)001:8710: 'di ltar zhes bya ba la sogs pas gsungs te //
NK116(le)001:8711: 'di ltar legs par bshad zin pa'i pha rola phyin pa druga po ni //
NK116(le)001:8712: dus gsum du byon dang 'byon par 'gyur ba'i rgyal
NK116(le)001:8713: ba kuna gyi gzhunga lam gcig pu nyid du nges
NK116(le)001:8714: te / gong du bstan pa bzhin /
NK116(le)001:8716: spyod pa'ang shina tu rnama par daga pa rang snang
NK116(le)001:8717: don gyi 'oga mina tu 'gro ba ste 'tshang rgya
NK116(le)001:8719: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi le'u dgu ba'i 'grel ba'o ////
NK116(le)001:8720: da ni 'jig rten na rnyed par dka' ba gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa /
NK116(le)001:8721: gdul bya dbang po rnon po dag gi ched du ston pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:8722: byang chub ces bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:8723: de yang byang chub semas dpa'i bslab bya rgyu dang
NK116(le)001:8724: 'bras bu gnyis las snga ma rgya cher bstan zin
NK116(le)001:8725: la / 'dir phyi ma sngagas kyi thega pa ston te /
NK116(le)001:8726: de la mig gi rnam grangs 'brasa bu'am gzhan ni rdo rje'i thega pa dang /
NK116(le)001:8728: riga pa 'dzina pa yi sde snod ces gragas te /
NK116(le)001:8729: rgyu lasa khyad para 'aphagas pa zhig go /
NK116(le)001:8731: gsang ba lung bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK116(le)001:8732: rgyu la mos pa rgyu'i chos kyi /
NK116(le)001:8733: 'khor lo rab tu bskong byas nas /
NK116(le)001:8734: 'bras bu'i theg pa'i nye lam zhig /
NK116(le)001:8737: thabs kyi sgo mtha' yas pas /
NK116(le)001:8738: sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang dka' tshegs la mi ltos par 'grub tu rung ba'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:8739: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i tha snyed cis grags she na /
NK116(le)001:8742: snying po'i rgyud phyi ma las //
NK116(le)001:8743: mnyam nyid don rtogs rang rig rgyal po ni //
NK116(le)001:8744: bla med don rtogs thabs chen 'di dag tu /
NK116(le)001:8745: rgya mtsho chen por chu klung kun 'babs ltar /
NK116(le)001:8746: rnam thar theg pa bsam yas ma lus 'dus /
NK116(le)001:8748: gsang sngags spyi'i mtshan gzhi dang khyad chos rgyun chags zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:8750: rgyud ni rgyun chags zhes bya brjod //
NK116(le)001:8752: mya ngan 'das pa rgyud phyi ma /
NK116(le)001:8754: 'di ltar 'khor 'das gnyis pi wam gi rgyud ltar
NK116(le)001:8755: 'brel zhing rgyun chagas pa'i ngosa nasa rgyud kyi tha
NK116(le)001:8757: gzhi rgyud bde gshegs snying po dang /
NK116(le)001:8758: lam rgyud lta bsgom zung 'jug /'brasa bu'i rgyud sku dang ye shes te /
NK116(le)001:8759: de yang bskyed dang rdzogs pa'i rima pa gnyis la
NK116(le)001:8760: brten nas thabas dang shesa raba zung du 'brela ba'i
NK116(le)001:8761: phyir / rgyu'i theg pa ltar daka'a thuba mthu yisa
NK116(le)001:8762: mi gdunga zhing 'juga pa'i sgo yangas pa gang zhig
NK116(le)001:8763: dabnga po rnona po'i dabnga du byas pas brtula zhugas
NK116(le)001:8764: kyang shin tu myur ba ni /
NK116(le)001:8766: don gcig na yang ma rmongs dang /
NK116(le)001:8767: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang //
NK116(le)001:8768: dbang po rnon po'i dbang byas nas //
NK116(le)001:8769: sngags kyi theg pa khyad par 'phags /
NK116(le)001:8771: sngags rgyud la gong 'og gi rnam bzhag yod dam
NK116(le)001:8772: zhe na yongs su grags par rgyud sde bzhir phye
NK116(le)001:8773: ba dag / gang gi phyir du gsungs pa'i tshul
NK116(le)001:8774: dus la zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te
NK116(le)001:8775: ba dag / / dusa la dgongas pa ni /
NK116(le)001:8776: rdzogas ldana gyi dus na nyon mongs pa 'dod chags
NK116(le)001:8777: kyang shas chung bas gcig la gcig bltas pa tsam
NK116(le)001:8779: gsum ldan gyii dus na bgad pas tshim pa dang /
NK116(le)001:8780: gnyis ldan gyi dus na phan tshun reg pas tshim pa dang gsum na 'das pa'i dus dang /
NK116(le)001:8781: rtsod par ldan pa'i dus da lta ba la dbang
NK116(le)001:8782: po gnyis sbyor gyi 'dod chags yod la snga phyi
NK116(le)001:8783: bsdom pa'i dus bzhisa gnyen por gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:8785: rdzogs ldan dang po bya ba'i rgyud //
NK116(le)001:8786: gsum ldan gnyis pa spyod pa'i rgyud //
NK116(le)001:8787: gnyis ldan gsum pa rnal 'byor rgyud //
NK116(le)001:8788: rtsod ldan bzhi pa bla med rgyud do //
NK116(le)001:8789: dus bzhi la ni dgongs nas kyang //
NK116(le)001:8790: rgyud ni rnam pa bzhir bshad do //
NK116(le)001:8792: kha sbyor gyi brtags pa drug pa'i rab dbye gsum pa las //
NK116(le)001:8793: dgod dang bltas dang lag bcangs dang //
NK116(le)001:8794: gnyis gnyis 'khyud pa rnam pa bzhi //
NK116(le)001:8795: srin bu'i tshul gyi rgyud bzhir gnas /
NK116(le)001:8797: riga la dgongas pa ni spyod pa'i sgo nas dbye ste /
NK116(le)001:8798: 'di ltar brama ze rnams gtsang sbra dang dka' thub la spyod pa de'i phyir dang /
NK116(le)001:8799: rje'u rigas ni sgo gsum cha mnyam pa'i spyod pa la bzo bas de'i phyir dang /
NK116(le)001:8800: rgyal po'i rigs kyi rgya che ba la mos pa'i
NK116(le)001:8801: sems kyi las gtso bor spyod pas de'i phyir dang
NK116(le)001:8802: ni / damngas rigs sama gdola ba ni gtsang sbra
NK116(le)001:8803: chung zhing nyon mong pa'i brtul zhugs che bas de'i
NK116(le)001:8804: ni / phyir ste bzhi'o // bde mchog rol ba'i rgyud las //
NK116(le)001:8805: bya ba bram ze gtsang dang bstun //
NK116(le)001:8806: spyod pa rje rigs de bas lhag /
NK116(le)001:8808: gzhi rmongs gdod nas grol ba ste //
NK116(le)001:8809: gzhan du su la'ang ma bstan par //
NK116(le)001:8810: mdzes ma khyon la bstan pa yin //
NK116(le)001:8813: rtula po rnams kyis sems kyi kun tu brtsam pa
NK116(le)001:8814: chen po nyams 'og tu mi chud pas lus ngag
NK116(le)001:8815: gi bya ba la che thang du mthong ba'i phyir
NK116(le)001:8816: / 'bringa gi sems kyi brtsam pa chen pos yang
NK116(le)001:8817: rtogs su rung la lus ngag gi bya ba dang
NK116(le)001:8818: sems kyi bsgom pa cha mnyam pa'i phyir dang /
NK116(le)001:8819: rnona pos sems kyi bsgom pa gtso la lus ngag
NK116(le)001:8820: gi spyod pa de'i grogs tsam du spyod pa'i phyir
NK116(le)001:8821: dang // mchoga gis sgo gsum bya ba thams cad
NK116(le)001:8822: yongs grub dgag sgrub bral te chos thams cad mnyam
NK116(le)001:8823: pa chen por spyod pa'i phyir du ste /
NK116(le)001:8825: dman pa rnams la bya ba'i rgyud //
NK116(le)001:8826: bya min rnal 'byor de lhag la //
NK116(le)001:8827: sems can mchog la rnal 'byor rgyud /
NK116(le)001:8828: rnal 'byor bla med de lhag la'o //
NK116(le)001:8830: sde tshan de dag gi nang du 'du tshul gyi rnam grangs rag pa ni /
NK116(le)001:8831: bshad rgyud rdo rje phreng ba las //
NK116(le)001:8832: stong phrag nyi shu rtsa bzhi ni //
NK116(le)001:8833: khrag 'babs par ni shes par bya //
NK116(le)001:8834: stong phrag nyi shu rtsa bzhi ni //
NK116(le)001:8835: byang chub sems ni rab tu bab //
NK116(le)001:8836: stong phrag nyi shu rtsa bzhi ni /
NK116(le)001:8837: rlung rgyu bar ni shes par bya /
NK116(le)001:8839: rtsa stong phrag bdun cu rtsa gnyis kyi rim pas
NK116(le)001:8840: der 'bab pa'i khu rngul gnyis dang rlung gi 'du
NK116(le)001:8841: ba las chos kyi rnam grangs de snyed cig 'char
NK116(le)001:8842: ba'i phyogs la blos yang bar bya ste /
NK116(le)001:8844: rnal 'byor pha rgyud rnams kyi tshad //
NK116(le)001:8845: bye ba phrag ni bdun cur gnas /
NK116(le)001:8846: de bzhin rnal 'byor ma rgyud grangs //
NK116(le)001:8847: bye ba phrag ni bcu drug grags /
NK116(le)001:8849: klu sgrub kyi rigs lnga'i 'grel ba las kyang //
NK116(le)001:8850: sngags kyi dbye ba ni stong phrag bdun cu rtsa gnyis so //
NK116(le)001:8851: zhes pa'i rnam grangs yang dpung bzang las //
NK116(le)001:8852: lha dang lha min mi la phan gdag phyir //
NK116(le)001:8853: gsang sngags rigs sngags rnam pa sna tshogs dang //
NK116(le)001:8854: bye ba phrag gsum dang ni 'bum phrag lnga //
NK116(le)001:8855: rig 'dzin sde snod gsal bar rgyal bas gsungs //
NK116(le)001:8856: zhes pas sems can gyi blo dang chos kyi dbyings
NK116(le)001:8857: dam pa'i rjes su 'gro ba yin pas ji bzhin
NK116(le)001:8858: tshad kyi dpag par mi sems so //
NK116(le)001:8859: gzhan yang phyin ci log bzhi'i phyogs la zhen pa dag rjes su bzung ba'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:8860: rgyud sde bzhir gsungs pa ni //
NK116(le)001:8861: 'di ltar gti mug can tshangs pa ni gtsang sbra chos su smra te /
NK116(le)001:8863: dri ma med par 'gyur pa bzhin //
NK116(le)001:8864: lus la chos sbyin gyis bgos la //
NK116(le)001:8866: zhes pa'i tshul gyis bzung ba'i phyir //
NK116(le)001:8868: khrus byas gtsang ma bzung bya ste //
NK116(le)001:8869: bkra shis ngo mtshar bzung byas la //
NK116(le)001:8870: bsgrub pa'i rdzas ni rjes su bzung //
NK116(le)001:8872: zhe sdang can khyab 'jug pa 'tshe ba chos su smra te //
NK116(le)001:8873: rgyal rigs la ni rgyal rigs dang //
NK116(le)001:8874: bram ze bsad pa bram ze dang /
NK116(le)001:8875: zhes pa'i don du spyod rgyud rnam snang mngon byang las //
NK116(le)001:8876: e ma ho gsod pa 'di ni bzang //
NK116(le)001:8877: gsod pas byang chub thob par byed /
NK116(le)001:8879: nga rgyal can brgya byin rjes su bzung ba'i phyir //
NK116(le)001:8880: dbang phyug 'byor ba lha yi rgyud //
NK116(le)001:8883: 'dod chags chos su smra ba dbang phyug gi rgyud la dga' zhing yul la sred pa rnams ni //
NK116(le)001:8884: goo tam bud med me yin te //
NK116(le)001:8885: de yi nye gnas thab khung yin /
NK116(le)001:8887: b+ha ga legs ldan khyab 'jug ste //
NK116(le)001:8888: bud med rnams kyi 'doms na gnas //
NK116(le)001:8889: mi rnams dga' bar byed pas na //
