NK116(le)001:8890: des na sred med bu zhes pa //
NK116(le)001:8893: bud med gzugs dang 'dab bzang pa //
NK116(le)001:8894: lo grangs bcu drug lon pa la //
NK116(le)001:8895: byin gyis brlabs te gnas gsum du //
NK116(le)001:8896: dben par mchod par rab tu brtsams /
NK116(le)001:8898: gzhan yang bag chags kyi sgo nas dbye ba'i tshul /
NK116(le)001:8900: shes rab rgyud ni shar nas slar yang rnal 'byor
NK116(le)001:8901: rjes su rigs pa nyid kyi nub kyi zhal nas
NK116(le)001:8902: so // g.yas kyi zhal nas rgyal ba'i bdag pos rnal 'byor rgyud gsungs /
NK116(le)001:8903: g.yon gyi zhal nas bya ba la sogs pa'o //
NK116(le)001:8904: zhes g.yon zhal sad pa'i bag chags kyi dbang gis
NK116(le)001:8905: rag pa phyi don du zhen pa la bya spyod
NK116(le)001:8906: kyi rgyud / g.yas zhal rmi lam gyi bag chags
NK116(le)001:8907: dbang gis sems kyi snang ba tsam du zhen pa
NK116(le)001:8909: mdun zhal gnyid 'thug po log pa'i bag chags kyi
NK116(le)001:8910: dbang gis snga phyi'i rtogs pa thams cad nub nas
NK116(le)001:8911: mi rtog par zhen pa la bla na med pa'i
NK116(le)001:8912: rgyud / rgyab zhal bzhi ba'i bag chags kyi dbang
NK116(le)001:8913: gis bde bar zhen pa la rnal 'byor rje'i rig
NK116(le)001:8914: gi rgyud sde'i rnam grangs phye'o //
NK116(le)001:8915: gdul bya'i khyad par bstan pa'i rjes nas 'dul byed
NK116(le)001:8916: kyi rnam bzhag chos ni zhes bya ba la sogs
NK116(le)001:8917: pas bstan ste // chosa ni rgyud sde bzhi ste //
NK116(le)001:8918: bya spyod rnala 'byor bla na meda pa bzhi'o //
NK116(le)001:8919: de las dang po gsuma ni gasnga sngagas phyi ba ste //
NK116(le)001:8920: thub pa chags bral gyi rnam pasa dngosa su gsungas pa matshana nyid kyi thega pa dang /
NK116(le)001:8921: gtsang sbra dang sdom pa'i kuna spyod phala chera mtshungas shing /
NK116(le)001:8922: rtsod pa'i dusa dang 'agal ba'i 'doda chagas gcig la
NK116(le)001:8923: gcig bltas kyis dga' bas tshim pa tsam gyi kuna
NK116(le)001:8924: spyod lam du byed pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:8925: lha mo rnams kyi yab la bltas pa tsam las
NK116(le)001:8926: lha yab yum yanga zunga 'brela du rol ba mina
NK116(le)001:8927: zhing / sha lnga bduda rtsi lnga la logas mi spyod de spyod mi nus pas so /
NK116(le)001:8928: phyag na rdo rje mngon par dbang bskur ba'i rgyud las /
NK116(le)001:8929: dbus su ni bcom ldan 'das spyan ras gzigs dbang bri //
NK116(le)001:8930: de'i g.yon du na bza' dkar mo bcom ldan 'das la blta ba bri'o //
NK116(le)001:8932: don yod zhags pa'i cho ga zhib mo las //
NK116(le)001:8933: bcom ldan 'das zhal khro gnyer can la gtod par bya zhing /
NK116(le)001:8934: g.yas phyogs na lha mo sgron ma mdzes bag dang bcas shing //
NK116(le)001:8935: lus btud pa la mchog sbyin pa'i phyag rgya la mig gtod par bya'o //
NK116(le)001:8936: g.yon du pad+ma'i rigs mdzes bag dang bcas pa sngags
NK116(le)001:8937: kyi tshul dang rjes su mthun zhing don yod zhag
NK116(le)001:8938: pa la mig gtod par bya'o //
NK116(le)001:8941: dkyil 'khor gyi ni lha tshogs rnams //
NK116(le)001:8942: pho yang mo la blta ba dang //
NK116(le)001:8943: mo yang pho la blta ba bri /
NK116(le)001:8945: de bas ni bya rgyud kyi lha rnams spyan rgyas par 'byung ba yin no //
NK116(le)001:8948: de yi g.yas su lha mo ni //
NK116(le)001:8949: sangs rgyas spyan zhes bya ba ste //
NK116(le)001:8950: lha mo cung zad 'dzum pa'i zhal //
NK116(le)001:8952: mtshungs med sku ni rab tu dngas //
NK116(le)001:8953: de ni sh+aakya thub pa'i yum /
NK116(le)001:8955: rnam par snang mdzad rgyal po che //
NK116(le)001:8956: yid tsam 'dzum pa'i zhal du bri /
NK116(le)001:8957: zhes pas spyod rgyud kyi lha rnams zhal 'dzum pa sha stag go /
NK116(le)001:8958: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud la'ang rtse mo las //
NK116(le)001:8959: rdo rje lha mo ca co sgrogs //
NK116(le)001:8960: lus 'khyud rang gi lha mo ni //
NK116(le)001:8961: de yi gla na mgo bsgyur zhing //
NK116(le)001:8962: 'dzum bcas kun tu blta ba yis //
NK116(le)001:8966: dkyil 'khor gyis ni lha tshogs rnams /
NK116(le)001:8967: dpung pa yid tsam dam par bzhag /
NK116(le)001:8969: de yi log la rdo rje che //
NK116(le)001:8970: mda' ni gsor ba la brtson pa //
NK116(le)001:8971: snyems pa'i phyag gis yongs 'khyud pa'i //
NK116(le)001:8972: chu srin rgyal mtshan bsgrengs dang bcas //
NK116(le)001:8974: lha rnams phyag rgya 'brel bar 'byung ngo /
NK116(le)001:8975: nges tshig kyang tshangs spyod kyi sdom pa'i dka' thub
NK116(le)001:8976: dang phyogs mtshungs pas dka' thub rigs byed dam thub
NK116(le)001:8977: pa rgyud kyi theg pa zhes bya'o //
NK116(le)001:8978: da ni so so'i rang bzhin dbye ba'i tshul dbye ba zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:8979: de dag so sor dbye ste bshad na bya ba dang ni spyod pa'i rgyud la semas dapa'a dang /
NK116(le)001:8984: dgongs pa grub pa'i rgyud las //
NK116(le)001:8985: gsang sngags kun gyi dbye ba ni /
NK116(le)001:8986: rnam pa gsum du shes bya ste /
NK116(le)001:8987: rigs sngags thabs kyi ngo bo yin /
NK116(le)001:8988: gzung sngags shes rab ngo bo yin //
NK116(le)001:8989: gsang sngags gnyis med ye shes so //
NK116(le)001:8993: spyod pasa spun grogsa kyi tshul du sgrub par byed pa las //
NK116(le)001:8994: phyogs dang po bya basa rjesa khola rnama para bsgruba pa'ang /
NK116(le)001:8996: lha dang rnam par dag pa gnyis //
NK116(le)001:8997: rje dang 'bangs kyi tshul du blta /
NK116(le)001:8999: de yang badga bskyeda meda para ranga nyid damna para bazhaga ste /
NK116(le)001:9000: bris sku la sogs pa dmigs rten byas na kri
NK116(le)001:9001: ya don gyi lha drug gi sgo nas dam tshig
NK116(le)001:9003: de yang rnam 'joms kyi rgyud las //
NK116(le)001:9004: stong pa yi ge sgra gzugs dang //
NK116(le)001:9005: phyag rgya mtshan ma drug yin no //
NK116(le)001:9013: la lara bdag bskyed yoda de gtso bora mduna bskyed ston pa ni /
NK116(le)001:9014: bya rgyud bla na med pa dang /
NK116(le)001:9015: med pa'i phyogs ni rang rgyud pa /
NK116(le)001:9017: phyi yi bya ba khrusa dang gatsanga sbra gtso ba ni /
NK116(le)001:9019: 'jug pa'i sgo ni dag pa gsum /
NK116(le)001:9024: dag pa rnam gsum gang zhe na //
NK116(le)001:9025: lha dang dkyil 'khor dag pa dang /
NK116(le)001:9026: rdzas dang longs spyod dag pa dang /
NK116(le)001:9030: dus su zos nas dus su khrus byas te //
NK116(le)001:9031: phreng ba me tog mar me spos dang dri /
NK116(le)001:9032: sha chang med pa'i lha bshos phul nas su /
NK116(le)001:9033: ku sha'i khri la 'dug nas bzlas brjod brtsam /
NK116(le)001:9035: de ltar mchoga damna gyi tshul du bsgrubsa nasa dangos gruba zhu bar 'doda pa ni /
NK116(le)001:9037: rje dpon rgyal po'i tshul bltas la //
NK116(le)001:9038: rang nyid bran gyi 'du shes kyis //
NK116(le)001:9039: sngags sgrub dngos grub snying po ni //
NK116(le)001:9040: bla na med pa'i mchog tu blangs /
NK116(le)001:9042: 'bras bu ni mi tshe bdun na /
NK116(le)001:9045: pad+ma'i rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sku gsum ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid can 'thob pa ste /
NK116(le)001:9047: mi tshe bdun na sangs rgyas sa //
NK116(le)001:9051: bya ba'i thabas lus ngag gi spyod pa dang //
NK116(le)001:9052: de lhaga nang gi rnal 'byor gnyis la cha ma
NK116(le)001:9053: nyamsa par spyod pasa spyod pa'i rgyud du gragas te
NK116(le)001:9055: u pa la ni 'di ltar te /
NK116(le)001:9056: lta ba yo gar lta ba dang /
NK116(le)001:9057: spyod pa kri yar spyod pa'o //
NK116(le)001:9058: de phyir gnyis ka'i rgyud ces grags /
NK116(le)001:9061: gnyis ka rgyud kyi 'dod pa ni /
NK116(le)001:9062: spyod pa bya ba'i rjes mthun yang //
NK116(le)001:9063: lta ba rnal 'byor rjes mthun phyir //
NK116(le)001:9064: rig dang blta bas khyad par 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:9066: de ltar ranga nyid dama tshiga semas dapara bskyed pa'i mduna tu bzhugas pa'i //
NK116(le)001:9067: ye shesa sems dpa'i lha la spuna ltar bsgrub te dngosa gruba lena la /
NK116(le)001:9069: mi tshe lnga na rigs bzhi rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa thob par 'dod pa ste /
NK116(le)001:9070: rig bzhi ni las kyi rigs rin po che rigs la bsdus pa'o //
NK116(le)001:9072: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang sar gnas /
NK116(le)001:9075: gnyis su med la mi tshe lngas sgrib grol /
NK116(le)001:9077: rnal 'byor rgyud kyi gru chad mana chada la ni
NK116(le)001:9078: 'og min stug po bkoda pa'i zhing chena po'i ston
NK116(le)001:9079: pa longas spyod rdzogas pa'i sku ltar phyogs mthun bstan
NK116(le)001:9080: yanga mi 'dra ba'i khyad par ni /
NK116(le)001:9081: yab yum zunga 'brela ma yina par dang bskyed pa
NK116(le)001:9082: dang rdzogas pa thabas dang shesa raba rnams zung 'jug
NK116(le)001:9083: ma yin par go rima cana so so ba ste
NK116(le)001:9085: lhun grub mnyam pa ma mthong bas /
NK116(le)001:9086: chos kun rnam dag ye shes kyi //
NK116(le)001:9087: byin brlabs rdo rje dbyings sprul ba //
NK116(le)001:9090: 'on kyang snga ma gnyis las 'phags te /
NK116(le)001:9091: nang gi rnal 'byora gtso bora spyod cing /
NK116(le)001:9092: lusa ngaga grogas su ston pa yin par /
NK116(le)001:9094: lha yi ting 'dzin la gnas te //
NK116(le)001:9095: sems can thams cad yongs mi gtong //
NK116(le)001:9096: rtag tu sangs rgyas yid la byed //
NK116(le)001:9097: rtag tu sangs rgyas mchod pa thob /
NK116(le)001:9100: las rgyal mchog dkyil 'khor rgyal mchog gang rung la brten nas //
NK116(le)001:9105: sku yongs 5su rdzogs par la byang chub pa ste /
NK116(le)001:9110: mchod 4pa dang cho 'phrul bzhi'i rnam grangs te /
NK116(le)001:9112: mi rtogs zla ba gsung rdo rje //
NK116(le)001:9113: spro bsdus bsgom pa'i sku ru gsal //
NK116(le)001:9114: ting 'dzin byin brlabs dbang bskur mchod //
NK116(le)001:9115: mngon byang lnga dang cho 'phrul bzhi //
NK116(le)001:9116: bsgom zhing mchod pa bya ba yang //
NK116(le)001:9117: bsod nams ldan phyir bya ba yin /
NK116(le)001:9119: de ltar bdag dam tshig sems dpa' bskyed pa la ye shesa sems dpa' dguga cig bstim la /
NK116(le)001:9120: sku phyag me long kun gzhi rgya chen po /
NK116(le)001:9121: gsung so sor rtogs pa'i chos rgya //
NK116(le)001:9122: thugs mnyam nyid nyon yid dam rgya /
NK116(le)001:9123: phrin byang sgo lnga las las rgya ste phyag rgya bzhi yisa dbyer med du bcingas pa dang /
NK116(le)001:9124: rgyas gdab ste me long lta bu la sogs pa'i
NK116(le)001:9125: ye shes bzhi mngon du bya ba dang sbyar zhing
NK116(le)001:9126: / chos dbyings ye shes ni de thams cad kyi rang bzhin du gnas pa'o //
NK116(le)001:9127: de nas dama tshig pa dang ye shes pa gnyis
NK116(le)001:9128: ro gciga pa'i nganga nasa dngosa grub blang pa rdo
NK116(le)001:9130: gnyis su med pa'i chos dbyings dang //
NK116(le)001:9131: bla med dngos grub dam pa blangs /
NK116(le)001:9133: bzlas ba rdzogs pa'i matha'a la gshegas gsola bya ba nas rang tha mal par gnas pa'o //
NK116(le)001:9134: 'bras bu ni mi tshe gsum na rigs lnga stug
NK116(le)001:9135: po bkod pa'i sa la sku gsum ye shes lnga'i
NK116(le)001:9138: yo ga sdug po bkod 'dod pa'i /
NK116(le)001:9139: mi tshe gsum na grol bar 'dod //
NK116(le)001:9141: gsang sngags nang ba ston pa'i phyir //
NK116(le)001:9142: bla na med pa zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:9143: rgyud 'di'i pha rol na thog ma gzhan med pa'i phyir bla na meda pa'i gasnga sngagas nanga pa'o //
NK116(le)001:9145: bskyed rim dang rdzogas rim dang /
NK116(le)001:9149: gnyis meda rgyud gsum du bazhaga go /
NK116(le)001:9152: skyes bu rnams ni 'dul don du /
NK116(le)001:9153: rnal 'byor rgyud ni rab tu bstan /
NK116(le)001:9154: btsun mo rnams ni bsrung ba'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:9155: rnal 'byor ma yi rgyud rab bstan /
NK116(le)001:9157: dbye ba gang gis shes na /
NK116(le)001:9158: lha pho shas che zhing dar dang rin chen gyi rgyan mang na pha rgyud /
NK116(le)001:9159: lha mo shas che zhing gcer pu dang rus rgyan /
NK116(le)001:9160: g.yang gzhi dang thal chen byug pa la sogs ma rgyud dam /
NK116(le)001:9161: yang dbus kyi gtso bo 'pho la gtso mo sdod na pha rgyud /
NK116(le)001:9163: 'di ltar dbyings phyug ma gcig po nyid rigs lnga'i
NK116(le)001:9164: dkyil 'khor gang bsgrub kyi gtso bo dang stong dpyal
NK116(le)001:9165: du gyur na snga ma yin pa 'dis gcig shos
NK116(le)001:9166: kyang shes sla'o // rgyud gang rung gi lha ni 'khrila sbyora dang /
NK116(le)001:9167: dama rdzas khyad para ba sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga
NK116(le)001:9168: la sogs par spyod cing gatsanga rtsogas la spangas lena
NK116(le)001:9169: meda pa'i ranga bzhina cana yin no //
NK116(le)001:9170: de dag bstan bshad gnyis las dang po rnal 'byor zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:9171: yang rnal 'byora chena po ni pha rgyud thabsa kyi
NK116(le)001:9172: lam yin pas bskyed rima gtso bora byas nas 'byung
NK116(le)001:9173: ba'i rlung lnga dag para byed cing /
NK116(le)001:9174: rjesa su rnal 'byor ni ma rgyud shesa raba kyi lam ste /
NK116(le)001:9175: rdzogas rima gtso bora byed pas khamas byang chub kyi sems lasa zhu bde bskyed cing /
NK116(le)001:9176: shina tu rnal 'byor ni gnyis meda ye shesa kyi lam ste /
NK116(le)001:9177: gciga dang du ma bral ba'i 'oda gasla chena pora sbyor ba yin no //
NK116(le)001:9178: gnyis pa bshad pa la rten ni /
NK116(le)001:9179: kun gyi zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:9180: de dag kuna gyi ganda du med thabs med pa'i
NK116(le)001:9181: rten 'byung ba lnga rnam par shes pa'i khamas te
NK116(le)001:9182: druga dang ldan pa'i mi lusa gang zhig phunga po
NK116(le)001:9183: khamas dang skye mched rnams gnas pa rtsa bkod pa
NK116(le)001:9184: thig le g.yo ba rlung gis lasa su runga ba'i
NK116(le)001:9185: phyir de lasa rten cing 'brel te bdag gi sgo
NK116(le)001:9186: gsum bskyed rdzogas zunga 'juga gsuma gyi yona tan ji
NK116(le)001:9187: snyed kun bskyed par byed pa rdo rje thega pa'i
NK116(le)001:9189: de la ji ltar dkri ba'i tshul rang bzhin zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:9190: snod bcud ranga bzhina lhuna gyis gruba pa'i dkyil 'khora chena pora ru /
NK116(le)001:9191: lta basa thaga bacada cing bsgoma pasa nyamsa su blangsa nas spyod pasa la dora bar byas nas /
NK116(le)001:9192: 'brasa bu rang gzhan gyi dona gnyis bde blag du 'grub ste /
NK116(le)001:9193: de'ang gzhi dang lam dang 'brasa bu'i rgyud la yang dag par brten pa'o //
NK116(le)001:9195: thabs kyi theg pa chen po ni //
NK116(le)001:9196: rnam par byang dang sdug bsngal dag /
NK116(le)001:9197: kun rdzob du'ang dbyer med de //
NK116(le)001:9198: lta ba mtho dman de tsam mo //
NK116(le)001:9200: lam thabs kyi rgyud la dbang bzhi dang rjes su
NK116(le)001:9201: 'brel bar bskyed rdzogs yan lag dang bcas pa la
NK116(le)001:9202: bslab pa'i tshul 'jug pa'i zhes bya ba la sogs
NK116(le)001:9203: pas bstan te / 'juga pa'i sgo ni smin para byeda pa'i dabnga gi rim pa dang /
NK116(le)001:9204: grol bar byeda pa'ang bskyed rim dang rdzogas rim rnam pa gnyis te /
NK116(le)001:9205: de la mthuna pa'i grogas su dama tshigas spyod pa
NK116(le)001:9206: dang gsum ni sngags kyi lam mchoga rnala mara ngesa
NK116(le)001:9208: dbang thob min gyi khe nyen dang po zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:9209: gsang sngags nyams su len pa'i dang po dabnga bskura
NK116(le)001:9210: ma thoba na dangos gruba meda cing bye ma btsira
NK116(le)001:9211: ba lasa zhuna mara 'dod pa bzhina du gyur pa
NK116(le)001:9212: ni / a ti yo ga las /
NK116(le)001:9213: gsang sngags dbang la ma brten ga la 'grub //
NK116(le)001:9214: dper na mnyan pa lag skya bral ba bzhin /
NK116(le)001:9217: dbang med pa la dngos grub med //
NK116(le)001:9218: bye ma btsir bas mar mi 'byung //
NK116(le)001:9219: mkhar la khu tshur gyis brdeg dang //
NK116(le)001:9220: smig rgyu'i chu ni 'thung dang mtshungs /
NK116(le)001:9222: de tsam du ma zad gsang sgrogs kyi nyes pa 'byung ba yang //
NK116(le)001:9224: dbang bskur med par rgyud 'chad dang /
NK116(le)001:9225: zab mo de nyid sgom byed pa //
NK116(le)001:9226: de don legs par shes na yang //
NK116(le)001:9227: dmyal ba 'gyur gyi grol ba med /
NK116(le)001:9229: gang zhig rgyud lung nga rgyal gyis //
NK116(le)001:9230: dbang bskur med par chos 'chad na //
NK116(le)001:9231: slob dpon slob ma shi ma thag /
NK116(le)001:9232: dngos grub thob kyang dmyal bar 'gro //
NK116(le)001:9233: zhes gsungs pa bzhin 'achada nyan sgom pa la sogs
NK116(le)001:9234: par brtsona kyang dmyal bar 'gro ba las 'os med
NK116(le)001:9235: do // thob pa'i phan yon ji ltar snyam na /
NK116(le)001:9236: dabnga thoba pa'i skyes bu dag de nas rgyal ba'i srasa su gyur ba smos ci dgos //
NK116(le)001:9237: dkyila 'khora mthonga ba tsam gyis kyang sdiga pa kun lasa rnam para grol te //
NK116(le)001:9238: gatsanga ma'i rigs 'ba' zhig tu skye zhing /
NK116(le)001:9239: skye ba bduna daga na dbang gi 'bras bu ngesa para 'grub cinga sa bcu thoba para bashada do //
NK116(le)001:9241: dbu rgyan cod pan phreng ba dang /
NK116(le)001:9242: go cha rgyal mtshan phyag rgya dang //
NK116(le)001:9243: gdugs dang bum pa bza' btung dang //
NK116(le)001:9244: snying po lnga yi dbang bskur na //
NK116(le)001:9245: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK116(le)001:9246: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK116(le)001:9247: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK116(le)001:9248: mtho ris thar ba'i bdag po 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:9251: mtshams med lnga yi las can yang //
NK116(le)001:9252: tshon rtsi mthong bas grol bar 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:9253: dkyil 'khor bcug dang dbang bskur ba /
NK116(le)001:9254: gtsang ma'i rigs su skye bar 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:9257: dbang bskur yang dag sbyin ldan na //
NK116(le)001:9258: skye zhing skye bar dbang bskur 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:9259: de yi skye ba bdun na ni //
NK116(le)001:9264: dbang bskur bas ni sa bcu non /
NK116(le)001:9266: dbang bskur ba po slob dpon gyi mtshan nyid la /
NK116(le)001:9267: spang bya ni dbang bskur zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:9268: dabnga bskura byed kyi slob dpona ni bskyed rdzogs rima pa gnyis kyi gdenga dang bral zhing //
NK116(le)001:9269: tshe 'di'i che thang mthon po bsti gansa bzung nas
NK116(le)001:9270: log 'tsho lnga la sogs pa'i dkora la bag med
NK116(le)001:9271: du spyod pa dang sdom pa gsum gyi gnang bkag
NK116(le)001:9272: ma bsdamas par khyim la chagas shing /
NK116(le)001:9273: snying rje chunga ba dang dam pa'i chos kyi rnam bzhag ci yang mi shes pa'am /
NK116(le)001:9274: gal te cung zad thos kyang don la ma sems par /
NK116(le)001:9275: tha snyad rtog ge'i rig pas zila gyis nona pa desa /
NK116(le)001:9276: dabnga bskura byas kyang dngos grub ci yang med par
NK116(le)001:9277: ma zad be sbrel gayanga sara lhung ba ltar gnyis
NK116(le)001:9278: ka ngan song du skyur ba ni /
NK116(le)001:9280: dkon mchog dkor la rngam sems can /
NK116(le)001:9281: khyim la chags shing nag chang brten //
NK116(le)001:9282: sdom pa 'chal zhing las la brtson //
NK116(le)001:9283: tshong dang khe spog lhu ru len //
NK116(le)001:9284: snying rje med cing srog chags gsod /
NK116(le)001:9286: de bstan dmyal bar 'phen par byed /
NK116(le)001:9289: dad ldan gcig bslus sems can brgya bsad pas //
NK116(le)001:9290: sdig pa shin tu che ba rgyal bas gsungs //
NK116(le)001:9291: de phyir rang 'dod bslu ba'i chos mi bshad /
NK116(le)001:9293: gzhan yang tshul mthong gi snang ba ma dag kho
NK116(le)001:9294: na yin pas phyi'i rtags kyis kyang dngos grub kyi
NK116(le)001:9295: gegs su 'gyur ba'am bstan rtsa 'dul ba la dgongs
NK116(le)001:9297: rten ni gsum las dge slong mchog /'bring ni dge tshul du brjod do //
NK116(le)001:9298: khyim gnas de ni dag pa'i mtha' //
NK116(le)001:9299: sa thob min pa'i khyim pa ni //
NK116(le)001:9300: rgyal po'i bla ma mi bya'o //
NK116(le)001:9302: 'o na ji lta bu la zhu snyam na phyi nang zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:9303: phyi nanga gasnga ba'i de nyid rnam pa bcu //
NK116(le)001:9304: riga cinga ranga nyid grol ba'i bla ma gang yin pa de yisa bskur bar bya ste //
NK116(le)001:9306: rdo rje snying po rgyan gyi rgyud las //
NK116(le)001:9307: phyir bzlog gnyis kyi cho ga dang //
NK116(le)001:9308: gsang dang shes rab ye shes dang //
NK116(le)001:9309: kha sbyor 'byed pa'i cho ga dang //
NK116(le)001:9310: gtor ma rdo rje'i bzlas pa dang //
NK116(le)001:9311: drag shul bsgrub pa'i cho ga dang //
NK116(le)001:9312: rab tu gnas dang dkyil 'khor bsgrub //
NK116(le)001:9313: gsang ba'i de nyid bcu yin no //
NK116(le)001:9315: stong stabs 'dug stangs bzlas brjod dang //
NK116(le)001:9316: sbyin sreg mchod pa las sbyor dang //
NK116(le)001:9317: slar sdud pa yi rnam pa ni //
NK116(le)001:9318: phyi yi de nyid bcu yin no //
NK116(le)001:9319: zhes gsung pa de nang gi de nyid bcu dang phyi'i de nyid bcu gsungs so //
NK116(le)001:9320: de la phyir bzlog gnyis ni //
NK116(le)001:9321: khro bo'i bsrung 'khor bsgom nas phyir bzlog pa dang /
NK116(le)001:9322: bris pa'i srung 'khor 'dogs nas phyi bzlog pa'o //
NK116(le)001:9323: gsang ba dang shes rab ye shes kyi dbang bskur
NK116(le)001:9324: ba gnyis las ma gsung kyang gsang dbang ni dbang
NK116(le)001:9325: thob pa la bskur ba des bum dbang mtshon la
NK116(le)001:9326: / gsum pas bzhi pa mtshon pas de ltar bsdu'o //
NK116(le)001:9327: kha sbyor phyed pa ni dgra bo bsrung ma dang bral nas bsgral ba dang /
NK116(le)001:9328: gtor ma'i cho ga dang rdo rje'i bzlas pa sogs sngags kyi de nyid dang //
NK116(le)001:9329: drag shul bsgrub pa ni ji bzhin bsgrubs kyang ma
NK116(le)001:9330: khol na lha la drag po'i sbyor pas gzir ba'o
NK116(le)001:9331: // rab gnas dang dkyil 'khor sgrub pa ni rang
NK116(le)001:9332: rang gzhung gis ston pa ltar byang chub par bya'o
NK116(le)001:9333: // // phyi'i de nyid bcu'i dkyil 'khor ni gzugs can yin min gnyis so //
NK116(le)001:9334: ting 'dzin lha'i rnal 'byor te dang po sbyor ba sogs so //
NK116(le)001:9335: phyag rgya ni lha la rgyas 'debs pa'i phyag rgya sogs so //
NK116(le)001:9336: stangs stabs dang 'dug stangs dang las la sbyor ba dang slar bsdu ba bzhi ni //
NK116(le)001:9337: rim pa ltar g.yas brkyang la sogs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:9338: rdo rje dkyil dkrung la sogs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:9339: bsrung zhing spyan drangs sogs pa dang //
NK116(le)001:9340: mchod pa bstod pa sogs sngon du 'gro bas gshegs gsol bya ba ste /
NK116(le)001:9342: phyi nang gi sgra zhug pa ni rgyud sde phyi nang gi phyes pa yin no //
NK116(le)001:9345: brtan zhing dul la g.yo rgyu med /
NK116(le)001:9346: gsang sngags rgyud kyi sbyor ba shes //
NK116(le)001:9347: dkyil 'khor bri ba'i las la mkhas //
NK116(le)001:9348: de nyid bcu ni yongs shes shing //
NK116(le)001:9349: sems can rnams la mi 'jig sbyin /
NK116(le)001:9352: dul zhing zhi ba'i cha byed can //
NK116(le)001:9353: sems can rnams la mi 'jigs sbyin //
NK116(le)001:9354: sbyor dang bzod dang thabs dag dang //
NK116(le)001:9355: rtag tu sbyin la sogs dga' zhing //
NK116(le)001:9356: rnal 'byor bsam gtan mchog tu brtson /
NK116(le)001:9357: de nyid bcu po rnam par rig /
NK116(le)001:9358: rdo rje slob dpon du bstan no //
NK116(le)001:9361: rtsa ba'i ltung ba rab 'dzem shing //
NK116(le)001:9362: sngags dang rgyud kyi rab sbyor gyis //
NK116(le)001:9363: 'jig rten rnams la bde ster ba //
NK116(le)001:9364: de 'dra'i bla ma dngos byas la /
NK116(le)001:9366: de lta bu'i slob dpon gyis slob ma gang rung
NK116(le)001:9367: la bskur ba bya ba yin nam zhe na min
NK116(le)001:9368: te / rgyas par rgyu'i theg pa'i skabs su bshad
NK116(le)001:9369: pas shes shing 'dir yang rtsa ba'i rjes su 'brang
NK116(le)001:9370: te / nas ston te / de la bcos min
NK116(le)001:9371: gyi dada pa dang ngo tsha dang khrel yod shesa
NK116(le)001:9373: sgrim pos brtagsa la ji ltar 'tshams pa'i dabnga bskur te /
NK116(le)001:9374: gdams ngag kyang de bzhin rima pasa sbyin para bya dgos te /
NK116(le)001:9375: bla ma lnga bcu pa las //
NK116(le)001:9376: bla ma dang ni slob ma dag /
NK116(le)001:9377: mtshungs par dam tshig nyams gyur bas //
NK116(le)001:9378: dpa' bo dang ni slob dpon dang /
NK116(le)001:9379: slob ma'i 'brel ba brtag par bya /
NK116(le)001:9382: ji ltar rin chen brdar ba dang //
NK116(le)001:9383: gser ni bsregs dang bcad pas brtags //
NK116(le)001:9384: de bzhin du ni slob ma yin //
NK116(le)001:9385: lo ni bcu gnyis bar du brtags //
NK116(le)001:9386: de ltar phan tshun de lta bus //
NK116(le)001:9387: dus kun tu ni de ltar brtags //
NK116(le)001:9389: dngos grub 'jom shing sdug bsngal ster /
NK116(le)001:9392: khro dang bcas shing rtog ger lus //
NK116(le)001:9393: na so dag ni yol ba dang //
NK116(le)001:9394: gang yang dge slong dngos gnas dang //
NK116(le)001:9395: zhen dang chags pas bcing pa las //
NK116(le)001:9396: rin thang med pa'i rin chen ni /
NK116(le)001:9397: de la sbyin par mi bya'o //
NK116(le)001:9399: ji ltar bskur ba'i sbyor ba la ni bsnyen pa zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:9400: de la dang po skye gnas rnam pa bzhi'i bag
NK116(le)001:9401: chags sbyong byed kyi mngon rtogs gang rung la ltos
NK116(le)001:9402: nas bskyed gzhi'i ting 'dzin gsum bsgom pa ni bsnyen
NK116(le)001:9403: pa'o // de las bdag nyid lhar bskyed pa ni nye bar bsnyen pa'o //
NK116(le)001:9404: yum dang bcas pa'i skye mched dang mkha' gsang byin gyis brlabs pa la sogs pa ni sgrub pa'o //
NK116(le)001:9405: de la ye shes pa dgug gzhug bya shing dbang
NK116(le)001:9406: bskur rgyas gad ba la sogs pa ni sgrub pa
NK116(le)001:9407: chen po ste // phur ba rnams 'byor chen po'i rgyud las //
NK116(le)001:9408: spyir na gsang basngagasa nges pa la /
NK116(le)001:9409: ting 'dzin gsum bskyed bsnyen pa yin //
NK116(le)001:9410: bdag nyid ltar bskyed nye bsnyen te //
NK116(le)001:9411: yum bskyed bsgrub par shes par bya //
NK116(le)001:9412: gzhan rnams sgrub pa chen po yin //
NK116(le)001:9413: zhes gsung pa ltar nges par byas nas mtshan ma dang //
NK116(le)001:9414: dus dang grangs kyi bsnyen pa rab 'bring tha ma'i
NK116(le)001:9415: sgo nas ji ltar nus pa sngon du 'gro ba
NK116(le)001:9416: gzhir byas nas khyad par gyi don du bsnyen pa
NK116(le)001:9418: gnyis pa sa yi cha ga la //
NK116(le)001:9424: dang po rdo rje mkha' 'gro las /
NK116(le)001:9425: grong dang dur khrod tshong dus dang /
NK116(le)001:9427: shar dang byang ga sa gzhi shes //
NK116(le)001:9428: lho dang nub phyogs de ltar min /
NK116(le)001:9431: phun sum tshogs pa kun bzang ba'i //
NK116(le)001:9432: tshogs pa dag ni rnyed par dka' //
NK116(le)001:9433: mdor na sa gzhi mnyam pa dang //
NK116(le)001:9434: mdangs snu ma shar du gzhol bar bzhed //
NK116(le)001:9435: chu mang ldan pa'i gnas dang ni //
NK116(le)001:9436: ljon shing bzang pos brgyan pa dang //
NK116(le)001:9437: bdag gi yid ni mgu ba dang /
NK116(le)001:9438: 'tshe med zug rngu spang ba ni //
NK116(le)001:9439: dkyil 'khor gnas su shes pa ste //
NK116(le)001:9440: mi yi dngos grub kun thob byed //
NK116(le)001:9442: gnyis pa slangs pa la gnyis te //
NK116(le)001:9443: snang ba la bslar ba dang //
NK116(le)001:9444: mi snag ba la bslang pa'o //
NK116(le)001:9445: dang po ni sa de bdag po'i mi la rin dang //
NK116(le)001:9446: gnyis pas lha la gtor ma dang phud sogs btang ba'o //
NK116(le)001:9448: lto 'phye brtags pa gzhan du shes la sa'i zug rngu dbyung ba ni //
NK116(le)001:9450: sman sogs dngos grub bye brag gis //
NK116(le)001:9451: pus mo mchu so lte ba'i bar //
NK116(le)001:9452: brkos la phub ma rdo dang ni //
NK116(le)001:9453: gyo mo sol ba zug rngu ni /
NK116(le)001:9454: tsher ma la sogs bsal la bcag /
NK116(le)001:9455: ces pa ltar byas nas rdzas sngags ting nge 'dzin
NK116(le)001:9456: gyi cho ga'i gzhung ltar sbyangs te slar sbyang bya
NK116(le)001:9457: spyod byed kyi spros pa thams cad rang bzhin med
NK116(le)001:9458: pa'i chos nyid gcig tu mnyam par 'jog pa ste
NK116(le)001:9460: sngags pa rtog la gnas nas su //
NK116(le)001:9461: gang zhig sa spyod byed pa ni //
NK116(le)001:9462: byang chub sems ni rnam spangs pas //
NK116(le)001:9463: gsang ba'i bdag po de yi bdag /
NK116(le)001:9464: de bas rtog pa rnams spangs nas //
NK116(le)001:9465: sa kun rnam par sbyang bar bya /
NK116(le)001:9468: rang nyid lha'i rnal 'byor gyi ngang nas bgegs la
NK116(le)001:9469: bka' bgo zhing gar gyi stangs stabs sogs brtul zhugs
NK116(le)001:9470: kyi spyod pa'i tsham rngams bya ste gzhi bdag tu
NK116(le)001:9471: bzung / lnga pa bsrung ba ni //
NK116(le)001:9472: bka' bsgo zhing dkyil 'khor gyi gzhi bzung ba'i dus
NK116(le)001:9473: de nyid du dam la mi 'du zhing slar gnod
NK116(le)001:9474: sems 'chang ba rnams bkug nas khro bcu'i phur bu
NK116(le)001:9475: gdab pa'o // gsum pa blta gona dang ni zhes
NK116(le)001:9476: pa 'dis zur gsum ston te lha bum slob gsum
NK116(le)001:9477: gdab pa'o // mo // dang po la gsum las /
NK116(le)001:9478: dang po gzhi bting ba ni /
NK116(le)001:9480: dkyil 'khor khru gang tshad du bya /
NK116(le)001:9481: yang na khru ni gsum gyi tshad /
NK116(le)001:9482: yang na lus gang tshad du ste //
NK116(le)001:9483: yang na lus ni gsum gyi tshad /
NK116(le)001:9484: yang na khru ni sum cu gnyis /
NK116(le)001:9486: gang 'tshams kyi gzhi nges par byas nas lha gnas shes par bya ba'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:9487: gnyis pa thig gi bya ba sgrub pa la /
NK116(le)001:9488: las thig sngon du gdab pa dang /
NK116(le)001:9489: ye thig sngon la gdab pa'i lugs gnyis las /
NK116(le)001:9490: dang po ni sa ra has //
NK116(le)001:9491: dang po dkar rtsi la sogs pas //
NK116(le)001:9492: rim bzhin thig gdab nges par bya //
NK116(le)001:9493: de steng ye shes thig gdab pas //
NK116(le)001:9494: kun kyang yongs su brkyang bar bya /
NK116(le)001:9498: blo ldan nam mkhar thig gdab bya //
NK116(le)001:9499: de bzhin 'og tu thig rab gdab //
NK116(le)001:9501: thig skud dang ye las thig gdab tshul rgyas par cho ga rang rang gis ston to //
NK116(le)001:9502: gsum pa lha lta gon dngos ni //
NK116(le)001:9503: thig gi mtshon pa'i lha gnas so sor /
NK116(le)001:9506: gtso bo'i gnas su gru bzhi pa dang //
NK116(le)001:9507: 'khor gyi gnas su zlum po byas la so so'i
NK116(le)001:9508: sngags brjod cing me tog gis tshom bu bkod nas
NK116(le)001:9509: rten la dmigs pa byas la /
NK116(le)001:9510: mthar mchod pas bskor nas bsang sbyangs byin gyis brlabs te /
NK116(le)001:9511: dam tshig gi 'khor lo ji lta ba baskyedanasa ye
NK116(le)001:9512: shes pa gzhug cing gom pa brtan pas ni sa
NK116(le)001:9513: bon bskyed pas kyang rung la //
NK116(le)001:9514: sngar sa chog gi skabs su bskyed nas nam mkhar
NK116(le)001:9515: bstegs pa yin na de nyid phabs pas kyang rung
NK116(le)001:9517: thig gdab cho ga ji bzhin bya //
NK116(le)001:9518: dri yi thig les mtshan ma bkod //
NK116(le)001:9519: nam mkha'i dkyil 'khor phab cing mchod /
NK116(le)001:9521: gnyis pa bum pa lta gon la gnyis te /
NK116(le)001:9524: bum 1pa dang rdzas2dang de'i yan lag 3 go /
NK116(le)001:9527: gser dang zangs sams nyid la //
NK116(le)001:9528: bum pa lto yangs mgrin pa phra /
NK116(le)001:9529: kha g.yel zhabs tshad zhum pa las /
NK116(le)001:9533: 'bru lnga spos lnga rin chen lnga //
NK116(le)001:9534: snying po lnga dang sman lnga dang //
NK116(le)001:9535: bdud rtsi lnga nyid rab bsnyam la /
NK116(le)001:9536: zhes rkang ba dang po dang gnyis pas phyi rgyud
NK116(le)001:9537: gsum gyi thun mong gi bum rdzas nyer lnga dang
NK116(le)001:9538: // gsum pas de'i steng du bdud rtsi lnga dngos
NK116(le)001:9539: dang sha lnga shugs kyi bstan pas sum cu rtsa
NK116(le)001:9540: lnga ni bla na med pa'i rgyud sde'i khyad chos
NK116(le)001:9541: // so // gsum pa la gnyis las /
NK116(le)001:9543: sangs rgyas gsang bas gsungs ba ltar gzhan gyis longs
NK116(le)001:9544: ma spyad pa'i ras gtsang mar thor cog gsum gyi
NK116(le)001:9545: tshul du dakri'o // zhes sku gsum mtshon pa rgyud sde 'og mar dgongs la /
NK116(le)001:9546: de bzhin rnal 'byor rgyud la sku lnga mtshon pa'i srog lnga /
NK116(le)001:9547: bla med la de'i steng du zhu bde'i ye shes
NK116(le)001:9548: mtshon pas srog bdud du bshad pa'ang yod par gsungs
NK116(le)001:9549: / gang ltar de nyid srad bu dkar po'am gang rung gis 'chings pa'i tshul /
NK116(le)001:9551: kha dog bcos pu'i skud pas brgyan /
NK116(le)001:9553: gnyis pa kha rgyan rgyud sde gong 'og rang rang gi bstan pas shes sla'o //
NK116(le)001:9554: de lta bu'i bum pa'i dngos pos sprul sku /
NK116(le)001:9556: nang gi bsil ba'i ngo bos nyon mongs tsha gdung bcil bas na chos sku /
NK116(le)001:9557: lha bsgom pas na ngobo nyid sku rnams mtshon pa'o //
NK116(le)001:9558: lha grangs longs na rdul mtshon gyi dkyil 'khor du mtshan ma 'god pa'i rim pa ltar ram /
NK116(le)001:9559: yang na sgo mtshams brgyad du dri'i thig le man+dala
NK116(le)001:9560: re re'i steng du bum pa brgyad dang gtso bum
NK116(le)001:9561: dbus su 'jog pa la gcig las med na'ang dbus
NK116(le)001:9563: gnyis pa bsang sbyangs byas te lha bskyed tshul yang de bzhin grangs dang bstun la /
NK116(le)001:9564: rnam bum gcig po'i skabs thams cad der bskyed pa kho na'o //
NK116(le)001:9565: las bum shar sgo'i g.yon du 'god par rgya gar gyi phyag len la /
NK116(le)001:9566: rje gter bdag gling pas rang gi mdun nam gang bder 'jog par yang gsungs so //
NK116(le)001:9567: gsum pa slob ma sta gona dang ni so so'i gzhung gis shes sla'o //
NK116(le)001:9571: dkyil 'khor sgrub pa 4bzhi so so'i dkyus ltar bya ste /
NK116(le)001:9572: dbang dngos gzhi la bab pa na thog mar slob dpon rang nyid 'jug dgos pa /
NK116(le)001:9574: rang snang dbyer med dkyil 'khor la /
NK116(le)001:9575: 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid mnyams sbyor bas /
NK116(le)001:9578: 'khor lo sngon du mthong ba yin //
NK116(le)001:9579: bsod nams brtag pa gang yin pa /
NK116(le)001:9580: phyis byas pa yang de bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:9583: kun byas dbang phyug rig pas 'jug /
NK116(le)001:9584: de nas slob ma 'jug par bya /
NK116(le)001:9586: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha la bla mas slob
NK116(le)001:9587: ma 'juga pa'i gnang ba nod cinga bden pa bsgrag
NK116(le)001:9588: ste // slar slob ma 'jug pa'i rim pa ni //
NK116(le)001:9590: khrus dgab dri dang lus dbul dang //
NK116(le)001:9591: bgegs bskrad slar rlabs dam tshig sbyin /
NK116(le)001:9592: de nyid dpog dang chu nan dang //
NK116(le)001:9593: bsgrag dang rin chen dor ba dang //
NK116(le)001:9594: lha dbab pa dang rin chen dang //
NK116(le)001:9595: mig dbye dkyil 'khor legs bstan dang //
NK116(le)001:9596: zhes pa'i rim pa rnams dkyus ltar byas pa'i rjes
NK116(le)001:9597: thog nas 'og tu 'byung ba'i rim pa rnams kyis
NK116(le)001:9598: smin par bya'o // mngon par rtog bya'i rgyud sde bzhi po gang rung re re nyid la'ang //
NK116(le)001:9599: bshad ma thag pa bzhi bzhira rdzogs dgos pa'i phyir
NK116(le)001:9600: yan lag gang ma tshanga na cho ga nyamsa pasa
NK116(le)001:9601: smina para nus pa ma yina no //
NK116(le)001:9602: da ni dbang spyi'i rnam pa mdor bstan pa dang /
NK116(le)001:9603: dbang bzhi'i ngo bo bye brag tu brjod pa las /
NK116(le)001:9604: dang po ston pa'i phyir du /
NK116(le)001:9605: rgyud sde zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:9606: de yang rgyud sde bzhi so so'i dabnga gi rigas dbye la /
NK116(le)001:9607: bya ba'i rgyud la chu dang coda pan gyi dbang gnyis tsam gyis 'grub pa dang /
NK116(le)001:9608: spyod pa'i rgyud la de'i steng du rdo rje ming gi dbang bsnan pa dngos bstan dang /
NK116(le)001:9609: rjes gnang gi yan lag yang mang nyung rgyud dang slob dpon so so'i gzhung gi khyad yod do //
NK116(le)001:9610: rnal 'byor rgyud la riga pa'i dabnga lnga dang //
NK116(le)001:9611: gasnga ba bka'a yi dabnga dang /
NK116(le)001:9612: matha'a rten bcas pas rdzogas so //
NK116(le)001:9613: 'di'i gsang dbang ni lha dang dkyil 'khor gyi de kho na nyid dang /
NK116(le)001:9614: slob dpon gyi las ston pa tsam la ltos nas
NK116(le)001:9615: btags pa las bla med kyi skabs dang mi 'dra'o
NK116(le)001:9617: bla na meda pa'i rgyud la /
NK116(le)001:9621: de dag las kyang thega pa'i rtse mo rang bzhin
NK116(le)001:9622: rdzogs pa chen po'i dbang gi rima pa la dbang
NK116(le)001:9623: bzhir btags pa las bla med spyi'i skabs kyi dbang
NK116(le)001:9625: de nyid kyi bye brag bshad pa ni /
NK116(le)001:9627: shina tu sprosa med dang raba tu spros meda de bzhi'o //
NK116(le)001:9628: spyir na rdo rje theg pa'i dabnga gi dbye bsdu matha'a yasa kyang /
NK116(le)001:9629: sa bcad zina sor 'jog 'atshamas rnama pa bzhi po de yina no //
NK116(le)001:9630: de dag gi tshul yang ye shes thig le'i rgyud las chu yi dbang bskur dbu rgyan dag /
NK116(le)001:9631: bya ba'i rgyud las rab tu grags //
NK116(le)001:9632: rdo rje dril bu de bzhin ming //
NK116(le)001:9633: spyod pa'i rgyud la rab tu gsal //
NK116(le)001:9634: phyir mi ldog pa yi ni dbang //
NK116(le)001:9635: rnal 'byor rgyud du gsal bar byas //
NK116(le)001:9636: de yi drug pa'i bye brag dbang //
NK116(le)001:9637: de ni slob dpon dbang zhes bya //
NK116(le)001:9638: rnal 'byor bla ma yi ni mtshan //
NK116(le)001:9639: gsang ba yi ni dbang rgyal bshad //
NK116(le)001:9640: shes rab ye shes bla na med //
NK116(le)001:9641: bzhi pa de yang de bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:9644: 'og min tshogs chen 'dus pa'i rtsa rgyud las /
NK116(le)001:9645: sridapa gsum gyis phyag byas pa'i //
NK116(le)001:9646: bla ma'i sa la gnas pa yis //
NK116(le)001:9647: dbang mchog sum cu rtsa drug yin //
NK116(le)001:9648: phyi yi dbang dang nang gi dbang //
NK116(le)001:9649: sgrub pa'i dbang dang gsang ba'i dbang /
NK116(le)001:9650: bcu dang bcu gcig bcu gsum dang //
NK116(le)001:9651: rnam pa gnyis kyi rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:9653: bshad rgyud dgongs pa 'dus pa las /
NK116(le)001:9654: la las ni rgyud kyi chu bo'i dbang dag gi dbang phyin no //
NK116(le)001:9655: zhes phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo dang /
NK116(le)001:9656: nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bo dang /
NK116(le)001:9657: sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo dang /
NK116(le)001:9658: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo bzhir dbye bsdu bya ba'i tshul /
NK116(le)001:9660: dang po phyi yi dbang bcu bskur //
NK116(le)001:9661: de nas nang dbang bcu dang gcig /
NK116(le)001:9662: de nas sgrub dbang bcu dang gsum //
NK116(le)001:9663: tha ma gsang ba rnam pa gnyis //
NK116(le)001:9664: bcu phrag gsum dang drug dag gi //
NK116(le)001:9665: dbang mchog dam pa bskur ba yin //
NK116(le)001:9667: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa 'gyur snga phyi gnyis dang /
NK116(le)001:9668: zla gsang thig le la sogs pa nas bum pa dang /
NK116(le)001:9670: shes rab ye shes zhes grags pa dang /
NK116(le)001:9671: dus 'khor las ni byis pa 'jug pa'i dbang bdun dang /
NK116(le)001:9672: dbang gong ma la 'jig rten pa gsum dang /
NK116(le)001:9673: 'jig rten las 'das pa gcig ste bcu gcig tu bshad pa dang //
NK116(le)001:9677: gsang ba byang chub sems kyi dbang gsum ste bco
NK116(le)001:9678: brgyad du phye ba sogs rgyud sde so sor dbye
NK116(le)001:9679: bsdu ci rig pa mang ngo //
NK116(le)001:9680: a ti'i khyad chos spros bcas sogs bzhi las snga ma gnyis bla med spyi dang phyogs mthun la /
NK116(le)001:9681: phyi ma gnyis la mi 'dra ba'i khyad ni /
NK116(le)001:9682: shin tu spros med kyi dbang la phyi nang gsang ba yongs rdzogs bzhi ste /
NK116(le)001:9683: dang po ni 'khor 'das ru shan 'byed pa'o //
NK116(le)001:9684: gnyis pa ye shes nyi shu rtsa lnga la spyod
NK116(le)001:9685: pa'i don du man+dala phul nas gsol ba gdab pa
NK116(le)001:9687: gsum pa nam mkha'i phyogs bzhi nas sems nyid kyi sgor 'jug go /
NK116(le)001:9688: bzhi pa nam mkha' rgya che ba'i sgra dbyangs kyi
NK116(le)001:9689: don la 'dris par byas nas ngo bo med pa'i
NK116(le)001:9690: sems nyid la mtha' dbus med pa mtshon pa ste
NK116(le)001:9692: shin tu spros pa med pa la //
NK116(le)001:9694: de tshe nam mkha'i mtshan nyid las //
NK116(le)001:9695: lus ngag yid gyi sgrib pa yang //
NK116(le)001:9696: mtshan nyid kyi ni nges par brtags //
NK116(le)001:9697: gal te spyod pa ma dag na //
NK116(le)001:9698: rang rang mthun pa'i dge bas sbyang //
NK116(le)001:9699: dbang gi brda' la brten pa yi //
NK116(le)001:9700: rang rig gsal ba'i rang ngo sprod //
NK116(le)001:9701: brda' grol man ngag mkhas pas spyad /
NK116(le)001:9703: rab tu spros pa med pa yang //
NK116(le)001:9705: nang gi lta stangs ston pa'o //
NK116(le)001:9706: gsang ba ni de gnyis bstun nas sangs rgyas kyi zhing du spyod pa'o //
NK116(le)001:9707: yongs su rdzogs pa ni songs shig la sogs pa'i tshig gis brda' don sprod pa ste /
NK116(le)001:9709: rab tu spros pa med pa la //
NK116(le)001:9710: sems kyi dkyil 'khor sgo phye la //
NK116(le)001:9711: lus kyi 'dug stangs nges par brtsams //
NK116(le)001:9712: de la gom de gzigs stangs sbyangs //
NK116(le)001:9713: mngon gsum rig pa lung gi barda'o //
NK116(le)001:9715: rgyu rkyen 'brel ba'i 'bras bu thob tshul gzhi dang zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:9716: de yang bla med bla na med pa'i lugs su
NK116(le)001:9717: gzhi rang bzhin lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor chen po
NK116(le)001:9718: phung khams skye mched kyi rten dang ba rten pa
NK116(le)001:9719: gang zhig lam bshad ma thag pa'i smin byed kyi
NK116(le)001:9720: dbang dang 'brel bas nus rung du byas nas /
NK116(le)001:9721: 'brasa bu rdo rje 'chang gi go 'phang thob pa'i
NK116(le)001:9722: phyir dabnga bzhi'i ngo bo ru gdoda nasa gruba pa
NK116(le)001:9723: yin no // de ltar rtsa sprul sku'i rten can bum dbang bskur yul /
NK116(le)001:9724: rlung longs sku'i rten can gsang dbang bskur yul //
NK116(le)001:9725: kun rdzob dkar dmar khams kyi thig le chos sku'i rten can sher dbang bskur yul /
NK116(le)001:9726: don dam pa mi shig pa'i thig le ngo bo
NK116(le)001:9727: nyid sku'i rten can bzhi pa bskur yul yin te
NK116(le)001:9729: lus la ye shes chen po gnas /
NK116(le)001:9730: rtog pa thams cad yang dag spangs /
NK116(le)001:9731: dngos po kun la khyab pa'o //
NK116(le)001:9732: lus gnas lus las ma skyes pa'o //
NK116(le)001:9734: dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud las //
NK116(le)001:9735: dbang mchog rang la med gyur na //
NK116(le)001:9736: bskur bas thob pa ga la 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:9737: bra sran 'bras su dbang bskur yangs //
NK116(le)001:9738: de la 'bras kyi dngos snang med /
NK116(le)001:9741: rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni //
NK116(le)001:9742: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags //
NK116(le)001:9743: skye mched khams ni mang po kun //
NK116(le)001:9744: byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK116(le)001:9745: sa chu spyan dang ma ma ki /
NK116(le)001:9746: me rlung gos dkar sgrol ma ste //
NK116(le)001:9747: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK116(le)001:9748: srid gsum ye nas sangs rgyas zhing /
NK116(le)001:9750: de ltar rtsol bas gsar sgrub ma yin par ye
NK116(le)001:9751: nas ranga chasa nyid de mtshungsa para ldana para rang
NK116(le)001:9753: zhing la lo tog smin pa'i dpe ltar rdo rje
NK116(le)001:9754: slob dpon gyi rtogs tshogs su snang ba chos can
NK116(le)001:9755: kun rdzob kyi bden pa nyid du dag pa ting
NK116(le)001:9756: nge 'dzin gyi nus pas brnyan can lhana gcig byed
NK116(le)001:9757: pa'i rgyu'i rten cing 'brel 'byung gis dbang gi bya
NK116(le)001:9758: ba ba sgrub pa la brten nas slob ma'i rgyud
NK116(le)001:9761: gang gi gang la dbang bskur bas //
NK116(le)001:9762: rgyud dag nus pa thob phyir dbang /
NK116(le)001:9764: rnam pa gnyis po de lasa nang gses snod du rung ba'i slob bu ni rgyu'i rkyen dang /
NK116(le)001:9765: lta ba shongs yangs shing dgongas pa mthon po dang ldan pa'i slob dpona badga po'i rkyen dang //
NK116(le)001:9766: lha sngags ting nge 'dzin gyi nus pa'i cho ga mkhyen pa dmigas pa'i rkyen dang /
NK116(le)001:9767: de dag gcig la gcig ltos kyi rten cinga 'brel 'byung grub pa de ma thaga pa'i rkyen te /
NK116(le)001:9768: rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi tshogas pa lasa dabnga bskur yang
NK116(le)001:9769: dag par 'gruba nas mchog gi sar snyegs pa rang
NK116(le)001:9770: shar las // rtogs pa ye shes dbang mchog ni /
NK116(le)001:9771: cir snang rig pa shes pa'o //
NK116(le)001:9772: rig pa dgag sgrub med pa ni //
NK116(le)001:9773: dbang rnams dus gcig rdzogs pa'o //
NK116(le)001:9774: dbang rnams grol byed gdams ngag go /
NK116(le)001:9775: dmigs med dkyil 'khor chen po nyid //
NK116(le)001:9776: dbang nyid rang la yod pa'o //
NK116(le)001:9778: de ltar na lus can yod do cog kun dbang bskur ba'i yul du 'gyur ram zhe na /
NK116(le)001:9781: gzugs med pa yi rten rnams la //
NK116(le)001:9782: dbang rnams bskur ba'i rten min te /
NK116(le)001:9783: rtsa rlung rtog pa mi dmigs pas //
NK116(le)001:9784: ye shes dbang bskur ga la nus //
NK116(le)001:9785: gzugs khams rtsa dang rlung yod kyang //
NK116(le)001:9786: khams kyi zas dang bral ba yin //
NK116(le)001:9787: des na 'dod khams gnas rigs ni //
NK116(le)001:9788: dbang rnams bskur ba'i rten yin te //
NK116(le)001:9789: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug dang //
NK116(le)001:9790: nga rgyal khong khro phrag dog gis //
NK116(le)001:9792: dbang gi snod du rung ba yin /
NK116(le)001:9794: de ltar na'ang 'dod pa'i khams kyis bsdus pa kun min te //
NK116(le)001:9796: de yang lha dang lha min sgra mi snyan pa
NK116(le)001:9797: gsum ni 'bras bu la spyod pas rgyud dman la
NK116(le)001:9798: gling gsum du skyed pa'i khams drug ldan ni khyad
NK116(le)001:9799: par pa dang // de las kyang 'dzam bu gling
NK116(le)001:9800: pa ni las kya sa bar grags pas mchog tu
NK116(le)001:9801: par pa dang // gyur pa'o // dmigs bsal dam pa'i rigs can lngar gtogs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:9802: nyan rang dgra bcom lhag med du zhugs pa 'ga'
NK116(le)001:9803: zhig yid lus kyi sngags lam la 'jug pa yod
NK116(le)001:9804: pa ni bsam pa'i rten khyad par can yod pas
NK116(le)001:9805: ma nges so / sbyongs byed gnyen po sbyong gzhi'i
NK116(le)001:9806: grangsa ngesa kyi sgo nas bazhaga pa ni 'di lta
NK116(le)001:9807: ma nges so / ste / lusa kyi gtso bora
NK116(le)001:9808: gyur pa rtsa dbu rkyang ro gsum dang 'khor lo
NK116(le)001:9810: rtsa yi rnama pa ma dag rigs drug gi sa bon dang /
NK116(le)001:9811: dag pa sku gsum gyi ngo bo yi ge gsum
NK116(le)001:9812: gyi rnam pa'i gzugas su gansa pa ro rkyang du
NK116(le)001:9813: dbyangs gsal byed rnams yod par gsungs so //
NK116(le)001:9814: de la rlung brten te byed las sna tshogs byed
NK116(le)001:9815: cing rlung la khamas dkar dmar rnams brten te khamas
NK116(le)001:9816: la dona dama byang chuba kyi semas zhes bde gshegs
NK116(le)001:9817: snying po brten pa ste bzhi'o //
NK116(le)001:9818: de yang sgyu 'phrul chen mo las /
NK116(le)001:9819: ro ma rkyang ma kun+d+ha ma //
NK116(le)001:9820: 'khor lo so so'i dkyil dag na //
NK116(le)001:9821: ka ba'i tshul du gnas pa la //
NK116(le)001:9823: khams dang rlung ni 'babs pa yi //
NK116(le)001:9824: ye shes rtsa ni stong phrag gcig /
NK116(le)001:9825: bdun cu rtsa gnyis bsgras pa yis //
NK116(le)001:9826: nyi khri chig stong drug brgya'i rlung /
NK116(le)001:9828: gzhan ni bzhi stong brgyad khri'o //
NK116(le)001:9830: da ni dbang bzhi so so'i rnam bzhag bshad pa la //
NK116(le)001:9831: dang po bum pa'i dbang ston pa'i phyir 'dod pa'i zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs ste /
NK116(le)001:9832: 'doda pa'i khamas kyi gang zaga ranga rgyud pa /
NK116(le)001:9833: kuna la 'doda chagas rnam pa bzhi gansa pa la sogas /
NK116(le)001:9834: daga bya daga byed kyi rim pa la rten pa'i ngesa pa yanga /
NK116(le)001:9835: dang po dag bya bltas pasa tshima pa'i 'doda chagas ni //
NK116(le)001:9836: gazhana 'phrul dabnga byed pa la gansa pa yin te /
NK116(le)001:9837: dag byed rdula mtshona gyi dkyil 'khora la brten pa
NK116(le)001:9838: bum pa'i dabnga bskur basa gnas skabs bzhi las sad
NK116(le)001:9839: pa'i gnas skabs dang sgrib pa bzhi las gtso bora
NK116(le)001:9840: lusa kyi sgrib pa 'adga cing phung po'i bdud 'joms
NK116(le)001:9841: pa'o // thob bya'i yon tan ni //
NK116(le)001:9842: snod bcud de brten dang g.yo bas bsdus so cog gi phunga po lnga dang khamas lnga ni //
NK116(le)001:9843: rigs lnga stangs dpyal lnga dang /
NK116(le)001:9844: skye mcheda kun ni rnam shes dag pa'i nang sems bzhi dang dbang po dag pa'i phyi sems bzhi /
NK116(le)001:9846: dus bzhi dag pa'i sems ma bsdom pas stangs dpyal brgyad /
NK116(le)001:9847: yan lag bzhi ni lus kyii rnam shes1 /
NK116(le)001:9850: reg shes 4bzhi dag pa'i sgo ba bzhi ste /
NK116(le)001:9851: de la rtag chad bdag mtshan bzhi gnas su dag
NK116(le)001:9852: pa'i yum bzhi bsdams pas stangs dpyal bzhi ste gadna
NK116(le)001:9853: gsuma tshangas pa'i lha'i sum cu so bzhi'i dkyila 'khora
NK116(le)001:9854: 'ba' zhig pa gciga tu shara ba de la phung
NK116(le)001:9855: khams gshegs pa gshegs ma'i gdan /
NK116(le)001:9856: skye mched sems dpa' sems ma'i gdan /
NK116(le)001:9857: las dbang bya ba dang bcas sam /
NK116(le)001:9858: yan lag khro bo'i khro mo'i gdan /
NK116(le)001:9860: de las 'phros pa rdo rje dbyings kyi lha lnga bcu dang /
NK116(le)001:9861: dam pa rigs brgya la sogs pa rgyud sde so
NK116(le)001:9862: so'i gzhung nas 'byung ba'i dag bya dag 'bras lha'i
NK116(le)001:9863: 'khor lo dbyibs kyi lam du sgom pas /
NK116(le)001:9866: sem thams cad rig stong zung 'jug sgyu ma'i rnal
NK116(le)001:9867: rol du shar ba de'ang gsal ba'i cha nas snang
NK116(le)001:9868: phyogs kyi ngo bo bskyed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:9869: rang bzhin med pa'i cha nas stong phyogsa kyi ngo bo rdzogs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:9870: lhun gyi grub pa'i cha nas zunga 'juga gi ngo
NK116(le)001:9871: bo bskyed rdzogs bde ba dbyer med chen por blta
NK116(le)001:9872: ba ngo bo nyid gsuma gyi gnad la rang byan
NK116(le)001:9873: chub bas gdos bcas la thog pa med /
NK116(le)001:9874: rtsa nang du rgyu ba'i khams ldog pas chu bo
NK116(le)001:9875: gyen la ldog rdul dbu mar chings pas nyi ma
NK116(le)001:9878: du ma ni gcig du byed pa nus /
NK116(le)001:9879: stong gsum yungs 'bru chud pa ste 'jig rten las 'das pa'i sa drug dang /
NK116(le)001:9880: gruba matha'a 'khora 'adsa gnyis su dbyer med pa'i rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor chen po ru la bzla ba'o //
NK116(le)001:9881: gal te grub pa'i mthar ma snyogs par 'chi ba'i
NK116(le)001:9882: dus la babs na ma bsgom sangs rgyas 'pho ba'i
NK116(le)001:9883: gdam pas snang ba bsgyur ba'i 'ad'a ka ma /
NK116(le)001:9885: sgra yi 'pho ba'i 'da' ka ma gsum gyis 'pho te /
NK116(le)001:9886: mthar thug 'bras bu ni rtsa yi 'grosa mdud rang
NK116(le)001:9887: rgyud pa thams cad rnam par dag pa'i dbyings na
NK116(le)001:9888: thima pa ste bskyed rima la ltos pas skye ba
NK116(le)001:9889: mchog gi sprul pa'i sku lhun gyis grub cing /
NK116(le)001:9890: mkha' khyab tu sku yi bkod pas 'gengs shing rang
NK116(le)001:9891: bzhin rdo rje lta bu 'dusa ma byas par gnas
NK116(le)001:9892: par 'gyur ro // glang po rab 'bog las /
NK116(le)001:9893: rtsa yi 'gros thim dbyings kyi lam dag pa //
NK116(le)001:9894: lus kyi sgrib byang bskyed rim sbrul pa'i sku /
NK116(le)001:9896: gnyis pa gsang dbang ston pa'i phyir b+ha ga'i zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:9897: 'di lta bla ma'i yum gyi b+ha ga'i dkyil 'khora
NK116(le)001:9898: la brten nas gasnga dabnga bskura ba dag byed yin
NK116(le)001:9899: la / dag bya bgoda pasa tshimas pa 'phrula dag'i 'doda chagsa /
NK116(le)001:9900: gnas skabs bzhi las rmi lam dang /
NK116(le)001:9901: ngaga gi sgriba pa sbyangsa nas badga byin gyis barlobas pa'i thabs lam khyad par pa ste /
NK116(le)001:9903: yum mkha' sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK116(le)001:9904: gsang ba zab mo'i dkyil 'khor te //
NK116(le)001:9905: ye shes bzhi yi rang bzhin du //
NK116(le)001:9906: gnyis su med par dbang bskur ro //
NK116(le)001:9908: gtum mo'i rgyud kyi rtsa ba las //
NK116(le)001:9909: e ma bde ba skyed tsam gyis //
NK116(le)001:9910: byang chub mchog ni thob byed pa'i //
NK116(le)001:9911: byed po bud med dang sbyor las //
NK116(le)001:9912: gzhan du nam yang ma yin no //
NK116(le)001:9913: sgyu ma'i de nyid thams cad las //
NK116(le)001:9914: bud med sgyu ma'i de nyid basngagasa //
NK116(le)001:9916: ji ltar bskur ba'i tshul ni //
NK116(le)001:9918: rdo rje pad+mo'i sbyor ba yi //
NK116(le)001:9919: rdo rje can gyi yang dag bsdu //
NK116(le)001:9920: sku gsung thugs kyi sbyor ba yi //
NK116(le)001:9921: de dag thams cad snying khar bsdus //
NK116(le)001:9922: rdo rje'i lam nas phyung nasani //
NK116(le)001:9923: slob ma'i khar ni dbab par bya /
NK116(le)001:9926: de ltar dbang thob nas gdams pa nyams su blang
NK116(le)001:9927: bas rlung gi rtsa mdud grol ba gtum mo'i byang
NK116(le)001:9928: sems zhu // 'khrul 'khor gyi rtsa gnas thams cad
NK116(le)001:9929: byang sems kyis khyab ste gzunga 'dzina las rlung rnams
NK116(le)001:9930: ro rkyang gi lam nas dbu mara 'dzuda de 'khor
NK116(le)001:9931: lo so so'i mdud pa grol nas lta ba ranga
NK116(le)001:9932: byung ye shes chen po'i gruba matha'a ma 'dresa yongs
NK116(le)001:9934: sa bdun pa nas bcu pa'i bar bzhi po la
NK116(le)001:9935: ngag dag pa a li ka li la dbang bas
NK116(le)001:9937: chos kyang de'i skad du ston /
NK116(le)001:9938: dgu par so so yang dag rig pa bzhi la
NK116(le)001:9939: dbang thob pas chos thams cad de nyid rig gal
NK116(le)001:9940: te grub mtha' ma rnyogs na 'da' ka dpe yi
NK116(le)001:9941: 'od gsal chena po'i nganga ni 'chi kha'i bsdu rim
NK116(le)001:9942: gyis rkyen byas te rlung thams cad dbu mar tshud
NK116(le)001:9943: nas rnam par mi rtog pa'i ting 'dzin skye zhing
NK116(le)001:9944: lus gnas kyi yi ge'i 'grosa rnams dag pa sku
NK116(le)001:9945: gsum gyi sa bon la thima ste /
NK116(le)001:9946: bar do longas spyod rdzogsa pa sgyu ma'i sku ru
NK116(le)001:9947: bzhengs pa la dbyangs kyi yan lag drug cura rdzogs
NK116(le)001:9948: pa'i gsunga rdo rje 'grub pa ni /
NK116(le)001:9950: yi ge'i 'gros thim sngags kyi lam dag pa /
NK116(le)001:9951: ngag gi sgrib dag rdzogs rim longs spyod rdzogs //
NK116(le)001:9953: gsum pa shes rab ye shes kyi dbang sten pa'i
NK116(le)001:9954: phyir gdan gsum zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs
NK116(le)001:9955: te / phung khams sogs gadna gsuma tshangs pa'i 'khor lo'i mngona rtog ngoma pa'i mdzesa ma yi /
NK116(le)001:9956: gasnga ba'i dkyil 'khora bde ba chen po la brtena
NK116(le)001:9957: nas shes rab ye shes kyi dbang gisa smin par
NK116(le)001:9958: byed pa dag / lag bcangsa kyis tshima pa'i dga'
NK116(le)001:9959: ldana lha gnas kyi 'doda chagas sogs daga nas gnas
NK116(le)001:9960: skabs bzhi las gnyid 'thug gi dus /
NK116(le)001:9961: yida kyi sgrib pa'ang sbyang nas 'chi bdag gi bdud 'joms pa ste /
NK116(le)001:9963: pad+ma'i snying po'i dbus na ni //
NK116(le)001:9964: rnal 'byor dbang phyug ma ni bzhugs //
NK116(le)001:9965: de ma rnyed pa'i bar du ni //
NK116(le)001:9966: thabs gzhan las ni byang chub med //
NK116(le)001:9967: de ni rang gi dga' ba'i gzugs //
NK116(le)001:9968: phra mo'i phra mo yang dag mchog /
NK116(le)001:9970: kha gcig tshangs spyod rdo rje 'dzin pa la dbang snga ma dang 'di gnyis ma gnang ste /
NK116(le)001:9972: gang zhig dge slong dngos gnas pa /
NK116(le)001:9973: de la de nyid bstan mi bya /
NK116(le)001:9976: gsang ba shes rab dbang bskur ni //
NK116(le)001:9977: dang pos sangs rgyas rgyud chen las //
NK116(le)001:9978: rab tu 'bad pa dka' ba'i phyir //
NK116(le)001:9979: tshangs par spyod pas blang mi bya //
NK116(le)001:9982: bskyed rdzogs gong ma'i gnad la nang byan ma chud cing //
NK116(le)001:9983: rang lam gyi brtul zhugs la mchog tu 'dzin pas
NK116(le)001:9984: dbang de gnyis blangs na ngo tsha dang 'khrel gyi
NK116(le)001:9985: 'jigs nas brtul zhugs nyams kyi dogs pas 'gyod par
NK116(le)001:9986: 'gyur bas so // gzhan gyi so thar gyi rten
NK116(le)001:9987: khyad par pa la bkag par 'dod mi nus te
NK116(le)001:9988: 'gyur bas so // / rdo rje gdan pa las //
NK116(le)001:9989: dge slong lus la phyag rgya brten //
NK116(le)001:9990: lho nub srin po'i kha gnon mdzad /
NK116(le)001:9991: pad+ma ka ra zhes bya ba'i //
NK116(le)001:9992: bla ma de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK116(le)001:9994: dge tshul lus la gdol ba'i rigs //
NK116(le)001:9995: phyag rgya ma dang dngos grub brnyes //
NK116(le)001:9996: ku ku ri ba zhes bya ba'i //
NK116(le)001:9997: bla ma de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK116(le)001:9998: zhes pa la sogs pa'i grub thob thams cad la bskur bar 'gyur bas so //
NK116(le)001:10001: pad+ma'i rigs dang dung can te //
NK116(le)001:10002: ri mo can dang has sti'o //
NK116(le)001:10005: dang por 'dus par byas nas ni //
NK116(le)001:10006: rdo rje cho ga rab tu bsgrub //
NK116(le)001:10007: de bzhin gshegs pa'i btsun mo'i mchog /
NK116(le)001:10008: dam tshig chen por byin gyis brlabs //
NK116(le)001:10009: zhes rgyud dag par byas te //
NK116(le)001:10010: slob dpon gyis cho ga bzhin gtad pa'i 'og tu //
NK116(le)001:10011: thabs shes gnyis ka lhar 'du shes pa'i gnas gsum yi ge gsum dang //
NK116(le)001:10012: thabs kyi rdo rje h'u las rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i rtse mor gyis mtshan pa //
NK116(le)001:10013: shes rab kyi pad+ma +aahls pad+ma dmar po 'dab ma
NK116(le)001:10014: bzhi ba'i ze'u 'bru h+r+aihs mtshan par yi ge 'du
NK116(le)001:10015: shes pa dang // thabs kyi nang nas thabs mchog
NK116(le)001:10016: tu gyur pa 'di la brten nas sems can thams
NK116(le)001:10017: cad kyi don du bde chen lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK116(le)001:10018: ye shes mngon du bya'o snyams pa'i sems bskyed pa
NK116(le)001:10019: chos kyi 'du shes te 'du shes gsum ldan gyis
NK116(le)001:10020: snyom par 'jug pa sogs rgya chen gzhan du gsal
NK116(le)001:10021: la deng dus 'di 'dra'i lag len theb pa'i bla
NK116(le)001:10022: slob dkon pa'i phyir 'dir ma spros so //
NK116(le)001:10024: de yang snang ba'i dus na rang bzhin brgyad cu'i
NK116(le)001:10025: rtog pa skyed byed kyi rlung dang bcas pa rang
NK116(le)001:10027: mcheda pa'i dus na snang ba skyod byedarlunga dang bcas pas stong pas shin tu stong pa /
NK116(le)001:10028: nyer thoba kyi dus na mched pa rlung dang bcas
NK116(le)001:10029: pas stong pas na stong pa chen po te gsuma
NK116(le)001:10030: dang / de yang rlung sems kyi chas khur ba'i
NK116(le)001:10031: bslad pa thams cad dang bral bas stong pa 'od
NK116(le)001:10034: lte bar gnas pa'i tsan+d+ha l+ai //
NK116(le)001:10035: mar me ltar 'bar de yi ni //
NK116(le)001:10036: zhu ba'i khu ba mchog la ni //
NK116(le)001:10037: de las skyes pa'i bde ba las //
NK116(le)001:10038: zhes zhu bde la brten nas ye shes 'dren dgos
NK116(le)001:10039: pa gang zhig gnas kyi sgo nas ngos bzung ba'i
NK116(le)001:10040: khyad par la // dus 'khor ltar na //
NK116(le)001:10041: gtsug tor nas ni mdzod spu yi //
NK116(le)001:10043: mgrin pa snying gar mchog dga' ba //
NK116(le)001:10044: khyad par dga' ba de nas 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:10045: sna tshogs dga' byed lte bar te //
NK116(le)001:10047: gsang gnas rdo rje nor bu'i bar //
NK116(le)001:10048: lhan skyes dga' bar mi 'pho ba'o //
NK116(le)001:10049: zhes dag'a bzhi'i ye shes dang de la nang gses
NK116(le)001:10050: bzhi bzhir dbye ba'i bcu drug rnams ni khamas kyi
NK116(le)001:10051: bdud rtsi zhu ba yas babs mas brten gyi bde
NK116(le)001:10054: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK116(le)001:10055: phyag rgya'i rkyen gyis rtog pa yin //
NK116(le)001:10056: mngon sum lam du grags pa ste //
NK116(le)001:10057: byin brlabs lam du 'gyur ba min /
NK116(le)001:10060: mkha' 'gro gsal 'bar tshe la sogs yid bzhin sprin gyi bdag por 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:10062: de'i gruba pa'i matha'a ni bde stong dbyer meda du
NK116(le)001:10063: nyamsa su myong bas sa bcu gcig pa dang bcu
NK116(le)001:10064: gnyis pa'i gnas skabs dang skal ba mnyams zhing /
NK116(le)001:10065: gal te grub mtha' ma snyogs na 'ad'a ka'i tshe
NK116(le)001:10066: dera snang zhen dmigs pa'i bzhag pa tsam yang ma
NK116(le)001:10067: grub pa'i rdo rje semas dpa' mthong ba 'gyur te
NK116(le)001:10068: / de la rdo rjee ni stong ba sems dpa' ni bde ba'o //
NK116(le)001:10069: de yang 'byung ba sdud rim gyis rkyen byas nas
NK116(le)001:10070: don dam pa'i byang chub sems kyi rten khams kyi
NK116(le)001:10071: thig le kun rdzob pa rnams lhan gcig tu 'tshogs
NK116(le)001:10072: zhing dbu mar zhugs pas snying ka'i rtsa mduda grol
NK116(le)001:10074: mkha'a khyab tu rgyal ba kun gyi thugas kyi rdo rje /
NK116(le)001:10078: bdud rtsi khams kyi dngas ma bcud kyi lam sems kyi sgrib sbyangs dngas ma chos kyi sku //
NK116(le)001:10080: bzhi pa tshig dbang rin po che'i rang bzhin ston
NK116(le)001:10081: pa'i phyir byang chub ces bya ba la sogs pa
NK116(le)001:10082: gsungs te / dbang mchog kun gyi mthar thug pa
NK116(le)001:10083: don dam byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor la brten
NK116(le)001:10085: de yang dbang gsum pa'i dus na phyag rgya ma
NK116(le)001:10086: las rnyed pa'i nyams su myong ba dpe'i lhan skyes
NK116(le)001:10087: ye shes kun rdzob pa gang zhig gi dri ma'i
NK116(le)001:10088: cha spangs pas rang bzhin gyi 'od gsal ba de
NK116(le)001:10089: nyid 'bras bu'i lhan skyes su slob dpon gyi tshig
NK116(le)001:10090: gi matshana pas ngo sprod nas slob mas go ba'
NK116(le)001:10093: bzhi ba'i dbang bskur bya ba la //
NK116(le)001:10094: rlung gi rang bzhin nges shes shing //
NK116(le)001:10095: ngo la ka ko la sbyar bas //
NK116(le)001:10096: rang bzhin bde stong phan tshun 'byung //
NK116(le)001:10097: bzung du med de brjod du med //
NK116(le)001:10098: rtog pa kun dang bral ba yi //
NK116(le)001:10099: rang bzhin 'od gsal der gnas pa //
NK116(le)001:10100: tshig tshogs dbang gi rang bzhin byin //
NK116(le)001:10103: lha thabs bral man chada pho mo 'khyud sbyor gyi
NK116(le)001:10104: 'dod chags yod pas de dang sgo gsum gyi sgrib
NK116(le)001:10105: pa dag ste 'khor 'das tha dad du 'dzin pa'i
NK116(le)001:10106: sems kyi dri ma shin tu phra ba cha mnyam
NK116(le)001:10107: par sbyangs shing lha'i bu'i bdud bcoms /
NK116(le)001:10108: gnas skabs bzhi las snyoms 'jug gi gnas skabs dang /
NK116(le)001:10109: de'ang 'dzag bde'i sred pa yin pas khu rdul rlung gsum las 'khor ba'i lus ngag yid gsum dang /
NK116(le)001:10110: bde sdug btang snyoms gsum 'char khu rdul rlung gsum la cha mnyam du 'jug pa'i sems dang /
NK116(le)001:10111: shes sgrib ches phra ba 'pho ba'i bag chags kyi
NK116(le)001:10112: sgrib pa cha dang bcas pa sbyongs pa yin te
NK116(le)001:10114: ji ltar zas kyi dri ma ni //
NK116(le)001:10115: ro yi sbyor bas nyams par 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:10116: de yi yod nyid nyams pa med //
NK116(le)001:10117: dri med nyid kyis yang dag gnas //
NK116(le)001:10118: de bzhin sems kyi dri ma ni //
NK116(le)001:10119: stong nyid sbyor bas rnam nyam 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:10120: de yi ye shes nyid nyams med //
NK116(le)001:10121: dri med yid kyis yang dag gnas //
NK116(le)001:10124: stong chen 'dus ma byas pa'i dbyings dang ro gcig
NK116(le)001:10125: pa'i 'od gsal thiga le riga pa'i snying po cana
NK116(le)001:10127: rdo rje khros pa'i bshad rgyud las /
NK116(le)001:10128: chos sku mngon sum mthong ba'i tshe //
NK116(le)001:10129: dbang gi mchog tu de nyid gnas //
NK116(le)001:10131: grub matha'a ni bde stong rgya chad phyogs lhung dang
NK116(le)001:10132: bral ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shesa te
NK116(le)001:10133: / bcu gsum gyi sa la lhun gyis grub par 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:10134: grub mtha' ma snyogs na 'ad'a ka ma /
NK116(le)001:10135: gasnga chena phyag rgya chena posa 'pho ba la sbyangs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:10137: las la sbyar ba gsum yin no //
NK116(le)001:10138: 'bras bu ni dbang skabs phye ste bstan pa'i gdams
NK116(le)001:10139: pa la dbang thob bas sangs rgyas thams cad kyi
NK116(le)001:10140: thugs kyi gsang ba'i mthar thug pa mkha'a khyab ngo
NK116(le)001:10141: bo nyid kyi sku sgra ji bzhin par thob pa'o
NK116(le)001:10142: // de yang glang po rab 'bog las /
NK116(le)001:10143: rlung gi 'gros thim mi shigs rdo rje'i sku //
NK116(le)001:10144: lus ngag yid dag ngo bo nyid kyi sku //
NK116(le)001:10146: kha cig sher dbang gi thig le nor bu gnas pa'i bde ba gsum pa byas nas /
NK116(le)001:10147: de las 'phos pa dang byang sems lces myang ba bzhi bar 'dod pa dang /
NK116(le)001:10148: kha cig sher dbang gis lhan skyes brdzun par rtogs
NK116(le)001:10149: nas de'i bde ba la stong ba'i rgyas btabs pa'i
NK116(le)001:10150: bde stong dbyer med ba zhi bar 'dod pa dag
NK116(le)001:10151: ni ji bzhin ma nges ste /
NK116(le)001:10153: gsum pa nyams myong lhan cig skyes pa'i yeshesa de'i
NK116(le)001:10154: mtha' la brten nas gang zhig rtogs bya'i mi mthun
NK116(le)001:10155: phyogs shin tu phra ba'i rnam rtogs kun chad khu
NK116(le)001:10156: rdul gnyis steng 'og tu thim zhing 'gags pa'i mod
NK116(le)001:10157: la rang bzhin gyis dag par byed pas //
NK116(le)001:10158: dbang bzhi ba'i dpe rung la don dam pa bdag tu lta ba dang /
NK116(le)001:10159: 'khor 'das kyi chos su 'dzin pa'i rnam par rig
NK116(le)001:10160: pa thams cad rang gi ngo bos stong pa'i de
NK116(le)001:10161: kho na nyid la dbang bzhi pa'i bla dag tu
NK116(le)001:10162: btags nas gnas skabs su tshig tsam gyis mtshon par
NK116(le)001:10163: byed la / mthar thug de'i don gnyis su med
NK116(le)001:10164: pa'i ye shes gang yin pa ni dad pa dang
NK116(le)001:10165: byin brlabs kyis rtogs par bya ba'i dbang yin pas
NK116(le)001:10166: byed la / na / do ha las /
NK116(le)001:10167: bla ma'i byin brlabs gang gi snying zhugs pas /
NK116(le)001:10168: lag pa'i mthil na gnas pa'i gter mthong 'dra /
NK116(le)001:10170: de ltas dbang bzhi po'i sgra bshad ni sgra don zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:10172: gtor dang blug pa zhes bya ba /
NK116(le)001:10173: des na dbang zhes brjod par bya /
NK116(le)001:10175: dbang gi sgra dona ni legs sbyar skad du na
NK116(le)001:10176: a b+hi shany+tsa'i sgras slob ma'i rgyud kyi kun brtag
NK116(le)001:10177: glo bura ba'i dri ma thams cad gtor ba dang
NK116(le)001:10178: she ka tas / 'bras bu ye shes kyi skal
NK116(le)001:10179: ba ji ltar lugs su blug ltar rgyud la 'jog
NK116(le)001:10180: pa ste rnama pa gnyis su gruba pa yin no
NK116(le)001:10181: she ka tas / // dbang bzhi po'i rim pa
NK116(le)001:10182: rnams da lta nas rgyu lam 'bras bu'i rang bzhin
NK116(le)001:10183: du gnas pa'i tshul ston pa'i phyir dbang mchog ces
NK116(le)001:10184: bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:10185: dabnga gi mchoga ni lhan skyes su ranga la gansa pa'o //
NK116(le)001:10187: 'byung ba lnga dang yid shes kyi khamas te druga gi /
NK116(le)001:10188: rten dang rtsa thig rlung gsum gyi 'byor pa yang
NK116(le)001:10189: dag par tshangs pa gang zhig sa bon nam rgyu'i
NK116(le)001:10190: dabnga yina te / gdan gsum tshang pa'i ngo bo yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:10192: dang po lha yi rang bzhin du //
NK116(le)001:10193: rdo rje sems dpa' rnam par bzhugs //
NK116(le)001:10195: sloba dpona nyid kyisa cho ga ji lta ba bzhina pas bskura ba dang /
NK116(le)001:10196: ranga gisa kyang ji ltar phogs pa'i dmigas pa la 'drisa para byed pa lam gyi dabnga ste /
NK116(le)001:10198: slob ma dkyil 'khor bsdus nas ni /
NK116(le)001:10199: yon gyi mchog de blang nas ni //
NK116(le)001:10200: rdo rje ming gi dbang bskur bas //
NK116(le)001:10201: de bzhin gshegs par de lung bstan //
NK116(le)001:10202: phyag rgya'i sbyor ba 'di dag gis //
NK116(le)001:10203: byang chub snying po'i bar du ni //
NK116(le)001:10204: rdo rje'i ming du rab tu grags //
NK116(le)001:10205: de nas sangs rgyas sras su 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:10207: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg par /
NK116(le)001:10208: sa dang po nas sa bcu pa'i bar bgrod pa'i
NK116(le)001:10209: dusa der sangs rgyas rnams kyis 'oda zera chena po'i
NK116(le)001:10210: spro bsdu byas pa'i dbang bskur ba bzhina du /
NK116(le)001:10211: da lta nyid du rang semas sku bzhira smin pa ni bla na med pa'i 'brasa bu'i dabnga ngo //
NK116(le)001:10212: gzhan yang dang po'i sangs rgyas las /
NK116(le)001:10213: gsum pa 'jig rten kun rdzob ste /
NK116(le)001:10214: bzhi pa don gyi dam pa yin /
NK116(le)001:10215: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar bum pa sogs 'jig rten
NK116(le)001:10216: pa'i dabnga snga ma gsum dang bzhi pa 'das pa'i
NK116(le)001:10217: dbang bcas rdzogas tshe riga 'dzina sngags kyi sdoma pa
NK116(le)001:10219: zhar la skabs kyi dam tshig dang yon 'bul ba ni /
NK116(le)001:10220: rdo rje phur pa'i rgyud las /
NK116(le)001:10221: bum pa'i dam tshig gang yin pa //
NK116(le)001:10222: bskyed pa'i rim pa brtags pa dang //
NK116(le)001:10223: rmongs pa rnams las 'das byas te //
NK116(le)001:10224: snod kyi 'jig rten gzhal yas khang //
NK116(le)001:10225: bcud kyi sems can lha yi mchog /
NK116(le)001:10226: de ni bum pa'i dam tshig yin //
NK116(le)001:10227: gang zhig gsang ba ston pa la //
NK116(le)001:10228: gsang ba'i dam tshig 'di yin te //
NK116(le)001:10229: bud med shes rab rang bzhin pas //
NK116(le)001:10230: tsan+da li la rtag tu bsgom //
NK116(le)001:10231: zas lnga rtag tu bza' bar bya //
NK116(le)001:10232: spyad par bya ba'i mchog yin no //
NK116(le)001:10233: ye shes chen po'i dam tshig ni //
NK116(le)001:10234: mo rnams kun la spyad pa dang //
NK116(le)001:10235: dga' ba rtag tu brten par bya //
NK116(le)001:10236: sems nyid d+hu tir rab tu bltas //
NK116(le)001:10237: ye shes snying po'i dam tshig go /
NK116(le)001:10238: de lta bu ni mi ldan pas //
NK116(le)001:10239: dbang dang dam tshig kun las 'das //
NK116(le)001:10241: sngags pa bya ba gang yang med //
NK116(le)001:10242: sngags pa sngags pa zhes bya ba //
NK116(le)001:10243: rtsa ba dang ni yan lag dang //
NK116(le)001:10244: khyad par dam tshig gang yin dang //
NK116(le)001:10245: shin tu dbang gi dam tshig dang //
NK116(le)001:10246: rtsa dang rlung gi dam tshig dang //
NK116(le)001:10247: byang chub sems kyi bzhag pa rnams //
NK116(le)001:10248: gang zhig bzhag pa basngagasa pa yin //
NK116(le)001:10249: de la mchog gi dngos grub 'babs /
NK116(le)001:10251: de nas slob mas phyag dang bcas te yo byad dbul dgos pa ni //
NK116(le)001:10252: mya ngan las 'das pa'i rgyud las //
NK116(le)001:10253: gser la sogs pa yo byad dang //
NK116(le)001:10254: rang gi lus dang nor gyi dbyig /
NK116(le)001:10255: ma sring mo rnams brgyan pa dang //
NK116(le)001:10256: grong dang grong khyer bcas pa rnams //
NK116(le)001:10257: dmigs pa med pa'i sems kyis ni /
NK116(le)001:10258: de dang mnyam par kho nar 'bul /
NK116(le)001:10260: dbang thob pa'i phan yon ston pa'i phyir dbang thob ces bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:10261: de ltar dabnga rnams thoba pa'i skyes bu de'i rgyud
NK116(le)001:10262: nyon mongs pas tha bar byas pa'i skyon sbyong ba'i
NK116(le)001:10263: dpe ni / 'di ltar zhing sa rgod po slog
NK116(le)001:10264: pa sogs kyis gshin por byas nas sa bona bazhaga
NK116(le)001:10265: na lo tog smin pa ji bzhina du /
NK116(le)001:10266: sgo gsum shes bya'i sgrib pa ste bzhi dag par
NK116(le)001:10267: byed cing sku bzhi'i 'bras bu mngona sum du snang
NK116(le)001:10270: 'di yi bcom ldan bdag nyid che //
NK116(le)001:10271: sku gsum mi phyed las byung ba //
NK116(le)001:10272: ye shes rgya mtshor rnam par brgyan //
NK116(le)001:10276: dbang bskur yang dag byin ldan na //
NK116(le)001:10277: skye zhing skye bar dbang bskur 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:10278: de yi skye ba bdun na ni //
NK116(le)001:10279: ma sgom par yang dngos grub thob /
NK116(le)001:10280: ces thob pa'i phan yon dngos dang zhar byung ma thob pa'i nyes dmigs ni /
NK116(le)001:10282: dkyil 'khor du ni ma zhugs dang //
NK116(le)001:10283: dam tshig rnams ni spangs pa dang //
NK116(le)001:10284: gsang ba'i de nyid mi shes pas //
NK116(le)001:10285: bsgrub kyang ci yang mi 'grub bo //
NK116(le)001:10288: dper na bu tsha med pa'i khyim //
NK116(le)001:10289: shi ba tsam gyis stong pa nyid /
NK116(le)001:10290: de bzhin dbang dang bral ba'i lus //
NK116(le)001:10291: ye shes kun gyi stong pa yin //
NK116(le)001:10292: dper na pi wam sbyor sogs kun /
NK116(le)001:10293: rgyud dang bral na brdung mi nus //
NK116(le)001:10294: de bzhin dbang dang bral na ni //
NK116(le)001:10297: da ni grol byed gdams pa'i rim pa la //
NK116(le)001:10299: dang po ni gnyis pa zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:10300: dang po gong du bstan zin pa'i smin byed kyi
NK116(le)001:10301: rim pa thob pa'i 'og tu gnyis pa lam gyi
NK116(le)001:10302: rim pa la bskyed rdzogsa rnam pa gnyis lasa /
NK116(le)001:10303: dang po ni skyes bu chen pos don du gnyer
NK116(le)001:10304: bya sems can gya don du gzugs kyi sku bsgrub
NK116(le)001:10305: pa kho na yin la de 'thob pa'i thabs bskyed
NK116(le)001:10306: pa'i rima pa 'ba' zhig la ltos shing /
NK116(le)001:10307: de yang skye gansa rnama pa bzhi'i baga chagas sbyangsa
NK116(le)001:10308: phyir de dang mthuna para sgom dgos te 'og tu
NK116(le)001:10310: cis phyir skye gnas bzhi dang sbyor dgos snyams na /
NK116(le)001:10311: bskyed tshul 'khora ba'i rnam pa ci 'dra ba dang mthuna par bskyed pasa /
NK116(le)001:10312: srida pa gsuma po'i tha mal gyi snang zhen ma lusa par sbyong zhing daga par byed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:10313: 'khor ba ma dag rang rgyud par mi 'dzin zhing /
NK116(le)001:10314: mya ngana las 'adsa pa sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams
NK116(le)001:10315: ji lta ba dang bzhugas tshul mthuna pa yisa gsal
NK116(le)001:10316: stong 'dzin med lha'i 'khor lo'i rnam pa bsgom pasa
NK116(le)001:10317: mthar gyi 'brasa bu rang chas su rdzogs pa gzhi
NK116(le)001:10319: gnyis ka'ang rdzogas pa'i rima pa'i smina byed du 'gro
NK116(le)001:10320: ba'i daga rdzogas smina gsuma spyi la gcesa pa ni
NK116(le)001:10321: // snying po'i rgyud kha che'i 'gyur las //
NK116(le)001:10322: 'jig rten pa yi dngos grub ni //
NK116(le)001:10323: bskyed pa'i rim pa'i sbyor bas 'thob //
NK116(le)001:10325: rdzogs pa'i rim pa'i sbyor pas so //
NK116(le)001:10328: sangs rgyas rnams kyi chos ston pa //
NK116(le)001:10329: rim pa gnyis la yang dag gnas //
NK116(le)001:10330: bskyed pa yi ni rim pa dang //
NK116(le)001:10331: rdzogs pa yi ni rim pa'o //
NK116(le)001:10333: gnyis pa so sor bshad pa ni /
NK116(le)001:10335: skye gnas bzhi po dag bya'i phyir //
NK116(le)001:10336: bskyed pa'ang de bzhin rnam pa bzhi /
NK116(le)001:10337: spros bcas spros dang spros pa med //
NK116(le)001:10338: shin tu spros pa med bzhi'o //
NK116(le)001:10339: zhes pa 'khor ba'i 'dra 'bag skye gnas bzhi'i bag
NK116(le)001:10340: chags sbyongs pa'i gnyen po rgyas par ston pa las
NK116(le)001:10341: dang po sgong skyes sbyongs pa'i tshul ji ltar zhes
NK116(le)001:10342: bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:10343: de la yang ji ltar na sgong skyes kyi rigs rnams lana gnyis skye ba ltar //
NK116(le)001:10344: srid pa de'i bag chags sbyangs phyir badga srasa gazhana srasa rnam pa gnyis su bskyed pa las /
NK116(le)001:10345: dang po badga gi srasa su gazhana bya ba la lnga ste /
NK116(le)001:10346: rnam smin gyi lus bsam gtan gsum gyi man ngag
NK116(le)001:10347: la brten nas nam mkha'i dbyings su rgyu'i rdo rje
NK116(le)001:10348: 'dzin pa ste sa bona lasa ni gtso bo yab
NK116(le)001:10349: yum gang yin pa bskyed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:10350: phyogs bcu'i sangas rgyas rnams bkuga pa ste spyan drangs
NK116(le)001:10351: nas sras kyi sa bon du bsgrub pa'i phyir yum
NK116(le)001:10353: de bzhin du semas can rnams kyang bkuga nas yum
NK116(le)001:10354: gyi mkhar bstim la sgrib pa sbyangsa ba dang bcas
NK116(le)001:10355: rdzogs pas srid zhi gnyis su med par ro gcig
NK116(le)001:10356: gyur pa'i bdag nyid chen po nga'o snyam la che
NK116(le)001:10358: de'i rkyen gyi 'bras bu rdo rje 'dzin par bzhengs
NK116(le)001:10359: la yul gyi mkha' gsang nas 'khor rnams bton nasa
NK116(le)001:10360: dkyil 'khor gyi gadna la 'goda pa la bdag gi
NK116(le)001:10361: sras su sangs rgyas byas pa zhes bya'o //
NK116(le)001:10363: sras dang btsun mor bcas pa ni //
NK116(le)001:10364: 'khor ba'i chos las skyes pa ste //
NK116(le)001:10365: sems can gyi ni sras su bya /
NK116(le)001:10367: de dag ni slob dpon pad+ma'i dgongs pa'i man ngag sgrub sde'i lung ltar yin la rgyud ltar na //
NK116(le)001:10369: rang rgyud dngos dang mi 'gal zhing //
NK116(le)001:10370: 'bras bu nyid la lam shes pas //
NK116(le)001:10371: ma lus dkyil 'khor thig le rnams //
NK116(le)001:10372: bdag gi sras su bsgom par bya //
NK116(le)001:10373: zhes pa'i don rdor sems sgyu 'phrul dra ba ltar na /
NK116(le)001:10374: gtso bo yab yum bskyed nas snyoms par 'jug pa dang /
NK116(le)001:10375: ngo mtshar sras kyi dkyil 'khor yi ge'i sprin las spros pa gnyis las snga ma ni /
NK116(le)001:10378: snga ma gnyis spyi dang mthun la rgyu ting gi
NK116(le)001:10379: khyad ni +aahzhesa brjod pa'i rkyen las sems kyi rang
NK116(le)001:10381: sproo bsdu yongs su gyur ba las mngon byang gi
NK116(le)001:10382: rang bzhin nyi zla'i gdan as mtshan pa las byung
NK116(le)001:10383: ba'i yi ge rgyu dus khams dkar dmar /
NK116(le)001:10384: lam dus yi ge'i rgyu'am sbyangs gzhi /'bras dus mtshan
NK116(le)001:10385: gyi sa bon tsheg drag bcas pa'i +aahli bcu drug
NK116(le)001:10386: thabs shes kyi dbye bas phrag gnyis dkar po mu
NK116(le)001:10387: tig gi phreng ba lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:10388: dpe byed sa bon d+aa ma ru sogs rnam 'gyur
NK116(le)001:10389: gyi yi ge drug bsnan pas k+aa li bzhi bcu
NK116(le)001:10390: yang snga ma ltar phrag gnyis pos mar me'i phreng
NK116(le)001:10391: ba lta bu'i bskor ba thog mtha' gnyis nas 'od
NK116(le)001:10392: du zhu nas h'u gis mtshan pa'i rdo rje dang
NK116(le)001:10393: / de yongs su gyur pa las rang bzhin gzhi'i kun tu bzang por bsgom mo //
NK116(le)001:10394: de yang myang 'das dang gzhugs tshul mthun pa'i sbyong
NK116(le)001:10395: ba'i dbang du byas na nyi zla'i dal me long
NK116(le)001:10396: lta bu dang rdo rje'i rigs so //
NK116(le)001:10397: 'od kyi gong bu ni mnyam pa nyid dang rin chen rigs so //
NK116(le)001:10398: rdo rje h'u gis mtshan pa ni so sor rtog pa dang pad+ma'i rigs so //
NK116(le)001:10399: spro bsdu byed pa bya 'grub pa dang las kyi rigs so /
NK116(le)001:10400: sku yongs su rdzogs pa ni chos dbyings ye shes dang de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs so //
NK116(le)001:10401: 'bras dus kyi mngon byang lnga'i yon tan yongs su rdzogs pa'i tshul //
NK116(le)001:10402: rdo rje snying po'i rgyan gyi rgyud las //
NK116(le)001:10403: +aa li dang ni k+aa li dang //
NK116(le)001:10404: rdo rje zla ba rnam pa gnyis //
NK116(le)001:10405: gcig tu gyur pa mnyam nyid de //
NK116(le)001:10406: sa bon mtshan mar gyur pa ni //
NK116(le)001:10407: so sor rtogs pa nges bshad do //
NK116(le)001:10408: de byung sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK116(le)001:10409: 'gro don byed pa bya nan tan //
NK116(le)001:10410: gzugs brnyan rdzogs pa chos dbyings te /
NK116(le)001:10412: de nas rgyud gzhung bzhin gzhal yas khang gdan dang
NK116(le)001:10413: bcas pa bskyed 'phral kun tu bzang po'i g.yon tu
NK116(le)001:10414: bzang mo yab dang 'dra bar bskyed pa gnyis su
NK116(le)001:10417: sbyor mtshams nas byang chub sems kyi sprin yi ge'i
NK116(le)001:10418: rang bzhin du spros nas ngo mtshar sras kyi dkyil
NK116(le)001:10419: 'khor du bya ba ni tha dang gyi bar te
NK116(le)001:10420: bdag sras su sangs rgyas rnams byas pa lha'i dkyil
NK116(le)001:10421: 'khor du gyur nas rgyal ba'i mdzad pa bsgrub slar
NK116(le)001:10422: dkyil 'khor du byon te rnam snang yab yum gtso
NK116(le)001:10423: bo yab yum la thim pa'i gzhan rang gnas su
NK116(le)001:10425: gnyis pa gazhana gyi sras su badga bya ba //
NK116(le)001:10427: ji ltar sangs rgyas mthu las byung //
NK116(le)001:10428: lhun gyi grub pa'i cho ga dang //
NK116(le)001:10429: cho ga'i yan lag rdzogs pa las //
NK116(le)001:10430: mkhas pa sangs rgyas sras yin no //
NK116(le)001:10432: 'di la rnam grangs brgyad de ji ltar bya rnams dang po sgo nga smin pa de dang /
NK116(le)001:10433: gzoda bya'i gzugs su smin pa der gyura pa bzhina du bskyed pa yin la //
NK116(le)001:10434: de yang snga ma bzhin sgrub rgyud kyi lugs gnyis kyi dang po ni //
NK116(le)001:10435: gtso bo yab yum 'oda du zhu nas thig le
NK116(le)001:10436: mthing nag gi gong bu sa bona phyag mtshan gyis
NK116(le)001:10437: mtshan par gyur ba ni sgo nga dang /
NK116(le)001:10438: de lasa 'bras bu'i rdo rje 'dzin pa yaba yuma
NK116(le)001:10439: skye mcheda rdzogas pa ni sgo khyim rdol nas btsas
NK116(le)001:10440: pa 2dang / yaba kyi kun rtog rgyu'i tshags pa yi ge'i ranga bzhin du gyura ba 3dang /
NK116(le)001:10441: yuma lasa 'oda 'phrosa te sras bkrun pa'i phyir lha la gsola ba gadba pa 4 dang /
NK116(le)001:10442: dbyings kyi lha rnams kuna kyang rang la bstim zhing
NK116(le)001:10443: dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi bdag nyid nga 'o snyams
NK116(le)001:10445: bdag nyid dpal chen po yab yum snyomsa para zhugas
NK116(le)001:10446: nasa yum gyi mkha'a ru dkyil 'khora bskyed pa 6dang
NK116(le)001:10447: / bdag gi rtog pa'i yi ge bzhi bcu zhe
NK116(le)001:10448: gnyis lhar gasla te mngal nas 'byin tshul gyi phyir
NK116(le)001:10449: / gdona pa 7dang / de dag rnams lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas spyan drangs zhags pas gdan la bzhugs /
NK116(le)001:10450: lcags sgrog gis dam ye dbyer med du bstan par gnas /
NK116(le)001:10451: dril bus thams cad dgyes pa chen po'i ngang du
NK116(le)001:10452: bzhugs par bsam ste phyag rgya bzhi yisa bcinga pa
NK116(le)001:10454: gnyis pa rgyud sde'i lugs ni /
NK116(le)001:10456: gang gis gang la gsol btab pas //
NK116(le)001:10457: thugs rje'i byin rlabs sbyangs byas nas //
NK116(le)001:10458: thugs zhugs 'dres pa dbyer med na //
NK116(le)001:10459: sras 'gyur dgongs pa ci la gnas /
NK116(le)001:10461: de las snang stong gi phyogs gnyis la ltos pa'i
NK116(le)001:10462: rtag chad kyi zhen pa sbyongs pa'i tshul gnyis las
