NK116(le)001:10463: dang po snang phyogs kyi zhen pa sbyor ba la'ang
NK116(le)001:10464: gnyis te / thugs dam bskul ba dang /
NK116(le)001:10465: byin rlabs rjes su gnang ba'o //
NK116(le)001:10466: dang po ni gtso bo'i thugs ka nas rigs pa'i
NK116(le)001:10467: kun tu bzang po sems dpa'i rgyan ldan rnam smiin
NK116(le)001:10468: gyi lus kyi rnam pa can rkang pa'i long bu
NK116(le)001:10469: sprad cing thal mo sbyar ba 'thon nas /
NK116(le)001:10470: dkyil 'khor la lan gsum bskor nas /
NK116(le)001:10471: dga' ba chen po'i sgo nas me tog gtor bzhin pas gsol ba gdab /
NK116(le)001:10473: lha rnams kyi bdag la rjes su dgongs te thabs
NK116(le)001:10474: dang shes rab kyi 'od zer spros pas sems dang
NK116(le)001:10475: sems byung gi rtog pa dang /
NK116(le)001:10476: de las gyur pa'i rnam smin gyi lus ngag sbyangs /
NK116(le)001:10477: gzung 'dzin gnyis bral gyi rang bzhin gser zhun ma lta bu'i 'od kyi gong bur gyur ba las /
NK116(le)001:10478: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi sku gsung thugs 'od
NK116(le)001:10479: zer yi ge gsum gyi rnam pas bdag la bstim
NK116(le)001:10480: pas / gong bu nyid kyi de dang gnyis su
NK116(le)001:10481: med pa'i 'bras bu gsum du gyur nas rags pa
NK116(le)001:10482: sku gsung gi sa bon phra ba thugs kyi sa
NK116(le)001:10483: bon la 'dres nas zla dkyil la h'u du gnas
NK116(le)001:10484: par gyur pa de nyid rlung gi dkyil 'khor gyi
NK116(le)001:10485: btegs pas gtso bo'i thugs kar mda' 'phangs pa ltar
NK116(le)001:10486: song ba'i rkyen gyis yab yum bde ba'i rol mos
NK116(le)001:10487: tshim nas byang chub kyi sems dang gnyis su med
NK116(le)001:10488: pa'i gong bur gyur pa'i yum gyi mkha' la gnas
NK116(le)001:10489: pa la lha tshogs thams cad kyang rang rang gi
NK116(le)001:10490: gsang sngags kyi sku dang bcas nas byang chub kyi
NK116(le)001:10491: sems gong bu'i bdag nyid can la thim /
NK116(le)001:10492: de'i ngang la gtso bo yab yum kyang rjes chags
NK116(le)001:10493: chen pos bde ba'i ngo bor zhu ste thams cad
NK116(le)001:10494: gcig tu 'dres pa'i gong bur bsam mo //
NK116(le)001:10495: gnyis pa stong phyogs kyi zhen pa sbyongs pa ni
NK116(le)001:10496: gong bu de nyid kyang yi ge dang phyag mtshan
NK116(le)001:10497: gyi rnam par song ba yongs su gyur pa las
NK116(le)001:10498: / zhi ba dang khro bo'i sku gang yin par
NK116(le)001:10499: nga rgyal bskyed nas shu nya ta'i sngags kyis de
NK116(le)001:10500: la ye shes lnga'i dbang bskur sku gsung thugs yon
NK116(le)001:10501: tan phrin las lngar byin gyis brlabs /
NK116(le)001:10502: de nas gtso bo yab yum gyi mkha' la mkha'
NK116(le)001:10503: gsang rdo rje dang pad+mara byin gyis brlabs nas sa
NK116(le)001:10504: ma ya ho la sogs pa'i brda' dang brda' lan
NK116(le)001:10505: gyis bskul nas snyoms par zhugs te /
NK116(le)001:10506: byang chub sems yum gyi mngal la spros pas mkha' gsang gzhal yas khang du byin gyis brlabs /
NK116(le)001:10507: de'i nang du lha rnams kyi sa bon gsal btab la /
NK116(le)001:10508: lha so so'i gsang sngags brjod pa'i rkyen gyi sku yongs su rdzogs par gyur /
NK116(le)001:10509: de rnams dzahzhesa brjod pa tsam gyi yum mkha' nas
NK116(le)001:10510: bton te mdun gyi nam mkhar bzhugs pa la 'bru
NK116(le)001:10511: gsum gyis gsang gsum byin gyis brlabs /
NK116(le)001:10512: 'od zer spro bsdus sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrub
NK116(le)001:10513: nas rang rang gi gdan la bzhugs par bsam mo
NK116(le)001:10514: // de'ang sgyu 'phrul zhi ba'i dbang du byas na
NK116(le)001:10515: kun bzang yab yum ni gtso bo'i thugs ka'i khyams
NK116(le)001:10516: // dang / thub drug phyi'i khyams la bskyed pa dmigs bsal lo //
NK116(le)001:10517: tshul de dag spros pa chung ngu'i dbang du dgongs
NK116(le)001:10518: nas bsdu na zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs
NK116(le)001:10519: te / bsdu na thoga mara ranga nyid bsgrub bya'i lha gang yin pa de'i skur gasla ba'i /
NK116(le)001:10520: mduna gyi nam makhara dkyil 'khora gyi lha gsal btab pa dang /
NK116(le)001:10521: rang gi thugs ka nas dkyil 'khor spro ba dang /
NK116(le)001:10522: dbyings nas spyan drangs zhing mdun mkhar bzhugs par dmigs
NK116(le)001:10523: pa ste gsum du yod pa gang rung dkyus ltar
NK116(le)001:10524: gasla btab nas rgyun bashagas yan lag bdun pa byas
NK116(le)001:10525: mthar / bdag dang tshogs zhing gnyis ka mi dmigas
NK116(le)001:10526: pa'i nganga nas slar lha so so'i dkyil 'khora mngona
NK116(le)001:10528: gnyis pa mangla skyes sbyong pa'i phyir mngona byang bzhi'am lnga'i rnam grangs bstan pa la /
NK116(le)001:10529: dang po ni khraga 'thunga he ru ka gala po'i dgongas pa ste de nyid las /
NK116(le)001:10530: dang po stong pa byang chub sems //
NK116(le)001:10531: gnyis pa sa bon 'byung ba ste //
NK116(le)001:10532: gsum pa la ni gzugs rdzogs pa //
NK116(le)001:10533: bzhi pa la ni yi ger 'god /
NK116(le)001:10535: 'chi srid zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:10536: 'chi ba dang ni srid pa'i bar dora bacasa pa stong nyid byang chub semas kyis sbyongs /
NK116(le)001:10537: dri za nye bar lena pa'i rnam shesa khu khrag
NK116(le)001:10538: dang 'dres pa ni lha yi sa bona gyi nus
NK116(le)001:10539: pasa sbyangsa la de nyid kyang khu rdula rlung gsum
NK116(le)001:10540: dang ro gcig tu 'dresa pa'i dus na rim bzhin
NK116(le)001:10541: gnas skabs lnga nyams su myong pa yin te /
NK116(le)001:10542: 'di ltar mera mera nur nur po rnams lha'i sa
NK116(le)001:10543: bona nyid lasa phyag matshana du gyur pasa sbyangsa zhing
NK116(le)001:10544: / ltar ltar dang mkhranga gyura po rnams phyag matshana
NK116(le)001:10545: 'oda kyi gonga bur gyur pas sbyongs la khyaba 'juga
NK116(le)001:10546: nya dang rusa sbala dabnga po rdzogas pa rnams ni
NK116(le)001:10547: lha yi rnam para gyur nasa sbyongas pa'o //
NK116(le)001:10548: de las bsdu na lha gang yin de'i rnam pa
NK116(le)001:10549: thams cad pa rdzogs par bsgom par phyag rgya sku
NK116(le)001:10550: la bslab pa / sa bon gyi yiga 'bru gang rung bsgom pa gsunga rdo rje ste /
NK116(le)001:10551: thugs ni rdo rje rtse lnga pa la sogs phyag matshana nyid du sbyor ba la /
NK116(le)001:10552: rdo rje'i cho ga gsuma zhesa pha rgyud kyi lugas
NK116(le)001:10553: de'i sbyang bya ni dang pos 'byung ba byer sdud
NK116(le)001:10554: kyi lus yongs su grub nas phyir btsas pa sbyongs
NK116(le)001:10555: la / gnyis pas khu khrag sems gsum 'dres nas gnas skabs lnga'i nyams su myongs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:10556: gsum pas mngal du khams dkar dmar tshogs pa dri za'i rnam shes zhugs pa'i skabs sbyong ngo /
NK116(le)001:10557: 'bras dus sgo gsum rdo rje gsum du bsgrub pa'i rten 'brel bsgrig go /
NK116(le)001:10559: btsun mo'i b+ha ga bde chen du //
NK116(le)001:10560: ston pa sum cu rtsa gnyis mtshan //
NK116(le)001:10561: gtso bo dpe byad brgyad bcur ldan /
NK116(le)001:10563: skye ba sprul pa'i sku dang sbyar ba'i 'dod tshul
NK116(le)001:10564: ni bar ma zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te
NK116(le)001:10565: / de la 'chi ba chos sku'i 'od gsal lugs
NK116(le)001:10566: ldog tu mched pa'i yid lus bar do longs spyod
NK116(le)001:10567: rdzogs pa'i skur ldang mi nus pa'am /
NK116(le)001:10568: nus kyang gzhan la rjes chags kyi skye ba 'dzin
NK116(le)001:10569: pa dag gis bar ma dora nasa sems bskyed dang
NK116(le)001:10570: ldan pas lusa rten 'tshola ba tshogas kyi lam dang
NK116(le)001:10571: / mangla gyi sgo 'dam nas de ma thag tu rnama shesa 'juga pa sbyor lam ste /
NK116(le)001:10572: lhumsa su zhugsa zin pa'i dus der byang chuba sems rnam pa lnga po mthonga sgoma gyi lam dang /
NK116(le)001:10573: zla ba bcu ni sa bcu dang raba tu sbyar
NK116(le)001:10574: te de nasa lhag pa'i lha gang yin gyi 'du
NK116(le)001:10575: shes dang ldan bzhin phyir batsa'a ba mi slob pa'i
NK116(le)001:10576: lam mtshon par gyur te mchog gi sku sprul pa'i
NK116(le)001:10579: mngal zhugs byang chub rnam lnga ste //
NK116(le)001:10580: zla ba bcu ni sa bcu'i tshul //
NK116(le)001:10581: skyes pa rang bzhin sprul pa'i sku //
NK116(le)001:10582: lhun grub sku gsum bdag nyid do //
NK116(le)001:10584: da ni mngon byang lnga'i mtshan nyid so sor bshad
NK116(le)001:10585: pa mngon byang dang po zhes bya ba la sogs
NK116(le)001:10586: pas bstan te // sbyongs byed ni rnam snang gi gtso bo +aa li las byung ba'i //
NK116(le)001:10587: mngona byang dang po zla ba'i dkyil 'khora du bsgom pa ni rnam pa lam byed /
NK116(le)001:10588: de'i ngo bo chos thams cad me long gi gzugs
NK116(le)001:10589: brnyan ltar snang bas me long lta bu'i ye shes
NK116(le)001:10590: su mos pa ni mos pa lam byed //
NK116(le)001:10591: de'ang chos sku'i ye shes sgrib med du gsal ba ni 'bras bu lam byed //
NK116(le)001:10592: de gsum la brten nas tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i rten
NK116(le)001:10593: 'brel du gyur pa ni byin rlabs lam byed ces
NK116(le)001:10594: bya ba las phyi ma 'di 'chad 'gyur bzhi so
NK116(le)001:10596: sbyang gzhi gzugs kyi phung po 'byung ba chu khams kun gzhi'i rnam shes /
NK116(le)001:10598: mangla skyes khu ba droda gshera skyes kyi gshera /
NK116(le)001:10599: sgonga skyesa kyi pha dang rdzus skyes kyis stong ba'i cha rnams so //
NK116(le)001:10600: de bzhina gnyis pa ni rin 'byung gi ngo bo
NK116(le)001:10601: k+aa li las byung ba'i nyi ma'i dkyila 'khora du
NK116(le)001:10602: bsgom pa yanga rnam pa dang /
NK116(le)001:10603: de'i ngo bo chos rnams mnyam nyid du rtogs pa'i ye shes su mos pa ni mos pa /
NK116(le)001:10604: de'ang 'khor 'das kyi rang bzhin dngos po gcig par
NK116(le)001:10605: thugs su chud pa'i ye shes sgrib med du gsal
NK116(le)001:10606: bas na 'bras bu lam byed te gnyis pa'o //
NK116(le)001:10607: sbyang gzhi tshor ba dang sa khams //
NK116(le)001:10608: nyon yid ser sna dang nga rgyal //
NK116(le)001:10609: mangla skyes kyi rdul dang drod gshera skyes kyi drod /
NK116(le)001:10610: sgong skyes kyi mas cha dang bardzusa skyes kyi gasla ba'i cha rnams so //
NK116(le)001:10611: mngona byang gsuma pa 'od dpag med kyi ngo bo
NK116(le)001:10612: sa bona phyag matshana dang bacasa pa'i rnam par bsgom
NK116(le)001:10614: de'i ngo bo chos rnams ma 'dres par rtogs pa'i ye shes su mos pa ni mos pa /
NK116(le)001:10615: de'ang chos kun ma sgrib par gsal zhing mkhyen pa'i
NK116(le)001:10616: ye shes so sor rtogs pa ni 'bras bu lam
NK116(le)001:10618: sbyang gzhi 'dus shes kyi phung po dang me khams /
NK116(le)001:10620: nyon mongs 'dod chags mngal skyes kyi khu rdul gnyis para rnam shesa zhugas pa dang /
NK116(le)001:10621: skye gansa bzhi po'i bar do'i rnama shesa sbyong pa'o //
NK116(le)001:10622: mngona byang bzhi pa ni don grub kyi ngo bo
NK116(le)001:10623: nyi zla phyag mtshan rnam pa gsuma po gciga tu
NK116(le)001:10624: 'dresa pa'i thig le gong bu'i rnam pa can du
NK116(le)001:10626: de'i ngo bo sangs rgyas rnams kyi mdzad pa ro gcig tu 'dres pa'i ye shes su mos pa /
NK116(le)001:10627: gang la gang 'dul gyi bya ba thams cad grub
NK116(le)001:10628: pa'i ye shes ni 'bras bu lam byed de gnyen
NK116(le)001:10629: po'o // sbyang gzhi 'du byed kyi phung po dang rlung khams //
NK116(le)001:10632: skye gnas snga ma gnyis dang bstun na khu rdul semas gsuma ro gciga 'dresa pa dang /
NK116(le)001:10633: droda gshera skyes kyi droda dang rnam shesa dang //
NK116(le)001:10634: bardzusa skyes kyi gasla la stong pa'i cha tsam dang //
NK116(le)001:10635: bar srid 'dresa pa'i cha rnamas sbyong ba yina no //
NK116(le)001:10636: mngona byang lnga pa rgyus he ru ka yab yum
NK116(le)001:10637: gyi sku ru grub para bskyed pa ni rnam pa
NK116(le)001:10638: // de la yon tan thams cad rdzoogs par sems pa mos pa /
NK116(le)001:10639: de'i ngo bo chos dbyings ye shes su ro gcig pa 'bras bu lam byed de gnyen po'o //
NK116(le)001:10640: sbyang gzhi rnam shes kyi phung po dang nam mkha'i khams /
NK116(le)001:10641: rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyi rten kun gzhi /
NK116(le)001:10643: skye gansa bzhi bo'i skye mcheda yongas su rdzogs nas /
NK116(le)001:10644: btsas te riga pa'i yula la dabnga po rnams sada
NK116(le)001:10645: pa yi dus sogs 'khora ba'i rnam pa cha dang
NK116(le)001:10646: bacasa pa sbyong pa yin no //
NK116(le)001:10648: zla ba me long ye shes te //
NK116(le)001:10649: bdun gyi bdun pa mnyam pa nyid //
NK116(le)001:10650: rang lha'i sa bon phyag mtshan ni //
NK116(le)001:10651: so sor rtog par brjod par bya /
NK116(le)001:10652: thams cad gcig gyur nan ga tan nyid //
NK116(le)001:10653: rdzogs pa chos dbyings dag pa ste /
NK116(le)001:10655: mngon byang lnga'i byed las kyi sbyangs pa'i mthar rgyu'i
NK116(le)001:10656: rdo rje 'dzin par rdzoogs pa ni mngal skyes la
NK116(le)001:10657: mtshon na rang gi pha ma'i mtshon pa'i sbyangs gzhi
NK116(le)001:10658: yin la / de'i ngang las rgyu'i rdo rje 'dzin
NK116(le)001:10659: pa yab yum thig ler zhu ba ni bar de'i
NK116(le)001:10660: yin la / skabs mtshon la // de nas zhu
NK116(le)001:10661: ba 'khor gyi lha mo'i glus bskul gyis sgras rkyen
NK116(le)001:10662: gyis khamas dang phunga po rnama para shesa pa'i tshogas
NK116(le)001:10663: yin la / skabs mtshon la // // gansa su
NK116(le)001:10664: daga pa gadna gsuma tshanga pa'i lha skur bzhengs te
NK116(le)001:10665: mya ngan las 'adsa pa'i zhing khams dang bzhugs tshul
NK116(le)001:10666: yin la / skabs mtshon la // // mthuna pa
NK116(le)001:10667: ni / rgyu lasa 'brasa bu'i he ru ka ste
NK116(le)001:10668: yin la / skabs mtshon la // // mthuna pa
NK116(le)001:10669: ni / / bur gyur pa'i cha dang rnam 'gyur
NK116(le)001:10672: mngal skyes glu yi sbyor ba yi //
NK116(le)001:10673: bsgom pa rnams ni yongs su brtag /
NK116(le)001:10674: sgong skyes glu ni med pa ste /
NK116(le)001:10675: zhes mngal skyes bshad ma thag pa dang /
NK116(le)001:10676: de las sgong skyes kyi dmigs gsal ni //
NK116(le)001:10677: nyi zla'i bar du 'od gong zhub sa bon dang mtshan ma'i rnam pas lha skur bzhengs pa'o //
NK116(le)001:10678: de ltar khu rdula rlung gsuma semas dang bacasa pa'i cha rnama para daga pasa na /
NK116(le)001:10679: 'chad 'gyur rdzogas rima gyi smin byed du yang 'gyura ba yin no //
NK116(le)001:10680: skye gnas rags pa gnyis kyi gnyen po ma h+aa yo gas rgyas par bshad nas /
NK116(le)001:10681: phra ba khu rdul la ma ltos pa gnyis po
NK116(le)001:10682: spros pa bskyung ste 'chad pa la gsum pa drod
NK116(le)001:10683: gsher zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:10684: droda gshera skyes ni drod dang gsher gnyis po 'dusa
NK116(le)001:10685: pa lasa bar do'i rnam shesa zhugas pa'i moda la
NK116(le)001:10687: bskyed rim snga ma gnyis goms brtan cher thob pa'i rnal 'byor bas /
NK116(le)001:10688: mngon byang lnga la sogs pa dor nas /
NK116(le)001:10689: a nu yo ga'i grub matha'i bskyed rim ni lha
NK116(le)001:10690: yi matshana dang mngona rtog drana pa'i brjod pa tsam
NK116(le)001:10691: gyis shes rab kyi dbyings stong nyid kun tu bzang
NK116(le)001:10692: mo'i klong lasa kun rdzob bden pa'i cha lha'i phyag
NK116(le)001:10693: rgya rdzogas pa'i bskyed rima tshangas para bsgom pa ste
NK116(le)001:10694: / bang mdzod 'phrul gyi sde mig las /
NK116(le)001:10695: a nu yo ga'i theg par ni /
NK116(le)001:10696: snying po tsam zhig brjod byas pas //
NK116(le)001:10697: ma bskyed rdzogs pa'i lha ru bsgom /
NK116(le)001:10699: bzhi pa bardzusa te zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:10700: bardzusa te skye ba ni rgyu rkyen tshogs pa la ma ltos par skad ciga la grub pa ste /
NK116(le)001:10701: de'i gnyen por lha de'i rnam pa'am snying po dran pa'i mod la 'khor lo yongs su rdzogas te /
NK116(le)001:10702: minga dang gzugas rim gyis pa la ma brten par
NK116(le)001:10703: wara gyis chu las nya 'phar ba bzhin gasla ba
NK116(le)001:10705: gcig char 'jug pa gang zhe na //
NK116(le)001:10706: lha rnams ma bskyed snying po dran pas rdzogs /
NK116(le)001:10709: skad cig tsam pa'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NK116(le)001:10710: rdzogs pa'i rim pa bsgom pa ni //
NK116(le)001:10711: khams gsum gzhal yas khang bdag nyid //
NK116(le)001:10712: srog chags rnams ni dkyil 'khor pa //
NK116(le)001:10713: de dbus skad cig rnam pa yi //
NK116(le)001:10717: sems can bardzusa te skye ba bzhin //
NK116(le)001:10718: sa bon med par rnam par bsgom //
NK116(le)001:10720: de lta'i sgom tshul bzhi po gom brtan gyi nus
NK116(le)001:10721: pa la dpag nas 'jug pa sgom tshul zhes bya
NK116(le)001:10722: ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:10723: de lta'i sgoma tshul bzhi po'ang dang po'i lasa cana gsar bu la /
NK116(le)001:10724: sgong skyes spyong ba'i bskyed rima gtso bora bsgoma pa dang /
NK116(le)001:10725: rima bzhina goma pa brtana pa la mngal skyes dang //
NK116(le)001:10726: brtan pa che ba'i dus drod gsher skyes /
NK116(le)001:10727: shina tu brtana pa'i dus bardzusa skyes te so so'i blo'i mthu dang mthuna para slob pa ni /
NK116(le)001:10729: bskyed pa'i rim pas dkyil 'khor bsgom /
NK116(le)001:10730: rtul 'bring dag gis bsam par bya //
NK116(le)001:10731: rnal 'byor skad cig rnam pa yi //
NK116(le)001:10732: sems tsam nyid kyi dkyil 'khor te //
NK116(le)001:10733: skad cig rnam pa'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NK116(le)001:10734: rdzogs pa'i rim pa bsgom par bya //
NK116(le)001:10736: de lta'i rnam par bzhag pa'i spyi chings ni kun kyang zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:10737: bskyed pa'i rim pa kuna kyang thog mar de bzhina nyid kyi ting nge 'dzina /
NK116(le)001:10738: sprosa pa kuna dang bral ba'i shesa raba kyi gadngas
NK116(le)001:10739: rang bzhin lhun grub kyi lta ba gtan la 'bebs
NK116(le)001:10741: stong pa bdag med ye mkhyen rang rig thugs //
NK116(le)001:10742: dmigs bya dmigs byed med par dran dbang bsgyur /
NK116(le)001:10743: ngo mtshar sku gsum yon tan zhing khams las //
NK116(le)001:10744: gzhan na med de de nyid de ltar yin /
NK116(le)001:10746: tshul de nyid sgra ji bzhin par rtogs na 'phags
NK116(le)001:10747: pa'i mthong lam sa dang po na yod pa'i lhag
NK116(le)001:10748: bsam rnam dag rang shugs kyi skye ba /
NK116(le)001:10749: so skyes sa na rjes dpag gi chos nyid de'i
NK116(le)001:10750: gdangs snying rje chen por longs pa mos pas spyod
NK116(le)001:10751: pa'i sems bskyed la kuna tu snang ba'i ting nge
NK116(le)001:10752: 'dzin zhes snying rje'i 'phena pa'i rjes su rgyu'i spro
NK116(le)001:10753: bsdu byas te bskyed rima du lha'i 'khor lo shara
NK116(le)001:10754: ba gang zhig thabas kyi lam mchoga ma nora ba
NK116(le)001:10755: yin zhing / snang stong res 'jog can min par
NK116(le)001:10756: snang dusa nyid nasa ranga bzhina ma gruba pa chu
NK116(le)001:10758: zaba mo snang stong thabas dang shesa rab zung du 'jug pa 'brel ba'i lam mchog tu gyur pa'o //
NK116(le)001:10760: bskyed pa'i rim pa'i rnal 'byor gyi brtul zhugs can gyis spros pa bsgom /
NK116(le)001:10761: spros pa rmi lam ltar bsgom na /
NK116(le)001:10762: spros pa nyid kyang spros med byed /
NK116(le)001:10764: bskyed pa'i rim pa nyid dang ni /
NK116(le)001:10765: rdzogs pa yi ni rim pa ste /
NK116(le)001:10766: rim gnyis mnyam par bzhag nas ni /
NK116(le)001:10767: rdo rje can gyi chos 'chad do //
NK116(le)001:10769: de lta'i bskyed pa'i rim pa las snga ma gnyis
NK116(le)001:10770: la thun mong du gyur pa phyag rgya bzhis bcing
NK116(le)001:10772: rgyas gdab pa'i tshul gsum gyi dang po ni ye
NK116(le)001:10773: shes pa spyan drangs ma thag phyag rgya bzhi dang
NK116(le)001:10774: sbrel ba'i sngags kyi dang pos /
NK116(le)001:10775: ye shes sems dpa' dam tshig sems dpa'i spyi bor bkugs /
NK116(le)001:10777: gsum pas dbyer med du bcing /
NK116(le)001:10778: bzhi pas dgyes pa bskyed pa'o //
NK116(le)001:10779: tshul de la sbyor ba'i ting 'dzin nam snyom 'jug gi tha snyad byed cing /
NK116(le)001:10780: 'khor gyi lha rnams yongs rdzogs bskyed pa dkyil 'khor rgyal mchog /
NK116(le)001:10781: mchod bstod phrin las la sogs las rgyal mchog te ting 'dzin gsum du bshad nas /
NK116(le)001:10784: sprul sku 'grub pa'i rten 'brel lam byed du bstan pa ni /
NK116(le)001:10786: dang po sbyor bas ting 'dzin mchog /
NK116(le)001:10788: de nas dkyil 'khor rgyal po mchog /
NK116(le)001:10789: de nas yang ni las rgyal po /
NK116(le)001:10791: gdan gsum tshangs pa'i lha spyan drangs nas cho ga'i snying po bsdus pas dbang bzhi bskur ba'am //
NK116(le)001:10792: yang na byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin du gnas
NK116(le)001:10793: pa'i chu rgyun gyis dbang bskur bas bag chags kyi
NK116(le)001:10795: smin mtshams mgrin pa snying ga rkang mthil yan chad khengs pas dbang bzhi thob /
NK116(le)001:10796: chu'i lhag ma gyen du 'khyil ba las rigs pa dag gang yin gyis rgyas gdab bo //
NK116(le)001:10799: phyag rgya rtags dang mtshan ma te /
NK116(le)001:10800: 'dis ni rigs ni mtshon par bya /
NK116(le)001:10801: zhes rigs bdag gis rgyas 'debs pa 'di ni rdo
NK116(le)001:10802: rje thegs pa'i gzhi lam 'bras gsum gyi mtshon pa'i
NK116(le)001:10803: don te / spyir mi bskyod pas lhag ma bzhi la rgyas gdab pa'i dgongs pa ni /
NK116(le)001:10804: de ni sems kyi ngo bo nyid yin cing /
NK116(le)001:10805: gzugs sogs sems tsam gyis las su zad pas de
NK116(le)001:10806: dag byed por shes pa'i don te rang bzhin la
NK116(le)001:10807: rang bzhin gyi rgya zhes bya'o //
NK116(le)001:10808: dbye na gtso bo yab yum rang sems su shes
NK116(le)001:10809: pa la yid kyi ngo bo mi bskyod pas rgyas
NK116(le)001:10810: 'debs pa ni / ngo bo la ngo bo nyid kyi rgya /
NK116(le)001:10811: lus dag pa'i ngo bo rnam snang la sems dag
NK116(le)001:10812: pa'i ngo bo mi bskyod pas rgyas 'debs pa ni
NK116(le)001:10814: yid dag pa'i ngo bo mi bskyod pa la lus
NK116(le)001:10815: dag pa'i ngo bo rnam snang gi rgyas 'debs pa
NK116(le)001:10816: ni sems la lus kyi rgya /
NK116(le)001:10817: 'dod chags dag pa'i ngo bo 'od dpag med la
NK116(le)001:10818: 'bras bu ser sna dag pa'i ngo bo rin 'byung
NK116(le)001:10819: gi rgyas 'debs pa ni rgyu la 'bras bu rgya
NK116(le)001:10820: / 'bras bu phrag dog dag pa'i ngo bo don grub la /
NK116(le)001:10821: rgyu 'dod chags dag pa'i ngo bo 'od dpag med
NK116(le)001:10822: kyis rgyas 'debs pa ni 'bras bu la rgyu'i rgya'o
NK116(le)001:10823: // spyir phung khams skye mched lhar bsgom pa ni /
NK116(le)001:10824: kun brtags la gzhan dbang dbang gi rgya /
NK116(le)001:10825: lha rnams kyi spyi bor rang rigs kyi rigs bdag gis rgyas gdabs pa ni /
NK116(le)001:10826: gzhan dbang la gzhan dbang gi rgya /
NK116(le)001:10827: rigs pa dag de'i spyi bor rang rigs kyi phyag
NK116(le)001:10828: mtshan gyis rgyas gdab pa ni gzhan dbang la yongs
NK116(le)001:10830: de bzhin skye mched bcu gnyis kyi lha la rgyas
NK116(le)001:10831: 'debs lugs kyang mig la rnam snang rna ba mi
NK116(le)001:10832: bskyod pa la / sna la rin 'byung /
NK116(le)001:10839: reg bya dang chos la mi bskyod pa /
NK116(le)001:10842: chu dang nam mkha' la mi bskyod pa /
NK116(le)001:10844: rlung la don grub ste so so'i yon tan gyi
NK116(le)001:10845: cha dang byed las dang mthun pa'i dag pa sbyor
NK116(le)001:10846: ro // de'i 'ga' zla de las zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:10847: de lasa 'agla ba'i bden grub kyi dmigas pa dang bacasa pa'i bskyed rima ni /
NK116(le)001:10848: mu stegsa byed dang mi ma yin pa'i gdona gyi
NK116(le)001:10849: rigas phal mo che la'ang yoda na byang chub kyi
NK116(le)001:10850: gsos su mi 'gro ba ltar zhog shin tu ma
NK116(le)001:10851: rungs par yang bgyid par 'gyur bas yang dag pa
NK116(le)001:10852: zhig gal che'o // snga ma'i grub 'bras ni sngags su zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:10853: de dag gi rim pa ni sngagas rdo rje'i theg
NK116(le)001:10854: pa'i lugs su rgyu'i byang chuba semas dpa'i mthonga lam
NK116(le)001:10855: sa dang po rab tu dga' ba la /
NK116(le)001:10856: phyag rgya chena po mchoga gi dngosa gruba cesa yongs
NK116(le)001:10857: la shina tu gragsa pa de mngona du byed pa'i
NK116(le)001:10858: / thabas ma nor ba yin te /
NK116(le)001:10860: he ru ka'i zhal lung las /
NK116(le)001:10861: snang cha lha sku gsal ba yi /
NK116(le)001:10862: bsod nams tshogs kyang 'di yis rdzogs /
NK116(le)001:10863: de la dngos zhen rnam dag pa'i //
NK116(le)001:10864: ye shes tshogs ni rdzogs pa yin /
NK116(le)001:10865: zhes snang cha lha sku gasla basa //
NK116(le)001:10867: de la ranga bzhina ma gruba pas ye shesa te /
NK116(le)001:10868: tshogas gnyis rdzogs pa'i nye rgyur brten pa'i dabnga po rnona po dag dang /
NK116(le)001:10869: rgyu'i theg pa'i lam lnga'i rnam par bzhag pa dang ji ltar 'brel ba'i tshul ni //
NK116(le)001:10870: rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde snod las //
NK116(le)001:10871: phung po khams rnams lnga ru bsgom //
NK116(le)001:10873: de nyid 'dris byed sbyor ba'i lam //
NK116(le)001:10874: kun tu bzang po he ru ka /
NK116(le)001:10875: sems su smin pa mthong ba'i lam //
NK116(le)001:10876: shin tu brtan pa bsgom pa'i lam //
NK116(le)001:10877: dbyings ye gnyis med mthar phyin lam //
NK116(le)001:10879: thog mar chos thams cad yi ge'i sgo la gnas pas na rim par slob pa'i tshul //
NK116(le)001:10880: rdo rje sems dpa'i sgyu dra las /
NK116(le)001:10881: sems nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin te //
NK116(le)001:10882: yi ge yid bzhin rin chen sprin /
NK116(le)001:10885: a ni yig 'bru kun gyi mchog /
NK116(le)001:10886: don chen yi ge dam pa yin /
NK116(le)001:10888: dbye ba rang bzhin lhun grub kyi yi ge 'od gsal ba'i sems nyid //
NK116(le)001:10889: lus gnas rtsa'i yi ge dbyangs gsal lha'i sa bon dang /
NK116(le)001:10890: sgra don rtags kyi yi ge sgra spyi dang don spyi'i rnam par brtags pa dang /
NK116(le)001:10891: mtshan ma gzugs kyi yi ge lany+tsa dang na gar sogs rgya gar shar nub kyi yig rigs dang /
NK116(le)001:10892: bod kyi yi ge'i mtshon pa'i lha'i thugs srog dang
NK116(le)001:10893: sngags phreng sogs la thog mar dmigs nas rim bzhin
NK116(le)001:10894: phyag mtshan sku rkyang de nas rgyan ldan yum dang
NK116(le)001:10896: 'od zer spro bsdu la zhugs pa ni dkyil 'khor dang po'i ting nge 'dzin te /
NK116(le)001:10897: tshogs lam gsum rdzogs nas spyan dang mngon shes phra
NK116(le)001:10898: mo grub pa nas chos kyi rgyun gyi ting nge
NK116(le)001:10899: 'dzin thob / sprul pa'i sku'i zhal mthong /
NK116(le)001:10900: de nas tshad med bzhi mtshon pa'i sgo bzhi dang /
NK116(le)001:10901: dbus kyi phyur bur bcas lnga la dkyil 'khor spro ba las //
NK116(le)001:10902: dbus ma'i gtsang khang du gzugs kyi rgyal po la sogs pa'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs pa gcig bsgom shing /
NK116(le)001:10903: de yang zhi khro spel mar sgom pa la brtan
NK116(le)001:10904: pa thob pa'i sbyor lam nges 'byed cha bzhi las
NK116(le)001:10905: dang po thob / de bzhin shar sgo'i rta bab kyi khang par mi bskyod bsgom pas gnyis pa /
NK116(le)001:10906: nub sgo snang mtha' gsum pa /
NK116(le)001:10907: lho sgo'i rin 'byung gis bzhi pa thob la /
NK116(le)001:10908: byang sgo don grub kyi mthong lam thob nas rgyu'i sa dang po'i yon tan rdzogs so //
NK116(le)001:10909: de lta'i dkyil 'khor stong phrag bcu gnyis dang /
NK116(le)001:10910: bye ba phrag bcu gnyis dang /
NK116(le)001:10911: bye ba khrag khrig brgya dang /
NK116(le)001:10912: bye ba phrag khrig stong dang /
NK116(le)001:10913: bye ba phrag khrig brgya stong dang /
NK116(le)001:10914: khri phrag brjod du med pa dang /
NK116(le)001:10917: grangs med bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK116(le)001:10918: gyi bar bsgom pas rim bzhin sa gnyis pa nas
NK116(le)001:10919: bcu pa dang / de'i mthar khya ba bdag rdo
NK116(le)001:10920: rje 'chang gis 'od zer chen po'i dbang bskur bas
NK116(le)001:10921: sa bcu gcig pa bgrod pa'i skad cig der sngags
NK116(le)001:10922: lam gyi sa khyad par can rnams kyang mnga' dbang
NK116(le)001:10923: chub bas mthar thug gi sangs rgyas brnyes pa'o //
NK116(le)001:10924: yang riga 'dzina rnama pa bzhi bgrod pa'i dbang du bshad na /
NK116(le)001:10925: rig 'dzin snga ma gnyis bzhed tshul gnyis kyi dang po ni /
NK116(le)001:10926: bskyed rim la brtan pa thob pa'i sems nyid lhar
NK116(le)001:10927: smin yang 'byung ba'i snyigs ma nye rgyu'i spyod pas
NK116(le)001:10928: sbyong bar ma nus pa rnams ni tshogs sbyor gyi
NK116(le)001:10929: lam la gnas pa'i rnam smin rig 'dzin te /
NK116(le)001:10930: des sbyor lam bzhi ma thob par lus rten bor na phyag rgya chen po thob ste /
NK116(le)001:10931: srid pa phyi ma ring du spang bar 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:10932: rten der chos mchog thob na tshe dbang rig 'dzin
NK116(le)001:10933: grub nas dngas ma'i lus rdo rje lta bur 'gyur
NK116(le)001:10935: de nas lo brgya'i dbang du byas pa'i mi tshe
NK116(le)001:10936: bcu drug na lhun grub rig 'dzin brnyes pa ni
NK116(le)001:10938: don mthong 'jug pa mtha' phyin pa'i //
NK116(le)001:10939: tshogs spyod bsgrub pa'i dngos grub kyis //
NK116(le)001:10940: lus khams skye gnas zag pa zad //
NK116(le)001:10941: rdo rje'i lus gyur tshe'i rig 'dzin /
NK116(le)001:10942: mthong ba'i chos la mya ngan 'da' //
NK116(le)001:10943: lus ma bor par rgyal ba'i sa /
NK116(le)001:10947: nus pa thob dang ma thob pa'i //
NK116(le)001:10948: mthong lam gnyis su 'gyur ba yin /
NK116(le)001:10950: chos nyid kyi bden pa mthong yang rnam smin gyi
NK116(le)001:10951: lus rten sbyong ma nus pa rnam smin rig 'dzin
NK116(le)001:10952: dang / nus pas dngas ma'i skur gyur pa la tshe dbang rig 'dzin du 'dod pa'o //
NK116(le)001:10953: de las mdo sngags spyi'i bshad sgros su bstun na snga ma de legs shing /
NK116(le)001:10954: phyi ma yang tshad ldan gyi gang zag dag 'dod pas mi 'thad pa ni min mod //
NK116(le)001:10955: 'on kyang 'grel chung gis bstan pa'i mthong lam gnyis
NK116(le)001:10956: po'i snga ma de dbang gis dus dpe'i ye shes
NK116(le)001:10957: la bshad na bde bar snyam mo //
NK116(le)001:10958: sgyu 'phrul lugs su sa gnyis pa nas lnga pa'i
NK116(le)001:10959: bar la rtogs pa'i ye shes rdo rje lta bu'i
NK116(le)001:10960: rang gi sa'i sgrib pa bcom pa'i phyir rdo rje'i
NK116(le)001:10961: rig 'dzin dang / drug pa dang bdun pa gnyis la sher phyin dang /
NK116(le)001:10962: thabs la mkhas pa 'khor lo ltar gyur pa 'khor lo'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK116(le)001:10963: brgyad pa mi rtogs pa'i ye shes la dbang bas rin po che'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK116(le)001:10964: dgu par chags pa med pa'i tshul gyis zhing sbyongs zhing gzhan don mdzad pas pad+ma'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK116(le)001:10965: bcu pa phrin las phun sum tshogs pas sems can
NK116(le)001:10966: gyi don byed pas ral gri'i rig 'dzin te bsgom
NK116(le)001:10967: pa'i lam gyi sa bcu po phyag rgya'i rig 'dzin
NK116(le)001:10968: du bsdus nas / rgyun matha'i ye shes las rnam grol dang /
NK116(le)001:10969: khyad par gyi lam mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin du 'dod do //
NK116(le)001:10970: thema skasa rig 'dzin gyi rim pa de dag nyid
NK116(le)001:10971: lasa son nas ngesa pa lnga ldana sogas sku lnga'i
NK116(le)001:10972: zhing du miga 'phrul lta bura 'gro ba yin no
NK116(le)001:10973: // rkang pa phyi ma gnyis po 'di'i mtha' thog
NK116(le)001:10974: gi don le'u bcu gsum pa 'chad pa'i skabs su
NK116(le)001:10976: de ltar skye ba kun rdzob bden pa lam byed bskyed pa'i rim pa bshad zin nas /
NK116(le)001:10977: 'chi ba don dam bden pa'i lam byed rdzogs pa'i rim pa la bstan bshad gnyis kyi /
NK116(le)001:10979: gnyis pa zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:10980: rim pa dang po song ba de nas gnyis pa
NK116(le)001:10981: rdzogas pa'i rima pa nyid la'ang pha ma gnyis med
NK116(le)001:10982: kyi rgyud gsum gyis dbye ba'i dang po pha rgyud
NK116(le)001:10983: gsang ba 'dus pa gshin rje gshed la sogs pa
NK116(le)001:10984: rnamas lasa 'byung ba lnga yi rlung gi bye brag
NK116(le)001:10985: rnam para daga pasa gasla stong gi ye shesa bskyed
NK116(le)001:10986: pa ste / de la slob dpon 'phags pa dang ye shes zhabs kyi lugs gnyis so /
NK116(le)001:10988: bden gnyis kyi rdzogs rim dang /
NK116(le)001:10992: rnal 'byor yan lag drug gis ni //
NK116(le)001:10993: bsnyen pa byas nas sgrub pa mchog /
NK116(le)001:10994: bsgrub par bya ste gzhan du na //
NK116(le)001:10995: dngos grub mchog ni thob mi 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:10996: zhes sngon du rang byin rlabs pa sgyu lus kun
NK116(le)001:10997: rdzob kyi bden pa thob dgos tshul rim lnga las
NK116(le)001:10998: / bdag byin rlabs pa'i ting 'dzin dang /
NK116(le)001:10999: de bzhin 'od gsal ba yi gnas //
NK116(le)001:11000: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i khyad par gyis /
NK116(le)001:11001: bden pa gnyis su bstan pa yin /
NK116(le)001:11005: sems can kun gyi srog gyur pa /
NK116(le)001:11006: rlung zhes bya bas las kun byed /
NK116(le)001:11007: 'di ni rnam shes bzhon pa ste /
NK116(le)001:11008: lnga yi bdag nyid bcu yang yin /
NK116(le)001:11009: zhes 'gro khams rlung dbang du gyur pa na dbang
NK116(le)001:11010: du 'dus pas thabs rdo rje'i bzlas pas ngag dben
NK116(le)001:11011: // sems la dmigs pas sems dben /
NK116(le)001:11012: bdag byin gyis brlabs pa lus dben te dben gsum /
NK116(le)001:11013: yang dag pa'i mtha' 'od gsal mi mngon par byang chub pa dang /
NK116(le)001:11014: gnyis med ye shes sam zung 'jug ste rim pa
NK116(le)001:11015: lnga'i lam gyis bsdus pa'i yon tan gyi tshogs ma
NK116(le)001:11016: lus par bskyed par 'gyur bas na rdzogs rim ste
NK116(le)001:11017: / he ru ka gal po las //
NK116(le)001:11018: rdo rje'i bzlas dang sems la dmigs //
NK116(le)001:11019: bdag byin rlabs dang 'od gsal dang //
NK116(le)001:11023: sgyu ma lta bu'i lha sku phyag rgya chen po gsal ba'i bdag nyid can dang /
NK116(le)001:11024: de kho na nyid bzhugs pa'i thugs zab cing gting
NK116(le)001:11025: dpag dka' ba gnyis dbyer med du sbyor ba zab
NK116(le)001:11026: gsal gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyi rdzogs rim
NK116(le)001:11028: des na zab gsal byang chub ni //
NK116(le)001:11029: gnyis med rtogs pas de grol lo //
NK116(le)001:11030: zab mo kho na rtogs pas min //
NK116(le)001:11031: gsal ba dag kyang de bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:11032: de bzhin thal byung zab mo yis //
NK116(le)001:11033: grol 'dod de la nga ma dad //
NK116(le)001:11034: de bas gnyis med rang bzhin du //
NK116(le)001:11035: rtog pas tshe 'dir nges thob nges //
NK116(le)001:11036: rnam par rtog pa kun bral bas /
NK116(le)001:11037: bsam brjod yul las shin tu 'das /
NK116(le)001:11042: dgyes rdor sogs ma rgyud rnams lasa ni khamas byang
NK116(le)001:11043: chub sems kyi thig le la zhu bde'i rnal 'byor
NK116(le)001:11044: gtso bor byed pa de yi bde stong gi ye
NK116(le)001:11045: shesa bskyed pa'i phyir gdams pa gnyis te /
NK116(le)001:11047: gdams ngag steng dang 'og gi sgo /
NK116(le)001:11049: ranga lusa thabas ldan dang ni /
NK116(le)001:11050: rtsa rlung la gnad du bsnun nas 'bar 'dzag gi
NK116(le)001:11051: sbyor ba'i 'khor lo bzhir bde ba'i ye shes bskyed
NK116(le)001:11052: pa la bslab pa rim gyis ste /
NK116(le)001:11054: 'khor lo gsum gnyis srog shing gsum /
NK116(le)001:11055: me rlung 'gro bas nam mkha'i ba /
NK116(le)001:11056: bzho bas steng du rnam par grags /
NK116(le)001:11058: gnyis pa gazhana lusa kyi 'og sgo mkha' gsang la
NK116(le)001:11059: brtena nas dbab bzung ldog khyab kyi sbyor bas skad
NK116(le)001:11060: cig la bde stong dag'a bzhi'i ye shesa bskyed pa
NK116(le)001:11061: cig char ste / rgyas pa las /
NK116(le)001:11062: phun sum tshogs pa lhun grub rnams /
NK116(le)001:11063: gsang dbang mchog gi sbyin par byed /
NK116(le)001:11065: khyad par du bdag byin rlabs kyi rim pa //
NK116(le)001:11066: sna tshogs rdo rje'i rim pa /
NK116(le)001:11069: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rim pa dang lnga las /
NK116(le)001:11070: snying ga'i thig le la dmigs nas 'byung ba lnga
NK116(le)001:11071: kha dog dang sbyar bas rlung 'byung 'jug gi sgrib
NK116(le)001:11072: pa sbyangs shing dngos grub bsdu ba dang po /
NK116(le)001:11073: 'khor lo lnga'i dbus su rigs lnga'i phyag mtshan la dmigs pa gnyis pa /
NK116(le)001:11074: rol pa chen po'i ngang nas 'khor lo bzhir dga' bzhi'i ye shes ngos 'dzin pa gsum pa /
NK116(le)001:11075: rigs lnga'i phyag mtshan skur gyur pa las bdud rtsi
NK116(le)001:11076: 'bebs shing gtum mo'i man ngag dang bsre ba bzhi
NK116(le)001:11077: pa / snying ga nas 'od zer sproos nas brtan g.yo 'od zhu'i rdzogs rim lnga pa'o //
NK116(le)001:11078: gsum pa gnyis su meda pa'i rgyud rdor sems sgyu dra /
NK116(le)001:11080: sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor sogs lasa /
NK116(le)001:11081: rtsa thig rlung gsum gyi zhu bdes drangs 'bras bsam
NK116(le)001:11082: gyi mi khyab pa'i thig le chen po'i rnal 'byor
NK116(le)001:11083: pa gciga dang du bral gyi /
NK116(le)001:11084: thiga le chena po'i 'oda gasla rdzogs rim gtso bora byed pas de la gsum ste /
NK116(le)001:11085: dang po bde ba'i 'od gsal ni dbu mar dngas
NK116(le)001:11086: ma babs te khams las su rung ba las zag
NK116(le)001:11087: med kyi bde ba'i ting nge 'dzin skye'o //
NK116(le)001:11088: gnyis pa gsal ba'i 'od gsal la ni rlung lnga'i
NK116(le)001:11089: dngas ma stobs su gyur te dbu mar tshud pa
NK116(le)001:11090: las / nang du dngas gsal sgrib pa med pa'i bsam gtan dang /
NK116(le)001:11091: phyi rol du sna sgo rlung lnga'i kha dog mngon pa dang //
NK116(le)001:11092: ye shes lnga'i 'od gdangs sku dang thig le'i rang bzhin du 'tsher ba'o //
NK116(le)001:11093: gsum pa mi rtogs pa'i 'od gsal ni /
NK116(le)001:11095: dngos po thams cad rnam bral ba'i //
NK116(le)001:11096: phung po khams dang skye mched dang //
NK116(le)001:11097: gzung dang 'dzin pa rnam par spangs //
NK116(le)001:11098: chos bdag med pa mnyam nyid pas //
NK116(le)001:11099: rang sems gdod nas ma skyes pa //
NK116(le)001:11100: stong pa nyid kyi rang bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:11102: de ltar rgyud gsum gyis bstan pa'i rdzogs rim gsum
NK116(le)001:11103: las snga ma gnyis ni snang bacasa dmigas pa'i lam
NK116(le)001:11104: dang / phyi ma gciga ni snang ba meda pa'i 'oda gasla te /
NK116(le)001:11105: dang po'i phyogsa la bstan bshad gnyis las /
NK116(le)001:11106: dang po ni gansa pa rtsa'i rang bzhin srang kha
NK116(le)001:11107: dang 'dra ba ni rlung rgyu ba'i lam yin pas
NK116(le)001:11108: so // g.yo ba rlung gi rang bzhin ni cang
NK116(le)001:11109: shes long ba dang 'dra ste thal byung du 'gro
NK116(le)001:11110: la lam dang lam ma yin pa mi shes so
NK116(le)001:11111: so // / bkoda pa byang chub semsa la brten
NK116(le)001:11112: pa'i rnam par shes pa ni skyes bu 'phye bo
NK116(le)001:11113: dang 'dra ste rlung gi chas mkhur na bskyod mi
NK116(le)001:11114: so // / nus pas so // de ltar rtsa
NK116(le)001:11115: thig rlung gsuma rten cing 'brel 'byung du tshogs shing
NK116(le)001:11116: gansa pa rdo rje phunga po'i gronga khyer ro //
NK116(le)001:11117: gnyis pa so sor bshad pa las dang po gnas
NK116(le)001:11118: pa rtsa'i mtshan nyid ni mi yi zhes bya ba
NK116(le)001:11119: la sogs pas bstan te 'di ltar 'gro ba rigs
NK116(le)001:11120: drug las khams drug ldan gyi mi yi mangla gyi
NK116(le)001:11121: gnas su lus rten 'dzina pa'i thoga ma ru /
NK116(le)001:11122: miga gnyis dang ni lte ba'i rtsa mduda chagas shing /
NK116(le)001:11123: de lasa lusa bskyed pa'i dang ma'i dbang por gyur
NK116(le)001:11124: pa yi rtsa gsuma ka ba lta bura chags pa
NK116(le)001:11126: lus kyi gnad ni rtsa yin te //
NK116(le)001:11127: gnas dang bkod par 'gyur ba dang //
NK116(le)001:11128: 'khor lo'i rten dang lus kyi srog /
NK116(le)001:11129: ming dang bye brag rgyu dang rkyen /
NK116(le)001:11130: byed pa'i las dang mtshan nyid dang //
NK116(le)001:11131: nyon mongs las dang ye shes las //
NK116(le)001:11132: lam la brten nas mngon snang ba //
NK116(le)001:11133: nad dang 'byung ba'i bye brag dang //
NK116(le)001:11134: 'khrug mar gnas pa'i mtha' yis dbye /
NK116(le)001:11138: rkyang ma gsum gansa par 'gyur ba'i dus na /
NK116(le)001:11139: phyi ru lusa ngaga yida gsum nanga du nyon mongas dug gsuma /
NK116(le)001:11140: gasnga bar sku gsunga thugas kyi rten byed pa'i /
NK116(le)001:11141: yi ge gsuma du gansa pa yin no //
NK116(le)001:11142: de la dabu ma snga skya'i yasa mara gyi rtsa
NK116(le)001:11143: sna tshangas pa'i sgo dang gasnga ba'i gansa gnyis la
NK116(le)001:11144: zuga cing / yas su pha las thob pa'i dngas ma ham yig gi rang bzhin du gnas shing /
NK116(le)001:11145: mas su ma las thob pa'i dmar cha a thung
NK116(le)001:11146: gi rang bzhin du gnas pa'i bar du kun gzhi'i
NK116(le)001:11147: rten srog gi rlung gnas te nam mkha' lta bu'o
NK116(le)001:11149: ro ma dang rkyang ma dakara dang damra ba'i mdog can nyid gnas te /
NK116(le)001:11150: buda meda nyid la rtsa de gnyis go ldoga pasa
NK116(le)001:11151: rkyang ma gayasa dang ro ma g.yon du gnas so
NK116(le)001:11153: dbu ma'i steng 'og man chad la dus can zhes
NK116(le)001:11154: bya ste dkar cha 'bab cing bde ba bskyed pa'i
NK116(le)001:11155: rtsa yin la / ro mas lus dang byang sems
NK116(le)001:11156: bskyed cing khrag dang dri chen 'phen sdom gyi las
NK116(le)001:11157: rtsa yin la / byed / rkyang mas ngag dang
NK116(le)001:11158: khrag bskyed cing dri chu 'byin sdom gyi las byed
NK116(le)001:11159: rtsa yin la / byed / pa ni / dbang mdor bstan las /
NK116(le)001:11160: zla ba'i lam gyi dri chen rtsa //
NK116(le)001:11161: nyi ma'i dri chu babs pa'o //
NK116(le)001:11166: rang bzhin du gzhag na don byed mi nus te ro dang mtshungs pas na ro ma /
NK116(le)001:11167: gzhan dang mi 'brel zhing ring bu ltar gnas pas
NK116(le)001:11168: na rkyang ma te gnyis kyi dbus na yod pas
NK116(le)001:11169: sam / bde stong gnyis med kyi ngo bo rtag
NK116(le)001:11170: chad kyi phyogs su mi lhung bas na dbu ma
NK116(le)001:11171: sam / zhes so // de ltar dbu ma sngo
NK116(le)001:11172: skyar gnas pa g.yas g.yon gyi gnyis posa lu gu
NK116(le)001:11173: sam / zhes so // rgyud du / mduda pa nyi shu rtsa gciga byas pa la /
NK116(le)001:11175: lu gu rgyud du bcings pa'i rtsa /
NK116(le)001:11176: srog dang thur sel gyi lam gsum /
NK116(le)001:11178: thur sel gyi lam gsum lcags sgrog ltar bcings pa'i
NK116(le)001:11179: rtsa las gyes pa'i rtsa chen nyi shu rtsa bzhi'i
NK116(le)001:11180: sna zugs pa'i rtsa mdud yig 'bru'i rnam pa yod
NK116(le)001:11181: pa las sku gsung thugs kyi bye brag gis /
NK116(le)001:11182: gnas su nye bar brjod cing de rnams las byung
NK116(le)001:11183: ba'i khams nyi shu rtsa bzhi po dang bcas pa
NK116(le)001:11184: nang gi yul chen nyer bzhi grub tshul ni /
NK116(le)001:11185: lus kyi g.yon phyogs kyi char skyes pa phyed ma /
NK116(le)001:11192: dbang bskur ma ste brgyad ni rim bzhin /
NK116(le)001:11200: phrag pa gnyis rnams su gnas te /
NK116(le)001:11201: de dag gi yul brgyad mtshon te /
NK116(le)001:11210: ma la wa rnams te 'di dag ni gnas dang nye ba'i gnas so //
NK116(le)001:11223: ko sa la ste zhing dang nye zhing zhes bya'o //
NK116(le)001:11226: gnyis ni kha dang mgrin pa'i dbus su gnas te /
NK116(le)001:11229: de dag rkyang mas brten pas shes rab kyi rang bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:11230: g.yas kyi char skyes pa gzhol ma /
NK116(le)001:11231: ra sa ma gnyis ni brang gzhung dang /
NK116(le)001:11232: lgang bar 'brel te kany+tsi ka dang /
NK116(le)001:11234: tsha n+d+ho dang ni nye ba'i tshan+d+ho zhes so /
NK116(le)001:11242: byin ba rnams la gnas te /
NK116(le)001:11246: soo bar+na d+ai ba ste 'du dang nye 'du zhes bya'o //
NK116(le)001:11254: pus mo'i gnyen gong rnams na gnas te /
NK116(le)001:11259: 'thung gcod dang nye ba'i 'thung gcod ces so //
NK116(le)001:11260: rtsa de dag gi lus kyi phyi nang gi khams bskyed par byed de /
NK116(le)001:11261: gsar rnying rgyud spyi'i 'gros bstun he ru ka'i gnas bcur sbyar nas /
NK116(le)001:11262: sa lam bsgrood tshul dang bstun na /
NK116(le)001:11264: gnas dang nye ba'i gnas dang ni //
NK116(le)001:11265: zhing dang nye ba'i zhing nyid dang //
NK116(le)001:11266: tshu n+d+ho nye pa'i tshan+d+ho dang //
NK116(le)001:11269: dur khrod nye ba'i dur khrod nyid //
NK116(le)001:11270: 'di rnams sa ni bcu gsum yin /
NK116(le)001:11272: 'thung gcod rnam gnyis las gzhan pa'i dang po gnyis la bzhi bzhi /
NK116(le)001:11273: lhag ma brgyad la gnyis gnyis te yul chen nyer bzhi dang /
NK116(le)001:11275: gnas ni rab tu dga' ba'i sa /
NK116(le)001:11277: nye ba'i dur khrod chos kyi sprin /
NK116(le)001:11278: pha rol phyin bcu'i sa rnams la /
NK116(le)001:11282: 'thung gcod gnyis po ye shes su sbyor tshul /
NK116(le)001:11284: 'thung gcod dpe med ye shes te //
NK116(le)001:11285: nye ba'i 'thung gcod ye shes che /
NK116(le)001:11287: de la sbas pa'i rtsa lnga snying gar gnas pa'i
NK116(le)001:11288: sgrib bral du gyur pa'i bcu gsum rdo rje 'dzin
NK116(le)001:11289: pa'o // da ni rtsa 'khor dang yan lag gi
NK116(le)001:11290: rnam grangs rgyas pa rim bzhin zhes bya ba la
NK116(le)001:11292: de yang 'khor lo rten gzhi dbu ma yin te /
NK116(le)001:11293: de nyid dngos por grub pa med pa 'dod pa dang /
NK116(le)001:11294: kha cig yod kyang srog rtsar 'dod pa dang /
NK116(le)001:11295: rgyungs pa la 'dod pa dag byung kyang snga phyi
NK116(le)001:11296: gnyis mi 'thad pa ni kun mkhyen chos rjes bkag
NK116(le)001:11297: zin pas dpyad mi dgos la /
NK116(le)001:11300: rlung dang 'gyu ba rtsar brten phyir na srog pa rtsar //
NK116(le)001:11301: bcud nas tha mal shes pa ngang gis 'gags par 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:11302: zhes kun gzhi srog rlung dang bcas pa'i rten yin pas tha snyad tsam du re zhig bzhed kyang /
NK116(le)001:11303: mtshan nyid bzhi ldan bsgoms byung gi rtsa du grags pa ni don la nges so /
NK116(le)001:11306: don dam pa'i dbu ma gsum ste /
NK116(le)001:11307: dang po ni bshad ma thag pa'i srog 'dzin gyi rtsa dang /
NK116(le)001:11309: rtsa de'i nang du chos nyid kyi dbu ma mtshan
NK116(le)001:11310: nyid bzhi ldan can 'od gsal ba'i rang bzhin thog
NK116(le)001:11311: reg dang bral ba'i ji srid du lus sems dbug
NK116(le)001:11312: gsum gyi tshogs pa yod pa'i ring la yod pa
NK116(le)001:11313: de / de gsum gyes dus dbus dang lhan gcig bltar mi mngon par 'gyur te /
NK116(le)001:11314: rtsa yi mdzes spyi las byung ba /
NK116(le)001:11315: de ni rdul phra rab tu grags /
NK116(le)001:11316: dag pa'i shel gyi 'od dang mnyams /
NK116(le)001:11323: mun pa ma sogs su grags la /
NK116(le)001:11326: dung can ma sogs gzugs can gyi rtsa yin yang dbu ma'i grangs phyogs su bsdu bar grags so //
NK116(le)001:11327: gsum pa tshig gi bla dag tsam las grub 'bras ngo bo nyid med pa'o //
NK116(le)001:11329: rima bzhina sku gsunga thugas mtshon byed lte mgrin snying ga gsum gyi grangs sama sku bzhi la /
NK116(le)001:11330: de'i steng du spyi bo dang sku lnga la /
NK116(le)001:11331: de'i steng du gsang gnas te 'khor lo'i ming ni yongs su grags pa ltar ro /
NK116(le)001:11332: phar phyin drug gi grangsa kyi cha la mtshon na
NK116(le)001:11333: snga ma'i steng du gtsug tor nam mkha'i 'khora lo'i
NK116(le)001:11335: de rnamas la phri bsnana gyur pa ni sbyangsa gzhi sbyongsa byed sbyang 'bras kyi tshula gyis so //
NK116(le)001:11337: lte bar rtsa 'dabs druga cu rtsa bzhi mgrina pa la brgyad tshana gnyis bcu drug dang /
NK116(le)001:11339: spyi bora suma cu rtsa gnyis bde skyong na //
NK116(le)001:11340: bduna cu rtsa gnyis dang de bzhina gtsug tora la /
NK116(le)001:11341: nam mkha'i khamas kyi 'khora lo zhesa su gragas so //
NK116(le)001:11342: 'dir de bzhin zhes pa 'khor lo drug las phyi
NK116(le)001:11343: ma yin pas na de skad gsungs la yan lag
NK116(le)001:11344: gi rtsa phran bde skyong dang 'dra bar bstan pa
NK116(le)001:11345: yin no // de la dus 'khor ltar na /
NK116(le)001:11346: bshad ma thag pa'i 'khora lo re dang so so'i bar matshamas su /
NK116(le)001:11347: nang ltar na 'pho ba bcu gnyis rlunga gi cha dang /
NK116(le)001:11348: phyi ltar na lug glang sogs dusa sbyor bcu gnyis dang /
NK116(le)001:11349: gsang ba ltar na de bzhina ma rig pa la
NK116(le)001:11350: sogs rten cinga 'brel 'byung bcu gnyis rnams gansa pa
NK116(le)001:11351: gang zhig / rlung gi byed ba cings kyis khamas
NK116(le)001:11352: phyir la 'pho ba spangsa ba'i lugas ldog 'grosa kyi
NK116(le)001:11353: gasnga gansa ye shesa kyi 'khora lo phyin pa dang
NK116(le)001:11354: gang zhig / mnyam du / rlung gi 'pho ba
NK116(le)001:11355: gciga dang rten 'brel gciga /'aggas nasa dang po'i sa
NK116(le)001:11357: rima bzhina nama mkha'i khamas kyi 'khora lo'i bar gyi /
NK116(le)001:11358: rlung dang rtena 'brela re re'i cha ldoga bas /
NK116(le)001:11359: sa ni bcu gnyis raba tu rdzogas pa'i mathara /
NK116(le)001:11360: thiga le gtsuga tor nama mkha'i 'khor lo'i rtsa khamas dang 'dresa pa'i tshe /
NK116(le)001:11361: mngona para rdzogs par 'atshangas rgya ba dang po'i sangsa rgyas su dus kyi 'khor lo'i lugas yin no //
NK116(le)001:11362: rgyud sde spyi'i rdzogs rim gyi dbyings 'jal shes pa'i
NK116(le)001:11363: phyir sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i dgongs don de dang zhes
NK116(le)001:11364: bya ba la sogs pas bstan te snga ma de
NK116(le)001:11365: dang rnam grangas mthuna pa'i rtsa 'adbas la /
NK116(le)001:11366: sbyang gzhira gansa pa'i yi ge rigas druga gi sa bona rnams /
NK116(le)001:11367: sbyongsa byed riga pa'i skyes bu thub pa rnam drug dang /
NK116(le)001:11368: pha rola phyin pa drug gi sbyangsa pa lasa /
NK116(le)001:11369: tha dada pa yi ye shesa rnam pa lnga ni yongs grangs ltar la /
NK116(le)001:11370: bsam gyisa mi khyab pa'i ye shes gciga dang /
NK116(le)001:11372: de bzhina snying khara zhi ba'i lha tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi 'khora lo dang /
NK116(le)001:11373: spyi gtsuga tu khro bo'i lha tshogs lnga bcu rtsa brgyad po'i 'khora lo rnama pa gnyisa la /
NK116(le)001:11374: rim bzhin lha dang rnam grangas mnyamsa pa'i rtsa 'adbas dang /
NK116(le)001:11375: thabas kyis grol ba'i gdams ngag steng 'oga lasa lam gyi sgo gnyis su rag par 'doda pa /
NK116(le)001:11376: rgyud kyi rgyal po sgyu 'phrula dra ba'i lugas te //
NK116(le)001:11377: ji ltar na steng sgo la gnyis te /
NK116(le)001:11379: 'bar 'dzag gi sbyor ba'i dga' bzhi'i ye shes bskyed pa ste /
NK116(le)001:11382: lte bar a thung dang bcas pa bsgom pas snying gar bam dngas pa las chu /
NK116(le)001:11383: mgrin par a dngas pas me /
NK116(le)001:11384: spyi bor ham dngas pas chu ste so so'i dngas ma zin /
NK116(le)001:11386: sgrom mdo rlung gi 'khor lo bskyod pas /
NK116(le)001:11387: sum mdo me yi 'khor lo 'bar te /
NK116(le)001:11388: 'khor lo bzhi'i thig le zhu ba las rlung gi dngas ma zin /
NK116(le)001:11389: dga' bzhi dang 'brel ba'i bde ba'i ye shes rgyud las skyes pa ni steng sgo thun mong pa'o //
NK116(le)001:11391: snying ga ste mgrin spyi bo'i 'khor lo bzhir /
NK116(le)001:11395: khyab bdal chen po'i man ngag bzhi rgyud kyi ston pa bzhin bsgom pas /
NK116(le)001:11396: 'khor lo bzhi'i dngas ma g.yo byed dang bral ba'i
NK116(le)001:11397: 'od gsal la dngas ma'i dngas ma rnams thim pas
NK116(le)001:11398: mchog tu mi 'gyur ba'i 'od gsal rnam par mi
NK116(le)001:11399: rtogs pa 'char ba steng sgo 'ju 'dul gyi man
NK116(le)001:11400: ngag zhes so // 'og sgo khams su ma rol
NK116(le)001:11401: ba'i man ngag ni thabs shes gnyis med phyag rgya
NK116(le)001:11402: bzhi'i rol pas rtsa khams nas thig le dbab ldog
NK116(le)001:11403: dgram gsum byed pas bde chen lhan skyes kyi ye
NK116(le)001:11404: shes la mngon gsum par spyod pa'o //
NK116(le)001:11405: gnyis pa rlung gi rab dbye la spyi'i rnam grangs
NK116(le)001:11406: ni g.yo ba zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan
NK116(le)001:11407: te / g.yo ba rlung la 'byung ba che chung gnyis te /
NK116(le)001:11408: che ba ni nyin zhaga phrug ciga daga la ni /
NK116(le)001:11409: nyi khri chiga stong druga brgya'i grangas su 'gyu zhing /
NK116(le)001:11410: de la chunga bar dbye na kuna rtog brgyad khri
NK116(le)001:11411: bzhi stong gi rnam grangas dang mnyam pa'i rlung ni
NK116(le)001:11412: sems skyed byed yin pas bzhona pa lta bur gansa
NK116(le)001:11413: so // byed las kyi sgo nas dbye ba'i phyir
NK116(le)001:11414: rtsa ba'i zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsung te
NK116(le)001:11415: so // / rtsa ba'i rlunga lnga ni snying gar gnas pa sroga 'dzina /
NK116(le)001:11416: lte bar gnas pa me mnyam dang /
NK116(le)001:11417: lus kyi dbyings la gnas pa khyab byed /
NK116(le)001:11418: ro stod la gnas pa gyen rgyu /
NK116(le)001:11419: ro smad du gnas pa thura sela te /
NK116(le)001:11421: byed lasa ni rima bzhina du sroga rten 1pa /
NK116(le)001:11425: 'gro 'duga gashanga gci 'phena pa'i bya ba byed do /
NK116(le)001:11426: de yanga pho rlung gyen rgyu stod na gansa shing /
NK116(le)001:11427: mo rlung thur sel smad dang /
NK116(le)001:11428: ma ninga gi rlung me mnyam ni bar du gnas te /
NK116(le)001:11430: gyen du rgyu dang thur du sel /
NK116(le)001:11431: bar na mkhas pas gnad nyid btsal /
NK116(le)001:11433: nanga gi rlung ni 'byung lnga'i kha doga can te /
NK116(le)001:11435: sa chu me rlung nam mkha' lnga'i rlung ni rim bzhin /
NK116(le)001:11436: ser dkar dmar ljang mthing ga ste /
NK116(le)001:11437: phunga po dang khamas dang skye mcheda rnams gnas par byed pa'i rten dang /
NK116(le)001:11438: ma dag pa duga lnga dang ni dag pa ye shesa rnam pa lnga bcas /
NK116(le)001:11439: so so rgyu 'brasa lta bura mcheda pa'i rten byed do //
NK116(le)001:11440: khyad para 'byung lnga'i dangs ma'i rlung lnga d+hu tir chud pa na /
NK116(le)001:11441: zada para sa dang chu dang me dang rlung nama mkha'a yi skye mched kyi ting nge 'dzina dang /
NK116(le)001:11445: g.yas rlung dbu mar tshud na du ba lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:11446: g.yon rlung chud pa smig rgyu /
NK116(le)001:11447: me rlung las mar me dang 'od 'bar ba /
NK116(le)001:11449: mthong khong gi zla 'od lta bu /
NK116(le)001:11450: sa rlung las gser gyi kha dog dang glog lta bu /
NK116(le)001:11451: mkha' rlung la dang por mthing ka de las 'od lnga'i thig le /
NK116(le)001:11452: thams cad dbu mar tshud pas 'od lnga dang /
NK116(le)001:11459: pad+ma la sogs pa mtha' yas 'char /
NK116(le)001:11461: rlung lnga'i dngas ma stobs gyur na //
NK116(le)001:11462: 'od lnga nang gi ye shes lnga //
NK116(le)001:11463: sku lnga bgrod pa'i zhing khams lnga //
NK116(le)001:11464: zad par lnga sogs thob par 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:11466: gasnga ba'i rlunga ni ye shesa rnam pa lnga ste /
NK116(le)001:11467: rag pa'i chosa dang shin tu rnam para 'agla pa can yina no //
NK116(le)001:11468: gsum pa khams kyi bzhugs tshul ni gsum pa zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:11469: gsum pa bkoda pa byang chub semas kyi khamas la kun rdzob dang /
NK116(le)001:11472: ro ma las ni zla ba'i rang bzhin gyi bduda
NK116(le)001:11473: rtsi stee khams dkar po ro ma'i yar sna spyi
NK116(le)001:11474: gtsugs ham las bab pa dang /
NK116(le)001:11476: nyi ma'i rang bzhin gyi rdula zhes rak+ta dmar po rkyang ma'i mar sna gsang gnas kyi /
NK116(le)001:11478: pho yi rkyang ma dang mo yi ro ma'i sna
NK116(le)001:11479: mduda para gyura basa de de'i khamas gnyis 'adzaga pa
NK116(le)001:11481: de basa gazhana du ro rkyang gnyis po lasa mcheda pa'i /
NK116(le)001:11482: rtsa mduda kun na dangs ma dakara damra gnyis /
NK116(le)001:11483: dapa'a bo dang ni rnal 'byor ma'i tshul du /
NK116(le)001:11484: 'khril zhing gnas pa 'dir rdo rje mkha' la sbyor
NK116(le)001:11485: basa bde stong rtsa mdud bdud rtsi'i mchoda pa lena
NK116(le)001:11486: pa ni / rdo rje mkha' 'gro las /
NK116(le)001:11487: ji bzhin shes rab snyoms 'jug pa'i /
NK116(le)001:11488: yang dag sbyor dang ldan pa yis //
NK116(le)001:11489: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gtsug tor dkar //
NK116(le)001:11490: yid nang chud pa de yis spyad //
NK116(le)001:11491: mchog tu dga' ba spro pa yi /
NK116(le)001:11492: gnas skabs su ni mnyes par 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:11494: de dag dpe'i sgo nas ston pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:11495: mdor na zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:11496: mdora bsdu na lus kyi rten gansa pa rtsa ni
NK116(le)001:11497: rlung dang thig le'i lam yin pas yura ba dang
NK116(le)001:11498: 'dra la / ngag gi rten g.yo ba rlunga ni
NK116(le)001:11499: 'khor 'das gnyis kar 'gro 'onga byed pas kha lo
NK116(le)001:11500: 'dra la / lta bu dang / yid kyi rten
NK116(le)001:11501: byang chub semas kyi thig le ni chu dang 'dra
NK116(le)001:11502: ste khrida sara 'du pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:11505: rtsa 'khora lo druga tu brtsegas pa'i sgra gacana gyi
NK116(le)001:11506: dbyingsa su sroga dang rtsol ba'i ste ro rkyang rlung
NK116(le)001:11507: gi shinga rtas drangas pa lasa te /
NK116(le)001:11509: brten bya nyid dang rtse rnams dang /
NK116(le)001:11510: dmigs bya dag gi lus rdzogs bya //
NK116(le)001:11511: de nas thig le kun rdzob nyid //
NK116(le)001:11512: rab bcings bzung dang ldog pa dang //
NK116(le)001:11513: rtsa la gdab cing rlung la bsre //
NK116(le)001:11514: stong nyid bstan bya blo rjes bcad //
NK116(le)001:11515: lus dang sems nyid go ldog bya //
NK116(le)001:11516: don dam thig le bstan pa yis //
NK116(le)001:11517: chos sku stong ba'i yul rnams rnyed /
NK116(le)001:11519: de la bsten nas dbu ma'i mdud pa nyer gcig
NK116(le)001:11520: po rim bzhin gnyis gnyis re grola ba dang tshul
NK116(le)001:11521: ni dang po // rlung dang khamas kyi dangs ma rnam gnyis re /
NK116(le)001:11522: sgra gacana gyi ltor zhugsa nas lte ba'i 'khor lor
NK116(le)001:11523: phyin pa na chos kyi rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin
NK116(le)001:11524: thob pa las tshogs lam chen po'i drod rtags 'char
NK116(le)001:11525: / der 'byung ba'i dbu ma'i rtsa mdud dang po
NK116(le)001:11526: gnyis grol te sangs rgyas sprul sku'i zhal mthong ba
NK116(le)001:11527: sogs kyi yon tan snang ba yin no //
NK116(le)001:11528: tshogs bsags yul ni nye bar len pa'i lha bzhi ste /
NK116(le)001:11529: bsod nams nyer len gyi lha dkon mchog gsum /
NK116(le)001:11530: dngos grub nyer len gyi lha yi dam /
NK116(le)001:11531: yang dag 'bras bu nyer len rdo rje slob dpon dang mched 3lcam /
NK116(le)001:11532: lus nyer len dus gsum gyi pha 4ma dang bzhi ste /
NK116(le)001:11534: dang po nye bar len pa'i lha bzhi ma mchod
NK116(le)001:11535: na phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas gang la
NK116(le)001:11536: phul kyang mnyes par mi 'gyur zhing bzhes par mi
NK116(le)001:11538: snying gar phyin tshe sbyor lam gyi drod rtags 'char /
NK116(le)001:11539: rtsa mdud gsum pa dang bzhi pa grol /
NK116(le)001:11540: ting nge 'dzin dang rdzu 'phrul snga ma las ches thob bo //
NK116(le)001:11541: mgrin par phyin pa mthong lam dang po'i sa'i drod rtags 'char /
NK116(le)001:11542: rtsa mdud lnga pa dang drug pa grol /
NK116(le)001:11543: rdzu 'phrul ni rgyu'i theg pas shes so //
NK116(le)001:11544: de nas gzung spyi bor bde chen gyi 'khor lor
NK116(le)001:11545: zhugs gnas thim gsum rdzogs pa'i ring la rtsa mdud
NK116(le)001:11546: lhag rnams grol nas bsgom lam sa dgu bgrod de
NK116(le)001:11547: / sa bcu'i yona tan gonga 'phela gyi rjes su
NK116(le)001:11548: gtsura tor 'khor lor phyin te rdo rje 'chang gi
NK116(le)001:11551: ro ma rkyang ma kun 'dar ma //
NK116(le)001:11553: grol ba'i ye shes mya ngan 'das /
NK116(le)001:11555: sa 'thob tshul 'khor lo drug du sbyar te //
NK116(le)001:11556: de dang cung mi mthun pa yang yod de /
NK116(le)001:11557: thig le bcu drug lus kyi lus kyi thig le /
NK116(le)001:11558: ngag gi lus kyi thig le /
NK116(le)001:11559: sems kyi lus kyi thig le /
NK116(le)001:11560: ye shes kyi lus kyi thig le ste bzhi /
NK116(le)001:11563: ye shes la bzhi bzhir phye ba'i bcu drug phyed
NK116(le)001:11564: phyed thig le de nyid dkar nag gi phyogs gnyis
NK116(le)001:11565: su phye bas yul nyer bzhi 'jug pa'i thig le
NK116(le)001:11566: nyi shu rtsa bzhi tshar bzhi sogs yang /
NK116(le)001:11567: byang sems gtsug tor 'khor lo dang rdul rdo rje
NK116(le)001:11568: nor bur phyin pa mnyams pas sa bcu gsum rdzogs
NK116(le)001:11570: byed bcings nyin mtshan rnal 'byor so nams byas /
NK116(le)001:11571: rtsa ni yur bar 'dra ste byang par dgos //
NK116(le)001:11572: byang sems chu 'dra khrid par yod par dgos //
NK116(le)001:11573: rlung ni khron skyogs 'dra ste skyon med dgos /
NK116(le)001:11574: de ltar rtsa rlung 'byongs ba'i rjes chags su /
NK116(le)001:11575: 'dod chags chen po'i bde chen nam mkha' gang //
NK116(le)001:11576: khu ba thub bas rdo rje nor bu brten /
NK116(le)001:11577: rdul ni gyen log gtsug tor 'khor lo brten //
NK116(le)001:11578: de ltar lo gsum dag la 'bad pa na /
NK116(le)001:11579: khu ba rdo rje nor bu yang 'phel pas //
NK116(le)001:11580: gsang gnas rtsa 'dams rnams ni phyed gang zhing /
NK116(le)001:11581: las rlung brgya phrag bco brgyad gcig 'gags pas /
NK116(le)001:11582: dbang bcu la sogs thob pa'i sems par 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:11583: sa ni dang po rab tu dga' ba rdzogs //
NK116(le)001:11584: yon tan brgya phrag bcu gnyis bcu gnyis thob /
NK116(le)001:11585: thur du rdul 'phel gtsug tor dpral ba yi /
NK116(le)001:11586: rtsa 'dabs phyed gang zla ba ham yig zhu //
NK116(le)001:11587: bdud rtsi thig le'i rgyun char phyir la bab //
NK116(le)001:11588: de bzhin khu ba gsang gnas rtsa 'dabs kyi //
NK116(le)001:11589: phyed bo lhag ma ma lus gang ba yis //
NK116(le)001:11590: las rlung brgya phrag bco brgyad gnyis 'gags pas //
NK116(le)001:11591: sa ni gnyis pa dri ma med par rdzogs //
NK116(le)001:11592: yon tan de nyid nam mkha' gang ba thob //
NK116(le)001:11593: rdul gyis dpral ba'i rtsa 'dabs phyed 'phro gang /
NK116(le)001:11594: de nas khu ba lte ba yar slebs shing //
NK116(le)001:11595: rdul gyi mgrin par phyir slebs rtsa 'dabs gang //
NK116(le)001:11596: las rlung brgya phrag bco brgyad gnyis 'gags pas //
NK116(le)001:11597: sa ni gsum pa 'od rab phyed pa dang //
NK116(le)001:11598: bzhi pa 'od 'phro gnyis po rdzogs pa yin //
NK116(le)001:11599: khu rdul gnyis ka snying khar slebs nas ni //
NK116(le)001:11600: snying gi rtsa 'dabs thams cad gang ba yis //
NK116(le)001:11601: las rlung brgya phrag bco brgyad gnyis 'gags pas /
NK116(le)001:11602: sa ni lnga pa sbyang ba dka' ba dang //
NK116(le)001:11603: drug pa mngon du gyur pa gnyis po rdzogs //
NK116(le)001:11604: khu ba yar song mgrin pa'i rtsa 'khor slebs //
NK116(le)001:11605: rdul ni lte ba'i 'khor lo phyi slebs nas /
NK116(le)001:11606: las rlung dus sbyor gnyis po rab 'gags pas //
NK116(le)001:11607: sa ni bdun pa ring du song ba dang //
NK116(le)001:11608: brgyad pa mi g.yo ba gnyis rdzogs pa yin //
NK116(le)001:11609: khu ba yar song dpral ba'i 'khor lor slebs /
NK116(le)001:11610: rdul ni gsang ba'i 'khor lo phyi slebs nas //
NK116(le)001:11611: las rlung dus sbyor gnyis po rab 'gags pas //
NK116(le)001:11612: sa ni dgu pa legs pa'i blo gros dang //
NK116(le)001:11613: bcu pa chos kyi sprin gnyis rdzogs pa yin /
NK116(le)001:11614: de nas khu ba gtsug tog yar slebs nas /
NK116(le)001:11615: rdul gyi rdo rje nor bur phyir slebs nas /
NK116(le)001:11616: las rlung dus sbyor gnyis po rab 'gags nas //
NK116(le)001:11617: sa ni bcu gcig kun tu 'od dang ni /
NK116(le)001:11618: bcu gsum rdo rje 'dzin par rdzogs pa yin /
NK116(le)001:11621: gsar rnying gi rgyud spyi'i dgongs pa dkrol nas dmigs
NK116(le)001:11622: gsal gyi rgyud don khyad par zhes bya ba la
NK116(le)001:11624: rgyud thams cad las kyang khyad para du 'phags pa
NK116(le)001:11625: sgyu 'phrula dra ba gasnga thiga gi lugas ltar na
NK116(le)001:11626: / phyi snod dang nang bcud gnyis bsdus kyi chos
NK116(le)001:11627: thams cad ranga la rdzogsa pa rdo rje phunga po'i
NK116(le)001:11628: / gronga na / dusa gsuma lunga du ma bstan pa'i bde gshegas snying po gnas so //
NK116(le)001:11630: 'das ma 'ongs da lta gyi rgyal ba matha'a daga mngona par rdzogs par 'tshang rgyas pa /
NK116(le)001:11632: rgya bzhin pa'i gnas gcig pu rdo rje'i gadna snying ga dapala gyi be'u'i khonga senga na gnas pa'o //
NK116(le)001:11633: de la rdo rje dang dpal gyi be'u cis phyir smos snyams na /
NK116(le)001:11634: phyi yul snying rgya gar rdo rje gdan yin pa bzhin /
NK116(le)001:11635: mi shig pa'i chos nyid 'dus ma byas kyi gnas yin pa dang /
NK116(le)001:11636: dbyings zab pa'i phyir smos so //
NK116(le)001:11637: de na'ang rtsa yi dangs ma brgyad du gansa pa lasa /
NK116(le)001:11638: dri med bshes gnyen gyi gsang thig las /
NK116(le)001:11639: gang la yod pa rnam pa brgyad du shes /
NK116(le)001:11641: gang la yod na snying khong stong gi dkyil na
NK116(le)001:11642: rtsa rtsa'i dngas ma rtsa bran rgyus pa bldad pa
NK116(le)001:11646: dbus ma gsuma ni sku gsuma gyi chosa nyid ces
NK116(le)001:11647: yongs grub 'gyur ba med pa'i rten gyi rtsa 'od
NK116(le)001:11648: snang ser la zlum pa'i rnam pa can dang /
NK116(le)001:11649: mduna ma gciga ni ye shes 'achara ba'i rtsa mthing ga gru bzhi'i rnam pa can /
NK116(le)001:11650: rgyab na yona tan rtsa lasa zhing khamas rnams gzhal
NK116(le)001:11651: yas khang la sogs pa dag pa'i snang ba mu
NK116(le)001:11653: g.yona na dug gsum ranga rgyud pa'i rtsa gsuma zla
NK116(le)001:11654: gam gyi dbyibs kha dog dmar po can 'khrul snang
NK116(le)001:11655: gi rten byed pa rnams yod de //
NK116(le)001:11656: de dag so so'i dbus na 'khora 'adsa kyi yiga 'bru ni /
NK116(le)001:11657: sbyang gzhi sbyong byed kyi tshul du gansa pa rnams ni /
NK116(le)001:11659: dbus kyi dkyil na sbyangs gzhi lha min dang /
NK116(le)001:11660: byol song gi sa bon su tri'i steng du sbyong
NK116(le)001:11661: byed sku rdo rje'i snying po dkar po rang 'od
NK116(le)001:11663: mdun ma'i sbub nas lha mi'i sa bon a n+ri
NK116(le)001:11664: dkar dmar gyi steng na thugs rdo rje'i rang bzhin
NK116(le)001:11665: h'u mthing ga / g.yon pa'i sdubs na yi dwag
NK116(le)001:11666: dang dmyal ba'i sa bon bre du'i steng gsung rdo
NK116(le)001:11667: rje'i rang bzhin +aahyiga pad+ma r+aa ga ltar 'tsher ba
NK116(le)001:11670: rnam bzhi bye brag drug dang brgyad dkyil na /
NK116(le)001:11672: de ltar sbyong gzhi de dag ni sbyongs byed sku
NK116(le)001:11673: gasung thugsa kyi yi ge gsum gyis daga para byed
NK116(le)001:11674: pa'o // bye brag 'od ser po la kun gzhi'i rnam shes /
NK116(le)001:11676: dmar po la nyon yid kyi /
NK116(le)001:11677: dmar nag la sgo lnga'i rnam shes gnas so //
NK116(le)001:11678: 'od ser po rtsa'i dngas ma dar dkar gyi skud pa 'dra ba la rgyu /
NK116(le)001:11679: mthing ga dbugs kyi dngas ma la rgyu /
NK116(le)001:11680: dmar po khrag gi dngas ma la rgyu /
NK116(le)001:11681: dmar nag sgo lnga'i rtsa'i dngas ma la rgyu'o //
NK116(le)001:11682: skyes bu'i byed las kyis dge sdig bag chags kyang
NK116(le)001:11683: so so'i yig 'brur song nas gnas dang gnas min
NK116(le)001:11685: rtsa kuna gyi dbus na dangs ma'i ye shes kyi
NK116(le)001:11686: 'od rtsa dakara po shel dkar gyi skud pa lta
NK116(le)001:11687: bu rta rnga'i bcu cha gcig tsam du phra ba'i
NK116(le)001:11688: nang / rdula ste khrag dang dbugsa kyi dangs ma 'dres pa'i 'oda /
NK116(le)001:11689: kha doga lnga pa shina tu phra ba nyid yod
NK116(le)001:11690: pa stong pa'i ranga bzhina 'oda gasla don dam byang
NK116(le)001:11691: chub semas kyi rang bzhin rten pa yin te /
NK116(le)001:11693: rtag tu snying gar gnas pa yis /
NK116(le)001:11694: thig le gcig la 'gyur ba med /
NK116(le)001:11695: de bsgom byed pa'i skye bo la /
NK116(le)001:11696: nges par ye shes skye bar 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:11698: de nyid kuna bzang rigas lnga bzhugas pa'i gazhala meda khanga yin pa ni /
NK116(le)001:11699: bshad rgyud rdo rje phreng ba las //
NK116(le)001:11700: snying kha'i pad+mo sbub mkha' la //
NK116(le)001:11701: ye shes rdo rje rtag tu bzhugs //
NK116(le)001:11702: gtso bo chen po mi bskyod pa'i //
NK116(le)001:11703: 'jig rten khams ni de nyid do //
NK116(le)001:11705: zhing de gang nas 'ongs dang ganga du 'gro ba med de /
NK116(le)001:11706: rlung dang semas kyi dangs ma der 'dusa pa'i tshe /
NK116(le)001:11707: mya ngana las 'adsa pa'i zhing khams kyi snang ba matha'a daga 'achara ro //
NK116(le)001:11708: de yang snang cha'i 'oda kha dog lnga dang stong
NK116(le)001:11709: cha'i chosa sku gnyis po ro gciga tu 'dresa pa'i
NK116(le)001:11710: lam gyisa tshogsa gnyis rdzogas pa ste /
NK116(le)001:11711: de bas na 'oga mina rnama daga stug po bkoda pa zhesa bya ba ni /
NK116(le)001:11714: nama zhiga spangas pa'i dusa dera lhuna gyi grub pa'i sa yin no //
NK116(le)001:11715: de phyir lusa ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye
NK116(le)001:11716: shesa chena po'i rten yin te 'di ltar 'khora ba
NK116(le)001:11717: nyid na'ang ngo bo bde gshegs snying po'i bzhugas tshul
NK116(le)001:11718: la / nyamsa pa dang damna para gyura pa gnyis
NK116(le)001:11719: ka meda cing 'gyur ba meda pa'i dona dama byang
NK116(le)001:11720: chuba kyi semas rin po che dper na til la
NK116(le)001:11721: mara gyi khyab pa ji bzhina du gnas pa yin
NK116(le)001:11722: la / no // de yang ye shes grub pa las //
NK116(le)001:11723: sems kyi dam pa 'od gsal ba //
NK116(le)001:11724: kun tu bzang po'i sangs rgyas te //
NK116(le)001:11725: sus kyang ma byas rang byung ba //
NK116(le)001:11726: ye nas nyid ni gnas pa'o //
NK116(le)001:11729: ji ltar sngar bzhin phyis de bzhin //
NK116(le)001:11730: 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid do //
NK116(le)001:11733: rin chen sems las phyir gyur ba'i //
NK116(le)001:11734: sangs rgyas med cing sems can med /
NK116(le)001:11736: 'di ltar rdo rje lusa kyi gansa lugas dang //
NK116(le)001:11737: gdoda ma gzhi yi bzhugas tshula rgya cher bstan zin pa ltar shesa par byas nasa /
NK116(le)001:11738: dngos gzhi nyams len dmigs bsal gyi rim pa la
NK116(le)001:11739: gnyis te dang por rang lus thabs ldan ni gtum
NK116(le)001:11740: mo zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:11742: gtum 1mo dang ni gzhi ma 2sgyu lus drod tshad nyid 3'khrula gyi lam /
NK116(le)001:11743: snying po 'oda gasla bsun ma bar do blo chod 'pho ba ste rnama pa drug las /
NK116(le)001:11745: rlung las su rung bar byas te gtum mo 'bar 'dzag gi nyams len byed pa'o //
NK116(le)001:11746: gnyis pa lam dag pa'i sgyu lus /
NK116(le)001:11748: sbas don rlung sems kyi sgyu lus gsum las /
NK116(le)001:11749: dang po ni snod bcud gnyis bsdus kyi chos thams
NK116(le)001:11750: cad med snang stong gzugs sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad ltar
NK116(le)001:11753: sgyu ma byed pa dag gis gzugs sprul te //
NK116(le)001:11754: rta dang glang po shing rta sna tshogs byas //
NK116(le)001:11755: de la ji bzhin snang ba gang yang med //
NK116(le)001:11756: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par gyis //
NK116(le)001:11759: lha sku sgyu ma lta bu'i gsal snang la gom par byas pa ste //
NK116(le)001:11760: zhe sdang sgyu lus la bsre ba sbrul sku'i //
NK116(le)001:11761: 'dod chags dbang dang bsre ba longs sku'i //
NK116(le)001:11762: gti mug 'od gsal du bsre ba chos sku'i zhing
NK116(le)001:11763: sbyongs gsum la 'dris pas bar do'i yid lus stong
NK116(le)001:11764: gzugs kyi lha skur sdang te mchog gi dngos grub
NK116(le)001:11766: rlung dbu mar thim pa las stong pa bzhis drangs pa'i don du sems bskyed de /
NK116(le)001:11767: 'od gsal gyi mthar rlung sems tsam gyi sgyu ma'i
NK116(le)001:11768: lha skur ldang ba'am dga' bzhi'i drangs pa'i rjes kyi
NK116(le)001:11769: lhan skyes las sgyu ma'i skur ldang ngo //
NK116(le)001:11770: gsum pa rmi lam gyi gdam pa ni /
NK116(le)001:11771: mkha' khyab 'gro ba'i don tu sems bskyed de /
NK116(le)001:11772: mgrin pa'i nang du drin chen gyi bla ma bsgoms la gsol ba nan tan gdab ste /
NK116(le)001:11773: de nas mgrin pa'i rtsa 'khor gyi dbus su pad+ma 'dab bzhi'i lte bar dkar po //
NK116(le)001:11774: mdun g.yas rgyab g.yon rnams la rim bzhin /
NK116(le)001:11775: a nu ta ra zhes bzhi sngo ser dmar ljang gi rnam pa gsal 'tsher can du bsgom ste /
NK116(le)001:11776: gnyid du 'gro khar de rnams la dran shes rtse
NK116(le)001:11777: gcig gtad na der rlung sems 'dus nas rmi lam
NK116(le)001:11779: rgyas par gzhan du shes so //
NK116(le)001:11780: sbyongs nas longs sku'i zhing khams nyul ba sogs kyi sprul bsgyur byed de /
NK116(le)001:11781: snga ma'i sgyu lus dang bsres nas sbyangs bas bar dor longs spyod rdzogs skur ldang bar 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:11783: thog mar sems bskyed nas snying khar bla ma yab yum bsgom nas gsol ba gdab /
NK116(le)001:11784: rdzogs rim gyi lha sku sgyu ma lta bur gsal
NK116(le)001:11785: ba'i snying kha'i rtsa 'khor gyi dbus su h'u yig
NK116(le)001:11786: sngon po gsal ba la sems gcig tu gtad de
NK116(le)001:11788: slar na da'i bar mi dmigs pa'i ngang la rim par bsdu ste /
NK116(le)001:11789: de ltar yang yang bsgom mo //
NK116(le)001:11790: nyal ba'i dus gnyid ma byung gi bar h'u de
NK116(le)001:11791: la sems gtad bas rlung sems cung zad 'dus pas
NK116(le)001:11792: 'byung ba rim gyis thim pas du ba dang smig
NK116(le)001:11797: thams cad stong pa bzhi rim par shar ba'i dus
NK116(le)001:11798: de'i ngang ma shor ba ni gdams pa'i ngo bo
NK116(le)001:11799: yin no // slar sad tshe bla ma la gsol ba gdabs //
NK116(le)001:11800: lus dbus su chos nyid kyi d+hu ti shel gyi
NK116(le)001:11801: ka ba btsugs pa lta bu phyin nang med par
NK116(le)001:11802: zang thal le ba'i snying ga'i thad +aa yig dmar
NK116(le)001:11803: po mar me sbar ba lta bu'i gsal snang gis
NK116(le)001:11804: lus kyi nang thams cad gsal ba la rig pa
NK116(le)001:11806: de yang nam mkha' klong yangs kyi rgyud las /
NK116(le)001:11807: gnyid ni bsgom par gsal 'debs ni //
NK116(le)001:11808: ldog kha bsad pa'i dus dag du /
NK116(le)001:11809: ti la chos sku dran byas nas //
NK116(le)001:11811: de la gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum gyis dbye na dang po la gnas lugs kyi 'od gsal /
NK116(le)001:11813: 'chi ba'i 'od gsal gsum ste sgom ma bsgom thams cad du yod pa'o //
NK116(le)001:11815: chos thams cad skye med du rtogs pa spyi don gyi 'od gsal dang /
NK116(le)001:11816: sad stug 'chi gsum gyi skabs su rlunga sems dbu
NK116(le)001:11817: ma pa 'dus shing thim pa la byung ba'i stong
NK116(le)001:11818: pa bzhi po myong thog tu ngo 'phrod pa'o //
NK116(le)001:11820: mi slob pa'i zung 'jug mngon du gyur pa la tha snyad du bya'o //
NK116(le)001:11822: 'di ltar srid pa phyi mar nying mtshams sbyong ba'i dus na //
NK116(le)001:11823: rlung rnams snying khar thim pa dang spyi bo'i thig le dkar po thur du bab /
NK116(le)001:11824: rnam shes snang ba la thim pa dang lte ba'i thig le dmar po gyen du log /
NK116(le)001:11826: de gnyis snying gar phrad cing mched pa nyer thob la thim ste so so'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK116(le)001:11827: rim bzhin sprin bral gyi nam mkha' zhes kun gyi mgo bor sbyar te /
NK116(le)001:11828: zla 'od kyi slongs ba lta bu'i dkar lam pa /
NK116(le)001:11829: nyi 'od kyis slongs ba lta bu'i dmar lam pa dang /
NK116(le)001:11830: mtshams kyi smag gis slongs ba lta bu'i snang ba
NK116(le)001:11831: 'char te tha ma'i dus dran pa nyams te brgyal
NK116(le)001:11832: nas rang bzhin brgyad cu'i rtogs pa 'gags par 'gyur
NK116(le)001:11833: ro // de nas nyer thob 'od gsal la thim pas brgyal sangs te /
NK116(le)001:11834: snga ma'i slong byed kyi rkyen gsum dang bral te
NK116(le)001:11835: tho rengs kyi ston gnam g.ya' dag pa lta bu
NK116(le)001:11836: zhig 'char ba de nyid la 'chi ba 'od gsal
NK116(le)001:11837: zhes bya ste / lus can yongs la lhan skyes
NK116(le)001:11838: kyi 'od gsal la mngon du gyur pa'i dus so
NK116(le)001:11839: zhes bya ste / // goms goms min gnyis las /
NK116(le)001:11840: dang po la grol ba longs yod du 'char la /
NK116(le)001:11841: gcig shos la shar yang ngos mi zin /
NK116(le)001:11842: khams drug ldan mi las gzhan la cung zad 'char
NK116(le)001:11843: ba tsam du zad pas ngo 'phrod pa'i skal ba
NK116(le)001:11845: rdzogs rim gyi stong pa bzhi'i 'od gsal la mnyam par 'jog pa /
NK116(le)001:11846: de las ldang ba'i tshe lugs ldog gi nyer thob
NK116(le)001:11847: nas smig rgyu'i bar gyi rtags snang dang lhan gcig
NK116(le)001:11848: yid ngo'i lha skur ldang ba /
NK116(le)001:11849: de las ldang ba dang rnam smin gyi phung po
NK116(le)001:11850: sems dpa' sum rtsegs kyi lha skur blta ba gsum
NK116(le)001:11851: / rim bzhin sad dus kyi yin pa 'dra zhing /
NK116(le)001:11854: sprul sku'i bsre ba yin pa ltar gnyid kyi dus na'ang sbyangs te goms pa brten dgos so //
NK116(le)001:11855: goms nas 'chi tshe 'byung ba sdud pa'i dus su
NK116(le)001:11856: bskyed rdzogs gang gom kyang sdur rim dang mthun par
NK116(le)001:11857: bsdus te chos nyid kyi dran pa las mi g.yo
NK116(le)001:11858: ba snang mched thob gsum gyi rtags rnams 'byung ba'i
NK116(le)001:11859: rgyus can shul lam du zhugs pa ltar rnam smin
NK116(le)001:11860: lus kyi rgya / bag chags snang ba'i rgya /
NK116(le)001:11861: rnam shes sems kyi rgya gsum las grol lo //
NK116(le)001:11862: slob lam gyi yon tan mthar phyin pas dag bya
NK116(le)001:11863: mtha' dang dag nas mi slob pa'i sangs rgyas chos
NK116(le)001:11864: sku'i yon tan dus gcig tu rdzogs pa yin no
NK116(le)001:11865: // 'od gsal de las lugs ldog tu ldang nas
NK116(le)001:11866: ming bzhis phung po can gyi bag chags de nyid
NK116(le)001:11867: rlung sems tsam las grub pa'i mtshan dpe'i bdag nyid
NK116(le)001:11868: can gyi yid ngos lha skur ldang ba ni bar
NK116(le)001:11869: do longs spyod rdzogs skur grol ba zhes bya'o //
NK116(le)001:11870: gal te de ltar ma nus pa'am /
NK116(le)001:11872: mngon par shes pas brtags te 'os pa'i rten gyi
NK116(le)001:11873: khu khrag dkar dmar tshogs pa nas lus rdzogs pa'i
NK116(le)001:11876: skad cig bardzusa skyes la sogs pas nying mtshams sbyor ba la skye ba sprul sku zhes bya'o //
NK116(le)001:11877: blo stobs zhan pas thal na bar srid kyi lus
NK116(le)001:11878: rten dbang po kun tshangs la rang bzhin brgyad bcu'i
NK116(le)001:11880: sa chu me rlung gi rlung bzhi las /
NK116(le)001:11884: dus kyi rlung sgra ste 'jigs pa'i sgra bzhi dug
NK116(le)001:11885: gsum gyi shes pa'i rang gzugs gcong rong dkar dmar
NK116(le)001:11886: nag po ste / ya nga ba'i g.yang sa gsum
NK116(le)001:11887: sogs 'char ba ni 'khrul snang gi stong gzugs las
NK116(le)001:11888: thog reg med pas ji ste 'jigs snyams nas /
NK116(le)001:11889: dad mos gang yod kyi lha dang bla mar yid
NK116(le)001:11890: gtad de skye ba bzang po len pa'i 'dun pa
NK116(le)001:11892: rab bskyed rdzogs kyi bden pas 'phang ba' rnam shes
NK116(le)001:11893: kyi rang bzhin 'chi ba don dam gyi bden pa
NK116(le)001:11894: 'od gsal ba'i ngang du 'pho ba dang /
NK116(le)001:11895: 'bring bar do'i 'od gsal zin nas sgyu lus kyi
NK116(le)001:11896: lha skur 'pho ba'i phyir tha snyad tsam la 'pho
NK116(le)001:11897: ba'i gdam pa dmigs gsal ba mi dgos //
NK116(le)001:11898: tha mas 'pho ba la gsum te /
NK116(le)001:11903: rlung la brten pa'i gang zag gam /
NK116(le)001:11904: min kyang gdams ngag rang lam nas sbyang ba spyi
NK116(le)001:11905: dang mthun te nam zhig 'chi ba'i rtags dang sbyar
NK116(le)001:11907: sems bskyed rgya chen po dang /
NK116(le)001:11908: gsol 'debs snang ba 'gyur ba tsam byas pa gong
NK116(le)001:11909: du 'pho bar 'dun pa rtse gcig gi ngang nas
NK116(le)001:11911: nyid lag dang bcas pa bkag pa'am /
NK116(le)001:11912: rdo rje rba rlabs kyi man ngag la brten nas 'pho bar bya'o //
NK116(le)001:11914: 'dun pa sngar bzhin las lus gnad mgo byang bstan gyi gla g.yas sa la phab /
NK116(le)001:11917: rkang pa gnyis ma bsnol bar steng 'og tu bzhag
NK116(le)001:11918: nas brkyang ba seng ge'i nyal stabs kyi ngang nas
NK116(le)001:11919: dag pa'i zhing khams yid la bya zhing 'pho ba'o
NK116(le)001:11920: // de dag ni skyes bu'i rtsola basa rang gi
NK116(le)001:11921: lus kyi stenga kho nas 'grub kyis gazhana rkyen la
NK116(le)001:11922: raga ma lusa pa'i phyir na ranga lusa thabas ldan
NK116(le)001:11925: rtsa thig ces bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:11926: rtsa thiga rlung la ganda du songa nasa slara /
NK116(le)001:11927: bde stong lam du byed pa gazhana phyag rgya'i lusa te rigs lnga'i rigs can gyi mi mo dang /
NK116(le)001:11928: rang lus la 'dzin pa med pa'i mkha' 'gro ma dang /
NK116(le)001:11929: de yang don gyi 'od gsal thob pa'i lhan skyes /
NK116(le)001:11930: dbang dang bskyed rim gyi rgyud spyangs pa'i sngags skyes
NK116(le)001:11931: yul nyer bzhi la sogs par skyes pa'i zhing skyes
NK116(le)001:11932: ma ni brten pa tsam gyis thabs dang shes rab
NK116(le)001:11933: tu 'brel ba'i rten 'brel bsgrigs pa'i sa bon rlung
NK116(le)001:11934: khug gcig 'gags nas 'gyur ba med pa'i bde chen
NK116(le)001:11935: ster zhing / mthar gyi nyi khri chig stong drug
NK116(le)001:11936: brgya'i 'gyur ba 'pho ba gcig tu thub nas lam
NK116(le)001:11937: gyi yon tan mtha' dag btsan thabs su 'phel ba'o
NK116(le)001:11938: ster zhing / // de bas na bskyed dang rdzogs
NK116(le)001:11939: pa'i gnad rnams kuna kyang yang dag pa'i lam du
NK116(le)001:11940: 'gro ba gzhan las phul du byung ba thabsa kyi
NK116(le)001:11941: lam bde ba chen po kho na yin pa /
NK116(le)001:11942: rgyud las rnam pa kun gyi mchog ldan ma //
NK116(le)001:11943: stong nyid shes rab mdzes ma nyid //
NK116(le)001:11944: rgyal ba thams cad bskyed pa'i yum //
NK116(le)001:11947: gnyis pa snang med kyi rdzogs rim ni gnyis pa zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan ste /
NK116(le)001:11948: snang ba dang bcas pa'i rdzogs rim bstan zin pa
NK116(le)001:11949: de nas gnyis pa snang ba meda pa'i rdzogas rima
NK116(le)001:11950: ni / sgo gsum rnam para gyur ba'i bskyed rdzogas kyi rim pa ganga yina yanga /
NK116(le)001:11951: tha mal a 'thas kyi 'dzin pa rnam par daga
NK116(le)001:11952: pa'i snod bcud brten g.yo thams cad sku dang ye
NK116(le)001:11953: shes su snang ba kuna kyang /
NK116(le)001:11954: mthar 'oda du zhu nas snying ga'i sa bona rnamas /
NK116(le)001:11955: thiga lera thima pa de yanga mas nas rima gyis yal nasa /
NK116(le)001:11956: ye stong spros pa thams cad bral bar gyur ba nama mkha'i ngo bo nyid /
