NK116(le)001:11957: chos dbyings ye shesa chena po'i spyod yula nyid la bazhaga par bya'o //
NK116(le)001:11958: de 'dra'i bskyed rima gyisa ni snang ba'i ma dag gzhan dbang ba'i bdena zhena 'goga cing /
NK116(le)001:11959: rdzogas rima gyis ni de nyid sgyu ma'i zhena rtog
NK116(le)001:11960: spong la thams cad sku dang ye shes su snang
NK116(le)001:11961: ba kun kyang / bde gasla mi rtogsa lhan cig
NK116(le)001:11962: skyes pa'i ye shesa mthar thug pa 'achara ba yin
NK116(le)001:11963: ba kun kyang / no // zaba pa'i rdzogas rima bla na meda pa 'di lta bu rnams ni /
NK116(le)001:11964: bla na med pa'i rgyud kho na lasa bstan pa
NK116(le)001:11965: tsam du zad kyi 'oga mara gang du yang gsungas
NK116(le)001:11966: pa meda do // de'i phyir skal ldan dbang po
NK116(le)001:11967: rnon po gang zhig tshe gciga gi rdo rje 'chang
NK116(le)001:11969: nye lam sbasa pa shin tu zaba mo yina pasa snying lasa kyang gces spras gyis la chongs shig ///
NK116(le)001:11970: da ni sngags kyi dngos grub 'dzin pa srog shing
NK116(le)001:11971: dam tshig bsrung tshul spyir ston pa'i phyir gsum pa
NK116(le)001:11972: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:11973: gsuma pa thabs grol gyi lam de dag dang mthuna pa'i grogas su gyur pa dama tshiga ni /
NK116(le)001:11974: sngagsa la zhugas pasa brtul zhugsa mi nyamsa par bsrunga nas /
NK116(le)001:11975: de'i spyod pa'i khyad par gang zag rang sgo nas
NK116(le)001:11976: shes rab dang ting 'dzin la sogs pa'i thabsa kyis
NK116(le)001:11977: zin pa dang // nyon mongs pa'i gnyena pora 'gyur
NK116(le)001:11978: ba'i rten cing 'brel 'byung gi blang dor mi 'chora
NK116(le)001:11979: bar byas tshe dper na rma bya'i mgrina para batsana
NK116(le)001:11980: duga zhugas pas lang tsho blta na sdug para 'gyur
NK116(le)001:11981: ba ltar bas ma gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes
NK116(le)001:11982: kyi rgyan du che bas spyad do //
NK116(le)001:11983: dam sdom gyi dbye ba ni de la zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:11984: de yang gang la la dag dama tshiga dang ni sdom pa'i khyad la rmong na 'di ltar ste /
NK116(le)001:11985: dama tshiga ni nam yang 'ad'a bar bya ba ma yina la /
NK116(le)001:11986: sdoma pa ni bsrung bar bya ba dang dgos pa
NK116(le)001:11987: byung na mi bya ba'i ngesa pa yang yod pa
NK116(le)001:11988: ste / de gnyis ngo bo gciga yin la ldoga chas dbye ba'o //
NK116(le)001:11989: de'ang sngagas sdoma yina na dama tshig 'dresa te /
NK116(le)001:11990: sdom pa gsum ka blangs nas gdod dbang bzhi la 'jug dgos pa'o //
NK116(le)001:11991: dama tshiga yina na sdom pa 'dres par mi 'gyur te /
NK116(le)001:11992: gnang bkag gi mtshams med pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:11996: sa zhes bya ba bskyed pa la /
NK116(le)001:11997: ma zhes bya ba ma nyams na //
NK116(le)001:11998: dngos grub thams cad ster ba yin //
NK116(le)001:11999: ya zhes nyams na yar bar 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:12004: dam nyid zhes bya bcings pa ste //
NK116(le)001:12005: de nyid grol na nyams pa nyid //
NK116(le)001:12006: tshig ces bya ba de 'das na //
NK116(le)001:12007: me yi sdug bsngal myong ba'o //
NK116(le)001:12009: ji bzhin du dam par bsrung na nyon mongs pa'i phyogs 'tshig pa dang //
NK116(le)001:12010: 'gal na nag po'i rnam smin gyis bdag rgyud dam
NK116(le)001:12011: por zin nas dmyal mesa'atshiga pas na dam tshig dang
NK116(le)001:12012: / de'i rang bzhin la nan tan du ldan pa'i sems kyis dam bca' ba ni sdom pa'o //
NK116(le)001:12013: 'o na de gnyis la 'da' rung min 'dra 'am zhe na //
NK116(le)001:12014: phyi ma rgyu 'bras thun mong du grags la /
NK116(le)001:12015: snga ma mtshan nyid kyi theg pa 'ba' zhig gi skabs su zad pa khyad che'o //
NK116(le)001:12016: dam tshig gi snod kun gyi zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:12017: smin grol kuna gyi spyi'i dona gal po che sngagsa sdom ma thob pa dang /
NK116(le)001:12018: thob kyang smyo ba la sogas 'du shes ranga bzhina
NK116(le)001:12019: du mi gansa pa la ltung ba dang dngosa grub
NK116(le)001:12021: sngagas sdom dang ldana zhing rtag tu ma nyamsa shing
NK116(le)001:12022: ma btang la shesa pa ranga bzhina rnal du gansa
NK116(le)001:12023: pa de nyid / ltung ba dang ni dngosa grub gnyis ka'i snod yin no //
NK116(le)001:12024: kun dkris dang sbom pa'i khyad par byang chub ces bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:12025: rtsa ltung lnga pa byang chub kyi semas 'dor ba lus gzhan pa'i rtsa ltung bcu gsum pa la /
NK116(le)001:12026: kuna dkris zhes bya ba ste /
NK116(le)001:12027: gal te nyes pa de'i gang gis phog na da
NK116(le)001:12028: dunga bya ba de byed 'doda ma loga pa dang
NK116(le)001:12029: // nyes dmigs de la 'gyod pa meda pa dang /
NK116(le)001:12030: ranga ngora ltos pa'i ngo tsha shesa pa dang /
NK116(le)001:12031: gazhana ngora ltos pa'i khrel yoda meda pa ste /
NK116(le)001:12032: zhes phyi ma gnyis gcig tu bsdom pa'i /
NK116(le)001:12033: chosa gsum po de tshang pa'i kuna slong ngan pa
NK116(le)001:12034: de bya ba'i dngos gzhi rdzogs mathara gtug pa de
NK116(le)001:12035: srid du / rgyun chagsa su yoda par gyur na
NK116(le)001:12036: kuna dkris tshangas pa'i phama par gyur pa ste ltung
NK116(le)001:12037: ba chen por gyur ba yina no //
NK116(le)001:12038: de lta bu'i kun slong gi dusa kyi nyes pa
NK116(le)001:12039: sogs bsam nas dngos bzhi ma rdzogs tshun bar chad
NK116(le)001:12040: nas rgyun chagas su meda pa 'am /
NK116(le)001:12041: chos gsuma po ganga lasa cig shosa ma tshang na /
NK116(le)001:12042: bya ba de'i yan lag ma tshanga ba'i phyir sgoma
NK116(le)001:12043: pora 'gyur pa las phas pham pa ma yin no
NK116(le)001:12044: // rtsa ltung gnyen po la mi rmongs par bya
NK116(le)001:12045: ba'i tshul de yis zhes bya ba la sogs pas
NK116(le)001:12046: // bstan te / 'di 'dra'i sdom pa thob pa'i
NK116(le)001:12047: gang zag de yisa shesa par bya ba'i gnas kyi
NK116(le)001:12048: rtsa ba dang yan lag kuna /
NK116(le)001:12049: yida kyi mi sponga lus kyis dora mi bya ste
NK116(le)001:12050: rtag tu nyin gsum dang matshana mo thun gsum ste
NK116(le)001:12051: cha drug tu bgosa pa la /
NK116(le)001:12052: cha re'i nanga du rtsa ltung bcu bzhi po'i /
NK116(le)001:12053: nyes pa byung ngam ma byung zhib tu bsgrims te
NK116(le)001:12054: sngo bgrang bya la gal te nyes pas gosa na
NK116(le)001:12055: / 'gyod pa bskyed cinga phyir 'chosa kyi thabs kho na semas shing /
NK116(le)001:12056: gosa pa meda na dag'a ba bsgoma zhing dge rtsa yongs la bsngo'o //
NK116(le)001:12057: sngona chad nyes pas gosa sama ma gosa gang yina kyang rung ste /
NK116(le)001:12058: phyin chad ni sroga la bab kyang nyes byas kyi
NK116(le)001:12059: las phra mos kyang gosa para mi bya sems pa'i
NK116(le)001:12060: sdoma semas shina tu brtan par bya'o //
NK116(le)001:12061: gang tshe nyin mtshan cha druga tu bgos pa ganga
NK116(le)001:12062: yanga rung ba'i nanga du sngo bgranga byed pa'i 'du
NK116(le)001:12064: kha na ma tho ba'i sboma po zhesa pa ni 'byung zhing /
NK116(le)001:12065: druga ka 'adsa na sboma po druga tu 'gyur zhing /
NK116(le)001:12066: zhaga de'i khongas su phyir bcosa ma grub na zhaga phyi ma'i skya rengas dang po 'achara ba dang /
NK116(le)001:12067: sboma po bcu gnyis daga tu 'gyur bar bshad de
NK116(le)001:12068: yan lag gi dama tshiga la yanga de yi 'gre
NK116(le)001:12070: khyad par thoga mara bla meda spyi la gcesa pa'i chingas /
NK116(le)001:12071: rtsa ltung bcu bzhi'i raba tu dbye ba 'di ltar brtagsa par bya'o //
NK116(le)001:12072: ci'i phyir spyi chings su 'gyur zhe na /
NK116(le)001:12073: rdo rje snying po rgyan gyi rgyud dang /
NK116(le)001:12075: dgra nag gi rgyud sogs las grangs nges pa'i phyir bla ma lnga bcu pa las /
NK116(le)001:12076: rtsa ba'i ltur ba bcu bzhi ni /
NK116(le)001:12077: bklag dang 'dzin pa nyid du bya /
NK116(le)001:12079: zhes gdams nas so sor bral ba dang po zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:12080: dang po dbang thoba yul gyi sloba dpona shin tu
NK116(le)001:12081: gnyan pa smosa ci dgosa te sngags kyi rgyud tshiga
NK116(le)001:12082: bacada gciga pa yana chada kyi don bkrala nas bslab
NK116(le)001:12083: pa dang / lam gyi man ngaga zaba mo bskyed
NK116(le)001:12084: rdzogs gnyis med kyi don la rmongs pa'i dra ba
NK116(le)001:12085: bsal ste ston par byed pa dang gsum po de
NK116(le)001:12086: la chosa kyi 'brel ba'i bka' drina bsam zhing bsnyen
NK116(le)001:12087: pa dang / bskura byed pa'i / khura ring du
NK116(le)001:12088: bor nas brnyasa shing gshung ba'i tha chad de la
NK116(le)001:12089: sngagas kyi dngosa gruba cung zad tsam yang yoda pa
NK116(le)001:12092: tshigs bcad gcig tsam mnyan pa de /
NK116(le)001:12093: gang gis bla mar mi 'dzin pa /
NK116(le)001:12094: khyi yi skye ba brgyar skyes nas /
NK116(le)001:12095: sme sha can du skye bar 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:12097: gnyis pa ni sdoma pa gsuma dang bslab pa'i gnas rnams /
NK116(le)001:12098: bde bar gshegas pa'i gannga bakaga gi matshamas ji bzhin
NK116(le)001:12099: du bsrungs dgos rgyu la de lasa 'adsa pa dang
NK116(le)001:12100: / de bzhina matshana nyid ldan pa'i bla ma yi /
NK116(le)001:12101: yula dang dusa la ltos nas dgongsa pa can du
NK116(le)001:12102: gsungs pa'i bka'a la khyad du basda ba yina no
NK116(le)001:12103: / gsum pa ni bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gcig
NK116(le)001:12104: la brten nas dabnga gi gral gciga du zhugs shing
NK116(le)001:12106: bskur zhing brnyas par byas pa dmigas kyis basla na'ang /
NK116(le)001:12107: ma zad matha'a yasa semas cana bde gshegas snying posa
NK116(le)001:12108: bsdus bas na spuna yina phyir spyi'i mched dag rgyal
NK116(le)001:12109: ba'i bstan pa la zhugs so cog bslabs pa'i gnas
NK116(le)001:12110: gang rung dang ldan phyir ringa ba'i mched dang rdo
NK116(le)001:12111: rje theg pa'i sdom pa la gnas pa nye ba'i
NK116(le)001:12112: mcheda rnams la'ang mtshungsa pa yin pas bkur ba sti
NK116(le)001:12113: dgos pa ngan song sbyongs rgyud las //
NK116(le)001:12114: rdo rje spun dang srin mo dang //
NK116(le)001:12115: rdo rje ma rnams nyid la ni //
NK116(le)001:12116: rnal 'byor can gyi brnyas mi bya /
NK116(le)001:12119: mtha' yas sems can rang rig phyir //
NK116(le)001:12120: gang dag bdag las gzhan med cing //
NK116(le)001:12121: bde gshegs snying pos spun yin phyir //
NK116(le)001:12122: ma 'ongs sangs rgyas rang bzhin ni //
NK116(le)001:12123: spyi yi mched de pha tshan bzhin //
NK116(le)001:12124: sangs rgyas chos zhugs ring ba dang //
NK116(le)001:12125: lta spyod mthun pa nye bar bshad //
NK116(le)001:12126: pha gcig dam tshig nang 'dres pa //
NK116(le)001:12129: 'di ltar bdag la sbyor bar ba rtsub pa'i semas
NK116(le)001:12130: cana zhiga tshe 'dir mthonga ba'i chosa la rgyal po'i
NK116(le)001:12131: chad pa sogs 'jigs pa gang rung zhig gi lasa
NK116(le)001:12132: kyi manra te sdug bsngal bar gyur pa de la
NK116(le)001:12133: dag'a ba bsgoma para byas nas byamsa pa'i semas /
NK116(le)001:12134: btor ba byang chuba semas dapara raba tu lci na //
NK116(le)001:12135: gazhana phal po che bde ba dang bral bar 'doda
NK116(le)001:12136: la smos ci dgosa te shin tu ma rung bar
NK116(le)001:12137: bgyid do // rdo rje snying po'i rgyan las /
NK116(le)001:12138: byams sems med par sems can spongs /
NK116(le)001:12141: gazhana dona gnyer ba'i byang chuba semas bskyed spangsa ba'i
NK116(le)001:12142: moda la smona semsa rtsa ba nas gtong ba'i phyir
NK116(le)001:12143: / kuna dkris tshangas pa'i phama para gyur pa yin la /
NK116(le)001:12144: gzhan yang gsang ba'i dbang dang gsum pa dang //
NK116(le)001:12145: ro mnyams pa dang lha mchod dang /
NK116(le)001:12146: rigs rgyud spel dang ril bu dang /
NK116(le)001:12147: 'chi ltas brtags pa'i dus yin te /
NK116(le)001:12149: gannga ba'i skabsa bduna po de mina para khu ba dbyung ba'o //
NK116(le)001:12152: mu stegs can la smad byas na //
NK116(le)001:12153: rnam par snang mdzad ring pa'i rgyu /
NK116(le)001:12156: phyi rol ba yang lam 'tshol zhugs //
NK116(le)001:12157: de phyir de la smad mi bya /
NK116(le)001:12158: lam zhugs nyan thos smos ci dgos //
NK116(le)001:12159: zhes phyi rol grub mtha' smra ba yang ci yang
NK116(le)001:12160: mi dpyod pa'i skye bo ba lang lta bu las
NK116(le)001:12161: ches 'phags pas smad ma bya na /
NK116(le)001:12162: gzhan thega pa gsuma la ltos pas rgyal ba'i bka'a rin po che nyams su len pa lta ci /
NK116(le)001:12163: thos pa kho na'i rnam smin yang bsam gyis mi
NK116(le)001:12164: khyab pa gang la dpyasa shinga ston pasa ma gsungas
NK116(le)001:12166: chos de dang mthun pa lasa rab 'byams dang dngosa
NK116(le)001:12167: grub rnam gnyis kyi rgyur runga ba'i tshad ldan gyi
NK116(le)001:12170: byin gyi brlabs pa'i bka'a ru ma bltasa par brnyas pa rnams so //
NK116(le)001:12172: dabnga gi cho ga ma byas pa ste /
NK116(le)001:12173: dkyil 'khor du ma zhugs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:12174: zhugs kyang bum dbang tsam las dbang bzhi ma rdzogsa pa dang /
NK116(le)001:12175: thob kyang nyamsa pa dang snod ngana ste theg dman
NK116(le)001:12176: rnams stong nyid zaba mosa skrag par 'gyur ba'i phyir
NK116(le)001:12177: gsang sngags kyi 'dula ba'i dus skabsa la ma bab
NK116(le)001:12178: pas ganda kyi bkal ba dag la /
NK116(le)001:12179: gasnga sngagas zaba mo'i dona dang dgongas spyod bsgragsa pa
NK116(le)001:12180: ni dmigas basla yina gyis rjesa gannga dang bzlas lunga
NK116(le)001:12181: tsam gyis kyang gasnga ba sgrogsa tu rung min ngosa
NK116(le)001:12182: 'dzina sgrim te 'dira ni pha rol pos snod la
NK116(le)001:12183: brtag dgos so // brgyad pa ni /
NK116(le)001:12184: gzugas phunga rnam snanga la sogas lnga yin la /
NK116(le)001:12185: de bzhina skye mcheda sems dpa' sems ma'i lha skur mi shesa para /
NK116(le)001:12186: sduga bsngal bdena para bsgrub pa'i rtog ge'i blo'i /
NK116(le)001:12187: brnyas pa dang bka'a thuba mthu yisa lhag para gdunga bar byed pa'o //
NK116(le)001:12189: ranga bzhina gdod nas dag pa'i stong nyid zab mo'i dona //
NK116(le)001:12190: sangsa rgyasa kho na'i spyod yula nyid lasa gazhana semas
NK116(le)001:12191: cana khamas dang 'brela yod ces gsungs pa rgyu tsam
NK116(le)001:12192: la ltos pa'am spro ba bskyed pa'i phyir ldema dgongas
NK116(le)001:12193: su yin nam snyams te the tshoma zosa nasa nges
NK116(le)001:12194: don gyi mdo dang rgyud sde zab mo'i dgongs don
NK116(le)001:12195: bdag gi rgyud la dkri ba spangsa ba'o //
NK116(le)001:12197: dkona mchoga gsuma dang bla ma la dmoda pa dang
NK116(le)001:12198: bstan pa 'jigas par byed pa gzhir bcas sogas khung
NK116(le)001:12199: nas zhing bcu rnams bstan te /
NK116(le)001:12201: dkon mchog slob dpon sku dgra gnyis //
NK116(le)001:12202: dam nyams log dang 'khu ba dang //
NK116(le)001:12204: dam dgra ngan pa'i ngang tshul can //
NK116(le)001:12205: ngan song gsum dang bcu po ni //
NK116(le)001:12206: rnal 'byor kun gyis dang du longs /
NK116(le)001:12208: dam tshig nyams te phyir bcos mi byed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:12209: sngags kyi theg par zhugs kyang slar log ste khyad du gsod pa dang /
NK116(le)001:12210: bla ma dang mched la zhe sdang bas 'khu ba dang /
NK116(le)001:12211: sngags la 'du bar mi dbang kyang phod btsug pa dang //
NK116(le)001:12212: sems can yongs la gnod pa /
NK116(le)001:12213: dam tshig can la dgra byed pa /
NK116(le)001:12214: mi dge ba'i las 'ba' zhig la 'jug pa'i ngang
NK116(le)001:12215: tshul ngan pa can dang ngan song gsum ste bcu
NK116(le)001:12216: po ni nus pa thob pa'i rnal 'byor bas draga
NK116(le)001:12217: shula gyi cho ga yisa mngona du sbyod par byed
NK116(le)001:12218: pa'i yula du gyur ba dang /
NK116(le)001:12220: glen pa dkon mchog gsum smod dang //
NK116(le)001:12221: sangs rgyas bstan la gnod byed dang //
NK116(le)001:12222: bla ma smod la brtson pa rnams //
NK116(le)001:12223: mkhas pas sgrim te gsad par bya zhes sogs gsungs
NK116(le)001:12224: pas de la bsrana cinga bzoda nas btang snyoms su
NK116(le)001:12225: 'jog pa ni nus pa thob pa'i rnal 'byor la
NK116(le)001:12226: dgongs pa dang / 'drisa shinga 'dza' bshesa su byas
NK116(le)001:12227: nasa byamsa para byas pa sngags kyi gang zag spyir
NK116(le)001:12228: btang la dgongs par grags kyang //
NK116(le)001:12229: sku dgra gnyis sogs dmigs bsal rnams nus ldan min kyang /
NK116(le)001:12230: byang chub sems kyis zin bzhin bsgral bar 'os pa'o //
NK116(le)001:12232: minga tha snyad las bral ba ni chosa kyi dbyings te /
NK116(le)001:12233: de la rtog ge'i tshad mas ji ltar gzhal kyang
NK116(le)001:12234: chosa kyi badga meda ni blo dang rdzasa 'agla ba
NK116(le)001:12235: yina pas tshul bzhina du mi rtog mod //
NK116(le)001:12236: de lta na'ang 'gal zhig phung sogas stong pa chad para blta ba la mchoga tu 'dzina pa'i blos /
NK116(le)001:12237: skye ba meda pa'i gruba matha'a rtog pasa 'ajala ba'o //
NK116(le)001:12239: chos nyid tshad ni bzung mi bya /
NK116(le)001:12242: chos la tshad mas gzhal mi bya /
NK116(le)001:12244: 'o na tshad ma sde bdun sogs kyang de ltar thal ba mi 'gyur ram zhe na /
NK116(le)001:12245: de ni yang dag pa'i tshad ma yin te /
NK116(le)001:12246: re zhig chos dang chos min gtan la dbab phyir
NK116(le)001:12247: dgos kyang mnyam bzhag ngos nas dpyad blo yod na
NK116(le)001:12248: gsor mi rung bar 'gyur bas rtog ge rnams kyis
NK116(le)001:12249: gzab par bya'o // bcu gnyis pa ni sngagas kyi snod du rung ba'i gdul bya'am /
NK116(le)001:12250: theg pa gang rung gi snod dad pa gsum yang
NK116(le)001:12251: ldan la dona du gnyer kyang chosa mi ston zhing
NK116(le)001:12252: // yon la 'khang nas kuna slong ngana pa dang
NK116(le)001:12253: bcas pa'i tshig gis gazhana pha rol po de'i sems
NK116(le)001:12254: // sum phyung nasa / dada dang 'duna pa phyin ci loga tu skyogsa par byed pa'o //
NK116(le)001:12256: dad ldan sems can bzlog pa min /
NK116(le)001:12259: spyad para bya ba'i dama rdzasa sha lnga dang bdud
NK116(le)001:12260: rtsi lnga sogs la ma dag ranga rgyud du bltas
NK116(le)001:12261: nas la la spangasa zhing la la sred de /
NK116(le)001:12262: sngagas kyi brtul zhugsa ji bzhina pa nyamsa 'oga tu
NK116(le)001:12263: ma chud pa'i skyon gyis blang dor matha'a gnyis kyi
NK116(le)001:12265: de yang bdud rtsi 'byung ba las //
NK116(le)001:12266: gtsang dang mi gtsang rnam rtog yin //
NK116(le)001:12267: mkhas pas dbus la'ang gnas mi bya /
NK116(le)001:12270: rdo rje rnal 'byor ma sogas 'jiga rten las 'adsa pa dang //
NK116(le)001:12271: gzhan yang ma mo mkha'a 'gro la sogas 'khor 'das kyi so 'atshamas 'dzina pa'i rigs rnams dang /
NK116(le)001:12272: 'byung ba lnga yi khamas sangs rgyas spyan ma sogs
NK116(le)001:12273: su ma shes te de la ranga rgyud par bltasa
NK116(le)001:12274: pa dang / dabnga gi skabs gsum pa'i rten du
NK116(le)001:12275: gyur nas bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes bskyed
NK116(le)001:12276: pa'i thabs bla nameda pa buda meda yina pas basngagasa
NK116(le)001:12278: de'i yan lag sbom po brgyad zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:12279: rtsa ltung bcu bzhi'i yan lag sboma pa gtod byed
NK116(le)001:12280: kyi rkyen pham pa mina yanga dngosa gruba rnam gnyis
NK116(le)001:12281: thoba pa la gegsa su che ba'i sbom po brgyad
NK116(le)001:12285: sdoma pasa rgyud ma sbyongsa ba'i tha mal gyi buda meda riga mar brten pa dang /
NK116(le)001:12286: matshana nyid dang 'agla ba'i bud med kyis drana pa'i
NK116(le)001:12287: khrona pa ste b+ha ga nas cho ga yanga dag
NK116(le)001:12288: ma yina par 'khrug bzhina bduda rtsi zhes rdul rang
NK116(le)001:12290: dabnga ma thoba pa dang lhag para dada pa meda pa la /
NK116(le)001:12291: sku gzugas glegsa bama phyag matshana phyag rgya ston 3pa dang /
NK116(le)001:12292: tshogas kyi 'khora lo'i dusa na 'athaba rtsod dang /
NK116(le)001:12293: baba bcola dang kyal kasa sngags kyi brtul zhugsa tha mala la sbyar ba 4dang /
NK116(le)001:12294: snod ldan gang zhig dama chosa 'dri ba la shesa bzhina du ji bzhin du mi 5smra bar /
NK116(le)001:12295: de lasa 'agla ba'i bsnyon dora lana du ldog pa dang /
NK116(le)001:12296: sngagas kyi gzhung gi lta spyod la bskur zhing nyamsa
NK116(le)001:12297: sada pa ste tshad bgom pa'i rtog ge nyan thosa
NK116(le)001:12298: kyi rigs cana dag gi tshogs nanga du zhaga bduna
NK116(le)001:12300: sngagas rgyud kyi de nyid dang cho ga mi shesa bzhina du /
NK116(le)001:12301: rdo rje 'dzina para rlom nas nga rgyal gyi mgo 'phang bstod de brdzun dang 'grogas pa 7dang //
NK116(le)001:12302: dabnga bskura thob kyang sngagsa la mi dada pa'i //
NK116(le)001:12303: the tshoma cana slara yanga gasnga ba 'achada pa dang
NK116(le)001:12304: brgyad po de dag klu grub kyis bsdus pa'i tshul
NK116(le)001:12306: bla ma'i zhabs kyi pad+mo la //
NK116(le)001:12307: kun nas dngas bas phyag 'tshal te //
NK116(le)001:12308: sbom po'i ltung ba rnam pa brgyad //
NK116(le)001:12309: rgyud las gsung pa bri bar bya //
NK116(le)001:12310: shes rab stobs kyi len pa dang //
NK116(le)001:12311: de yi bdud rtsi stobs kyis len //
NK116(le)001:12312: snod min la ni mi gsang dang /
NK116(le)001:12313: tshogs kyi nang du rtsod pa dang //
NK116(le)001:12314: dad ldan la gzhan chos ston dang //
NK116(le)001:12315: nyan thos nang du zhag bdun gnas //
NK116(le)001:12316: rdzun gyi rnal 'byor nga rgyal byed //
NK116(le)001:12317: dad pa med la chos ston pa //
NK116(le)001:12318: 'di rnams sbom pos ltung bar bshad //
NK116(le)001:12319: rtsa ltung sbom po'i rim pa dag /
NK116(le)001:12320: cho ga yis ni shes bya zhing //
NK116(le)001:12321: nyams par gyur na bshags par bya /
NK116(le)001:12323: de bzhina du slob dpon dapa'a bo dang /
NK116(le)001:12324: lak+shim k+aazazha r+aasa de lasa 'dra min dona gazhana pa yang yod de //
NK116(le)001:12325: gang na grangs dus mtshan ma tshad gang rung ltar
NK116(le)001:12326: bsnyen pa daga para ma byas para dabnga bskur byed
NK116(le)001:12329: sloba ma'i 'khor tshogs bsdu bar ringas nas g.yo zol byed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:12330: tshogas 'khor yin na dus kyi yin pa nges pa
NK116(le)001:12331: med la de las gazhana phyi dro'i kha zasa za
NK116(le)001:12332: ba dang / sogas khong nas so byang gnyis ldan
NK116(le)001:12333: gyi rnal 'byor pa yin na bacasa pa phra rags
NK116(le)001:12334: la dgosa pa meda par 'ad'a ba yisa badga nyid
NK116(le)001:12335: suna 'byin cing dngosa gruba 'phrog pa'i rgyur /
NK116(le)001:12336: gsungsa pasa sboma po snga ma'i cha mthun rnams la'ang brtagsa te bsrung bar bya'o //
NK116(le)001:12338: bla na meda pa'i rgyud sde thuna monga gi rtsa
NK116(le)001:12339: ltung bcu bzhira slob dpon b+ha wa lhas bsdus pa
NK116(le)001:12341: rgya boda kun la khyab cing yongas su gragas che ba zhig ste /
NK116(le)001:12342: gazhana du rgyud sde bzhi po'i ranga rang lugas kyi
NK116(le)001:12343: bcu bzhi'i grangsa ngesa dusa kyi 'khora lo dang spyi
NK116(le)001:12344: rgyud dang rnam par snang mdzad mngona par byang chub
NK116(le)001:12345: pa'i rgyud la sogas lasa gasla bora gsungsa te /
NK116(le)001:12346: ji ltar na dus 'khor dbang le las /
NK116(le)001:12347: dpal ldan bla ma'i thugs dkrugs pa las bu rnams
NK116(le)001:12348: kyi ni rtsa ba'i ltung ba ri bong 'dzin par
NK116(le)001:12349: 1'gyur / de yi bka' la 'gongs pa ltung 2ba
NK116(le)001:12350: gnyis su 'gyur te nges par de bzhin spun la
NK116(le)001:12352: byams pa btang bas bzhi bar 'gyur 4te byang chub
NK116(le)001:12353: sems ni ni raba tu nyams pa las kyang mda'
NK116(le)001:12354: 5ru 'gyur / drug pa grub pa'i mtha' la smod
NK116(le)001:12355: 6pa'o ri bo dag kyang ma smin mi la gsang
NK116(le)001:12357: phung bo nyon mongs pa las klu ru 'gyur te
NK116(le)001:12358: slar yang dgu 9pa dad pa'i chos la ma dad
NK116(le)001:12359: gang / rgyu yi byams 10pa dang ni ming sogs
NK116(le)001:12360: bral ba'i bde ba 11ster la rtog pa phyogs gang
NK116(le)001:12361: gang / drag po'o // dag pa'i sems can dag
NK116(le)001:12362: la skyon brjod pa las nyi 12 ma'i dam tshig
NK116(le)001:12363: thob pa gtod pa las kyang bzhan13 /
NK116(le)001:12364: bud med thams cad la smod nges par ma 14nur
NK116(le)001:12365: 'gyur te rdo rje theg par gnas pa rnams la'o
NK116(le)001:12367: de bzhin du rgyud sde 'og ma gsum la yang bya rgyud la mtshon na spyi rgyud las /
NK116(le)001:12368: de ring phyin chad khyed rnams kyis /
NK116(le)001:12369: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun dang //
NK116(le)001:12370: byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang ni //
NK116(le)001:12371: gsang sngags rigs sngags tshogs rnams la //
NK116(le)001:12372: dad pa rab tu brtan par bya //
NK116(le)001:12373: rtag par theg pa chen po la //
NK116(le)001:12374: khyad par du ni mos par bya //
NK116(le)001:12375: dam tshig can dang mdza' bo dang //
NK116(le)001:12376: bla ma la yang gus par bya //
NK116(le)001:12377: lha rnams kun la sdang mi bya //
NK116(le)001:12378: dus mtshams dag tu mchod pa bya //
NK116(le)001:12379: ston pa gzhan gyi gzhung mi mchod //
NK116(le)001:12380: rtag tu gla bur mgron mchod bya //
NK116(le)001:12381: srog chags kun la byams pa'i sems //
NK116(le)001:12382: rab tu brtan pa nye bar bzhag /
NK116(le)001:12383: theg chen la ni dga' rnams kyis //
NK116(le)001:12384: bsod nams dag la nan tan bskyed //
NK116(le)001:12385: bzlas brjod byed la 'bad pa yis //
NK116(le)001:12386: gsang sngags spyod pa brtson par bya //
NK116(le)001:12387: gsang sngags rgyud las bstan pa yi /
NK116(le)001:12388: dam tshig rnams kyang bsrung bar bya //
NK116(le)001:12389: dam tshig med pa rnams la ni //
NK116(le)001:12390: sngags dang phyag rgya mi sbyin no //
NK116(le)001:12391: gsang sngags rgyud ni legs bsrung zhing /
NK116(le)001:12392: de yang bdag gis rtogs par bya /
NK116(le)001:12394: de'i ldog phyogs rnams 'gal ba yin pas bla med kyi rtsa ltung dang po dang /
NK116(le)001:12399: bcu gsum pa rnams su dngos shugs ci rigs kyis bstan cing /
NK116(le)001:12400: khyad par tshig rkang nyi shu pa dang nyer gcig
NK116(le)001:12401: pa gnyis kyi rtsa ltung thams cad shugs kyis bstan
NK116(le)001:12402: no // spyod rgyud la yang mngon byang las //
NK116(le)001:12403: bcu po 'di dag byang chub sems dpa' gsang sngags
NK116(le)001:12404: kyi sgor spyod pa'i bslabs pa thams cad kyi rtsa
NK116(le)001:12405: ba yin pas gzhi zhes bya'o //
NK116(le)001:12406: zhes mi dge bcu spong gi khrims dang /
NK116(le)001:12407: de'i steng du sngar drangs pa'i rtsa ba'i ltung ba
NK116(le)001:12408: bzhi ni srog gi phyir yang yongs su nyams par
NK116(le)001:12409: mi bya'o // zhes rtsa ltung dngos bstan bzhi gsungs so //
NK116(le)001:12410: rnal 'byor rgyud las ni de nyid snang chen las /
NK116(le)001:12411: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi tshul khrims ni /
NK116(le)001:12412: ji ltar dusa gsum mgon po rnams //
NK116(le)001:12413: byang chub du ni nges mdzad pa //
NK116(le)001:12414: zhes pa la sogs pa'i rigs lnga'i sdom bzung bstan pa las /
NK116(le)001:12415: de bzhin rigs kyi tshul khrims la /
NK116(le)001:12416: dkon mchog gsum la skyabs 'gro mi gtong ba gsum //
NK116(le)001:12417: rdo rje'i rigs la rdor dril phyag rgya slob dpon bzung ba ste bzhin //
NK116(le)001:12418: rin chen rigs la chos dang zang zing mi 'jigs byams pa ste bzhi /
NK116(le)001:12419: pad+ma'i rigs la dam chos ma lus pa 'dzin pa ste gcig /
NK116(le)001:12420: las kyi rigs la sdom pa de rnams mi gtong
NK116(le)001:12421: ba dang mchod pa la brtson pa ste gnyis bcas
NK116(le)001:12423: de dag nan tan du bsrung ba la 'bad dgos
NK116(le)001:12424: par rnal 'byor zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan
NK116(le)001:12425: te / sngags kyi rnal 'byor dang ldana pa gang
NK116(le)001:12426: zhig 'chi bas nyen pa rgyal po'i chad pa pa'am
NK116(le)001:12427: rkyen gang rung ba'i srog la rgol yang gtong bar
NK116(le)001:12428: te / sla la / rtag tu dama tshiga la 'da' ba ni de lta ma yin no //
NK116(le)001:12430: de ltar bsrung bar ma byas na /
NK116(le)001:12431: sngagas la spyod pa'i skyes bu rnams ni nyams na ngan songa mnar med pa dang /
NK116(le)001:12432: bsrung na sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang 'thob pa gnyis
NK116(le)001:12433: po de lasa 'gro sa gsuma pa meda pa ni
NK116(le)001:12434: gong du sgra bshad kyis shes so //
NK116(le)001:12436: gal te dngos grub mchog 'dod na //
NK116(le)001:12437: srog ni yongs su gtong yang sla //
NK116(le)001:12438: 'chi ba'i dus la bab kyang sla //
NK116(le)001:12439: rtag tu dam tshig bsrung bar bya /
NK116(le)001:12442: sngags kyi dngos grub don 'dod pas //
NK116(le)001:12443: dam tshig bsrung la brtson par bya //
NK116(le)001:12444: gzhan du byas na sngags mkhan gyis //
NK116(le)001:12445: sngags la sogs pa'i don mi 'grub //
NK116(le)001:12446: gsol yang bzhes su mi gnang te //
NK116(le)001:12448: 'jig rten pha rol dmyal ba rnams //
NK116(le)001:12449: dam tshig spyod las 'das pa yi //
NK116(le)001:12450: rmongs pa'i bdag nyid des thob bo //
NK116(le)001:12452: gal te nyams na bcos pa'i tshul de phyir zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:12453: tshul de'i phyira ltung bas phog na badga nyid du
NK116(le)001:12454: sun phyung nas phyir bcosa pa'i thabas la de ma
NK116(le)001:12456: khyad para de dag las kyang rtsa ltung dang po shina tu lci ba ni /
NK116(le)001:12458: bla ma la ni smod pa dang //
NK116(le)001:12459: thugs dkrugs pa yi nyes pa ni //
NK116(le)001:12460: phyi yi rgya mtsho chen po las //
NK116(le)001:12461: chu de skra yi gtor gyur ba //
NK116(le)001:12462: de yi tshad du sdug bsngal myong //
NK116(le)001:12463: rdo rje dmyal bar grags pa yin /
NK116(le)001:12465: des na rtag tu bla mara bsnyena bskura bya zhing 'khora gsuma yongas su daga pa 'bul la //
NK116(le)001:12466: slar dabnga bskur bskyar nasa sdoma pa gsora gzhuga cing /
NK116(le)001:12467: bla ma dang sa thag gis bkal te nye bar
NK116(le)001:12468: mi gansa na gtsug tu bsgom te rtags ma byung
NK116(le)001:12469: bar badga 'juga lana manga du blang bar bya la
NK116(le)001:12470: / de bzhina du gazhana pa dag la'ang khrela yoda
NK116(le)001:12471: pa dang ngo tsha'i rten du rung bar bya ba'i
NK116(le)001:12473: bla ma gshegs nas meda na sngagsa kyi sdoma ldana ganga rung gi mdun du /
NK116(le)001:12474: snying thag pa nas phyag dang spyod lam dula ba'i
NK116(le)001:12475: ranga gi minga smos nasa rdo rje thega pa'i 'dula
NK116(le)001:12476: ba dang 'agla ba'i nongas pa 'di dang 'di lta
NK116(le)001:12477: bu byung bas / 'achaba na badga nyid gtan du bde bar gansa par mi 'gyur bas na /
NK116(le)001:12478: cung zad kyang 'achaba pa meda par legas para gsola nas bashagas yula gyis kyang /
NK116(le)001:12479: nongs pa nyes para mthonga ngama zhes dris par /
NK116(le)001:12481: yang yula gyis te bla mas phyin chada sdoma para byed dama dris pa'i lan /
NK116(le)001:12482: chosa bzhina du 'dula ba bzhina du spyi bo'i noda /
NK116(le)001:12483: cesa bya ba lana gsum brjod pa'i rjes la phan tshan gyis thabas legas bya'o //
NK116(le)001:12484: de skad du'ang snying po rgyan las /
NK116(le)001:12485: ltung sogs nyes pa'i rim pa las /
NK116(le)001:12486: dang po bdag sems sun phyung ste //
NK116(le)001:12487: yul mdun snyan gsan phab nas kyang //
NK116(le)001:12488: gsum blang gsum 'gal bshags pa dang /
NK116(le)001:12490: gala te nyes par byung nas phyir bcosa 'gyangsa nasa
NK116(le)001:12491: zhaga re song bzhina gonga 'phela du 'gro bar 'gyur
NK116(le)001:12492: ba'i phyir de'i gnyen po rgyu ru /
NK116(le)001:12493: stobsa bzhi tshangas pa'i yiga brgyas rtag tu bashagas pa ni /
NK116(le)001:12495: rdo rje sems dpa' la dmigs te //
NK116(le)001:12496: yi ge brgya ba cho ga bzhin //
NK116(le)001:12497: nyi shu rtsa gcig re re bzlas //
NK116(le)001:12498: ltung sogs byin gyis brlabs 'gyur bas /
NK116(le)001:12500: grub pa mchog rnams kyis bshad pas //
NK116(le)001:12501: thun mtshams su ni sbyangs par bya //
NK116(le)001:12502: 'bum phrag du ni bzlas gyur na //
NK116(le)001:12503: rnam par dag pa'i bdag nyid 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:12505: de bzhin du 'gyod sems drag pos rtsa ltung bcu
NK116(le)001:12506: bzhi'i bsngo bgrangsa brjod pa'i bashagas tshigas kyang grangs mang
NK116(le)001:12507: 'dona par bya'o // gzhan yang dam tshig rnam grangs
NK116(le)001:12508: rgyas par 'chad par spyi dang bye brag gnyis kyi
NK116(le)001:12509: 'dona par bya'o // dang po ni // sh+aan+ta tan+t+ra las //
NK116(le)001:12510: so so thar dang byang chub sems //
NK116(le)001:12511: bya spyod rnal 'byor rgyud rnams lasa //
NK116(le)001:12512: bsrung bar bya ba gang gsungs pa //
NK116(le)001:12513: thun mong spyi yi dam tshig yin //
NK116(le)001:12515: gnyis pa ni khyad par zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te //
NK116(le)001:12516: snga ma de dag las khyad para mdo sgyu semas gsuma ringa lugas ni //
NK116(le)001:12517: spyi mdora sku dang gsunga dang thugsa ste rdo rje
NK116(le)001:12518: gsum po de yi bsrunga bya gsum dang de nas
NK116(le)001:12519: lnga tshan ni // spyad pa dang //
NK116(le)001:12523: bsgruba pa'i grangs kyi dbye basa nyi shu rtsa brgyad 'byung ste //
NK116(le)001:12525: sku dang gsung thugs rdo rje yi //
NK116(le)001:12526: bsrung dang spyad dang yid 'ong dang //
NK116(le)001:12527: mi 'dor bya ba bsgrub pa dang /
NK116(le)001:12529: de la'ang nang gses su rtsa ba sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig la phyi nang gsang gsum dang //
NK116(le)001:12530: re re la'ang gsum gsum du dbyer ba'i nyi shu rtsa bdun dang //
NK116(le)001:12531: rkang pa phyi ma gnyis kyis nyi shu rtsa lnga ston pa rnams 'og tu 'chad do //
NK116(le)001:12532: sgyu 'phrula dra ba'i gzhung du rtsa ba'i dama tshiga rnam pa lnga dang //
NK116(le)001:12533: yan lag gi dam tshig bcu ste bsdom pa'i bco lngar bshad de //
NK116(le)001:12535: rdo rje sloba dpona mi sponga bkura stis bsnyen no //
NK116(le)001:12537: spyi dang 'dren dang dam tshig dbang /
NK116(le)001:12538: nyams chags skong dang shes rgyud grol /
NK116(le)001:12539: man ngag lung gi slob dpon rnams //
NK116(le)001:12540: zhes drug tu bshad la khyad par rang la chos
NK116(le)001:12541: kyi bka' drin gal che ba gtso bor bzung nas
NK116(le)001:12542: bsti stang dgos pa de nyid las /
NK116(le)001:12543: yul la dbang ba'i rgyal po dang //
NK116(le)001:12544: khu bo pha dang ma dang mig /
NK116(le)001:12545: snying bas lhag pa'i tshul bltas te /
NK116(le)001:12547: lha'i sngagas dang phyag rgya sku bsgom pa rgyun mi bacada pa dang /
NK116(le)001:12548: yang dag pa'i lam du bzhugas so cog la byamsa para byed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:12549: gasnga ba'i dona zab mo rnams gazhana la mi bsgrag pa'o //
NK116(le)001:12550: yan lag dama tshiga gzhan du rnam grangs mang yang 'dir sde tshana ganyis su bsdu ba las /
NK116(le)001:12551: dang po'i phyogsa ni nyon mongas lnga mi spangsa pa'o //
NK116(le)001:12553: de kho na nyid kyi ranga bzhina shesa pa'i dus
NK116(le)001:12554: na nyon mongas kyang de bzhina nyid du shes te
NK116(le)001:12555: / de lta'i thabsa dang shes rab kyis zina para
NK116(le)001:12556: gyur tshe dper na rma byas duga zosa pa dang
NK116(le)001:12559: gti mug chags dang zhe sdang dang //
NK116(le)001:12560: nga rgyal phrag dog mi spang ngo /
NK116(le)001:12562: ye nasa rigas lnga'i rang bzhin can yin pa ni /
NK116(le)001:12563: bskyed rdzogs kyi skabs su bstan zin la /
NK116(le)001:12564: de lta'i tshul la ma rmongs para shesa pasa ye shesa 'gyur ba yin no //
NK116(le)001:12567: dkar rtsi dmar rtsi dri sha chen /
NK116(le)001:12568: dag pa'i snod chu mi dor ro //
NK116(le)001:12569: zhes byang sems dkar dmar gnyis dang //
NK116(le)001:12570: dri chen dang sha chen dang /
NK116(le)001:12571: dri chu ste bduda rtsi chena po lnga ni shin
NK116(le)001:12572: tu blang byar ngesa pa'i sems kyis dang du len
NK116(le)001:12573: pa'o // ji ltar len na chosa nyid rola pa chen po'i rgyan du shes par blang zhing //
NK116(le)001:12574: ye shes lnga dang rigas lnga'i ranga bzhina nyid du shes pasa kyang blang ngo //
NK116(le)001:12575: ci'i phyir len na dngosa gruba rnam gnyis bsgruba pa'i dam rdzasa yina pasa blangsa zhing /
NK116(le)001:12576: dpa' bo mkha'a 'gro ma rnams 'du zhing dngosa gruba ster la nye bar brgyud pas na blang ngo //
NK116(le)001:12578: dus gsum sangsa rgyas kun gyi blanga ba'i brtul zhugas
NK116(le)001:12579: mchog tu gyur pa yina pas na blang bar bya'o
NK116(le)001:12580: // de la cha shas kyi dbye basa nyis brgya'i grangas su ngesa par byas pa ni /
NK116(le)001:12581: nyi shura bsdu bar de las gyes pa kun gzigas chen po rong zom chos bzang ba'i lugas te /
NK116(le)001:12582: de skad du rtsa rgyud las //
NK116(le)001:12583: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga la ni //
NK116(le)001:12584: gcig la'ang gnyis dang bcu phrag gsum /
NK116(le)001:12586: rtsa ba gcig la'ang re re bzhin thabs shes gnyis su phye bas bcu dang //
NK116(le)001:12587: yang de nyid re re la'ang sku gsung thugs kyi
NK116(le)001:12588: grangs su phye bas bcu phrag gsum ste sum cu
NK116(le)001:12589: phrag lnga bsdom pas lnga bcus lhag pa'i brgya sngar
NK116(le)001:12590: gyi dbye gzhi bcu po bsres pas brgya dang drug
NK116(le)001:12591: cu'o // de yang phra rgyas las /
NK116(le)001:12593: dang po nyid nas thabs spyod dang //
NK116(le)001:12594: shes rab nyid kyis nyis 'gyur yin //
NK116(le)001:12595: re re'ang bsrung bya sum cu ste /
NK116(le)001:12599: yan lag gi dam tshig ni /
NK116(le)001:12600: yan lag nyi shu dbye ba bya ste /
NK116(le)001:12601: gcig la yang sku gsum thugs yon tan phrin las kyi yan lag rnam pa lnga /
NK116(le)001:12602: sku gsum thugs kyi dngos gzhi gsum yang de nyid du zhig ste yan lag gi gzhi med /
NK116(le)001:12603: rtsa ba thabs dang shes rab gnyis kyi thabs shes rab dang ldan /
NK116(le)001:12604: shes rab thabs dang ldan pas rtsa ba gnyis po zhig ste yan lag bzhir 'gyur bas /
NK116(le)001:12605: de yang sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i
NK116(le)001:12606: cha shas su 'gyur bas rtsa ba'i 'phro gzhi med
NK116(le)001:12607: de // yan lag dang cha shas nyi shu nyi shur 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:12609: rang bzhin rdzogs pa'i dam tshig ni sems kyi zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan ste /
NK116(le)001:12610: semas kyi phyogsa la rdzogs pa chen po'i lta ba
NK116(le)001:12611: bsrung bya bsrung byed las 'das kyang re zhig tha
NK116(le)001:12614: de dus bsrung ba'i mtshams 'das pa'i //
NK116(le)001:12615: dam tshig lhun grub chen po dang //
NK116(le)001:12616: med dang gcig pu phyal ba yis //
NK116(le)001:12617: de yi grogs su de 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:12619: rnam pa bzhir gnas pa ni /
NK116(le)001:12621: rang rig ye shes chen po la /
NK116(le)001:12622: bsrung dang bsrung bya gnyis med pas //
NK116(le)001:12623: nyams dang ma nyams gnyis su med //
NK116(le)001:12624: theg brgyad bcos ma'i tshig gi grangs //
NK116(le)001:12625: nga mi bsrung bas med ces bya /
NK116(le)001:12628: bsrung bya bsrung byed med pa ni //
NK116(le)001:12629: chos nyid dam pa'i dam tshig yin /
NK116(le)001:12630: zhes meda pa dang po dang /
NK116(le)001:12632: bsrung du med pa'i dam tshig las /
NK116(le)001:12633: 'da' mi srid pa'i bsrung thabs ni //
NK116(le)001:12634: rang rig ye shes gcig pu pas //
NK116(le)001:12635: gcig pu zhes su btags pa yin /
NK116(le)001:12638: sems su kun gcig gcig pur bstan pa yin /
NK116(le)001:12639: zhes gcig pu ste gnyis pa dang //
NK116(le)001:12641: dngos po mi spyod ye shes ma 'gags pa //
NK116(le)001:12642: de la phyal ba zhes su btags pa yin /
NK116(le)001:12645: 'og ma'i dam tshig las grol zhing //
NK116(le)001:12646: rang gi sgo gsum yangs pas ni //
NK116(le)001:12647: phyal pa gcig pu btags pa yin //
NK116(le)001:12648: zhes phyal ba ste gsum pa dang ni /
NK116(le)001:12650: rang rig ye shes gcig pu la //
NK116(le)001:12651: bya rtsol med pa yongs bsrung bas //
NK116(le)001:12652: lhun grub zhes su btags pa yin /
NK116(le)001:12655: ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams ma lus kun //
NK116(le)001:12656: yid chos byang chub sems su rdzogs pa'i phyir //
NK116(le)001:12657: lhun gyis grub pa zhes su nga yis bshad /
NK116(le)001:12658: ces lhun gruba cesa pa rnams su gragas pa gang
NK116(le)001:12659: zhig bsrunga matshamas brala la 'ad'a bya mi dmigas pa'i
NK116(le)001:12660: phyir / ngo bo'i bzhugs tshul dam tshig gi chings kyi bcings ste /
NK116(le)001:12661: ya nas de rnams nyamsa med rdo rje rgyal po'i lugs yin no /
NK116(le)001:12662: de lta'i 'bras bu lkog tu gyur lam du zhugs
NK116(le)001:12663: pa rnams kyi rang rgyuddag par bya ba'iphyir gal te
NK116(le)001:12664: nyams par gyur na phyir bcos kyi thabs rin chen
NK116(le)001:12665: bum pa bzang po lta bu cung zad zhom kyang
NK116(le)001:12666: gso sla ba ltar yod pa rnams la sems shig
NK116(le)001:12667: ces gdams pa'o / gong du drangs pa'i spyi mdo'i
NK116(le)001:12668: lung rkang pa dang po'i don dam tshig rnam para
NK116(le)001:12669: bakod pa'i grub mtha' gzhung gis 'chad pa ni /
NK116(le)001:12671: sku dang gsung dang thugs dag la'ang re re la'ang dgu dgu ste /
NK116(le)001:12672: 'jug dang las kyi rnam pas shes /
NK116(le)001:12674: rtsa ba bla ma'isku gsung thugsa gsuma lasa /
NK116(le)001:12675: phyi nanga gasnga ba'i dam tshiga gsuma tshana gsum gyi
NK116(le)001:12676: dbye bas nyi shu rtsa bdun yod pa ni 'di
NK116(le)001:12677: ltar ste / rku phyi'i gsum ni gsang ba srog gcoda nang gi mi tshangas spyod dang /
NK116(le)001:12679: nang gi gsum ni pha ma spuna sring smad pa phyi dang /
NK116(le)001:12680: ranga lusa lha'i 'khor lo la smad pa gsang ba /
NK116(le)001:12681: theg pa che chung gi chos gang la zhugs pa dag smoda de mtho brtsam pa nang ngo /
NK116(le)001:12683: bla ma 'i griba ma 'goma pa sogs gsang ba /
NK116(le)001:12684: rmi lam gyi skabs su'ang gsuma la gcesa pa sogs nang /
NK116(le)001:12685: rdo rje spun nam sriing mo brdegs pa sogs phyi'o //
NK116(le)001:12686: gsung gi phyi gsum lasa rdzuna phyi dang phra ma nang dang /
NK116(le)001:12687: tshiga rtsub spanga ba gsang ba'o //
NK116(le)001:12688: nang gi gsum chosa smras pa phyi /
NK116(le)001:12690: gansa lugas bsgom pa mi bkur ba gsang ba'o //
NK116(le)001:12692: bla ma'i yuma la smad pa nang dang /
NK116(le)001:12693: rdo rje spun sring gi tshiga mi brnyas te phyi dang /
NK116(le)001:12694: bla ma smod pa gsang ba'o //
NK116(le)001:12696: yida kyi rnam gsuma ste rna ba sems phyi dang /
NK116(le)001:12700: spyod pa log pa phyi dang /
NK116(le)001:12701: bsgom pa bying rgod nang dang /
NK116(le)001:12702: lta ba loga pa gsang ba ste de dag spang bar bya'o //
NK116(le)001:12704: bla ma nyin zhag tsam du ma dran pa gsang ba //
NK116(le)001:12705: yi dam gyi lha dang grogs mched kyang bla ma'i phyogs su lta ba nang /
NK116(le)001:12706: lta bsgoma spyod pa thuna kuna tu semas par ma byas pa phyi'o //
NK116(le)001:12709: 'grel ba po blun por the tshom na rtsa ba'i rjes su 'brang pas mi skyon no //
NK116(le)001:12710: 'o na rtsa ba'i go rim 'chol ba ma gzigs
NK116(le)001:12711: sam zhe na rgyud kyi tshig gi rjes su 'brang
NK116(le)001:12712: ba yin pas de ltar bsam mi rung ngo //
NK116(le)001:12713: de ltar nyi shu rtsa bdun po ni 'da' bar
NK116(le)001:12714: bya ba ma yin pa'i rtsa ba'i dam tshig tu
NK116(le)001:12715: bzhag pa la / thabs kyis zin min gyi cha
NK116(le)001:12716: nas gzhan don 'gyur min la dgongs te gnang bkag
NK116(le)001:12717: gnyis su spyod pa spyi mdo'i lung tshig rkang pa
NK116(le)001:12718: phyi ma gnyis kyi don so sor ston pa'i phyir
NK116(le)001:12719: bzhag pa la / / thabs kyi zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:12721: nyon mongs lam ni dag pa che /
NK116(le)001:12722: thabs kyi 'dod yon rgyana gyi mchog /
NK116(le)001:12723: thams cad thams cad rol pa yis /
NK116(le)001:12724: myur du he ru ka dpal 'gyur zhes pa ltar /
NK116(le)001:12725: thabas kyi dabang du gyur ba'i yana lag gi dam
NK116(le)001:12726: tshig nyi shu rtsa lnga lasa lnga tshan dang po
NK116(le)001:12727: ni / ta na zhes 1sgrol pa ga na 2 sbyor ba /
NK116(le)001:12728: gzung ma sogs dgos pa chen po'i phyir nus pa'i
NK116(le)001:12729: tshod dang dpag nas ma byin par 3 lena pa
NK116(le)001:12730: / gzhan la phan pa'i phyir rdzuna smra ba gang
NK116(le)001:12731: zhig chos lam la drangs pa'i phyir sgrung sogs kyal
NK116(le)001:12732: pa'i tshig smra ba rnams ste sbyang bya lnga po
NK116(le)001:12733: de ni gannga bakaga gi mtshams shesa bzhin pasa spyod
NK116(le)001:12735: 'doda chagas dang zhe sdang dang la sogas pa'i khongs
NK116(le)001:12736: nas gti mug nga rgyal phrag dog ste nyon monga
NK116(le)001:12737: pa lnga ni mi sponga ba lnga yin pas de
NK116(le)001:12738: ni ranga rgyud pa dang dbrala bar spyad pa gong
NK116(le)001:12739: du / rtsa rgyud kyi dam tshig bco lnga bshad pa'i skabs su shes so //
NK116(le)001:12741: dra chena dri chu m+aam s+aa rak+ta zila ba ste /
NK116(le)001:12742: dang du lena pa lnga la gatsanga rme'i gnyis /
NK116(le)001:12745: dri chen dri chu mam sa dang //
NK116(le)001:12747: sems can rtog pa ldog pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:12748: gtso ru dang du blang bar bya /
NK116(le)001:12754: dabnga po dang shes pa sems dpa'/
NK116(le)001:12755: kha doga lnga ye shes lngar gnas pa sogs lhar
NK116(le)001:12756: gsal ba gong du bskyed rdzogs kyi skabs su bshad
NK116(le)001:12757: pa ltar shesa par bya ba lnga tshan gyi sde
NK116(le)001:12758: ba ni shesa raba stobsa kyisa spyod par bya ba
NK116(le)001:12759: ni / dam tshig gsum bkod las //
NK116(le)001:12760: phung po lnga dang 'byung ba rnam pa lnga /
NK116(le)001:12761: rnam shes dbang po yul la sogs pa rnams /
NK116(le)001:12762: lha dang dkyil 'khor rang bzhin shes par bya /
NK116(le)001:12769: de bzhina nyid dang bsgrub bya lnga ni bshad ma
NK116(le)001:12770: thag pa'i shes bya lnga po de rtog gomas kyi
NK116(le)001:12771: mthu yisa rang rgyud la mngon sum du bsgrub par
NK116(le)001:12772: bya ba 'di daga dama tshiga gasla bkra'i dgongas pa
NK116(le)001:12774: bsgrub par bya ba'i dam tshig rnam lnga ni /
NK116(le)001:12775: phung po lnga dang 'byung ba rnam lnga dang /
NK116(le)001:12776: rnam shes yul rnams dkyil 'khor bsgrub byed pa /
NK116(le)001:12777: ting 'dzin gsum dang cho ga lnga rdzogs nas /
NK116(le)001:12778: rgyal ba rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor sgrub byed pa /
NK116(le)001:12779: ting 'dzin cho ga lnga yis sems rtsol byed /
NK116(le)001:12781: de bzhina du dus kyi 'khora lo las brtul zhugas nyi shu rtsa lnga bshad de /
NK116(le)001:12782: lnga tshan lnga las dang po ni /
NK116(le)001:12787: chang 5bcas bslab pa'i gzhi las sdig pa lnga ste
NK116(le)001:12788: ma bsrungs na brtul zhugs lhag ma 'phrog pa'i phyir
NK116(le)001:12789: bslab pa'i gzhi lngar grags so //
NK116(le)001:12794: mtshun lha gsol phyir phyugs kyi machod sbyin byed 4pa /
NK116(le)001:12795: rang gi bsad sha las mi za ba sogs kla
NK116(le)001:12796: klo'i chos lugs la spyod pa 5ni nye ba'i sdig
NK116(le)001:12797: pa lnga'o // gsum pa ni mtho ris 'dod pa'i mchod sbyin la dmigs nas ba lang gsod ba /
NK116(le)001:12798: ma mo mchod phyir byis pa gsod pa /
NK116(le)001:12799: skyes pa'i don du skyes pa gsod pa /
NK116(le)001:12800: bud med kyi don du bud med gsod pa /
NK116(le)001:12801: lha mi'i bla ma gsod ba zhes sku gzugs dang
NK116(le)001:12802: glegs bam mchod rten bshig pa la gsod pa'i sgra
NK116(le)001:12803: btags pa ste gsod pa lnga po ni 'tshe ba
NK116(le)001:12804: chos su smra ba kla klo'i lugs so //
NK116(le)001:12810: bla ma 5mkhan slob gang rung ste yul lnga po de la khong khro ba ni 'khu ba lnga'o //
NK116(le)001:12812: yul lnga la chags pas na chags pa lnga'o //
NK116(le)001:12813: de dag ni spang bar bya'o //
NK116(le)001:12814: gsar rnying thun mong gi rgyud gasnga ba 'dusa pa dang /
NK116(le)001:12817: sngona dang phyin chad 'gyur ba'i rgyud sde yi /
NK116(le)001:12818: spyi dona du gyur ba rigas lnga'i sdom pa la
NK116(le)001:12819: ni sangs rgyas zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs
NK116(le)001:12820: te / sangsa rgyas rigs kyi dam tshig tu /
NK116(le)001:12821: rnal 'byor bas smon sems blangsa nas 'juga pa tha
NK116(le)001:12822: ma la snang zhen las log pa'i nyes spyod sdom
NK116(le)001:12823: pa na / 'khrul snang ye shes su sdud pa'i dge ba chos sdud kyi /
NK116(le)001:12824: las bzhi'i phrin las 'jug pa'i sems can don byed kyi ste tshul khrimas gsuma bsrung /
NK116(le)001:12825: mi bskyod pa'i dam tshig tu rdo rje dang drila
NK116(le)001:12826: bu dang phyag rgya dang bla ma gzung ba rnams
NK116(le)001:12827: so // rina 'byung gi dam tshig tu //
NK116(le)001:12829: mi 'jigas pa byamsa pa sbyin pa rnams so //
NK116(le)001:12830: snang ba matha'a yas kyi dam tshig tu so byang
NK116(le)001:12831: sngags kyi thega pa gsuma 'dzina cing chosa rnams bashada
NK116(le)001:12832: pa'o // dona 'grub kyi dam tshig tu /
NK116(le)001:12833: sras bcas rgyal bar mchoda bstoda sbyin sreg la sogs phrina lasa kuna la gusa pa'o //
NK116(le)001:12834: rgyud sde gong ma'i rnal 'byor la dmigs su bsal
NK116(le)001:12835: ba khyad par zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan
NK116(le)001:12836: te / khyad para rnal 'byor bla na meda pa'i rgyud kyi rigas lnga'i sdom pa ni /
NK116(le)001:12837: rdo rje'i rigas gyur sroga la 'tshe bar gsungs pa de yanga /
NK116(le)001:12838: zhing bcu tshangs pa'i nyams pa bdun ldan gsod pa
NK116(le)001:12839: lasa gang rung rung min te gazhana dabu mara las
NK116(le)001:12840: rlung bcud pas rtogsa tshogs brgya khrid bzhi stong gsoda
NK116(le)001:12841: pa'o / rana chena rigsa la ma byin blang bya ni /
NK116(le)001:12842: mtshan ldan gzunga ma dang skal med skyes bo' nor
NK116(le)001:12843: rnams rang gzhan rdzogsa pa' byang chub thob phyir ranga
NK116(le)001:12844: stobsa kyi mthu yod na de yisa blangsa pa'o //
NK116(le)001:12845: pad+ma'i rigas la ri dwagsa mi gacana te bud med mtshan ldan mchoda pa dang /
NK116(le)001:12846: stong pa nyid kyi gshis la buda meda kyi sgras
NK116(le)001:12847: brjod de de la rnam pa kuna tu spyod pa
NK116(le)001:12850: phyag rgya chen po rnams brten /
NK116(le)001:12851: 'khora lo'am de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs la sha chen
NK116(le)001:12852: lnga dang changa la 'du shes gnas 'gyur gyis rol
NK116(le)001:12853: ba dang / lasa kyi rigs la chos thams cad
NK116(le)001:12854: bden med du shes na dgos pa'i dbang gi rdzuna
NK116(le)001:12855: tshiga sgyu ma lta bura sgrogsa /
NK116(le)001:12857: sgra ji bzhin pa ma yin pa'i phyir tshiga gi gaba pa ni /
NK116(le)001:12859: ma bsgral ba rnams bsgral ba dang sogs khong nas ma grol ba rnams grol ba /
NK116(le)001:12860: dbugs ma byung rnams dbugs dbyung ba bya ba la
NK116(le)001:12861: sogs byang chub sems dpa'i sa dang mthuna mongas pa
NK116(le)001:12862: rnams ni rgyu'i theg pa'i skabs su shes la khyad
NK116(le)001:12863: par lha zhes ye shes pa dang /
NK116(le)001:12864: lha mina te 'jig rten pa dang /
NK116(le)001:12865: gzhan yang gasnga ba pa mi brnyas pa /
NK116(le)001:12866: phyag rgya gzhona pa mtshona cha matshana ma la /
NK116(le)001:12868: de'i nang gses so so'i don ni lha lha min gnyis ni dngosa su bstan pa te /
NK116(le)001:12869: lhag ma rnams ni gasnga ba pa gnoda sbyin te
NK116(le)001:12870: ston pa'i tha tshig la gnas pa'i bstan bsrung gi
NK116(le)001:12871: rigs dang / phyag rgya bris 'bur gyi sku gzugas mtshan nyid rdzogas pa /
NK116(le)001:12872: gzhona pa bla ma'i stan dang chibas pa la sogas pa /
NK116(le)001:12873: mtshona cha rdo rje kha t+aam phur ba sogs lha'i phyag mtshan gyi cheda du byas pa'i rigas dang /
NK116(le)001:12874: matshana ma ste phyag matshana dang /
NK116(le)001:12876: mchoda rten sogs kyi griba ma 'goma pa la smad pa'i sgra mdo rgyud kun nas zhugs pa'o //
NK116(le)001:12877: de bzhina mchoda pa'i rdzasa rnyingsa pa'i rigs la bza'
NK116(le)001:12878: ba'am 'gom par byas na yang damna mara gragas la
NK116(le)001:12879: / rtsam pa la sogs pa la phyag matshana gyi
NK116(le)001:12880: rnama pa dod pa'ang baza'a ba bakaga pa yina no
NK116(le)001:12881: / // de dag las kyang khyad para gsoda pa
NK116(le)001:12882: dang ma byin lena pa dang sogas khongs nas mi
NK116(le)001:12884: phra ma tshig rtsub ngag kyal rnams te dngosa bstan
NK116(le)001:12885: nyid dang pha ma ni gsod par bya gsungs pa
NK116(le)001:12886: sogs dgongas pa lunga ston gyi /
NK116(le)001:12887: rnam par dbye ba ma phyed par sgra ji bzhin
NK116(le)001:12888: spyad pas ru ta thal ba nag po'i rnam thar
NK116(le)001:12889: bzhin sngagsa pa mnar med pa'i gnas su thura la
NK116(le)001:12890: ltung bar 'gyur bas na shin tu bsgrims shing bag
NK116(le)001:12891: yod par byed pa gal che'o //
NK116(le)001:12892: bshad ma thag pa'i dam tshig gi rnam grangs mdora
NK116(le)001:12893: bsdu na bde gshegs snying po bum nang gi mar
NK116(le)001:12894: me bzhin ye nas rang la gnas tshul sngon chad
NK116(le)001:12896: de mngon sum du ma gyur pa gaba pa'i tshul
NK116(le)001:12897: du yod pa'i gasnga ba gang zhig ma rtogsa para
NK116(le)001:12898: / sbas pa'i gasnga ba bla ma'i man ngag mkha'
NK116(le)001:12899: 'gro'i snying gi thig par pho tshod kyi mngona par
NK116(le)001:12900: 'chela ba kuna la nam yang gzura bar bya'o //
NK116(le)001:12901: de la cung zad phral na /
NK116(le)001:12903: dam nyams dam las log pa dang /
NK116(le)001:12904: dam med dkyil 'khor ma mthong dang /
NK116(le)001:12906: zhes pas gsang ba'i yul bstan la /
NK116(le)001:12907: ji ltar gsang ba'i dngos po ni bcu ste /
NK116(le)001:12908: spyi dang bar gsang bzhi bzhi dang /
NK116(le)001:12909: 'os dang gnyer gtad rnam pa bcu /
NK116(le)001:12912: rtsa ltung bdun pa'i mtshan nyid de /
NK116(le)001:12913: lta ba zab mo blo dman dang the tshom can la gsang ba 1dang /
NK116(le)001:12914: spyod pa barlanga po gsar du zhugs pa dang log lta can la gsang ba 2dang /
NK116(le)001:12916: de grub pa'i rtags mtshan gzhan la gsang 4ba'o //
NK116(le)001:12917: de yang ma 'dresa pa la bstan na bdun par 'gyur zhing /
NK116(le)001:12918: 'dres pa la'ang gya tshom du bstan na dngos grub nyams pa'i phyir na gsang bar bya ste //
NK116(le)001:12920: lta zab spyod pa barlanga bo dang //
NK116(le)001:12921: lha'i ming gzung dang grub rtags rnams //
NK116(le)001:12922: spyi gsang rnam pa bzhi yin no //
NK116(le)001:12928: rdzas 4la sogs pa tshogs bsgrub bam gsang ba'i spyod
NK116(le)001:12929: pa la zhugs pa de srid du gsang ba ste
NK116(le)001:12930: // bsgrub pa'i gnas dus grogs dang rdzas //
NK116(le)001:12931: bar du gsang la bsgrub par bya /
NK116(le)001:12934: sngags kyi spyod pa khyad par ba dang /
NK116(le)001:12935: dam tshig gi rdzas 'du bar zhugs pa'i spyod lam mi mthun pa'i cha thams cad do //
NK116(le)001:12937: bla ma dang mched kyis kyang rung ste 'di ni gzhan la brjod par mi bya'o /
NK116(le)001:12938: zhes gsung bar gdam pa las mi 'da' ba ste /
NK116(le)001:12940: gzhan yang slob dpon mched lcam gyis /
NK116(le)001:12941: gsang bar bsgrags nas gnas skabs su //
NK116(le)001:12942: de ltar 'os pa shin tu gsang /
NK116(le)001:12944: rdo rje theg pa gzhan las phul byung du basngagasa
NK116(le)001:12945: pa nyin bzhin zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs
NK116(le)001:12946: te / 'di ltar nyin re bzhina du bram ze
NK116(le)001:12947: gsoda pa dang matshamas meda lnga spyod pa ni dmyal
NK116(le)001:12948: ba'i sa bon do zla med pa yin te /
NK116(le)001:12949: theg pa gzhan gyis spangs kyang /
NK116(le)001:12950: sngags sdoma skye ba'i rten du rung basa na /
NK116(le)001:12951: gsang sngags thabas kyi che ba smos cinga dgosa /
NK116(le)001:12953: tshul de gdan bzhi las kyang //
NK116(le)001:12954: nyin bzhin bram ze gsod pa dang //
NK116(le)001:12955: mtshams med lha ni byed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:12956: chom rkun las kyi longs spyod pa //
NK116(le)001:12957: 'di yi lam gyi grol gyur te //
NK116(le)001:12958: sdig pas gos par mi 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:12960: dam tshig nyams par byed pa'i rgyu ni ltung mtshams zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:12961: dam tshig gi rnam grangs la blun bas ltung matshamas mi shesa pa 1dang /
NK116(le)001:12963: baga meda pa la goma pa 3dang /
NK116(le)001:12964: ha cang nyona mongas pa mthu che ba bzhi ni /
NK116(le)001:12966: de'i steng du le lo'i g.yeng ste brjed ngasa che ba dang /
NK116(le)001:12967: gnyid rmug gis drana pa mi gasla ba gnyis bsnana
NK116(le)001:12968: pas dama tshiga nyamsa pa'i rgyu druga yin pa ni
NK116(le)001:12970: mi shes pa dang bag med dang //
NK116(le)001:12971: nyon mongs mang dang mi gus dang /
NK116(le)001:12972: brjed ngasa dran pa mi gsal ba //
NK116(le)001:12973: 'di drug dama tshiga nyamsa pa'i rgyu /
NK116(le)001:12975: bsrung tshul dpe'i sgo nas de bas zhes bya ba la sogs pas gdam ste /
NK116(le)001:12976: de basa rtag tu drana dang shes bazhana ldan pa'i gnyen po yisa mel tshe byed tshul //
NK116(le)001:12977: dper na longa ba zhig la sman pa mkhas pas
NK116(le)001:12978: thur dpyad kyis dabye bar byed pa' cho ga la
NK116(le)001:12979: 'jug pa'i gansa skabsa thob pa'i dus na gnyis kas
NK116(le)001:12980: gzab cing baga yod pas bsrung ba ji bzhina du
NK116(le)001:12981: / nyin matshana thuna drug tu spang bya dang blang
NK116(le)001:12982: bya'i gansa phra rag rnams la sgrimsa shinga rab tu
NK116(le)001:12983: / bsgrimsa shinga / dpyad pa gal che ba ni /
NK116(le)001:12985: ma grangs grol ba'i khrod gnas na //
NK116(le)001:12986: bsgrims te rma yi bag byed bzhin //
NK116(le)001:12987: skye bo ngan khrod gnas pas kyang //
NK116(le)001:12988: sems kyi rma ni rtag tu bsrung /
NK116(le)001:12990: de lta'i bag yod kyi sems dang ldan pas tshor
NK116(le)001:12991: ba nyams su myong ba rnams kyis gsang sngags la
NK116(le)001:12992: dam tshig gi rnam grangs bsam las 'das pa'i phyir
NK116(le)001:12993: gal te nyams na bshags thab kyi sgo mang pas
NK116(le)001:12994: nyams na zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te
NK116(le)001:12995: / tshul 'dir 'jug pa'i skal ldan rnams kyis bsrung bya mtha' klas pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:12996: gal te bag tsam nyamsa na gso ba'ang theg pa
NK116(le)001:12997: 'oga ma lasa chos 'aphagas te ci'i phyir zhe na
NK116(le)001:12998: / nyan thosa sdoma khrimsa nyams pa 'achaba semas ma skyes par bshags na /
NK116(le)001:12999: lana bduna gsora rung ba yoda la /
NK116(le)001:13000: 'achaba pa dang bacasa pa'i ltung ba ni lana gciga kyang /
NK116(le)001:13001: gso ba'i yula meda pa ni ji ltar rdza be'u chagas pa bzhina no //
NK116(le)001:13002: byang chuba semas pa sdom nyams na rina chena gyi
NK116(le)001:13003: nyer spyod chag grum du song ba bzo bos bcos
NK116(le)001:13005: gazhana rkyen dge ba'i gashasa gnyen la bsten nas gas ba yin la /
NK116(le)001:13006: gsang sngagsa kyi sdom pa nyams pa ni /
NK116(le)001:13007: rina po che'i snod gang zhig cung zad zhoma pa
NK116(le)001:13008: ltar gyur ba mgar ba min kyang ranga stobs mthu
NK116(le)001:13009: yisa gso rung bar yoda pasa kyang 'phags so //
NK116(le)001:13011: bla ma dang rdo rje'i spun grogs la zhe brnyasa
NK116(le)001:13012: shor na 'phrala du tshogs kyi 'khor lo la sogs
NK116(le)001:13013: pas mnyes par byas pas nyams chags skong bar 'gyur
NK116(le)001:13014: ro // gsung gi dama tshiga nyamsa na bla ma
NK116(le)001:13015: rdo rje chosa kyi skur bsgoma la de'i snying po
NK116(le)001:13016: 'am yiga brgya 'buma thera gdona par bya'o //
NK116(le)001:13017: thugas lasa nyamsa na lo gsuma gyi bar smra ba
NK116(le)001:13018: bacada de bla ma dang thugs yid dbyer med kyi
NK116(le)001:13019: ting nge 'dzin rtse gcig tu mnyam par bazhaga pa
NK116(le)001:13020: gso ba'i thabas dam pa yin no //
NK116(le)001:13021: de la'ang nang gses kyi dbye ba ni nyin mtshan
NK116(le)001:13022: thun drug gi cha lasa thala na thuna tshoda 'adsa
NK116(le)001:13024: 'agla dang nyamsa dang 'adsa dang rala ba zhes rim
NK116(le)001:13025: pa bzhin zhag dang zla ba dang lo gciga lo
NK116(le)001:13026: gnyis rnams 'adsa pa la brjod cing de dag gso
NK116(le)001:13027: bar runga ste / 'on kyang phyi ma phyi ma rnams lci zhing /
NK116(le)001:13028: gal te lo gsum 'adsa na gso bar runga ba ma yina na /
NK116(le)001:13030: nyamsa na bdoga dgu spongs dag byas nas bskang zhing /
NK116(le)001:13031: 'adsa na bu dang chung ma dang nora gyi dbyig ste rin chen rnams kyis bkang la /
NK116(le)001:13032: rala ni bla ma'i sku glud du rang gi lus
NK116(le)001:13033: srog gis btong ba'i bsam pas gso pa'i thabs kyi
NK116(le)001:13035: de rnams kyi shes byed gang du yod snyams na /
NK116(le)001:13036: rdo rje nyi ma rnama para bkoda pa zhes bya ba'i rgyud lasa gsungsa so //
NK116(le)001:13037: phyir bcos kyi don bsdu ba ni gzhan yang zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te //
NK116(le)001:13038: gazhana yanga dabnga bzhi bskyar nas zhu ba dang badga 'juga yang yang blanga pa dang /
NK116(le)001:13039: bskyed rdzogas bzlas brjod dang khams 'dzag med du bsrung ba 'pho meda kyi tshul khrimas dang /
NK116(le)001:13040: kun rdzob kyi thiga le'i rnala 'byor byed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:13042: 'das dang ma 'das kyi lha la gator ma gtong ba /
NK116(le)001:13043: ngan song gsum gyi sdig sgrib dral ba'i sngagas dang /
NK116(le)001:13045: chu ma ma ki ru gsal bar khrus la zhugs te bkru ba dang /
NK116(le)001:13046: gtuma mo'i me'i bsrega pa dang /
NK116(le)001:13047: dge 'dun 'dus pa'i tshogas sama rten gsum gyi mduna du rang gi nyes pa bsgraga pa dang /
NK116(le)001:13049: gsunga raba bklag pa dang yiga brgya bzla ba dang /
NK116(le)001:13051: yan lag bduna pa dang mchoda rten bzhengas pa la
NK116(le)001:13052: sogsa dge ba'i thabas su gyur ba bsam gyisa gtugsa
NK116(le)001:13053: pa ma yina pa kun la 'jug cing khyad para
NK116(le)001:13054: dongas sprug bashagas pasa mi 'adga med pa ni /
NK116(le)001:13055: mar me brgya rtsa'i chog dang /
NK116(le)001:13056: spang skong brgya rtsa 'don pa dang /
NK116(le)001:13057: bshags pa rnam pa sna tshogs bya /
NK116(le)001:13058: des na bya ba'i yon tan 'thob /
NK116(le)001:13060: rjes thob dmigas bacasa kyi dus su nyams chags kuna
NK116(le)001:13061: la 'gyoda semas lhag para byed nas mnyam bzhag tu
NK116(le)001:13062: chos thams cad gdod nas rnam par dag cing dge
NK116(le)001:13063: sdig gi tha snyad bral ba'i gnas la 'jog pa
NK116(le)001:13064: ni bshags pa'i mchog tu gyur pa yin pas shin
NK116(le)001:13065: tu gcesa so // lar dam tshig gi bsrung tshul
NK116(le)001:13066: ni slob dpon dang slob ma gnyis ka la rag
NK116(le)001:13067: tu gcesa so // las ste / cis phyir zhe na /
NK116(le)001:13068: kha na ma tho ba'i las byed pa 'di sems can rang brgyud pa'i chos nyid yin gshis /
NK116(le)001:13069: las dang po'i slob ma sa bsrung tshul mi shes pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:13070: 'o na gnyis kas ji ltar bsrung na /
NK116(le)001:13071: slob dpon gyis shes pa bcu'i bsrung ngo //
NK116(le)001:13073: don gyi gnad shes pa1 dang /
NK116(le)001:13075: dbang dang man ngag gi skabs shes pa 3 dang /
NK116(le)001:13076: lta ba yangs bar shes pa 4dang /
NK116(le)001:13077: bsgom pa dang che bar 5shes pa /
NK116(le)001:13078: 'khor ba dang ma 'dres pa shes pa 6 /
NK116(le)001:13079: chos nyid zad par shes pa7 /
NK116(le)001:13080: 'das pa'i sa la gnas par shes 8pa /
NK116(le)001:13082: chos can 10 gyi mtshan nyid shes pa ste /
NK116(le)001:13084: shes pa gcig gi khyad par gyis //
NK116(le)001:13085: khyad par bcu yi bsrung thabs 'phags zhes so //
NK116(le)001:13086: slob mas slob dpon gyi gsung ji ltar brtsal ba
NK116(le)001:13087: byis pas ma'i nu zho 'jib pa bzhin du dang
NK116(le)001:13089: phyir bcos ma byas pa'i nyes pa ni ma bshags zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:13090: chos 'di thams cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang bsgrub par
NK116(le)001:13091: byed pa la thabs gzhan las phul byung du ji
NK116(le)001:13092: ltar zab pa de tsam du nyams na nag po'i
NK116(le)001:13093: rnam smin kyang zab pa'i phyir nyes ltung gis phog
NK116(le)001:13095: tshe 'dira bde legas kyi yona tan thams cad me
NK116(le)001:13096: shi ba'i du ba bzhin du mar mar 'griba nas
NK116(le)001:13097: 'jigs pa chen po brgyad kyis rgol zhing dus ma
NK116(le)001:13098: yin par 'chi bar 'gyur te 'jig rten pha rol
NK116(le)001:13099: du 'gro ba spyi'i sdug bsngal dang grang dmyal brgyad
NK116(le)001:13100: dang tsha dmyal gong ma la sogs pa thams cad
NK116(le)001:13101: gcig tu bsdoms kyang sdug bsngal la do zla meda
NK116(le)001:13102: pa'i rdo rje'i dmyal bar ltung ba ni /
NK116(le)001:13104: rtsa kun nyams pa'i 'chal ba dang //
NK116(le)001:13105: gso la nye bar mi brtson na //
NK116(le)001:13106: rdo rje'i dmyal bar de ltung ste //
NK116(le)001:13107: dmyal ba phal ba thams cad kyi //
NK116(le)001:13108: sdug bsngal gcig du bsdom pas ni //
NK116(le)001:13109: de yi 'bum gyi char mi phod //
NK116(le)001:13110: sangs rgyas stong gi 'od zer dang /
NK116(le)001:13111: byang chub sems dpa'i phrin las kun //
NK116(le)001:13112: rgyun du mdzad kyang phan mi 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:13113: bskal pa ther 'bum la sogs su //
NK116(le)001:13114: de ni thon par mi 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:13117: 'o na bsrung ba'i phan yon ji ltar yod snyams
NK116(le)001:13118: na dam tshig zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan
NK116(le)001:13119: te / dama tshiga rnam grangs ji snyed tshul bzhin
NK116(le)001:13120: du bsrung shing rgyud la ldan pa gang zhig skye
NK116(le)001:13122: brtson 'grus myur na tshe 'di'am 'chi kha'i bar ma
NK116(le)001:13123: dora sogs gang rung ba'i dus der gruba pa brgyad
NK116(le)001:13124: la sogs pa'i yon tan 'thob ste de dag ni
NK116(le)001:13126: mkha' spyod ral gri ril bu dang /
NK116(le)001:13127: rkang mgyogs bum pa gnod sbyin khol /
NK116(le)001:13128: bcud len dang ni mig sman no //
NK116(le)001:13129: de la mkha' spyod ni mkha' la gnas nus shing 'chi ba med pa'o //
NK116(le)001:13130: ral gri ni pha rol las rgyal bar byed pa'o //
NK116(le)001:13131: ril lu ni sman gang la gang sgrubs pa lag tu thogs pas lus mi snang ngo //
NK116(le)001:13132: rkang mgyogs ni mchil lhwam grub ste gyon pas yud tsam la rgya mtsho'i mtha' yang 'khor ba'o //
NK116(le)001:13133: bum pa ni de'i nang du zad mi shes pa'i 'dod dgu'i gter 'byung ba'o //
NK116(le)001:13134: gnod sbyin gyi khol po ni de bran du byas
NK116(le)001:13135: nas yid la ji ltar 'dod pa skad cig gi
NK116(le)001:13137: nyi zla'i tshe glang po che'i stobs pad+ma'i mdangs dang
NK116(le)001:13138: ldan shing lus shing bal ltar yang pa sogs so
NK116(le)001:13139: // mig sman ni mig la byugs pas sa 'og gi gter mthong ba'o //
NK116(le)001:13142: tshe la dbang bas bskal ba'i grangs ji tsam 'dod par gnas pa dang /
NK116(le)001:13143: sems la dbang bas ting nge 'dzin dpag tu med
NK116(le)001:13144: pa las skad cig re rer mnyam par 'jog cing
NK116(le)001:13146: yo byad la dbang bas bsam pa tsam gyi 'jig
NK116(le)001:13147: rten du zas nor sna tshogs pas gang bar nus
NK116(le)001:13148: pa dang / las la dbang bas bzo sogs las
NK116(le)001:13149: gnas thams cad la ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin spyod
NK116(le)001:13150: pa dang / pa dang / skye ba la dbang
NK116(le)001:13151: bas lha dang mi'i gnas gang 'dod du skye ba
NK116(le)001:13152: pa dang / pa dang / dang / mos pa
NK116(le)001:13153: la dbang bas sems can gyi yid la ji ltar
NK116(le)001:13154: re ba de ltar bskang nus pa dang /
NK116(le)001:13155: smon lam la dbang bas 'jig rten gyi khams thams
NK116(le)001:13156: cad sangs rgyas kyis gang ba la sogs ji ltar
NK116(le)001:13158: rdzu 'phrul la dbang bas zhing khams dpag tu med
NK116(le)001:13159: pa skra rtse gcig gi nam mkha' la 'dzin pa
NK116(le)001:13160: sogs gang 'dod du sprul nus pa dang /
NK116(le)001:13161: ye shes la dbang bas shes bya gang shes par 'dod pa de shes pa dang /
NK116(le)001:13162: chos la dbang bas chos thams cad kyi ming dang don rnam par bzhag pa la mkhas pa'o //
NK116(le)001:13163: de dag sa bdun tshun chad phyogs mthun yod pas
NK116(le)001:13164: dbang bcu phyi dang dag sa gsum na snga ma
NK116(le)001:13165: las nus khyad che bas nang ste gnyis dang /
NK116(le)001:13166: mthar thug pa ni sangs rgyas sa na yod do //
NK116(le)001:13169: phra zhing yang ba phra rab nus pa dang /
NK116(le)001:13170: spyod par nus dang bdag nyid chen po dang /
NK116(le)001:13171: dga' mgur byed dang thams cad dbang du 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:13172: ci 'dod byed dang dbang phyug don brgyad do //
NK116(le)001:13173: de la phra zhing ni 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad dbu ma'i rang bzhin du mthong ba'o //
NK116(le)001:13175: ye shes kyi rlung ste de'i stobs kyis mkha' khyab
NK116(le)001:13176: 'jig rten gyi khams su rdzu 'phrul gyis skad cig
NK116(le)001:13177: tsam la 'gro ba dang blta bar nus pa'o //
NK116(le)001:13179: dbu mar rlung sems zhugs pas bdag gzhan mtha' stong
NK116(le)001:13180: pa nyid du thim par rtogs pas gnyis snang thams
NK116(le)001:13181: cad nub pa'o // spyod pa nus pa ni /
NK116(le)001:13182: nang gi btsun mo dbu ma yin pas der rlung
NK116(le)001:13183: sems zhugs pa'i rten 'brel gyis phyi rol du gzugs
NK116(le)001:13184: rdo rje'i bdag nyid can la sogs pa zag med
NK116(le)001:13186: bdag nyid chen po ni mtshan dpe 'bar ba la sogs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:13187: bdud bzhi las rnam par rgyal ba dang //
NK116(le)001:13188: mthu stobs kyi bdag por gyur ba'o //
NK116(le)001:13190: 'gro ba ji snyed rnams la ji ltar 'dod pa'i
NK116(le)001:13191: sku dang gsung la sogs pa'i rnam par 'phrul ba
NK116(le)001:13192: sna tshogs bstan nas bsam pa tshim par byed nus
NK116(le)001:13193: pa'o // thams cad dbang du gyur ba ni /
NK116(le)001:13194: sems can rnams tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i go 'phang la
NK116(le)001:13195: 'god par nus pas gzhan don du mi'agyura ba skad
NK116(le)001:13198: rang gzhan gnyis ka'i don du gnam rdo thang la lhung ba dang /
NK116(le)001:13201: du ma las gcig du byed pa la sogs pa'i rdzu 'phrul la dbang thob pa'am /
NK116(le)001:13202: de kun kyang rang gis bzhed pa tsam la rag
NK116(le)001:13203: las pa yin pas zag med kyi yon tan ma
NK116(le)001:13204: lus pa la dbang 'byor ba'i phyir dbang phyug dang
NK116(le)001:13210: lhun grub ste gong du bstan pas shes so //
NK116(le)001:13211: mchoga gi dngosa gruba kha sbyor yan lag bduna ni /
NK116(le)001:13213: longs spyod rdzogs dang kha sbyor bde chen rang bzhin med /
NK116(le)001:13214: snying rjes yongs gang rgyun mi 'chad dang 'gog pa med /
NK116(le)001:13216: de yang rnam pa longs spyod rdzogs pa /
NK116(le)001:13217: des chos kyi sku dang sprul pa'i sku yang bzung bas /
NK116(le)001:13218: sku gsum yan lag bdun du bzhugs pa'i tshul /
NK116(le)001:13219: dmigs pa med pa'i thugs rgyud snying rje chen pos gang ba dang /
NK116(le)001:13220: de'i phrin las thugs rje'i 'jug pa sems can gyi khams la rgyun mi 'chad pa dang /
NK116(le)001:13221: 'gog pa med pa ste sprul sku'i yan lag gsum /
NK116(le)001:13222: ye shes kyi sku rang 'od kyi lha mo dang kha sbyor dang /
NK116(le)001:13223: de las zag pa med pa'i bde ba chen po rgyun mi 'chad pa dang /
NK116(le)001:13224: tshig dang yi ge med pa dgongs rgyud kyi chos 'khor la rtag par longs spyod pa ste //
NK116(le)001:13226: rnam pa de dag dang ldan kyang rang gi ngo
NK116(le)001:13227: bo spros pa kun gyi pha rol du son pa'i
NK116(le)001:13228: rang bzhin med pa chos sku'i yan lag gcig ste
NK116(le)001:13229: spyir btang bdun gyi bdag nyid can du bzhugs pa'o
NK116(le)001:13231: de lta'i yon tan mtha' dag pa rdzogs pa nas /
NK116(le)001:13232: sku lnga'i zhing khams su 'gro zhing dona gnyis lhuna gyis 'gruba par 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:13233: yon tan rin po ches mdzod kyi le'u bcu pa'i 'grel pa'o //
NK116(le)001:13234: theg pa mtha' dag gi rtse mor gyur ba rdzogs
NK116(le)001:13235: pa chen po'i grub mthar gyur ba le'u bcu gcig
NK116(le)001:13236: pa 'chad par byed pa'i dang po gzhi'i rang bzhin
NK116(le)001:13237: la bstan bshad gnyis las dang po ni rgyal bas
NK116(le)001:13238: shes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te rgyal basa
NK116(le)001:13239: 'khora lo bar bar gnyen por 'dzin pa las grol
NK116(le)001:13240: ba'i thabs su chos thams cad rnama par thara ba'i
NK116(le)001:13241: sgo gsum gyis gtan la 'bebs pa la /
NK116(le)001:13242: chos nyid tsam du'ang dmigs pa med pa stong pa nyid /
NK116(le)001:13243: ngo bo rdul tsam yang ma grub pa mtshan ma med pa /
NK116(le)001:13244: yang dag pa'i mtha' la gnas pa'i phyir smon pa med pa ste /
NK116(le)001:13246: stong pa nyid kyi mtshan nyid ni //
NK116(le)001:13247: dmigs pa med pa rnam dben nyid /
NK116(le)001:13248: mtshan ma med pas zhi nyid dang //
NK116(le)001:13249: gsum pa'i mtshan nyid sdug bsngal dang //
NK116(le)001:13250: gti mug ces ni bshad phyir drongs /
NK116(le)001:13251: de ltar bstana par bya ba'i ngo bo ni so so ranga riga pa'i ye shes nyid do //
NK116(le)001:13252: tshul de 'khor lo bar ba las tha mas mi ston nam zhe na /
NK116(le)001:13253: ston mod kyang 'dir grub mtha' spros pa 'gog pa'i
NK116(le)001:13254: gnyen por tha snyad kyi lam du bar ba bde
NK116(le)001:13256: mkhas pa snga ma rnams 'di gnyis drangs nges la
NK116(le)001:13257: 'dod tshul ma mthun par rtsod gzhir gyur kyang tshad
NK116(le)001:13258: ma gsum gyis gtan la phab na kho bos ni
NK116(le)001:13259: 'di la rtog ges rig pa'i khur gyis ngal du
NK116(le)001:13261: stobs sogs yon tan rgya mtsho'i 'byung gnas bsam gyis
NK116(le)001:13262: mi khyab pa'i ye shes gang zhig ston pa la
NK116(le)001:13263: tha ma sgo shin tu yangs mod la /
NK116(le)001:13264: bar bas kyang mi ston pa min ste /
NK116(le)001:13266: ye shes med na yon tan 'phel med byang chub med //
NK116(le)001:13267: rgya mtsho 'dra ba'i sangs rgyas chos kyang med par 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:13269: don dam bden pa de'i rang ngos nas yod med kyi spros pa nye bar zhi ba ste /
NK116(le)001:13271: tshu rol pha rol mtha' la min //
NK116(le)001:13272: de dag bar na mi gnas pa //
NK116(le)001:13273: dus rnams mnyam pa ces bya ba //
NK116(le)001:13274: shes rab pha rol phyin pa 'dod /
NK116(le)001:13277: so sor rang rig tshad med spyod yul ni //
NK116(le)001:13278: brjod du med cing tha snyad yongs chad pas //
NK116(le)001:13279: rtsod dang bral ba don dam chos yin te //
NK116(le)001:13280: de ni tog ge'i yul las 'das pa'o //
NK116(le)001:13282: semas cana gyi khamas la bde gshegas snying po yang dag pa'i mtha' ru thug pa de /
NK116(le)001:13283: rgyu rkyen la ma ltos par ranga bzhina gyis bzhugas pa la rdzogas pa chena pora gragas so //
NK116(le)001:13284: tshul 'di'i grub mtha' 'og ma'i gang zag gi blo
NK116(le)001:13285: gros kyi snod du mi shong bas the tshom na
NK116(le)001:13288: bde gshegs snying po'i 'gro ba yongs la khyab /
NK116(le)001:13291: sa yi dkyil na gnas pa'i chu //
NK116(le)001:13292: dri ma med par gnas pa ltar //
NK116(le)001:13293: nyon mongs nang na ye shes kyang //
NK116(le)001:13294: de bzhin dri ma med par gnas /
NK116(le)001:13297: rdzogs sangs sku ni 'phro phyir dang //
NK116(le)001:13298: de bzhin nyid dbyer med phyir dang //
NK116(le)001:13299: rigs yod phyir na lus can kun //
NK116(le)001:13300: rtag tu sangs rgyas snying po can /
NK116(le)001:13303: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rang bzhin gang //
NK116(le)001:13306: 'o na mthar thug 'bras bu'i theg pa gang rung
NK116(le)001:13307: rung tu snang bar 'gyur ba zhig na gnas 'di
NK116(le)001:13308: khyad par du 'phags pa'i tshul ci yin snyams na
NK116(le)001:13310: rdzogs pa chen po lta ba'i rdzong //
NK116(le)001:13311: sa lam skad cig gcod pa yin /
NK116(le)001:13312: theg dman 'og mas do zla min /
NK116(le)001:13314: lta sgom gyis 'phags tshul 'og tu ston no //
NK116(le)001:13316: grub mtha' gzhan dang mthun tshul gang du zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te //
NK116(le)001:13317: ganga gi tshe gzhan du med cing mkha' ltar rgya
NK116(le)001:13318: che ba mi slob pa'i lam bazanga dama pa'i dona
NK116(le)001:13319: mthar thug pa / matha'a dag mngon du gyur te
NK116(le)001:13320: sku bzhi lhun gyis grub pa'i 'bras chos gang zhig
NK116(le)001:13321: mthar thug pa / / so so'i blo'a dri ma
NK116(le)001:13322: phyi dara byas pa kho na'i khyad chos yin mod
NK116(le)001:13323: de'i phyir gong du bstan pa'i sdom pa gsum dang
NK116(le)001:13324: mthar thug pa / / / phar phyin druga dang /
NK116(le)001:13325: bskyed rdzogas la sogas pa'i bslab bya ji snyed kuna kyang rdzogas pa chena po'i lam stegsa yina no //
NK116(le)001:13326: gzhi'i bzhugs tshul gtan la dbab pa'i phyir 'dir ni zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:13327: gzhung lugs 'dira ni 'khora ba dang mya ngan las
NK116(le)001:13328: 'adsa pa'i chosa thams cad rnam par dag pa'i phyir
NK116(le)001:13329: rtogs te sangs rgyas ma byung pas dbyingsa lasa ma
NK116(le)001:13330: g.yosa 'khrul te 'khor ba ma byung bas gazhana du
NK116(le)001:13331: 'gyur ba meda cing 'khora 'adsa gnyis ye nas ma
NK116(le)001:13332: grub pa gzhi 'gyur ba med pa'i chosa nyid do
NK116(le)001:13333: // de nyid kyang ngo bo ranga bzhina thugas rje gsum gyi bdag nyid can du nges te /
NK116(le)001:13335: dbyings de'i ngo bo ni nam mkha' lta bu'o /
NK116(le)001:13337: thugs rje ni snying po gnas te yon tan thams cad kyi 'char gzhir gyur ba'o //
NK116(le)001:13338: zhes ma btsal yon tan ye rdzogas su rnam pa kun tu gnas so //
NK116(le)001:13339: de nyid kyi nganga ngam gshis na daga pa sangsa rgyas dang /
NK116(le)001:13340: ma daga semas can zhes dben kyang 'khora 'adsa gnyis
NK116(le)001:13341: kyi cha ltar grub pa 'di rang snang la gzhan
NK116(le)001:13342: du bzung bas yul yul can ltar yon kyang /
NK116(le)001:13343: dper na gnyid kyi nganga na rmi lam ji ltar
NK116(le)001:13344: rmis kyang ngang de las mi g.yo ba bzhina du
NK116(le)001:13345: / ganga nasa kyang ma 'onga gazhana du 'pho ba'ang meda pa kho na'o //
NK116(le)001:13346: de lta na'ang re zhiga gzhi'i bzhugas tshul gyi grub pa'i matha'a rnam par bzhag pa ni /
NK116(le)001:13352: cira yanga khasa blanga du btub pa 6dang //
NK116(le)001:13353: sna tshogas su 'doda pa'i gzhi ste rnam grangs bduna no //
NK116(le)001:13354: tshul 'di'i gnas la dgag bzhag spangs gsum rgyas par
NK116(le)001:13355: tshig don rin po che'i mdzod du snang bas spro
NK116(le)001:13357: de la rnam grangs kyi 'dod tshul gzhan yang yod de /
NK116(le)001:13361: bag chags sna tshogs pa'i kun gzhi bzhi'o //
NK116(le)001:13363: dbyings de'i ngang nas dpyod byed thog ma'i 'gyu ba
NK116(le)001:13364: rig pa la ltos pa'i ma rig pa mtshungs ldan
NK116(le)001:13365: gyi 'khor 'das 'byed pa'i cha nas brjod pa'o //
NK116(le)001:13367: dpyod byed kyi shes pa de nyid rang ma rig pa kha phyir bltas kyi 'khor bar sbyor la /
NK116(le)001:13368: rang gi rang bzhin rig pa la myang 'das su sbyor ba'o //
NK116(le)001:13370: shes pa de nyid la bag chags yod pas sa'i rang bzhin sha /
NK116(le)001:13373: rlung gi rang bzhin yid lus 'char ba'i cha nas btags pa'o //
NK116(le)001:13375: shes pa de nyis kyis sems kyi bag chags sna tshogs pa brten pa'i cha nas brjod pa'o //
NK116(le)001:13376: 'on kyang de dag thams cad kyang /
NK116(le)001:13377: ngo bo ka daga gciga pu'i phyogsa re la tha
NK116(le)001:13378: snyad so sora btagsa pa'i ranga rang 'doda gzhunga 'dzina
NK116(le)001:13380: ji ltar khonga longa bduna gyis glanga po'i skye mcheda dang /
NK116(le)001:13381: nganga pa'i kha doga brjod pa ji bzhina du gyur pas tshad ma ma yin no //
NK116(le)001:13383: rgyal pos long ba du ma bsags te glang po che bstan nas /
NK116(le)001:13384: glang po che'i mtshan nyid so sor smros shig /
NK116(le)001:13386: glang po che'i sna la reg pa rnams ni lcags kyu dang 'dra'o //
NK116(le)001:13388: mig la reg pa rnams ni phor ba dang 'dra'o //
NK116(le)001:13390: rna ba la reg pa rnams ni zhim ma dang 'dra'o //
NK116(le)001:13392: rgyab la reg pa rnams ni khyogs dang 'dra'o //
NK116(le)001:13394: mjug ma la reg pa rnams ni the bu dang 'dra'o //
NK116(le)001:13396: long ba rnams kyis glang po che las gzhan smras pa ma yin yang //
NK116(le)001:13397: thams cad du rtogs pa ni ma yin no //
NK116(le)001:13398: de bzhin du sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin yang /
NK116(le)001:13401: 'od gsal la sogs pa tha dad par smras kyang thams cad du rtogs pa ni ma yin no //
NK116(le)001:13404: gang so so'i skye bo dang /
NK116(le)001:13407: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi kyang ji lta ba
NK116(le)001:13408: bzhin du sangs rgyas kyis snying po mthong ba ma
NK116(le)001:13409: yin no // dper na dmus long zhig gis gzhan zhig la mar gyi kha dog dris pa las /
NK116(le)001:13410: kha ba 'dra'o zhes smras pa dang /
NK116(le)001:13411: des kha ba la lag pa reg bas mar gyi kha dog grang mor 'dzin to //
NK116(le)001:13412: dris pa kha ba'i kha dog ci 'dra /
NK116(le)001:13415: ngang pa'i gshog sgra thos pa kha ba'i kha dog 'ur 'ur po 'dzin to /
NK116(le)001:13416: dris pa gshog pa'i kha dog ci 'dra /
NK116(le)001:13418: dung la reg bas 'jam por 'dug na //
NK116(le)001:13420: ji ltar smras kyang dmus long gis kha dog ji blta ba bzhin mi shes pa de ltar /
NK116(le)001:13421: sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin yang mthong ba rab tu dka' 'o //
NK116(le)001:13424: rang gi dam bca' 'ang bsgrub pa 'dir ni zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:13425: 'dira rang lugs ni ngo bo ka nasa daga pa'a dbyings la /
NK116(le)001:13426: yona tan lhun gyi gruba pa chu dag de'i rlan bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:13427: de nyid gciga dang tha dada mina te /
NK116(le)001:13429: dngosa po matshana ma'i sprosa pa thams cad bral basa ka daga la /
NK116(le)001:13430: gting gasla 'aggas pa meda pasa lhun grub bo //
NK116(le)001:13433: ngo bo nyid la ka dag pa'i /
NK116(le)001:13434: rang bzhin nyid du lhun grub bo //
NK116(le)001:13437: ngo bo ka dag brjod gzhi bral /
NK116(le)001:13438: rang bzhin lhun grub gcig snang rdzogs /
NK116(le)001:13441: gong ltar so sor 'dod pa dgag pa'i gnas su gyur na /
NK116(le)001:13442: 'dir rdzas gnyis gcig du bsgrub pa mi 'gal lam bshad pa /
