NK116(le)001:13443: gzhi gciga la rdzasa gnyis su snang ba 'gal ba'ang ma yina te /
NK116(le)001:13444: dper na gnyid du phyogsa pa la khad pa dang
NK116(le)001:13445: gnyid stug po'i dusa kyi rang bzhin brgyad cu'i rtog
NK116(le)001:13446: tshogs 'gag pas rmi lam med cing slar yang rlung
NK116(le)001:13447: g.yos pas shesa ngo la rmi lam rmi ba ltar
NK116(le)001:13448: sems gcig la rdzas ldog tha dad snang ba bzhin
NK116(le)001:13449: / ngo bo ka daga yina pasa 'khora ba dus gsum du /
NK116(le)001:13453: rang bzhin lhuna gruba kyi rtsala la 'khor 'das kyi rola ba cira yanga snang ba yin no //
NK116(le)001:13454: de'i don man ngag gis dpe'i sgo nas gtan la
NK116(le)001:13455: dbab pa ni ji ltar zhes bya ba la sogs
NK116(le)001:13456: pa gsungs te / ji ltar ni nor bu bed+aur+ya'i
NK116(le)001:13457: ranga 'oda ni gting nas rtag tu gasla kyang nyi
NK116(le)001:13458: 'od la sogas rkyen gyisa ma bskyed par phyir mi
NK116(le)001:13459: snang ba de bzhina du ka daga dngosa po dang
NK116(le)001:13460: mtshan ma spangsa pa'i rang gadngas lhun gyis grub pa
NK116(le)001:13461: gang zhig phyi rgya ma rala par gzhon nu bum
NK116(le)001:13463: ngo bo spros pas stong la rang gadnga 'od gsal gyis ma 'agga pasa na /
NK116(le)001:13465: sems la sems ma mchis te sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal ba'o //
NK116(le)001:13468: snang ba kuna gyi 'achara gzhira de nyid dus gsum du rtag par bzhugas kyang /
NK116(le)001:13469: gzhi ngo bo stong pa nyid de lasa g.yosa pa
NK116(le)001:13470: meda pa'i byang chub kyi semas rin po che nyid
NK116(le)001:13471: dngos po dang matshana ma ma grub pa ni risa
NK116(le)001:13472: su chad pa can du phyir mi gasla ba'o //
NK116(le)001:13473: de yang ngo bo ka dag la ltos nas de ni zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:13474: ka dag gi ye gzhi skyon dang yon tan gyi
NK116(le)001:13475: mtha' las 'das pa de ni tha snyad kyi btags
NK116(le)001:13476: pa'i sangsa rgyas zhes bya ba de ma yina la
NK116(le)001:13478: dngos mtshan las 'das phyir gciga dang tha dada kyang ma yina la matha'a dbus yod pa'ang mina no //
NK116(le)001:13479: ci yang med pa'i stong pa phyang chada ma yina la dngosa po yod pa'ang mina no //
NK116(le)001:13481: rang bzhin gnas pa'i ngo bo la //
NK116(le)001:13482: sangs rgyas med cing sems can med //
NK116(le)001:13483: ma rig med cing 'khrul ba med //
NK116(le)001:13484: sems med yid kyang yod ma yin //
NK116(le)001:13485: dgra med bshes med gnyen yang med //
NK116(le)001:13486: nyon mongs med cing ngar 'dzin med //
NK116(le)001:13488: chos med chos su snang ba med //
NK116(le)001:13489: thabs med shes rab nyid kyang med //
NK116(le)001:13490: phung po med cing khams kyang med //
NK116(le)001:13491: yul med 'dzin med bya ba med //
NK116(le)001:13492: dbang po med cing yul kyang med //
NK116(le)001:13493: bzung bar bya dang 'dzin pa med //
NK116(le)001:13494: sku med ye shes nyid kyang med //
NK116(le)001:13495: shes dang shes bya'i bdag po med /
NK116(le)001:13496: 'od med kha dog yod ma yin //
NK116(le)001:13497: sgra med dri la sogs pa med //
NK116(le)001:13498: 'dod pa med cing zhen pa med //
NK116(le)001:13499: dbyings med gzhal yas khang yang med //
NK116(le)001:13500: lha med mchod pa'i yul las 'das /
NK116(le)001:13503: 'di la dbang por snang ba med //
NK116(le)001:13504: rdos bcas mtshan ma rang dag phyir //
NK116(le)001:13505: gting gsal chen po'i gzhi mar gnas //
NK116(le)001:13506: khyab dang khyab pa nyid kyis stong //
NK116(le)001:13507: phyi nang chad pa med snang bar //
NK116(le)001:13508: gsal byed snang bas cha ma 'gags //
NK116(le)001:13509: snying po thams cad bcud bsdus pa'i //
NK116(le)001:13510: dri ma med cing rang sar dag /
NK116(le)001:13511: sangs rgyas rnams ni gsang chen du //
NK116(le)001:13512: rang bzhin gyis ni cha la bzhugs //
NK116(le)001:13514: ngo bo skye 'gags dang yod meda sogs mtha' brgyad
NK116(le)001:13515: bral ba'i chos nyid gang du yang ma phye ba'i
NK116(le)001:13516: ka dag / rang bzhin 'gags pa med pas sku
NK116(le)001:13517: dang ye shes su 'du 'bral med pa'i lhun grub
NK116(le)001:13518: ka dag / // thugs rje'i go ma 'gags pas
NK116(le)001:13519: mdzad pa phrin las kun la khyab pa'i snang ba
NK116(le)001:13520: gsuma dang thabas gcig pa zhig go /
NK116(le)001:13522: ngo bo ka dag ye shes la //
NK116(le)001:13523: ma rig pa zhes srid ming med //
NK116(le)001:13524: gcig dang gnyis kyi grangs med pa'o //
NK116(le)001:13525: brtags pa'i don med grub pa med //
NK116(le)001:13526: gang du ma phye'i chos nyid las //
NK116(le)001:13527: ye shes tsam du'ang grub pa med //
NK116(le)001:13528: tshig med brjod pa grub pa med //
NK116(le)001:13529: mtha' la mi gnas rang rig dag /
NK116(le)001:13530: brjod 'dzin ming gi mtha' zad pa'o //
NK116(le)001:13531: rgyu med rkyen gyi grangs med la //
NK116(le)001:13532: gnyis snang yul dang yul can med //
NK116(le)001:13533: mtshan nyid gang du'ang phye ba med //
NK116(le)001:13534: yul can rag pa zad pa'o //
NK116(le)001:13535: ye nas med pa'i dag pas dag /'khrul rtogs 'gags pas cir ma mdzad //
NK116(le)001:13536: ma skyes bas na 'gags stong ngo //
NK116(le)001:13537: rang bzhin lhun grub ye shes zhes //
NK116(le)001:13538: mi skye mi 'gags cir mi dgongs //
NK116(le)001:13539: yul dag nges pa med phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:13540: rtsal dang yon tan 'gags med pas /
NK116(le)001:13541: rol pa tsam du snang ba las //
NK116(le)001:13542: sna tshogs rdzogs pa'i gzhi ma'o //
NK116(le)001:13543: med phyir snang la snang phyir stong //
NK116(le)001:13544: snang stong 'jug pa'i yan lag can //
NK116(le)001:13545: sangs rgyas sems can dag yul lo //
NK116(le)001:13546: 'di ltar gzhi zhes mngon par gnas //
NK116(le)001:13547: rang bzhin tsam du gnas pa las //
NK116(le)001:13548: ngo bo'i cha nas brtags pas stong //
NK116(le)001:13549: yan lag spros phyir mkhyen pa rdzogs //
NK116(le)001:13550: rang gnas lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir //
NK116(le)001:13551: 'di la spangs blang gnyis med pa'o //
NK116(le)001:13552: thugs rje kun khyab ye shes las //
NK116(le)001:13553: mi mdzad sna tshogs 'char ba'i sgo //
NK116(le)001:13554: mdzad pa ltar snang ngo bor rdzogs //
NK116(le)001:13555: chos sku stong pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK116(le)001:13556: ye shes mkhyen pa rdzogs pa'i cha //
NK116(le)001:13557: shugs kyis sems can rnams la 'chad //
NK116(le)001:13559: mkhyen pas rig cing gsal ba'o //
NK116(le)001:13560: rang rig gsal ba'i bdag nyid las //
NK116(le)001:13561: rang bzhin shugs kyi thugs rje nyid //
NK116(le)001:13564: da ni gzhi las gzhi snang g.yo tshul ston pa'i
NK116(le)001:13565: phyir de nyid ces bya ba la sogs pa gsungs
NK116(le)001:13566: te / gzhi de nyid kyi nganga ngam klong lasa /
NK116(le)001:13567: riga pa sku bzhi 'byung bar rung ba'i badga nyid
NK116(le)001:13568: cana shin tu phra ba'i ye shes kyi rlung lnga'i
NK116(le)001:13569: snying po de nyid srog rlung gi chas cung zad
NK116(le)001:13570: bskyod pa nas gdangsa kyis snang ba phyir 'aphagas pasa
NK116(le)001:13571: / nang gasla gzhona nu bum sku'i tshul tu bzhugs
NK116(le)001:13572: pa'i rgya rala nasa ye gzhi ka dag lasa g.yosa
NK116(le)001:13573: pa meda bzhina gzhi snang shara ba'i dus ganga gi
NK116(le)001:13574: tshe thugas rje 'gags pa med pa'i riga gadngas sogs
NK116(le)001:13575: 'od lnga'i rnam pa'i yul dang yula can ltar snang
NK116(le)001:13576: ste dpyod byed shes para shara ba na rang ngo
NK116(le)001:13577: rang gis shes pa'i riga pa zhes bya ba de
NK116(le)001:13578: la ltos pa'i ma riga pa ste snga ma'i ldog
NK116(le)001:13579: pa cana gyi cha bzunga basa 'khrul ba rgya 'byams
NK116(le)001:13580: / su song ngo // ji ltar sprin dang bral
NK116(le)001:13581: ba'i nam mkha'a bzhina kun nas dangs ba'i ka daga
NK116(le)001:13582: / su song ngo // lasa / rang bzhin lhun
NK116(le)001:13583: gruba g.yo ba 'achara tshul brgyad du shara ba la
NK116(le)001:13584: rin chen ga'u'i gnas lugs zhes kyang bya ste thugs
NK116(le)001:13585: rje'i rtsal la 'dod yon gyi go ma 'gag pa'o
NK116(le)001:13586: / su song ngo // lasa / // de yang
NK116(le)001:13587: 'di ltar ma grub pa'i grub pa chen por gnas
NK116(le)001:13589: thugs rje ltar 'char 2ba'i go ma 'gags pas sems can gyi don byung //
NK116(le)001:13590: ye shes ltar 'char pa'i 3longs spyod ma 'gags pas ye she lnga'i rang 'od du snang /
NK116(le)001:13591: sku ltar 'char 4ba'i ngo bo ma 'gags pas rig pa sku ru smin //
NK116(le)001:13592: gnyis med ltar 'char 5ba'i lta ba ma nges pas gcig dang du ma las grol /
NK116(le)001:13593: mtha' grol ltar 'char 6ba'i thabs ma 'gags pas 'khrul snang rang rgyud bar mi gnas /
NK116(le)001:13594: dag pa ye shes kyi sgo mthar phyin pas //
NK116(le)001:13595: bde gshegs snying po ka dag tu 'char //
NK116(le)001:13596: ma dag pa sems can ltar 'char bas rigs drug gi snang ba 'byunga ba'o //
NK116(le)001:13597: gzhi lam 'bras gsum du bsdu na /
NK116(le)001:13598: gong du bshad pa ltar 'khor 'das lung du ma
NK116(le)001:13599: bstan pa'i skabs kyi rig pa bum sku'i tshul du
NK116(le)001:13600: yod pa gzhi lhun grub rin po che'i sbubsa so
NK116(le)001:13601: // de las gzhi snang chen por shar ba lam lhun grub rin po che'i sbubs te //
NK116(le)001:13602: de yang gnas gcig la snang lugs chen po bzhi byung ba ni //
NK116(le)001:13603: lhun grub la sna tshogs su snang ba1 //
NK116(le)001:13604: longs sku la kha mig rna ba can 'od kyi rang bzhin sgyu ma'i skur snang ba2 /
NK116(le)001:13606: sems can la tha dad du snang 4ba'o //
NK116(le)001:13607: de ltar snang ba'i tshe gzhan rkyen la ma ltos
NK116(le)001:13608: par rig pa ka dag chen po ye sangs rgyas
NK116(le)001:13609: pa ni 'bras bu lhun grub rin po che'i sbubs
NK116(le)001:13611: tshul 'di ni 'khora 'adsa gnyis 'brela pa'i sgo 'aphara lta bur ste /
NK116(le)001:13612: thega pa'i rtse mo shina tu rnal 'byor gyi rgyud sde rnams dang /
NK116(le)001:13613: mana ngaga snying thig gi gzhung rnams su gab pa'i
NK116(le)001:13614: tshul du yod pa gang zhig /'di ltar la sogs
NK116(le)001:13615: par 'byed pa'i lde miga gcig pu ni /
NK116(le)001:13616: bod gangsa ldana gyi ri'i ljongsa 'dir 'gran gyi zla med pa dri meda 'oda zera stong ldana zhes /
NK116(le)001:13617: rab 'byams rgyal ba'i mkhyen nus gcig tu bkrun pa
NK116(le)001:13618: rnam 'dren bzhi ba'i mdo sngags kyi bstan pa'i shing
NK116(le)001:13619: rta chen po // rgya gar pan chen bi ma
NK116(le)001:13620: la mi tra de nyid kyi 'ja' lus 'pho chen
NK116(le)001:13621: stong gsal dngas ma'i 'od sku nges pa lnga ldan
NK116(le)001:13622: gyi dbyings na bzhugs bzhin 'gags med thugs rje chen
NK116(le)001:13623: po'i rnam rol mi yi zol du snang ba bdag
NK116(le)001:13624: cag gi yang mes sa gsum 'gro ba'i mig gciga
NK116(le)001:13625: kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po klong chen rab 'byams
NK116(le)001:13626: bzang po gang gisa legs par phyes pa yin no
NK116(le)001:13627: rta chen po // // gzhi de las kun tu bzang po'i grol tshul ni /
NK116(le)001:13628: de tshe gzhi yi snang ba mthonga ba'i skad cig mara de nyid /
NK116(le)001:13629: dang po'i sangsa rgyas kun tu bazanga po zhes bya ba desa //
NK116(le)001:13630: snang ba'i cha'i 'od zer 'khrul bar ma mcheda par
NK116(le)001:13631: ranga snang gi cho 'phrul du rig pasa lunga ma
NK116(le)001:13633: gzhi de nyid 'bras bura smin pa'i zhes rang ngo shes 2pa'i shes raba kyis /
NK116(le)001:13634: skad cig ma gciga la rig ma rig gis 'khor
NK116(le)001:13635: 'das su 'phang ba'i bye braga raba tu phyed cing
NK116(le)001:13636: / phyed thoga de nas shesa raba kyi nyid kyang skur smin pa /
NK116(le)001:13637: gazhana byung rkyen la ma ltos par ranga sara lhun gyis grub par gansa par /
NK116(le)001:13639: de tshe kun bzang chos drug gis //
NK116(le)001:13640: gzhi shes ma rig drug bcom nas //
NK116(le)001:13641: nyug tsam las ni yid tsam stong /
NK116(le)001:13642: rig tsam byung bas rig 'grib brlag /
NK116(le)001:13643: sal gyis gsal bas mun song sangs //
NK116(le)001:13644: wal gyis byung bas 'thibs pa med //
NK116(le)001:13645: sgro skur bral bas ma rig dag /'gyur ba med pa nam mkha' 'dra //
NK116(le)001:13646: de yang rdo rje sems dpa' nyon //
NK116(le)001:13647: 'khrul pa ma rig log bcom pas //
NK116(le)001:13648: lung ma bstan pa rang brlag stong //
NK116(le)001:13649: bem rig phyed pas gzhi dang phrad //
NK116(le)001:13650: de phyir ma rig mun pa sangs /
NK116(le)001:13652: de yang nyug tsam pa'i rig pas gzhi las 'phags1 /
NK116(le)001:13653: rig tsam du yod pas rang ngor snang ba ma 'gags2 //
NK116(le)001:13654: sal gyis gsal bas bye brag phyed3 //
NK116(le)001:13655: wal gyis byung bas phyed pa'i thog tu grol /
NK116(le)001:13656: sgro skur dang bral bas gzhan rkyen la ma 5ltos //
NK116(le)001:13657: 'gyur ba medapa'i rang sar gnas pa ste khyad chos drug ldan //
NK116(le)001:13658: sku dang ye shesa rgya mtsho'i mnga' badga chen po nyid du //
NK116(le)001:13659: skad cig gciga la mngona para sangsa rgyasa so //
NK116(le)001:13663: sangs rgyas 'khrul par ma gyur bas //
NK116(le)001:13664: gzhi las 'phags pa'i dbang po yis //
NK116(le)001:13665: rang snang rang bzhin med par shes //
NK116(le)001:13666: rtogs dpyod yul rnams phyir ma shor //
NK116(le)001:13669: kha gcig lhun grub rin po che'i gzhi de nyid
NK116(le)001:13670: du grol ba 'dod pa ni gnad ma go ba'i
NK116(le)001:13671: gtam ste 'khor 'das lung du ma bstan pa'i gzhi
NK116(le)001:13672: la phyin pas grol na thog ma yang /
NK116(le)001:13674: phyi nas kyang mi ldog pa'i stangs mi chod do //
NK116(le)001:13675: 'o na gang du grol zhe na /
NK116(le)001:13676: lhun grub sgo brgyad ral ba'i snang ba chen po
NK116(le)001:13677: de nyid shes rab kyi rigs pas gzhan du ma
NK116(le)001:13678: bzung bar gzhi rang rtsal du shar ba go nas
NK116(le)001:13679: 'khrul bar rang log para ngo bo nyid med pa'i
NK116(le)001:13680: nang dbyings spros bral dag mnyam chen por thim pa
NK116(le)001:13681: la tshogs chen ye rdzogs kyi sangs rgyas zhes bya'o
NK116(le)001:13684: skad cig gcig gis bye brag phyed //
NK116(le)001:13685: skad cig gcig gis rdzogs sangs rgyas /
NK116(le)001:13687: de las gzhan don rgyun mi chad par 'byung ba
NK116(le)001:13688: ni gang tshe zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan
NK116(le)001:13689: te / dus gang gi tshe na ka dag chosa sku'i dbyingsa lasa ma g.yosa bzhina du /
NK116(le)001:13690: 'od gsal chen po ris med du rnam par grol
NK116(le)001:13691: nas stobs bcu la sogs pa'i yona tan rgyas pa'i
NK116(le)001:13692: lhuna gruba kyi sgo longas spyod rdzogas pa'i sku ru
NK116(le)001:13694: de yi rtsa lasa tshangsa chena gyi bskal ba bkoda cing /
NK116(le)001:13695: de las daga pa ranga bzhina du sprul sku'i snang ba dang /
NK116(le)001:13696: ma daga 'khora ba'i sgo lasa semas cana gyi snang ba nyid dang mthuna pa'i ston pa yisa /
NK116(le)001:13697: 'khora ba stong ba'i slad du phrin lasa zada mi shes so //
NK116(le)001:13698: zaga meda chos nyid ranga gi ngo bo shesa pa'i
NK116(le)001:13699: dge tshogas rgya chen rgyun mi chad pa'i stobs kyisa
NK116(le)001:13700: mang'a dabnga rdzogas pa'i ston pa chena po de'i //
NK116(le)001:13701: zhing dang madzada pa chos kyi dbyingsa bla 'og dang
NK116(le)001:13702: phan tshun gyi mtha' mi dmigs pa dang mnyam pa
NK116(le)001:13703: ste / sangsa rgyas nyid kyi snang ba ni de tsam mo //
NK116(le)001:13704: de la gnyis su 'dzina pa yoda pa mina pasa na /
NK116(le)001:13706: 'dula byed so sor rnam para mi rtog mod kyang /
NK116(le)001:13707: ji ltar nora bu mchoga dang /
NK116(le)001:13708: dapaga bsam gyi shinga chena ltar /
NK116(le)001:13709: rtsol ba meda pa'i thugas rje gazhana ngora snang ba yin no //
NK116(le)001:13710: rgyas pa 'og tu 'bras bu'i le'ura 'chad do //
NK116(le)001:13711: sems can gyi 'khrul tshul ni de nyid ces bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:13712: grol ba de nyid ma riga pa'i khamas gsuma gyizha semsa cana rnams /
NK116(le)001:13713: thoga ma'i gzhi lhun grub chen po la 'khrul bar ma mchisa kyang /
NK116(le)001:13714: gzhi snang shar ba'i rnam pa rang rtsal du ma riga pa'i /
NK116(le)001:13715: glo bur gyi rkyen ni rgyu badga nyid gcig 1pa ste /
NK116(le)001:13716: de nyid las dpyod byed kyi shes pa phra mo
NK116(le)001:13717: zhes langs pa nus pa je thur du song ba
NK116(le)001:13719: de nas minga dang dona dang badga dang gzhan la
NK116(le)001:13720: sogs rtog pa cher skyes pa kuna tu brtag 3pa
NK116(le)001:13721: yina ste / ma riga pa gsum po de la 'khrula ba'i rkyen bzhi mched pa'o //
NK116(le)001:13722: de la rkyen bzhi ni gzhi nyid 'od khyim ltar du gnas pa rgyu'i rkyen1 /
NK116(le)001:13723: de lasa rtogsa dpyod shar ba badga po'i rkyen2 /
NK116(le)001:13724: de lasa yula dang yula can so sor 'dzin pas
NK116(le)001:13725: dmigas pa'i rkyen gsum po dusa mtshungsa su byung ba
NK116(le)001:13726: de ma thaga pa'i rkyen te tshogas pa de lasa
NK116(le)001:13727: rima bzhina 'khrul ba stobsa su gyur nasa /
NK116(le)001:13728: nyon mongas pa'i tshogas rnams 1'phela zhing 'khor ba'i gansa
NK116(le)001:13729: rigas gang du skyes bu gsum gyi thun mong gi
NK116(le)001:13730: lam rim du bstan zin pa de ltar grub ste
NK116(le)001:13731: / rten 'brel bcu gnyisa shinga rta'i 'aphanga lo bzhina lu gu rgyuda du 'khor ba yin no /
NK116(le)001:13732: de yang rgyu gsum ni ma rig pa /
NK116(le)001:13734: yul rnam par dpyod pa rnam shes /
NK116(le)001:13735: tha dad kyi ming dang gzugs ni ming gzugs //
NK116(le)001:13736: 'byung ba so so'i cha dang kha dog du grub pa skye mched drug /
NK116(le)001:13737: des yul la longs spyod pa ni reg pa /
NK116(le)001:13738: dga' gdung bar mi'i 'du shes ni tshor ba /
NK116(le)001:13739: bde bar chags pa ni sred pa /
NK116(le)001:13740: dang du len pa ni len pa /
NK116(le)001:13741: las des phyi ma'i skye bar 'phen pas srid pa'o //
NK116(le)001:13742: tshul 'di ltar du rigas drug skye gansa bzhi po'ang /
NK116(le)001:13743: ngo bo meda bzhin du snang ba sgyu ma'i rta glang lta bu'i ranga gzugas su snang dus nasa /
NK116(le)001:13744: yoda ma myong ba'i stong gzugs thoga ma la ma
NK116(le)001:13745: rig pa drug las dpyod byed yida druga langas nas
NK116(le)001:13746: tshogas druga shar / ma rig pa drug ni /
NK116(le)001:13747: rang shar gyis bstan pa ltar /
NK116(le)001:13748: rtsa ba sems kyi ma rig pa ni lhan cig skyes pa bshad zin to //
NK116(le)001:13749: 'khrul ba yul gyi ma rig pa ni rang rtsal
NK116(le)001:13750: las shar ba'i snod bcud gnyis bsdus kyi chos so
NK116(le)001:13751: // 'khrul gzhi gzhi'i ma rig 3pa ni rkyen bzhi bshad zin pa de ma thag pa'o //
NK116(le)001:13752: 'dzin pa rtogs pa'i ma rig 4pa ni yid drug ste /
NK116(le)001:13753: ma rig pa dang mtshungs par ldan pa'i yid ni rig byed 'gyu ba dang bcas pa'o //
NK116(le)001:13754: yid 2kyi rnam par shes pa ni yul la bdag 'dzina gyi rtogs pa shar ba'o //
NK116(le)001:13755: gtan la 'bebs pa'i yid ni de la chags pa skyes pa'o //
NK116(le)001:13756: kun tu 'tshol ba'i yid 4ni nyon mongs pa phra ba'i tshogs rnams sdud pa'o //
NK116(le)001:13757: rnam par rags pa'i yid ni mi dge ba sna tshogs byed pa'o //
NK116(le)001:13758: nges par 'jog pa'i yid 2ni snang ba'i dngong po
NK116(le)001:13759: bdag dang gzhan la ris su bcod pa ste drug
NK116(le)001:13760: go // bcos pa lam gyi ma rig pa ni
NK116(le)001:13761: phyin ci log ltas sangs rgyas snang ba mi mthong
NK116(le)001:13762: go // ba'o // mi shes rmongs pa'i ma rig
NK116(le)001:13763: pa 6ni sangs rgyas dang la yod pa ma shes
NK116(le)001:13765: de ltar rnama rtog badga tu 'dzina pa'i 'chinga ba ni //
NK116(le)001:13766: raba tu mthu che bas semsa nyid nam mkha'i khamsa
NK116(le)001:13767: lta bu ngo bo nyid meda pa 'di yanga raba
NK116(le)001:13768: tu bcing nasa / badga yoda pa ltara la zhena
NK116(le)001:13769: nas 'agla me'i 'khora lo bskor ba bzhina du 'khor
NK116(le)001:13770: tu bcing nasa / ro // de phyir srid pa
NK116(le)001:13771: 'di na yul gyi dngos po mthong tshul tha dad
NK116(le)001:13772: de la la'i snang ba la la'i muna pa dang
NK116(le)001:13773: tu bcing nasa / ro // / la la'i bduda rtsi ni /
NK116(le)001:13774: la la'i chu dang la la'i me ste /
NK116(le)001:13775: kuna nasa rnam para 'agla ba'i 'du shes rnams /
NK116(le)001:13776: rang rang gi bag chagas kyi snying rjes rjes su 'gro ba las ngesa pa 'agla yanga meda do //
NK116(le)001:13777: pad+mo rnam par rol pa'i mdo las /
NK116(le)001:13778: lha'i bu rnam par rol pas 'jam dpal la smras pa /
NK116(le)001:13779: 'jam dpal phyi rol gyi yul 'di dag byed pa pos byas pa'am ji ltar lta bur bgyi /
NK116(le)001:13782: phyi rol gyi yul 'di rnams ni byed pa pos
NK116(le)001:13783: byas pa ma yin te sems sam rtog pa'i bag
NK116(le)001:13784: chags kyi snang ba yin no //
NK116(le)001:13786: bag chags ji ltar bltas kyang ri dang rgya mtsho
NK116(le)001:13787: dang nyi ma zla ba la sogs pa sra zhing
NK116(le)001:13788: 'thas pa ltar gyur pa snang du ga la rung
NK116(le)001:13790: lha'i bu snang du rung ste /
NK116(le)001:13791: grong khyer chen po wa ra n+aa si na bram
NK116(le)001:13792: ze me sbyin zhes bya bas rang gi lus rtag
NK116(le)001:13793: tu bsgom pas grong khyer gyi mi rnams kyi rtag
NK116(le)001:13794: tu mthong nas bros pas grong khyer stong par byung
NK116(le)001:13795: ngo // zad pa sa dang chu bsgom pas sa dang chur snang ba /
NK116(le)001:13796: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dge slong gis mi gtsang ba
NK116(le)001:13797: dang keng rus kyi 'du shes bsgom pas der snang
NK116(le)001:13798: ba yin na thog ma med pa'i bag chags brtas
NK116(le)001:13801: bag chags brtas pa'i dbang gis rnam pa sna tshogs pa dag ci'i phyir snang ba yin /
NK116(le)001:13803: snang ba thams cad ma nges pa yin te /
NK116(le)001:13804: la la'i snang ba ni la las mun pa yin no //
NK116(le)001:13805: 'di ltar sa 'bab zhig la'ang sa la sar 'du shes pa'ang yod //
NK116(le)001:13806: sa la mer 'du shes pa'ang yod //
NK116(le)001:13807: sa la longs spyod du 'du shes pa'ang yod //
NK116(le)001:13808: sa la sdug bsngal du 'du shes pa'ang yod //
NK116(le)001:13809: me la mer 'du shes pa'ang yod //
NK116(le)001:13810: me la longs spyod du 'du shes pa'ang yod //
NK116(le)001:13811: me la gnas su 'du shes pa'ang yod //
NK116(le)001:13812: me la zas su 'du shes pa'ang yod /
NK116(le)001:13813: chu la chur 'du shes pa'ang yod //
NK116(le)001:13814: chu la mer 'du shes pa'ang yod /
NK116(le)001:13815: chu la sar 'du shes pa'ang yod //
NK116(le)001:13816: chu la bdud rtsir 'du shes pa'ang yod //
NK116(le)001:13817: chu la gnas su 'du shes pa 'ang yod //
NK116(le)001:13818: nam mkha' la nam mkhar 'du shes pa'ang yod //
NK116(le)001:13819: nam mkha' la gnas su 'du shes pa'ang yod //
NK116(le)001:13820: nam mkha' la sar 'du shes pa'ang yod //
NK116(le)001:13821: de bas na nges pa med pa'i phyir bag chags
NK116(le)001:13822: kyi dbang gis gang ltar yang snang ba yin no
NK116(le)001:13824: snang dang snang yul gyi dbye ba ni de lta'ang zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te //
NK116(le)001:13825: bshad ma thag pas de lta na'ang snang yula ni semas ma yin te //
NK116(le)001:13826: dper na bzhina gyi gzugs brnyan me longa gi nanga du zhugsa kyang //
NK116(le)001:13827: yul dang rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i rkyen gyis
NK116(le)001:13828: snang ba tsam lasa bzhina dang me longa nama yanga
NK116(le)001:13829: 'drasa ma myong ba mthong chos su shes mod de
NK116(le)001:13831: me long ngos sam 'bru mar snod dag du //
NK116(le)001:13832: bud med kha bzhin brgyan pas bltas pa na //
NK116(le)001:13833: de na bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor kun snang yang /
NK116(le)001:13834: yod pa ma yin med pa'ang ma yin ltar //
NK116(le)001:13835: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par bya /
NK116(le)001:13837: gzung 'dzin gyi dbye ba ston pa'i phyir med bzhin zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:13838: chos thams cad meda bzhina gyi snanga ba la dera
NK116(le)001:13839: 'dzina 'khrul ba'i semas yin pa ni dper na glo
NK116(le)001:13840: bur du thaga khra mthonga tshe sbrul lo snyam du
NK116(le)001:13841: 'dzina byed kyi / shes pa dang po de gzunga ba'i chos yina la /
NK116(le)001:13842: rdzas la rtogsa cing dpyod pa zhib mor zhugas pa ni 'dzina pa'o //
NK116(le)001:13843: de yang spyan ras gzigs kyi brtul zhugs las //
NK116(le)001:13844: de la gzung ba ni yul du 'dzin pa'i sems dang //
NK116(le)001:13845: 'dzin pa ni de la dpyod pa'i sems sems las byung ba'o //
NK116(le)001:13847: kha gcig gzung ba yul kyi dngos por 'dod pa ni ma go ba ste /
NK116(le)001:13848: de ltar 'phags pa'i gang zag gi snang ngor sgyu ma lta bur dang //
NK116(le)001:13849: sangs rgyas kyi gzigs ngor dag pa'i gzhan dbang yang med par thal te //
NK116(le)001:13851: snang ba dang yul gyi dbye ba ston pa'i phyir
NK116(le)001:13852: gal te zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te
NK116(le)001:13853: / 'di la rtsa ba bshad pa dang mtha' dbyad gnyis las dang po ni /
NK116(le)001:13854: gala te sbrul du snang ba de bzunga ba yin la /
NK116(le)001:13855: 'dzina pa badga posa shesa pa yin para smra par byed na /
NK116(le)001:13856: snang ba dang snang yula ma byed pa'i skyes bu de yanga /
NK116(le)001:13857: snang ba nyid dang lhana gciga tu yoda meda byed do //
NK116(le)001:13862: snang ba dang snang yul gcig tu 'dod pa'i blo chos can //
NK116(le)001:13863: khyod kyi snang ba ldog pa'i dus gang gi tshe yul ma grub par thal 'dod pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:13865: khyod phyogs su rtol ba dang lhan gcig tu snga ma'i gnas med par thal /
NK116(le)001:13866: khyod la mi snang ba'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:13867: de thal rtsa ba 'dod mi nus te /
NK116(le)001:13868: khyod med pa'i dus su yang yul yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:13870: yul sems bag chags mthu brtas pa'i 'khrul snang du shar ba las bden grub med kyang /
NK116(le)001:13872: sems rdzing bu snang ba gzugs brnyen lta bu ste /
NK116(le)001:13873: rdzing bu rnams skams na gzugs brnyen mi snang ba la /
NK116(le)001:13874: zla ba yod pa bzhin sems ni 'gags na snang
NK116(le)001:13875: ba nub kyi yul gnas pa mngon sum gyi tshad
NK116(le)001:13876: ma grub bo // de bas yul der 'dzin gyi
NK116(le)001:13877: blo dang po snang ba zhes mkhas pa rnams gsungs
NK116(le)001:13878: tshul 'dis ni sems tsam bden rdzun sogs kyang kheg
NK116(le)001:13879: ma grub bo // pa yin no // kha cig
NK116(le)001:13880: rdzogs chen lugs su snang yul 'jog tshul sems tsam
NK116(le)001:13881: dang 'dra bar smra bar phyogs tsam ma go ba'i
NK116(le)001:13882: mngon rtogs su zad de bshad pa de dag gis
NK116(le)001:13883: ma grub bo // pa yin no // shes sla'o
NK116(le)001:13884: // lar phyin ci log lta'i mthu stobs su gyur
NK116(le)001:13885: nas 'brel med kyi 'o dod 'bod pa dag ci
NK116(le)001:13889: log pa'i lam la mtha' med phyir //
NK116(le)001:13890: de dag 'di na spro bya min /
NK116(le)001:13892: sems kyi rtsa bar rtags na 'dzin pa rang grol
NK116(le)001:13893: du 'gro ba'i tshul gang du 'ang zhes bya ba
NK116(le)001:13895: gang su dag rnam pa thams cad du'ang ma riga gzunga 'dzin glo bura ba'i rkyen //
NK116(le)001:13896: srid pa'i badga po des rang ngor ltos te nga'o snyams pa dang /
NK116(le)001:13898: 'di ni gzhan no snyams pa'i mtha' 'am bar mada
NK116(le)001:13899: bzhina du 'khrul ba'i rtsa ba sems kyi phu thag
NK116(le)001:13901: kuna byed rgyal po ste bde gshegs snying po ranga
NK116(le)001:13902: las thog mar byung zhing tha mal yang ranga la
NK116(le)001:13904: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi le'u bcu gcig pa'i 'grel ba'o ////
NK116(le)001:13905: thun mongs ma yin pa lam gtan la dbab pa'i
NK116(le)001:13906: phyir gang zhig ces bya ba la sogs pa gsungs
NK116(le)001:13907: te / 'di na ganga zhiga slob pa mina pa'i
NK116(le)001:13908: snang stong zunga du 'juga pa mthar thug gi 'bras
NK116(le)001:13909: bu'i go sa la dkri ba'i lam chena po pha
NK116(le)001:13910: rol tu phyin pa drug gi yona tan kun kyang
NK116(le)001:13911: shesa raba pha rola phyin pa la yang dag par
NK116(le)001:13914: lam de ni thams cad mkhyen pa'i bar tu nama yanga gazhana gyi rgyur mi 'gyur bas so //
NK116(le)001:13915: 'di la shes rab zlos sam snyams na /
NK116(le)001:13916: shes rab rnam pa gsum las snga ma gnyis snga
NK116(le)001:13917: ma'i grangs su bgrangs la phyi ma de dag bstan
NK116(le)001:13918: byar dgongs nas gsungs pas skyon med do //
NK116(le)001:13919: kha cig 'dus byas kyi dge bas ci bya zer
NK116(le)001:13920: te rgyu 'bras khyad du gsod nas chos nyid bsgom
NK116(le)001:13921: pa skad kyis // sgoo nga ltar ci yang ma sems par had de 'dug pa /
NK116(le)001:13922: de las mu stegs rtag par lta ba'i gang zag gi dga' 'am snyams mo //
NK116(le)001:13923: lar stong nyid rtogs kyang las 'bras la bag yod par byed dgos te /
NK116(le)001:13924: ci'i phyir na chos nyid bden pa mngon sum par
NK116(le)001:13925: rtogs pa rgya gar shing rta chen po rnam gnyis
NK116(le)001:13926: sogs kyi skyes rabs la bltas pas gsal tshul 'di
NK116(le)001:13927: bsam na slob dpon sangs rgyas gnyis pas /
NK116(le)001:13928: tha tshig rdo rje'i ri mo bstan ma bcu gnyis
NK116(le)001:13929: kyi snying la bltar bas mu stegs dngos su rgyu
NK116(le)001:13931: rgyangs 'phen dag gi bar do'i rnam shes 'dir mchi'am bdag yid 'phyang mo nyug du gyur to //
NK116(le)001:13932: rdzogs pa chen po'i mtshan nyid 'di ltar zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:13933: 'di ltar rdzogas pa'i sangsa rgyas kuna gyi gasnga ba chen po //
NK116(le)001:13934: stong pa nyid la matshana nyid gang yang mi gansa shing /
NK116(le)001:13935: matha'a brgyad dang bral bas dona dam pa de la dbu mar bzunga ba tsam du'ang meda de /
NK116(le)001:13936: ngo bo nyid gdod nas rnam par dag pas spros
NK116(le)001:13937: pa spangas pa gang zhig rdzogas pa chena po zhes
NK116(le)001:13939: de ni rtog ge'i spyod yul min pa rtsod pa zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:13941: rtsod pa mngona para 'phela ba'i rtog ge bas ni /
NK116(le)001:13942: kun tu rtogs pa'i 'thor rlung g.yos pas /
NK116(le)001:13943: brtagsa shinga rjesa su dapagas pa'i phyi bzhina 'brang ba zhig na /
NK116(le)001:13944: dona dama pa'i yula ni de dang 'agla ba cana
NK116(le)001:13945: so so ranga gi riga pa brjod pa'i yula lasa
NK116(le)001:13947: de la'ang dngosa pora smra ba grub matha'i rtog gesa
NK116(le)001:13948: ni zab mo'i don nam mkha'i tha snyad 'doms kyis
NK116(le)001:13950: sa 'atshamas damna pa so skyes rtog ge yisa ni
NK116(le)001:13951: phung po lnga las nyer len gyi rtog dpyod byed
NK116(le)001:13952: la de lasa 'adsa pa rgyal ba'i ye shesa ni
NK116(le)001:13953: / gdoda nas grola ba rdzogas pa chena po'i lam yin te /
NK116(le)001:13955: rdzogs pa chen po'i lta spyod ni /
NK116(le)001:13957: lta spyod byang chub sems 'di ni //
NK116(le)001:13958: nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin te //
NK116(le)001:13959: nam mkha' la ni rtog dpyod 'das /
NK116(le)001:13960: gang zhig rtog dpyod byed pa des //
NK116(le)001:13961: byang chub nam mkha' bzhin mi 'grub /
NK116(le)001:13964: snang ba gnyis ltos grub tu 'dzin pa las ldog
NK116(le)001:13965: pa'i tshul shes bya zhes pa la sogs pas bstan
NK116(le)001:13966: te / shesa bya phung po lnga'i nyer len rang
NK116(le)001:13967: bzhin gyi rnam par stong bas don la mnyam par
NK116(le)001:13968: bzhag nas snang ba'i yul gyis ma bcinga shing stong
NK116(le)001:13969: pa'i dngosa sam mtshan nyid kyang /
NK116(le)001:13970: thal byung gi stong pa kho na ma yin te rang bazhana 'od gsal ba' snying po ni /
NK116(le)001:13971: rang rig pa rang byung chen por bzhugs pa'i phyir
NK116(le)001:13972: na sku dang ye shes dang phrin las kyi chos
NK116(le)001:13973: khamsa gdod nas 'adu 'bral med pa nyi ma' zer
NK116(le)001:13975: de yang blo'i rim pas mjal lugs gsum yod pa
NK116(le)001:13976: gang la zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston te
NK116(le)001:13977: / de lta'i rdzogs pa chen po'i don ganga la
NK116(le)001:13978: blo yi stobs khyad kyi rima pasa majala lugas gsum
NK116(le)001:13979: / ste // bkod pa chen po las //
NK116(le)001:13980: yid can rnams la sems kyi sde //
NK116(le)001:13981: nam mkha' can la klong gi sde //
NK116(le)001:13982: rim rtsol can la man ngag go /
NK116(le)001:13984: de la dang po semsa kyi sde ba ni /
NK116(le)001:13985: 'khor 'das lam gsum gyi chos thams cad sems kyi rola ba'i rtsal du shara bar 'dod de /
NK116(le)001:13987: snang srid snod bcud sangs rgyas sems can kun //
NK116(le)001:13988: sems kyis byas shing sems kyi ngang du gcig /
NK116(le)001:13991: dang po sems kyi phyogs yin smra ba ni //
NK116(le)001:13992: lhun grub kyi gdangs las 'khor 'das kyi sgo gnyis
NK116(le)001:13993: su shar yang shar mkhan la ngo bo nyid med
NK116(le)001:13994: pas shar ba rang grol du 'gro ba'o //
NK116(le)001:13995: gnyis pa 'bras bu sems kyi byung bar 'dod pa ni /
NK116(le)001:13996: 'di ltar snang ba thams cad dang po dbyings las byung /
NK116(le)001:13998: tha ma dbyings su grol bas nam mkha' la /
NK116(le)001:13999: khur rlang snang zhing thim pa lta bu ste //
NK116(le)001:14000: ye grol yin pas yang grol mi dgos /
NK116(le)001:14001: rang bzhag yin pas gnyen pos mi bzhag /'bras bu yin pas 'bad rtsol med par la bazla'o //
NK116(le)001:14002: gsum pa gol sgrib la zla ba ni /
NK116(le)001:14003: yod pa dang med pas mtha' gol /
NK116(le)001:14004: gnyis ka ma yin pas dbus gol la /
NK116(le)001:14005: 'dir chos nyid ye stong chen po la phyogs 'dzin gyis 'ching grol med pa'o //
NK116(le)001:14006: bzhi pa gtan tshig gi khungs rdibs pa ni /
NK116(le)001:14007: rang bzhin skye med du grol bas rol ba 'gags med phyogs yan chen por dengs nas /
NK116(le)001:14008: dge bas 'phang ba'i myang 'das sdig pas 'phangs pa'i
NK116(le)001:14009: 'khor ba zhes bya ba brjod bya rjod byed dang
NK116(le)001:14010: bral ba'o // lnga pa rang byung gi ye shes phyogs lhung med pa ni /
NK116(le)001:14011: bsam las 'das pa'i ye shes kyi gshis gang du'ang
NK116(le)001:14012: ma grub pas snang stong zung 'jug gsum ka'i phyogs
NK116(le)001:14014: yul la mi rtogs pas phyi stong pa nyid yul can du mi 'dzin pas nang stong pa nyid //
NK116(le)001:14015: gnyis kar sgro mi 'dogs pas stong pa nyid stong pa nyid /
NK116(le)001:14016: chos can dang chos nyid du 'dzin pa'i phyogs las
NK116(le)001:14017: 'das pas lta ba nam mkha' lta bu la chen
NK116(le)001:14018: po stong pa nyid de rdzogs pa chen pos mtshan
NK116(le)001:14019: nyid do // drug pa phyogs 'dzin grub mtha' ba'i lugs ni /
NK116(le)001:14020: lha mi'i theg pa nas myang 'das bar gyi grub
NK116(le)001:14021: matha'i 'dod zhen mtha' dag ji ltar me long ngos
NK116(le)001:14022: la gzugs brnyan sna tshogs snang ba bzhin /
NK116(le)001:14023: sems kyis bzos pa las chos kyi dbyings la phan
NK116(le)001:14024: gnod ma byas pa'i phyir gang yang mi 'gags pa'o
NK116(le)001:14025: // bdun pa blo bral phyogs 'dzin 'das pa'i lugs ni /
NK116(le)001:14026: snang ba'i rol ba ji ltar shar yang blo 'das
NK116(le)001:14027: kyi chos nyid la bden rdzun gyi srog mi chags
NK116(le)001:14028: / stong dngos la der 'dzin gyi blo zhen mi
NK116(le)001:14029: 'dzug pas dngos po med pa'i stong pa nyid do
NK116(le)001:14030: / // gnyis pa klong gi sde ni /
NK116(le)001:14031: ranga snang bkoda pa'i rgyan du shar ba ni /
NK116(le)001:14032: ji ltar snang ba thams cad mkha' la gza' skar
NK116(le)001:14033: bkram pa bzhin chos nyid kun tu bzang mo klong
NK116(le)001:14034: yangs par rig pa rang snang ba'i rgyan du bkod
NK116(le)001:14035: pa las / sems sde ltar rtsal dang rol bar shar ba mi 'dod do //
NK116(le)001:14037: klong nag po rgyu med du smra bas rang byung
NK116(le)001:14038: gi ye shes lnga rgyu rkyen la ma ltos par
NK116(le)001:14039: bstan / klong khra bo sna tshogs su smra bas rol ba'i chos nyid la dgags sgrub med //
NK116(le)001:14040: klong dkar po sems su smra bas phyi nang gi snang rig sems kyi rtsal du rdzogs /
NK116(le)001:14041: klong rab 'byams rgyu 'bras la bzla bas 'khor 'das
NK116(le)001:14042: su ma phye ba'i yul sems gnyis med kyi rig
NK116(le)001:14043: pa la rang thog du ngos zin pa'i gzer thebs
NK116(le)001:14044: pa'o // bsdu na lhun grub yangs pa chen po'i klong /
NK116(le)001:14045: rang gsal 'bad rtsol bral ba'i klong /
NK116(le)001:14046: byas med gdod nas grub pa'i klong gsum du 'adu'o ////
NK116(le)001:14047: gsum pa mana ngaga gi sde ni meda snang stong ba'i gzugas brnyan te /
NK116(le)001:14048: ngo bo ka dag blo bral chen po'i gdangs rang
NK116(le)001:14049: snang lhun grub kyi sgo la rang shar ba'i rtsal
NK116(le)001:14050: snang la sgrib byed dang 'dzol sa med cing chos
NK116(le)001:14051: can gyi snang ba chos nyid spros bral du 'dum
NK116(le)001:14052: pa'i gnad kyi khyad par 'phags pa'o //
NK116(le)001:14056: rgyud rang gzhung du bstan pa gsum las /
NK116(le)001:14057: dang po blo dang bral ba'i ye shes la dbye
NK116(le)001:14058: gsal gyis bcos su med pas bya rtsol gyis bslad
NK116(le)001:14059: mi gzhug / don dam gyi gshis la bden gnyis
NK116(le)001:14060: dang rgyu 'bras med pas gsar du grol ba'i ltos
NK116(le)001:14062: sku gsum lam snang du bkod pa shes bya gzhan
NK116(le)001:14063: la mi ltos pas ma grol ba gang yang med
NK116(le)001:14065: kha gtam gyi tshul du gsungs pas ngo bo ma 'khrul ba /
NK116(le)001:14066: rang bzhin rnam rtog gi gzhi rtsa chod pa /
NK116(le)001:14067: mtshan nyid ngos bzung dang bral ba'o //
NK116(le)001:14068: dbye na glen pa yengs la bor ba'i kha gtam ni rtsa gnad kyi rlung /
NK116(le)001:14069: rlung gnad kyi sems chos nyid du zhi bas ye shes khungs nas don /
NK116(le)001:14070: sgo gsum 'brel thag chod pa'i gnad kyi 'gyu ba
NK116(le)001:14071: rang sar grol te 'khor 'das brjod pa chad pa'o
NK116(le)001:14072: // khar phog dus med pa'i kha gtam ni //
NK116(le)001:14073: dbyings la mi shong ba med pas 'khor 'das la khyab /
NK116(le)001:14074: stong nyid la ngos bzung med pas ngo bo mi 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:14075: gnyis ka bya rtsol med pas rang gnas kyi ye shes ngos bzung ba'o //
NK116(le)001:14077: rgyud rang gzhung gi man ngag 'khor 'das la spangs blang med /
NK116(le)001:14078: chos nyid sgra tshig du mi gnas pas stong nyid la tha snyad kyis mi thug pa'o //
NK116(le)001:14079: dbye na lta ba sgang dril bas spros bral gzhi la khyab /
NK116(le)001:14080: las la bzang ngan med pas khams gsum yongs grol du shar /
NK116(le)001:14081: rang bzhin stong gsal du shar bas dge sdig gi phan gnod med /
NK116(le)001:14082: mtshan nyid la yi ge med pas theg pa sna
NK116(le)001:14083: tshogs kyis sangs mi rgya bas dbang po cig char
NK116(le)001:14086: snang brtags kyi lta ba la byar med pa dang //
NK116(le)001:14087: sems kyi dran rtog skye med du dril ba'o //
NK116(le)001:14089: ngo bo la chos nyid med pas sangs rgyas ming du'ang ma grub /
NK116(le)001:14090: rang bzhin 'gags pa med pas 'khor ba tha dad du shar /
NK116(le)001:14091: mtshan nyid gcig du mi gnas pas lta sgom la tshad med pa'o //
NK116(le)001:14093: ngo bo skyed med du dag pas nyon mongs pa gzhi med du dngas /
NK116(le)001:14094: rang bzhin ma 'gags par shar yang spang blang bya rtsol dang bral /
NK116(le)001:14095: mtshan nyid ye grol yin pas 'khor 'das kyi khungs rdib pa'o //
NK116(le)001:14096: man ngag sde ba'i lugs kyi lta sgom grol thog
NK116(le)001:14097: tu gtan la dbab pa sogs kun kyang zhes bya
NK116(le)001:14098: ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:14099: de dag kuna kyang na da grol ba'i gzhi meda pa'i byang chub kyi semas gang zhig /
NK116(le)001:14100: thabs gang gisa 'grol ba spangsa pa'i ranga gasla gyi
NK116(le)001:14101: gadnga gzhi 'byung yul dang rtsa ba sa bon meda
NK116(le)001:14102: pa'i klong na gasla ba ni grol ba lnga'i khyad
NK116(le)001:14105: phung po lnga dang tshogs brgyad kyi nyer len sprin
NK116(le)001:14106: dang 'dra ba'i dbus na'ang rig pa'i mtshan nyid ni
NK116(le)001:14107: ye stong rtsa bral rjes med nam mkha' ltar rang
NK116(le)001:14108: bzhin med pas srid pa kun tu sbyor ba'i khur
NK116(le)001:14110: rang ngos spros pa dang bral bar byas shinga bcosa pa meda pasa ye grol yin no //
NK116(le)001:14112: 'ching byed gzhan na med pa'i phyir gnyen po la ltos bzhag med de chu'i ri mo'am /
NK116(le)001:14113: sbrul gyi mdud pa bzhin ranga gi ranga grola te rkyen la raga ma lusa so //
NK116(le)001:14115: mthong ba'i yul dang mig shes gnyis gcera gyis zug
NK116(le)001:14116: pa'i skad cig ma dang po rang la gzugs su
NK116(le)001:14119: snang bas shes par mi gos te /
NK116(le)001:14120: snang thog tu grola 3ba yina pas gnyen por ltos pa dang grol gzhi gzhan kuna dang bral ba'o //
NK116(le)001:14122: don de la gciga dang du ma zhes bya bar
NK116(le)001:14123: tha snyad gadgas pasa mi thug ste ci'i phyir na
NK116(le)001:14124: skye ba med pas yod matha'a lasa grol /
NK116(le)001:14125: 'gags pa med pas med mtha' las grol //
NK116(le)001:14126: gnyis ka'i bar du mi gnas pas dbus mtha' las grol ba'o //
NK116(le)001:14128: 'di ltar chos nyid gdag gzhi'i mtshan ma ma grub
NK116(le)001:14129: pas na gciga pora riga para grol basa matshana nyid
NK116(le)001:14130: meda kyang shes bya shes byed kyis bzhag pa'i grub
NK116(le)001:14131: matha'i blo yul gyi sbubs nas so so rang rig
NK116(le)001:14132: pa'i ye shes zang thal rjen par bud pa'i thig
NK116(le)001:14133: le nyag cig gi ye shes zhes bya ste snga
NK116(le)001:14134: ma bzhi po'ang mthar thugs so sor rang gi rig
NK116(le)001:14135: pa'i chos nyid gcig tu grol ba'i mtshan nyid shes
NK116(le)001:14136: na 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rgya grol ye
NK116(le)001:14137: 'byams chen po stong pa nyid du la bzla bar
NK116(le)001:14139: lta ba gang daga rnam par rtog pa'i bag chags
NK116(le)001:14140: kyi semas lasa 'adsa pa'i riga pa zhes bya ba
NK116(le)001:14141: 'di ni / 'og mar ma grags pa'i phyir ranga
NK116(le)001:14142: bzhina rdzogas pa chena po'i khyad chosa yina la rtogsa
NK116(le)001:14143: pa rnamas ni lung ma bstan gyi gazha las 'das
NK116(le)001:14144: te so sor rang rig par grol zhing ma rtogsa
NK116(le)001:14145: semsa can rnams ni de nyid ngang du gnyid dang
NK116(le)001:14147: rnam pas dbye na kun gzhi chu lta bu dang sems can rnams chu bur ji bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:14148: de'i tshul dpe'i sgo nas ston na mnyam par bzhag
NK116(le)001:14149: pa'i skabs rnam par rtogsa pa meda tsam du semas
NK116(le)001:14150: riga gnyis mtshungsa par snyam na'ang /
NK116(le)001:14151: 'byed chos ni riga pa ranga bzhina meda para zanga thala gyis gsal la /
NK116(le)001:14152: semas ni ldinga ka'i chu bran lta bura 'khyil zhing rmongas pa'o //
NK116(le)001:14153: yang rig pa ganma stong gi zla ba lta bu
NK116(le)001:14154: phyi rol du 'brel chad kyang gting gasla gyi gdangs
NK116(le)001:14156: semsa ni bco lnga'i zla ba yula dang 'dresa pa
NK116(le)001:14157: dang mtshungsa te tshegs drug gi snang ba la bgas
NK116(le)001:14159: kha gting med par dangsa la mtha' dbus bral bas yula meda par riga pa'i yona tan yin te /
NK116(le)001:14160: yula drug dang kuna nasa 'dresa pa semas kyi khyad par ro //
NK116(le)001:14161: de bzhina riga pa ni chos kyi dbyings kyi ranga
NK116(le)001:14162: bzhin gdod ma nas gansa shing mi 'gyur ba'i shesa
NK116(le)001:14163: raba ste / bsam gtan gyi ngang du sems gcun
NK116(le)001:14164: ba'i thabsa la ma ltos shig bying rgoda bral ba'o
NK116(le)001:14165: raba ste / // semsa ni dmigas pa ganga yang
NK116(le)001:14166: rung ba'i yula la rtse gciga pasa ting nge 'dzina
NK116(le)001:14167: raba ste / // dang / rten dang brten para 'brela zhing /
NK116(le)001:14168: riga pa yula steng 'og bar mtshams med par khyab brdal la shara kyang /
NK116(le)001:14169: snang ba yi zila gyis mi non pa dper na
NK116(le)001:14170: dngula chu sara ltung kyang rngul gyis mi gos pa
NK116(le)001:14171: dang 'dra la / semas ni gzunga 'dzina gyi cha dang bacasa pa yi /
NK116(le)001:14172: rnam rtog nye bar lena pa'i phyogsa dang 'dresa so //
NK116(le)001:14173: riga pasa semas nyid gazhana du ma spang mod kyang /
NK116(le)001:14174: semas dang riga pa lhan ciga mi 'du basa na /
NK116(le)001:14175: yula lnga dang der 'dzin gyi rnam para shar ba
NK116(le)001:14176: ranga dang rdzasa gcig pa'i nyon mongas rnams kyang lhan
NK116(le)001:14177: gciga du sbran nasa bros pa ltar 'gyur zhing /
NK116(le)001:14178: de ltar bros pasa nyon mongsa pa'i brtson ra lasa
NK116(le)001:14179: ngesa para 'byin te 'tshang rgya ba ni mana ngaga
NK116(le)001:14180: sde ba yi khyad para gyi chosa te gazhana du
NK116(le)001:14181: nyon mongas pa'i tshogas nyan ranga gi spongas zhing byang
NK116(le)001:14183: sngagsa spyir lam du gtong la rdzogs chen semas sdera
NK116(le)001:14184: gnas lugs kyis gshisa thoga du grola bar 'dod cing
NK116(le)001:14185: klong sdera spang gnyen gnyis chosa nyid gciga du daga
NK116(le)001:14187: man ngag gi lugs 'dir spros bral riga pa'i klong
NK116(le)001:14188: na lta ba'i ranga tshugsa 'dzin pa zhiga pa 'di
NK116(le)001:14189: e ma ho ngo matshara rmad du byung ba'o /
NK116(le)001:14191: sems rig gi dpe de bzhina du /
NK116(le)001:14192: kuna gzhi dang ni chosa sku gnyis kyang ka dag
NK116(le)001:14193: gi dbyingsa su gciga kyang 'byed chos chosa sku rtog
NK116(le)001:14195: kuna gzhi'i rnama shesa ni de yi sgrib cha ste /
NK116(le)001:14196: dper na rgya mtsho'i khar gru pa bgrod pa bzhina du 'khora 'adsa gnyis ka ldinga ngo //
NK116(le)001:14197: gzhi de nyid nasa 'khrul ba dang grola ba chosa nyid gcig du zad kyang /
NK116(le)001:14198: gnyid du song dang de lasa sad pa bzhina no //
NK116(le)001:14199: de yang 'gro drug 'khrul ba'i dabnga po nyamsa pa'i gnyid 'thuga pa'i dus bzhina la /
NK116(le)001:14200: grola ba'i sangs rgyas ni de lasa sada pa'i gansa skabsa dang 'dra'o //
NK116(le)001:14201: rdzogs pa chen por khas 'che ba'i gzugs brnyan 'ga'
NK116(le)001:14202: zhig gis gzhi thog grol skad smra ba sogs la
NK116(le)001:14203: dgongs nas thog ma'i zhes bya ba la sogs pa
NK116(le)001:14204: gsungs te // de yang thoga ma'i 'khor 'das gang
NK116(le)001:14205: du'ang ngesa pa meda pa'i gzhi yi lhuna grub dang
NK116(le)001:14206: gsungs te // / mathara phyin gyi grol ba'i ka daga dri brala gnyis po //
NK116(le)001:14207: rdzasa su gciga pa lta bu'i tha snyad 'dogs chog kyang slad kyi 'khrula ba'i gzhi /
NK116(le)001:14208: byed pa dang mi byed pa'i khyad para shesa pa gcesa so //
NK116(le)001:14209: zhes mkhyen pa gnyis ldan gyi ye shes gang zhig
NK116(le)001:14210: lhun grub kyi gzhi thog tu phyin nas thob pa
NK116(le)001:14211: min la spros bral ka dag gi dbyings su grol
NK116(le)001:14213: de bzhina 'bras dus dbyingsa kyi grola sa ka daga dang /
NK116(le)001:14214: da lta'i mnyams bzhag lam gyi riga pa ka daga gnyis so //
NK116(le)001:14215: rgya chada phyogsa lhunga meda pa mnyam par bzhag na'ang
NK116(le)001:14216: snga ma grol sa nyid ni rlung semas kyi cha
NK116(le)001:14218: rnam para byang ba'i 'khora ba myang 'adsa gnyis ka
NK116(le)001:14219: las mi gnas pa'i ka daga ste phyi ma lam
NK116(le)001:14220: dusa rlung semas ma daga pa'i rkyen dbang dang 'grogsa
NK116(le)001:14221: shing semsa dang sems byunga gi dri ma' chos kyis
NK116(le)001:14222: bslad cing khur bas dngosa po'i gshis thog tu gnas
NK116(le)001:14223: pa res 'ga' tsam las mnyam rjes 'dres par med
NK116(le)001:14224: do / de bzhin du chos nyida bar do'i riga gadngas stong gzugs dang /
NK116(le)001:14225: bskyed rim rtog bcas la gomas pa'i lha yi rnam
NK116(le)001:14226: pa'i sgyu lusa gnyis po ltar snang lha skur mtshungas
NK116(le)001:14227: kyang snang ba longs sku'i zhing khamas su shara zhing
NK116(le)001:14228: de ngo shesa thoga skad cig mar grola dang mi
NK116(le)001:14230: thun mong gi rgyud sde rmad du byung pa dag
NK116(le)001:14231: las kyang ches khyad para 'phags pa'i lam 'dira zhugas
NK116(le)001:14233: sa bcu'i byang sems kyi snang basa bsdusa pa'i dbyings kyi longsa skur mjal ba la /
NK116(le)001:14234: thogas pa ma yina te ji ltar snyams na ston pa de yi mtshan dpe'i byad dbyibs ni /
NK116(le)001:14235: rang snang lhun grub kyi sgor ranga bzhina gyi me
NK116(le)001:14236: long dang gzugs brnyan ltar sprul par bkoda pa sangs
NK116(le)001:14237: rgyas la mngon sum du chos mnyan nas mi slob
NK116(le)001:14238: pa'i zung 'jug gi go 'phangs pa myur du 'gro'o
NK116(le)001:14239: // stong ngos ka dag la ltos nas rig pa
NK116(le)001:14240: spros bral du byung ste stong pa'i chos nyid zad
NK116(le)001:14242: snang ngos lhun grub la ltos nas brdos bcas 'od
NK116(le)001:14243: gsal du dngas te zad par byed pa'i tshul gnyis
NK116(le)001:14245: thog mar lta ba ye grol na ma mkha' lta
NK116(le)001:14246: bu ston pa'i tshul de phyir zhes bya ba la
NK116(le)001:14248: don de'i phyir na 'di ni 'gyur ba med pa rdo rje'i lam mchog mthar thug pa ste /
NK116(le)001:14249: gdoda nas rnam par grol ba'i riga pa ka daga
NK116(le)001:14250: 'di ni rnam thar sgo gsum dang ldan te kun
NK116(le)001:14251: nas stong pa ngo bo nyid meda pa'i phyir bsam
NK116(le)001:14253: matshana nyid rdul tsam ma grub pas na blo yi brjod pasa thugsa pa spangs pa gnyis pa /
NK116(le)001:14254: thob bya'i 'bras bu gzhan la smon pa meda la
NK116(le)001:14255: so so rang riga pa'i ye shes la yona tan
NK116(le)001:14256: mtha' dag rdzogas pa gsum pa'o //
NK116(le)001:14257: de lta'i riga pa'ang shesa bya'i yul la mi gnas pasa /
NK116(le)001:14258: nga dang nga yira 'dzina pa'i gang zag dang chosa kyi bdag gnyis dang bral ba /
NK116(le)001:14259: de lasa sgom byed dang bsgom para bya ba meda
NK116(le)001:14260: de gshis ma bcosa par rnal mara bazhaga na rig
NK116(le)001:14261: pa ye shes / tshogs brgyad kyi sbubs nas 'thon te rjena para mthonga ngo //
NK116(le)001:14262: de lta'i chos nyid ranga gi ngo bo gazhana du mi 'gyur ba'i dus na /
NK116(le)001:14263: ma riga pa 'dzina pasa srida para 'khrida mi nus te /
NK116(le)001:14264: sprin gyi rjes su nam mkha' mi 'gro ba bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:14265: brjod bya gting zab pa rnams su so sor rang
NK116(le)001:14266: rig cha de la phung po lnga'i tha snyad kyang
NK116(le)001:14267: grags te / nyi zla kha sbyor las /
NK116(le)001:14268: mi rtog pa'i phung po 'di ltar ste /
NK116(le)001:14269: bsam gtan thams cad 'dus pas na ting 'dzin gyi phung po dang /
NK116(le)001:14270: rig pa nyid zag pa med pa'i phyir rnam par grol ba ye shes kyi phung po dang /
NK116(le)001:14271: de nyid don skye med du snang ba'i phyir na shes rab kyi phung po dang /
NK116(le)001:14272: dri ma rnams sngon du dag pa'i phyir tshul khrims kyi phung po dang /
NK116(le)001:14273: rnam par dag pa thams cad las 'das pa'i phyir rnam par grol ba'i phung po'o //
NK116(le)001:14275: de lta'i don la nang byan chub tshe phyi rola yul dang badga du zhena pa rnams /
NK116(le)001:14276: byed posa ma byas shing semas kyi rnam par rtog
NK116(le)001:14277: pa mthu brtas pa lasa grub pa'i phyir gzhi dang
NK116(le)001:14278: rtsa ba rdul tsam med pa lasa re zhig thams
NK116(le)001:14280: skyes pa tsam nyid lasa skye ba meda par rdzoogs nas grol bar 'gyur te /
NK116(le)001:14281: de lasa gazhana pa'i shes rab kyi rtogas pa yoda mi dgos so //
NK116(le)001:14282: de tsa na klog pa dang 'dzina pa dang bsgoma pa dang bstan bcos brtsam pa dang /
NK116(le)001:14283: de'i don la semas pa la sogs mtha' daga pa
NK116(le)001:14284: blo yisa byas pa'i grub mtha' kun rdzob chu'i ri
NK116(le)001:14285: mo lta bur zhiga par gyur ba'i tshe na phyi
NK116(le)001:14286: snang ba nang rang lus gsang ba sems su 'dus
NK116(le)001:14287: pa'i tshogs pa gsum po rdos bcas las 'das te
NK116(le)001:14288: stong gsal chu zla lta bur rtogs pas snang ba'i
NK116(le)001:14289: chos zad / ri brag dang rtsig pa la thog pa med /
NK116(le)001:14290: sems 'phags pa'i bden pa la gnas pas spyan dang mngon shes la sogs pa thob cing /
NK116(le)001:14291: yang srid las rnam par grol ba ni /
NK116(le)001:14293: 'phags pa'i bden pa mthong ba rgyal ba'i sras /
NK116(le)001:14294: rtogs pa khongs su chud na nam yang bde /
NK116(le)001:14296: de yang stong pa dag mnyam ka dag gi sa
NK116(le)001:14297: la grol na lus kyi 'byung bzhi'i rdul phran kyang
NK116(le)001:14298: ye shes kyi mes sbyangs te na bun yal ba
NK116(le)001:14299: ltar nam mkha'i mthong su cho 'phrul chen po dang
NK116(le)001:14301: rig pa chos sku'i dbyings su 'khyil tshe yida smon
NK116(le)001:14302: meda pa'i sangsa rgyas zhes bya ba de kho na
NK116(le)001:14303: nyid do // de yang rin chen spungs pa las //
NK116(le)001:14304: mi snang rtogs pa med pa yis //
NK116(le)001:14305: snang ba thams cad rang dag nas //
NK116(le)001:14306: thams cad zang ma thal byung du //
NK116(le)001:14307: stong gsal chen po'i rigs su 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:14308: sa chu me rlung 'byung ba bzhis //
NK116(le)001:14309: so so'i nus pa mi snang ba //
NK116(le)001:14310: na bun bzhin du mkha' la dengs /
NK116(le)001:14312: gal te gzhan don du gyur na rdul phran du
NK116(le)001:14313: dengs pa de dag ring bsrel du byin gyis rlabs
NK116(le)001:14315: rtogs pa'i tshad du phyin nas gzhan don gyi rnam
NK116(le)001:14316: g.yengs med pa'i rlung sems rang mal du dengs su
NK116(le)001:14317: bcug pa rnams rdul phran du cung ma phyin yang
NK116(le)001:14318: phung po chung zhing lcing shin tu yang ba la
NK116(le)001:14319: sogs 'byung ste / rig pa zang thal la gom
NK116(le)001:14320: pa ka dag la zim pa las byung ba ni
NK116(le)001:14321: sogs 'byung ste / / mu tig phreng ba las /
NK116(le)001:14322: ka nas dag pa dri ma zad //
NK116(le)001:14323: thog mar byung bas rgyud pa zad /
NK116(le)001:14325: gnyis pa snang ba zad par byed pa thod rgal
NK116(le)001:14326: gyi man ngag ston pa'i khyad par zhes bya ba
NK116(le)001:14328: theg rim dgu'i yang rtse nang gses sems klong gnyis
NK116(le)001:14329: las kyang khyad para 'phags pa ma zad man ngag
NK116(le)001:14330: khregs chod las kyang zab pa bla na med pa'i
NK116(le)001:14332: riga pa rdo rje lu gu rgyud nas lha sku'i
NK116(le)001:14333: bar du rtsal rdzogs shing smin pa'i 'od gsal gyi
NK116(le)001:14334: go ma 'gags pa'i gadngas ji bzhin pa mngona sum
NK116(le)001:14335: du mthonga basa gola sa nyung ba ni /
NK116(le)001:14337: 'di ni rang yul bstan pa las /
NK116(le)001:14339: zang ma nyid du thal byung du //
NK116(le)001:14340: yul dang shes pa'i snang cha la //
NK116(le)001:14341: thad ka so so'i gzhi las grol /
NK116(le)001:14343: phyi 'byung sa rdo ri brag sogs yul snang gi
NK116(le)001:14344: dngos po rdosa bacasa dang nang du nyon mongs kyi
NK116(le)001:14345: dri ma mtha' dag zada par byed pasa na 'byung
NK116(le)001:14346: chena gyi snang ba ye shesa 'oda gasla chena pora
NK116(le)001:14347: dangs par byed pa mi slob pa'i lam 'bras mngona
NK116(le)001:14348: du byed pa 'dis ni gang zhig nang gi 'byung
NK116(le)001:14349: khams khregsa chod kyis sbyangs pa tshad du phyin na
NK116(le)001:14350: lus rdula phrana nyid lasa dangs para 'gro ba yod
NK116(le)001:14351: med kyi 'od lus kyis 'khor ba ma stong bar
NK116(le)001:14352: bzhugs nas phrin las kyi cho 'phrul bsam las 'das
NK116(le)001:14353: pa bkye ba ni ma yin no //
NK116(le)001:14354: gal te tshad du ma 'byong pas de ltar ma
NK116(le)001:14355: nusa pasa kyang 'dir zhugs na gnad kyi mthu snga
NK116(le)001:14357: 'ja' lus 'pho ba chena po rdo rje'i skura smin pa ni /
NK116(le)001:14359: 'khrul ba bzung ba'i yid kyi lus //
NK116(le)001:14360: 'byung ba rang sar sangs pa'i phyir //
NK116(le)001:14361: 'di yang mi snang rang sar yal //
NK116(le)001:14362: rig pas bzung ba'i 'od kyi lus //
NK116(le)001:14364: 'di tshe chos nyid zad dang nye /
NK116(le)001:14366: de nas gazhana dona 'khora ba ma stongsa bar du madzada pa yang /
NK116(le)001:14368: zag pa zad phyir rdos bcas min //
NK116(le)001:14369: dngos por zad phyir stong bar gnas //
NK116(le)001:14370: gnyis med 'phel med ngo bo nyid //
NK116(le)001:14371: chos dang bral ba'i thabs las 'das //
NK116(le)001:14372: rtog med gsal bas 'gyu ba sangs /
NK116(le)001:14373: bem rig gnyis med tshogs gnyis rdzogs zhes so //
NK116(le)001:14374: dngos gzhi nyams len gyi rim pa ni gzhan du
NK116(le)001:14375: shes la man ngag 'di'i khyad chos sgron ma bzhir
NK116(le)001:14377: nam mkha' stong pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK116(le)001:14378: bcas med sgron ma rnam pa bzhi //
NK116(le)001:14379: ma 'gags pa yi don gyis gsal //
NK116(le)001:14380: rig pa dbyings kyi sgron ma ni /
NK116(le)001:14381: nam mkha' stong pa'i dbyings dkyil du /
NK116(le)001:14382: dbyings kyi rang bzhin 'od kyi sku //
NK116(le)001:14384: ye shes lnga ldan thugs kyi sku //
NK116(le)001:14385: lu gu rgyud kyi tshul du 'char /
NK116(le)001:14388: rig pa dbyings kyi sgron ma ru //
NK116(le)001:14389: bcug de rig pa ma 'gul na //
NK116(le)001:14390: 'gyur med rtogs pa rab tu bshad //
NK116(le)001:14391: shes rab rang byung sgron ma ni /
NK116(le)001:14392: sgro 'dogs thams cad gcod pa dang //
NK116(le)001:14393: thig le stong ba'i sgron ma ni //
NK116(le)001:14394: rtsol ba med par shar gyur na //
NK116(le)001:14395: rgyang zhags chu yi sgron ma yis //
NK116(le)001:14396: de la lta ba ma yengs na //
NK116(le)001:14397: mthar phyin sgom pa'i tshad du gsungs /
NK116(le)001:14399: thal 'gyur du dag pa dbyings sgron ma gsungs pa ni //
NK116(le)001:14400: 'di ltar bstan pa'i rig pa dbyings sgron dang don gcig go /
NK116(le)001:14401: de ltar sgron ma bzhi po las rgyang zhags chu sgron ni 'char byed kyi sgo yin te /
NK116(le)001:14402: rig cha'i gdangs phyi rol gyi yul la mthong ba'i rgyang zhes bya la /
NK116(le)001:14403: mthong ba de yang skyes bu yod med kyi rjes
NK116(le)001:14404: su 'ching grol byed pas zhags pa'i sgra zhugs pa'o
NK116(le)001:14405: // dag pa dbyings sgron ni 'char gzhi'i nang dbyings dang /
NK116(le)001:14406: 'char yul gyi phyi dbyings gnyis so //
NK116(le)001:14408: stong gzugs kyi rnam pa sna tshogs 'char ba'o //
NK116(le)001:14409: shes rab rang sgron ni rang rig gi ngo bo lhag mthong ji bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:14411: rnam par zhes pa kun gyi thog mar sbyar la //
NK116(le)001:14415: 'byed byed 4kyi shes rab byed las kyi sgo nas gzhir bzhag pa /
NK116(le)001:14417: de yang rig pa'i ngo bo la //
NK116(le)001:14418: shes rab rnams pa bzhi dang ldan //
NK116(le)001:14419: shes rab rnam bzhi 'di ltar ste //
NK116(le)001:14420: rnam par grol byed shes rab ni //
NK116(le)001:14421: thams cad sgrol bar byed pa'o //
NK116(le)001:14422: nyon mongs dag pa'i zhing du sgrol //
NK116(le)001:14423: rtog med skye med dang du sgrol //
NK116(le)001:14424: ma rig rig pa'i klong du sgrol //
NK116(le)001:14425: shes rab rtog med ngang du sgrol //
NK116(le)001:14426: de phyir sgrol byed shes rab po //
NK116(le)001:14427: rnam par skyod byed shes rab ni //
NK116(le)001:14428: sku lnga ka dag dbyings su skyod par byed //
NK116(le)001:14429: 'od lnga 'dzin med dbyings su skyod par byed //
NK116(le)001:14430: rig pa ye shes dbyings su skyod par byed //
NK116(le)001:14431: sgron ma nam mkha'i dbyings su bskyod par byed //
NK116(le)001:14432: de phyir skyod byed shes rab bo //
NK116(le)001:14433: rnam par sdud byed shes rab ni //
NK116(le)001:14435: nam mkha' sgron ma'i nang du sdud //
NK116(le)001:14436: sku lnga rig pa'i ngang du sdud //
NK116(le)001:14437: rig pa rtog med nang du sdud //
NK116(le)001:14438: de phyir sdud byed shes rab bo //
NK116(le)001:14439: rnam par 'byed byed shes rab ni //
NK116(le)001:14440: ma rig rig pa gnyis su 'byed //
NK116(le)001:14441: nyon mongs ye shes gnyis su 'byed //
NK116(le)001:14442: dag dang ma dag gnyis su 'byed //
NK116(le)001:14444: rtog dang ma rtog gnyis su 'byed //
NK116(le)001:14445: bzang dang ngan pa gnyis su 'byed //
NK116(le)001:14446: de phyir 'byed byed shes rab bo //
NK116(le)001:14449: lhun grub snang ba bzhi rim gyis 'char ste //
NK116(le)001:14451: chos nyid mngon sum snang ba yis //
NK116(le)001:14453: nyams snang gong du 'phel ba las //
NK116(le)001:14454: 'khrul pa'i snang ba nub pa dang //
NK116(le)001:14455: bar do'i ye shes mngon du byed //
NK116(le)001:14456: rig pa tshad phebs snang ba yis //
NK116(le)001:14457: sku gsum rtog pa'i lam snang 'das //
NK116(le)001:14458: chos nyid zad pa'i snang ba yis //
NK116(le)001:14459: khams gsum 'khor ba'i rgyun thag chad /
NK116(le)001:14461: lhag mthong gi rig pa rdo rje lu gu rgyud
NK116(le)001:14462: la bltas pas chos nyid mngon sum gyis zhing khams
NK116(le)001:14463: kyi sgo 'byed // nyams gong 'phel du sprul sku //
NK116(le)001:14465: zad par chos sku'i snang ba mthong ba'o //
NK116(le)001:14466: de yang rnam pa thams cad du bzhag thabs bzhi las mi g.yo ba las /
NK116(le)001:14467: dang po rgya mtsho cog bzhag ni /
NK116(le)001:14469: dbang po'i sgo rnams gsal ba la /
NK116(le)001:14470: yid kyi rtog pa med pa ste /
NK116(le)001:14472: rgya mtsho rlung gis rkyen dang bral ba la gza'
NK116(le)001:14473: skar gcal du bkram pa ltar snang yang chu la
NK116(le)001:14474: der 'dzin med cing gza' skar rang mal nas ma
NK116(le)001:14475: g.yos bzhin du yul snang ma 'gags kyang rig pa
NK116(le)001:14476: zang thal du song bas 'ching ba med do //
NK116(le)001:14477: gnyis pa rig pa cog bzhag ni /
NK116(le)001:14479: dam pa'i don ni blo bral nas /
NK116(le)001:14480: dbang po gcig char grol ba na /
NK116(le)001:14481: rang gi grub pa'i mtha' zhig nas /
NK116(le)001:14482: gang la rten dang 'dzin med par //
NK116(le)001:14483: yang dag chos nyid ro myong nas //
NK116(le)001:14484: khams gsum ldog pa'i rten med par /
NK116(le)001:14485: mkha' la mkha' nyid thim par ltar //
NK116(le)001:14486: rnar 'byor mchog kyang de bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:14487: zhes rang rig klong yang chen po phyi nang mtha'
NK116(le)001:14488: dbus med par gsal ba de tha snyed las 'das
NK116(le)001:14489: shing khams gsum du ldog pa'i zag pa zad do
NK116(le)001:14490: // gsum pa snang ba cog bzhag ni /
NK116(le)001:14492: chos can mtshan mar snang dus su //
NK116(le)001:14493: nga la yon tan rang snang bas /
NK116(le)001:14494: 'di la blangs dang dor mi bya /
NK116(le)001:14495: zhes yul lnga'i snang ba tshon ris ma 'dres pa
NK116(le)001:14496: ltar rig pa'i dngas me long lta bur shar ba
NK116(le)001:14499: rang sa ru mi skyil bar cir snang rgya yan
NK116(le)001:14500: du bsgyur ba'i chos nyid kyi ngang las 'da' ba
NK116(le)001:14501: med do // bzhi pa ri bo cog bzhag ni yi ge med pa las /
NK116(le)001:14502: ri bo cog bzhag lta ba gsang ba nyid /
NK116(le)001:14503: the tshom ma yin 'gyu ba ngang gis med /
NK116(le)001:14505: dgongs pa chos nyid kyi ngang la gnas nas ri
NK116(le)001:14506: bo lta bur mi g.yo ba'i gdengs rnyed pa'i tshe
NK116(le)001:14507: / rkyen snang sna tshogs rlung lta bu'i mi g.yo ba'o //
NK116(le)001:14508: de lta'i gom pa tshad du 'khyol ba'i rtags tshad ni /
NK116(le)001:14510: de lta'i nyams su sus blangs pas /
NK116(le)001:14511: rtags dang tshad na 'di ltar ste /
NK116(le)001:14512: lus ni yang zhing zang thal snang //
NK116(le)001:14513: sa la reg med thog med dang //
NK116(le)001:14514: ngag gi nus rdzogs gtam zung zad //
NK116(le)001:14516: mig dang rna ba sna dang lce //
NK116(le)001:14517: lus kyi dbang po kun zad de //
NK116(le)001:14518: rang bzhin med par gyur bar tshad /
NK116(le)001:14520: de ltar rtags gsum gyi khyad par so sor bshad na /
NK116(le)001:14521: lus rtags rdzogs pas bar dor sa thob la /
NK116(le)001:14522: lus la ngag gi rtags rdzogs na sprul pa'i zhing dang //
NK116(le)001:14523: de gnyis gcig shos kyi steng du sems rtags rdzogs
NK116(le)001:14524: na bar do la skad gcig gsum gyis grol la
NK116(le)001:14525: gsum ka rdzogs na rang don mthar phyin yang snying
NK116(le)001:14526: rje'i gzhan don la dgongs nas tshe lo bye ba
NK116(le)001:14527: brgya stong du byin gyis brlabs te mthar gyis mngon
NK116(le)001:14529: lus dang sems kyi rtags ldan lo bcu nas 'od lus su 'gro zhing /
NK116(le)001:14530: lus ngag yid gsum ka'i rtags dang ldan yang rten
NK116(le)001:14531: des gzhan don mi 'byung ba rnams lo gnyis nas
NK116(le)001:14532: bar do'i 'gro ba sum stong dus gcig du grol
NK116(le)001:14533: bar byas nas 'byung ba rang sar dengs pa yin
NK116(le)001:14534: pa'i tshul sku gdungs 'bar ba las gsungs so //
NK116(le)001:14535: de ltar grol lugs myur bur la tha dad pa
NK116(le)001:14536: las rten de nyid gdod ma'i gnas lugs zhing khams
NK116(le)001:14537: dam pa'i grong khyer du mya ngan las 'das pa
NK116(le)001:14538: dag ni phung po'i zag pa dengs pa'i phyir yang
NK116(le)001:14539: dag par sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK116(le)001:14544: sa g.yo ba'i rtags lnga dang bcas te gshegs pa
NK116(le)001:14545: la mngon pa rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa zhes bya'o
NK116(le)001:14546: // de yang phung po'i zag pa dang bcas pa
NK116(le)001:14547: rnams la'ang ka dag khred chod du grol ba nam
NK116(le)001:14549: lhun grub thod rgal du grol ba me dpung dang rig 'dzin gyi 'chi lugs bzhi las /
NK116(le)001:14551: dbyings la sgribs byed rlung sems kyi dri ma shin
NK116(le)001:14552: tu phra ba'ang dag pas nang dbyings zad sar phyin
NK116(le)001:14553: pas phyi'i lus kyang rdul phran du dengs ba'i mod
NK116(le)001:14554: la / bum nang gi nam mkha' bum pa chags
NK116(le)001:14555: pa'i dus na phyis nam mkha' dang 'dres pa ltar
NK116(le)001:14556: rang bzhin chos kyi dbyings la phung pos bzung ba'i
NK116(le)001:14557: rig pa'i de kho na nyid 'dres pas /
NK116(le)001:14558: dbyings rig dag mnyam tha dad med par sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK116(le)001:14560: mkha' 'gro ma dang rdzus skyes 'chi ba'i dus ro
NK116(le)001:14561: sus kyang mi mthong ba ltar rten lus dang brten
NK116(le)001:14562: pa rigs pa 'dres pa da lta rang yod 'phro
NK116(le)001:14563: lus kyi rdul phran ltar mi mngon par dengs pa'i
NK116(le)001:14564: mod la rig pa'ang dbyings su thim nas phyir mi
NK116(le)001:14565: ldog par dpag chen gyi mda' 'phangs pa lta bu'o
NK116(le)001:14567: rlung sems kyi bslad pa dengs nas rig pa'i thim lugs dang grol ba'i dbyings gcig kyang /
NK116(le)001:14568: bsreg bya bud shing tshig nas bsregs byed kyi me
NK116(le)001:14569: phung kyang mi gnas pa ltar nang 'byung zad pa'i
NK116(le)001:14570: rdos po 'od phung du yal lo //
NK116(le)001:14572: rig 'dzin rnams sa nas sar 'phags pa'i tshe nam
NK116(le)001:14573: mkha' la sgra dang 'od du bcas pas song ste
NK116(le)001:14574: zhing khams gzhan du rdzu 'phrul bsam gyis mi khyab
NK116(le)001:14575: pas gzhan don byed pa ltar rnam smin bag chags
NK116(le)001:14576: skyes kyi lus 'od lus su dengs nas gzhan bstan
NK116(le)001:14577: pa la bzhag pa'i don du skyes bu kun gyis
NK116(le)001:14583: me dpung lta bu rang zad pa dang /
NK116(le)001:14584: mi snang nam mkha' chung lta dang //
NK116(le)001:14586: mi snang mi len 'di lta bu /
NK116(le)001:14587: rnal 'byor rab kyi spyod yul te /
NK116(le)001:14588: 'di la goms pas rang shugs rnyed /
NK116(le)001:14590: de lta na'ang lta sgom snga ma bzhin zad sar 'khyol bar de lta'i nus pa yod kyang /
NK116(le)001:14591: bstan 'gro'i ched du bya ba las kyi 'khor lo
NK116(le)001:14592: bzhes pa las rlung zad par yang ma byas la
NK116(le)001:14593: / tha na gdungs dang ring bsrel tsam gyis kyang
NK116(le)001:14594: sems can la phan phyir rnam par smin pa'i rig
NK116(le)001:14595: 'dzin gyi tshul bsgrub pa yod de //
NK116(le)001:14596: gdod ma'i sangs rgyas kun tu bzang po'i sgyu 'phrul
NK116(le)001:14597: gdul bya'i snang ngor shar ba rigs brgya'i khyab bdag
NK116(le)001:14598: grub pa'i dbang phyug chen po 'jigs med phrin las
NK116(le)001:14599: 'od zer dpal du 'bar ba ste bdag cag gi
NK116(le)001:14600: skyabs gnas dam pa de lta bu'o //
NK116(le)001:14601: de ltar 'byung bzhi zad sar ma khyol na'ang de
NK116(le)001:14602: kho na nyid kyi don mthong ba'i yul gyi mngon
NK116(le)001:14603: zhen dag nas 'jig rten mthun 'jug gi mi bardzi
NK116(le)001:14604: / na na mo sman rim gro la mi re /
NK116(le)001:14605: shi na bdun tshig dang ro bsreg sogs la mi re bas /
NK116(le)001:14606: ri dwags bzhin du mi mi rgyu ba'i 'brog dgon chen por spro /
NK116(le)001:14607: seng ge gang la'ang bag mi tsha ba'i dpes 'chi ba la mi 'jigs /
NK116(le)001:14608: sprang lta gzhi mdo dang rgya lam du shi yang yid chad med /
NK116(le)001:14609: bu chung ltar 'chi mi 'chi'i gtad ra med pa dang bzhi po ldan pa yin ste /
NK116(le)001:14611: de bzhin dbang po 'bring po rnams /
NK116(le)001:14612: ri dwags lta bu'i 'chi lugs te /
NK116(le)001:14614: de bzhin seng ge lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:14615: gang zhig sprang po lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:14616: de bzhin bu chung ltar shi ba /
NK116(le)001:14618: zhes sgyu lus kyi sgong rgya grol ma thag rig
NK116(le)001:14619: pa chos sku'i mkha' la thim nas sprul pa'i 'gro
NK116(le)001:14620: don byed pa seng ge rtsal rdzogs las //
NK116(le)001:14621: sems can kun gyi rang lus la //
NK116(le)001:14622: ye shes dag pa'i ngo bo gnas //
NK116(le)001:14623: rgya che snang ba ma nus te //
NK116(le)001:14624: dper na mngal dang sgo nga'i rgya /
NK116(le)001:14625: mngon du mi 'byung bsgrib gyur kyang //
NK116(le)001:14626: rang rtsal rdzogs nas 'byung ba bzhin /
NK116(le)001:14627: rnam rtog lus 'di bor ma thag /
NK116(le)001:14629: ye nas gnas pa'i rang rig nyid //
NK116(le)001:14630: ngo bo rtogs med mthong bar 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:14631: ye shes dag pa'i snang ba la //
NK116(le)001:14632: sangs rgyas bden par mthong bar 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:14633: ye shes rang snang ngo bo nyid //
NK116(le)001:14634: yid kyi rnam rtog med pa ste //
NK116(le)001:14636: snang ba thad dkar bcad pa'o //
NK116(le)001:14638: zhar byung de las gzhan pa dag la mched grogs
NK116(le)001:14639: kyis gdams ngag tshangs sprug su gsal gdab lugs zab
NK116(le)001:14640: mo ni / pha rol po'i dbugs dang bral dus rang chos nyid kyi dgongs pa gnas pas /
NK116(le)001:14641: de'i kha sna dang rang ngo thad kar sprad la rlung 'gro ldog dum bu gsum gsum las /
NK116(le)001:14642: phar 'phos dus dang po la dkar po //
NK116(le)001:14644: gsum par h'u mthing ka stong pa nyid kyi ngang nas khos snying nang du 'phang zhing /
NK116(le)001:14645: tshur ldog pa'i gsum ka la ngag tu h'u brjod pa dang bsgrag /
NK116(le)001:14646: rgyu zhabs 'ub 'then nas kho'i shes pa h'u mthing
NK116(le)001:14647: ka'i rnam pas drangs te rig pa blo 'das chen
NK116(le)001:14649: de'i tshe pha rol po ming hrig pa dang /
NK116(le)001:14651: skad thon pa byung na ngo sprod gdabs par bya ba'ang /
NK116(le)001:14653: gal te gzhan gyi don byed na //
NK116(le)001:14654: de nyid thugs rjes bzungs pa'i phyir //
NK116(le)001:14655: sgo gsum dag ni sgo sprad pas /
NK116(le)001:14656: dbugs ni gtub dang rdub dang 'phang //
NK116(le)001:14657: yi ge 'bru gsum gzhugs pas ni //
NK116(le)001:14658: lus dang ngag yid stobs bskyed phyir //
NK116(le)001:14659: dbugs dang bcas te mkhas pas bya //
NK116(le)001:14660: de ltar yang dang yang byas pas //
NK116(le)001:14661: de yi snang ba 'di lta bu /
NK116(le)001:14662: gal te lus kyi stobs rnyed nas //
NK116(le)001:14663: gdams pa dag ni gdab par bya //
NK116(le)001:14664: 'on te shes pa gsal gyur na //
NK116(le)001:14665: dgongs pa nyid la mnyam par bzhag /
NK116(le)001:14666: dbang po'i sgo rnams rang drung nas /
NK116(le)001:14667: mig gi de nyid blta ru gzhugs //
NK116(le)001:14668: mnyam par bzhag pa'i sems byung na //
NK116(le)001:14669: mi rtogs ldan pa'i ting 'dzin thob /
NK116(le)001:14671: byed pa po de tsam nus pa min na 'pho ba'i zhing sbyongs pa la 'bad do //
NK116(le)001:14672: 'gro ba phal ba mtho ris su drangs pa'i phyir
NK116(le)001:14673: skye med kyi ye shes la brten nas sbyangs na
NK116(le)001:14674: / kho'i snying nang du a dkar po'am /
NK116(le)001:14675: 'od gong dkar po bsam du bcug la /
NK116(le)001:14676: phar phar song bar dmigs shing byas la /
NK116(le)001:14677: rang bdun pa de la gcur te //
NK116(le)001:14678: rlung phyir 'gro ring po dang bstun nas de'i lo grangs kyi a dbyangs kyi nges pas bzlas te /
NK116(le)001:14679: dbugs chad pa dang spyi bor kha gtad la a
NK116(le)001:14680: nyi shu rtsa gcig brtsegs mar brjod pas sems bskyed
NK116(le)001:14681: dang man ngag gi gnad kyis mtho ris su 'drongs
NK116(le)001:14683: yi ge a yi sbyor ba yi //
NK116(le)001:14684: dbugs dang de yi grangs dang sbyar /
NK116(le)001:14685: gal te de bar ma shi na //
NK116(le)001:14686: spyi bo kha gtad dbugs kyis ni //
NK116(le)001:14687: shes pa lus kyi dkyil du yang //
NK116(le)001:14688: a ni dmigs te bsdu bar bya /
NK116(le)001:14690: de ltar cho ga ldan pa'i tshe //
NK116(le)001:14691: mi de dbugs dang ma bral na //
NK116(le)001:14692: yi ge dbugs dang bcas pa yis //
NK116(le)001:14693: the tshom med par gnas nas sbyongs /
NK116(le)001:14695: de tsam nus pa min na //
NK116(le)001:14696: kho'i rna bar kha gtad la //
NK116(le)001:14697: dkon mchog gi mtshan dang gzung sngags rnams brjod pas
NK116(le)001:14698: phan che ba mdo sde du ma nas gsungs pas
NK116(le)001:14699: shes so // bshad zin pa'i don /
NK116(le)001:14700: de dag gi phyir na phyag rdzogs dbu gsum sogs
NK116(le)001:14701: ranga ranga gi sde basa yida dpyod kyi lam las
NK116(le)001:14702: 'das kyang rung ste lta sgoma spyod 'brasa kun dang
NK116(le)001:14703: ches khyad par zhugsa pa ni //
NK116(le)001:14705: lta ba kun gyi yang rtse ni /
NK116(le)001:14706: a ti rdzogs pa chen por bshad /
NK116(le)001:14707: ces phul du byung bar basngagasa pas na srid pa
NK116(le)001:14708: hrul por byed nus pa 'dod pa rnams kyi matshana
NK116(le)001:14709: nyid legas para phyed para byed pa'i blo gros brang
NK116(le)001:14710: 'og tu 'ubs chub par byas nas mi tshe'i nyi
NK116(le)001:14711: ma nub ri la yol bar bsam gyis mi khyab
NK116(le)001:14712: pa'i gnas 'di la gcig tu gces spras mdzad nas
NK116(le)001:14713: spyod pa rje rang byung rdo rje nyid kyi zhal
NK116(le)001:14714: gdams kyi mana ngaga gi mthar thug pa yina no
NK116(le)001:14716: de ltar na'ang las dang po pa thod rgal du
NK116(le)001:14717: 'jug mi nus par dgongs nas de ltar zhes bya
NK116(le)001:14718: ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:14719: sbyangs pa sngon du song ba'i gang zag dbang po rab rnams chos 'di dang 'phrad nas /
NK116(le)001:14720: da ltar grol moda kyi gzhan pa rnams badga 'dzina glo bura gyi rkyen dag /
NK116(le)001:14721: chos dbyingsa daga pa'i klonga du ma nuba pa yod
NK116(le)001:14722: ring glo bura rkyen gyis bsdu ba'i rtogas tshogas kyi
NK116(le)001:14723: chos tha mala ranga lugsa srida pa'i badga po 'di
NK116(le)001:14724: yisa / dang po'i lasa can rnams la sgrib pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:14725: de'i ched du zhi gansa lhag mthonga ngo bo gciga pa dang /
NK116(le)001:14726: so so pa yi 'khrida tshul gyi gdams ngag rnam pa gnyis lasa /
NK116(le)001:14727: dang po'i phyogsa la gansa cha'i bsam gtan dang gasla
NK116(le)001:14728: cha'i shesa raba zhi lhag zunga du 'brel ba lasa
NK116(le)001:14729: gnyis pa mina pa'i matha'a bral gyi dona la mnyam
NK116(le)001:14730: par bazhaga par bya ba ni /
NK116(le)001:14732: brjod du med pa'i sems nyid la /
NK116(le)001:14733: zhi gnas lhag mthong rang shar bas /
NK116(le)001:14734: mnyam par bzhag dang rjes su ni /
NK116(le)001:14735: mi g.yos bsam gtan nyid du rdzogs /
NK116(le)001:14737: gnyis pa'i phyogsa la'ang dbye ba gnyis gruba ste gang
NK116(le)001:14738: na shes raba lasa byung ba dang gadmas ngaga lasa
NK116(le)001:14740: shesa raba lasa byung ba ni rjod byed kyi sgra
NK116(le)001:14741: gang yin pa de yi rjesa su mthuna para thosa
NK116(le)001:14742: pa'i dona de la rtse gciga du yid dbang gtad
NK116(le)001:14743: cing sems pa ni zhi gansa dang de lasa brjod
NK116(le)001:14744: bya'i dona rtogsa pa gang zhig lhag mthonga gi matshana
NK116(le)001:14745: nyid do // mana ngaga lasa byung ba ni tha
NK116(le)001:14746: snyad las 'das pa dona gyi rjes su 'gro ba'i
NK116(le)001:14747: nyid do // phyir // semsa ni rnam pa thams
NK116(le)001:14748: cad du g.yo ba meda pa zhi gansa yin la
NK116(le)001:14749: nyid do // phyir // / de yi ranga bzhina
NK116(le)001:14750: smra bsam brjod med du shes pa lhag mthonga ste
NK116(le)001:14751: nyid do // phyir // / / de yang 'phags pa dgongs ba nges 'grel las //
NK116(le)001:14752: zhi gnas dang lhag mthong ni gnyis te //
NK116(le)001:14753: shes rab las byung ba dang /
NK116(le)001:14755: shes rab las byung ba ni /
NK116(le)001:14756: mdo sde bcu gnyis kyi tshig yid la byed pa ni /
NK116(le)001:14760: gdams ngag las byung ba ni //
NK116(le)001:14761: man ngag gi sems mi g.yo bar byeed ba ni zhi gnas so //
NK116(le)001:14762: de'i don rtogs pa ni lhag mthong ngo /
NK116(le)001:14764: de yang mdora na gang zag dbang po raba kyis
NK116(le)001:14765: ngana rtog gang shar chos sku'i yo lang 'ba' zhig
NK116(le)001:14766: par lhod pas / bazanga ngana mnyamsa pa nyid du gyur na /
NK116(le)001:14767: gnyen po gzhan nas bstan mi dgos te /
NK116(le)001:14769: ji bzhin ma bcos rgyal ba'i dgongs pa la //
NK116(le)001:14770: sems dang sems byung rtogs pa ci skyes kyang //
NK116(le)001:14771: de nyid skye med ngang du gnas shes pas //
NK116(le)001:14772: bya brtsol mtshan ma'i 'du shes kun dang bral /
NK116(le)001:14774: dbang po 'bring gisa bying rgod bral ba'i lta ba
NK116(le)001:14775: skyed med kyi ngang rang bzhin gyi dwangs pa zhi
NK116(le)001:14776: lhag zung du 'brel ba'i lam gomsa pasa ji zhig
NK116(le)001:14777: na bazanga ngana gyi rtog pa matha'a daga dbyingas su
NK116(le)001:14780: ji ltar bar snang cung zad sprin med las //
NK116(le)001:14781: skad cig du ni sprin gyi dkyil 'khor snang //
NK116(le)001:14782: byung nas zhig ste sprin gyi dkyil 'khor med //
NK116(le)001:14783: thog mar gang las byung pa brtag par bya /
NK116(le)001:14784: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par gyis /
NK116(le)001:14786: tha mas thoga mara zhi gansa 'ab'a zhiga batsala pa'i tshul la /
NK116(le)001:14787: ganga dmigas pa de brtan pa thoba par bya ba ni /
NK116(le)001:14789: dmigs yul la ni sems gtad nas //
NK116(le)001:14790: de rgyun rnam par g.yeng mi bya /
NK116(le)001:14792: de nasa lhag mthonga gi ye shesa so sora rtog pa'i shes rab la brtson pa /
NK116(le)001:14794: zhi gnas grub pas lhag mthong la bslab par bya'o //
NK116(le)001:14796: de ltar goma pa tshad du 'khyol ba na mathara
NK116(le)001:14797: gyi dusa na ji ltar gsera gling du phyin tshe
NK116(le)001:14798: sa rdo'i rnam par rdul tsam mi rnyed par bzhina
NK116(le)001:14799: du / semas dang semas byung rtog pa ganga skyes kyanga //
NK116(le)001:14800: snang semas dbyer meda gzhi grol chena pora 'char bas bsam gtan thun 'jog dang bral ba ni /
NK116(le)001:14802: 'dzin med chos nyid rang gsal bde ba'i klong /
NK116(le)001:14803: rtog med mkha' khyab chos nyid kun la rol //
NK116(le)001:14804: 'dzin pa med pa'i chos nyid rang sar dag /
NK116(le)001:14805: rtog pa med pa'i rang grol bde ba'i shugs /
NK116(le)001:14806: yangs pa med pas rang snang kun la khyab /
NK116(le)001:14807: yang dag chos nyid bde chen sa la gshegs /
NK116(le)001:14809: de ltar bsgom pa'i dus na 'phrang gsal ba'i tshul
NK116(le)001:14810: thabs kyi zhes bya ba la sogs pas gsungs te
NK116(le)001:14811: / tshogs drug yon tan gyi grogs su 'char ba'i thabas kyi choga tu rtog pa ganga shara yanga //
NK116(le)001:14812: dagga para mi bya zhing bsgrub para bya ba yang meda cing /
NK116(le)001:14813: rjes su mi 'brang bar skyed med kyi nganga lasa ma g.yosa na /
NK116(le)001:14814: lha yi miga dang sha'i spyan sogs lnga dang mngona par shes pa drug sogas //
NK116(le)001:14815: dabnga po dangsa pa'i yona tan matha'a daga 'thoba par 'gyur ro //
NK116(le)001:14816: de skad du'ang kun byed las /
NK116(le)001:14817: thog ma tha ma dbus zhi zhing //
NK116(le)001:14818: srid dang mya ngan 'das zhi ba /
NK116(le)001:14819: lhun gyis grub pa'i bde chen te //
NK116(le)001:14820: matshungasapa med pa'i ye shes kyi //
NK116(le)001:14821: rang gi mthu yi rig pa las //
NK116(le)001:14824: rtog pa yula dang 'brel bar gyur na tha mala pa ste /
NK116(le)001:14825: de las ldog na bshad ma thag pa bzhin /
NK116(le)001:14826: me longa lta bura dangsa pa'i shesa pa la /
NK116(le)001:14827: snang yula ma 'aggas par mtsho la gaza'a skar shar
NK116(le)001:14828: bzhina bkra yanga rnama par rtog pa'i blo yisa gos
NK116(le)001:14829: para ma gyur pa'i dus na //
NK116(le)001:14830: gzunga ba'i yul dang 'dzina pa'i semas 'brel chada pasa na //
NK116(le)001:14831: so so ranga riga rnama para mi rtogsa pa'i ye
NK116(le)001:14832: shesa bla ma'i sa la da lta ru phyin par
NK116(le)001:14834: dngos dang dngos med rnam dag nas //
NK116(le)001:14835: sgo lnga'i yul zhen dag pa dang //
NK116(le)001:14836: 'byung lnga'i rags pa dag pa dang /
NK116(le)001:14837: ye shes dag pa'i 'phel snang ston //
NK116(le)001:14838: de las zad pa'i chos nyid do //
NK116(le)001:14840: skabs kyi don bsdu ba ni mdor na zhes bya ba la sogs pas gsungs te /
NK116(le)001:14841: ji skad bshad pa rnams mdora na 'chad 'gyur gyi lam lngar 'du ste /
NK116(le)001:14842: dang po dbyingsa kyi lam ni chosa nyid bsam gyis mi khyab pa gciga pura zad de /
NK116(le)001:14844: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes ni //
NK116(le)001:14845: stong pa chen po yul nyid dang //
NK116(le)001:14846: gsal ba 'od kyi snang ba dang //
NK116(le)001:14847: ye shes rig pa'i spyod yul gsum //
NK116(le)001:14848: de gsum 'dzoms pa'i dbyings zhes bya /
NK116(le)001:14850: gnyis pa riga pa'i lam ni shes raba khyad par cana te //
NK116(le)001:14851: rnam par mi rtogs bzhin du chos thams cad kyi spyi dang /
NK116(le)001:14852: rang mtshan ma 'dres par rig cing rang bzhin zang
