NK116(le)001:14853: ma thal du shes pa gang gis pha rol na
NK116(le)001:14856: shes pas chos rnams cig char rtogs //
NK116(le)001:14857: rab ni kun gyi rtse mor gyur //
NK116(le)001:14860: shes rab chen pos skad cig la //
NK116(le)001:14861: chos kun khong du chud par 'chang //
NK116(le)001:14863: gsum pa 'oda gasla gyi lam ni rgyang zhags chu'i
NK116(le)001:14864: sgrona ma dang thig le stong pa'i sgron ma ste
NK116(le)001:14866: dang po mngal du chags pa'i dus na lte ba'i rtsa mdud kyi nang du sgron ma dang /
NK116(le)001:14867: 'byung ba'i spyan gnyis sngon du chags pa las /
NK116(le)001:14868: phyi mas lus bskyed cing dang po las mig gi dbang rten dbang po /
NK116(le)001:14869: 'od rtsa'i dngas ma gsum byung ba lte ba nas snying ka /
NK116(le)001:14871: de nas rna ba gnyis kyi nang ngos klad rgya dkris nas yal ga gsum du gyes so //
NK116(le)001:14872: de yang mig so so'i a 'bras kyi dkyil du
NK116(le)001:14873: khrag dang chu ser med pa'i rtsa ba man gyi
NK116(le)001:14874: rwa bla 'og log pa lta bu'i nang 'od kyi
NK116(le)001:14875: snal mas khengs shing gdongs kha mig la zug pa'i
NK116(le)001:14876: nang na 'od rtsa re re dang /
NK116(le)001:14877: dbus ma gcig lhag pa tshangs bug la zug pa'i
NK116(le)001:14878: nang na rig pa rtog med lu gu rgyud dang
NK116(le)001:14879: 'od kyi thig le brtsegs ma lnga ldan dgu 'char
NK116(le)001:14880: ba la sgron ma bzhi ka'i cha yod pa'i tshul
NK116(le)001:14881: / rtsa sna ni chu'i sgron ma /
NK116(le)001:14884: shes pa mi rtogs pa ni shes rab kyi sgron ma'o //
NK116(le)001:14885: dbye na 'byung ba 'dus pa'i rgyangs zhags ni rlung gi dngas ma'i rtsa rwa dbyibs lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:14886: snang ba sdud 'dzin mched gsum gyi char gnas pa dang //
NK116(le)001:14887: ye shes 'dus pa'i rgyang zhags ni /
NK116(le)001:14888: 'od gdangs 'khrul snang dag tshe 'od gsal gyi rang snang 'dzin pa dang /
NK116(le)001:14889: dbang po 'dus pa'i rgyang zhags ni mthong byed snang yul rang mtshan par 'dzin pa dang gsum mo //
NK116(le)001:14891: 'khor 'das kyi chos rgyang nas snang ba zhags pa'i
NK116(le)001:14892: byed las ltar 'ching grol byed pa ste lam dang
NK116(le)001:14893: sbyar nas gong du yang bstan no //
NK116(le)001:14895: nang gsal ka dag gi dbyings mtha' bral dri ma
NK116(le)001:14896: med pa'i don la goms pas dbyings la ye ldan
NK116(le)001:14897: du yod pa'i sku gsum gyi snang cha las rlung
NK116(le)001:14898: dag pa'i cha las 'od gsal gyi lam snang du
NK116(le)001:14899: mngon pa ste dbye na lnga las /
NK116(le)001:14900: zhi gnas rig pa'i thig les 'khor 'das kyi gnyis snang gcig tu bzlums /
NK116(le)001:14901: lus gnas rtsa'i thig les sdug bsngal bde chen du 'char /
NK116(le)001:14902: kun rdzob rgyu'i thig les phung khams ro gcig tu sdud /
NK116(le)001:14903: don dam spros med kyi thig les dbyings rig mnyam par sbyor /
NK116(le)001:14904: rang byung 'bras bu'i thig les nyin mtshan 'od gsal
NK116(le)001:14905: du 'dres pa'i rgyal ba'i dgongs pa rgya grol klong
NK116(le)001:14907: bzhi pa khregas chod kyi lam ni shar grol dusa mnyam pa ste /
NK116(le)001:14908: gzhi yul med du rtogs pa'i dus na gshis ka
NK116(le)001:14909: dag las mi 'gyur bas rtsa ba ji ltar g.yo
NK116(le)001:14910: yang / snang ba gzhi med du /
NK116(le)001:14913: chos zad ming med du go ba bzhi rdzogs so //
NK116(le)001:14914: de yang rtogs lugs zang thal du rtog pa dang /
NK116(le)001:14915: grol lugs ka dag du grol ba dang //
NK116(le)001:14916: thob lugs rang mal du thob pa gsum la gdengs
NK116(le)001:14917: rnyed nas de'i ngang du goms par byed pa'i gnad
NK116(le)001:14918: gsum las mi g.yo bar bya ste /
NK116(le)001:14919: 'di ltar rang bzhin med pa'i zang thal du blta /
NK116(le)001:14920: shar grol mnyam pa'i chig chod du bzhag /
NK116(le)001:14921: blo las 'das pa'i zad sar bskyel ba'i tshul /
NK116(le)001:14923: rig pa nyid kyi gnas lugs tshe /
NK116(le)001:14924: grol lugs rtogs lugs thob lugs so //
NK116(le)001:14925: skye med yul la gnas pa'i tshe //
NK116(le)001:14926: lta thabs bzhag thabs bskyel thabs so //
NK116(le)001:14928: lnga ba thod rgal gyi lam ni dbyingsa dang riga
NK116(le)001:14929: pa yina te nang dbyings gong du bstan zin la
NK116(le)001:14930: / phyi dbyings nam mkha' dag pa ste /
NK116(le)001:14931: 'od gsal lam du byed dus dbyings kyi ra bar
NK116(le)001:14932: chos nyid kyi gdangs dbang po dngas pa'i yul la
NK116(le)001:14933: shar ba'i rig pa rdo rje lu gu rgyud kyi
NK116(le)001:14934: ngo bo sdud pa'i rnam dag dbyings kyi sgron ma
NK116(le)001:14936: rnam dag dbyings kyi sgron ma ni //
NK116(le)001:14937: rig pa ye nas ngo bo sdud //
NK116(le)001:14938: lu gu rgyud kyi dra bar snang /
NK116(le)001:14939: 'di la sus goms don de nyid //
NK116(le)001:14940: mthing ga mi 'gyur rang gsal ba //
NK116(le)001:14941: mu khyud kyi ni ra bar gnas //
NK116(le)001:14942: rang gsal phyi yi yul snang du //
NK116(le)001:14943: ngo bo nyid ni ma bcos pa'o /
NK116(le)001:14947: gzhi la gnas pa'i dag dbyings kyis //
NK116(le)001:14948: rig pa'i ye shes sku ru 'dzin //
NK116(le)001:14949: lam la snang ba'i dbyings kyis ni //
NK116(le)001:14950: rig pa'i thig le'i dngas ma sdud /
NK116(le)001:14951: yul la snang ba'i dbyings kyis ni //
NK116(le)001:14952: lu gu rgyud de brtson du 'dzin //
NK116(le)001:14955: 'byung 'gyur skal bar ldan pa'i gangazaga rnams lam mchog
NK116(le)001:14956: 'di la 'jug par bskul ba 'di dag ces bya
NK116(le)001:14957: ba la sogs pa gsungs te //
NK116(le)001:14958: tshul 'di daga ni ranga bzhina rdzogas pa chena po
NK116(le)001:14959: yi thuna mong ma yina pa'i lam mchog lnga ste
NK116(le)001:14960: kun mkhyen nyi ma'i gnyen gyi rang lugs mtha' dag
NK116(le)001:14961: pa las ches rab tu phul du byung bar tshe
NK116(le)001:14962: gcig gis srid pa tha mar 'dod pa rnams kyis
NK116(le)001:14963: mkhyen par 'atshala nasa thog med nas ma riga pa'i
NK116(le)001:14964: grogas dang lhan gcig par 'grogs te phyin ci log
NK116(le)001:14965: tu 'khrul ba'i bslu brid kyis khrid de mu matha'a
NK116(le)001:14966: meda pa 'khora ba'i 'broga dgona mi bzod pa'i 'jigas
NK116(le)001:14967: su runga ba skyi g.ya' zhing ya nga ba'i rgyar
NK116(le)001:14968: mi dge bcu'i lasa dang nyon mongsa pa brgyad khri
NK116(le)001:14969: bzhi stong gi 'du byed kyi lcagsa sgrog dam po
NK116(le)001:14970: btab pas 'chor ba srid pa tsam du zad pa
NK116(le)001:14971: gang gisa / dus de ringa phana chad du rnam
NK116(le)001:14972: par bcingas pa la skyo ba'i semas drag po ri
NK116(le)001:14973: gzar gyi rbabs lta bu bskyed nas zhi ba dama
NK116(le)001:14974: pa bde ba chen po'i gronga khyer du myur du
NK116(le)001:14975: mya ngana las 'adsa nas sku bzhi'i rgyal sa zin
NK116(le)001:14976: pa'i thabs sam lam gyi mchoga 'di nyid la bsnyen
NK116(le)001:14978: deng sang thos bsam gyi blo gros bzang po'i snang bas ring du spangs te gti mug /
NK116(le)001:14979: rmad du byung ba'i smag rum du tshud nas yang
NK116(le)001:14980: dag pa'i don la ce re long bzhin rang rig
NK116(le)001:14981: gsal stong tsam du go yul du byas nas nga
NK116(le)001:14982: ni rdzogs pa chen po'i rnar 'byor pa chos nyid
NK116(le)001:14983: mngon sum du rtogs te myang 'das la mi re
NK116(le)001:14985: snyigs ma'i dbang gi lus rgyal ba gong ma bzhin du ma gyur na'ang /
NK116(le)001:14986: rtog pa de tsho dang mnyam pa'i phyir ji srid
NK116(le)001:14987: lus rgya ral ma thag tu bum pa chag pa'i
NK116(le)001:14988: nam mkha' bzhin du chos sku'i sar gshegs pa yin
NK116(le)001:14989: no zer nas chang nag la rang dgar spyad nas
NK116(le)001:14990: spyod pa hrul po byed pa 'ga' zhig dang //
NK116(le)001:14991: yang grub mtha' gang rung na bka' babs rig 'dzin
NK116(le)001:14992: brgyad kyis brnag pa'i badudartsi sgrub sde'i skor rnams rngon
NK116(le)001:14993: pa'i lag cha ltar byas nas grong gseb du sems
NK116(le)001:14994: can gyi sha khrag dron mo dmar tse re bas
NK116(le)001:14995: dkon mchog mchod par yin par rlom nas mu stegs
NK116(le)001:14996: rgyang 'phen gyi cho ga la yang dag par byang
NK116(le)001:14997: chub pa rnams kyi ni sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa
NK116(le)001:14998: rin po che'i ljon shing rtsa ba nas 'don pa'i
NK116(le)001:14999: bdud kyi rgyog rdo btsan po ldog pa med par
NK116(le)001:15000: mtha' gcig du nges par snyam te mchi ma 'khrug
NK116(le)001:15002: de yang shin rta chen po klu grub kyis /
NK116(le)001:15003: da ni shin tu ngan pa'i mis /
NK116(le)001:15004: rgyal ba'i bstan pa nub tu nye //
NK116(le)001:15005: da ni ma basngagasa ngan spyod dang //
NK116(le)001:15006: log par lta ba ngan pa'i mi //
NK116(le)001:15007: rmongs pa dag gis bcom ldan gyi //
NK116(le)001:15008: bstan pa'i ljon shing bcad kyis med //
NK116(le)001:15009: da ni snying rje med pa yis //
NK116(le)001:15010: chos lugs bor zhing rang bzo byed //
NK116(le)001:15011: bskam chags pha rol mi mthong bas //
NK116(le)001:15012: bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan bsnyil gyis med /
NK116(le)001:15013: da ni gdul dka' ngo tsha med //
NK116(le)001:15014: sdig la dga' zhing tshul 'chos byed //
NK116(le)001:15015: sdig can rnams kyi thub pa yis //
NK116(le)001:15016: bstan pa'i zam pa bcag gis med //
NK116(le)001:15017: da ni mgo bregs nyams mi len //
NK116(le)001:15019: ngan g.yo can gyi thub pa yi //
NK116(le)001:15020: bstan pa'i tshong dus bcom gyis med //
NK116(le)001:15021: da ni khro da nga nga rgyal dang //
NK116(le)001:15022: rgyag chos byed cing rnyed la zhen //
NK116(le)001:15023: sdig pa sna tshogs byed pa'i mis //
NK116(le)001:15024: chos kyi gru bo bcag gis med //
NK116(le)001:15025: da ni thub pa'i bstan pa yang //
NK116(le)001:15026: cung zad tsam zhig lus par zad //
NK116(le)001:15027: thub pa'i bstan pa gangs can mtsho //
NK116(le)001:15028: ring por mi thog skam par 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:15029: seng ge'i sgra yi bstan pa 'di //
NK116(le)001:15030: dus kyi 'khor los rab bcom nas //
NK116(le)001:15033: bde 'dod rnams kyis phan pa'i don //
NK116(le)001:15034: da ni legs par brtags pa'i rig /
NK116(le)001:15035: dus kyi 'khor lo ngan byed pa //
NK116(le)001:15036: ma rab shes rab 'chal ba dang //
NK116(le)001:15037: tshul 'chal dag gis brten mi shes //
NK116(le)001:15038: nyes pa bsten zhing tshul khrims sdangs //
NK116(le)001:15040: mi mkhas slab nyes slob dpon nor //
NK116(le)001:15041: gdug rtsub nga rgyal brnyes pa che //
NK116(le)001:15042: ngan pa'i mi la yid rton pas //
NK116(le)001:15043: sangs rgyas bstan pa ma rung byas //
NK116(le)001:15044: zhi zhing bde ba'i dus ni zad //
NK116(le)001:15045: gdug rtsub mi bzad dus ni 'byung //
NK116(le)001:15046: shes rab can gyi mi rnams dang //
NK116(le)001:15047: dpang gyur skye bo rnams ni zad //
NK116(le)001:15048: de lta'i dus rnams byung ba'i tshe //
NK116(le)001:15049: rang gi yul 'khor gnas spangs te //
NK116(le)001:15050: gzhan gyi ljongs su phyin nas su //
NK116(le)001:15051: der yang nags 'dabs dben pa ru //
NK116(le)001:15052: smra ba bsnyungs te gnas par bya //
NK116(le)001:15053: zhes bya ba'i dus la bab par 'dug pas thar
NK116(le)001:15054: ba 'dod pa rnams kyis gtan gyi phongs tsheng gi
NK116(le)001:15055: 'dun ma la rnam rig ma bsgribs par ltar snang
NK116(le)001:15056: chos brgyad kyi rdzig rdzig rngam pa tsam la yid
NK116(le)001:15057: ston te rgyal ba'i mdo rgyud kyi gzhung rnams la
NK116(le)001:15058: thos bsam byed pa dgra ru bltas nas tshe 'di'i
NK116(le)001:15059: che thang gi bya ba bsgrub tshugs la zhugs pa'am
NK116(le)001:15060: // gal te dben par bsgom lo byed kyang srid
NK116(le)001:15061: rtse'i grub mtha' snyogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin ni shes
NK116(le)001:15062: rab kyi pha rol du phyin par 'khrul nas mi
NK116(le)001:15063: tshe bul ba dag la ba lang rdzi bo sangs
NK116(le)001:15064: rgyas su blta ba 'di ni mi rigs te /
NK116(le)001:15066: stobs 'byor nor rdzas la sogs 'di snang gi /'dun ma 'ba' zhig sgrub la rtag 'cha' ba //
NK116(le)001:15067: zas gtsang sras kyi sprul par grags gyur kyang //
NK116(le)001:15068: 'dun ma'i 'gram chu snying nas ga la ldang /
NK116(le)001:15070: tshe 'dir sbyangs shing mkhas la tha mal zer //
NK116(le)001:15071: thos bral ma bslab skyes bu dam par blta //
NK116(le)001:15072: gser dang snag tsha barje ba'i rgyal khams 'di //
NK116(le)001:15073: yul dbus zer yang kla klo'i grong khyer 'dra /
NK116(le)001:15075: kha gcig rmi lam gsal ba'am //
NK116(le)001:15076: mngon shes phra mo shar ba dang //
NK116(le)001:15077: gzugs med sgra las legs nyes shes pa dang //
NK116(le)001:15078: mkha' 'gro ma'i lung bstan tsam thob pa la mngon
NK116(le)001:15079: par rlom shing khengs par yang bdud kyi dbang du
NK116(le)001:15082: gal te byang chub sems dpa' gzhan gyis lung bstan rlom //
NK116(le)001:15083: rloms sems gnas pa de yi blo chung shes par bya //
NK116(le)001:15084: ming gi gzhi las bdud ni nyer bar longs gyur nas /
NK116(le)001:15085: 'di skad smras te 'di ni khyod dang pha ma dang /
NK116(le)001:15086: khyod kyi bdun mes brgyud kyi bar gyi ming yin zhing //
NK116(le)001:15087: gang tshe khyod ni sangs rgyas 'gyur ba'i ming 'di yin //
NK116(le)001:15088: sbyongs sdom rnal 'byor ldan pa ci 'dra 'byung gyur la /
NK116(le)001:15089: khyod sngon yon tan tshul yang 'di 'dra'o zhes brjod do //
NK116(le)001:15090: de skad gang thos rloms sems byang chub sems dpa' ni /
NK116(le)001:15091: bdud kyi yongs su bslangs zhing blo chung rig par bya /
NK116(le)001:15093: lar rnal 'byor pa'i nyams la ye shes rnam par
NK116(le)001:15094: dag pa'i mkha' 'gro ma ni 'jig rten du mi
NK116(le)001:15095: 'byung la / sha za las kyi mkha' 'gro mas rnal 'byor pa'i nyams sad pa yod do //
NK116(le)001:15096: de'i tshe lung ston pa la bden 'dzin ma byas
NK116(le)001:15097: par spros bral du bzhag na mkha' 'gro ma bdag
NK116(le)001:15098: gi dbang du gyur pas las thams cad 'grub cing
NK116(le)001:15100: de la rlom sems skyes na bdag mkha' 'gro ma'i dbang du gyur pa ste //
NK116(le)001:15101: bdud kyi bslu brid yin pa bshad zin pas shes so //
NK116(le)001:15102: de bas na grogs po tsho //
NK116(le)001:15103: bstan pa thams cad 'gal med du rtogs nas /
NK116(le)001:15104: gsungs rab ma lus gdams ngag du shar te /
NK116(le)001:15105: yin lugs phu thag chod pas chos nyid rang zhal 'jal ba'i bar /
NK116(le)001:15106: phyogs re tsam ma yin par mdo rgyud kyi gzhung
NK116(le)001:15107: ji snyed nas thos bsam gyi blo gros na 'phar
NK116(le)001:15108: ba ra byed pa'i mtshan ldan gyi bla ma'i mdun
NK116(le)001:15109: sar tshe gcig myang 'das la snyogs pa'i gdam ngag
NK116(le)001:15110: cig nang byan chub par byas te phyi nas srid
NK116(le)001:15111: pa'i nyes mang brgya phrag mang po'i btson rwa la
NK116(le)001:15112: mi 'jigs pa'i btsan sa zhig 'dzin par byed pa'i
NK116(le)001:15113: dus la de ring nas bab pa'o //
NK116(le)001:15114: yon tan rin po che'i mjod kyi le'u bcu gnyis pa'i 'grel ba'o ////
NK116(le)001:15115: da ni 'bras chos gtan la dbab par bya ba la gnyis te //
NK116(le)001:15116: rang gi chos nyid las gzhan du ma yin pa'i tshul dang //
NK116(le)001:15117: sku dang ye shes kyi rang bzhin bye brag du bshad pa'o //
NK116(le)001:15118: dang po ni de ltar zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:15119: de ltar gzhi dang lam gyi matshana nyid legas par rtogsa nasa /
NK116(le)001:15120: mathara phyin pa'i dus kyi thob rung gi 'bras bu sku dang ye shesa gang zhig ni /
NK116(le)001:15121: gazhana lasa ma byung par kuna gzhi'i rnyogsa pa dangsa
NK116(le)001:15122: nas semas dang semas byung chosa kyi dbyingsa su zhi
NK116(le)001:15123: ba yina no // ci'i phyir na gong du rgya
NK116(le)001:15124: cher bshad pa ltar 'khor 'das ganga du'ang ma nges
NK116(le)001:15125: pa'i dus lhun grub kyi gzhi lasa gzhi snang g.yosa
NK116(le)001:15126: ba yina no // pa yi / badga 'dzina baga chagas shesa bya'i yul dang /
NK116(le)001:15127: shes byeda yul can gyi cha 'dzina pa'i tshogas brgyad
NK116(le)001:15128: nyer lena gyi dri ma sprin dang 'dra ba rnams
NK116(le)001:15129: kyi ka dag bsgrib pa yin te nam zhiga rnam
NK116(le)001:15131: mkhyen pa gnyis ldan gyi ye shesa nyi ma lta bu ni /
NK116(le)001:15132: sgrib pa meda pa ranga bzhina gyi 'od du gasla ba yin te /
NK116(le)001:15134: nyes pa glo bur dang ldan dang /
NK116(le)001:15135: yon tan rang bzhin nyid ldan phyir //
NK116(le)001:15136: ji ltar sngar bzhin phyis de bzhin /
NK116(le)001:15137: 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid do //
NK116(le)001:15139: rang bzhin 'od gsal zhes brjod nyi dang mkha' bzhin glo bur gyis /
NK116(le)001:15140: nyon mongs shes bya'i sprin tshogs stug po'i sgrib pa las ni grol gyur bas /
NK116(le)001:15141: dri med sangs rgyas yon tan kun ldan rtag brtan g.yung drung sangs rgyas nyid /
NK116(le)001:15142: de ni chos la mi rtogs rnam 'byed ye shes dag la brten pas thob /
NK116(le)001:15146: sku lnga ye shes chos rab lta /
NK116(le)001:15149: sangs rgyas sku lnga'i bdag nyid ca na /
NK116(le)001:15150: khyab bdag ye shes lnga yi bdag /
NK116(le)001:15152: ye shes lnga dang 'brel ba'i sku lnga'i mtshan nyid las /
NK116(le)001:15154: glo bur zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:15155: ngo bo ye nas spros pas dag pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15156: glo bura gyi dri ma cha dang bacasa pa spangs shing dag pa ste /
NK116(le)001:15157: daga pa gnyis ldan byang chub mchoga gi dngosa po //
NK116(le)001:15158: gdoda ma'i sangsa rgyas smon pa meda pa'i chos dbyingsa te //
NK116(le)001:15159: ji ltar nya rgyas zla ba spros pa de snang ba'i yul phyira gsal ba cana /
NK116(le)001:15160: stong gi cha la mi snang ba'i dbyingsa su nuba pa ltar /
NK116(le)001:15161: rnam pa kun tu mi rtog pa'i chosa nyid 'pho
NK116(le)001:15162: 'gyur meda pa ni nam mkha'i dbyingsa kyisa mtshon pa
NK116(le)001:15163: te rtag pa mi 'gyur rdo rje'i sku'o //
NK116(le)001:15165: spros bral chos nyid 'gyur ba med //
NK116(le)001:15166: mtha' dang dbus med phyogs cha bral /
NK116(le)001:15167: rang snang chos dbyings rnam dag cing /
NK116(le)001:15168: dang po'i sangs rgyas rgyu med pa //
NK116(le)001:15169: tha ma rkyen gyis bskyed du med //
NK116(le)001:15170: stong pa ye shes snying po can //
NK116(le)001:15171: mtha' la mi gnas rdo rje'i sku /
NK116(le)001:15174: dbyings kyi dag pa rdo rje'i sku //
NK116(le)001:15178: de lta'i rnam pa kuna gyi mchoga ldan zhi ba'i dbyingsa na //
NK116(le)001:15179: stobsa sogas yona tan rgya mtsho kun ma btsal lhun
NK116(le)001:15180: gyis grub par 'ub chuba kyang snang cha ngo bora
NK116(le)001:15181: ma 'dresa par me long la phra phab pa ltar
NK116(le)001:15182: gsal zhing spang rtog gnyis kyi cha nas gzhal ba
NK116(le)001:15183: mngona para byang chub pa'i sku ste /
NK116(le)001:15185: phra rab rdul gyi chos nyid 'das //
NK116(le)001:15186: phra phab pa yi rang bzhin ni //
NK116(le)001:15187: rnam pa kun gyi mchog ldan ma //
NK116(le)001:15188: phyag rgya chen po de la 'dud /
NK116(le)001:15191: dri ma bral phyir byang ba ste //
NK116(le)001:15192: yon tan rgyas pas chub pa nyid //
NK116(le)001:15194: mngon par byang chub skur brjod do //
NK116(le)001:15197: shes bya don dam pa'i yula la blo yi 'jug pa zhi zhing /
NK116(le)001:15198: shes byed blo la 'dzina pa'i kuna rdzob spangas nas /
NK116(le)001:15199: so so ranga gi riga pa rtag chad kyi mathara
NK116(le)001:15200: ma lhung zhing rtsal snang dbyings la dengs pa'i phyir
NK116(le)001:15201: thima pa la ma rmugsa phra ba'i ye shesa ni
NK116(le)001:15202: ji lta ba don dam mkhyen pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15203: ji snyed kun rdzob mkhyen pa'i cha 'aggas pa meda pa sku dang ye shesa thams cad kyi rten /
NK116(le)001:15204: shina tu mnyam par bazhaga pa ste mi slob pa'i
NK116(le)001:15205: sa la gnas pa rnams kyis mthonga byar gyur pa
NK116(le)001:15206: ganga la zhi ba chosa kyi sku zhesa brjod pa
NK116(le)001:15208: ches phra'i ye shes nang du gsal /
NK116(le)001:15209: dmigs med 'char gzhi chos kyi sku //
NK116(le)001:15212: dbyings su 'khyil bas mthong du med //
NK116(le)001:15213: med pa min te phra ba'i phyir //
NK116(le)001:15214: tshes kyi sngon rol zla ba bzhin /
NK116(le)001:15215: zab pa zhi ba ches phra ba'o //
NK116(le)001:15218: gting gsal chen po'i gzhi mar bzhugs //
NK116(le)001:15219: khyab dang khyab pa nyid kyi stong //
NK116(le)001:15220: phyang nas chad pa med snang ba //
NK116(le)001:15221: gsal byed snang ba'i chas ma 'gags /
NK116(le)001:15223: de ltar dbyings kyi sku gsum po ni stong pa
NK116(le)001:15224: nyid gang du'ang ma grub pa'i dngos po med pa'i
NK116(le)001:15225: ngo bo nyid du gnas pa'i tshul so so zhes
NK116(le)001:15226: bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:15227: so so ranga gi riga par bya ba rgyal ba'i khamas bde gshegs snying po ni //
NK116(le)001:15228: gciga dang du mar ma yina par dngosa po dang /
NK116(le)001:15229: dangos meda lasa 'adsa shing mkha'a ltar rnama par mi
NK116(le)001:15230: rtogsa cing mtshan mas gosa pa meda cing rnam par
NK116(le)001:15231: 'gyur ba'i spros pa thams cad zhi zhing /
NK116(le)001:15232: ngaga gi spyod yula du 'adsa te dona dama bdena pasa bsdus phyir /
NK116(le)001:15233: rtog dpyod dang tha snyad dang gtan tshigas kyis mi mtshona /
NK116(le)001:15235: snyam byed shes pa dang dpe dpe can dang 'agla ba'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:15236: sa bcu'i dabnga phyug gi yanga spyod yul mina pa ni /
NK116(le)001:15238: ngag yul min phyir don dam gyis bsdus phyir /
NK116(le)001:15239: rtogs gnas min phyir dpe las 'das pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:15240: bla na med phyir srid zhis ma sdus phyir /
NK116(le)001:15241: rgyal yul 'phags rnams kyis kyang bsam mi khyab /
NK116(le)001:15243: chos kyi dbyings su ji ltar bzhugs tshul /
NK116(le)001:15244: 'dren pa zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:15245: 'drena pa'i mchog sangs rgyas rnams la mngona suma gyur
NK116(le)001:15246: pa'i gnas gting mtha' mi dmigs phyir zaba cing rang
NK116(le)001:15247: bzhin rnam par dag pa'i zhi ba dngas gsal gzhona
NK116(le)001:15248: nu bum pa'i khanga mdzesa kyi nang na /
NK116(le)001:15249: dusa gsuma sangsa rgyasa rnams ni rtag tu bzhugas kyang /
NK116(le)001:15250: rnam pa'i cha nasa gciga gisa gciga mi gzigas te /
NK116(le)001:15251: ranga bzhina spros bral gyi dbyingsa na dgongsa pa'i klong gciga tu 'khyil ba ni /
NK116(le)001:15253: chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang na /
NK116(le)001:15254: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad gcig gis gcig mi gzigs pa'i tshul gyis bzhugs te /
NK116(le)001:15257: bstan bshad gnyis kyi dang po ni /
NK116(le)001:15258: mkhyen cha zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:15259: de lta bu'i mkhyen cha 'aggas pa meda pa'i ranga
NK116(le)001:15260: gadngas lasa thugas rje phyir gasla longas spyod rdzogas pa'i
NK116(le)001:15261: sku ni // gansa dang dus dang ston pa dang
NK116(le)001:15262: chosa dang 'khora te ngesa pa lnga ldana gyi sku
NK116(le)001:15264: matshana dpe yona tan rgya mtsho'i badga nyid cana no //
NK116(le)001:15265: gnyis par so sor bshad pa la zhi khro gnyis
NK116(le)001:15266: las dang po'i phyogs gnas ni zhes bya ba la
NK116(le)001:15268: dang po gansa ni ma btsal yon tan lhun gyis
NK116(le)001:15269: grub par rdzogas pa 'oga mina stuga po bkoda pa'i
NK116(le)001:15270: zhing khams // ye shesa lnga yi rang mdangs kyi
NK116(le)001:15271: 'oda zer gsal 'tshera 'abra ba ji ltar mkha'a dbyingsa
NK116(le)001:15272: dbang po'i mtshona cha ste 'ja' tshon gyisa bakaba pa
NK116(le)001:15273: zhing khams // bzhina du / manna na nema zhing
NK116(le)001:15274: btegsa na 'aphara ba lta bu'i gazhala meda khanga mdzesa
NK116(le)001:15275: phyogs bzhir sgo 'aphara rnam pa bzhi dang ldan pa
NK116(le)001:15276: zhing khams // bzhina du / / rta rkang rnam pa brgyad ldana ye shesa lnga'i rtsigsa pa /
NK116(le)001:15277: pha gu dra phyed dang mad'a yaba dang pu shu
NK116(le)001:15278: can gyi snam bura 'doda pa'i yona tan gyi miga
NK116(le)001:15279: yangas ma ste lha mo sna tshogs kyi bde stong
NK116(le)001:15280: gi mchoda sprin brtse zhing dag'a ba'i phan tshun dang
NK116(le)001:15281: rnam 'gyur g.yo ba cana rnams dang /
NK116(le)001:15283: 'aphana gdugas rgyal matshana nora bu'i rtog can bla bre dang za ra tshagsa dang //
NK116(le)001:15284: gatsanga khanga byur bura mdzesa shing /
NK116(le)001:15286: srida du ste phan tshun dang thog tha mi mngona
NK116(le)001:15287: par ganga du ltas pa'i snang yul gang zhing grangsa
NK116(le)001:15289: nam mkha'a dbyingsa snod du gyur pa bzhina no //
NK116(le)001:15290: rten gzhi gazhala med khanga pa re re'i nang na /
NK116(le)001:15291: rten pa'i gtso bo rgyal ba rigs lnga yi gadna khri ni /
NK116(le)001:15292: rang snang ba'i cho 'phrul mi 'jigs 'phrog byed seng ge dang /
NK116(le)001:15295: dbang zlos gara cana rma bya thogs pa med pa shang shang te 'u rnams kyi khri'i steng na /
NK116(le)001:15296: gos pa med pa chu skyes te pad+ma dang /
NK116(le)001:15297: rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba nyi ma dang zla
NK116(le)001:15298: ba'i gdan gyi steng na dkyil 'khor gyi bdag po
NK116(le)001:15299: rnams bzhugs so // gnyis pa dus ni /
NK116(le)001:15300: 'das ma 'ong da lta te dusa gsuma bzhira rdzogas
NK116(le)001:15301: dus bzhi mnyams pa nyid dam kun tu bazanga po'i
NK116(le)001:15302: dus so // gsum pa ston pa ni /
NK116(le)001:15303: gdod nas 'pho 'gyur bral ba'i matshana rdzogas kyi ston pa lnga ni /
NK116(le)001:15304: rnama par snang madzada mi bskyod rdo rje rina chen 'gyur ldan /
NK116(le)001:15305: snang ba mtha' yas sam 'oda matshana stong 'abra //
NK116(le)001:15306: dona yoda grub pa dang lnga ni //
NK116(le)001:15312: sgron ma ste lnga dang bacasa pa rnams la kha sbyor bdun gyi badga nyid chena pora bzhugs pa'o //
NK116(le)001:15314: rgyal ba ranga nyid lasa mi gazhana pa'i semas dapa'a brgyad dang semas ma dang bcas pa'i 'khora dang //
NK116(le)001:15315: de bzhin sgo ba bzhi dang de bzhina so so'i yum bzhi dang bcas pa'o //
NK116(le)001:15317: ranga bzhina rdzogas pa chena po'i chos kyi 'khora lo ni /
NK116(le)001:15318: sgra tshiga matshana ma'i yul lasa 'adsa para bskor ba ni //
NK116(le)001:15319: ji ltar rmi lam gyi tshig bzhin skye med kyi dgongs pa 'pho ba kho na'o //
NK116(le)001:15320: de yang 'chad 'gyur khro bo'i gzhal med khang gi
NK116(le)001:15321: steng khanga na zhi ba byang chub snying po'i gansa
NK116(le)001:15322: bshad ma thag pa de nas /
NK116(le)001:15323: 'khor 'das yongs la dabnga bsgyur madzada pa zhi ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis lasa /
NK116(le)001:15324: dama pa'i stang dpyal gnyis te //
NK116(le)001:15325: kun bzang yab yum gnyis ni dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi sprul gzhi ste /
NK116(le)001:15326: kuna la khyab para badla pa'i chosa kyi sku ni /
NK116(le)001:15328: 'gro druga so so'i gansa su dona madzada pa'i /
NK116(le)001:15329: riga pa'i skyes bu thuba druga ni sprul para shara ro //
NK116(le)001:15330: ranga snang longas sku'i zhing na snga ma brgyad kyi lhag ma sum cu rtsa bzhi ste /
NK116(le)001:15331: gtso bo rigs lnga yab yum bcu la lhag ma
NK116(le)001:15332: nyer bzhi'i 'khora gyi tshul du bzhugs shing zhi tshul
NK116(le)001:15333: dgu dang ldan pa gang zhig yul gshed du grub
NK116(le)001:15334: pa mi sems te rang gi phung po khamsa dang
NK116(le)001:15335: / skye mcheda gansa su daga pa'i lha ste /
NK116(le)001:15336: gadna gsuma tshangas pa'i dkyil 'khora chena po kho na yina no //
NK116(le)001:15338: bi ma'i rin chen sgron ma las kyang //
NK116(le)001:15339: mi gnas chos dbyings dkyil 'khor na //
NK116(le)001:15340: kun bzang yab yum zhes bya bzhugs /
NK116(le)001:15341: de las longs sku bzhengs pa ni /
NK116(le)001:15342: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas yin par grags //
NK116(le)001:15343: sprul pa'i mgro don spyod pa na /
NK116(le)001:15344: rdo rje sems dpa' rdo rje 'dzin /
NK116(le)001:15345: grangs med dpag gi mi lang ngo //
NK116(le)001:15347: tshul 'di daga ni sgyu 'phrul dra ba dang sangs
NK116(le)001:15348: rgyas mnyam sbyor dang 'dus rgyud snga phyi gnyis la
NK116(le)001:15349: sogas pa'i bla meda kyi rgyud lasa lusa grub kyi
NK116(le)001:15350: dkyil 'khora ni / ji snyed cig bstana pa dang rnam daga tu mtshungas pa yina no //
NK116(le)001:15351: gnyis pa'i phyogs ni 'og khang zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:15352: snga ma gang de'i 'oga khanga tshogas chena 'dusa pa'i pho brang ni 'dus pa mdos ston na /
NK116(le)001:15353: shin tu rngams zhing 'abra ba'i gazhala yasa khang phyi nang rima pa dgu dang ldan pa la /
NK116(le)001:15354: sgo khyamsa yang de bzhin dgu yod pa'i phyi ma'i sgo so so'i steng na rgyu 'brasa kyi /
NK116(le)001:15355: rta babas gnyis dang ldana pa sogs sgrub sde'i thig
NK116(le)001:15356: chog tu gsal ba ltar pho brang dbus ma'i nang
NK116(le)001:15357: gi 'og gzhi rdo rje brag chen gtam pa mu
NK116(le)001:15358: khyud rim pa gsum las dang po pad+ma dmar po
NK116(le)001:15359: 'dab ma stong bardal ba'i gzhi la /
NK116(le)001:15360: thabas shes nyi zla brtsegs pa'i gdan steng gang der dabnga phyug khyo shugas ni //
NK116(le)001:15361: nyi shu rtsa bzhi pho mo byi chings su rdzogs
NK116(le)001:15362: steng du dapa'a gtum stag /'jigas byed senga ge gdug
NK116(le)001:15364: gtum pa doma dang stobsa chena glang po che dang /
NK116(le)001:15365: brjid pa'i ma he 'dzina pa'i chu srin dang /
NK116(le)001:15366: zhe sdang lto 'gro ste byol songa gtso bo brgyad re resa /
NK116(le)001:15367: dregsa pa pho mo bzung zhing barjisa pa'i steng na /
NK116(le)001:15368: 'khora 'adsa kuna gyi spyi dapala bcoma ldana 'adsa //
NK116(le)001:15369: che ba'i che mchoga he ru ka dpal mdog in+d+ra n+ai la'i lhun po'i madngas la /
NK116(le)001:15370: nyi ma bye ba'i 'oda kyis 'khyud pa'i gzi brjid
NK116(le)001:15371: dang ldana pa la dbus dang g.yas g.yon so sor
NK116(le)001:15372: bduna tshan gsuma gyi zhala can /
NK116(le)001:15373: zhabas brgyad g.yas brkyang g.yon bskum gyis 'gyid ba /
NK116(le)001:15374: g.yas g.yon phyag ni bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis na /
NK116(le)001:15375: zhi ba'i lha tshogas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ni yab
NK116(le)001:15376: rnams g.yas dang yum rnams g.yon du bsnamsa shing ngom
NK116(le)001:15377: pa'o // gnam zhala dbyings kyi yuma mchoga dbang phyug ma yang sngon mo dbu dgu phyag bco brgyada /
NK116(le)001:15378: rtsa ba'i phyag gnyis rdo rje dang dunga khrag 'dzina cing //
NK116(le)001:15379: lhag ma gansa yuma gyi ma mo dang phra mena brgyad brgyad bsnamsa pas /
NK116(le)001:15380: yaba yuma khro makhara te bla 'og gi tshul la mnyam para sbyor te /
NK116(le)001:15381: srida dang zhi ba'i chosa khamas ma lus pa thams
NK116(le)001:15382: cad bcoma ldana 'adsa kyi zhabsa kyi gadna khri nasa
NK116(le)001:15383: / dabu rgyan 'khora lo'i bar la ranga bzhina gyis rdzogs pa'o //
NK116(le)001:15384: 'dir gdan la khyo shugs nyi shu rtsa gcig zhes
NK116(le)001:15385: rtsa 'grel du bris 'dug kyang rtsa rgyud kun 'dus
NK116(le)001:15386: rig pa'i lung shing rtar drangs pa /
NK116(le)001:15387: pad+ma'i steng nyi ma nyi shu rtsa bzhi dang /
NK116(le)001:15388: zla ba nyi shu rtsa bzhi kha sbyor du bkod
NK116(le)001:15389: pa la dbang phyug po nyi shu rtsa bzhi dang
NK116(le)001:15390: / mo nyi shu rtsa bzhir rdzogs par mthong ngo /
NK116(le)001:15392: rje gter chen 'gyur med rdo rje'i sgrubs thabs dngos grub char 'bebs las kyang de ltar snang zhing /
NK116(le)001:15393: bdag cag gi skyabs mgon bla ma'i'agrela par yang /
NK116(le)001:15394: lha klu gza' gsum brgyad tshan gsum du gsung phyir /
NK116(le)001:15395: kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po nyid rdo rje 'chang dang /
NK116(le)001:15396: dgongs pa mi gnyis pas 'khrul par ga la srid kyang /
NK116(le)001:15397: bar gyi skabs su zhu dag pa rnams blo gros
NK116(le)001:15398: kyi mig rgyangs thung bas nor ba yin snyam mo
NK116(le)001:15399: // 'o na che mchog 'dus pa'i rtsa rgyud du
NK116(le)001:15400: yab che mchog gis yum khro mo gnam zhal ma
NK116(le)001:15401: la dgyes pa chen po'i mdangs kyis gzigs te /
NK116(le)001:15402: yum gyi sku la dgyes pa chen pos mchod pa phul pas /
NK116(le)001:15403: yum gyi mkha' las byang chub kyi sems kyi 'od
NK116(le)001:15404: zer las sprul ba'i khro bo bsam gyis mi khyab
NK116(le)001:15405: pa phyogs bcu thams cad du 'phros pas 'jig rten
NK116(le)001:15406: gyi dregs pa can lha chen po nyi shu rtsa
NK116(le)001:15407: gcig la sogs pa thams cad bsgral te zhes 'dug
NK116(le)001:15409: de ni 'khor gyi gdan bshad skabs yin no //
NK116(le)001:15410: 'o na der gtso bo'i gdan la lha brgyad klu
NK116(le)001:15411: brgyad bsnol ba'i gdan zhes bcu drug las med pa'i
NK116(le)001:15412: phyir mtha' gcig tu ma nges mod ce na /
NK116(le)001:15414: 'dir 'grel bar drangs pa'i lung gi dgongs pa gtso bor byed dgos te /
NK116(le)001:15415: rtsa 'brel ya 'dzol du mkhas pas 'chad par mi rig pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:15416: dbus kyi mu khyud gnyis par gtso bo'i mdun phyogs
NK116(le)001:15417: su dabnga mchoga he ru ka mthing nag dbu dgu
NK116(le)001:15418: dang phyag bco brgyad zhabs bzhi pa /
NK116(le)001:15419: yum khro mo dbang phyug ma dang sbyor ba ni pad nyi ru tra'i gdan la rol ba'o //
NK116(le)001:15420: he ru ka dapala dagu las mu khyud gsum par
NK116(le)001:15421: snga ma'i mdun du badz+ra he ru ka mthing nag
NK116(le)001:15423: zhabs bzhi yum kro ti shwa ri ma dang sbyor pa dom zung gi gdan la rol ba'o //
NK116(le)001:15428: las kyi khrag mthung bzhi phyogs mdog mtshams bzhi rak+sha /
NK116(le)001:15430: gu ya yak+sha he ru ka rnams phyogs mdog /
NK116(le)001:15431: dkar pa'i mdangs la dmigs gsal nub byang du kha'o //
NK116(le)001:15432: dbu phyag zhabs snga ma ltar la //
NK116(le)001:15433: rang rang gi rigs kyi yum dang sbyor ba /
NK116(le)001:15436: stag gzig zung gi gdan gyis lhag pa las pad+ma
NK116(le)001:15437: dang nyi zla brtsegs pa la dregs pa khyo shug
NK116(le)001:15439: glo 'bura bzhi dang gru chada rnama pa bzhi ste brgyad la /
NK116(le)001:15440: rnama shes tshogas brgyad gnas su daga pa koo r+ai la sogas brgyad dang /
NK116(le)001:15441: dkyil 'khora dang po'i zhes dbus ma'i khyamsa la dur khrod brgyad gnas su dag pa phra mena brgyad /
NK116(le)001:15442: de bzhin gnyis pa'i khyamsa la phyogs mtshams kyi dngos po gnas su dag pa phra mena brgyad /
NK116(le)001:15443: de bzhin gnyis pa'i khyamsa la phyogs mtshams kyi dngos
NK116(le)001:15444: po gnas su dag pa spora ma rnam pa brgyad
NK116(le)001:15445: dang / gsuma pa'i khyamsa la rgal tshigs gnas su dag pa dabnga mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad de /
NK116(le)001:15446: kuna la ranga ranga gi sgo ba bzhi re gzhal
NK116(le)001:15447: yas khang gi sgo bzhira ldana pa bsdoms pas bcu
NK116(le)001:15449: dang po dang gnyis pa ni /
NK116(le)001:15452: rta phag seng spyang gi gdong can bzhi dang //
NK116(le)001:15453: dkar mo mig gcig rgyas 'debs ma /
NK116(le)001:15454: ser mo las mkhan tshe 'phel ma //
NK116(le)001:15455: dmar mo za byed dbang bsdud ma /
NK116(le)001:15456: nag mo ral gcig rmongs byed ma bzhi'o //
NK116(le)001:15457: phyi ma ni bzhugs pa'i khyad par las dmigs bsal med do //
NK116(le)001:15458: 'di yang rtsa 'grel gnyis na sgo ba /
NK116(le)001:15459: zhes par 'dug kyang yig nor du song pa'o //
NK116(le)001:15460: de dag sku gsung thugs shin tu 'abra ba'i rnam rola can sku sgegs 1dpa' 2'jigs 3rung //
NK116(le)001:15462: thugs snying 1rje 2rngams zhi 3ste gara dgu'i nyamsa kyis
NK116(le)001:15463: brjid pa 'di daga ranga snang longas spyod rdzogs sku'i
NK116(le)001:15464: dkyil 'khora te / gzhi ka dag gi snang cha
NK116(le)001:15465: ye nas lhun gyis grub pa dona gyi 'oga mina
NK116(le)001:15467: 'dir bshad pa'i gdan dregs pa nyer bzhi la sogs
NK116(le)001:15468: pa rang rgyud pa yin nam zhe na min te
NK116(le)001:15469: / gdul bya de ltar gdul pa'i rten 'brel gyi
NK116(le)001:15470: sgo dbyings snang la lhun grub tu shar ba yin
NK116(le)001:15471: / no // de'i phyi rol du gzhan snang gis
NK116(le)001:15472: bsdus pa'i dkyil 'khor la phrin las myur mgyogs kyi
NK116(le)001:15474: sgrol ba ging gi pho nya'i dkyil 'khor bzhi las /
NK116(le)001:15475: dang po dkyil 'khor bzhi pa'i 'khyamsa la so dang
NK116(le)001:15476: rus pa'i dngos po gnas su dag byed mkha'a 'gro
NK116(le)001:15478: mkha' 'gro so so'i mgor smos la shar du bde byed ma /
NK116(le)001:15505: rus pa'i phreng ba can ma dang bdun no //
NK116(le)001:15507: lho sgor gshin rje rnam 'joms ma /
NK116(le)001:15508: nub sgor d+ha sha g+h+ri wa /
NK116(le)001:15509: byang sgor 'bod sgrogs ma dang bzhi /
NK116(le)001:15510: gnyis pa lnga ba'i khyamsa la /
NK116(le)001:15511: shar du rdo rje kun grags ma /
NK116(le)001:15513: lhor rdo rje kun gsal ma dang /
NK116(le)001:15515: nub tu rdo rje 'od chags ma dang /
NK116(le)001:15517: byang du rdo rje g.yu'i sgron ma ste ma bduna dang //
NK116(le)001:15518: shar sgor gling bzhi mgyogs ma /
NK116(le)001:15519: lhor sgor mkha' la khyung lding ma /
NK116(le)001:15521: byang sgor nag mo sder can ma ste sring mo bzhi'o /
NK116(le)001:15522: gsum pa druga pa'i khyamsa la gur rtsib bco brgyad
NK116(le)001:15523: gnas su dag byed ging chena drug tshan gsuma ni
NK116(le)001:15524: / rdo rje so so'i mgor sbyar ba'i /
NK116(le)001:15538: rna nyan phra ma mkhan dang /
NK116(le)001:15542: khro bo ging ka ra dang /
NK116(le)001:15543: khro mo dbang sdud ma gnyis bka' nod pa'i tshul gyis shar nub tu gnas so /
NK116(le)001:15547: dam tshig rgya mtsho'i dkyil 'khor gsum las /
NK116(le)001:15548: dang po khyams bduna para rus mgo tshig mgo'i dngos
NK116(le)001:15549: po gnas su dag byed khro bo yaba yuma bcu
NK116(le)001:15550: phrag drug ni / rnam par rgyal ba dang snyem ma /
NK116(le)001:15551: dbyung sngon can dang sder mo /
NK116(le)001:15552: gshin rje gshed dang dur khrod ma /
NK116(le)001:15553: mi g.yo ba dang gtun khung ma /
NK116(le)001:15555: gzhan gyi mi thub pa dang mda' snyem ma //
NK116(le)001:15556: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa dang rlung 'byin ma /
NK116(le)001:15557: khams gsum rnam rgyal dang gsod byed ma /
NK116(le)001:15558: stobs po che dang bskyod byed ma h'u mdzad sgra 'byin ma /
NK116(le)001:15559: rdo rje phur bu dang rgyas 'debs ma //
NK116(le)001:15562: rdo rje gnod sbyin dang yag mo //
NK116(le)001:15563: khro bo dmar nag dang dbang bsgyur ma //
NK116(le)001:15564: khro bo sa 'og dang sa 'og ma //
NK116(le)001:15566: ma h+aa ka la dang ra sgreng ma /
NK116(le)001:15567: mi 'chi thabs sbyor dang 'joms chen ma //
NK116(le)001:15568: gu lang dang las kun ma //
NK116(le)001:15569: rab rngams dang gtum chen ma //
NK116(le)001:15570: 'jig rten gsum snang dang mi pham ma //
NK116(le)001:15571: 'jig rten gsum 'dul dang lcags kyu ma //
NK116(le)001:15572: rngams chen dang dbang sdud ma //
NK116(le)001:15573: 'jig rten gsum 'jigs dang khro gnyer can //
NK116(le)001:15574: 'jig rten gsum 'ching dang zhags pa ma //
NK116(le)001:15575: khro bo pad rgyal dang ro lang ma //
NK116(le)001:15576: khro bo be con dang lcags sgrogs ma //
NK116(le)001:15577: rdo rje tho ba dang za byed ma //
NK116(le)001:15578: badz+ra ka ta ri dang ral gcig ma //
NK116(le)001:15579: rdo rje go cha dang dril bu ma rnams //
NK116(le)001:15580: phyogs mtshams brgyad du gsum gsum dang /
NK116(le)001:15581: shar nub gyi nang dang sgo bzhir zung re re gnas so //
NK116(le)001:15582: gnyis pa khyams brgyada para rtsa mang po'i dngos po
NK116(le)001:15583: gnas su dag byed pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu
NK116(le)001:15584: ste shar phyogs su 'jigs byed chen po'i sku'i pho
NK116(le)001:15586: lho phyogs su yon tan gyi pho nya mo drug
NK116(le)001:15587: cu nub phyogs su gsung gi pho nya mo druga
NK116(le)001:15588: cu byang phyogs su phrin las kyi pho nya mo
NK116(le)001:15589: drug cu'o // gsum pa dgu pa'i khyamsa la sha
NK116(le)001:15590: khrag gi dngos po gnas su dag byed sku'i 'od
NK116(le)001:15591: zer smug nag las las byed kyi pho nya mo
NK116(le)001:15592: ma mo druga cu rnams ni loga 'drena 'dul phyir
NK116(le)001:15594: bgegas sogas gdula bya so so'i ranga ngora snang ba
NK116(le)001:15595: de'i phyir khyams gsum pa yan chad ltar ranga snang
NK116(le)001:15597: de lta'i zhing khams rang ngo'i sgrib pa las grol
NK116(le)001:15598: stobs kyi yon tan las byung tshul chos sku'i zhes
NK116(le)001:15599: bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:15600: zhing de ni chos sku'i ye shes kyi snang cha
NK116(le)001:15601: phyi ru gasla ba'i gadngas las shar ba phuna tshogas
NK116(le)001:15602: lnga ldan longas spyod rdzogsa pa'i gnas bshad ma thag
NK116(le)001:15603: pa de dag ganga mi slob lam du sgrib pa
NK116(le)001:15604: matha'a daga spangsa bar gyur ba'i mthar thug gi sangsa
NK116(le)001:15605: rgyas kho na'i rgyud kyis bsdus pa yi /
NK116(le)001:15606: rola ba nyid kyi phyir gtso 'khora mchoga damna med
NK116(le)001:15607: par mnyamsa pa kun gyi thugas kyang rnam para mi
NK116(le)001:15608: rtogsa shing / gsung ni brjod bral sku ni matshana dpera rdzogas te /
NK116(le)001:15609: ranga snang ye shes mthonga ba daga pa'i sangs rgyas
NK116(le)001:15610: kyi spyan gyis phan tshun gciga gisa gciga la gzigas
NK116(le)001:15611: shing nama yanga sgrib pa meda pa'o //
NK116(le)001:15612: de ltar dus gsuma rgyal ba rnams kyi spyod yul ni /
NK116(le)001:15613: bla na meda phyir srid zhisa ma bsdusa pa'i phyir na /
NK116(le)001:15614: daga pa'i semas can chena pos dang po nas bcu
NK116(le)001:15615: pa'i bar gnas pa rnams kyis kyang mthonga bar mi
NK116(le)001:15616: nus te / rgyal ba'i ye shesa dang 'agla ba'i
NK116(le)001:15617: shes sgrib phra mos bzhags pa'i bag chags kyi cha
NK116(le)001:15618: da dung ma spangsa pa'i phyir ro //
NK116(le)001:15619: de yang rgyud bla ma las //
NK116(le)001:15620: bla med ye shes thugs rje che sogs yon tan gyis //
NK116(le)001:15621: yon tan pha rol phyin pa'i rgyal ba bsam mi khyab /
NK116(le)001:15622: des na rang byung rnams kyi tha ma'i tshul 'di ni /
NK116(le)001:15623: drang srong chen po dbang thob rnams kyis kyang rig min /
NK116(le)001:15625: 'adsa dang ma 'onga da lta dusa gsum gyi /
NK116(le)001:15626: ngesa pa lasa 'adsa pa 'oga mina chena po'i zhing
NK116(le)001:15627: na bzhugs pa'i sangsa rgyas dusa bzhi'i badga nyid cana
NK116(le)001:15628: / gtso 'khora ngo bo tha mi dad par mthuna pa'i ranga snang ngo //
NK116(le)001:15629: lnga pa sprul pa'i sku la /
NK116(le)001:15630: bstan bshad gnyis kyi dang po ni /
NK116(le)001:15631: de nyid ces bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:15632: bshad zin pa'i zhing de nyid kyi dang lasa sems can gdula ba'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:15633: 'dula byed ston pa gsum du bkoda pa ni /
NK116(le)001:15634: ranga bzhina sprul ba dang 'gro 'dula sprul ba dang /
NK116(le)001:15635: sna tshogas sprul ba dang gsuma mo //
NK116(le)001:15636: gnyis pa so sor bshad pa las rang bzhina ni /
NK116(le)001:15638: ji ltar sprin med nam mkha'i zla ba'i gzugs /
NK116(le)001:15639: ston ka'i chu sngon mtshor ni mthong ba ltar /
NK116(le)001:15640: de bzhin rgyal sras rnams kyi khyab bdag gzugs /
NK116(le)001:15641: rdzogs sangs dkyil 'khor nang du mthong bar 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:15642: zhes rgyal ba'i ye shesa kyi snang ba 'oga mina gyi /
NK116(le)001:15643: dbyingsa snang longas sku'i dpe byad dwangsa shela ji bzhin
NK116(le)001:15644: pa'i nanga na 'phosa pa lta bu'i gzugas brnyan phyed
NK116(le)001:15645: sprul longas sku'i gansa ston pa la gnas dang /
NK116(le)001:15650: sbyangs bya ste rnam pa drug las /
NK116(le)001:15651: dang po ni dbus na zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te //
NK116(le)001:15652: de yang dbus na dbang phyug chen po'i 'oga mina dang /
NK116(le)001:15653: shar na mngona para dga' ba /
NK116(le)001:15654: lho na dapala dang ldana pa /
NK116(le)001:15656: byang na lasa raba grub pa rnam pa lngar gnas so //
NK116(le)001:15657: gnyis pa ni gzugs kyi zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:15658: gzugsa kyi rgyal po rnam snang la sogsa pa'i khung na /
NK116(le)001:15661: snang mtha' don grub te ston mchoga lnga po dbus
NK116(le)001:15662: nas rim pa bzhin bzhugs pa gang zhig matshana dape
NK116(le)001:15663: yona tan rgya mtsho'i badga nyid cana te /
NK116(le)001:15664: de yang drin len bsab mdo las /
NK116(le)001:15665: 'di lta ste zhabs kyi mthil mnyams shing gang ba yin /
NK116(le)001:15666: zhabs kyi mthil na 'khor lo rtsibs stong dang ldan pa yod pa yin /
NK116(le)001:15667: phyag sor phral ring ba yin /
NK116(le)001:15668: zhabs kyi rting ba zlum la gang ba yin /
NK116(le)001:15669: phyag sor kyi bar dra bar 'brel ba yin /
NK116(le)001:15670: phyag dang zhabs 'jams shing gnyen pa yin /
NK116(le)001:15671: zhabs byin pa ri dwags kyi rgyal po e na ya ltar zlum la shugs kyis gzhol ba yin /
NK116(le)001:15672: zhabs kyi longs su phyir mi snang ba yin /
NK116(le)001:15673: phyag pus mor slems pa yin /
NK116(le)001:15674: rta'i rgyal po ltar mtshan ma sbubs kyi nang nas phyir mi snang ba yin /
NK116(le)001:15675: shing nya gro d+ha ltar sku'i yan lag yongs su rdzogs pa yin /
NK116(le)001:15676: sku ba spu gyen du nyal ba yin /
NK116(le)001:15677: ba spu re re nas g.yas su 'khyil ba yin /
NK116(le)001:15678: sku mdog gser btso ma ltar 'dug pa yin /
NK116(le)001:15679: rtag pa'i 'od 'dom gang dang ldan pa yin /
NK116(le)001:15680: pags pa gnyen zhing 'jam la rdul dang dri ma mi gos pa yin /
NK116(le)001:15681: gnas bdun yongs su gang ba yin /
NK116(le)001:15682: sku'i stod seng ge ltar 'dug pa yin /
NK116(le)001:15683: phyag gi lag sor zlum la shugs kyis gzhol ba yin /
NK116(le)001:15684: sgrogs rus mnyam par gang ba yin /
NK116(le)001:15685: sku'i stod smad 'byes pa'i mtshan dang ldan pa yin /
NK116(le)001:15686: zhal gyi tshems bzhi bcu ldan pa yin /
NK116(le)001:15687: tshems gyi thag bzang mnyams pa yin /
NK116(le)001:15688: tshems kyi mdog dkar ba yin /
NK116(le)001:15689: 'gram pa ri dwags kyi rgyal po seng+ge ltar gang ba yin /
NK116(le)001:15690: bro ba'i mchog dang ldan pa yin /
NK116(le)001:15691: sha'i do ker gyi mtshan dang ldan pa yin //
NK116(le)001:15692: ljags ring la yangs pa yin /
NK116(le)001:15693: tshangs pa'i sgra dbyangs dang ldan pa yin /
NK116(le)001:15694: spyan gyi mdog mthon mthing ltar 'dug pa yin /
NK116(le)001:15695: spyan khyu mchog gi rgyal po ltar 'dug pa yin /
NK116(le)001:15696: smin mtshams mdzod spu dkar po dang ldan pa yin /
NK116(le)001:15701: ltag pa'i phyogs ste gnas bdun sku shas gang ba'i tshul can dang /
NK116(le)001:15702: sha'i do ker ni gtsug gtor bltar mi mngon pa'o //
NK116(le)001:15703: dpe byad brgyad cu yang mdo sde'i don /
NK116(le)001:15704: sen mo zangs kyi mdog lta bu dmar skya dang /
NK116(le)001:15705: sen mo'i mdog snum pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15706: shang shong med cing mthong ba dang /
NK116(le)001:15710: sku lus kyi rtsa mi mngon pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15712: zhabs kyi long bu mi mngon pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15713: ring thung med pa'i mnyams pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15714: mi zil gyis gnon pa la mkhas pa seng+gesa stabs su gshegs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15715: klu zil gyis gnon pa la mkhas pa glang po che lta bur gshegs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15716: nam mkha' la 'byon pa bya ngang pa'i stabs su gshegs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15717: sems can gyi 'dren pa la mkhas pa khyu mchog gi stabs su gshegs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15718: bskor phyogs kyi man ngag dang mthun pa g.yas su blta shing gshegs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15719: blta na sdug cing mdzes par gshegs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15720: mi g.yo ba drang por gshegs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15721: sha rgyas shing 'gying legs pas 'khril chags par gshegs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15722: gtsang zhing dag pa'i sku phyi dor byas pa lta bur dang /
NK116(le)001:15723: sku ring thung sbom phra sogs thad kar ma 'chol bas rim par 'tshams pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15724: sku rnyogs pa zhi ba'i gtsang ba dang /
NK116(le)001:15725: 'jams pa dang rnam par dag pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15726: mtshan yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15727: sku'i khyon che bas kho lag yongs su rdzogs shing bzang ba dang /
NK116(le)001:15728: goms pa dal myur snyoms pa dang //
NK116(le)001:15729: dri ma ra ri med pas spyan gnyis dag pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15730: sku gzhon sha chags pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15731: sku zhum pa med pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15734: yan lag dang nying lag rnam par 'byes pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15735: glo bur gyi dri ma dang bral ba'i gzigs pa rnam par dag pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15737: rked skabs 'tshams pa'i skabs phyed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15738: rked pa ha cang ring pa ma yin pas sku ma rnyong pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15739: sku'i phyal phyang de bas mtho dman med pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15740: lte ba zab cing g.yas phyogs su 'khyil ba dang /
NK116(le)001:15741: spyod lam kun nas blta na sdug pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15742: sku gsung thugs kun spyod gtsang ba dang /
NK116(le)001:15743: sku la rme ba dang gnag bag med pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15744: phyag shing bal ltar 'jams pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15745: phyag gi ri mo mdangs gsal ba dang /
NK116(le)001:15746: rgyangs ring mo nas gsal ba'i zab pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15747: phyag gi ri mo ring ba dang /
NK116(le)001:15748: zhal ha cang mi ring ba dang /
NK116(le)001:15749: zhal la gzugs kyi gzugs brnyan snang zhing mchu spros bim pa ltar /
NK116(le)001:15751: ljags ring zhing mnyen pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15753: dmar pa dang gsung 'brug ltar sgrog pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15760: shangs kyi gzeng mtho ba dang /
NK116(le)001:15761: zag pa med pas dag cing gtsang ba dang /
NK116(le)001:15764: dkar nag ma 'dres pa pad+ma'i 'dab ma ring ba lta bur rdzogs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15769: phyag ring zhing rgyas pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15771: de'i dbang po ma nyams pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15772: skra mtsham dod pas dpral ba legs par 'byes pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15774: dbu gdugs ltar rgyas pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15775: dbu skra bung ba ltar gnag pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15776: go 'tsham med par stug pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15781: thugs dkar dpal gyi be'u dang /
NK116(le)001:15782: phyag zhabs kyi mthil la ri mo gru bzhi pa bkra shis dang /
NK116(le)001:15783: des mthar srin lag la sogs pa'i gsham du ri
NK116(le)001:15784: mo bdun g.yas su 'khyil ba g.yung drung 'khyil bas
NK116(le)001:15787: zhi ba dang khro bo'i rnam 'gyur dapaga tu meda cing bsam gyi mi khyab pa yod do //
NK116(le)001:15788: gsum pa ni ye shes zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:15789: ye shesa rnam pa lnga po re re la'ang nang
NK116(le)001:15790: gses su so sor bzhi bzhi'i 'khora dang bacasa pasa
NK116(le)001:15792: chos dbyingsa ye shesa g.yo ba med pa ni /
NK116(le)001:15793: nam mkha'i gzugsa bzhina shesa bya'i mtha' lasa 'adsa shing /
NK116(le)001:15794: me longa ye shesa gzunga 'dzina gyi rdul bral ba ni rtsol ba dang /
NK116(le)001:15795: mngona para 'du byed pa med bzhin yon tan sna tshogs mcheda pa'i gzhi gyur la /
NK116(le)001:15796: mnyam nyid ye shes chosa rnams kuna la dngos po dang matshana nyid med cing /
NK116(le)001:15797: srida zhi dbyer meda zhi ba'i dbyingsa su chams kyis bzhugas pa yin la /
NK116(le)001:15798: sora rtogsa ye shesa chosa nyid ji lta ba dang /
NK116(le)001:15799: chos cana shes bya ji snyed pa rtag tu thoga pa med par mkhyen cing /
NK116(le)001:15800: bya grub ye shesa 'phrin lasa gazhana phana cana /
NK116(le)001:15801: chagas pa dang thoga pa spangsa pa'i madzada pa lhun gyis gruba pa ste /
NK116(le)001:15803: me long ye shes mi g.yo ba /
NK116(le)001:15804: ye shes gsum ni de la brten /
NK116(le)001:15805: mnyam nyid ye shes so sor rtog /
NK116(le)001:15806: bya ba grub pa kho na'o /
NK116(le)001:15808: bzhi pa ni 'khor ni zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:15809: zhing des 'khora ni gzhan rgyud pa ste sa bcu'i
NK116(le)001:15810: byang chub sems dpa' 'ab'a zhiga yin la ston pas
NK116(le)001:15811: sku yi chosa rnams 'ajala ba'i mod la 'oda bkye
NK116(le)001:15812: basa / ji ltar byad kyi dri ma me longa nang du gasla ba ltar /
NK116(le)001:15813: rang sa'i shes sgrib ston pa'i mtshan dpe'i dwangs shel
NK116(le)001:15814: la snang ba ltar rig nas da dung badga dang
NK116(le)001:15815: ston pa'i khyad par mthonga nas /
NK116(le)001:15816: byang chuba kyi sgrib pa gting dapaga par shin tu
NK116(le)001:15817: daka'a ba daga brtson pas sbyangsa nas bcu gciga kuna
NK116(le)001:15820: 'og min bla med gnas mchog tu /
NK116(le)001:15821: sku ni rnam par snang mdzad tshul /
NK116(le)001:15822: byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor rnams la /
NK116(le)001:15823: de bzhin gsungs mchog mi smra te /
NK116(le)001:15824: sku yis chos rnams 'jal bar ston /
NK116(le)001:15825: me long bstan pa'i tshul bzhin du /
NK116(le)001:15826: dngos kyi mdog ngan thams cad sel /
NK116(le)001:15827: 'khor gyis de bzhin sku ltas na /
NK116(le)001:15828: byang chub sgrib pa gting dpag med /
NK116(le)001:15829: me long bzhin tu sku la snang //
NK116(le)001:15830: de nas sa bcu rim gyis 'byor //
NK116(le)001:15831: bla med byang chub yang dag 'thob /
NK116(le)001:15834: dus ni zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:15835: dusa kyi tshad ni sa bcu'i dabnga phyug chena po rnams /
NK116(le)001:15836: 'jiga rten gsum gyi mgona po ngo bo meda pa'i dbyingsa su /
NK116(le)001:15837: mi zada rgyan gyi 'khora lo sku gsunga thugas kyi
NK116(le)001:15838: ngang lasa ston 'khora dgongas pa gciga tu ma gyur
NK116(le)001:15839: bar du 'chi ba'i bduda bcoma ste 'jiga rten gyi
NK116(le)001:15840: legs tshogs 'byor ba'i slad du rtagsa pa ni /
NK116(le)001:15842: chos kyi dbang phyug 'chi ba'i bdud bcom nas /
NK116(le)001:15843: ngo bo med phyir 'jig rten mgon po rtag /
NK116(le)001:15846: gdul bya'i zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:15847: gdula bya'i gti mug la sogas pa'i nyona mongas lnga
NK116(le)001:15848: bo gang gi gnyen pora che ba'i zhing khamas dang
NK116(le)001:15849: / ston par bstan pa'i sku lnga dang /
NK116(le)001:15851: gansa 'gyur ye shesa rnam pa lnga po yanga /
NK116(le)001:15852: mthonga lam nasa bzungsa sa bcu rgyun matha'i bar /
NK116(le)001:15853: rima par rdzogas nas rdzogas pa'i byang chub snying pora 'gro ba yin la /
NK116(le)001:15854: de yang mthong lam gyi dus su kun brtag las gyur pa'i gti mug gnas 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:15855: kun gzhi dbyings su nub pa'i chos dbyings ye shes
NK116(le)001:15856: kyi ngo bo sa dang po rab tu dga' ba
NK116(le)001:15858: de bzhin du 'phags pa'i bsgom lam chung ngu gsum du nga rgyal gnas 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:15859: yid kyi rnam shes dbyings su nub /
NK116(le)001:15860: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes brnyes /
NK116(le)001:15861: sa gnyis pa nas bzhi pa bar thob /
NK116(le)001:15863: 'bring po gsum du rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i chags rtogs gnas 'gyur /
NK116(le)001:15866: sa lnga pa nas bdun pa'i bar thob /
NK116(le)001:15868: chen po gsum la sa brgyad par zhe sdang gi sa bon rtog pa'i zug rngu dang /
NK116(le)001:15870: me long lta bu'i ye shes thob /
NK116(le)001:15872: sa lhag ma gnyis la phrag dog gi sa bon dang /
NK116(le)001:15873: sgo lnga'i rnam shes dbyings su nub nas so sor
NK116(le)001:15874: yang dag rig bzhis 'gro khams rgya mtsho'i don byed
NK116(le)001:15875: pa'i phrin las rlabs po che'i bdag nyid bya ba
NK116(le)001:15877: don yod grub pa'i sku mthong /
NK116(le)001:15878: de nas rgyun matha'i sems dpa' chen po de la
NK116(le)001:15879: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba thams cad kyis 'od zer chen
NK116(le)001:15881: sangs rgyas pa'i tshul sngon bstan pa ltar ro /
NK116(le)001:15882: de skad du sgyu 'phrul mngon byang las /
NK116(le)001:15883: dag pa sa yi dbang nyid phyir //
NK116(le)001:15884: ston pa lnga dang chos rab lnga //
NK116(le)001:15885: ye shes lnga yongs rdzogs pa las //
NK116(le)001:15886: rdzogs pa'i byang chub snying por 'gro //
NK116(le)001:15888: go rim gyis mthong tshul yang //
NK116(le)001:15890: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs sku'i 'khor bstan pa //
NK116(le)001:15891: longs spyod bzhi yi sa las 'das pa yis //
NK116(le)001:15892: dang po rab tu dga' ba'i sa mnan nas //
NK116(le)001:15893: sa bcu chos kyi sprin gyi sa ba ste //
NK116(le)001:15894: de ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i 'khor du bstan /
NK116(le)001:15896: pha rol du phyin pa'i lugs ltar na //
NK116(le)001:15897: zhing khams 'di ni sa bcu'i byang chub semas dapa'a kho na lasa //
NK116(le)001:15898: gzhan gyi spyod pa'i yula du snang ba min zhing /
NK116(le)001:15899: gong du bshad zin pa'i longs sku chen po'i zhing khams //
NK116(le)001:15900: de bzhina du ston pa longas spyod rdzogas na'ang //
NK116(le)001:15901: 'khora sogas ranga snang ma yina rgyud gazhana pasa /
NK116(le)001:15902: bsdusa phyir phyed snang longs sku'am //
NK116(le)001:15903: ranga bzhina sprul pa'i zhing zhes //
NK116(le)001:15904: nyi zla kha sbyor chena po'i rgyud kyisa bstan pa yin no //
NK116(le)001:15905: de yang theg pa gong mas gzhal na bgrang ba
NK116(le)001:15906: dang gnas su 'dod pa'i snga ma ni phar phyiin
NK116(le)001:15907: lam gyis bgrang ba'i 'bras bu sa kun tu 'od
NK116(le)001:15908: brnyes pa'i tshe 'og min du sangs rgyas pa'i longs
NK116(le)001:15909: sku de sa bcu'i spyod yul du gyur kyang skur
NK116(le)001:15910: mi mthong zhing gsung thos pas shes sgrib spangs nas
NK116(le)001:15912: ston pa mthong ba mnyam par 'dod do //
NK116(le)001:15913: phyi ma ni khyad par zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan de /
NK116(le)001:15914: khyad para ranga bzhina rdzogas pa chena po yi /
NK116(le)001:15915: ranga snang ye shesa kyi dkyila 'khora dama pa ru
NK116(le)001:15916: lta ba mchoga gzigas pa'i bla mas ji bzhin du
NK116(le)001:15917: dabnga bskur ba'i dam tshig ma nyamsa la /
NK116(le)001:15918: nyin dusa ranga snang mngona suma 'oda gasla dang /
NK116(le)001:15919: matshana mo snying ga'i 'oda gadngas gomas pa rnams ni /
NK116(le)001:15920: rtogsa pa'i ranga bzhina tshad du ma phyin yanga /
NK116(le)001:15921: chosa nyid kyi bdena pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15922: bla ma'i byin rlabsa kyis lus rten gyi rgya grol ba'i tshe //
NK116(le)001:15923: sprul pa'i zhing yid la dran ma thag /
NK116(le)001:15924: sa thoba gyi 'phags pa rnams dang skal ba mtshungsa para gyur nasa /
NK116(le)001:15925: gzhi snang lhun grub phyogsa bcu'i sprul pa'i zhing der 'gro ba ni /
NK116(le)001:15926: a ti bkod pa chen po las /
NK116(le)001:15927: snyigs ma lnga brgya'i dus kyi tha ma la //
NK116(le)001:15928: gsang ba'i snying po 'di ni mi yul snang /
NK116(le)001:15929: de rjes 'dzin pa'i gang zag skal ba can /
NK116(le)001:15930: snying po 'di ni su la snang gyur ba /
NK116(le)001:15931: de dag rnams ni mi 'gyur sa la gda'/
NK116(le)001:15932: gal te snyig ma tshe thung na da mang pas /
NK116(le)001:15933: snying po'i don 'di gdengs su ma gyur kyang //
NK116(le)001:15934: 'di nyid mthong bas dbugs chen nyid 'byin pa /
NK116(le)001:15935: bcu gcig kun tu 'od de sprul pa'i zhing /
NK116(le)001:15936: bardzusa skyes dag pas mngal gyi rgya dang bral /
NK116(le)001:15939: rnam grol dbugs chen 'byin pa'i zhing lnga ni /
NK116(le)001:15940: khyad par zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:15941: spyir sangs rgyas kyi stong gsum yungs 'brur btsud pa dang /
NK116(le)001:15942: skra rtser zhing khams bsam las 'das pa sprul pa'i phyir su zhig gis brjod nus te /
NK116(le)001:15944: skra rtse'i khyon la sangs rgyas mang por ni //
NK116(le)001:15945: gang ga'i klung gi bye ma ji yod snyed //
NK116(le)001:15946: rgyal ba de dag zhing yang de rnyed de //
NK116(le)001:15947: de dag mtshan nyid mi 'dra skal mi mnyams /
NK116(le)001:15949: 'dir thun mong gi 'dod tshul las mi 'dra ba'i
NK116(le)001:15950: zhing khams khyad para ba rnam grola dbugas chena 'byin
NK116(le)001:15951: pa lnga ni / de yang 'di nas shar phyogs 'jig rten gyi khams dang /
NK116(le)001:15952: de bzhin lho nasa byang gi bar rim bzhin /
NK116(le)001:15956: las rab grub zhes bya ba yod la /
NK116(le)001:15957: de dag na'ang rima pa bzhina shela dang su war+na dang /
NK116(le)001:15958: pada raga in+t+ra n+ai la bzhi po so so'i gzhal meda khanga /
NK116(le)001:15959: sgo bzhi khyamsa dang rta babas snang byed ba glanga mig dang bcas pa /
NK116(le)001:15960: zura bzhira mu tig las grub pa'i mchoda rten dang /
NK116(le)001:15962: g.yera khasa sbrel ba'i dpyang thaga rlung gis bskyod pa
NK116(le)001:15963: las sgra rnama thara stong mtshan smon gsum ldana pa'i
NK116(le)001:15964: chosa dbyangs mi shig na d+aa'i sgra dara dira sgrog
NK116(le)001:15965: pa / phyogsa bzhira spos kyi sprina te /
NK116(le)001:15966: dri bsung g.yo ba'i ba dana bzhi dang /
NK116(le)001:15967: phyi ri ma na gtsang dngas bsil yang 'jam bsung
NK116(le)001:15968: ngom dang bde zhim ste yan lag brgyad dang ldan
NK116(le)001:15970: ta la'i ljon pa'i yal ga lo ma rnams dra phyed 'phyang 'phrul cana na /
NK116(le)001:15972: shang shang te'u rma bya ka ta ri /
NK116(le)001:15973: ne tsho mi skad 'byin dang ngang pa gzhona nu /
NK116(le)001:15974: ri skeg zera mo sbaba dang /
NK116(le)001:15976: lha'i bya drila bu'i sgra cana khu byung dang /
NK116(le)001:15977: gsera gyi rdo rje'i gzugas can kri ti pa rnams /
NK116(le)001:15978: g.yu dang bye ru in+t+ra n+ai la dang /
NK116(le)001:15979: dunga ltar so so'i kha doga phyed pa'i bya tshogsa kyis /
NK116(le)001:15980: snyan sgrogsa mgrina pa'i rgyud manga rnam pa kuna tu 'khrol ba yin no //
NK116(le)001:15981: de dag na bzhugs pa'i byang chub semsa dapa'a rnams
NK116(le)001:15982: kyis nyon mongas pa'i gnod pa zhi ba'i chu klung
NK116(le)001:15983: de la / spyad pa tsam gyis 'du ba'i nada mi 'byung ngo //
NK116(le)001:15984: yid la ji ltar bsam pa thams cad drana pa'i moda la 'byung zhing /
NK116(le)001:15985: sum cu rtsa gsuma lha dang longsa spyod mnyam par yod cing /
NK116(le)001:15986: phyi rima rina chena sna bduna gyi pha gu can dang ldan pa /
NK116(le)001:15987: zhing mchoga de na rigas bzhi'i ston pa yisa /
NK116(le)001:15992: nyin phyed lta bsgom gyi chosa kyi sgra sgrogsa pa rgyun mi chada do //
NK116(le)001:15993: de kuna gyi dbus kyi bar snang na he ru ka dpal gyi zhing /
NK116(le)001:15994: dura khrod chen po me ri 'abra ba zhes bya ba /
NK116(le)001:15996: shar ri yod pas rtsig pa /
NK116(le)001:15997: b+ha na d+ha lcang lo can gyis kha bad byas pa /
NK116(le)001:15998: tshad dpag tu med pa gnam lcags kyi gzer btab pa /
NK116(le)001:16001: chu srin gyi ka gzhu byas pa /
NK116(le)001:16002: lha chen po brgyad gdung du bres pa /
NK116(le)001:16003: mchog chen pos grab btang ba /
NK116(le)001:16006: steng du zhing chen gyi gdug phub pa /
NK116(le)001:16007: lha mo lnga gar byed pa /
NK116(le)001:16008: sa gzhi thams cad rak+ta'i rba klong 'khrugs pa yod de /
NK116(le)001:16009: de'i dbus na ston pa gzhona nu dapa'a bo bcoma
NK116(le)001:16010: ldana 'adsa thugs zhi ba las ma g.yos bzhin khro
NK116(le)001:16011: bo'i cha byed du bstan pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16012: de'i sprul pa lag na rdo rje la sogas pa dapa'a bo'i tshogs dang /
NK116(le)001:16013: dga' rab rdo rje la sogs mi'i 'khor dang /
NK116(le)001:16014: pur+na nyer bzhi la sogs mkha' 'gro ma dang /
NK116(le)001:16015: e ka tsa ti spun drug sogs 'khor gyi mkha'a
NK116(le)001:16016: 'gro'i sde tshogs rnams ji ltar sprin phung 'phro ba
NK116(le)001:16017: lta bu'i dbus nyid na 'brasa bu bla na meda
NK116(le)001:16019: gzhan yang pad+ma lasa skyes pa'i rgyal sras kyang /
NK116(le)001:16021: kuna kyang lha dang lha mo'i khye'u chung dang /
NK116(le)001:16022: bu mo'i rnam pa can dang drang srong grub pa cana rnams /
NK116(le)001:16023: rnam par rtog pa med cing semas gsum meda la
NK116(le)001:16024: yida druga dang ni nyon mongas drug kyang med de
NK116(le)001:16025: / ma riga pa med rkyen bzhi yoda ma yina zhing /
NK116(le)001:16026: de dang mtshungsa para ldan pa'i sgrib pa rnams kyang meda do //
NK116(le)001:16027: gang de na bshad ma thag pa'i ston pa rdo
NK116(le)001:16028: rje 'chang gi byin gyis rlabsa lasa ranga bzhina nyid
NK116(le)001:16029: du bkod phyir de'i ranga bzhina ni sprula pa'i zhing
NK116(le)001:16030: zhesa rgyal sras sar gnas rnams la yongs su gragas
NK116(le)001:16031: so // zhing 'di ni ranga bzhina rdzogas pa chena
NK116(le)001:16032: po'i gasnga ba'i lam rmad du byung ba riga pa
NK116(le)001:16033: ranga shar chena po'i rgyud lasa bstan no //
NK116(le)001:16034: gsang sngags thun mong du grags pa'i zhing snga ma
NK116(le)001:16035: dang rnam pa mthun pa 'ga' zhig ni gzhan du
NK116(le)001:16036: zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:16037: de yang gazhana du bde chen mkha'a la spyod pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16038: sa spyod zhesa su gragas pa'i zhing gang zhig na dona gyi 'oda gasla la /
NK116(le)001:16039: dabnga thob pa'i lhan ciga skyes pa'i d+aak+ki ma dang /
NK116(le)001:16040: yula chena nyer bzhira spyod pa'i zhing skyes ma la
NK116(le)001:16041: sogas pa dapa'a bo dang rnal 'byor ma'i tshogas dang
NK116(le)001:16042: skal pa mnyam pa'i riga 'dzina gyi grala gang du
NK116(le)001:16043: / lam gyi 'phro sbyangsa phyir riga pa 'dzina pa yi /
NK116(le)001:16044: rdo rje'i theg pa'i bla ma rnams ni raba tu
NK116(le)001:16045: bzhugas nas sngagas kyi lta spyod rlabsa po che la
NK116(le)001:16047: 'di daga ni ranga snang dge ba'i sa bon mngon
NK116(le)001:16048: du gyur pa dang bskyeda rdzoga zaba mo'i brtul zhugsa
NK116(le)001:16049: mathara son pa'i gasnga sngagas gruba pa thob pa rnams
NK116(le)001:16051: rtog pa'i rang 'doda cana gyis phyin du yoda pa
NK116(le)001:16052: yi phyogas dang risa chada cana du bsam para mi
NK116(le)001:16053: bya'o / 'gro 'dul sprul pa'i khyad par ni de nyid ces bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:16054: de nyid nganga lasa longas spyod rdzogas pa yi sangs
NK116(le)001:16055: rgyas rnams kyis yi ge'i sprin gyi 'oda zera raba
NK116(le)001:16056: tu 'phrosa pasa // 'jiga rten 'dula bar byed pa'i sbrul pa'i sku mchoga ni /
NK116(le)001:16057: gansa rigas drug gi gdula bya'i snang ba la /
NK116(le)001:16058: ranga ranga minga gi mngona brjod tha dad pa'i rjesa su 'gro ba yi /
NK116(le)001:16059: 'dula byed riga pa'i skyes bu thuba pa drug tu phyogsa bcu matha'a yasa mu med stong gsuma gyi /
NK116(le)001:16060: stong chen po ji snyed dang mnyam par raba tu sprul nasa /
NK116(le)001:16061: gdula ba bzhi yi 'gro dona mdzad pa bsam gyis mi khyab ste /
NK116(le)001:16062: de'nga sku bsoda namsa chena po'i gdul ba ni /
NK116(le)001:16063: sku yi madzada pa chen po bcu gnyis yina te /
NK116(le)001:16064: rgyud bla ma'i lung gis sa bcad tsam sher phyin gyi khungs su bstan pa ltar ro //
NK116(le)001:16066: yan lag drug cu rtsa bzhi'i dbyangs kyi bstan pa'i
NK116(le)001:16067: thega pa gsum mama gciga gam du mar snang ba
NK116(le)001:16068: ganga yanga 'gro ba'i 'du shes kyi rjesa su 'gro
NK116(le)001:16069: ste semas cana gyi nyon mongas pa'i gnyena pora 'gro
NK116(le)001:16070: ba'i dgongas pa ste gsungsa pa la /
NK116(le)001:16071: chosa kyi sgo 'aphara brgyada khri bzhi stong gi grangsa
NK116(le)001:16072: su gsungas pa ltar snang yanga sgra tshiga ranga matshana
NK116(le)001:16073: pa ma yina par semas cana khamas la byina rlabsa
NK116(le)001:16074: kyi mthusa rdzas rnam para riga pa nyid dang mthuna
NK116(le)001:16076: de la yan lag drug cu rtsa bzhi ni /
NK116(le)001:16078: gsungs ni tshig sbyor legs pa la /
NK116(le)001:16079: tshangs pa'i dbyangs ni yan lag drug ces pa'i don
NK116(le)001:16080: nyi khri snang ba las gsang ba bsam gyis mi
NK116(le)001:16081: khyab pas ston pa ltar 'chad na /
NK116(le)001:16082: sems can khams kyi dge ba'i rtsa ba nye bar ston pa'i phyir mnyen pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16083: mthong chos su bde ba la reg pa'i phyir 'jam pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16084: don bzang ba'i phyir yid du 'ong ba dang /
NK116(le)001:16085: yi ge bzang ba'i phyir yid du 'thad pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16086: 'jig rten las 'das pa bla na med pa'i rjes las 'thon pa'i phyir dag pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16087: nyon mongs pa bag la nyal gyi bag chags thams cad bral ba'i phyir dri ma med pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16088: tshig dang yi ge rab tu grags pa'i phyir rab tu gsal ba dang /
NK116(le)001:16089: mu stegs can blo gros ngan pa thams cad kyi
NK116(le)001:16090: lta ba rnam par 'joms pa'i stobs kyi yon tan
NK116(le)001:16091: dang ldan pa'i phyir snyan cing 'jebs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16092: sgrub pa nges par 'byung ba dang ldan pa'i phyir mnyan par 'os pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16093: pha rol gyi rgol ba thams cad kyis mi bardzi ba'i phyir mi tshugs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16094: thams cad dag par byed pa'i phyir snyan pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16095: 'dod chags la sogs pa'i gnyen po yin pa'i phyir dul ba dang /
NK116(le)001:16096: bslab pa bca' pa'i thabs bde ba'i phyir mi rtsub pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16097: nges par 'byung ba'i thabs yang dag par stoon par mdzad pa'i phyir mi barlanga ba dang /
NK116(le)001:16098: theg pa gsum char gyi 'dul ba ston pa'i phyir rab tu 'dul ba dang /
NK116(le)001:16099: rnam g.yeng gi gnyen por gyur pa'i phyir rna bar snyan pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16100: ting nge 'dzin bskyed par mdzad pa'i phyir lus sim par byed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16101: lhag mthong gi rab tu dga' ba bskyed par mdzad phyir sems sim par byed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16102: the tsom gcod par mdzad pa'i phyir snying dga' bar byed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16103: log pa dang ma nges pa sel bar byed pa'i phyir dga' ba dang bde ba bskyed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16104: bsgrub pa la 'gyod pa med pa'i phyir yongs su gdung ba med pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16105: thos pa las byung ba phun sum tshogs pa'i rten yin pa'i phyir kun shes par bya ba dang /
NK116(le)001:16106: bsam pa las byung pa'i shes rab phun sum tshogs pa'i rten yin pa'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:16107: rnam par rig par bya ba dang slob dpon kyi
NK116(le)001:16108: dpe ma khyud mi mnga' bar chos ston par mdzad
NK116(le)001:16109: pa'i phyir rnam par gsal ba dang /
NK116(le)001:16110: rang gi don rjes su thob pa rnam par dga' bar byed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16111: rang gi don ma thob pa rnams kyis dga' bar
NK116(le)001:16112: bya ba ma yin pa'i phyir mngon par dga' ba
NK116(le)001:16113: bya ba dang / bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos
NK116(le)001:16114: rnams yang dag par ston par mdzad pa'i phyir kun
NK116(le)001:16115: bya ba dang / shes pa dang / bsam gyis
NK116(le)001:16116: mi khyab pa'i chos rnams yang dag par ston par
NK116(le)001:16117: mdzad pa'i phyir rnam par rig par bya ba dang
NK116(le)001:16118: bya ba dang / shes pa dang / / tshad ma dang mi 'gal ba'i phyir rigs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16119: gdul bya rnams ji lta rigs par ston par mdzad pa'i phyir 'brel ba dang /
NK116(le)001:16120: don med mi gsung ba'i phyir zlos pa'i skyon med pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16121: mu stegs can gyi tshogs thams cad skrag par mdzad pa'i phyir seng ge'i sgra'i shugs dang /
NK116(le)001:16122: gsung rgya che ba nyid kyi phyir glang po che'i sgra skad dang /
NK116(le)001:16123: zab pa nyid kyi phyir 'brug gi sgra dbyangs dang
NK116(le)001:16124: bzung par 'os pa'i phyir lag 'gro'i dbang po'i sgra
NK116(le)001:16125: dbyangs dang / shin tu snyan pa'i phyir dri za'i klu dbyangs dang /
NK116(le)001:16126: rno ba gnyis su gsungs phyir ka la ping ka'i sgra dbyangs dang /
NK116(le)001:16127: thag ring du grags pa'i phyir tshangs pa'i sgra dbyangs
NK116(le)001:16128: dang grub pa thams cad kyi sngon du 'gro ba
NK116(le)001:16129: yin pa'i phyir shang shang te'u'i sgra dbyangs dang /
NK116(le)001:16130: 'da' bar bya ba ma yin pa'i phyir lha'i dbang po'i dbyangs ltar snyan pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16131: bdud dang phyir rgol ba thams cad las rnam par
NK116(le)001:16132: rgyal ba'i sngon du 'gro ba'i phyir rnga sgra dang
NK116(le)001:16133: / bstod pas kun nas nyon mongs pa mi mnga' ba'i phyir ma khengs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16134: smad pas zhum pa mi mngar phyir mi dma' ba dang /
NK116(le)001:16135: legs par sbyar ba'i skad la sogs sgra'i mtshan nyid
NK116(le)001:16136: rnam pa thams cad pa'i rjes su zhugs pa dang
NK116(le)001:16137: bsnyil te gsung ba mi mnga' ba'i zur chags med
NK116(le)001:16138: pa dang / gdul bya rnams kyi bya ba dus
NK116(le)001:16139: thams cad du nye bar gnas par mdzad pa'i phyir
NK116(le)001:16140: ma tshang ba med pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16141: rnyed pa dang bkur sti la mi brten pa'i phyir ma zhum pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16142: bsnyengs pa dang bral ba'i phyir mi zhan pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16143: skye ba med pa'i phyi rab tu dga' ba dang /
NK116(le)001:16144: rig pa'i gnas thams cad la mkhas pa dang ldan pa'i phyir khyab pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16145: sems can rnams kyi don thams cad rdzogs par mdzad pa'i phyir tha pa med pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16146: rgyun chad par med pa'i phyir bya bas rgyun chags pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16147: rnam par sna tshogs su nye bar gnas pa'i phyir brjod pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16148: gsung sgra'i rnam par du mar gnas pa'i phyir sgra thams cad rdzogs par byed pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16149: gcig las du ma'i rnam par rig pa nye bar
NK116(le)001:16150: gnas phyir dbang po thams cad tshim par byed pa
NK116(le)001:16151: dang / ji ltar dam bcas pa bzhin du mdzad pa'i phyir ma slad pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16152: thob pa'i dus su rab tu sbyor ba'i phyir mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK116(le)001:16153: brjod pa dal zhing 'brel chags pa'i phyir ma brtags pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16154: de'i gsungs thag ring po dang nye bar mtshungs pa thos pa'i phyir kun tu grags pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16155: 'jig rten pa'i don thams cad dpe'i chos su bsgyur
NK116(le)001:16156: ba'i phyir rnam pa thams cad kyis mchog dang ldan
NK116(le)001:16157: pa ste gsungs yan lag drug cu rtsa bzhi'o //
NK116(le)001:16158: thugas kyi gdula ba dus gsum mkhyen cinga gzigas pa yin la /
NK116(le)001:16159: de la 'das dusa kyang 'das pa'am ma 'ongs par
NK116(le)001:16160: so sor rnam par mi rtog par dus gsum gyi
NK116(le)001:16161: tha snyad bral ba dusa med kyi dusa na ranga
NK116(le)001:16162: bzhina gdoda ma'i gansa skabsa kuna tu bazanga pos gazhana
NK116(le)001:16163: gyi semas rgyud mkhyen pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16164: de bzhina du rdzu 'phrul chena po'i spyan dang snyan
NK116(le)001:16165: la sogas pa'i mngona shesa druga po dusa lasa yola
NK116(le)001:16166: ba meda pa'o // de yang ji skad du /
NK116(le)001:16167: dbang po lnga rnams gazhana gyur na /
NK116(le)001:16168: don kun 'jug dang thams cad kyis /
NK116(le)001:16169: yon tan brgya phrag bcu gnyis 'byung /
NK116(le)001:16171: phrina lasa kyi gdula ba ni /
NK116(le)001:16172: 'jig rten gyi khams kuna tu sna tshogs pa'i sku
NK116(le)001:16173: dang zhing ni kun tu thugas dang de bzhina du
NK116(le)001:16175: kuna tu gsunga gi gasnga ba bsam gyis mi khyab ste /
NK116(le)001:16176: de yang sku gsunga thugas kyi dngosa su dona madzada la /
NK116(le)001:16177: phrina lasa kyis ni dngosa dang brgyud mar kuna tu madzada do //
NK116(le)001:16178: de ltar spros bral dbyingsa lasa gdul bya'i ngor sprul
NK116(le)001:16179: pa'i sku mchoga rnams chos nyid la ltos ji ltar
NK116(le)001:16182: ji snyed mkhyen pa yi ye shesa gnyis kyis gdula bya'i rgyud /
NK116(le)001:16183: 'grol bar 'gyur zhing lta ba nye bar zhi ba
NK116(le)001:16184: dang rtogs byed ma 'drisa pa'i chosa tshul mtha' klas
NK116(le)001:16185: par ston to // de las yang sprul 'byung tshul
NK116(le)001:16186: de las zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te
NK116(le)001:16187: par ston to // / de lasa yanga sprul dang
NK116(le)001:16188: nyid sbrul gyi rnam pa brjod kyi mi langas te
NK116(le)001:16189: par ston to // / / 'gro ba druga gi gansa rigas de snyed du /
NK116(le)001:16190: lha rnams 'dula byed tshangas dang dabnga po bde 'byung sogas dang /
NK116(le)001:16191: mi la nyan thos ranga rgyal byang sems 'khora lo'i bsgyur ba sogs dang /
NK116(le)001:16192: de bzhina lha ma yina la thaga bazanga risa dang /
NK116(le)001:16193: bya la shing rta mo dang rma bya'i rgyal po gser du snang ba dang /
NK116(le)001:16194: sreg pa la sogs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16195: ri dwagas kyi phyir senga ge'i rgyal po yi dama bstan pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16198: mdor na dmyal ba yi dwagas la sogs 'gro ba ganga dang yang zhig 'dul byed de dang /
NK116(le)001:16200: semas cana gyi dona la nam yanga g.yela ba meda pa'o //
NK116(le)001:16201: 'di ni 'jiga rten drug gi zhing khamsa rnams su
NK116(le)001:16202: so so'i lasa dang baga chagas dge sdiga rgyu 'bras
NK116(le)001:16203: kyis / gansa rigas bde sduga mtho damna ltar snang
NK116(le)001:16204: ba'i phyir ranga snang dang mthuna pa'i ston pasa dona
NK116(le)001:16205: kyis / madzada cinga / chos kyang ma ngesa gdula bya'i blo rtogsa ltar dang /
NK116(le)001:16206: dusa kyang ranga ranga skal pa'i rjesa su 'gro ba ste /
NK116(le)001:16207: ma daga zhing gi 'gro la de ltar snang ba yin no //
NK116(le)001:16208: de dag don la bden med yin tshul gang zhig ces bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:16209: de 'dra'i mdzad pa sna tshogs snang yang ganga zhiga rmi lam gyi nanga du sangsa rgyas mthonga ste /
NK116(le)001:16210: rmi lam lta bura sprul pa'i chos bstan pa yanga /
NK116(le)001:16211: ngo bo nyid meda cing ranga bzhina ma grub la /
NK116(le)001:16212: badga meda stong pa bsob gsoga tu riga para bya'o //
NK116(le)001:16213: zhesa zaba mo'i mdo sde daga la gsungas pa gong du bstan zina to de bas na /
NK116(le)001:16214: 'khora 'adsa rmi lam lta bu'i rola pa la /
NK116(le)001:16215: snang ba'i sangsa rgyas ngo bo rnam par daga na'ang /
NK116(le)001:16216: sprul pa rnam pa gdula bya nyid ltar snang ba'i phyir /
NK116(le)001:16217: ma daga pa ltar du thugas rje'i rola pa'i sprul pa yanga /
NK116(le)001:16218: ji srida 'khora ba'i rjesa su 'gro ste rgyun mi chad do //
NK116(le)001:16219: sna tshogs sprul sku ni de nyid ces bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:16220: de nyid kyi nganga lasa sna tshogas pa'i sprul pa ni /
NK116(le)001:16221: sku gsung thugs rten skyes bu'i rtsol ba la ma
NK116(le)001:16222: ltos par ranga bzhina gyis byona pa dang 'du byed
NK116(le)001:16223: lasa byung ba'i 'bura du byas pa dang risa su
NK116(le)001:16224: bris pa dang / gan+d+ho la te gtsug lag khang dang /
NK116(le)001:16225: khanga bazanga phal ba dang skyed mosa tshala dang /
NK116(le)001:16226: mya ngama gyi thang la sprul pa'i grong khyer dang /
NK116(le)001:16227: pad+ma dang dpag bsam gyi shinga dang yida bzhina gyi nora bu dang /
NK116(le)001:16228: gru gzingsa dang zama pa dang shing rta dang zas dang gosa sogas /
NK116(le)001:16229: semsa meda bema po'i tshul du snang ba dang /
NK116(le)001:16230: skye ba'i sprul pa mu ge'i tshe na nya bo che dang /
NK116(le)001:16231: nada kyisa gdungsa ba la srog chagsa ngesa pa lta bu dang /
NK116(le)001:16232: srina po'i gling du cang shesa ba la ha dang /
NK116(le)001:16233: mi gatsanga 'adma du gsera gyi bunga ba sogas /
NK116(le)001:16234: sprul pa sna tshogsa rnamas pa kuna tu sems can bde ba'i gzhir /
NK116(le)001:16235: rtog pa meda cing ga yo ba med pa lta
NK116(le)001:16236: busa sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang 'thob pa'i dona chena
NK116(le)001:16237: gyi phyir du ni gdul bya'i dapala du nye bar
NK116(le)001:16238: gansa pa ni / rgyud bla ma las //
NK116(le)001:16239: snang ba de ni shin tu yang //
NK116(le)001:16240: rtog pa med pa g.yo ba med //
NK116(le)001:16241: de ltar mod kyi sa steng na //
NK116(le)001:16242: don chen gyi ni nye bar gnas /
NK116(le)001:16244: de ltar snang yang rang byung rang la thim pa'i
NK116(le)001:16245: tshul gal te zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan
NK116(le)001:16246: te // gala te nam zhig 'khor ba stongs te
NK116(le)001:16247: gdula bar bya ba'i dusa yola bar gyur pa na
NK116(le)001:16248: 'dula byed dbyingas su nuba pa'i matshana dpe ni /
NK116(le)001:16249: ji ltar chu snod meda tshe chu zla'i gzugas brnyan sprul gzhi'i zla ba nyid la thima pa ltar /
NK116(le)001:16250: gdula bya'i snang basa bsdus pa'i sprul pa rnams /
NK116(le)001:16251: ranga snang longas spyod rdzogas pa'i dbyingsa su thima par 'gyur zhing /
NK116(le)001:16252: de'ang ganma stong gi zla ba ciga shos nas gciga
NK116(le)001:16253: shos dag tu thim pa meda kyang yul khams la
NK116(le)001:16254: phyir gasla gyi gadngas 'gag ste nanga dbyingsa spros pa
NK116(le)001:16255: meda pa'i nganga du thim pa ltar /
NK116(le)001:16256: longsa spyod rdzogas pa'i ranga snang chosa kyi sku spros
NK116(le)001:16257: pa bral ba'i ye shesa chena pora 'khyil ba de
NK116(le)001:16258: nyid la / dabu ma pa rnams spros pa'i 'juga
NK116(le)001:16259: pa chos kyi dbyingsa su nye bar zhi ba'i 'goga
NK116(le)001:16261: 'dir rang lugs ni so so ranga riga pa'i ye shesa nyid /
NK116(le)001:16262: phra ba'i ye shesa nanga gasla chos kyi dbyingsa su
NK116(le)001:16263: thima la ma rmuga gzhona nu bum pa'i sku ste
NK116(le)001:16264: / nyi ma'i rkyen dang bral ba'i shel gyi 'ja' tshon spubs su gsal ba ba zhin no //
NK116(le)001:16265: de lta bu mchi'am zhe na 'byung ste /
NK116(le)001:16266: bskal pa bzang po 'di stongs nas bskal pa'i chags 'jig byed pa song ba na /
NK116(le)001:16267: bskal pa 'khor ba dongs sprug zhes bya ba la /
NK116(le)001:16268: sangs rgyas 'khor lo glog gi phreng bas bstan pa dam pa 'di yongs su bzung ste /
NK116(le)001:16269: sems can rnams 'khor ba las grol bar mdzad nas /
NK116(le)001:16270: rdo rje 'chang gi bkod pa'i tshangs chen gyi bskal
NK116(le)001:16271: pa'i 'gro ba rnams thams cad gdod ma'i sar grol
NK116(le)001:16272: ste / bstan pa'i btsas gsum yang /
NK116(le)001:16273: chos nyid kyi dbyings su thim la /
NK116(le)001:16275: de nas bskal pa chen po stong phrag nyi shur lus can rnam par mi snang ngo //
