NK116(le)001:16276: de nas yang snga ma bzhin bag la nyal ba langs pas 'gro ba'i snod bcud snang ba na /
NK116(le)001:16277: 'dul byed kyi ston pa'ang thog ma'i kun tu bzang pos mthus 'byung ba yin no //
NK116(le)001:16279: bstan pa'i snying thig gsang ba 'di //
NK116(le)001:16280: de ltar bstan pa bdun 'das nas //
NK116(le)001:16281: zhing khams bdun pa nges sbyang nas //
NK116(le)001:16282: de ltar bdun po thal nas kyang //
NK116(le)001:16283: rdo rje gdan gyi spo la ni //
NK116(le)001:16284: bstan pa kun gyi gsung gi btsas //
NK116(le)001:16285: rang byung chen po'i yi ge nyid //
NK116(le)001:16286: sgra dang bcas te babs pa ni //
NK116(le)001:16287: 'di nas bskal pa bye ba na //
NK116(le)001:16288: 'khor lo glog gi phreng ba yis //
NK116(le)001:16290: de nas lo ni brgya phrag gsum /
NK116(le)001:16291: de ltar gsum ni thal ba'i 'og /
NK116(le)001:16292: bstan pa thugs kyi rdo rje yang /
NK116(le)001:16293: ston pa de la snang bar 'gyur //
NK116(le)001:16294: de nas lo ni lnga brgya na //
NK116(le)001:16295: bstan pa'i sku yang der bab ste //
NK116(le)001:16296: de ltar bstan pa dngos babs nas //
NK116(le)001:16297: yang ni bstan pa'i me ro ldang //
NK116(le)001:16298: ston pa de yi 'khor du yang //
NK116(le)001:16300: rdzu 'phrul stobs ldan rdzogs pa la //
NK116(le)001:16301: rab tu dad cing bdun pa nyid //
NK116(le)001:16302: nges par bzung ste mngon par snang //
NK116(le)001:16303: de la sogs ste ston pa'i 'khor //
NK116(le)001:16304: 'phags pa nyan thos khri phrag gnyis //
NK116(le)001:16305: 'dul ba'i bstan pa bskal pa gcig /
NK116(le)001:16307: de nas mun pa'i bskal pa drug /
NK116(le)001:16308: de nas dgra bcom 'bum phrag gnyis //
NK116(le)001:16310: mdo sde'i bstan pa bskal pa brgyad //
NK116(le)001:16311: drang nges las kyi mtha' la 'god //
NK116(le)001:16312: rdzu 'phrul stobs la dbang bsgyur nas //
NK116(le)001:16313: nges par 'phen te bstan pa rdzogs //
NK116(le)001:16314: yang ni mya ngan 'da' tshul ston //
NK116(le)001:16315: de nas mun pa'i bskal pa gnyis //
NK116(le)001:16316: de nas ston pa'i sku 'khrungs nas //
NK116(le)001:16317: byang chub sems dpa' chen po'i 'khor //
NK116(le)001:16318: stong phrag brgyad ni 'dus pa las //
NK116(le)001:16320: rab tu ston pa'i bstan pa sdud //
NK116(le)001:16321: mngon pa'i bstan pa bskal pa brgya //
NK116(le)001:16322: thams cad tshe gcig 'bras bu thob //
NK116(le)001:16324: sems can rnams kyis sangs rgyas 'thob //
NK116(le)001:16325: 'gro ba drug kyang snang mi srid //
NK116(le)001:16326: bskal pa stong phrag nyi shu ni //
NK116(le)001:16327: sems can 'khor ba rgyun chad nas //
NK116(le)001:16328: lus can rnam par mi snang ngo //
NK116(le)001:16329: de nas las kyi bye brag gis //
NK116(le)001:16330: sems can nyon mongs sngon med kyang //
NK116(le)001:16331: bag la nyal ba langs pa'i dbang //
NK116(le)001:16332: shin tu phra ba blang pa'i gzugs //
NK116(le)001:16333: grangs mang rab tu phra ba la //
NK116(le)001:16335: de ltar barjodakyisa mi langs pa'i //
NK116(le)001:16336: bstan pa'i tha ma bsam mi khyab //
NK116(le)001:16337: re zhig tshig gis mtshon pa'o //
NK116(le)001:16339: 'di la snga rabs pa kha gcig gis //
NK116(le)001:16340: kun tu bzang pos dgongs pa yod do cog gi sems can rnams stong pa dang //
NK116(le)001:16341: kha gcig tshangs chen gyi sems can yod do cog grol ba la dgongs pa yin te //
NK116(le)001:16342: bstan pa'i tha ma bsam mi khyab /
NK116(le)001:16344: kun tu bzang po'i go na dang tshad med zhes bzhed do //
NK116(le)001:16345: kun mkhyen chos rje rin po ches gang ltar kyang 'gal ba med la /
NK116(le)001:16346: grol ba rgya che shos ltar ngos bzung na legs zhes gsungs pa ltar //
NK116(le)001:16348: slar yang gzhi las snga ma bzhin ma rig bag
NK116(le)001:16349: nyal langs nas sems can srid par 'gyur tshe rgyal
NK116(le)001:16350: ba'i thugs rje yang de bzhin 'byung ste /
NK116(le)001:16351: gdul bya ma zad par bstan pa'i tha ma'am /
NK116(le)001:16352: gnas tshad bsam las 'das pa la dgongs pa dang /
NK116(le)001:16353: re zhig stong dus chos sku'i go na yod do
NK116(le)001:16354: cog pa'i sems can yin ces brjod na bde bar
NK116(le)001:16355: snyam mo // slar yang gang du gdula bya'i sems
NK116(le)001:16356: can nam snang ba'i mod nyid la 'aggas meda thugas
NK116(le)001:16357: rje ye shes sngon ji lta ba bzhin du mcheda
NK116(le)001:16358: snyam mo // para 'gyur ro // de lta bu'i
NK116(le)001:16359: gzhi shina tu manyama para bzhag pa'i spyod yul chosa
NK116(le)001:16360: nyid 'dus ma byas pa mngon tu gyur pa ni
NK116(le)001:16361: snyam mo // para 'gyur ro // / mthar thug
NK116(le)001:16362: gi 'brasa bu bla na med pa rang byung lhuna
NK116(le)001:16363: grub chena po'i go 'aphanga yina no //
NK116(le)001:16364: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi le'u bcu gsum pa'i 'grel ba'o ////
NK116(le)001:16365: de ltar lus dngos kyi don bshad zin nas /
NK116(le)001:16366: da ni gsum pa mjug gi don bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK116(le)001:16367: mdo rgyud 'chad pa'i spobs pa bla ma'i byin rlabs thob tshul /
NK116(le)001:16368: phyogs re ba'i blo gros kyi snod du chos tshul
NK116(le)001:16369: 'di nyid mi shong pa la lhag par brtse tshul
NK116(le)001:16370: / grub matha'i gnas bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chu phran mnyam bzhag gi rgya mtshor bab tshul /
NK116(le)001:16371: dge rtsa rdzogs byang du bsngo tshul lo //
NK116(le)001:16372: dang po bdag rgyud ces bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:16373: badga rgyud snod kyi nang 'dir chags pa'i shes rab
NK116(le)001:16374: gsum gyi sgron me yang dag tu sbyar te dpyad
NK116(le)001:16375: gsum lam du drang ba'i bstan chos le'u bcu gsum
NK116(le)001:16376: pa'i bdag nyid yongs su rdzogas par gyur pa'i spob
NK116(le)001:16377: pa ji ltar thob ce na /
NK116(le)001:16378: dus gang gi tshe bsam yas mchi phu'i brag dmar
NK116(le)001:16379: ke'u tshang gi sgrub gnas su sgrub par rtse gcig
NK116(le)001:16381: 'jiga rten gsum gyi mgona po dri meda 'oda zera
NK116(le)001:16382: gyi zhal mthonga zhing thugas rje nus pa'i byang chen
NK116(le)001:16383: gyi go sar dbugs 'byin ma thoba na /
NK116(le)001:16384: lam mina srid pa'i gayanga sar dala 'byor gyi rten rin po che stong loga byas par zad do //
NK116(le)001:16386: 'o na rje nyid rgyal ba de'i sprul par zhal
NK116(le)001:16387: gyis ma bzhes sam zhe na yin mod kyang de
NK116(le)001:16388: la 'gal ba med de sprul gzhi sangs rgyas yin
NK116(le)001:16389: kyang / re zhig sprul pa ni gdul bya'i ngor
NK116(le)001:16390: shar ba'i phyir lam sbyang bgrod kyi tshul mdzad la
NK116(le)001:16391: kyang / / sprul pa byung bas sprul gzhi 'gags par mi 'gyur te /
NK116(le)001:16392: mkha' zla dang chu zla ji bzhin no //
NK116(le)001:16393: gnyis pa ni de phyir zhes bya ba la sogs pas bstan te /
NK116(le)001:16394: don de'i phyir gzhung 'di la legas para bashada pa'i
NK116(le)001:16395: cha gang yod bla ma'i byin rlabsa snying la 'phos
NK116(le)001:16396: pa'i sgom byung shes raba kyi stobs lasa //
NK116(le)001:16397: thosa bsam rtog ge'i riga pa 'ba' zhig la byas
NK116(le)001:16398: te dgag sgrubs kyis ha cang ma bskyed pasa na
NK116(le)001:16399: / ranga ranga gi 'doda gzhung phyogsa dang mthun las
NK116(le)001:16400: che la gal te 'agla na'ang ri bo khab mig
NK116(le)001:16401: tu mi tshud pa chos nyid yin ga shis khong
NK116(le)001:16402: mi 'khrugs par ma zad gus dang brtse ba'i tshul
NK116(le)001:16406: chos tshul zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:16408: chosa kyi tshul rgya mtsho lta bu gting dapaga shin
NK116(le)001:16409: tu dka' ba'i dona gang zhig mnyam para bazhaga pa
NK116(le)001:16410: kho na'i khyad chosa kyi mthu 'ba' zhig gis dpog
NK116(le)001:16411: par 'gyur ba lasa gzhan gyis ma yin no //
NK116(le)001:16412: de'i phyir ji ltar ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shesa
NK116(le)001:16413: kyi gansa yang dag par mthong ba la nam yanga
NK116(le)001:16414: bslu ba meda pa yin no //
NK116(le)001:16415: bzhi pa dge ba ces bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK116(le)001:16416: mdo dang sngags kyi gzhung lugs thams cad kyi gnad
NK116(le)001:16417: gcig tu bsdus te legasapara sbyar ba'i dge ba 'di
NK116(le)001:16418: yisa bstan bcos byed pa po badga dang ma gyur
NK116(le)001:16419: semas cana rnams / rgyal ba'i ringa lugsa nora ba meda pa yang dag pa'i lam bzang /
NK116(le)001:16420: sgrib pa gnyis kyi rnyogsa pa dwangsa pa'i gru gzengsa
NK116(le)001:16421: lta bu la zhugsa nas srid pa'i chu mtsho las
NK116(le)001:16422: bsgral te byang chub zhi ba rina po che'i gling
NK116(le)001:16424: de srid du dben pa'i nagas mthonga ri dwagsa sna tshogs dkyu pa'i sman ljongsa na /
NK116(le)001:16425: dus bzhi'i mngona rtogsa ngomas pa'i shing ljona pa rnams kyis ni /
NK116(le)001:16426: bsam gtan la mnyam par 'jog pa'i drang srong rnams la mi snyan pa sgrogsa par mi byed cing /
NK116(le)001:16427: gzugs sdug cing skad snying la 'abba par smra ba'i
NK116(le)001:16428: bya tshogas rnams kyang ji ltar sbrul gduga dkri ba'i
NK116(le)001:16430: skyo ba'i ngesa 'byung chen po'i shing rtas yida dbang 'dren pa'i /
NK116(le)001:16431: ca co shina tu zhi ba sgrog par 'gyur la
NK116(le)001:16432: de thos nasa kyang ting 'dzin gyi grogs su gyur
NK116(le)001:16433: te / tshogs drug gi dabnga po nye bar zhi ba dam pa'i dpal thob par shog cig /
NK116(le)001:16434: de yang spros bral gyi lta ba yida byed kyi
NK116(le)001:16435: rlung gis ma dkruga la spyod pa rgyal sras dama
NK116(le)001:16437: nama du yanga gazhana gyi sman du gyur ba las
NK116(le)001:16438: 'tshe ba'i khur du mi 'gro zhing rlabsa chena phrin
NK116(le)001:16439: lasa 'gro ba srid do cog gi dapala du 'gyur
NK116(le)001:16441: yona tan rina po che'i mdzoda dga' ba'i char zhesa
NK116(le)001:16442: bya ba gtsang la stod kyi chos rje brag phuga
NK116(le)001:16443: pasa bskul ba'i ngora rgyal ba 'od mtshan stong du
NK116(le)001:16444: 'bar ba rdzus skyes kyi zlos gar bzung ste 'ja'
NK116(le)001:16445: lus 'pho chen gyi go 'phang bsgrub pa /
NK116(le)001:16446: dpal o brgyan gyi slob dpon chen po sangsa rgyas
NK116(le)001:16447: gnyis pa pad+ma sama b+ha wa'i zhabsa rdul la spyi
NK116(le)001:16448: bosa rega pa'i 'bangs rdzogas chena pa ranga byung don
NK116(le)001:16449: gyi rdo rjesa 'dus ma byas dbyings mngon sum du
NK116(le)001:16450: gzigs te // mkhyen pa dang brtse ba'i 'oda zera
NK116(le)001:16451: gyi snang bas 'khor 'das yongs la khyab par byed
NK116(le)001:16452: pa pos sa gsum gyi dge legs kyi dapala dang
NK116(le)001:16453: ldan pa pad+ma 'oda kyi gling du sbyar ba yongs
NK116(le)001:16454: gzigs te // su rdzogs so // zhes gsungs so //
NK116(le)001:16455: bskal bzang rnam 'dren dgu brgya dgu bcu dgu'i //
NK116(le)001:16456: rgyu skar dbus na ga bur dbang po bzhin //
NK116(le)001:16457: phyogs bcu kun tu chos snang 'byed mkhas pa //
NK116(le)001:16458: zas gtsang sras kyi bstan pa mdzes pa'i rgyan /
NK116(le)001:16459: 1 kun mkhyen ye shes na kra'i grong khyer du //
NK116(le)001:16460: phul byung mos gus ri bo bsgril ba las //
NK116(le)001:16461: sngon med chos mdzod nyi zla'i snang ba che //
NK116(le)001:16462: thob 'di la stod chos rje 'jug bcu'i mthu /
NK116(le)001:16464: 2 / de lta na'ang dbus gtsang shar ri'i phrag /
NK116(le)001:16465: snying stobs rmad byung btsan po'i skya rings kyis //
NK116(le)001:16466: nyer bsus mdo khams skye dgus yid mun dpungs //
NK116(le)001:16467: cig car bcom byed khyab ba dag grub dbang nyi /
NK116(le)001:16469: 3 / gang gi bka' drin 'khor ba med pa'i lan //
NK116(le)001:16470: gzhan du ma rnyed rnam dpyod na phra yang //
NK116(le)001:16471: dge ba gsum dang 'brel ba'i legs bshad tika /
NK116(le)001:16472: brtsam 'dis gtan gyis skyabs khyod mnyes gyur cig 4 /
NK116(le)001:16473: mtshan gyis ngan song grol ba'i rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK116(le)001:16474: rin chen gtsug tor mi yi zol 'dzin pa //
NK116(le)001:16475: gang gi zhabs sen 'od bkrag ma ku ra //
NK116(le)001:16476: lus can dbang phyug thod du rtag brtan shog 5 /
NK116(le)001:16477: sa gsum 'gro ba'i yid dbang ba ku la //
NK116(le)001:16478: rgyal ba'i byin rlabs sgegs mo'i 'gram chang gis //
NK116(le)001:16479: rnam par grol te thams cad mkhyen pa'i bar //
NK116(le)001:16480: nam yang zum pa'i go skabs dben gyur cig 6 /
NK116(le)001:16481: bdag kyang deng nas tshe rabs thams cad du //
NK116(le)001:16482: shes rab rnam gsum shing rta'i blar zhon nas //
NK116(le)001:16483: dus gsum rgyal kun gshegs pa'i lam bzang 'dir //
NK116(le)001:16484: bgrod pa'i 'gros stobs rtsal myur barlinga gyur cig 7 /
NK116(le)001:16485: de srid gzhung lugs sgo brgya cig car du //
NK116(le)001:16486: phye ba'i rnam dpyod zab mo'i sde mig gang //
NK116(le)001:16487: yab cig 'jam mgon bla mas pha phog tu //
NK116(le)001:16488: stsol la thugs rjes 'jug pa g.yel ma gyur /
NK116(le)001:16490: 8 / rgyal gsum rdo rje'i re kha snying bris pa'i //
NK116(le)001:16491: snang srid dregs pa'i tshogs rnams dus sprin bzhin //
NK116(le)001:16492: 'khrigs nas legs tshogs gru char 'gro khams la //
NK116(le)001:16493: phabs te phan bde'i nyal 'gro 'phyur gyur cig 9 /
NK116(le)001:16494: khyad par gsang chen bstan pa'i bya ra ba //
NK116(le)001:16495: spyan gcig khrag rlabs g.yo ba'i ma mo dang //
NK116(le)001:16496: 'dren byed stong phrag 'bar ba r+aa hu las //
NK116(le)001:16497: bstan pa'i yangs bcud mdzod 'di'i gnyer gyi shig 10 /
NK116(le)001:16498: rdzogs chen pa'i 'bangs sog po bstan dar pas sbyar ba dge bar gyur cig //
NK116(le)001:16500: stobs bcu mi 'jigs bzhi dang ma 'dres chos //
NK116(le)001:16501: yongs rdzogs lha mi'i ston pa mchog de nyid //
NK116(le)001:16502: gdul bya'i mos ngor rgyal sras rdzur bzhugs pa //
NK116(le)001:16503: mi yi seng ge mkhyen brtse'i 'od stong 'bar //
NK116(le)001:16504: mnyam bzhag rgyal kun thugs kyidagongasa pa'i bcud //
NK116(le)001:16505: rjes thob ming tshig yi ge'i ris su brgyud //
NK116(le)001:16506: skal ldan rig 'dzin rna bar legs sgrogs pa //
NK116(le)001:16507: brgyud gsum thugs kyi thig le yon tan mdzod //
NK116(le)001:16508: de 'grel rgyas bsdus mtshams shing tshig don legs //
NK116(le)001:16509: 'chos skyobs yon tan tshang ba drang srong gtam //
NK116(le)001:16510: mkhas grub bla ma rnams kyis basngagasa pa 'di //
NK116(le)001:16511: rdzogs chen yongs 'dzin bstan dar zhes pas mdzad //
NK116(le)001:16512: 'di nyid bstan 'dzin bzang pos yon sbyar te //
NK116(le)001:16513: dpal ldan sbyin pa bzang po'i mtshan can gyis //
NK116(le)001:16514: dad gsum rnam pa dkar po'i rgyu las byung //
NK116(le)001:16515: dge ba 'di yis snying po'i bstan pa dang //
NK116(le)001:16516: bstan 'dzin tshogs rnams bskal brgyar zhabs brtan cing //
NK116(le)001:16517: theg mchog chos kyis sa gsum rtag khyab shog /
NK116(le)001:16518: de mthus bskal pa bzang po 'jig rten 'dir //
NK116(le)001:16519: rmad byung rdzogs ldan gsar ba'i snod bcud kyi //
NK116(le)001:16520: yon tan rgyas shing dge bcu yang dag ltas //
NK116(le)001:16521: 'da' zhing 'gro kun mngon par byang chub shog /
NK116(le)001:16522: bkra shis rtsa gsum srung ma'i nyin byed gzis //
NK116(le)001:16523: bkra shis phan bde dga' tshal rab rgyas shing //
NK116(le)001:16524: bkra shis rkang drug bde ba'i ro myong nas //
NK116(le)001:16525: bkra shis dge legs 'bum gyi dbyangs sgrogs shog /
